NK024(ya)001:1: // mu ts+tsha s+au tra s+y+aa b+hi shi ny+tsa s+y+ao pa
NK024(ya)001:2: yi ka pra b+y+au gri nya ma n+da la sa
NK024(ya)001:3: mu dra de sha ba ta ra n+aa ma bi
NK024(ya)001:4: ha ram /// /'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga
NK024(ya)001:5: khrigs su byas pa dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs
NK024(ya)001:7: mnyam pa'i brit+ta las stag rnam len zhes bya ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8: sdeb sbyor ///+aa d+yo bee d+hu ma h+aa su kham
NK024(ya)001:9: sa ma ka shu d+d+ho d+ha rma k+aa yam bu
NK024(ya)001:10: d+d+ha /// gdod ma'i ngo bo mnyam nyid khyab brdal
NK024(ya)001:11: ka dag bde ba chen po chos kyi sku ru
NK024(ya)001:12: d+d+ha /// sangs rgyas kyang /// /+aa dwee ni t+ya
NK024(ya)001:13: ka m+aa ya ma n+da la sa mu dram k+aa
NK024(ya)001:14: ya sa m+b+ho ga ta ma ////
NK024(ya)001:15: zung 'jug rang bzhin lhun grub sgyu 'phrul gar mdzad
NK024(ya)001:16: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17: sku //// kri t+y+aam k+aa ru na nee rma k+aa ya d+ha ra mi tra shel badz+r+aa tsa r+yam ////
NK024(ya)001:18: gdul bya'i snang ngor thugs rje sprul pa'i skur ston
NK024(ya)001:19: zhing 'dir bshes gnyen tshul 'dzin rdo rje'i slob dpon
NK024(ya)001:20: mchog /// sh+r+ai m+aam n+aa gu ru b+aa ra sh+aa
NK024(ya)001:21: su su ma tee bo d+hee mi tram k+aa r+ya
NK024(ya)001:22: mchog /// h+ai / rnam 'dren dpal ldan bla ma
NK024(ya)001:23: nyang ston blo gros mchog gi rdo rje byang chub
NK024(ya)001:25: don dam chos dbyings rtog pa kun bral mngon byang
NK024(ya)001:26: rdo rje'i sku brnyes rang don mthar phyin nas //'gro
NK024(ya)001:27: la rjes chags snying rje'i rang gzugs rgyal dgongs brda
NK024(ya)001:28: dang snyan brgyud rig 'dzin bla ma mchog /
NK024(ya)001:29: gang 'dul mos blor 'tshams pa'i mkhas grub ngur smrig tshul 'dzin la la gos dkar lcang lo can //
NK024(ya)001:30: rgya bod pan grub brgyud par bcas pa'i zhabs sen bdag gi spyi bor rtag tu mchod cing bstod //
NK024(ya)001:31: bsil ldan ljongs kyi bsod nams ra bar rgyal rnams ye shes sa bon dus smin pas //
NK024(ya)001:32: thugs rje'i grib bsil rgya che'i ljon shing mkhyen brtse'i 'dab rgyas yon tan 'bras bus phyug /
NK024(ya)001:33: yongs rdzogs bstan pa'i mnga' bdag bskal bzang 'dren pa rgyal bo'i dbang po thams cad mkhyen //
NK024(ya)001:34: rigs brgya'i khyab bdag kun bzang rdo rje 'chang dngos ngag dbang blo bzang rgya mtshor 'dud //
NK024(ya)001:35: khyad par khyab bdag he ru ka dngos gos dkar 'dzin pa'i zol bsten pa //
NK024(ya)001:36: zur chen dngos slob rim par byon dang 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan rje //
NK024(ya)001:37: de sras 'khor lo'i dbang phyug mkhas grub legs ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje'i zhabs //
NK024(ya)001:38: mdo dbang la sogs snga 'gyur bka' gter bstan pa'i srog shing 'dzin rnams rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:39: thun mong gdul byar mchog gi sprul skus nyan rang byang sems theg /
NK024(ya)001:40: lnga ldan longs skus gsang sngags phyi rgyud bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:41: chos sku kun bzang rdo rje 'chang gis rgyud lung man ngag ste //
NK024(ya)001:42: rigs can snang ngor theg dgu'i lam ston dkyil 'khor lha tshogs bstod //
NK024(ya)001:43: rnam dag dri med theg dgu'i lam srol gad+g+aa'i rgyun //
NK024(ya)001:44: rab 'byams mdo rgyud tshangs pa'i ral par legs 'khyil ba //
NK024(ya)001:45: gdul byar 'dren mkhas snga 'gyur skal ldan shing rta yi //
NK024(ya)001:46: bstan pa rin chen dbang gi rgyal por gus phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:47: rgya chen rgyal bstan 'o ma'i rgya mtsho yi //
NK024(ya)001:48: snying po snga 'gyur ring lugs mar gyi bcud //
NK024(ya)001:49: bka' gter dag snang ro bad'i zil da ngar can //
NK024(ya)001:50: blo gsal skal ldan skye rgu'i bsod nams dpyid //
NK024(ya)001:51: khyad par dgongs pa rig 'dzin snyan brgyud pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:52: rnam dag bka' ma'i gzhung lugs rta bdun dbang //
NK024(ya)001:53: thub bstan shar ri'i phrag par legs shar bas //
NK024(ya)001:54: bstan 'dzin blo ldan du ma'i pad tshal bzhad //
NK024(ya)001:55: smin grol lam gyis rgyud sbyangs rin chen khams //
NK024(ya)001:56: grub pa'i mkha' la spyod pa'i rdo rje 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:57: rig 'dzin rgyu skar bye ba'i gral bsnyeg pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:58: me khyer bdag 'dra'i blo gros ches phra yang //
NK024(ya)001:59: mngon mtho'i rgyu las dal 'byor 'bras thob cing //
NK024(ya)001:60: bshes gnyen yongs 'dzin rgya mtshos rjes su bzung //'khrul med snga 'gyur bstan pa'i sgor zhugs te //
NK024(ya)001:61: sdom gsum lam la 'jug pa'i skal bzang thob //
NK024(ya)001:62: khyad par 'jam mgon bla ma thams cad mkhyen //
NK024(ya)001:63: ngag gi dbang phyug blo bzang rgya mtsho'i sdes //
NK024(ya)001:64: skye dang skye bar rjes bzung drin gyis bskyangs //'chad rtsod rtsom la mi 'jigs gnang ba sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:65: rnam mang lam gyi bgrod pa gcig pu'i phul //'dus pa mdo dbang rin chen them skas kyi //
NK024(ya)001:66: dbang gi cho ga 'thor ba kun bsdebs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:67: lam stegs khrigs su legs par gyis zhes gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:68: gang gsung bdud rtsi'i zegs mas kha 'byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:69: kho bo'i blo gros ba k+au la'i me tog /
NK024(ya)001:70: gtsug phud can gyi rna bar 'brug sgra bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:71: dga' spro'i mgrin bteg gus pa'i gar gyis brel //
NK024(ya)001:72: lhag par ye shes gzigs pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:73: thugs rje'i zla ba blo mtshor gsal byas pas //
NK024(ya)001:74: mi shes mun pa'i snang ba bcom pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:75: lhan cig shes bya'i blo gros rgya cher 'phel //
NK024(ya)001:76: de phyir rigs kyi khyab bdag bla ma'i bka'//
NK024(ya)001:77: spyi bor mdzes pa'i rgyan du legs bcings nas //
NK024(ya)001:78: rtsom pa'i tshul 'dir 'bad pas 'jug pa la //
NK024(ya)001:79: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gros byin gyis rlobs //
NK024(ya)001:80: brgyud ldan dam tshig rdo rje'i bka' nyan pa //
NK024(ya)001:81: dpal ldan ye shes mgon po legs ldan nag /
NK024(ya)001:82: lcam dral pho nyar bcas pas bka' 'grol zhing //
NK024(ya)001:83: bar chod zhi nas kun tu dge bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:85: dka' thub rig byed dbang sgyur thabs //
NK024(ya)001:87: bshad rgyud dgongs pa 'dus las gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:88: snga 'gyur bka' ma mdo sgyu sems //
NK024(ya)001:89: kun 'dus khyad par mdo yi phyogs //
NK024(ya)001:90: brgyud srol zur lugs kahthoga lugs //
NK024(ya)001:91: thun min thun mong gnyis su grags //'dir ni thun mong ma yin pa //
NK024(ya)001:92: zur hwam sh+aaka 'byung phyag len bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:93: dngos slob bde legs gsung rjes 'brangs //
NK024(ya)001:94: gsal byed cho ga khrigs su bya //
NK024(ya)001:95: snyigs ma'i gdul bya blo gros zhan //
NK024(ya)001:96: rgyud lung gab dkrugs don mi shes //
NK024(ya)001:97: rang bzo'i dri mas spags pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:98: blo dman rnams kyi don du'o //
NK024(ya)001:99: gang las byung ba'i brgyud pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:100: de las byung ba'i gdams ngag dngos //
NK024(ya)001:101: mtha' rten gtad rgya'i bar tshang ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:102: spyi don rnam pa gsum gyis bsdus //
NK024(ya)001:103: zab zab mdo sngags chu klung kun 'dus shing //
NK024(ya)001:104: legs legs brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes nor bus gtams //
NK024(ya)001:105: lhod lhod legs bshad rlabs phreng gis brgyan pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:106: gsal gsal dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs 'dri //
NK024(ya)001:107: rnam mang mdo rgyud rgya mtsho ma brgal yang //
NK024(ya)001:108: rnam dag yongs 'dzin ded dpon nyer bsten nas //
NK024(ya)001:109: rnam grol mdo dbang rin chen legs nos na //
NK024(ya)001:110: rnam kun dngos grub yid bzhin 'dod rgur 'jo //
NK024(ya)001:111: thub bstan yongs rdzogs lus brjid gnyis 'thung dbang //
NK024(ya)001:112: dbang bskur rgya mtsho'i rin chen rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:113: mdzes ldan lung rigs nor bu'i khur ldan mchog /
NK024(ya)001:114: mchog gyur bstan bcos glang po che 'di rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:115: dgos don rin chen btso sbyangs las grub bsdus don lte ba zlum por 'khyil //
NK024(ya)001:116: tshig don ma 'dres gsal rdzogs rtsibs la mtshams sbyor mu khyud kun nas mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:117: brgal lan lung rigs rno ngar ldan pas log rtog phyogs las rnam rgyal ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:118: mdo dbang chos kyi 'khor lo che 'di tshul bzhin legs par 'dir bshad bya //
NK024(ya)001:119: gzhan du lung khungs sa bcad rgya tshos kyis //
NK024(ya)001:120: rnam par phye ste lung dngos ser 'byed kyang //'dir ni rtsa ba rin chen phreng ba nyid //
NK024(ya)001:121: mi nyams rtogs par sla bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:122: dmar pos bsnan te sa bcad lung khungs rnams //
NK024(ya)001:123: sngon pos rab phye lung rnams rgya tshos kyis //
NK024(ya)001:124: bsnan te gsar du sgrigs rnams dkyus nyid la //
NK024(ya)001:125: ser mas phye ba de bzhin shes par bya //
NK024(ya)001:126: de la 'dir gsang sngags snga 'gyur bka' ma'i gzhung
NK024(ya)001:127: lugs dri ma med pa mdo sde dang rgyud sde
NK024(ya)001:128: zab mo thams cad kyi lam tshang la ma nor
NK024(ya)001:129: bar ston pa'i 'jug sgo'i srol chen por gyur pas
NK024(ya)001:131: smin par byed pa'i phyir dbang zhes yongs su grags
NK024(ya)001:132: pa 'di nyid kyi cho ga khrigs su bya ba
NK024(ya)001:134: yid ches shing khungs btsun par bya ba'i phyir gang las byung ba'i brgyud pa bshad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:135: gdul bya rnams lam du 'jug pa'i phyir brgyud pa
NK024(ya)001:136: de las byung ba'i man ngag dngos 'chad pa dang
NK024(ya)001:137: / bka' srol mi nub par bya ba'i phyir mtha' rten gtad rgya bya ba ste don gsum mo //
NK024(ya)001:139: bla ma brgyud pa'i tshul bshad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:140: brgyud pa'i bla ma de rnams kyi lo rgyus rtogs brjod rnam thar bshad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:142: spyi mdo dbang lugs kyi theg pa'i bab tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:143: bye brag yo ga gsum gyi brgyud tshul lo //
NK024(ya)001:145: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa des /
NK024(ya)001:146: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi
NK024(ya)001:147: stong gi gnyen por dam pa'i chos kyi sgo'am tshul
NK024(ya)001:148: brgyad khri bzhi stong bka' stsal pa de dag spyir
NK024(ya)001:149: sde snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhir yongs su grags
NK024(ya)001:150: la / snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa'i bzhed srol
NK024(ya)001:151: la gdul bya'i lam gyi 'jug tshul gyi dbang gis
NK024(ya)001:152: theg pa rim pa dgur dbye ba las /
NK024(ya)001:153: de rnams dbang gi chu bo chen po bzhi'i tshul
NK024(ya)001:154: gyis snod ldan gyi slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:155: rim pa ste / dbang don bsdus pa las /
NK024(ya)001:156: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK024(ya)001:157: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK024(ya)001:158: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK024(ya)001:159: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK024(ya)001:160: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK024(ya)001:161: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK024(ya)001:162: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga ni //
NK024(ya)001:163: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK024(ya)001:164: zhes phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bcu la nang gses dbye na brgya dang rtsa brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:165: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig la nang gses dbye na drug brgya dang drug /
NK024(ya)001:166: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bcu gsum la nang gses dbye na brgya dang bco lnga /
NK024(ya)001:167: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis po la nang
NK024(ya)001:168: gses med pas kun dril rnam grangs brgyad brgya dang
NK024(ya)001:170: de lta bu'i dbang gi chu bo babs tshul la
NK024(ya)001:171: bshad thabs kyi rnam grangs mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig
NK024(ya)001:172: yod kyang 'dir 'dus pa mdo'i lugs kyi theg dgu'i
NK024(ya)001:173: dbang gi chu bo babs tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:174: nyan thos kyi theg pa chu bo nee rany+dza na /
NK024(ya)001:175: rang rgyal gyi theg pa kun dga' ra ba /
NK024(ya)001:176: byang sems kyi theg pa bya rgod phung po'i ri bo ste rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum /
NK024(ya)001:177: kri ya bya rgyud kyi theg pa yul wa ra n+aa si /
NK024(ya)001:178: u pa ya spyod rgyud kyi theg pa ri rab kyi rtse /
NK024(ya)001:179: yo ga rnal 'byor rgyud kyi theg pa me ri 'bar ba ste phyi rgyud sde gsum /
NK024(ya)001:180: bskyed pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga pha rgyud rnal
NK024(ya)001:181: 'byor chen po'i theg pa chos rgyal dzah'i pho brang
NK024(ya)001:182: steng / lung rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ma
NK024(ya)001:183: rgyud shin tu rnal 'byor gyi theg pa dur khrod
NK024(ya)001:184: steng / bsil ba'i tshal / man ngag rdzogs pa
NK024(ya)001:185: chen po a ti yo ga gnyis med rgyud rjes
NK024(ya)001:186: su rnal 'byor gyi theg pa d+ha na ko sha'i
NK024(ya)001:187: gling du babs pa ste nang rgyud sde gsum mo
NK024(ya)001:188: //'di rnams la dbang gzhung du 'gag drug ces kyang
NK024(ya)001:189: steng / bsil ba'i tshal / bshad / de'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:190: nye brgyud ltar na slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes
NK024(ya)001:191: rgyal po d+ha he na'i bu mo rin chen gsal
NK024(ya)001:192: sgron phyag rgya khrid nas d+ha na ko sha'i gling
NK024(ya)001:194: rdo rje sems dpa' dang gsang ba'i bdag po dngos
NK024(ya)001:195: su byon nas dbang gi chu bo bzhi po rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:196: par bskur zhing rtog tshogs lha dang ye shes su
NK024(ya)001:197: ngo sprad / dbang rtags chags shing dang me long byin pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:199: o rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu //
NK024(ya)001:200: rdor sems sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje dang //
NK024(ya)001:201: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron la //
NK024(ya)001:202: rdor sems gsang ba'i bdag po dngos byon nas //
NK024(ya)001:203: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtog tshogs lha ngo 'phrod //
NK024(ya)001:204: dbang rtags chags shing me long rnam gnyis byin //
NK024(ya)001:205: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK024(ya)001:207: ring brgyud ltar na dga' rab rdo rje yab yum
NK024(ya)001:208: gnyis kyi zla gam 'od 'phro seng ge nags steng
NK024(ya)001:209: gi tshal du slob dpon ging ka ra la rtsal
NK024(ya)001:210: chen gyi dbang zhes pa phar phyin nyi shu'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:211: nos / pad+ma me tog ljon shing gi tshal du
NK024(ya)001:212: klu sgrub tsan+di ka la kri ya'i mchog dbang nyer
NK024(ya)001:213: nos / drug nos / lha bya skad snyan ljon
NK024(ya)001:214: shing tshal du slob dpon pad+ma ku ma ti la
NK024(ya)001:215: yo ga bkra shis drug cu'i dbang nos /
NK024(ya)001:216: slob dpon chen po rab tu gsal ba zhes gsang
NK024(ya)001:217: sngags rgyud sde thams cad kyi bka' babs pa de
NK024(ya)001:218: la rgyud lung man ngag thams cad kyi dbang gi
NK024(ya)001:219: bka' yongs su rdzogs par nos te /
NK024(ya)001:220: slob dpon des dga' rab rdo rje'am ro langs bde
NK024(ya)001:221: ba la dbang rtags su shes gyi chags shing rin
NK024(ya)001:222: po che sna lngas brgyan pa byin /
NK024(ya)001:223: rin chen gsal sgron la snang srid kyi me long 'dzam gling dus gcig tu gsal ba sbyin no //
NK024(ya)001:224: de ltar dga' rab rdo rje yab yum gyis slar
NK024(ya)001:225: yang rin chen g.yu sdings tshal du byon pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:226: / rgyal po d+ha rma ka ya dang klu'i bu
NK024(ya)001:227: mo rgya mtsho gnyis kyis o rgyan gyi yul nas
NK024(ya)001:228: slob ma bsdus te m+aa ra ti ka'i brag phug
NK024(ya)001:229: tu dga' rab rdo rje spyan drangs te dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:230: zhing tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor du bsgrubs pas
NK024(ya)001:231: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas so //
NK024(ya)001:232: des za hor rgyal po la /
NK024(ya)001:233: des sing+ha la'i rgyal po la /
NK024(ya)001:234: des dge slong so kya de ba la /
NK024(ya)001:235: des slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rje zhes gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal la /
NK024(ya)001:236: des chos blon de ba la /
NK024(ya)001:237: des mkhan po chos rgyal skyong la /
NK024(ya)001:238: de thams cad yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:239: dang dgongs pa mnyam zhing ye shes lhas mngon sum
NK024(ya)001:240: du dbang bskur ba sangs rgyas rnams dang bka' bgro
NK024(ya)001:241: zhing da lta yang rig 'dzin gyi gral na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:243: mkhan po chos rgyal skyong gis gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:244: de man chad 'og tu gsal lo //
NK024(ya)001:245: de ltar theg rim dgu po thams cad bsdu na yo ga gsum du rdzogs shing 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:246: gnyis pa bye brag yo ga gsum gyi brgyud tshul
NK024(ya)001:247: la gsum gyi dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud
NK024(ya)001:248: pa ni / chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK024(ya)001:252: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:253: rgyal po dzah rgyal po sha tra pu tri /
NK024(ya)001:254: rgyan rgyal po sing+ha r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:255: rgyal po u pa r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:256: sras mo go ma de w+ai /
NK024(ya)001:259: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK024(ya)001:260: slob dpon nyid byed seng ge /
NK024(ya)001:261: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:263: dge slong so kya de wa /
NK024(ya)001:264: slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:267: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che'o //
NK024(ya)001:268: gnyis pa gtso che ba lung a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:270: longs sku zhi khro rigs lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:271: lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar /
NK024(ya)001:274: phyag na rdo rje ste rgyal ba dgongs brgyud /
NK024(ya)001:275: brda brgyud dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga ni /
NK024(ya)001:278: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK024(ya)001:280: mi li tsa byi dri med grags pa ste lnga'o //
NK024(ya)001:281: snyan brgyud ni skal ldan rgyal po dzah slob dpon u pa r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:283: klu rgyal n+aa ga pu tri /
NK024(ya)001:284: rgyal po gu h+ya pu tri /
NK024(ya)001:286: ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:287: slob dpon ro langs bde ba /
NK024(ya)001:288: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK024(ya)001:289: za hor rgyal po pra hasti /
NK024(ya)001:290: slob dpon sh+aakya seng ge ste o rgyan chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK024(ya)001:291: de dang lhan cig pa'i grogs sh+aakya mi tra dang sh+aakya pra b+ha /
NK024(ya)001:295: +aa tsar+ya bde ba gsal mdzad dam rab tu gsal ba /
NK024(ya)001:298: bal po ba su d+ha ra /
NK024(ya)001:299: rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge /
NK024(ya)001:300: bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes /
NK024(ya)001:301: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:302: gsum pa rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:303: chos sku kun tu bzang po /
NK024(ya)001:305: sdud mdzad phyag na rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:308: rgyal po d+ha na ta lo //
NK024(ya)001:314: slob dpon a k+sho b+h+yah slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:315: smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa m+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:316: smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa m+aa ti /
NK024(ya)001:318: sras mo go ma de wi /
NK024(ya)001:321: slob dpon ma h+aa r+aa dza /
NK024(ya)001:330: dge slong ma kun dga' mo //
NK024(ya)001:332: lo ts+aa ba bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:333: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po /
NK024(ya)001:334: gnyags dz+nya na ku m+aa ra /
NK024(ya)001:335: sog po dpal gyi ye shes /
NK024(ya)001:336: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:337: 'di yan chad la rgya gar gyi pan grub lo
NK024(ya)001:338: ts+aa ba'i brgyud tshul mi 'dra ba du ma byung
NK024(ya)001:339: zhing / sangs rgyas ye shes nas kyang mdo sgyu sems gsum so so'i brgyud lugs mang yang /
NK024(ya)001:340: gtso bor gnubs kyi bu bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:343: 'khor brgya drug cu sogs yod pa las /
NK024(ya)001:344: 'di'i brgyud par gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK024(ya)001:345: sras gnubs ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK024(ya)001:346: de'i sras byang chub rnam gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:347: rgya ston blo gros byang chub /
NK024(ya)001:348: 'di la slob ma tho gar dang zhu bsod gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:349: tho gar nam mkha' lde rdo rje dngos grub gter /
NK024(ya)001:350: 'ug bya lung pa bde gshegs zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK024(ya)001:351: de'i slob ma rtse mo bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:353: lta dgongs kyi rtse mo zur chung pa shes rab grags /
NK024(ya)001:354: de'i slob ma skyo ston sh+aaka ye sogs ka ba bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:355: ka ba bzhi ka la gsang bdag sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng ges gsan /
NK024(ya)001:357: sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan /
NK024(ya)001:358: glan nya tshal ba rdo rje 'od /
NK024(ya)001:364: glan ston mkhas mchog bsod nams mgon po /
NK024(ya)001:366: zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aaka 'byung phyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:367: lang gro sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po /
NK024(ya)001:369: mkhas grub tshad ma lha rigs 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan /
NK024(ya)001:370: mkhas grub rgya mtsho'i spyi phud rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po legs ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:371: skyi ston tshe ring dbang po /
NK024(ya)001:372: bla chen bres gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:373: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag sman lung pa chen
NK024(ya)001:374: po blo gros mchog gi rdo rje'am gsang mtshan rig
NK024(ya)001:376: dam pa des bdag lha rigs kyi btsun pa pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:377: phrin las gsang ming rdo rje bdud 'joms rtsal la
NK024(ya)001:378: dbang lung man ngag phyag bzhes gtad rgyar bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:379: stsal lo // yang na gsang bdag sgro phug pa nas /
NK024(ya)001:388: zur sh+aakya sh+r+ai dpal bzang po /
NK024(ya)001:392: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan man 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:393: yang na sh+aakya bshes gnyen nas slob dpon dpal bzang /
NK024(ya)001:395: mnyam med 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan man 'dra'o //
NK024(ya)001:396: gzhan yang zur lugs kyi brgyud srol 'dir gtad rgya
NK024(ya)001:397: gsang mtshan ma dang mthun pa'i brgyud srol khyad par
NK024(ya)001:399: de dang 'brel bar mkhas grub legs ldan rjes mdo
NK024(ya)001:400: yongs rdzogs kyi bla ma la gsol 'debs tshigs bcad
NK024(ya)001:401: ma zhig mdzad pa sogs yod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:402: gtso bor gong bzhin brgyud dgos pa dang yig tshogs la 'jigs te re zhig de tsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:403: gnyis pa brgyud pa'i bla ma de rnams kyi lo
NK024(ya)001:404: rgyus rtogs brjod rnam thar bshad pa ni chos 'di'i
NK024(ya)001:405: rgyab chos su dmigs nas logs su bris yod pas
NK024(ya)001:407: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa gdul bya rnams lam
NK024(ya)001:408: du 'jug pa'i phyir brgyud pa de las byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:409: man ngag dngos 'chad pa la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:413: sems can gyi rgyud la gzhi bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:414: snying po rang chas su yod pa de ji lta
NK024(ya)001:415: ba bzhin ston par byed pa rgyud kyi lam dang
NK024(ya)001:416: / smin byed dbang gi lam gnyis su bzhed pa'i dang po ni /
NK024(ya)001:418: skye med ye shes nyid kyi dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:419: gdod nas bde gshegs snying po la //
NK024(ya)001:420: rnam rtog glo bur las kyis bsgribs //
NK024(ya)001:421: de nyid 'gro mgon skyabs chen yin //
NK024(ya)001:424: thams cad sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK024(ya)001:425: rtog pas bsgribs pas ngo ma shes //
NK024(ya)001:428: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK024(ya)001:429: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK024(ya)001:430: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK024(ya)001:433: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK024(ya)001:434: bstan ni rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK024(ya)001:437: sems can rnams ni sangs rgyas nyid //'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK024(ya)001:439: bde gshegs snying pos 'gro kun yongs la khyab //'gro ba 'di dag thams cad sangs rgyas rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:440: zhes sogs gsar rnying thams cad dgongs pa mthun par
NK024(ya)001:441: gsungs pa'i don sems can gyi sems nyid 'di rtsa
NK024(ya)001:442: ba kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems su gcig pa
NK024(ya)001:443: yin pa la / de ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis bdag las gzhan 'dzin /
NK024(ya)001:445: kun brtags sna tshogs su 'khrul zhing 'khyams so //
NK024(ya)001:446: de lta bu'i rgyu rgyud gtan la 'beb par byed
NK024(ya)001:447: pa la yang grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba dang
NK024(ya)001:448: / bsgyur ba gnyis su grags pa'i snga ma ni gzhung lugs gang la yang mi bsten /
NK024(ya)001:449: bgrod byed kyi lam don du mi gnyer /
NK024(ya)001:450: 'bras bu mtho ris dang thar pa mi 'dod /
NK024(ya)001:451: 'phral gyi bde skyid kho na don du gnyer ba
NK024(ya)001:452: so so skye bo lam la mi 'jug pa ste
NK024(ya)001:454: phyi ma grub mthas blo bsgyur ba la yang nor ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:455: ma nor ba'i lam gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:456: grub mtha' la zhugs kyang nor ba log pa'i lam
NK024(ya)001:457: du gol ba mu stegs byed de rgyu log pa'o
NK024(ya)001:458: // ma nor ba'i lam gyi rim pa ni 'dir
NK024(ya)001:459: gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi lugs srol theg pa bcu
NK024(ya)001:460: gcig ces pa'i rnam grangs 'chad tshul yod de /
NK024(ya)001:461: rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po las /
NK024(ya)001:462: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:463: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:464: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:465: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:466: bla na med pa'i theg pas /
NK024(ya)001:468: 'jig rten lha dang mi'i theg pa ni lam la
NK024(ya)001:469: 'jug pa'i sgo ste bsnyen gnas dang dge bcu mi
NK024(ya)001:470: chos gtsang ma bcu drug sogs kyi sgo nas lam
NK024(ya)001:471: la dkri tshul rgyas par 'og tu cho ga dngos
NK024(ya)001:472: las 'chad do // theg pa rim pa dgu ni /
NK024(ya)001:475: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:477: kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa mtshan nyid sde gsum /
NK024(ya)001:478: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa rgyud sde 'og ma bya spyod rnal 'byor gsum /
NK024(ya)001:479: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa rgyud sde gong ma
NK024(ya)001:480: rnal 'byor chen po gsang sngags bla na med pa
NK024(ya)001:481: pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud dam bskyed pa ma
NK024(ya)001:482: h+aa yo ga thabs kyi rgyud /
NK024(ya)001:483: lung a nu yo ga rdzogs pa shes rab kyi rgyud /
NK024(ya)001:484: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga thabs shes gnyis su med pa gsum du 'dod /
NK024(ya)001:485: de yang cung zhig bshad na /
NK024(ya)001:486: rgya gar gyi slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rje'i bzhed pas /
NK024(ya)001:490: gzhi dbang du byed pa'i gnyen po /
NK024(ya)001:491: gzhi spang blang dang dgag sgrub med pa dang lngar mdzad pa las /
NK024(ya)001:492: nyan rang gnyis ni gzhi spong ba'i gnyen po ste /
NK024(ya)001:493: nyon mongs dug lnga dang dug gsum dgra dang tsher ma ltar spong bas na rgyud dman pa /
NK024(ya)001:494: byang sems kyi theg pa gzhi sbyong ba'i gnyen po
NK024(ya)001:495: ste phar phyin lam lnga sa bcu rim par bgrod
NK024(ya)001:496: pa'i thabs kyis nyon mongs kyi ngo bo rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:497: med par sbyong ba yin na'ang rdo rje theg pa
NK024(ya)001:498: la ltos na rgyu ma tshang bar bshad /
NK024(ya)001:500: gzhi bsgyur ba'i gnyen po ste dug lnga rigs lnga /
NK024(ya)001:501: dug gsum sku gsung thugs su bsgyur nas lam du byed cing bsgom /
NK024(ya)001:502: ma h+aa a nu gnyis gzhi dbang du byed pa'i
NK024(ya)001:503: gnyen po ste nyon mongs rtog tshogs ye shes chen
NK024(ya)001:504: por dbang byed / a ti yo ga ni gzhi spang blang dang dgag sgrub med pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:505: chos thams cad mnyam nyid blo 'das chen po'i ngo
NK024(ya)001:506: bo nyid du rang grol bas bstan pa dang theg
NK024(ya)001:507: pa thams cad kyi yang rtser gyur pa tshang la
NK024(ya)001:508: ma nor ba'i lam yin no //
NK024(ya)001:509: de yang dpes mtshon na bza' shing gi ra bar
NK024(ya)001:510: dug gi sdong po skyes pa la ngo ma shes
NK024(ya)001:511: par 'ga' zhig gis zos nas shi ba la /
NK024(ya)001:512: mkhas pas dug yin par shes nas rtsa ba nas
NK024(ya)001:513: bcad de thag ring por skyel ba lta bu ni
NK024(ya)001:514: nyan rang / de 'dra'i 'bad rtsol mi dgos par
NK024(ya)001:515: thabs mkhas pa'i skyes bus sdong po de nyid du
NK024(ya)001:516: mer bsregs shing rlung la bskur ba lta bu byang
NK024(ya)001:517: nyan rang / sems / de lta bu'i dka' tshegs
NK024(ya)001:518: kyang mi dgos par sngags mkhan gyis ting nge 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:519: dang phyag rgya dang sngags btab ste bzar rung pa
NK024(ya)001:521: de las kyang khyad par du che ba rma byas
NK024(ya)001:522: ngo shes nas zos pas spu sdug mdog legs skad
NK024(ya)001:523: snyan gyi grogs su gyur pa lta bu nang pa
NK024(ya)001:524: rgyud lung gnyis / dug shing skyes pa la dga'
NK024(ya)001:525: sdug med par mnyam pa nyid du blta ba rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:526: pa chen por mtshungs zhes bla ma dag gsung ste
NK024(ya)001:527: rgyud lung gnyis / / de ni rgyu'i lam zhes bya la /
NK024(ya)001:528: gsar mar yang kun gzhi rgyu rgyud la 'khor 'das
NK024(ya)001:529: dbyer med kyi lta ba bsgom zhes bya ba dang
NK024(ya)001:530: mtshungs so // gnyis pa smin byed dbang gi lam ni /
NK024(ya)001:531: de lta bu'i rgyu rgyud sbyang ba'i phyir dbang bskur dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:532: de yang rgyud sde so sor dbang gi sgo mang
NK024(ya)001:533: du gsungs kyang 'dir bstan pa dang theg pa thams
NK024(ya)001:534: cad 'dus pa'i mdo don gcig tu dril ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:535: gi rim pa 'di rtsis 'go lnga'i tshul gyis 'chad
NK024(ya)001:537: rgyud lung gang nas btus pa /
NK024(ya)001:538: mdzad pa po gang gis mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:540: don ched su'i ched du mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:541: dbu zhabs su don ji tsam gyis bsdus pa dang lnga yin pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:542: de la dang po rgyud lung gang nas btus pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:543: rtsa ba'i rgyud rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo /
NK024(ya)001:545: sgyu 'phrul rtsa ba'i rgyud dpal gsang ba snying po /
NK024(ya)001:546: bshad pa'i rgyud dgongs pa 'dus pa /
NK024(ya)001:549: rdo rje me long rnams las btus so //
NK024(ya)001:550: gnyis pa slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:551: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga ltar na pan+di ta chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK024(ya)001:552: pan chen bi ma la mi tra la sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:553: 'dir gtso che ba lung a nu yo ga ltar
NK024(ya)001:554: na 'dus pa mdo'i dbang la mkhas pa rgya gar
NK024(ya)001:555: wa ra n+aa si'i pan+di ta chen po +aa tsar+ya
NK024(ya)001:556: gsal ba'i rgyan zhes bya ba dgung lo stong dang
NK024(ya)001:557: drug brgya lhag tsam lon pa de dang /
NK024(ya)001:560: rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge /
NK024(ya)001:561: bal po ba su d+ha ra sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:562: man ngag a ti ltar na slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:564: o di ya na'i mkhan po chen po dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK024(ya)001:565: rgya gar pan chen mkhas pa nyer lnga sogs kyis
NK024(ya)001:566: dbang gi las tho chen po la sogs pa'i rgya
NK024(ya)001:568: gsum pa phyogs gar gtogs ni /
NK024(ya)001:569: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa a nu yo ga'i phyogs snga 'gyur bka' ma mdo dang /
NK024(ya)001:572: mdo gtso bor ston pa'i zhar la sgyu 'phrul dang sems phyogs kyang ston par byed pa yin no //
NK024(ya)001:574: gdul bya rnams rdo rje theg par dkris te bstan
NK024(ya)001:575: pa yongs rdzogs kyi nyams len la 'jug pa'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:576: du'o // lnga pa dbu zhabs kyi don ni /
NK024(ya)001:577: 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pa'i tshul gyis bsdus te /
NK024(ya)001:581: phyag bzhes byin rlabs las byang dang 'brel dgos pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:582: de la dang po ni gong du bstan pa'i rgyud de rnams dang 'brel lo //
NK024(ya)001:583: gnyis pa ni gdams ngag dbang don chen po'i dbang rin chen 'khor lo //
NK024(ya)001:584: dbang nor bu'i phreng ba'am rin chen phreng ba /
NK024(ya)001:585: dbang mi 'jigs phreng ba'am khro bo las tsar phreng /
NK024(ya)001:586: dbang rin chen skas gdang la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:587: lo ts+aa ba chen po sangs rgyas ye shes rin
NK024(ya)001:588: po che'i bzhed pas drug gsum bco brgyad dang 'brel
NK024(ya)001:589: bar gsungs te / spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi
NK024(ya)001:590: dang //'dren pa'i las byang che le dang //'dren pa'i
NK024(ya)001:592: yongs su grub pa'i dbang le dang //
NK024(ya)001:593: lta ba ye 'byams dbang le dang //
NK024(ya)001:594: kun bzang thugs kyi gdams ngag le //
NK024(ya)001:595: rnam pa drug tu las gnyer gtad //
NK024(ya)001:596: bar du dgos pa'i sgrub thabs drug /
NK024(ya)001:597: dbang don bsdus dang dbang don rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:598: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:599: las tho rab gnas bshags pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:600: gsang sngags byung tshul gleng gzhi dang //
NK024(ya)001:601: drug gis sgrub pa'i don rnams bshad //
NK024(ya)001:602: rgyun du dgos pa'i lag len drug /
NK024(ya)001:603: sbyin sreg lhag chog dkyil 'khor thig /
NK024(ya)001:604: rgyud khungs gtad rgya gleng gzhi drug /
NK024(ya)001:605: drug gsum bco brgyad yi ge 'di //
NK024(ya)001:606: sangs rgyas ye shes bdag gis rnyed //
NK024(ya)001:607: snod ldan rnams dang 'phrad par shog /
NK024(ya)001:609: gsum pa ni rgya bod kyi pan grub rig 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:610: brgyud pa rnams kyi phyag len rnam par dag pa
NK024(ya)001:611: dang bar ma chod par 'brel lo //
NK024(ya)001:612: bzhi pa ni rgyas par gzhung dngos kyi skabs su shes par nus so //
NK024(ya)001:613: bye brag dbang chog khrigs su bgyis pa 'di'i rtsis
NK024(ya)001:614: 'go lnga'i 'chad tshul ni gong du brtsam par dam
NK024(ya)001:615: bca' ba'i skabs su bstan zin to //
NK024(ya)001:616: zhar la rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:617: mdo'i dbang zhes pa'i mtshan don las 'khrul te mdo
NK024(ya)001:618: rang skad la dbang med pa rgyu mtshan du byas
NK024(ya)001:619: nas mdo la dbang bskur ba'i ming 'dogs su mi
NK024(ya)001:620: rung ba dang / gsang sngags la mdo'i ming gis btags pa mi 'thad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:621: mdo la cho ga mi 'byung ba sogs kyi log par rtog pa rnams la 'di skad bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:622: dbang zhes pa sgra yangs pa'i dbang du byas na
NK024(ya)001:623: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba
NK024(ya)001:624: zhes sam rgyal sar dbang bskur ba'i las la brten
NK024(ya)001:625: nas mnga' 'bangs la dbang sgyur nus par bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:626: dang / mdo las 'od zer chen po'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:628: byang chub sems dpa' blo gros chen po la sogs
NK024(ya)001:629: pa dag sangs rgyas thams cad kyi phyag gis dbang
NK024(ya)001:630: bskur bas dbang bskur ba zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:631: byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po dga'
NK024(ya)001:632: ldan nas 'pho ba'i tshe byams pa'i dbu la cod
NK024(ya)001:633: pan bcings te rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ba sogs
NK024(ya)001:634: kyang dbang yin par don gyi 'grub pas nyes pa'i
NK024(ya)001:635: skyon med la / gsang sngags la mdo'i ming gis btags pa la yang klan ka mi 'jug ste /
NK024(ya)001:637: gsang sngags mdo sde'i tshul bzhin ngas bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:640: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i mdo
NK024(ya)001:641: sde'i dbang po zhes gsungs pa'i rnam par bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:644: mdo sde 'di ni mnyan byas nas //
NK024(ya)001:646: rgyud do cog gi rtsa ba ste //
NK024(ya)001:647: zhes gsungs pa yang 'gal ba med par bsgrub dgos pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:648: gzhan yang cho ga zhes sngags rang skad yin no zhe na /
NK024(ya)001:649: de yang sgra rig smra ba dag bying las ming dang /
NK024(ya)001:650: ming las tshig bsgrub pa'i cho ga zhes grags shing /
NK024(ya)001:651: 'dul bar sngon chog dang da chog gi tha snyad
NK024(ya)001:652: gsungs pa sogs yod pa'i phyir shes bya'i gnas la
NK024(ya)001:653: mtha' rgya chod na log par rtog pa las grol
NK024(ya)001:654: bar 'gyur ro //'o na gsang sngags bla med kyi
NK024(ya)001:655: dkyil 'khor gcig tu dbang bskur rigs pa la /
NK024(ya)001:656: theg pa rim dgu so sor mthar chags su ston pa ci yin zhe na dgos pa yod de /
NK024(ya)001:658: sems can dang po'i las can rnams //
NK024(ya)001:659: dam pa'i don la 'jug pa la //
NK024(ya)001:660: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK024(ya)001:661: skas kyi rim pa lta bur gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:664: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:665: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK024(ya)001:666: mdo sde pa yang de bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:667: de rjes rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK024(ya)001:668: de yi rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK024(ya)001:669: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK024(ya)001:670: de rjes kye yi rdo rje brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:672: dri med rgya bod brgyud pa'i pan grub phreng //
NK024(ya)001:673: rin chen mu tig m+aa la ltar spel ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:674: ngo mtshar gtam gyi do shal gsar pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:675: snga 'gyur bstan dang de 'dzin mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:676: rnam dag mdo sngags rin chen 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:677: zab don gting mtha' bsam yas klong chen por //
NK024(ya)001:678: legs bshad rlabs phreng kun nas nyer mdzes pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:679: smin byed dbang gi chu bo 'di na mtshar //
NK024(ya)001:680: log rtog rgyu skar bye ba rnam bkra yang //
NK024(ya)001:681: lung rigs nyin byed snang ba 'di shar bas //
NK024(ya)001:682: rgol ngan 'od ris mtha' dag yongs bcom ste //
NK024(ya)001:683: skal bzang blo gsal pad+ma rnam par rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:684: zhes pa yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////de
NK024(ya)001:685: ltar rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pas spyi don mdor
NK024(ya)001:686: bstan nas / gzhung don dngos la 'jug par bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:687: zur thams cad mkhyen pa'i dngos slob bde legs pas
NK024(ya)001:688: mdzad pa'i mdo dbang chog khrigs rin chen phreng ba'i
NK024(ya)001:689: steng nas dbang bskur gyi phyag len mdzad pa brgyud
NK024(ya)001:690: pa rin po che 'di'i lugs la yod pas /
NK024(ya)001:691: de nyid rtsa bar byas te chog khrigs de'i 'grel
NK024(ya)001:692: ba'i tshul gyis gsal byed legs par 'chad pa la
NK024(ya)001:694: gdod nas rnam dag khyab gdal gnyug ma'i ngang //
NK024(ya)001:695: phyogs dus kun khyab rgyal ba zhi khro'i tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:696: stong gsal 'bras med 'gro la rtag tu bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:697: kun gyi bla ma mchog der gus phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:698: de yi sgrub thabs dbang gi phyag len rnams //
NK024(ya)001:699: rtsa brgyud rig 'dzin bla ma'i gsung bzhin du //
NK024(ya)001:700: rang bzo spangs te du mar 'thor ba rnams //
NK024(ya)001:701: gzhan phan bsam pas phyogs gcig 'dir 'god bya //'dir
NK024(ya)001:702: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i sgrub dbang la don gsum
NK024(ya)001:703: ste / phun sum tshogs pa lnga'am drug gis sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:704: bsnyen sgrub bzhis las kyi gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:705: rjes don brgyad kyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:712: sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:713: dang po ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:715: slob dpon mtshan nyid brtag pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:716: ye shes snying po khyod nyon cig /
NK024(ya)001:717: brtan cing dul la g.yo sgyu med //
NK024(ya)001:718: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor shes pas //
NK024(ya)001:719: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK024(ya)001:720: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK024(ya)001:721: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:722: theg pa che la rtag dga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:723: de ni slob dpon yin par gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:726: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:727: gnyen ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK024(ya)001:730: mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan pa'i bla ma'o //
NK024(ya)001:731: la lar rgya thebs dang gzungs ma yang ston par bsdu bar bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:732: gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:734: zur brgyad la sogs rtse mang dang //
NK024(ya)001:735: chu bo bzhin du ma bo zhing //
NK024(ya)001:736: mnyam zhing 'o ga'i chu ltar dwangs //
NK024(ya)001:737: nyi ma shin tu gnas pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:738: nam mkha'i mtshan nyid shes par bya //
NK024(ya)001:739: mtho dang 'dud pa nub byang yin //
NK024(ya)001:740: shar lho gzhol zhing 'jam pa la //
NK024(ya)001:741: mtho sgro grog po chu sna sogs //
NK024(ya)001:742: dkyil 'khor dbang dgra mtshams brtag bya //
NK024(ya)001:743: lhun stug ri bo nags tshal ldan //
NK024(ya)001:744: rab tu mnyam zhing snum bag can //
NK024(ya)001:745: chu bo dbang gi phyogs yin te //
NK024(ya)001:746: cung zad kyis ni rlung nyung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:747: me tog shing tshal bya skad brtag /
NK024(ya)001:748: lo rgyus shes pa'ang mchog tu gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:751: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing //
NK024(ya)001:752: sa dang bar snang shis pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:753: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:754: yid 'ong sa btsal rgyas par bya //'khor khang phyi nang bar ldan par //
NK024(ya)001:755: rin chen byug pas bsrung ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:756: rin chen spras pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK024(ya)001:757: zhes pas gnas dang khang pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK024(ya)001:758: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:763: sgrub dang sgom la dga' ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:764: rtag tu bla ma la gus shing //
NK024(ya)001:765: dus gsum bla ma mchod byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:766: yon tan dang ldan slob ma yin //
NK024(ya)001:769: thos bsam sgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:770: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis zung //
NK024(ya)001:771: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la brtan //
NK024(ya)001:772: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:773: zhes pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:774: bzhi pa yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:776: yo byad dka' ba kun bsdus nas //
NK024(ya)001:777: khyad par tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:778: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:779: ces pas sku'i rten phyi nang gi tsakli dang /
NK024(ya)001:780: bris sku lugs ma la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:781: gsung gi rten glegs bam dang /
NK024(ya)001:782: thugs kyi rten phyag mtshan du ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:783: dbang gi rdzas bum pa bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:784: sgrub pa'i rdzas ka p+aa la dang /
NK024(ya)001:785: sman raka gtor ma la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:786: mchod pa'i rdzas me tog la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:787: bgegs bzlog pa'i phur bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:790: nad zhi ba'i sman la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:791: dgra rkyen bzlog pa'i go mtshon dang /
NK024(ya)001:792: gzhan yang rnga dang dung dang sil snyan la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:795: yol ba bla bre la sogs pa nye bar mkho ba du ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:796: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:807: rdo rje kun tu rgyu dang /
NK024(ya)001:808: rdo rje ka ta ri la sogs pa dgos pa thams cad sta gon bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:809: de yang bla ma gong ma'i gsung rgyun la /
NK024(ya)001:811: gal phyi ni bra ldum btsos pa /
NK024(ya)001:817: mang sa g.yu mdog khur ba /
NK024(ya)001:820: rdo rje kun tu rgyu tsh+wa /
NK024(ya)001:821: rdo rje ka ta ri sha yin zhes gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:822: gter ma rnams la ngos 'dzin 'di dang cung zad mi 'dra ba'i khyad par yod do //
NK024(ya)001:823: de dag kyang ma 'grub na spogs pa'i phyir lhag thang du bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:824: mdor na de dag kyang tha mal par mi blta ste /
NK024(ya)001:826: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:827: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams kyang //
NK024(ya)001:828: dkyil 'khor yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:829: dngos grub rten dang bar chod bzlog /
NK024(ya)001:830: yo byad dag pa bsdu byas te //
NK024(ya)001:831: tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis brlabs //
NK024(ya)001:833: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:834: ston pa gnas 'khor yo byad de dag 'dzom pa'i dus yin la /
NK024(ya)001:835: bye brag sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus ni /
NK024(ya)001:837: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:838: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:839: byang chub spyod pa cher spyad bya //
NK024(ya)001:840: snga dro'i dus su dkyil 'khor bri //
NK024(ya)001:842: yang na sgrub pa gzung ba'i dus /
NK024(ya)001:844: smin par slob pa dbang du sgrub pa'i dus te gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:845: dang po ni rngam glog gi lung gis shes /
NK024(ya)001:846: gnyis pa ni so thar dang byang sdom thob pa'i dus su yin te /
NK024(ya)001:848: dang po sems bskyed 'jug dus su //
NK024(ya)001:849: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par byin //
NK024(ya)001:853: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK024(ya)001:854: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK024(ya)001:855: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK024(ya)001:857: drug pa sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa ni ston 'khor rnams la ngos bzung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:858: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:860: sgrub pa dang sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK024(ya)001:862: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK024(ya)001:863: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK024(ya)001:865: de ltar don bzhis bstan pa las /
NK024(ya)001:866: spyir na dang po ni dbang thob sa rnon pa'i
NK024(ya)001:867: rdo rje slob dpon la dbang gi zhu ba phul
NK024(ya)001:869: bla ma thugs dam la bzhugs nas sta gon yan chad bsnyen pa /
NK024(ya)001:870: zhag ji tsam byed pa'i phyed nye bsnyen /
NK024(ya)001:871: nub tha ma ma gtogs pa'i dbang du tshogs bzhi tshogs sam drug tshogs su byed pa sgrub pa /
NK024(ya)001:872: nub tha ma la rtags dang mtshan ma bzang po
NK024(ya)001:873: byung nas dngos grub len kha ma sgrub pa chen
NK024(ya)001:878: dang po gzhi'i bsnyen pa ni nges par bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:880: bsnyen pa'i don du sngon bya ba //
NK024(ya)001:881: rdzogs pa'i las rnams zin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:884: gnas mtshan nyid dang ldan par sngon 'gro'i chos rnams rdzogs par byas la /
NK024(ya)001:885: lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med rtogs pa'i ngang
NK024(ya)001:886: las sgom pa don dang yi ge'i rjes su 'jug
NK024(ya)001:887: pas yi dam la brtan pa ma thob kyi bar
NK024(ya)001:888: la bsnyen pa bskyal bar smin pa slob ma'o //
NK024(ya)001:890: de yang 'dus pa mdo dang sgyu 'phrul gyi lugs
NK024(ya)001:891: ltar bla ma'i man ngag gis legs par zin pa'i
NK024(ya)001:892: sgo nas zhi khro dam pa rigs brgya'i bsnyen pa'am
NK024(ya)001:893: / spro na sngon 'gro phyag rdor nas a nu'i
NK024(ya)001:894: bar dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad la grangs bsnyen
NK024(ya)001:895: tsam byung na legs par snang ste /
NK024(ya)001:896: ha cang mang bas sgyid lugs pa'i rgyur 'gyur bas /
NK024(ya)001:897: mdor bsdus na snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi bka' brgyad
NK024(ya)001:898: spyi bka' sgos bka' gang rung zhig la rang rang
NK024(ya)001:899: gi sgrub gzhung ltar bsnyen sgrub mthar phyin pas kyang
NK024(ya)001:901: bde gshegs gcig 'grub kun gyi ngang //
NK024(ya)001:903: gsar ma ba dag kyang bla med gcig la bsnyen pa song na gzhan rnams khyab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:904: bye brag phreng ba mkhan po rnams kyang de ltar du bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:905: gnyis pa mos slob la gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:906: sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:909: dbang bskur ba la 'jug khar bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:910: glan ston bsod nams mgon po'i chog khrigs las /
NK024(ya)001:911: slob bus slob dpon rdo rje rgyal po dbang gi chu bo rdzogs shing /
NK024(ya)001:913: bka' dang rgyu 'bras kyi chos la ma rmongs par mkhyen pa'i bla ma la zhu ba phul la /
NK024(ya)001:914: de nas slob dpon gyis bum pa bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:915: sngon 'gro dngos gzhi mjug gsum du phye la /
NK024(ya)001:916: rang gang mos kyi lha la grangs kyi bsnyen pa ci rigs par bskyal lo //
NK024(ya)001:917: de'i bar du slob bus mdzad byang bzhin du gang
NK024(ya)001:918: dgos pa'i yo byad rnams zhal las byung ba bzhin
NK024(ya)001:919: bsag go // zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:920: 'di gong gi bsnyen pa dang mi 'dra bas nye
NK024(ya)001:921: bsnyen nam dbang gi bsnyen pa zhes sgyu 'phrul ba'i
NK024(ya)001:923: 'dir yang mdo dbang bskur kha lta bur byed dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:924: deng sang sa skya pa rnams lam 'bras kyi dus
NK024(ya)001:925: su yang 'di ltar mdzad pa'i lag len 'dug cing
NK024(ya)001:926: / rtsa bar dang po ni bla mas gong ltar
NK024(ya)001:927: lha grangs kyi bsnyen pa ci 'grub tu bskyal lo
NK024(ya)001:928: / zhes gsungs pas / de yang ji ltar bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:929: slob dpon gyis dben par mtshams bcad de /
NK024(ya)001:930: mdo dbang a nu'i lung gi zhi khro'i phrin las lta bu thun bzhir bya ba'am /
NK024(ya)001:931: yang na rgyud ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i phrin las thun bzhir bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:932: yo byad 'dzom na thun mtshams ji ltar 'os par
NK024(ya)001:933: tshogs chen gyi zhi ba'i bum pa dang khro bo
NK024(ya)001:934: gsang bum gnyis gzhung ltar bsgrub pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:935: slob mas gong du yo byad phun sum tshogs par sgrub pa'i sa bcad skabs ltar gsog pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:936: man+dala yig brgya sogs bsags sbyang gi rnal 'byor la brtson par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:937: mdor na bla ma'i bsnyen dus bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi tshang tshul gong gis shes la /
NK024(ya)001:938: bye brag gi dkyil 'khor so sor yang 'di bzhi don gyis tshang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:939: khyad par rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ma h+aa a nu
NK024(ya)001:940: gnyis la 'di bzhi tshang tshul cho ga'i skabs su
NK024(ya)001:941: shes par bya'o // gnyis pa las kyi rim pa la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:942: bsnyen sgrub kyi skabs su dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba'i las rim dang /
NK024(ya)001:943: sgrub pa chen po'i skabs su dngos grub thob nas dbang gi las rim mo //
NK024(ya)001:946: sa gzhi mnyam dang tshad thig dang //
NK024(ya)001:947: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:948: rab gnas sbyin sreg 'jug pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:949: yon tan rnam bcus rgyas shes bya //
NK024(ya)001:952: dang po sa gzhi yongs su bzung //
NK024(ya)001:953: gnyis pa sta gon la gnas te //
NK024(ya)001:954: nub gsum pa la 'jug par bya //
NK024(ya)001:955: spyi dbang chen po dbang bskur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:956: dang po phun sum tshogs ldan pas //
NK024(ya)001:957: tshad phyin rab 'byams slob dpon gyis //
NK024(ya)001:958: snod dang ldan pa'i 'khor bsdus nas //
NK024(ya)001:959: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NK024(ya)001:960: sa chog rdzogs byas dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK024(ya)001:961: zhes gsungs pa'i dang po sa chog la don brgyad de /
NK024(ya)001:962: sa gzhi spyi mtshan du brtag pa /
NK024(ya)001:969: bzung ba rnams yin pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:970: dang po spyir brtag pa ni gong du gnas phun sum tshogs pa'i skabs su bstan zin /
NK024(ya)001:971: gnyis pa bye brag tu brtag pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:973: thang ka sog le lta bu dang //
NK024(ya)001:974: dma' dang bo ba'i mtshan nyid dang //
NK024(ya)001:975: tsh+wa sgo zug rdo rus spal dang //
NK024(ya)001:976: gram pa thal ba shing sol dang //
NK024(ya)001:977: gyo mo rus pa gseg la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:978: ny+aa gro d+ha dang pa lak+sha //
NK024(ya)001:979: u dum wa ra a shwa t+tha //
NK024(ya)001:980: u rdzu na la sogs pa'i tshul //'dod pa ma yin sbyong spo bya //
NK024(ya)001:982: bkra shis r+ts+wa dang me tog shing //
NK024(ya)001:983: gnag dang kha dog ldan pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:984: rtsigs ma rgyus pa rab nyung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:985: lhag par 'gyur ba rab tu bshad //
NK024(ya)001:986: ces bzang po'i sa brtag go //
NK024(ya)001:987: gsum pa blang ba la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:988: mngon pa mi la blang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:989: mi mngon pa la blang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:990: dang po ni yul de'i rgyal po'am blon po'am sa'i
NK024(ya)001:991: bdag po gang yin la rin bcal zhing ngag gis
NK024(ya)001:992: bden pas blang ba dang sa rgyas btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:993: gnyis pa mi mngon pa la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:994: bde bar gshegs pa sangs rgyas la blang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:995: sa'i lha mo la blang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:997: dang po gnas der man+dala khru gang ba zhig byas
NK024(ya)001:998: la ga bur dang tsan+dana gyi chus chag chag gdab
NK024(ya)001:999: / de'i steng du mchod pa lnga dang dkar gtor gcig /
NK024(ya)001:1001: rang chas gos dkar po dang ldan pas stan la 'dug ste /
NK024(ya)001:1002: zhes gsungs pa'i don rgyas par nyams su blang ba
NK024(ya)001:1003: ni gang du dkyil 'khor bya ba'i sar stegs bu
NK024(ya)001:1004: khru gang gru bzhi pa zhig byas la /
NK024(ya)001:1005: de la ba lang gi lci ba gsar pa dri
NK024(ya)001:1006: bzang pos bgos pa glang ko'i srab 'thug tsam du
NK024(ya)001:1008: de'i steng du ga bur dang tsan+dana gyi chus chag chag gdab dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:1010: shin tu'ang brtags pa'i sa dbus su //
NK024(ya)001:1011: dkyil 'khor lci ba dril byugs la //
NK024(ya)001:1012: mnyam zhing glang ko tsam byas la //
NK024(ya)001:1013: ga bur tsan+dana ldan par bya //
NK024(ya)001:1014: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir stegs bu'i dbus su many+dzi'i khar
NK024(ya)001:1015: man+dala la dri bzang gis byugs pa'i steng sa lha'i
NK024(ya)001:1016: tshom bu bkod pa'i mdun du chu gnyis sngon du
NK024(ya)001:1017: 'gro ba'i mchod pa lnga dang dkar gtor bsham /
NK024(ya)001:1018: gzhan yang gzhi bgegs la dkar gtor dmar gtor /
NK024(ya)001:1019: gser skyems rin po che'i brdar phye dang chos sman 'bru tshoms btab pa rnams kyang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:1020: logs shig tu lcog tse'i khar zhi ba'i gtor ma
NK024(ya)001:1021: dpal bshos pad 'dab bzhi pa dkar dmar rgyan gyis
NK024(ya)001:1022: brgyan pa dang / kun 'dus kyi rtsa gsum gtor ma /
NK024(ya)001:1024: nyer spyod lnga yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:1025: de nas slob dpon rang nyid zhi ba'i chas gos
NK024(ya)001:1026: dkar po dang ldan pas stan la 'dug dgos te
NK024(ya)001:1028: sngags mkhan zhi ba'i chas ldan pas //
NK024(ya)001:1030: ces gsungs pa'i phyir cho ga la 'jug pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1031: bde legs pa'i chog khrigs rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:1033: ces pas rang bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed la mchod pa rnam pa lnga byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:1034: gtor ma bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyi sngags kyis bdud rtsi dang /
NK024(ya)001:1035: gser skyems brtag pa gsum gyis brlab la /
NK024(ya)001:1036: zhi thung lugs su 'dzab yan chad bya /
NK024(ya)001:1037: zhes gsungs pa ltar bya dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:1038: kun gyi thog mar skyabs su 'gro zhing sems bskyed pa sogs cho ga yan lag brgyad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1039: rtsa ba'i bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pa
NK024(ya)001:1040: la phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skyabs yul ma tshang ba
NK024(ya)001:1041: med pas bskor ba mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa
NK024(ya)001:1042: m+aa dzahzhesa rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:1043: mjug tu se gol bsnol mar gtog bdag dang mkha'
NK024(ya)001:1045: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK024(ya)001:1046: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:1047: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK024(ya)001:1048: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:1049: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:1050: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1051: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:1052: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:1053: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK024(ya)001:1054: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK024(ya)001:1055: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK024(ya)001:1056: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK024(ya)001:1057: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK024(ya)001:1058: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:1059: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK024(ya)001:1060: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:1061: zhes lan gsum brjod rjes tshogs zhing rnams rang la
NK024(ya)001:1062: bsdus te ka dag gi ngang du mnyam par bzhag
NK024(ya)001:1063: go // de yang yan lag brgyad pas bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:1064: rnam par mi rtog pa bsgom pa ye shes kyi
NK024(ya)001:1065: tshogs yin zhes se ston chen po rin chen rgyal
NK024(ya)001:1067: thog mar sa lha'i mchod gtor rnams byin gyis brlabs
NK024(ya)001:1068: nas zhi thung gi cho ga byed par gsungs kyang
NK024(ya)001:1069: / thog mar cho ga byas te slad kyi sa
NK024(ya)001:1070: lha'i mchod gtor rnams byin gyis brlabs na legs shing
NK024(ya)001:1071: / / zhi thung lugs su 'dzab yan chad bya /
NK024(ya)001:1072: zhes gsungs pa'i don spyir zhi thung khro thung gi
NK024(ya)001:1073: rtsa ba sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rgya gzhung rtsod bral
NK024(ya)001:1074: yin na'ang / lugs srol so so'i bzhed lugs ltar
NK024(ya)001:1075: mi 'dra ba 'ga' re 'dug pas zhi khro thung
NK024(ya)001:1076: ba khungs ma 'ga' zhig las dpyad de 'dir zhi
NK024(ya)001:1078: thog mar bskyed rdzogs 'bring po dang sbyar ba'i sngon 'gro'i klad kyi mtshams bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:1079: so lugs kyi phyag bzhes se lugs kyi dgongs pa ltar bri bar bya ba la bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:1080: dang po mtshams kyi phrin las bskul zhing bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1082: sa dang dus kyi gnas 'di ru //
NK024(ya)001:1083: yang dag don la mi brtson zhing //
NK024(ya)001:1084: byang chub don la mi gnas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:1085: mi dang mi min gang yang rung //
NK024(ya)001:1086: thams cad gcig tu bsdus nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:1087: rdul phran bzhin du brlag pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:1088: sems nyid theg pa chen po yi //
NK024(ya)001:1089: rnam thar dag la dgod par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:1090: ye shes phrin las can gyis mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:1091: btang snyoms yal bar ma btang zhig /
NK024(ya)001:1092: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya se gol gtog pas /
NK024(ya)001:1093: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK024(ya)001:1094: cad sngon gyi smon lam gyi dbang gis mdun gyi
NK024(ya)001:1095: nam mkha' la sprin phung bzhin du gtibs nas mtshams
NK024(ya)001:1096: kyi phrin las mdzad pa gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1097: gnyis pa bgegs bskrad pa ni gzhung du nga rgyal gang la brten nas mi gsal yang /
NK024(ya)001:1098: bka' ma'i mtshams gcod phal cher badz+ra he ru ka'i
NK024(ya)001:1099: nga rgyal kho nas mdzad pa shas che bas 'dir
NK024(ya)001:1100: yang legs par mthong bas de'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:1101: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka zhes brjod pas
NK024(ya)001:1102: rang nyid badz+ra he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag
NK024(ya)001:1103: / mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi
NK024(ya)001:1104: dang po gnyis kyi rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril
NK024(ya)001:1105: / bu / bar pa gnyis kyi rtse lnga dang b+hany+dza /
NK024(ya)001:1106: tha ma gnyis kyi zhing dbyug dang 'jig rten 'degs tshul can /
NK024(ya)001:1107: zhabs bzhi g.yo rkyang gis ru tra pho mo mnan pa /
NK024(ya)001:1108: yum khro mo dbang phyug ma sngon mo dril bu dang thod khrag 'dzin pas yab la 'khril ba /
NK024(ya)001:1109: yab yum gnyis ka dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan
NK024(ya)001:1110: cing ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:1113: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:1114: thams cad thugs rjes bskang zin gyi //
NK024(ya)001:1115: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK024(ya)001:1117: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1118: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:1119: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:1121: gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba yang gsang thugs
NK024(ya)001:1122: kyi dkyil 'khor 'dir bka' gsang rmad du byung ba
NK024(ya)001:1123: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi gnas 'di ru 'du
NK024(ya)001:1124: ba'i lha la mi gtogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:1125: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'i rigs su gyur pa /
NK024(ya)001:1126: mi min mi ru bardzu ba /
NK024(ya)001:1127: lha min lha ru bardzu ba /
NK024(ya)001:1128: gsang sngags bla na med pa'i bka' dang dam tshig ma nos shing /
NK024(ya)001:1129: sngags gnyan po la mi dbang ba /
NK024(ya)001:1130: phyag rgya lha la mi dbang ba /
NK024(ya)001:1131: rnal 'byor pa mched dang lcam dral gyi tshe srog
NK024(ya)001:1132: gi bar du gcod cing dngos grub kyi bgegs dang
NK024(ya)001:1133: gcugs su byed pa de dag thams cad bskal pa'i
NK024(ya)001:1134: me dpung 'bar ba la srog gi sbrang bu mi
NK024(ya)001:1135: gnas pa'am / mar khol ma la chu'i thigs pa mi gnas pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:1136: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la mun pa'i gzhi mi gnas pa bzhin du ma gnas par dengs shig /
NK024(ya)001:1138: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:1139: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK024(ya)001:1140: na mo badz+ra kro d+ha ya /
NK024(ya)001:1141: ma h+aa damsh+tmo ta ka ta bee ra w+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:1142: a si mu sa la d+h+aa ra ya /
NK024(ya)001:1143: pa ra shu pa sha has+t+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:1145: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK024(ya)001:1153: bi s+pho ta ya bi s+pho ta ya /
NK024(ya)001:1154: sarba big+h+nana bi n+aa ya ka n+aan /
NK024(ya)001:1155: ma h+aa ga na pa ti /
NK024(ya)001:1157: an+ta ka r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1159: gsum pa khro bo'i rol mtshams ni /
NK024(ya)001:1160: bdag gi thugs ka nas khro bo bcu spros te
NK024(ya)001:1161: phyogs mtshams rang gnas su bzhugs te bsrung bar gyur
NK024(ya)001:1162: / badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1164: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1166: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1167: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1168: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1169: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1170: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1171: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1172: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1174: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1175: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1176: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1178: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1180: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1182: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1183: s+pho ta ya s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1186: grih+n+aa pa ya grih+n+aa pa ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1187: +aa na ya ho b+ha ga wan badz+ra bid+y+aa r+aa dza h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1188: bzhi pa mtshon cha'i mtshams ni /
NK024(ya)001:1189: bdag gi thugs kar nyi ma'i gdan steng sa bon
NK024(ya)001:1190: las rigs lnga yab yum bcu bskyed pa sbyor ba
NK024(ya)001:1191: mdzad pa'i sbyor mtshams nas phyag mtshan rnam pa lnga
NK024(ya)001:1192: 'phros te mtshon cha'i gur spro ba'i sngags ni /
NK024(ya)001:1209: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1212: sum+b+ha ni man+ta dz+wa la badz+ra h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1218: mtshon cha rnams rim pa bzhin 'phros te gur khang gis gtams par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1220: nga yi dkyil 'khor bstan bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:1221: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:1222: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:1223: dkyil 'khor rim pa'i tshul bzhin srungs //
NK024(ya)001:1224: rdo rje bsdams pa'i mthe bong mathe'u chung gung mo rnams sgrengs /
NK024(ya)001:1225: mdzub mo gnyis bkug pa'i rtse gung mo'i tshigs gsum
NK024(ya)001:1226: par btsugs pa rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya
NK024(ya)001:1227: bcas la / steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi ste //
NK024(ya)001:1228: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa las //
NK024(ya)001:1229: rdo rje'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da'//
NK024(ya)001:1231: thal mo sbyar te sor mo bsnol ba 'khor lo'i rgyal /
NK024(ya)001:1232: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla bre la //'og kyang 'khor lo'i sa gzhi ste //
NK024(ya)001:1233: phyogs mtshams 'khor los gtams pa las //
NK024(ya)001:1234: gsang ba 'khor lo'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da'//
NK024(ya)001:1235: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra ha na tsakra h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1236: lag pa gnyis mthe bos mdzub mo bkug nas mnan pa ral gri'i rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:1237: steng yang ral gri'i bla bre la //'og kyang ral gri'i sa gzhi ste //
NK024(ya)001:1238: phyogs mtshams ral gris gtams pa las //
NK024(ya)001:1239: gsang ba ral gri'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da'//
NK024(ya)001:1240: badz+ra tik+sha na tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1241: tsan+da ro sha khad+ga h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1242: sor mo'i rtse rnams bkug ste mgo bo lta bu dbyug to'i rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:1243: steng yang dbyug to'i bla bre la //'og kyang dbyug to'i sa gzhi ste //
NK024(ya)001:1244: phyogs mtshams dbyug tos gtams pa las /
NK024(ya)001:1245: gsang ba dbyug to'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da'//
NK024(ya)001:1246: a ko ta mung+ga ra h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1247: badz+ra k+aa la r+au pa sha ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1248: sor mo rnams rtse sprad srin lag gnyis nang du bkug pa rgya gram gyi rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:1249: steng yang rgya gram bla bre la //'og kyang rgya gram sa gzhi ste //
NK024(ya)001:1250: phyogs mtshams rgya gram gtams pa las //
NK024(ya)001:1251: gsang ba rgya gram mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK024(ya)001:1252: badz+ra karma sarba sat+wa ha ha h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1254: mtshams bcad nang ni tshun chad du //
NK024(ya)001:1255: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK024(ya)001:1256: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:1257: tho ba lcags kyu 'khrigs pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:1258: snying nas drangs shing brdung bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:1263: mtshon cha'i mtshams te mtshams gcod bzhi'i rim pa'o //'dir
NK024(ya)001:1264: phyag mtshan rnams thugs nas 'phro ba 'di ga'i lugs
NK024(ya)001:1265: thun mong ma yin pa yin cing /
NK024(ya)001:1266: la la dag lag pa'i sor mo rnams rigs lnga yab yum du byin gyis brlab par bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:1267: phyag mtshan thugs nas spro ba gzhung nas gsungs phyin 'di ga legs par sems so //
NK024(ya)001:1268: sngon 'gro sman raka gtor mchod byin brlab ni /
NK024(ya)001:1269: sa lha'i mchod gtor rnams 'og tu byin brlab dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:1270: 'dir 'das gtor gyi dbang gis zhi ba'i las byang
NK024(ya)001:1271: gi mchod gtor rnams brlab rgyu yin pa ma 'dres
NK024(ya)001:1273: de la thog mar bdud rtsi byin brlab ni /
NK024(ya)001:1274: a mri ta kun+da l+ai badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:1275: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1276: zhes bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang 'khor lo dang bcas par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:1279: zhes bcud sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i steng rigs lnga yab yum bcur bsam //
NK024(ya)001:1280: h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta kri ta badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1281: +aahmh'u zhes kha gcod la bdud rtsi'i srung ma rta mgrin yum bzhis bskor bar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:1282: rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi 'bab par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:1283: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aahzhesa lan bdun nam gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:1284: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku 'chang ba //
NK024(ya)001:1285: rdo rje mi phyed sku dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:1286: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1287: rdo rje sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1288: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK024(ya)001:1289: bdud rtsi'i phud gtor zhing lhag ma smin mtshams su bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1290: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK024(ya)001:1293: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1295: ces brjod pas smin mtshams su zla ba'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:1296: dkar po'i 'phro 'du las sku rdo rje dkar po
NK024(ya)001:1297: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1298: par gyur / dpal ldan rdo rje'i gsung 'chang ba //
NK024(ya)001:1299: rdo rje mi phyed gsung dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:1300: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1301: rdo rje gsung gi dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1302: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK024(ya)001:1303: phud gtor zhing lhag ma mgrin par bzhag la w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah s+pha ra na phata /
NK024(ya)001:1305: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1307: mgrin par pad+ma'i gdan la +aah dmar po'i 'phro 'du
NK024(ya)001:1308: las gsung rdo rje dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK024(ya)001:1309: pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1310: dpal ldan rdo rje'i thugs 'chang ba //
NK024(ya)001:1311: rdo rje mi phyed thugs dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:1312: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1313: rdo rje thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1314: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK024(ya)001:1315: phud gtor zhing lhag ma snying khar bzhag la tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1318: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1320: snying khar nyi ma'i gdan la h+aum sngon po'i 'phro
NK024(ya)001:1321: 'du las thugs rdo rje mthing kha zhal gcig phyag
NK024(ya)001:1322: gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1323: sku gsung thugs sra zhing mkhregs pa'i dbang dang dngos grub dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:1324: bdud rtsi'i zegs ma las khro bo spros te bgegs bskrad par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:1325: bi shud+d+he a mri te h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1326: d+harma a mri te h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1327: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1328: phog pa tsam gyis brgyal bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:1329: reg pa tsam gyis tshig par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:1330: rtogs pa rnams kyi bdud rtsi yin /
NK024(ya)001:1331: ma rtogs pa rnams kyi dug yin no //
NK024(ya)001:1332: gsang ba bdud rtsi'i mtshams las ma 'da' bar dengs shig /
NK024(ya)001:1334: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum gis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:1335: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus /
NK024(ya)001:1336: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1337: snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK024(ya)001:1339: ba lin+ta te dzo ba lin+ta ba la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1340: zhes bdun nam gsum brjod pas bcud lha tshogs rnams
NK024(ya)001:1341: dgyes bzhad tshim par nus pa'i 'dod yon gyi phung
NK024(ya)001:1342: por bsam / rak+ta byin brlab ni /
NK024(ya)001:1343: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum gis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:1346: zhes brjod pas snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang /
NK024(ya)001:1347: +aahh+aum rak+ta m+au la rak+ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aah zhes bdun nam
NK024(ya)001:1348: gsum brjod pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:1349: du brlab bo // phyi mchod rnams a mri tas bsang /
NK024(ya)001:1351: b+h+aum zhes snod rin po cher bsam /
NK024(ya)001:1354: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1355: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1356: +aahh+aum zhes brjod pas nyer spyod dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:1357: de yang snga 'gyur lugs la mchod gtor thams cad
NK024(ya)001:1358: slob dpon gyi mdun du byin gyis brlabs nas dkyil
NK024(ya)001:1359: 'khor la 'god pa'i phyag len yod pas /
NK024(ya)001:1360: tshig dang bstun nas 'god dgos pa yin na'ang skabs 'dir phyi dkyil med pas 'god ma dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:1361: byin rlabs kyi rgyun mi nyams pa'i phyir tshig bton pa kho nas khyab pas /
NK024(ya)001:1364: gzhong pa rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:1365: gtor ma ye shes phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:1366: rak+ta dmar gyi thig bkye zhing //
NK024(ya)001:1367: dkyil 'khor zla gam dbyings dang bstun lags shing //
NK024(ya)001:1368: tshe dang gal gnyis mthun bsdebs nas //'bul ni yi dam lha la 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:1369: mchod ni gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor mchod //
NK024(ya)001:1370: bla med dpal la 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1371: ma h+aa ba lin+ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1374: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba phud kyi phud //'bru bcud stong sbyar dza gad dpa' bo 'di //
NK024(ya)001:1375: mthu dang gzi brjid che bas 'gro ba 'dul //
NK024(ya)001:1376: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yul mchog m+aa ma k+ai //
NK024(ya)001:1377: skal med rnams kyi rkyen dang mi 'tshams te //
NK024(ya)001:1378: skal ldan thugs rje can gyis bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1379: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1382: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK024(ya)001:1383: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi rang bzhin las //
NK024(ya)001:1384: rten 'brel bcu gnyis m+au la rak+ta dang //
NK024(ya)001:1385: dug gsum bsgral ba bam gyi rak+ta dang /
NK024(ya)001:1386: khams gsum bsgral ba rtsa ba'i rak+ta dang //
NK024(ya)001:1387: chags pa 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:1388: bla med dbal gyi mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1389: ma h+aa rak+ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1391: thun mong gi mchod pa bkod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1394: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1395: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1396: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK024(ya)001:1400: g+ai ti h+r+aih sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1403: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes bshags yul spyan drangs //
NK024(ya)001:1404: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK024(ya)001:1406: de yang zhi thung gi sngon 'gro la lar /
NK024(ya)001:1407: ye shes lha dang mkha' 'gro dam tshig can //
NK024(ya)001:1410: bshags pa ni brjod med do //
NK024(ya)001:1411: zhes gsungs pa btsan par byas so //
NK024(ya)001:1412: zhi thung gi sngon 'gror dam bca' byin 'bebs sogs mi 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:1413: snga 'gyur bka' ma spyi gzhung ltar byas na legs
NK024(ya)001:1414: shing rgyas bsdus mang yang 'dir bsdus pa tsam gyis
NK024(ya)001:1415: khyab pa ste / dam bca' ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1416: se ston rin po ches bsdu na /
NK024(ya)001:1417: kun tu bzang po sh+lo ka gcig gis kyang chog /
NK024(ya)001:1419: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:1420: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK024(ya)001:1421: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:1422: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:1424: se ston rin po ches dpal phreng dam pa las
NK024(ya)001:1425: byung ba'i bab drug 'das bzhi mdzod gcig gis bya
NK024(ya)001:1427: a la la hoh b+ha ga wan /
NK024(ya)001:1428: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1429: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1430: khyad par bstan pa'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1431: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1432: byin gyis brlab pa'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1433: dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1434: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK024(ya)001:1436: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:1437: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:1438: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:1439: bdag cag las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:1441: zhes tshogs zhing rnams rang la bstim mo //
NK024(ya)001:1443: dngos gzhi zhi thung gi rtsa ba ting nge 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1444: gsum nas mchod pa 'bul ba yan chad yin na'ang
NK024(ya)001:1445: / rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyis cung zad phye
NK024(ya)001:1446: ba ltar 'dir sgom don yang mdo tsam smos te
NK024(ya)001:1447: / 'chad pa la / zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bdag bskyed kyi tshul du bsgom zhing 'di skad do //
NK024(ya)001:1449: mi dmigs chos nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK024(ya)001:1450: rang bzhin 'od gsal kun tu snang //
NK024(ya)001:1451: a nyid rgyu las dkyil 'khor byung //
NK024(ya)001:1452: zhes chos nyid de bzhin nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:1453: rang bzhin 'od gsal snying rje'i rang mdangs can kun snang dang /
NK024(ya)001:1454: rang rig +aahdakara por gsal ba'i rgyu'i ting 'dzin te rnam pa gsum bsgom mo //
NK024(ya)001:1455: de las dbang chen gzhal yas khang //
NK024(ya)001:1456: e yam bam su lam ram /
NK024(ya)001:1457: e las nam mkha' mtha' dbus med //
NK024(ya)001:1458: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor te //
NK024(ya)001:1459: bam las chu yi rba klong 'khyil //
NK024(ya)001:1460: su las gser gyi sa gzhi chags //
NK024(ya)001:1461: lam las rin chen ri rab mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:1463: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala b+h+r+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1466: b+h+r+aum las rin chen zhal yas khang //
NK024(ya)001:1467: glang chen seng ge rta rma te'u //
NK024(ya)001:1468: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:1469: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK024(ya)001:1470: ces 'byung rim gzhal yas khang 'khor lo gdan khri pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan rnams bskyed do //
NK024(ya)001:1472: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK024(ya)001:1473: ces dbang po rab kyis skad cig la mkha' mnyam
NK024(ya)001:1474: dkyil 'khor du lhag gis gsal 'debs pa'i dgongs pa
NK024(ya)001:1476: dbang rtul gyis mi gsal phyir bla ma gong mas
NK024(ya)001:1477: lha rnams kyi bskyed sngags kyis gsal 'debs shing dbang
NK024(ya)001:1478: bskur byin rlabs rnams byed par gsungs la /
NK024(ya)001:1479: de yang zhi khro'i mngon rtogs la 'dris pas sngags tsam gyis gsal thebs mod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:1480: de ltar ma yin pas sgom mi shes pa'i skyon
NK024(ya)001:1481: bsal phyir sngags kyi bar du mngon rtogs mdo tsam
NK024(ya)001:1482: bris yod pa ltar rtogs par bya la /
NK024(ya)001:1483: de la zhi khro'i mngon rtogs rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum las 'dir bsdus pa kho nas khyab ste /
NK024(ya)001:1485: sgyu 'phrul 'bring po'am bsdus pa ltar lha rnams zhal gcig phyag gnyis par gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:1488: 'khor lo'i dbus kyi seng ge'i khri'i steng du rang
NK024(ya)001:1489: rig yi ge +aah yongs su gyur pa las mi
NK024(ya)001:1490: bskyod rdo rje sems dpa' mthing kha zhal gcig phyag
NK024(ya)001:1491: gnyis / g.yas rdo rje thugs ka dang g.yon dril
NK024(ya)001:1492: bu dkur brten pa la yum dbyings phyug ma sngon
NK024(ya)001:1493: mo g.yas dril bu dang g.yon rdo rje 'dzin pas
NK024(ya)001:1496: shar gyi rtsibs la glang po che'i khrir rnam snang
NK024(ya)001:1497: dkar po g.yas 'khor lo dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1498: pa yum spyan ma dkar mo dril bu 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:1501: m+aam mo ha ra ti lho'i rtsibs la rta'i khrir
NK024(ya)001:1502: rin 'byung yab yum gnyis ka ser po rin po
NK024(ya)001:1503: che dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //+aamha ro lika /
NK024(ya)001:1505: nub kyi rtsibs la rma bya'i khrir snang mtha' yab
NK024(ya)001:1506: yum gnyis ka dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1509: byang gi rtsibs la shang shang te 'u'i khrir don
NK024(ya)001:1510: grub yab yum gnyis ka ljang gu ral gri dang
NK024(ya)001:1513: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1514: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sa snying dkar po rin
NK024(ya)001:1515: po che'i myu gu dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang
NK024(ya)001:1516: yum sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1518: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh lho nub kyi
NK024(ya)001:1519: rtsibs mchan la nam mkha'i snying po ser po ral
NK024(ya)001:1520: gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang yum phreng ba
NK024(ya)001:1521: ma ser mo phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1522: h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK024(ya)001:1524: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la spyan ras gzigs dmar
NK024(ya)001:1525: po pad dkar dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang yum
NK024(ya)001:1526: glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1527: dz+r+aim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK024(ya)001:1528: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la phyag na rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:1529: ljang gu rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang
NK024(ya)001:1530: yum gar ma ljang gu gar gyi phu rung 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1531: pa'o // mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1532: dzah d+h+au pe pra be sha /
NK024(ya)001:1533: shar lho'i gru chad la byams pa dkar ser klu
NK024(ya)001:1534: shing dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang yum spos ma
NK024(ya)001:1536: th+l+him nis+sa ram p+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1538: lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib sel dmar ser
NK024(ya)001:1539: chos kyi 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang
NK024(ya)001:1540: yum me tog ma dmar ser me tog 'dzin pa'o
NK024(ya)001:1541: // h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1542: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK024(ya)001:1543: nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang dmar ljang
NK024(ya)001:1544: rin po che'i myu gu dang dril bu 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:1545: dang yum mar me ma dmar ljang mar me 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:1546: pa'o // m+aum sh+r+ai a r+aam ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1548: byang shar gyi gru chad la 'jam dpal dkar ljang
NK024(ya)001:1549: ut+pala dang dril bu 'dzin pa dang yum dri chab
NK024(ya)001:1550: ma dkar ljang dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1554: badz+r+ai b+ha d+r+aa sa man+ta a /
NK024(ya)001:1555: kun bzang yab yum gnyis kyi bzhugs gnas gtso bo'i
NK024(ya)001:1556: thugs ka dang mdun rgyab khyams kyi shar nub sogs
NK024(ya)001:1557: lugs gsum yod kyang 'dir g.yung ston sogs kyi rjes
NK024(ya)001:1558: su 'brangs te / khyams kyi shar du byed pa
NK024(ya)001:1559: po kun tu bzang po mthing kha mnyam gzhag gi
NK024(ya)001:1560: phyag rgya can dang nub tu bya ba mo kun
NK024(ya)001:1561: tu bzang mo mthing kha thal mo thugs kar sbyar
NK024(ya)001:1562: su 'brangs te / te bzhugs pa'o // mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1563: snam bu'i shar lho'i lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wang bsnams te bzhengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1564: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1565: snam bu'i byang du lha min thub pa mthing kha go mtshon bsnams te bzhengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1567: snam pu'i lhor mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par bsnams te bzhengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1569: snam bu'i nub byang du byol song gi thub pa dmar nag glegs bam bsnams te bzhengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1571: snam bu'i lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa
NK024(ya)001:1572: ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu bsnams te bzhengs
NK024(ya)001:1573: pa'o // mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1574: snam bu'i byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu bsnams te bzhengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1575: h+aum ya m+aa n+ta kri ta phata /
NK024(ya)001:1576: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1577: shar sgor gshin rje mthar byed smug nag mi mgo
NK024(ya)001:1578: 'dzin pa dang yum lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags
