NK024(ya)001:1579: kyu 'dzin pa'o // h+aum pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata /
NK024(ya)001:1580: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1581: lho sgor shes rab mthar byed stobs chen ser nag
NK024(ya)001:1582: thod pa rdo rjes gnon thabs su 'dzin pa dang
NK024(ya)001:1583: yum zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa'o
NK024(ya)001:1585: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1586: nub sgor pad+ma mthar byed rta mgrin dmar nag thod
NK024(ya)001:1587: pa sbrul dkris can 'dzin pa dang yum lcags sgrog
NK024(ya)001:1588: ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1590: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+aa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1591: byang sgor bgegs mthar byed 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya
NK024(ya)001:1592: gram gnon thabs su 'dzin pa dang yum dril bu
NK024(ya)001:1593: ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1595: se ston rin po che'i bzhed pa ltar /
NK024(ya)001:1596: lha rnams rang rang gi thugs srog las 'od 'phros te dbang lha rigs lnga yab yum spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:1597: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tu m+aamh
NK024(ya)001:1598: zhes gsol ba btab pas nam mkha'i rigs lngas dbang
NK024(ya)001:1600: rdo rje phyi bsdams las gus mo gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1601: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1602: rdo rje bsdams pa'i mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba dpral bar bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1603: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1604: srin lag gnyis brkyang pa rna ltag g.yas su bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1605: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1606: mthe bong gnyis brkyang ba ltag par bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1607: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha n+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1608: mathe'u chung gnyis brkyang ba rna ltag g.yon du bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:1609: ma h+aa krit+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1610: zhes dbang bskur bas sku gang dri ma dang chu'i
NK024(ya)001:1611: lhag ma yar lud pa las gtso bo yab yum
NK024(ya)001:1612: dang kun bzang yab yum gnyis thub pa drug la
NK024(ya)001:1613: mi bskyod pa gtso bor bzhugs pa'i rigs lnga /
NK024(ya)001:1614: shar dang shar lho ba rnams la rnam snang gis gtso mdzad pa'i rigs lnga /
NK024(ya)001:1615: lho dang lho nub pa rnams la rin 'byung gis gtso mdzad pa'i rigs lnga /
NK024(ya)001:1616: nub dang nub byang ba rnams la snang mthas gtso mdzad pa'i rigs lnga /
NK024(ya)001:1617: byang dang byang shar ba rnams la don grub kyis gtso mdzad pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK024(ya)001:1618: 'di ni g.yung ston rdo rje dpal ba dang se
NK024(ya)001:1619: ston rin po che'i dgongs pa thun mong ma yin
NK024(ya)001:1620: pa'o // yang lha thams cad kyi dpral bar zla ba la dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:1622: thugs kar nyi ma la h+aum sngon po de las
NK024(ya)001:1623: 'od zer 'phros shing 'dus pas sku gsung thugs kyi
NK024(ya)001:1624: lhar gyur / rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK024(ya)001:1625: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1626: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1627: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1628: sgyu 'phrul chen mor snyan gsan spyan 'dren phyag rgya bzhi sogs rim par bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:1629: 'dir phyag rgya bzhir don gyi tshang bas de la
NK024(ya)001:1630: yang thog mar 'og min nas ye shes kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:1631: 'khor nam mkha'i khams gang bar byon par bsam zhing
NK024(ya)001:1632: / rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK024(ya)001:1633: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:1634: lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas nam mkhar dgug /
NK024(ya)001:1635: zhags pas dam tshig pa la gzhug /
NK024(ya)001:1636: lcags sgrog gis gnyis med du bcings /
NK024(ya)001:1637: dril bus dgyes pa bskyed par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:1638: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK024(ya)001:1639: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK024(ya)001:1640: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod la //
NK024(ya)001:1641: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:1642: dzahh+aum bam hoh phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1644: dbyings kyi rang bzhin rnam dag las //
NK024(ya)001:1645: thugs rje'i dbang gis skur bzhengs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:1646: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dag /
NK024(ya)001:1647: rang snang lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:1648: a la la hoh bzhugs gsol ni /
NK024(ya)001:1649: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK024(ya)001:1650: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1651: mi dmigs don du dngos grub mchog gi rnams //
NK024(ya)001:1652: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1654: mchod pa'i dang po phyag rgya gar mchod ni /
NK024(ya)001:1655: sku mdog zhal phyag cir yang bsgyur //
NK024(ya)001:1656: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:1657: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:1658: mchod bzhes dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1659: bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1662: ti pu pa ra muh sarba th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1663: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1664: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1665: sgyu 'phrul chen mor bzhi bsnol gyi sngon du pa
NK024(ya)001:1666: na pem sogs 'gro dgos kyang 'dir bsdus pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:1668: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1669: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1670: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1671: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga nee wid+ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1672: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga shap+da s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1673: sgyu 'phrul rang lugs la bzhi bsnol zhes spos me
NK024(ya)001:1674: tog mar me dri chab bzhir bshad kyang zhal zas
NK024(ya)001:1675: dang rol mo gsar rnying kun gyi mchod pa'i yan
NK024(ya)001:1678: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:1680: glu tshig bro gar rol mo yis //
NK024(ya)001:1681: zhes gsungs pas 'gal ba med par sems /
NK024(ya)001:1682: 'on kyang sgyu 'phrul kho na gtsang bar byed na
NK024(ya)001:1683: byin rlabs dang 'bul dus gnyis kar dri chab yan
NK024(ya)001:1684: bya'o // bdud rtsi sman mchod ni /
NK024(ya)001:1685: rang byung gdod nas rnam dag pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:1686: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK024(ya)001:1687: rigs lnga ye shes lnga yi dngos //
NK024(ya)001:1688: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK024(ya)001:1689: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK024(ya)001:1690: byang chub lcam dral thub drug dang //
NK024(ya)001:1691: kun bzang yab yum 'khor bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:1692: bla med bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:1693: thugs rje cher dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1696: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK024(ya)001:1697: zhes gtso bo nas sgo skyong bar gyi lha tshogs
NK024(ya)001:1698: thams cad la rtsa sngags kyi mthar bdud rtsi'i 'bul
NK024(ya)001:1700: bdud rtsi la brten nas bshags pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1701: lta ba 'phangs dmas chos nyid don ma rtogs //
NK024(ya)001:1702: sgom pa yun thung yi dam lha ma gsal //'bad rtsol chung bas slob dpon sku ma mnyes //
NK024(ya)001:1703: brtse gdung chung bas mched lcam dam las 'gal //
NK024(ya)001:1704: ye shes lha yi spyan sngar mthol lo bshags //
NK024(ya)001:1705: mthol bshags 'bul lo tshangs par stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1706: rtsa ba yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag 'gal
NK024(ya)001:1707: 'khrul gyur pa ci mchis pa thams cad bdud rtsi
NK024(ya)001:1708: sman gyi sgo nas mthol lo bshags so //
NK024(ya)001:1709: bdud rtsi'i dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1710: rgyal ba sras bcas thugs kyi dpa' be'u nas //
NK024(ya)001:1711: dngos grub stsal dang stsol ba mi dmigs kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1712: sngon gyi thugs dam dbang gis dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:1713: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1714: bdud rtsi mtheb srin gyis gnas gsum du reg la /
NK024(ya)001:1718: gtor ma dang sbyor sgrol yid mchod sogs bsdus te 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1719: tshogs dang gtor ma pany+tsa a mri ta //
NK024(ya)001:1720: ta na ga na la sogs ci 'byor ba //
NK024(ya)001:1721: ting 'dzin yid kyis dmigs pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:1722: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams kyis bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1723: badz+ra ba lin+ta pra t+ai ts+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1724: zhi thung gi rtsa ba 'di yan chod yin na'ang
NK024(ya)001:1725: bstod pa mchod pa'i yan lag tu sgyu 'phrul ba
NK024(ya)001:1726: rnams mdzad phyir bstod pa zhig nges par dgos la
NK024(ya)001:1727: / de yang zhi thung la lar /
NK024(ya)001:1728: rnam shes rnam dag bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK024(ya)001:1730: 'dir rgyud las byung ba dang glu ye shes kyi
NK024(ya)001:1731: mchod pa dang bstod pa gnyis go chod pa'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:1732: len gda' bas bstod pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1734: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:1735: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK024(ya)001:1736: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:1737: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:1739: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK024(ya)001:1740: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK024(ya)001:1741: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK024(ya)001:1742: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che //
NK024(ya)001:1744: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK024(ya)001:1745: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:1746: ye nas lhun grub kun tu bzang //'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che //
NK024(ya)001:1748: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:1749: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs 'phro //
NK024(ya)001:1750: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK024(ya)001:1751: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po //
NK024(ya)001:1753: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK024(ya)001:1754: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran snyed //
NK024(ya)001:1755: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK024(ya)001:1756: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub //
NK024(ya)001:1758: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK024(ya)001:1759: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK024(ya)001:1760: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK024(ya)001:1761: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che //
NK024(ya)001:1764: mdo sgyu gnyis ka'i lugs la 'dzab khang phye nas byed pa'i phyag bzhes yod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:1765: 'dir spyi 'dzab kyis 'thus pas ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK024(ya)001:1766: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi thugs srog la rang sngags
NK024(ya)001:1767: kyis bskor bar bsam pa'am bsdu na gtso 'khor thams
NK024(ya)001:1768: cad kyi thugs srog la bo d+hi'i sngags phreng gis
NK024(ya)001:1769: bskor ba las 'od 'phros don gnyis byas /
NK024(ya)001:1770: tshur 'dus pas nyams chag bskang zhing dngos grub thob par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:1771: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu +aah zhes ci rigs bzla /
NK024(ya)001:1772: mthar rgyal ba zhi khro rab 'byams gyi lha tshogs
NK024(ya)001:1773: rnams kyis bdag la mchog dang thun mong gi dngos
NK024(ya)001:1774: grub dang / khyad par sa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:1776: rdo rje sems dpa'i yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyis nyams chag bskang zhing bzod par gsol /
NK024(ya)001:1778: se ston rin po che'i dgongs pa ltar /
NK024(ya)001:1779: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor mi dmigs pa'i ngang du bsdus te /
NK024(ya)001:1780: stong pa 'i ngang las thun mtshams kyi lha rdo rjee sems dpar lam gyis blta /
NK024(ya)001:1781: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i ham /
NK024(ya)001:1782: de las 'phro 'dus lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyis gtams par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:1786: rdo rje phyi sngags kyi sor mo bsnol /
NK024(ya)001:1787: mthe bong gnyis gshibs te sgreng /
NK024(ya)001:1788: mthil gnyis phye ba rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya dpral bar gtugs la /
NK024(ya)001:1789: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha rak+sha /
NK024(ya)001:1790: gnas drug bsrung ba'i dmigs pa ni khro bo rdo
NK024(ya)001:1791: rje gnod sbyin dang mi 'chi thal sbyor gnyis kyis
NK024(ya)001:1793: lte ba dang bcu drug mdor bcings /
NK024(ya)001:1794: snying ga dang tshig pa bdun par bcings /
NK024(ya)001:1796: dpral ba dang ltag khung du 'ching ba'i tshul /
NK024(ya)001:1797: spyi bor bzhengs pa'i tshul gyis bsrung bar bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:1798: las gnyis so sor rdo rje khu tshur gyi mdzub
NK024(ya)001:1799: mo gnyis gnas so sor bsnol ba rdo rje bsrung
NK024(ya)001:1800: ba'i rgya dang trum lan drug gis srung /
NK024(ya)001:1801: dar dkar pos gnas dgur mdud par bsam la lag
NK024(ya)001:1802: gnyis spyi bor rtse sprad pa bsham brdab ste badz+ra
NK024(ya)001:1803: tu sh+ya hoh rat+na mu ku tram tram tram tram
NK024(ya)001:1804: tram / +aar+ya lam bo d+ha ra badz+ra dri sh+ya
NK024(ya)001:1805: hoh zhi thung khro thung gi dpe dkon zhing gang
NK024(ya)001:1806: yod rnams kyang bcos mang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:1807: khyad par stod phyogs kyi dpe rgyun la sa lugs
NK024(ya)001:1808: dang bo lugs kyi lhad mang bar zhugs pa'i ma
NK024(ya)001:1809: dag pa'i dri ma thams cang byang bar byas shing
NK024(ya)001:1810: / sngags tshig phra mo tshun yang rgyud 'grel rgya
NK024(ya)001:1811: gzhung sogs rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyi gsung las
NK024(ya)001:1812: legs par dpyad de dag par bcos shing /
NK024(ya)001:1813: sgom don dang phyag rgya rnams kyang zhib par bris yod pas yid brtan du rung bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:1815: de nas sa gzhi ye nas sangs rgyas spyan gyi
NK024(ya)001:1816: rang bzhin yin pa la yin par ngo shes pas
NK024(ya)001:1817: de ltar gyur par bsgom la /
NK024(ya)001:1818: ma s+au r+ya man+da la zhes brjod pas gser gyi sa ga zhir bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:1819: de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa las blang ba'i rim pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:1820: dang po'i gnyis pa sa'i lha mo la blang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1823: mchod pa ting 'dzin ye shes brlab //
NK024(ya)001:1826: rang bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed de mchod gtor byin gyis brlab par gsungs pas de'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:1828: ces brjod pas skad cig dran rdzogs su rang nyid
NK024(ya)001:1829: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag zhal gcig
NK024(ya)001:1830: phyag gnyis pa g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje rtse lnga
NK024(ya)001:1831: pa 'phyar zhing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa khro
NK024(ya)001:1832: bo'i rgyan dang ldan pa la /
NK024(ya)001:1833: yum rlung 'byin ma ljang gu zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK024(ya)001:1834: g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten
NK024(ya)001:1835: pa dang 'khril ba'i rnam par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1836: mchod gtor gser skyems byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1838: stong gsum kun tu dri mchog 'byung gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:1839: spos dang sman sbyar chu gtsang dag pa'i khrus //
NK024(ya)001:1840: yid bzhin sprin phul mkha' la char 'bebs bas //
NK024(ya)001:1841: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs kun dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:1842: shud+d+he shud+d+he sho d+ha na ye s+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1844: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus /
NK024(ya)001:1845: b+h+r+aum las rin po che las grub pa'i snod yangs
NK024(ya)001:1846: shing rgya che ba rnams kyi nang du zhu ba
NK024(ya)001:1847: las byung ba'i lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod yon
NK024(ya)001:1854: rol mo rnams dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1863: zhes so so'i phyag rgya dang rol mo dkrol zhing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:1865: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i snod du +aahh+aum las gtor
NK024(ya)001:1866: ma zag pa med pa ye shes kyi bdud rtsi
NK024(ya)001:1867: 'dod pa'i yon tan ma tshang ba med par gyur
NK024(ya)001:1868: / big+h+nan+ta krita badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:1869: bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyi phyag rgyar bcas te lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:1870: gser skyems brtag pa gsum gyis brlab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1871: gzhung las dngos su gsal bar ma byung zhing bla
NK024(ya)001:1872: ma dag la dris shing rtsad pas kyang ram yam
NK024(ya)001:1874: phyis bka' ma'i cha gsum dpal sdom ma'i yig rnying
NK024(ya)001:1875: zhig rnyed pa las gtor ma brtag pa bzhis byin
NK024(ya)001:1876: gyis brlab par bshad pa'i brtag pa bzhi ni sbyang
NK024(ya)001:1877: spel bsgyur thob bzhir bshad pas des na /
NK024(ya)001:1878: brtag pa gsum sbyang spel bsgyur gsum la the tshom ma dgos phyir /
NK024(ya)001:1879: chos nyid rnam dag gi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:1880: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags lan gsum gyis sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:1881: b+h+aum las rin po che'i snod du gser skyems gzugs
NK024(ya)001:1882: sgra dri ro reg bya 'dod pa'i yon tan dang
NK024(ya)001:1883: ldan pa bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1884: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:1885: b+h+yo bi shwa'i sngags lan gsum gyis spel /
NK024(ya)001:1886: bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:1887: badz+ra a mri ta'i sngags lan gsum gyis bdud rtsir bsgyur zhing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:1888: sa lha dngos ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:1889: dkyil 'khor du lam ser po bsam ste /
NK024(ya)001:1890: lam rat+na p+aa sh+yam sid+d+hi ku ru h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1892: zhes pas sa'i lha mo sku mdog ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis ma g.yas sa gnon /
NK024(ya)001:1893: g.yon rin po che'i bum pa bsnams pa phag gi
NK024(ya)001:1894: khri la bzhugs pa 'od lnga dang ldan pa sku
NK024(ya)001:1895: gsung thugs byin gyis brlab la /
NK024(ya)001:1896: zhes gsungs pa'i don ji ltar bya ba la /
NK024(ya)001:1897: man+dala steng gi tshom bu la dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:1898: +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta kri ta h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:1901: lam rat+na p+aa sh+yam sid+d+hi ku ru h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:1903: zhes brjod pas tshom bu lam ser po las sa'i
NK024(ya)001:1904: lha mo sku mdog ser mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK024(ya)001:1905: ma phyag g.yas rin po che'i gter bum thugs kar
NK024(ya)001:1906: bsnams shing / phyag g.yon mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya
NK024(ya)001:1907: ston par mdzad pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan
NK024(ya)001:1908: bsnams shing / gyis brgyan cing / 'ja' tshon sna
NK024(ya)001:1909: lnga'i 'od dang ldan pa phag gi khri la bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:1910: bsnams shing / gyis brgyan cing / par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:1911: lha mo'i phyag mtshan zur lugs glan lugs sogs la
NK024(ya)001:1912: g.yas sa gnon dang g.yon bum pa bsnams pa mdzad
NK024(ya)001:1913: bsnams shing / gyis brgyan cing / par gyur / kyang / las rim las /
NK024(ya)001:1914: sa gzhi lam las gser mdog can //
NK024(ya)001:1915: bum pa rin chen gang ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:1916: phyag rgya ston pa mchog sbyin yin //
NK024(ya)001:1917: zhes pa'i gzhung don ltar g.yung dang kahthoga rdor bzang
NK024(ya)001:1918: sogs kyi yang de bzhin mdzad pa legs par mthong
NK024(ya)001:1920: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab la zhes pa tsam las mi 'byung yang /
NK024(ya)001:1921: glan ston bsod nams mgon po dang g.yung ston gyis
NK024(ya)001:1922: rnam snang gis gtso byas pa'i rigs lngas dbu brgyan
NK024(ya)001:1923: cing / sku gsung thugs brlab par gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:1925: lha mo spyan gyi rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:1926: sku gsung thugs kyis brtan par bya //
NK024(ya)001:1927: rang snying snang mdzad phyag rgyas gdab //
NK024(ya)001:1929: mi bskyod pa stong nyid ye shes dang /
NK024(ya)001:1930: rnam snang me long ye shes kyi ngo bor mdzad pa sgyu 'phrul ba'i lugs yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:1931: 'dir rigs kyi dbang gis rnam snang dbus su bton
NK024(ya)001:1932: te rdor bsdams mdzub mo brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag
NK024(ya)001:1934: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:1935: gung mo brkyang ba dpral bar /
NK024(ya)001:1936: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na srin lag brkyang ba rna g.yas su /
NK024(ya)001:1937: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa mthe bong brkyang ba ltag par /
NK024(ya)001:1938: ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha mathe'u chung brkyang ba rna g.yon du /
NK024(ya)001:1939: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nu sh+tha zhes dbang bskur /
NK024(ya)001:1940: rdo rje phyag rgya gnas gsum du gtug tshul bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:1941: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sarba
NK024(ya)001:1942: ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka sarba ta
NK024(ya)001:1943: th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta zhes gnas gsum byin
NK024(ya)001:1944: gyis brlab bo // badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo
NK024(ya)001:1945: rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas te snyan gsan dbab
NK024(ya)001:1947: rdo rje dril bu thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:1948: don dam gser gyi sa la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK024(ya)001:1949: yid du 'ong ba'i pho brang dbus na bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:1950: nyi zla skar ma dag gis rab brgyan te //
NK024(ya)001:1951: byams thugs brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1953: e h+ye his spyan drangs zhes pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:1955: e h+ye hi b+ha su d+ha ri ma h+aa k+aa
NK024(ya)001:1956: ru n+ai k+aa dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK024(ya)001:1958: lag pa gnyis rdo rje khu tshur gyis mathe'u chung sprel ba h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgyas spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:1959: phyag rgya bzhi bca' zhing dzahh+aum bam hoh'i sngags rgyas bstim /
NK024(ya)001:1960: tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par bya /
NK024(ya)001:1962: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK024(ya)001:1963: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:1964: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK024(ya)001:1965: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK024(ya)001:1966: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK024(ya)001:1967: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yohbi shwa mu khe
NK024(ya)001:1968: b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam ga
NK024(ya)001:1970: zhabs bsil ni ar+g+ha'i phyag rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:1971: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK024(ya)001:1972: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:1973: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:1974: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK024(ya)001:1975: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bu d+d+h+aa n+aam ga
NK024(ya)001:1976: ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:1978: so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas /
NK024(ya)001:1981: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1982: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK024(ya)001:1983: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK024(ya)001:1985: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK024(ya)001:1987: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih pa na pem sogs nas /
NK024(ya)001:1988: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK024(ya)001:1990: mchod pa bdud rtsi glu gar gyis //
NK024(ya)001:1991: rgyas mchod 'dod don gsol ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:1993: bstod cing 'dod don dpang du gsol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:1994: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK024(ya)001:1995: spyod pa'i tshul dang khyad par las //
NK024(ya)001:1996: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK024(ya)001:1997: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK024(ya)001:1998: zhes brjod la lag g.yas tri shu la'i phyag rgya sa la bsnun cing /
NK024(ya)001:1999: e h+ye hi pra ti b+ha ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2000: zhes brjod pas sa'i lha mo nyid dpang po'i tshul
NK024(ya)001:2001: du sku lte ba yan chad thon te bzhugs par
NK024(ya)001:2003: sngags 'di rtsa bar b+ha ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2004: zhes pa zhig 'dug kyang glan ston bsod nams mgon
NK024(ya)001:2005: pos 'di ltar mdzad 'dug pas thogs pa med par
NK024(ya)001:2007: de nas mgron spyi spyan drang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2009: 'dzam gling spyir gnas mthu chen dbang sgyur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:2010: nam zlu dus 'dzin dbyar dgun ston dpyid la //
NK024(ya)001:2011: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston cing kun la 'tshe //
NK024(ya)001:2012: sa bdag tsang kun kun nas 'khor ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:2013: sa bdag hong phan dang ni the se dang //
NK024(ya)001:2014: be sna yag chen sa bdag gnyan chen rnams //
NK024(ya)001:2015: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i mgron du gnas 'dir spyon //
NK024(ya)001:2016: thugs dam brtse phyir gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2017: bye brag sgrub pa gang byed kyi yul gyi sa bdag spyan drang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2018: khyad par yul 'di'i sa la mnga' mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:2019: gangs ri g.ya' ri brag ri spang ri dang //
NK024(ya)001:2020: bye ri la gnas sa bdag 'khor dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:2021: khyad par sa 'di'i bdag po 'khor dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:2022: rigs dang kha dog mi mthun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:2023: mchod sbyin gtor ma'i mgron du sbyan 'dren na //
NK024(ya)001:2024: bde gshegs bka' yi gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2025: zhes pas mdun du byon par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:2028: rgyas par bshams pa'i mchod sbyin gtor ma 'di //
NK024(ya)001:2029: gser dngul la sogs rin chen sna lngas brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:2030: sa bdag 'khor dang bcas la mchod par 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:2031: nor dbyig srang mang grangs su bzhengs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2032: rin chen 'bru sna ma lus zas kyi tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:2033: rang lus lhu tshigs nyams pa bskang slad du //
NK024(ya)001:2034: chags med stobs ldan sems kyis 'bul lags na //
NK024(ya)001:2035: bzhes nas lhu tshigs nad rnams bral bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:2036: bu ram sprang rtsi ka ra 'o ma mar //
NK024(ya)001:2037: dug gsum sems la zhugs pa'i nad rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:2038: khro gtum drag po'i nad rnams bsal slad du //
NK024(ya)001:2039: zhi dul mnyes te mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2040: n+aa ga ge sar la sogs sman sna brgyad //
NK024(ya)001:2041: chag nyams nad 'bras ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:2042: sa bdag sku snyung rkyen ngan sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:2043: dka' zhing dkon pa'i yul nas btsal bsags te //
NK024(ya)001:2044: dbang chen sa bdag 'khor dang bcas pa la //
NK024(ya)001:2045: nyes skyon gos sob gdan du 'bul lags na //
NK024(ya)001:2046: yun du skyid cing bde ba'i sems nyid kyis //
NK024(ya)001:2047: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i gtor ma bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2050: gtor ma dang dkar gsum mngar gsum so so'i sngags
NK024(ya)001:2051: dang phyag rgya byin la gang bcol nyan par bsam
NK024(ya)001:2052: ste / zhes 'byung bas bsdu na rdo rje bsdams pa 'degs pa'i rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:2053: a k+aa ro mu kham sarba d+har+m+aa nam +aad+ya nut+pan+na t+w+aat+ta +aahh+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2054: lan bdun nam gsum gyis bsngo /
NK024(ya)001:2056: ri rab chen po gling bzhi rab tu 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:2057: kun dag'i bdag po dbang byed chen po 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:2058: kun tu sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:2059: sa bdag mthu chen 'khor gyi gnas rnams su //
NK024(ya)001:2060: mchod sbyin dam pa'i gtor ma 'di bsngosa pas //
NK024(ya)001:2061: so so'i 'khor gyi re ba bskangs gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:2062: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:2064: sa'i bdag po rnams rang rang gi gnas su bskyod
NK024(ya)001:2065: pa'i phyir gdan skyems sam gser skyems 'bul ba ni
NK024(ya)001:2067: lcags ri gser ri dngul gyi ri //
NK024(ya)001:2068: shel ri gangs ri khyud 'khor nas //
NK024(ya)001:2069: mi la nor gyi dbyig 'byung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:2070: chos bzang gnas lugs spyod pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:2071: mthu chen lha'am sman la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:2072: sa bdag gnyan po 'khor bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:2073: kun sbyangs dri sbyar 'bru yi skyems //
NK024(ya)001:2074: rin chen sa le spram gyis spras //
NK024(ya)001:2075: rgyud bshad mchod sbyin gser skyems 'di //
NK024(ya)001:2078: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK024(ya)001:2079: khe b+h+yahsogasa nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang phyag rgyas
NK024(ya)001:2080: gser skyems phyogs kun tu gtor la gnod 'tshe ma
NK024(ya)001:2083: gtor ma bza' btung me tog ldan //
NK024(ya)001:2084: de bzhin rin chen ldan pa'i chang //'dod yon bdud rtsir byin brlab la //
NK024(ya)001:2085: zhing skyong rnams la rgyas par byin //
NK024(ya)001:2088: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:2089: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2090: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2091: bden pa chen po byin gyis brlabs kyis bdag cag
NK024(ya)001:2092: gis mos te sbyar ba'i mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma
NK024(ya)001:2094: 'dzam bu'i gling na gnas pa'i sa bdag ma lus pa rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:2095: yul phyogs 'di na gnas pa'i sa bdag klu gnyan gyi tshogs /
NK024(ya)001:2098: bu smad g.yog 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:2100: de dag rnams kyi spyan lam du gnas khyad par can /
NK024(ya)001:2102: sman gyi grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:2103: gzhan yang gling bzhi gling phran brgyad na bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun /
NK024(ya)001:2113: rin po che'i phung po la sogs pa yid dang
NK024(ya)001:2114: mthun pa 'i gnas su gyur nas gzhan du dengs
NK024(ya)001:2115: shig / rgya mtsho lbu ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:2117: dbang po lag pa la sogs pa sman sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:2118: kyis sa bdag rnams 'od dang gzi brjid dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:2119: par gyur cig / sa'i phyogs 'dir 'dus pa chen
NK024(ya)001:2120: po'i dkyil 'khor bzhengs su gsol bas cho ga ma
NK024(ya)001:2121: grub bar du gzhan du song zhig /
NK024(ya)001:2122: ces brjod pas tshim nas gzhan du song bar bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:2123: de nas mdzub mo gnyis smin mtshams su bsnol te /
NK024(ya)001:2124: a hohbe ga kra ma ya /
NK024(ya)001:2125: zhes pas sa'i lha mo re zhig nam mkha' la dpang por bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:2126: sa lha'i tshom bu bsdu'o //'di yan chod bdud rtsi
NK024(ya)001:2127: 'khyil ba'i nga rgyal la gnas pa kho nas bya'o
NK024(ya)001:2128: // de nas sa'i bar chad bsal ba'i phyir badz+ra
NK024(ya)001:2129: sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes pas rdo rje bsdu
NK024(ya)001:2130: ba'i phyag rgya byas te sngags lan gsum brjod pas
NK024(ya)001:2131: mdun gyi nam mkhar rgyal ba sras bcas 'thibs kyis
NK024(ya)001:2132: // spyan drang ngo // de yang las rim las /
NK024(ya)001:2133: sangs rgyas byin rlabs h+aum bsdus te //
NK024(ya)001:2134: mi bzad shin tu 'jigs pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:2135: zhe sdang rdo rje spyan 'bar ba //
NK024(ya)001:2139: dpang po'i lha rnams spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:2140: h+aum bzhis dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:2141: kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas bdag la thim pas bdag
NK024(ya)001:2142: gi lus 'od du gyur pa las /
NK024(ya)001:2143: zhes gsungs pas h+aum bzhis byin bsdu ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2144: h+aum zhes brjod pas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:2145: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK024(ya)001:2146: kyi byin rlabs thams cad 'od zer gyi tshul du
NK024(ya)001:2147: bsdu / yang h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od zer thams cad bdag la bsdu /
NK024(ya)001:2148: yang h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od zer des bdag gi
NK024(ya)001:2149: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib bag chags thams
NK024(ya)001:2150: cad ba mo la nyi zer phog pa bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:2151: sbyangs / yang h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces brjod pas rang
NK024(ya)001:2152: zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag g.yas rdo
NK024(ya)001:2153: rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub gdengs pa 'jigs pa'i sdang
NK024(ya)001:2154: mig bgegs la lta ba'i rkang mthil gnyis dang thugs
NK024(ya)001:2155: kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:2156: rgya gram 'bar ba h+aum gis mtshan pa re res
NK024(ya)001:2157: sbyangs / mtshan par gyur / rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:2158: rdo rje gsor zhing mi 'gro ba'i bgegs la bka' basgo'o //
NK024(ya)001:2160: bka' bsgo ba g.yung gi gsung 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:2163: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2164: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2165: bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis bdag rdo rje slob
NK024(ya)001:2166: dpon che ge mos slob ma che ge mo la
NK024(ya)001:2167: sogs pa sems can thamsacada kyi bla na med pa'i
NK024(ya)001:2168: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:2169: sa phyogs 'dir dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rgyal po
NK024(ya)001:2170: 'dus pa chen po mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:2172: sa 'di la gnas pa'i sa bdag pho mo dang /
NK024(ya)001:2174: rig sngags 'chang ba rgan po dang /
NK024(ya)001:2176: de la sogs pa'i 'khor rigs ngan du gtogs pa
NK024(ya)001:2177: thams cad bdag cag gi sgrub pa 'di la gegs
NK024(ya)001:2178: dang bar gcod ma byed par sgrub pa 'di ma
NK024(ya)001:2179: thon gyi bar du gnas gzhan du dengs shig /
NK024(ya)001:2180: gang dag mi 'gro ba de dag ni dpal rdo
NK024(ya)001:2181: rje h+aum zhes bya ba spyan rab tu 'bar bas
NK024(ya)001:2182: / mgo bo tshal pa brgya ru 'gas par 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:2183: zhes brjod cing rol mo dang bcas te dkar dmar gtor ma phyir bskyal /
NK024(ya)001:2185: rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu 'khrol /
NK024(ya)001:2186: yungs kar gyis bgegs la gtor bas 'jig rten gyi
NK024(ya)001:2187: khams thams cad khro bo'i sprul pas nam mkha' gang
NK024(ya)001:2189: tshur 'dus pas khro bo'i gur du bsam la khro bo'i rol mtshams kyis bsrung /
NK024(ya)001:2190: spyan las ye shes kyi me byung bas me'i gur du gyur par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:2191: spro na rdo rje rgya gram gyi 'gros bya /
NK024(ya)001:2192: gom pa'i 'og dang phyogs mtshams thams cad rdo rje rgya gram gyi gur gyis gtams par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:2194: de nas rang gi gnas su lha mo'i mdun du 'dug la zhes 'byung bas /
NK024(ya)001:2195: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su brjid bag dang ldan par
NK024(ya)001:2196: 'dug la lag g.yas rdo rje dang bcas pas mthe
NK024(ya)001:2197: bong gis mathe'u chung mnan pa'i tri shu la'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:2198: rgyas sa la bsnun pa ltar bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2199: g.yon dril bu bar mtshams su 'khrol ba dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:2200: sa lha bar snang la gnas par gdong phyogs te /
NK024(ya)001:2201: ji ltar che mchog rdo rje yis //
NK024(ya)001:2202: dpung bzhi bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK024(ya)001:2203: rgyal srid chos kyi dpung btsugs pa //
NK024(ya)001:2204: de bzhin du ni bdag gis kyang //
NK024(ya)001:2205: nges par bya phyir dkyil 'khor bri //
NK024(ya)001:2206: sa yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2207: rat+na p+aa sham sid+d+hi ku ru sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:2208: zhes lan gsum brjod de phyag rgya sa la bsnun pas //
NK024(ya)001:2209: sa'i lha mo dgyes bzhin sa la thim pas sa
NK024(ya)001:2210: gzhi rin po che sna tshogs pa'i rang bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:2211: bsam mo // de rnams kyi don ni las rim gyi gong gi 'phros las bshad pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:2212: rkang mthil thugs la mthing nag h+aum //
NK024(ya)001:2213: gsang sngags rdo rje gom par bcas //
NK024(ya)001:2214: khro bo yungs kar phyogs bcur 'phro //'og dang phyogs
NK024(ya)001:2215: mtshams rgya gram gur //'bar ba me yis phyogs mtshams
NK024(ya)001:2216: bskor // rang gi rang gnas brjid bag gis //'dug ste rin chen blang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:2217: phyag rgya tri shul gnyis mnan te //
NK024(ya)001:2219: lha mo rang bzhin gnyis med phyir //'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis 'od khyab pas //
NK024(ya)001:2220: thams cad rin chen ngo bo ste //
NK024(ya)001:2221: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:2222: brtan bya dngos grub mchog tu 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:2224: bzhi pa sa dbang du bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2225: sa gzhi dngos grub can de bar chod kyi dbang du mi btang ba'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:2226: zangs sam shing dmar po la phur pa rtse mo
NK024(ya)001:2227: la zla gam pa cig byas pa zhig rang gi
NK024(ya)001:2228: mdun du phur gdan la btsugs la /
NK024(ya)001:2229: bdag zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka'i h+aum las pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:2230: k+ai la ya phata dzah brjod pa las byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:2231: khro bo sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi
NK024(ya)001:2232: pa / phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis kyis pad+ma dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:2234: sku smad dbang gi phur pa la zla gam can zhig tu yod pa gsal bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:2235: h+aum pad+ma k+ai la ya phata dzahzhesa brjod pas thugs
NK024(ya)001:2236: ka'i khro bo phyir phyungs te phur pa la thim
NK024(ya)001:2237: / sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab ste /
NK024(ya)001:2239: rdo rje'i phyag rgyas phur pa'i gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK024(ya)001:2240: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:2241: de bzhin du w+aa ka dang tsit+ta sogs 'agre'o //
NK024(ya)001:2242: pad+ma dbang gi khro mchog chags pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:2243: ma lus dbang du sdud pa'i las mdzad pa //'dzam bu gling gi ye shes pa 'di dag /
NK024(ya)001:2244: bdag gi byang chub grogs su gyur par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:2245: ces bstod cing phrin las bcol //
NK024(ya)001:2246: bdag zhe sdang rdo rje'i bsam gtan dang ldan pas
NK024(ya)001:2247: lag gnyis kyis phur bu 'dril zhing dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:2249: pad+ma k+ai li k+ai la ya p+aa sham ma na ye w+aa sham ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2250: zhes brjod pas phur pa lhar gsal ba dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:2251: gyi dbus su btab pa de las 'od zer dmar
NK024(ya)001:2252: po 'phros pas sa gzhi la thim pas sa gzhi
NK024(ya)001:2253: bdag gi dbang du gyur par bsam ste /
NK024(ya)001:2255: dngos grub dbang du bya ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:2256: zangs sogs phur bu zla gam la //
NK024(ya)001:2257: h+aum las byung ba'i dbang mchog khro //
NK024(ya)001:2258: r+aa ga'i mdog 'dra zla gam rtse //
NK024(ya)001:2260: sdang mig phyag bzhii nges bsam ste //
NK024(ya)001:2261: sku gsung byin rlabs dbus su sbyar //'od kyis thams cad bsdus byas la //
NK024(ya)001:2262: bdag gir gyur pa'i sa dag ni //
NK024(ya)001:2263: las thams cad la shis par gyur //
NK024(ya)001:2265: lnga pa sa sbyang ba la bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:2267: sbyang ba las me sngags phyag rgya //
NK024(ya)001:2268: ti nga nge 'dzin gyis dag par sbyangs //
NK024(ya)001:2270: dang po las dang bya bas sbyang ba la dang po lto 'phye brtag pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:2272: phyogs bzhi theg dgu bu'i byang shar nas /
NK024(ya)001:2274: dpe rnying gcig la phyogs bzhi theg dgu bu'i byang
NK024(ya)001:2275: par byas nas zhes 'dug kyang dpe rgyun ma dag
NK024(ya)001:2276: pa 'dra ste / phyogs bzhi stegs bu'i byang shar nas zhes pa 'chol ba 'dra bar snang /
NK024(ya)001:2277: gang ltar yang lag len ni /
NK024(ya)001:2278: sa bzung gi phur pa'i lha bdag gi thugs kar bstim zhing phur pa dben par bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:2279: lto 'phye brtag tshul rgyas par gzhan las shes shing /
NK024(ya)001:2280: 'dir bsdu na stegs bu'i shar nas brtsams te dpyid gsum stag yos 'brug /
NK024(ya)001:2283: dgun gsum phag byi glang ste zla ba gang shar la mgo gtad cing /
NK024(ya)001:2284: de'i mdun zur du mjug ma gnas so //
NK024(ya)001:2285: des gling khams thams cad khyab na'ang sa gcig tu bsdu ste /
NK024(ya)001:2286: khru gru bzhi'i tshad tsam brkos pas 'thus shing /
NK024(ya)001:2287: de yang g.yas rin po che bzung ba'i thad lto ba nas brus pas dngos grub thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:2288: de las gzhan mgo las bla ma /
NK024(ya)001:2292: de yang ji ltar bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:2293: sa bdag lto 'phye la mchod gtor phul nas /
NK024(ya)001:2294: de'i lus lto ba'i thad du bsdus te nam mkhar
NK024(ya)001:2295: bteg la me tog gtor phud kyis mchod cing bden
NK024(ya)001:2296: pa brdar / thog mar de'i lto ba'i thad nas
NK024(ya)001:2297: cung zad brus pa'i sa phud kyis de bzhin gshegs
NK024(ya)001:2298: pa rnams la mchod cing phyogs kun tu gtor bar
NK024(ya)001:2299: pa brdar / bya'o // brtag pa dngos la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:2303: der rgya ji tsam 'dod pa brkos la gong ltar
NK024(ya)001:2304: ngan pa byung na yang bzang po byung zhing sngar
NK024(ya)001:2305: bas lhag pa ni zhes 'dug pa ma dag pa
NK024(ya)001:2306: 'dra'o // lag len ni gong du brkos pa'i shul
NK024(ya)001:2307: nas 'og gi chu'am rdo la thug par ji tsam
NK024(ya)001:2308: 'dod par brkos kyang skyon med la /
NK024(ya)001:2309: yang na rgya dpangs khru gang gru bzhi'i tshad du brko /
NK024(ya)001:2310: de la gong du sa gzhi spyi mtshan du brtag
NK024(ya)001:2311: pa'i skabs las rim gyi lung drangs pa ltar bzang
NK024(ya)001:2312: ngan gyi ltas blta zhing brkos pa'i shul sa ros
NK024(ya)001:2313: ma khengs na ngan zhing lhag na bzang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:2314: de ni sa sas brtag pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:2315: gnyis pa chus brtag pa ni sa brkos pa'i nang
NK024(ya)001:2316: du chu blug ste gom pa brgya phyin nas 'ongs
NK024(ya)001:2317: pas bri tshabs che na ngan /
NK024(ya)001:2318: ma bri ba'i khar ri mo legs pa'i gzugs ni
NK024(ya)001:2319: bzang ba ste chus brtag pa'o //'di la glan bsod
NK024(ya)001:2320: nams mgon pos / sa brkos pa'i nang du chu
NK024(ya)001:2321: blug ste las mkhan nyid yi ge brgya pa bgrang
NK024(ya)001:2322: zhing phar la gom pa lnga bcu phyin /
NK024(ya)001:2323: tshur la lnga bcu yongs la zhes gsungs pa /
NK024(ya)001:2324: gom pa brgyas brtag dgos par da lta phyag len phal cher la nyis brgya yong 'dug pas /
NK024(ya)001:2325: las rim gyi mchan bur yang glan gyi gsung ltar 'dug pas legs 'dra snyam ste dpyad par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2327: lto 'phye'i dus tshod gzhan shes bya //
NK024(ya)001:2328: ma nor phyogs nas las rnams brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:2329: rgya dpangs khru gang gru bzhi'i dbus //
NK024(ya)001:2330: bshad pa'i mtshan nyid shin tu brtag /
NK024(ya)001:2331: chus bkang gom pa brgya lta bya //
NK024(ya)001:2333: de ltar sa bskos pa'i shul du rdzu bum du rdzas nyer lnga bcug nas sba ste /
NK024(ya)001:2334: bum pa de a las zla ba tram las rin
NK024(ya)001:2335: po che'i mchod sdong rang gi ji ltar 'dod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:2336: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bar bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:2337: de ltar yang las rim las /
NK024(ya)001:2338: bzang dang bkra shis rin chen sa //'bru sna bcas gzhug 'thas par brdung //
NK024(ya)001:2340: lto 'phye brtag pa deng sang gtsug lag khang sogs brtsig pa'i tshe ma gtogs mdzad mkhan dkon la /
NK024(ya)001:2341: de'i rgyu mtshan dkyil 'khor stegs bu ched du mi
NK024(ya)001:2342: brtsig par zhal ba'am shing stegs la mdzad pa shas
NK024(ya)001:2343: che la / de yang grub na phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyur 'gyur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2344: ma grub kyang chad pa'i skyon med la /
NK024(ya)001:2345: bum gter 'jug pa zhal bar ched du bru mi
NK024(ya)001:2346: thub kyang shing stegs la 'og tu 'jog thub cing
NK024(ya)001:2347: / zhal stegs gang la mdzad kyang bum gter bsham ste dmigs pas bcug cing /
NK024(ya)001:2348: slar gnas khang gi go babs gang der bcug na
NK024(ya)001:2349: legs par mngon zhing de ga'i phyag len kyang yod
NK024(ya)001:2350: / rtsa bar lto 'phye brtag cing bru ba'i dbang gis bum gter bcug zin rjes /
NK024(ya)001:2351: de nas ji tsam 'dod pa'i stegs bu brtsigs la /
NK024(ya)001:2352: slar yang rdzas nyer lnga dang ba byung lnga sbyar
NK024(ya)001:2353: bas byug cing me long gi ngos ltar bya'o //'di
NK024(ya)001:2354: la go ma ye btang ba zhes gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:2356: gzhan sel dang don gnyer gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:2357: gzhan sel phung po lnga rang dag nas /
NK024(ya)001:2358: don gnyer sku lnga ma btsal bar thob par bya ba'i phyir 'bru lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2359: dbang po lnga dag nas phrin las lnga thob par bya ba'i phyir spos lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2360: yul lnga dag nas yon tan lnga thob pa'i phyir rin chen lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2361: rnam shes lnga dag nas ye shes lnga thob pa'i phyir snying po lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2362: 'dod yon lnga dag nas gsung lnga thob pa'i phyir sman lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2363: khams lnga dag nas rigs lnga thob pa'i phyir bdud rtsi lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2364: de'i steng du ba byung lnga ste sum cu so lnga'o //
NK024(ya)001:2365: rdzas de dag gi ngos 'dzin tshul cung zad mi 'dra tsam re 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:2366: rgyal ba g.yung gis nas sran gro 'bras til dkar te 'bru lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2367: gur gum gla rtsi tsan+dana dkar dmar ga bur te spos lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2368: byu ru mu tig mu men sbur len g.yu dang lnga ni rin po che lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2369: tsh+wa bu ram sbrang a 'bras mar te snying po lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2370: kan+da ka ri sle tre shu dag dkar po shu zur snying zho sha ste sman lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2371: byang sems dkar dmar dri chen dri chu sha chen te bdud rtsi lngar gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:2372: las rim gyi mchan bur de dang mi 'dra ba zhig kyang gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:2373: yang na rgya gzhung ltar bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2374: yang na g.yung ston par 'khrul pa mi mnga' bas 'di ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2376: zho 'o ma mar dri chu lci ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:2377: de rnams kyang lnga tshan so sor rim gyis sam cig car ba ko'i srab 'thug tsam 'byug go //
NK024(ya)001:2378: de ltar bgyid dgos par rgyud gsang snying las /
NK024(ya)001:2379: 'bru lnga spos lnga rin chen lnga //
NK024(ya)001:2380: snying po lnga dang sman lnga dang //
NK024(ya)001:2381: bdud rtsi lngas ni rab mnyam la //
NK024(ya)001:2384: tshad dang mnyam pa'i rgya byas la //'jim pa ba spus mnyam par bya //
NK024(ya)001:2385: nas sran gro 'bras til dkar po //
NK024(ya)001:2386: rang bzhin sku lnga thob phyir yang //
NK024(ya)001:2387: dag pa phung po lnga ru shes //
NK024(ya)001:2388: gur gum la gu tsan+dana gnyis //
NK024(ya)001:2389: gran ti ka yi dri 'di dag /
NK024(ya)001:2390: phrin las yul gyi rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:2391: thob phyir nges par tshang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:2392: byu ru gser dngul mi tig dang //
NK024(ya)001:2393: rin po che ni 'byung ba'i dngos //
NK024(ya)001:2394: zhing sogs yon tan thob phyir sbyar //
NK024(ya)001:2395: lan tsh+wa sbrang rtsi bu ram mar //
NK024(ya)001:2397: rnam shes ye shes rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:2398: nges pa nyid du bzung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:2399: ha sa de ba bri ha ti //
NK024(ya)001:2400: se ta kan+da ka ri dang //
NK024(ya)001:2401: a pra tsit+ta sman gyi mchog /
NK024(ya)001:2402: dbang po dag pa gsung gi mchog /
NK024(ya)001:2403: nyi zla chu sa m+aam sar bcas //
NK024(ya)001:2404: rnam pa lnga yi m+aam sa ni /
NK024(ya)001:2405: khams kyi rang bzhin rigs lnga ste //
NK024(ya)001:2406: sum cus rab mnyam bstim par bya //
NK024(ya)001:2409: la gu zhes pa gla rtsi /
NK024(ya)001:2411: ha sa de ba rgya mtsho lbu ba /
NK024(ya)001:2413: se ta shu dag dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:2415: a bra tsit+ta snying zho sha /
NK024(ya)001:2416: nyi zla byang sems dkar dmar /
NK024(ya)001:2419: m+aam sa sha chen rnams yin par gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:2420: go ma ye 'di rnams rgyud dang man ngag las
NK024(ya)001:2421: bshad pas stegs bu mi brtsig kyang byugs na legs
NK024(ya)001:2422: so // gnyis pa mes sbyang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2424: mtshan ma gang byung yang skabs 'dir zhi ba'i sbyin sreg bya ste mes sbyang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:2425: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun par /
NK024(ya)001:2427: sa'i mtshan nyid bzang ngan ji ltar 'dug kyang rdo
NK024(ya)001:2428: rje slob dpon gyis me lha spyan drangs pa yan
NK024(ya)001:2429: chad byas la / las mkhan gyis zhi ba'i sbyin sreg skabs 'dir rgyas par btang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:2430: zhes gsungs pas legs nyes ji ltar yang mes sbyang
NK024(ya)001:2431: ba'i sa bcad mi stongs pa'i phyir sbyin sreg bya
NK024(ya)001:2432: bar gsungs la / g.yung ston chen pos ni sa'i
NK024(ya)001:2433: mtshan ltas ngan na bya bar gsungs pa'i shugs las
NK024(ya)001:2434: bzang na mi dgos par gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:2435: de ltar yang las rim las /
NK024(ya)001:2436: kun nas mtshan ma ngan gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:2437: gzhan du bgrod dam zhi ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:2438: me yis rab tu dag par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:2440: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2441: de nas rang khro bo zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal
NK024(ya)001:2442: ba'i lag g.yas kyi sor mo lnga la nyi ma'i
NK024(ya)001:2443: dkyil 'khor la h+aum mthing kha re re bsam /
NK024(ya)001:2444: de las 'od zer 'phros shing 'dus pa las rdo
NK024(ya)001:2445: rje rtse lnga h+aum mthing gas mtshan pa re rer
NK024(ya)001:2447: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:2448: ces lan gsum brjod cing lag pa sa la lan
NK024(ya)001:2449: gsum brdab pas rdo rje dang h+aum gi 'od kyis
NK024(ya)001:2450: sa'i nyes skyon thams cad dag nas sa gzhi ye
NK024(ya)001:2451: shes rang snang gi sa gzhir gyur par bsam ste
NK024(ya)001:2453: 'bring gyur lag g.yas mthil sor la //
NK024(ya)001:2454: nyi ma 'bru lnga h+aum lnga mthing //
NK024(ya)001:2455: rtse lnga rdo rje h+aum bcas bsam //
NK024(ya)001:2456: sngags kyis lan gsum sa la bskul //'od kyis ma lus sbyang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2458: thams cad dag par 'gyur pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:2459: phyag rgya sngags kyis sbyang zhes bya //
NK024(ya)001:2461: bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:2465: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyi ye nas rnam par
NK024(ya)001:2466: dag pas sa dang sar 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa sogs
NK024(ya)001:2467: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK024(ya)001:2468: skye med stong pa nyid do //
NK024(ya)001:2469: de'i don dran bzhin du ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:2470: chos kun rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK024(ya)001:2471: bdag kyang rang bzhin rnam par dag /
NK024(ya)001:2472: ces pa skye med stong nyid do //
NK024(ya)001:2474: de ltar yang las rim las /
NK024(ya)001:2475: thams cad rang sems rnam pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:2476: mtshan nyid med pa'i phyag rgya ni //
NK024(ya)001:2477: nam mkha' lta bur rang bzhin gnas //'khrul snang sa
NK024(ya)001:2478: dang sar 'dzin ni //'khrul chos chos can la gnas
NK024(ya)001:2479: phyir // dag par bltas na mtshan nyid med //
NK024(ya)001:2480: rjes su bskul bar byed pa'i sngags //
NK024(ya)001:2482: rang rig stong pa'i ye shes la //
NK024(ya)001:2483: gzung dang 'dzin pa gnyis med phyir //
NK024(ya)001:2484: spyod yul yongs su dag par bya //
NK024(ya)001:2488: skad cig ma las rang gi rig pa h+aum du gyur par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:2489: de'i 'og tu 'byung ba rim brtsegs la zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs par bskyed la /
NK024(ya)001:2490: sa dang sar 'dzin gyi rtog pa kun rdzob lha'i rang bzhin du sbyang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:2491: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni h+aum zhes brjod pas /
NK024(ya)001:2492: skad cig gis rang rig yi ge h+aum sngon po
NK024(ya)001:2493: las rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa lte ba
NK024(ya)001:2494: la h+aum gis mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:2495: h+aum de las 'og phyogs su e yam ram bam lam rnams 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:2497: yi ge de rnams las 'od zer 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:2498: sems can thams cad kyi 'byung ba lnga dang ngar 'dzin gyi rtog pa sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:2500: tshur 'dus te e las nam mkha' mthing nag gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK024(ya)001:2501: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sngon po gzhu'i dbyibs can ba dan gyis mtshan pa /
NK024(ya)001:2502: ram las me'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum dmar po /
NK024(ya)001:2503: bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor zlum po dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:2504: lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi ser por gyur /
NK024(ya)001:2505: de'i steng du b+h+rum zhes brjod cing rdo rje las
NK024(ya)001:2506: b+h+r+aum dkar po zhig 'phros te 'byung lnga'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:2507: la phog pas thams cad 'od du zhu /
NK024(ya)001:2508: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shu d+d+he dz+ny+aa na badz+ra tsakra ces brjod pas /
NK024(ya)001:2509: nam mkha'i khams dang chos kyi dbyings thams cad khyab
NK024(ya)001:2510: pa'i 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor rten dang brten
NK024(ya)001:2512: sngags dmigs 'di rnams g.yung ston chen po'i gsung mdor bsdus te bris pa yin cing /
NK024(ya)001:2513: 'on kyang g.yung gis zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka
NK024(ya)001:2514: nas 'phro bar gsung mod kyang 'dir mtshan med kyi
NK024(ya)001:2515: sbyangs zin pas rgya gzhung ltar legs pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:2517: rang rig skad cig h+aum bsam ste //
NK024(ya)001:2518: ye shes snying po h+aum nyid las //
NK024(ya)001:2519: rtse lnga rdo rje h+aum bcas pa //
NK024(ya)001:2520: yongs gyur nam mkha' e gzugs can //
NK024(ya)001:2521: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:2522: dran bskyod rlung ni yam sngon po //
NK024(ya)001:2523: sa bon chu ste bam dkar po //
NK024(ya)001:2524: ma lus gzhir gyur gser mdog lam //
NK024(ya)001:2525: skad cig sgra med dmar ser ram //
NK024(ya)001:2526: ma nges kun gzhi sna tshogs b+h+r+aum //
NK024(ya)001:2527: rgyas dang 'bring la sogs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:2528: sna tshogs rgyan ldan rin chen khams //
NK024(ya)001:2529: ji ltar 'gyur ba bzhin du sgom //
NK024(ya)001:2532: drug pa sa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2533: bdun pa bsrung ba ni dkyil 'khor sta gon gyi skabs su bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2534: zhes gsungs pa ltar zur hwam thams cad mkhyen pa
NK024(ya)001:2535: sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi phyag len brgyud pa rin po
NK024(ya)001:2536: che'i 'di'i lugs la 'og tu rnal 'byor chen po
NK024(ya)001:2537: tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod kyi sngon 'gro'i
NK024(ya)001:2538: skabs cho ga de gnyis rgyas par mdzad pa dang
NK024(ya)001:2539: / lha lhag gnas kyi sta gon dang bum pa
NK024(ya)001:2540: slob ma'i sta gon yang de'i dus su mdzad par
NK024(ya)001:2541: / bzhed / sngon 'gror sgo 'byed phyag rdor dang
NK024(ya)001:2542: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bris la sgrub mchod byas
NK024(ya)001:2544: lha mi nyan rang byang sems rnams la dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:2545: rang gzhung ltar bris te sgrub mchod byas te sdom
NK024(ya)001:2546: pa dang dbang bskur sogs so so'i skabs thob ltar
NK024(ya)001:2547: bya / kri yog sogs phyi rgyud rnams la yang so sor mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:2548: rgyud sde gong ma gsum la sgrub chen ltar spros pa cher bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2549: sgrub khongs der dbang rdzogs par bskur bar mdzad pa sogs kyi phyag len 'dug pa /
NK024(ya)001:2550: 'phral 'jug pa bde zhing dngos gtsang la don dang mthun par sems /
NK024(ya)001:2551: kahthoga rdor bzang gi chog khrigs su bshad gzhi dang
NK024(ya)001:2552: spros pa shin tu che zhing ngo mtshar ba snang
NK024(ya)001:2553: mod kyang / sa byin rlabs dang bsrung ba sogs
NK024(ya)001:2554: skabs 'dir byas pas rgyal tho sgo byang dam sri
NK024(ya)001:2555: ma tram sogs thams cad de'i khog tu yod gshis
NK024(ya)001:2556: thog ma nas spros pa che zhing byed rgyu mang
NK024(ya)001:2557: mod kyang / ba dang / de mtshungs lha mi
NK024(ya)001:2558: nas bzung dkyil 'khor thams cad la lha sta gon
NK024(ya)001:2559: dang bum pa sta gon sogs sdebs su mdzad cing
NK024(ya)001:2560: mod kyang / ba dang / / rnal 'byor chen
NK024(ya)001:2561: po'i khyad chos 'ga' zhig kyang thog ma nas yar
NK024(ya)001:2562: slebs pas nyan rang nas bzung ste bstan par ma
NK024(ya)001:2563: zhugs pa 'ga' la gsang sgrog gi nyes par 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:2565: dkyil 'khor thams cad sdebs su bris te dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:2566: yang lhan cig tu byed pa 'dra zhig gi sgrub
NK024(ya)001:2567: mchod dbang bskur thams cad cung zad mi bde bar
NK024(ya)001:2568: mngon / khyad par sgo 'byed phyag rdor la sgrub
NK024(ya)001:2569: mchod sogs zur tsam yang med par sngon 'gro'i tshul
NK024(ya)001:2570: gyis dbang thod rgal du bskur tshul shin tu mi
NK024(ya)001:2572: 'dir ni zur lugs bzhin bri bar bya ba la /
NK024(ya)001:2573: sa chog gi rtsa ba'i sa bcad drug pa byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:2574: bdun pa bsrung ba gnyis tshogs chen gyi sta gon dus 'byung bas 'dir btang snyoms su bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:2575: gzhan yang rang lugs skyi ston tshe ring dbang pos
NK024(ya)001:2576: bsam rtser mdo dbang gnang dus nyin dang po rang
NK024(ya)001:2577: la rgyal tho dam sri sogs gnang 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:2578: rjes 'jug 'dras zin bris mdzad par yang de ltar snang mod /
NK024(ya)001:2579: de lta na yang de skabs kahthoga lugs kho na
NK024(ya)001:2580: dar bas gzhan gyi lad zlos lta bur snang zhing
NK024(ya)001:2581: rang gzhung dang ma mthun la /
NK024(ya)001:2582: 'on kyang rnam pa gcig tu lha sta gon sogs
NK024(ya)001:2583: tshogs chen dkyil 'khor gyi spros pa mtha' dag ma
NK024(ya)001:2586: sri gnon rnams mdzad pa skyon cher med cing /
NK024(ya)001:2587: khyad par dam sri gnon pa mi rung ba med de /
NK024(ya)001:2588: glan ston bsod nams mgon po'i chog khrigs las /
NK024(ya)001:2589: sa bcad brgyad pa bshad pa'i rjes su phur pa drug skor gyi dam sri'i mgo brdungs te /
NK024(ya)001:2590: de yang ngag nus dang ldan pa'i sngags pa gnyis
NK024(ya)001:2591: kyi rdo rje phur pa'i phrin chog tshang ba zhig
NK024(ya)001:2592: gyer nas / tshogs tha ma'i dus su bstan pa
NK024(ya)001:2593: la gnod pa'i dgra dang bgegs gang rung gi lid+ga
NK024(ya)001:2595: them pa'i phyi rol du dong gru gsum pa brus par mnan la drag po'i bro bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2597: kho bo'i bla ma khyab bdag sman lung pa chen pos bdag smin par mdzad dus /
NK024(ya)001:2598: spyir bshad pas mtha' bcad de phyag len dngos zur lugs sor gnas gong gsal ltar mdzad pas na /
NK024(ya)001:2599: 'dir yang bla ma dam pa'i man ngag gi rjes
NK024(ya)001:2600: su 'brangs te 'chad par byed dgos pas sa bcad
NK024(ya)001:2605: cha rkyen bsdus shing slob ma rnams //
NK024(ya)001:2606: nang du 'dus la gleng gzhi bshad //
NK024(ya)001:2607: gegs brgyad bshad la thugs dam bskang //'di dag dbang gi sngon 'gro yin //
NK024(ya)001:2608: zhes gsungs pas thog mar cha rkyen bsdu ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2610: 'byor pa'i yo byad tshang ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:2611: bde ba chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK024(ya)001:2613: khu byug rol pa'i rgyud phyi ma las /
NK024(ya)001:2614: kun tu rgyu dang gal phyi dang //
NK024(ya)001:2615: zla rgyas zla khrom lnga gsum rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:2616: sgrub pa tshogs kyi rdzas su bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:2619: mda' dang dar dang ral gri dang //
NK024(ya)001:2620: thugs rje'i rgyun thag phur bu dang //'phan dang bla bre rgyal mtshan dang //
NK024(ya)001:2621: do shal rdzas rnams bsdus te bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:2623: gzhung nas 'byung ba bzhin bsham ste dbang gi bum pa lnga /
NK024(ya)001:2624: las bum dang phyi nang gsang ba'i rdzas rnams tshang bar bsags la /
NK024(ya)001:2625: zhes 'byung bas gong du yo byad phun tshogs kyi skabs ltar bsag go //
NK024(ya)001:2626: phyi 'jig rten pa'i thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2629: byin gyis brlab la gser skyems rgyas par btang /
NK024(ya)001:2630: khyad par gzhi bdag la gser skyems dang gtor ma byin la sdong grogs gzhol lo //
NK024(ya)001:2631: zhes pa ni snga 'gyur gyi ring lugs las ji
NK024(ya)001:2632: ltar 'byung ba bzhin thog mtha' bar mtshams thams cad
NK024(ya)001:2633: du lha bsangs rgyags rngan gser skyems sogs rgyas pa
NK024(ya)001:2634: yang yang bya'o // gtsang rigs kyi dpal mgon bdun
NK024(ya)001:2635: cu rtsa lnga la cha gsum btang la thugs dam
NK024(ya)001:2636: yang yang bya'o // bskang / 'jig rten gyi lha
NK024(ya)001:2637: 'dre thams cad la phud gtor sbyin la sgrub pa
NK024(ya)001:2638: chen po 'di la zhugs nas ma thon gyi bar
NK024(ya)001:2639: la bar chad ma byed par bka' bsgo /
NK024(ya)001:2641: sngon 'gror cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bris nas dbang
NK024(ya)001:2642: ma tshar gyi bar du nyin re bzhin cha gsum
NK024(ya)001:2643: gyi cho ga byed dgos pas der tshang /
NK024(ya)001:2644: khyad par du mgon po dang lha mo la sgrub pa'i sdong grogs zhu /
NK024(ya)001:2645: dkon mchog gsum la gsol ba drag tu gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:2646: zhes pa ni spyir bka' gter gyi ma mgon gang rigs mchod pas kyang khyab mod de /
NK024(ya)001:2647: 'dir ni mdo mgon legs ldan lcam dral gyi gtor bsngo mdzad srol yod /
NK024(ya)001:2648: gtso bor dkon mchog gsum la bar gcod med cing
NK024(ya)001:2649: smin grol 'byung ba'i gsol ba kha zhe med par
NK024(ya)001:2650: gdab bo // nang gi thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2651: cha gsum dri chab khyer la tshogs las bya //
NK024(ya)001:2652: zhes bya ba ni tshugs nas ma grol gyi bar
NK024(ya)001:2653: nub re bzhin zhi khro'i phrin las tshogs dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:2655: mchod pa mdos kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs la phyi cha
NK024(ya)001:2656: mthun sprul pa'i ma mo gzhung bzhin mchod la thugs
NK024(ya)001:2657: dam bskul / nang ting nge 'dzin gyi ma mo
NK024(ya)001:2658: yig 'bru'i sgo nas bskyed la ye shes pa spyan
NK024(ya)001:2659: dam bskul / drangs bstim / mchod bstod 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab /
NK024(ya)001:2660: gsang ba thig le'i ma mo tsan+da li'i gnas kyis rtsa rlung gcun /
NK024(ya)001:2661: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi ma mo mkha' klong gnyis su med pa'i ngang du la ba zla /
NK024(ya)001:2662: srung ma thugs dam can la bar chad bsrung bar bka' bsgo bya /
NK024(ya)001:2663: ma 'dres pa bsre ba'i cho ga bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2665: phyi'i ma mo skong phyir rgyas par na ma mo srid pa bem mdos lta bu grub na bya /
NK024(ya)001:2666: de ltar min kyang ma mo khrag mdos sam /
NK024(ya)001:2667: sngags srung e ka dz+aa ti'am /
NK024(ya)001:2668: re ma ti'i bskang mdos sam /
NK024(ya)001:2669: chos rgyal dbang po'i sde'i dag snang srid pa spyi
NK024(ya)001:2670: mdos lta bu zhig nges par bsham dgos shing tshogs
NK024(ya)001:2671: chen gyi dus kyang byang shar du mdos raka ces
NK024(ya)001:2673: nang gi ma mo mchod bstod bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:2674: mngon rdzogs ma mo'i las gzhung bsrang thub na rab /
NK024(ya)001:2675: de min ye shes dang 'jig rten gyi ma mo
NK024(ya)001:2676: thams cad rdo rje khro mo rag gdong ma nyid
NK024(ya)001:2677: la 'dus shing gsang sngags snying po'i bstan srung gi
NK024(ya)001:2678: gtso bor bzhugs pas 'di nyid kyi mchod bstod la
NK024(ya)001:2679: 'bad pas 'thus par kho bo sems so //
NK024(ya)001:2680: gsang ba dang rang bzhin gyi ma mo gcun thabs
NK024(ya)001:2681: ni a nu dang a ti'i rnal 'byor zab mo
NK024(ya)001:2683: gzhan yang dam chos skyong ba'i srung ma spyi sger
NK024(ya)001:2684: thams cad la tshogs bskang rgyas par bya zhing phrin
NK024(ya)001:2685: las gzhol / dam ma 'dres pa bsre ba'i cho
NK024(ya)001:2686: ga yang tshogs chen gyi skabs su shes par bya
NK024(ya)001:2688: de nas zab cing rgya che ba'i chos bshad de /
NK024(ya)001:2689: zhes slob ma 'dus pa la chos bshad skabs 'dir
NK024(ya)001:2690: byed par bshad kyang 'og tu gleng gzhi bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:2691: dang / gegs brgyad bshad pa ni sngon 'gro'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:2692: dus su 'byung ba ltar de dang sbyar te 'chad
NK024(ya)001:2693: pas rtogs par bya'o //'og nas 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:2694: mtha' dag gi sa'i cho ga rnams 'dis khyab la
NK024(ya)001:2695: dang / / lha sta gon bya rgyud yan la ma gsungs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2696: thig tshon byin rlabs tshogs chen 'dus pa'i skabs su
NK024(ya)001:2697: rgyas par 'byung zhing dkyil 'khor gzhan rnams la mi
NK024(ya)001:2698: gsal yang / thig tshon byin gyis ma brlabs par brir mi rung zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2699: 'on kyang las thig kho na ye thig tu byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2700: tshon byin gyis brlab pa'i tshul mdor bsdus par 'dod na /
NK024(ya)001:2701: las thig gi srad bu dkar chal la sbang du rung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:2702: tshon lnga rin po che'i snod du 'du byas te /
NK024(ya)001:2703: dbus su sngon po la h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:2707: byang du ljang gu la h+aa rnams rdo rje'i rwa
NK024(ya)001:2708: rtses bris la bkod pa'i mthar nyer spyod lnga bsham
NK024(ya)001:2709: pa'am yid mchod kyis kyang rung /
NK024(ya)001:2710: gong du lnga pa sa sbyang ba la bzhi'i ting
NK024(ya)001:2711: nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba la gnyis kyi mtshan med
NK024(ya)001:2712: dang mtshan bcas kyi skabs su snang srid thams cad
NK024(ya)001:2713: dkyil 'khor du sgom pa'i tshe rang byung lhun grub
NK024(ya)001:2714: kyi dkyil 'khor chen por gyur zin pas /
NK024(ya)001:2715: de lta bu'i nga rgyal gnas bzhin pas thig tshon
NK024(ya)001:2716: byin brlab byas kyang mi rung ba ma yin mod
NK024(ya)001:2717: / 'on kyang skabs su babs pa rang thun mtshams
NK024(ya)001:2718: kyi lha rdo rje sems dpar lam gyis bltas la
NK024(ya)001:2719: de'i nga rgyal gyis thig tshon bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:2720: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:2721: steng du h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aa ste yig 'bru lngar
NK024(ya)001:2722: gyur / badz+ra sa ma ya dzahe h+ye hi /
NK024(ya)001:2723: lan gsum gyis rgyal ba sras bcas mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:2724: badz+ra tish+tha tish+tha gu h+ye sa ma ya dz+ny+aa na am gu sha dzah dzah lan gsum brjod pas /
NK024(ya)001:2725: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas byang sems kyi
NK024(ya)001:2726: chu rgyun ye shes kha dog lnga'i rang bzhin byung
NK024(ya)001:2727: / thig tshon la thim par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:2728: tshon gyi yig 'bru rnams srin lag gis mnye zhing thig skud 'phur ro //
NK024(ya)001:2729: de ltar byin gyis brlab pa'i las thig ye shes
NK024(ya)001:2730: kyi thig gi rang bzhin can des tshogs chen yan
NK024(ya)001:2731: chod kyi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi las thig bya /
NK024(ya)001:2732: byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshon de rnams kyis 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:2733: dkyil 'khor gang 'bri ba de rnams la 'dres par
NK024(ya)001:2734: bya'o // thig tshon gyi cho ga mdor bsdus pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:2735: de nas sngon 'gro phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bskur ba la /
NK024(ya)001:2737: phyag na rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thig le dbang gi rgyud las gsungs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2738: dpung bzang gi rgyud las gsungs pa'i cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis so //
NK024(ya)001:2739: ji ltar bri ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:2741: dang po dkyil 'khor ji tsam rigs par 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ser /
NK024(ya)001:2746: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ling tshe dgu'i dbus mthing /
NK024(ya)001:2752: mu khyud sogs sgo rta babs thams cad mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:2754: zur hwam sh+aaka 'byung gis phyag rdor gyi dbang logs su bkol ba'i dkyil 'khor bri tshul las /
NK024(ya)001:2755: dbus pad+ma 'dab bzhi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi rgya gram
NK024(ya)001:2756: rwa bzhi gang byas kyang rung zhes gsungs kyang phyag
NK024(ya)001:2757: len du snga ma ltar mdzad cing /
NK024(ya)001:2758: rtsibs phyogs mdog gam ser po gang bder mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:2759: glo 'bur gyi gru chad ljang gu dang phyi'i khyams phyogs mdog tu bri'o //
NK024(ya)001:2760: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i rtsig pa nang nas mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba /
NK024(ya)001:2761: mun pa dang glang rgyab nag po /
NK024(ya)001:2766: d+r+wa gzhi nag po d+r+wa phyed dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:2772: ljang ba pad+ma chos 'khor gdugs tog can /
NK024(ya)001:2776: rdo ra me ri sogs spyi ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:2777: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la lha snam ljang gu la phyogs skyong bcu /
NK024(ya)001:2778: pad+ma'i phyir khor yug nag po la 'byung po sde brgyad bgegs rigs kyi gnas so //
NK024(ya)001:2779: de gnyis la 'og nas 'byung ba'i lha'i mngon rtogs
NK024(ya)001:2780: dang mthun par phyag mtshan nam sa bon tshon spungs
NK024(ya)001:2783: dkyil 'khor bri ba zin nas de'i tha mar yan lag mchod pa /
NK024(ya)001:2795: chos skyong 'gro drug bgegs rnams la dkar gtor cha gsum dang zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:2797: 'di'i skabs kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis ka spyod rgyud yin
NK024(ya)001:2798: phyir zhal phyogs chen gyi nub tu gzigs par bsham
NK024(ya)001:2799: na sgom bde / 'on kyang gnas khang dang sbyar
NK024(ya)001:2800: ba'i rgyab ma yin pa'i gang bder bsham pa'am bla
NK024(ya)001:2801: ma'i khri dang zhal sprod du bya thub na sgom
NK024(ya)001:2802: na sgom bde / bde / dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i
NK024(ya)001:2803: me ri'i phyir byang shar du mtshams 'dzin gyi me
NK024(ya)001:2804: na sgom bde / bde / tog / shar du mchod yon /
NK024(ya)001:2810: byang du zhal zas rnams bkod legs su bsham /
NK024(ya)001:2811: phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor la dkar gtor zlum po
NK024(ya)001:2812: mtheb skyus bskor ba rgyan gyis brgyan pa zhig dang
NK024(ya)001:2813: / cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la cha dang po phyogs skyong mgon po rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:2814: cha gnyis pa 'byung po rnams la dkar gtor zlum po mtheb skyu bzhis bskor ba gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:2815: rigs drug dang bye brag yi dwags la bsil gtor cha /
NK024(ya)001:2816: cha gsum pa bgegs rigs la bgegs gtor phyag len bzhin bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:2818: nang gi sman gtor rak+ta tshogs dang bcas pa bsham ste phyi ltar phyag rdo nyid /
NK024(ya)001:2819: nang ltar rdo rje sems dpa' dang he ru ka dang chos skyong mgon po lcam dral lo //
NK024(ya)001:2820: zhes gsungs pas sman gtor rak+ta tshogs rnams dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:2821: gnyis kyi mchod pa'i yo byad du bsham kyang mi
NK024(ya)001:2822: 'gal mod / 'on kyang gong du zhi thung gi
NK024(ya)001:2823: cho ga byas ma thag yin pas der slar yang
NK024(ya)001:2824: rtsa ba gsum la mchod gtor tshogs dang bcas rgya
NK024(ya)001:2827: de nas gu gul gyis bum pa bsang /
NK024(ya)001:2828: dri chu bum rdzas mgul chings kha rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:2831: dkyil 'khor dang bla ma dang gzhan ji ltar 'os pa bsham zhing tsakli yang 'god do //
NK024(ya)001:2832: skyabs 'gro'i rten thub pa'i sku dang 'thor nas dang gser skyems yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:2833: snga dro gtor ma brgya rtsa dang chab gtor klu gtor yang btang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:2835: rin po che'i bum pa gnyis gu gul gyis bdug /
NK024(ya)001:2837: h+aum bzhi'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK024(ya)001:2840: nang gtsang po'i chu la sogs pa rgya mtshor 'bab
NK024(ya)001:2841: pa'i chus sum gnyis bkang dgos te drang srong mang
NK024(ya)001:2842: po'i khrus chu'i rta yod pas byin che gsung ngo
NK024(ya)001:2845: rnam rgyal la mgul chings sngon po dang rdo rje'i mtshan ma /
NK024(ya)001:2846: las bum la ljang gu dang rgya gram gyis mtshan ma bya /
NK024(ya)001:2847: ku sha dang rma bya'i mdongs kyis kha brgyan /
NK024(ya)001:2848: gnyis ka la gzungs rdor dang dung chos dri bzang gi chus bkang ba bzhag pa /
NK024(ya)001:2849: rnam rgyal phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor dbus su many+dzi'i khrir bkod /
NK024(ya)001:2850: las bum slob dpon gyi mdun du bsham /
NK024(ya)001:2851: dkyil 'khor gnyis la lha rnams kyi tsakli bkod par 'dir yang bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:2852: spyod rgyud rnam snang mngon byang las kyang de ltar
NK024(ya)001:2853: du bshad pas tsakli bkod tshe rdul tshon gyi mtshan
NK024(ya)001:2854: ma mi dgos / 'on kyang phyag len du gtso
NK024(ya)001:2855: bo tsam ma gtogs 'khor la lha dbang med phyir
NK024(ya)001:2856: tsakli med pas rdul tshon gyi mtshan ma 'god par
NK024(ya)001:2857: ma mi dgos / mdzad / 'di nas bzung lha
NK024(ya)001:2858: mi nyan rang byang sems kyi sdom rten du bkod
NK024(ya)001:2859: pas mdzes pa'i khrir ston pa'i sku byin rlabs can
NK024(ya)001:2860: na bza' bklubs pa bzhugs pa'i mdun du mchod stegs
NK024(ya)001:2861: bang rim can la nyer spyod kyi phreng ba tshar
NK024(ya)001:2863: slob dpon gyi mdun du dung chos lta bur dri bzang btab pa'i bsang chu /
NK024(ya)001:2864: 'thor byed ku sha dang bcas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2865: rdor dril d+aa ma ru gdab phur 'thor nas yungs thun gu gul sogs thams cad 'tshogs par bya /
NK024(ya)001:2866: 'og tu dgos pa'i bgegs gtor dang /
NK024(ya)001:2867: man+dala me tog dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:2868: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi mchod pa kha gso ba'i yo byad chu gtsang /
NK024(ya)001:2872: zhal zas sogs kyang ci 'byor mi brel bar bsham par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:2873: dus thams cad du phyi gtor brgya rtsa dang /
NK024(ya)001:2874: klu thebs sogs kyi tshe klu gtor yang bya ste sa gzhi rnams klus dbang byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK024(ya)001:2876: de nas rang nyid stan bde ba la 'dug ste skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sngon du song bas /
NK024(ya)001:2877: zhes 'byung bas slob dpon stan la 'khod de mdun
NK024(ya)001:2878: gyi nam mkhar skyabs yul rnams badz+ra sa m+aa dzahzhesa
NK024(ya)001:2879: rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgyas spyan drangs la /
NK024(ya)001:2880: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK024(ya)001:2882: 'og tu dbang gi sngon 'gro nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK024(ya)001:2883: phyogs dus kun nas brtse bar bzhugs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:2884: bla ma dkon mchog thams cad dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:2886: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su mchi /
NK024(ya)001:2887: zhes sogs kyi skyabs 'gro rnams lan gsum re dang /
NK024(ya)001:2888: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK024(ya)001:2889: yang dag byang chub bskyed mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:2890: de bzhin bla med byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:2891: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:2892: zhes pa'i sems bskyed lan gsum bya /
NK024(ya)001:2893: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi bla dper rigs
NK024(ya)001:2894: sras mnga' ris pan chen rin po ches mchan bu
NK024(ya)001:2895: mdzad pa las / dbang 'di nas 'go bzung nas
NK024(ya)001:2896: theg pa rim pa thams cad kyi dbang la bdag
NK024(ya)001:2897: mdun bum pa dbang rdzas rnams sgrub cing mchod bstod
NK024(ya)001:2898: gsol btab sogs tshar mtshams su slob bu la ji
NK024(ya)001:2900: dbang rnams ma lus par rang gi dbang nos pa'i
NK024(ya)001:2901: bla ma de 'di skabs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK024(ya)001:2902: bo dang tha mi dad du byas nas /
NK024(ya)001:2903: des gnang bar mos nas yongs su rdzogs par blang
NK024(ya)001:2904: zhing man+dala phyag sogs gtang rag tshar rjes slob bu
NK024(ya)001:2905: 'jug cing dbang sbyin pa gnad che gsung /
NK024(ya)001:2906: thams cad mkhyen pa zur hwam rin po che'i zhal gdams so //
NK024(ya)001:2908: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi go rims su sdebs na
NK024(ya)001:2909: bla ma gong ma'i phyag bzhes dang mthun par 'dug
NK024(ya)001:2910: pas de ltar byas na 'thad par mthong la /
NK024(ya)001:2911: 'on kyang rtsa bar mdun bskyed dang bum bskyed tsam
NK024(ya)001:2912: las bdag bskyed kha gsal mi 'dug pa bdag mdun
NK024(ya)001:2914: slob ma la dbang bskur khar rang gsang bdag gi
NK024(ya)001:2915: nga rgyal dang ldan pas zhes gsungs pas bdag bskyed
NK024(ya)001:2916: zur tsam smos pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:2919: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:2920: rang gi sems nyid h+aum sngon po yongs su gyur
NK024(ya)001:2921: pa las / gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga h+aum gis mtshan par gyur //
NK024(ya)001:2925: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK024(ya)001:2926: rang nyid gsang ba'i bdag po dpal phyag na rdo
NK024(ya)001:2927: rje sku mdog sngon po g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon
NK024(ya)001:2928: sdigs mdzub can / zhabs g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang bas bzhengs pa /
NK024(ya)001:2929: dbu skra kham pa gyen du bardzesa shing khro gnyer bsdus pa /
NK024(ya)001:2930: zhal bgrad cing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK024(ya)001:2931: spyan gsum gyen du ldog cing /
NK024(ya)001:2932: sma ra ag tshoms smin ma me ltar 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:2933: rus pa dang rin po che rgyan gyis brgyan cing /
NK024(ya)001:2934: pa ti khra bo'i na bza' dang /
NK024(ya)001:2936: seng ge'i pags pas stod g.yogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:2937: stag lpags kyi sham thabs can ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'i dpral bar /
NK024(ya)001:2939: de las 'od zer 'phros pas rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK024(ya)001:2940: nas ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa ya dzah dzahh+aum
NK024(ya)001:2941: bam hoh tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2943: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih +aah +aahh+aum zhes dbang bskur zhing sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:2944: thugs kar rang 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar
NK024(ya)001:2945: rdo rje'i lte bar h+aum la sngags phreng gis bskor
NK024(ya)001:2946: ba la 'od zer 'phros shing don gnyis byas /
NK024(ya)001:2947: tshur 'dus bdag la thim pas byin gyis brlab par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:2948: n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni r+aadz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:2950: bcom ldan 'das bdag la dngos grub stsal du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:2953: mdun bskyed zin nas cha gsum gyi sngon du skyabs 'gro yan lag bdun pas phyag btsal bas /
NK024(ya)001:2954: rang gtso bo'i thugs ka'i lha dang mchod rdzas kyi
NK024(ya)001:2955: dri ma thams cad dag par bsam zhing ye d+har+m+aa
NK024(ya)001:2956: bzlas te / phyogs thams cad du me tog gtor
NK024(ya)001:2957: zhing lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod rdzas dwangs shing
NK024(ya)001:2958: thogs pa med pa bsam gyis mi khyab par bsam
NK024(ya)001:2959: bzlas te / la / zhes gsungs pa ni gab dkrugs yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:2960: 'dir bdag bskyed sngon du 'gro bas mchod rdzas byin brlab byed dgos pa gsal por bshad pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:2961: de yang zur thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag rdor dbang gi zin bris las /
NK024(ya)001:2962: lha'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:2964: dngos grub kyi rdzas ye shes kyi rang snang du
NK024(ya)001:2965: byas pa la lha'i 'dzab bzlas kyis nus pa bskyed
NK024(ya)001:2966: / ye d+ha r+m+aa bgrangs shing basngagasa pa'i me tog 'thor /
NK024(ya)001:2967: dkon mchog gsum gyi 'od zer bstim la /
NK024(ya)001:2968: rdo rje dril bu bzung skor ba lan bdun dang /
NK024(ya)001:2969: yig brgya rol mo dang bcas pas lhag chad nongs pa bskang /
NK024(ya)001:2970: shoms tshar ba dang rab gnas dang mchod pa byed /
NK024(ya)001:2971: ces gsungs pas rgyas par spros na de ltar byed /
NK024(ya)001:2972: ha cang spros pas dub na rang phyag rdor gyi
NK024(ya)001:2973: nga rgyal la gnas pa' rdor dril 'dzin cing rtsa
NK024(ya)001:2974: sngags kyis 'go mnan pa'i rten 'brel snying pos basngagasa
NK024(ya)001:2978: dkyil 'khor thams cad la gtor la /
NK024(ya)001:2979: thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis ma dag pa bsangs shing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:2980: skyabs 'gro dang yan lag bdun pa song ma thag pa yin la /
NK024(ya)001:2981: mchod rdzas rnams brlab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:2982: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi mchod pa la dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:2985: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+rum las rin po che las
NK024(ya)001:2986: grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:2987: nang du 'od du zhu ba las byung ba'i lha
NK024(ya)001:2988: rdzas las grub pa'i mchod yon /
NK024(ya)001:2996: gtor ma rnams dwangs shing thogs pa med pa bsam gyis mi khyab par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:2997: so so'i phyag rgyar bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:3006: dril bu rgyun chags su dkrol la rol mo'i sngags ni /
NK024(ya)001:3010: sarba bud+d+ha k+she tra pra ts+aa li ni pradz+ny+aa p+aa ra mi ta n+aa da sam b+ha we /
NK024(ya)001:3011: badz+ra sa t+wa h+r+aih da ya san+to sha ni h+aum
NK024(ya)001:3012: h+aum h+aum ho ho ho +aa kham s+aa h+aa mchod
NK024(ya)001:3014: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:3015: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK024(ya)001:3016: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:3021: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK024(ya)001:3022: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+no pa sam kra ma na
NK024(ya)001:3023: badz+re sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha
NK024(ya)001:3027: thog mar cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK024(ya)001:3028: de'i thugs ka nas phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor lha rnams 'phro bar gzhung las gsal por bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:3029: nged rang gi sngon smon bsod nams kyi mthu las
NK024(ya)001:3030: rtsom par 'jug dus mnga' ris pan chen rin po
NK024(ya)001:3031: che'i phyag bris ma zur h+aam sh+aaka 'byung gis mdzad
NK024(ya)001:3032: pa'i mdo dbang gi lha thems sogs yig rnying mang
NK024(ya)001:3033: du rnyed pa'i lha thems las /
NK024(ya)001:3034: rang shar gtso bo nub gzigs mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:3035: pad zlar rdor sems las kyi lha //
NK024(ya)001:3036: phyag rdor rdor sems thugs las bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:3037: ces gtan tshigs bzang po'i nges shes rnyed do //
NK024(ya)001:3038: yi ge rnying pa rnams dang rtsa bar lha rnams
NK024(ya)001:3039: bskyed tshul lam tsam las gzhal yas khang bskyed tshul
NK024(ya)001:3040: med pas / las dang po pa rnams shin tu
NK024(ya)001:3041: sgom mi bde bas gzhung don ji bzhin la gzhal
NK024(ya)001:3042: yas khang bskyed pa sogs rgyas par 'chad rigs pa
NK024(ya)001:3043: med pas / yin la / zur thams cad mkhyen
NK024(ya)001:3044: pa'i zin bris su sngon la bum pa bskyed nas
NK024(ya)001:3045: med pas / yin la / / dkyil 'khor bsang
NK024(ya)001:3046: chu dang las bum gnyis kas bsang dgos par gsungs
NK024(ya)001:3047: med pas / yin la / / kyang / gzhung rtsa bar mdun bskyed sngon la bsgrubs /
NK024(ya)001:3048: de nas las bum dang dri chab kyi bsang chu sgrub /
NK024(ya)001:3049: de gnyis kyis gtso bum bsang zhing bsgrub par gsungs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3050: pan chen rin po ches kyang bdag mdun bum gsum go rim du bshad pa ltar legs pas /
NK024(ya)001:3051: ji ltar bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:3052: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor gnyis la dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:3055: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi ma'i steng du
NK024(ya)001:3056: h+aum las byung ba'i sna tshogs rdo rje h+aum gis
NK024(ya)001:3058: rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla
NK024(ya)001:3059: bre ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar ba'i srung
NK024(ya)001:3060: 'khor gnyis kyi nang du sna tshogs pad+ma'i ge sar
NK024(ya)001:3061: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyis khebs pa'i lte bar sna
NK024(ya)001:3062: tshogs rdo rje rwa bcu gnyis pa phyogs kyi mdog
NK024(ya)001:3063: can lte ba sngon po gru bzhi pa'i steng b+h+r+aum
NK024(ya)001:3064: las rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal
NK024(ya)001:3065: yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi mtshan nyid thams cad
NK024(ya)001:3066: yongs su rdzogs pa re rer gyur pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3067: nang nas rim pa bzhin du mthing dkar ser dmar
NK024(ya)001:3068: ljang ba'i rtsig steng nas phyed 'phyar gyi pha gu
NK024(ya)001:3069: ser po rin po che'i phra tshoms can /
NK024(ya)001:3070: gser gyi ska rags las 'phyang ba'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa /
NK024(ya)001:3071: mda' yab sngon po phyir 'phyang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3072: pu shu dkar po gyen du langs pa /
