NK024(ya)001:3073: phyi rol gyi 'dod snam la mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:3074: nang ka ba brgyad dang ldan pa la rdo rje'i
NK024(ya)001:3075: gdung bzhis bris pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:3077: sgo bzhi'i thad sor ka ba bzhis btegs pa'i rta
NK024(ya)001:3078: babs bang rim bzhi pa'i steng du pad+ma la gnas
NK024(ya)001:3079: pa'i bum pa dang bre chos 'khor gdugs dang tog
NK024(ya)001:3080: gis mdzes par spras pa'i g.yas g.yon du ri dwags
NK024(ya)001:3082: rta babs kyi snam bu so so dang t+wa ra
NK024(ya)001:3083: na'i rtser gdugs rgyal mtshan 'phan la sogs pa rgyan
NK024(ya)001:3084: du mas spras pa'i gzhal yas khang gnyis su gyur
NK024(ya)001:3085: / cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor ling tshe dgu pa'i dbus sngon /
NK024(ya)001:3090: lha rnam ljang gus mdzes shing phyi rol tu 'jig rten pa'i khor yug nag po can /
NK024(ya)001:3091: phyag na rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus sngo /
NK024(ya)001:3095: byang ljang ba'i phyir mu khyud sngon po la rdo rje phreng bas mtshan pa /
NK024(ya)001:3096: glo 'bur ljang gu'i gru chad kyis mdzes pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:3097: dkyil 'khor dang po bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3098: de ltar bu'i cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK024(ya)001:3099: su rin po che'i khri pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:3100: h+aum sngon po de las 'od zer 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:3101: 'phags pa mchod pa dang sems can gyi don gnyis byas /
NK024(ya)001:3102: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:3103: rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po zhal gcig
NK024(ya)001:3104: phyag gnyis dar dang rin po che rgyan thams cad
NK024(ya)001:3105: kyis brgyan pa / phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar btod de 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3106: g.yon dngul dkar gyi dril bu dkur brten pa zhabs
NK024(ya)001:3107: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa zhal nub
NK024(ya)001:3108: tu phyogs pa'o // de yang phyi ltar phyag na rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:3109: nang rdo rje sems dpa' dang dpal chen po badz+ra
NK024(ya)001:3110: he ru ka sku mdog sngon po rdo rje dang
NK024(ya)001:3111: dung khrag 'dzin pa khyung gshog can khrag zhag gi
NK024(ya)001:3112: tshom bu / sbrul stag glang zhing chen thod phreng gis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:3114: gnyis ka bsnyen dus su rdor dril bsnol ba'am /
NK024(ya)001:3115: rdor sems ltar bsnol dus su rdo rje dung khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:3116: zhes gsungs pa 'di kho nas 'thus so //
NK024(ya)001:3117: gsang ba ma h+aa k+aa la legs ldan nag po lcam dral gyi bdag nyid can du snang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:3118: phyi rim ling tshe brgyad kyi gtso bo'i zhal phyogs
NK024(ya)001:3119: chen gyi nub tu blta ba'i mdun shar du sgeg
NK024(ya)001:3120: mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3121: gtso bo'i g.yas su phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3122: rgyab tu glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3123: g.yon du gar ma ljang gu gar gyi phu rung 'dzin cing gar bsgyur ba /
NK024(ya)001:3124: ling tshe'i nub byang sogs gra bzhir phyogs chen gyi
NK024(ya)001:3125: nub byang du bdug spos ma dkar ser spos khang
NK024(ya)001:3126: 'dzin pa / byang shar du me tog ma dmar ser me tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3127: shar lhor mar me ma dmar ljang mar me 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3128: lho nub tu dri chab ma dkar ljang dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:3129: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo //
NK024(ya)001:3130: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu /
NK024(ya)001:3131: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo //
NK024(ya)001:3132: lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo rnams rang rtags 'dzin cing bzhengs te sgo skyong ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:3134: sku mdog phyag mtshan gzhan dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:3135: zhes gsungs pa gsal bar byas so //
NK024(ya)001:3136: nang gi lha snam la mgon po bdun cu rtsa lnga /
NK024(ya)001:3137: phyi'i khor yug la 'gro ba rigs drug /
NK024(ya)001:3138: me ri'i phyi rol tu lan chags kyi mgron rnams rang rang gi cha lugs 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:3140: de nas gtso bo'i thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:3141: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas ye shes pa spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:3142: ar+g+ham la sogs pa mchod pa lngas mchod nas /
NK024(ya)001:3143: dzahh+aum bam hohs dam tshig pa la bstim nas zhes gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK024(ya)001:3144: gtso 'khor rnams kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:3147: thugs ka'i h+aum yig las 'od zer 'phros pas rang
NK024(ya)001:3148: bzhin gyi gnas nas rang 'dra'i ye shes kyi 'khor
NK024(ya)001:3149: lo mdun gyi nam mkhar badz+ra sa ma ya dzah
NK024(ya)001:3157: dzahh+aum bam hohs dam tshig pa la bstim mo //
NK024(ya)001:3158: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od kyis mdun gyi
NK024(ya)001:3159: nam mkhar dbang gi lha rigs lnga badz+ra sa m+aa
NK024(ya)001:3160: dzah sarba ta th+aa ga ta ab+hi shiny+tsa tu mamh
NK024(ya)001:3162: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah zhes dbang bskur /
NK024(ya)001:3164: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las rigs lngas dbu brgyan /
NK024(ya)001:3166: slar yang mchod nas zhes pa'i don ni /
NK024(ya)001:3167: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi spos dang mar me rnams spar la /
NK024(ya)001:3168: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK024(ya)001:3169: ar+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu
NK024(ya)001:3170: dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3171: de bzhin du ar+g+ham gyi gnas su p+aad+yam /
NK024(ya)001:3177: shap+da zhes bcug pa phyag rgyar bcas te mchod /
NK024(ya)001:3181: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:3182: zhing rdul kun gyi grangs snyed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:3183: lus btud pa yi rnam kun tu //
NK024(ya)001:3184: mchog tu dad pas phyag 'tshal bstod //'dzab bzlas pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3185: de nas gtso bo'i thugs ka pad+ma kha bye ba'i
NK024(ya)001:3186: steng du zla ba dang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la
NK024(ya)001:3187: h+aum dkar po ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rigs lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:3188: bdag nyid can de la badz+ra sat+wa a /
NK024(ya)001:3189: zhes pa dngul chu'i phreng ba lta bus bskor ba las 'od byung /
NK024(ya)001:3190: bdag gzhan gyi sgo gsum gyi sdig sgrib thams cad dag par gyur par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3191: snying po de nyid sgrub grogs yod na kun gyis
NK024(ya)001:3192: 'dzab tu bzlas te grangs ni bargya'am stong la sogs
NK024(ya)001:3194: bzlas pa song nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3195: bcom ldan 'das bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum gyi sdig sgrib dag go //
NK024(ya)001:3196: sku gsung thugs kyi nyams chag bskang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:3197: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad mthol lo bshags so //
NK024(ya)001:3198: nyes ltung dri ma'i tshogs thams cad byang zhing dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:3200: de'i ngang la ma bcos par bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:3201: dkyil 'khor phyi ma bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3203: de nas gsang bdag gi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su
NK024(ya)001:3204: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka'i rigs
NK024(ya)001:3205: lnga'i rnam snang gi thugs ka nas gser gyi rdo
NK024(ya)001:3206: rje rtse lnga pa h+aum gis mtshan pa zhig byung
NK024(ya)001:3207: ba las nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la /
NK024(ya)001:3209: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor dbus kyi bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:3210: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka'i h+aum rigs lnga'i bdag
NK024(ya)001:3211: nyid can de las gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga
NK024(ya)001:3212: pa h+aum gis mtshan pa zhig byung ste /
NK024(ya)001:3213: gsang ba'i bdag po'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan la 'khod par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:3217: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las gsang ba'i bdag
NK024(ya)001:3218: po dpal phyag na rdo rje sku mdog sngon po
NK024(ya)001:3219: g.yas rdo rje 'phyar zhing g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:3220: / zhabs nang ltar g.yas brkyang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:3221: phyi ltar zhabs g.yon brkyang ba'i stabs kyis bzhengs pa /
NK024(ya)001:3222: gdul bya zhi ba'i snang ngor sems dpa'i skyil mo
NK024(ya)001:3223: krung du bzhugs pa'i snang tshul cir yang 'char ba
NK024(ya)001:3224: / zhi ba ba ti khra bo dang dar sngon po'i chos gos te na bza'/
NK024(ya)001:3225: rgyas pa rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:3226: dbang dar zab sna tshogs kyi na bza' gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:3227: drag po rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan cing seng ge dkar mo'i pags pa'i stod g.yogs gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:3228: stag lpags kyi sham thabs can /
NK024(ya)001:3229: zhal bgrad cing mche ba gtsig pa sma ra dang ag tshoms me ltar 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:3230: khro gnyer bsdus pa spyan gsum bgrad cing smin ma dmar ser me ltar g.yo ba /
NK024(ya)001:3231: dbu skra kham pa gyen du 'bar ba la thod
NK024(ya)001:3232: skam rin po che 'bar ba lngas bcings pa mi
NK024(ya)001:3233: bskyod pa'i dbu rgyan can ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK024(ya)001:3236: dkyil 'khor bri tshul bshad dus rtsibs bzhi bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:3237: sgom dus phyogs bzhi'i glo 'bur la /
NK024(ya)001:3238: zhes bshad kyang bri bya dang mi 'gal zhing gong
NK024(ya)001:3239: ma'i phyag bzhes su shar gyi rtsibs la sgeg mo
NK024(ya)001:3243: glo 'bur gyi grwa bzhir shar lhor bdug spos ma /
NK024(ya)001:3244: lho nub tu me tog ma /
NK024(ya)001:3245: nub byang du mar me ma /
NK024(ya)001:3246: byang shar du dri chab ma /
NK024(ya)001:3250: khor yug la 'gro ba rigs drug /
NK024(ya)001:3251: phyi rol du lan chags kyi mgron bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:3252: zhes pa rnams kyi don ni /
NK024(ya)001:3256: byang sgor dril bu ma rnams sku mdog phyag mtshan thams cad snga ma dang 'dra ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:3257: phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor 'di la zur hwam thams
NK024(ya)001:3258: cad mkhyen pa'i zin bris su gtso bo gsang ba
NK024(ya)001:3259: gsum bcas / rtsibs bzhi la gos sngon can rigs bzhi yum bcas kyi lugs dang /
NK024(ya)001:3260: yang na shar rtsibs la khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK024(ya)001:3262: nub tu rnam sras ser chen /
NK024(ya)001:3263: byang du klu sog ma med rnams byed pa'i lugs dang /
NK024(ya)001:3264: phyag rdor mdo lugs ltar na rgyal byed tshal gyi
NK024(ya)001:3265: srung ma lag na rdo rje gos sngon can ces
NK024(ya)001:3266: grags tshul gyi bshad lugs dang sbyar ba'i 'khor phyogs
NK024(ya)001:3268: mtshams bzhir gnod sbyin sde bzhi ni /
NK024(ya)001:3270: bden bral du rdo rje srin po /
NK024(ya)001:3271: rlung du rdo rje gdon chen /
NK024(ya)001:3272: dbang ldan du rdo rje ro langs rnams te mdo lugs lha dgu ma'i lugs dang /
NK024(ya)001:3273: yang na mdo lugs dpa' rkyang ste bzhir gsungs la /
NK024(ya)001:3274: lha thebs las kyang de ltar du bshad /
NK024(ya)001:3275: 'on kyang 'dir cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor dang 'brel
NK024(ya)001:3276: ba'i dbang gis gnyis ka'i phyi 'khor rnams mthun par
NK024(ya)001:3277: mdzad pa rtsa ba dang yig rnying gzhan dag las
NK024(ya)001:3278: kyang bshad do // kahthoga lugs la chog gzhung rang
NK024(ya)001:3279: la cha gsum dang phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK024(ya)001:3280: ka ming tsam yang mi gsal ba 'dra zhig 'dug
NK024(ya)001:3281: kyang bshad do // na'ang / bla ma rnams zur
NK024(ya)001:3282: lugs nas kha bkang ste mdzad srol yod 'dra bas
NK024(ya)001:3283: rjes 'jug 'gas zin bris btab par dkyil 'khor gnyis
NK024(ya)001:3284: kyang bshad do // na'ang / ka 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:3285: lha tshogs kyi grangs des kyang thun mong rnams mthun
NK024(ya)001:3286: par 'dug /'on kyang thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs
NK024(ya)001:3287: bzhi po kahthoga lugs sogs brgyud pa gzhan la ming
NK024(ya)001:3289: zur lugs snyan brgyud yin nges par go //
NK024(ya)001:3290: lugs gnyis ka la cha gsum gyi mgron mgon po
NK024(ya)001:3291: bdun cu sogs phyag rdor gyi dkyil 'khor la bkod
NK024(ya)001:3292: pa ni the tshom gyi gzhir 'dug par /
NK024(ya)001:3293: zur hwam thams cad mkhyen pa'i zin bris zur bkol
NK024(ya)001:3294: du cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor logs su mi byed
NK024(ya)001:3295: par phyag rdor la cha gsum gyis kha bskang na
NK024(ya)001:3296: cha gsum gyi mgron rnams phyag rdor dkyil 'khor la
NK024(ya)001:3297: bkod de / cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor mi dgos
NK024(ya)001:3298: pa'i lugs su mdzad 'dug pa la yid ches dang
NK024(ya)001:3299: nges shes brtan po rnyed cing /
NK024(ya)001:3300: de ltar na dkyil 'khor gnyis su byas phyin cha
NK024(ya)001:3301: gsum gyi mgron rnams cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor rang
NK024(ya)001:3302: la bkod na legs shing mtshan don mthun par 'dug
NK024(ya)001:3303: cing / lha thebs las kyang de bzhin gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:3304: lag len shin tu bsdus par bya dgos na /
NK024(ya)001:3305: cha gsum la dkyil 'khor mi bya bar phyag rdor
NK024(ya)001:3306: kho nar bsdu ba zur lugs rtsod bral yin 'dug
NK024(ya)001:3307: pas ma 'dres par shes dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:3308: de nas lha de thams cad kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:3311: thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros pas 'og min
NK024(ya)001:3312: nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor badz+ra sa ma ya
NK024(ya)001:3313: dzahdzah zhes pas rang bzhin gyi gnas nas ye shes
NK024(ya)001:3315: rtsa bar cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la nam mkhar mchod de bstim par bshad la /
NK024(ya)001:3316: 'dir gsal kha ma byung yang cho ga rigs mthun phyin gong gis shes nus par byas pas na /
NK024(ya)001:3317: badz+ra ar+g+ham sogs snga ma ltar mchod /
NK024(ya)001:3318: dzahh+aum bam hohs dam tshig pa la bstim /
NK024(ya)001:3319: tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aas brtan par bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK024(ya)001:3320: slar yang thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od kyis dbang lha
NK024(ya)001:3321: rigs lnga badz+ra sa m+aa dzah sarba th+aa ga ta
NK024(ya)001:3322: a b+hi shiny+tsa tu mamh zhes gsol ba btab pas
NK024(ya)001:3323: / h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah zhes dbang bskur /
NK024(ya)001:3325: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las rigs lngas dbu brgya na par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:3326: +aahh+aum gis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:3327: phyag rdor gyi mchod pa spar la /
NK024(ya)001:3328: badz+ra p+aa ni sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra
NK024(ya)001:3329: t+aits+tsha p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra
NK024(ya)001:3331: de bzhin du ar+g+ham gyi gnas su p+aa d+yam /
NK024(ya)001:3337: shap+da rnams bcug la thog mthar sngar bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:3338: dril bu dkrol zhing d+har+m+aa ra ni'i sngags dang /
NK024(ya)001:3339: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:3340: sogs mchod pa'i sprin gyi sngags kyang brjod /
NK024(ya)001:3343: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK024(ya)001:3344: byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:3345: gsang bdag 'phags pa gos sngon can //'khor bcas ma lus phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:3348: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra ba zhig bsam /
NK024(ya)001:3349: de nas mchod pa lngas mchod nas dbang ma bskur ba'i gong du tad+ya th+aa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3351: n+ai lam zhes sogs 'dzab tu bzlas te zhes gsungs pa'i mchod pa gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:3352: sngags la 'don 'jug bya bar bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3353: dbang ma bskur ba'i gong du rig sngags dang gzungs sngags ltar 'di lta ste /
NK024(ya)001:3354: zhes bas 'go 'dren la dbang bskur nas gsang sngags kho na ltar 'jug pa yin 'dra zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3355: 'on kyang bla ma rnams thog ma nas gsungs bar 'dug pas /
NK024(ya)001:3356: n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni r+aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3357: zhes bzla zhing thugs kar rang 'dra'i ye shes sems
NK024(ya)001:3358: dpa'i thugs kar nyi zla'i gdan la h+aum sngon po
NK024(ya)001:3359: la sngags phreng klog thabs su 'khor ba las 'od
NK024(ya)001:3360: zer 'phros pas don gnyis byas shing bdag la thim
NK024(ya)001:3361: pas dngos grub thob par bsam la bazla'o //
NK024(ya)001:3364: de nas las bum gtso bo'i thugs ka nas bdud
NK024(ya)001:3365: rtsi 'khyil ba sku mdog ljang gu g.yas rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:3366: rgya gram dang g.yon dril bu bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:3367: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa zhig byung bar bsams la /
NK024(ya)001:3368: de'i thugs kar rdo rje rgya gram h+aum gis mtshan pa 'od 'phro ba bsgom /
NK024(ya)001:3369: gtso bo'i las byed bgegs mthar byed la +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:3371: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:3373: bstod nas zhes gsungs pa'i de'i tshul ni las bum a mri tas bsang /
NK024(ya)001:3375: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i bum
NK024(ya)001:3376: pa dbyibs zlum po tshad dang mtshan nyid thams cad
NK024(ya)001:3377: tshang ba nang dri bzang gi chu dang bcud kyis
NK024(ya)001:3378: gang bar gyur / dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo gsang
NK024(ya)001:3379: ba'i bdag po'i thugs ka nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba
NK024(ya)001:3380: sku mdog ljang gu g.yas rdo rje rgya gram dang
NK024(ya)001:3381: g.yon dril bu bsnams pa dar dang rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:3382: rgyan gyis brgyan cing sems dpa'i skyil mo krung can
NK024(ya)001:3383: zhig byung ste bum nang du pad+ma dang nyi zla'i
NK024(ya)001:3385: de'i thugs ka nas khro bo bgegs mthar byed ljang
NK024(ya)001:3386: nag rdo rje rgya gram gnon thabs su 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:3387: zhig byung ste / dri chab kyi nang du pad nyi'i gdan la gnas par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:3388: lha 'di gnyis gtso bo'i thugs nas spros phyir ye shes dgug bstim dbang bskur sogs mi dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:3390: dbang byin ye shes mi bskyed par //
NK024(ya)001:3391: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir bdag gi thugs ka'i 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:3392: gyi sne las mchod pa'i bye brag byung ste bum
NK024(ya)001:3393: pa dang dri chab kyi lha gnyis mchod par bsam
NK024(ya)001:3402: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrog cing //
NK024(ya)001:3403: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:3404: dngos grub ma lus stsol ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3405: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK024(ya)001:3406: gzungs thag nas bzung ste bdag gi thugs ka nas
NK024(ya)001:3407: 'od zer gzungs thag la 'khril te song bas lha
NK024(ya)001:3408: gnyis la phog pas thugs rgyud bskul /
NK024(ya)001:3409: sku las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:3410: las bum la +aahbadz+ra a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:3412: dri chab la +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:3413: ces nyer gcig tsam bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:3414: slar yang gong bzhin mchod bstod byas la /
NK024(ya)001:3415: +aahh+aum zhes dung chos kyi mchod yon phul bas gnyis ka chur zhu bar bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:3416: las bum dang dri chab gnyis 'og gi cho ga
NK024(ya)001:3417: dmigs bsal med pa rnams la nang re bzhin bum
NK024(ya)001:3418: chu kha bsos la 'di ltar bsgrub dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:3419: rnam rgyal bum pa bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3421: dri chab dang las bum gnyis kas gtso bo'i dbang gi lha bum bsang la lha gong ltar bskyed /
NK024(ya)001:3423: dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs nas rtsa ba'i snying po bzlas te gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:3425: gtso bum la dri chab dang las bum gyi chu
NK024(ya)001:3426: gnyis ka 'thor zhing so so'i rang sngags kyis bsang
NK024(ya)001:3428: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che bum pa zlum po lto ba yangs pa /
NK024(ya)001:3432: phyi bum pa'i dbyibs la nang gzhal yas khang mtshan
NK024(ya)001:3433: nyid dang ldan par gyur pa'i dbus su pad+ma dang
NK024(ya)001:3434: zla ba nyi ma'i gdan la h+aum dang rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:3435: h+aum gis mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las /
NK024(ya)001:3436: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje sku mdog
NK024(ya)001:3437: in+d+ra n+ai la ltar sngon ba zhal mche ba gtsigs
NK024(ya)001:3438: shing ljags 'dril zhing ag tshoms 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:3439: spyan gsum dmar la zlum zhing 'khyil ba'i smin ma dmar ser me ltar 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:3440: dbu skra kham nag gyen du bardzesa pa la thod
NK024(ya)001:3441: skam gyi rtsa chings can phyag g.yas gser gyi rdo
NK024(ya)001:3443: g.yon sdigs mdzub thugs kar mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:3444: dar sngon po dang seng ge'i pags pas stod g.yogs shing stag lpags kyi sham thabs can /
NK024(ya)001:3445: rin po che dang rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa
NK024(ya)001:3446: zhabs g.yas bskum zhing g.yon brkyang bas ye shes kyi
NK024(ya)001:3447: me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //'di la zur
NK024(ya)001:3448: hwam thams cad mkhyen pas sgeg sogs lha mo brgyad
NK024(ya)001:3449: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor dang thun mong ba yin
NK024(ya)001:3450: par gsungs phyir gtso rkyang gis chog par sems te
NK024(ya)001:3452: phyag rdor mdo lugs dpa' rkyang ngam //
NK024(ya)001:3457: de las 'od zer 'phros 'og min nas gsang ba'i
NK024(ya)001:3458: bdag po'i lha tshogs badz+ra sa ma ya dzahdzah zhes
NK024(ya)001:3459: spyan drangs / dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim /
NK024(ya)001:3460: tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aas brtan par byas /
NK024(ya)001:3461: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah zhes dbang bskur /
NK024(ya)001:3463: badz+ra p+aa ni sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham sogs mtshan sngags sngon 'gros mchod /
NK024(ya)001:3464: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
NK024(ya)001:3467: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:3469: gzungs thag nas bzung ste rang gi thugs ka nas
NK024(ya)001:3470: sngags kyi phreng ba gzungs thag la 'khril te song
NK024(ya)001:3471: / thugs kar phog pas thugs rgyud bskul sku las
NK024(ya)001:3472: 'od zer 'phros don gnyis byas byin rlabs dngos grub
NK024(ya)001:3473: kyi bcud rnams tshur 'dus te sku'i cha thams cad
NK024(ya)001:3474: las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang bar
NK024(ya)001:3475: / bsam zhing / n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra
NK024(ya)001:3476: badz+ra p+aa ni r+aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:3479: rtsa ba'i snying po bzlas te chu thigs gcig bum par blug pas bum pa lha'i gzhal yas khang /
NK024(ya)001:3480: bum chu rgya mtsho'i chu zil pa re re yang tshe dpal bde ba skyed byed kyi lha /
NK024(ya)001:3489: de ltar bzlas pa brgya rtsa re la mchod pa tshar re /
NK024(ya)001:3491: zhes gsungs pas bzlas pa brgya tshar ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:3492: gong bzhin mchod pa tshar re bya /
NK024(ya)001:3493: yang bzlas pa brgya re dang mchod pa tshar re bya /
NK024(ya)001:3494: de ltar lan bcu bya zhing bzlas pa stong phrag gcig nges par bya dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:3495: yungs kar la yang basngagasa te bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:3496: de yang zur hwam thams cad mkhyen pas lha mi
NK024(ya)001:3497: zhu bar chu nang gi zla ba dang nam mkha'i
NK024(ya)001:3498: gza' skar ltar mdzad gsungs pas na /
NK024(ya)001:3499: dung chos kyi chu bum par blug pas lha dang
NK024(ya)001:3500: gzhal yas khang gsal ba la bum chu gong gi
NK024(ya)001:3501: yon tan de dag dang ldan par blta'o //
NK024(ya)001:3503: de grub pa dang bum pa'i kha rgyan spyi bor bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:3504: chu khar btung pas bdag kyang lhar nges pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:3505: de nas mdun gyi byin rlabs rang la bsdus pas
NK024(ya)001:3506: h+aum bzhis dpral mgrin snying lter thig le byas pas
NK024(ya)001:3507: sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje'i rang bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:3508: bsam la mi rtog pa la dar cig bzhag go
NK024(ya)001:3509: // zhes gsungs pa'i don ni rnam rgyal gyi kha rgyan bdag gi spyi bor bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:3510: bum chu hub gcig 'thungs pas bdag dang lha gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin du gyur par mos /
NK024(ya)001:3511: h+aum bzhi brjod cing spyi mgrin snying lter bum chu'i thig le byas pas /
NK024(ya)001:3512: de lta bu'i sku gsung thugs ye shes rdo rje'i rang bzhin du bsam la mnyam bzhag bskyang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:3513: de nas cha gsum btang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3514: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i mchod phreng dang tshul mtshungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:3515: de yang rtsa ba bzhin la mi gsal ba rnams cung zad gsal bar byas pas 'thus par sems /
NK024(ya)001:3516: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams sngon nas sgrub mchod rgyas par grub kyang /
NK024(ya)001:3517: dang po 'das gtor 'bul ba'i dbang gis slar yang
NK024(ya)001:3518: gtor mgron du spyan drangs ba'i tshul gyis spos dang
NK024(ya)001:3521: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK024(ya)001:3522: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:3523: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK024(ya)001:3524: mchod nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:3525: ye shes phung po mkha' 'dra ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:3526: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK024(ya)001:3527: sprul pa kun gyi 'byung gnas gtso //
NK024(ya)001:3528: rdo rje sems dpa' gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3529: dmigs pa kun las rab 'das shing //
NK024(ya)001:3530: byin rlabs kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:3531: rnal 'byor kun gyi dbang phyug che //
NK024(ya)001:3532: sa gzhi lta bur gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3533: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pas //
NK024(ya)001:3534: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3535: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK024(ya)001:3536: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs bcas gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:3537: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wa na ma h+aa k+aa
NK024(ya)001:3538: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK024(ya)001:3541: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK024(ya)001:3542: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan 'dren gyi //
NK024(ya)001:3543: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK024(ya)001:3544: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnal 'byor dgyes pa bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:3545: badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3548: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK024(ya)001:3549: zhes sku gsung thugs brtan par byas /
NK024(ya)001:3550: a nut+ta ra p+au dza ud+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa //
NK024(ya)001:3551: rin chen 'tsher bas brgyan pa yi //'ja' tshon spel legs bkod 'dra ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:3552: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:3554: rim bzhin yangs par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3555: pad+ma ka ma la le s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3556: zhes gdan phul te bzhugs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:3558: so so'i phyag rgyar bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:3559: ma h+aa su ka badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3560: dzah h+aum bam hoh ma h+aa a r+g+ham pra t+ai ts+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3561: nags tshal bcud ni yid khar 'ong //
NK024(ya)001:3562: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:3563: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:3564: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3565: bdag gis dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK024(ya)001:3566: bzhes nas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:3567: badz+ra d+h+au pe p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3568: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:3569: lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3570: bdag gis dad bas bzhes nas badz+ra push+pe sdug bsngal 'joms shing bkra shis pa //
NK024(ya)001:3571: dgyes shing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3572: bdag gis bzhes nas badz+ra +aa lo ke gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:3573: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3574: bdag gis bzhes nas gan+d+he sman rnams bcud ni yid khar 'ong //
NK024(ya)001:3575: sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK024(ya)001:3577: nee wi d+ye sgra dbyangs snyan zhing yid 'ong ldan //
NK024(ya)001:3578: lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3579: bdag gis thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3580: shap+da rol mo rgyun chags su dkrol zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3584: sarba bud+d+ha k+she tra pra ts+aa li ni pradz+ny+aa p+aa ra mi ta n+aa da sam b+ha we /
NK024(ya)001:3585: badz+ra sat+w+aa h+r+aihd ya san+to sha ni h+aum h+aum h+aum ho ho ho +aa kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3586: mchod pa'i sprin gyi gzungs ni /
NK024(ya)001:3587: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:3588: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra s+aa ra pra mrda ne /
NK024(ya)001:3589: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:3594: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsit+ta badz+re /
NK024(ya)001:3595: ma h+aa bo d+hi man+do pa sam kra ma na
NK024(ya)001:3596: badz+re sarba karma +aa wa ra na bi sho d+ha
NK024(ya)001:3598: yid du 'ong ba'i mchod sprin dang //
NK024(ya)001:3599: rol mo sil snyan sprin gyi tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:3600: mchod 'os tshul dang mthun pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:3601: nam mkha'i khams kun khyab gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3602: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK024(ya)001:3603: zhes sogs bzang spyod nas 'byung ba'i yan lag bdun
NK024(ya)001:3604: pa byas nas dkyil 'khor pa rnams kyi ljags rdo
NK024(ya)001:3605: rje'i sbu gus gtor ma gsol bar bsam zhing nam
NK024(ya)001:3606: mkha' mdzod kyi rgyas na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te
NK024(ya)001:3607: b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ud+ga te
NK024(ya)001:3608: s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:3609: h+aa / lan gsum gyis dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i 'das gtor phul /
NK024(ya)001:3610: bstod cing 'dod don gsol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3611: mi mnyam mnyam pa'i lha khyod rtag tu bdag la ni //
NK024(ya)001:3612: thugs rje'i spyan gyis gzigs shing rgyun du 'gro ba'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:3613: byang chub mchog gi spyod pa bsgrub par dam bcas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:3614: bdag gi re ba'i 'bras bu 'di yang mchis par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:3615: gti mug mun pa'i d+r+wa bas bag chags nongs gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:3616: byams mgon ci slad bdag la thugs mi brtse //
NK024(ya)001:3617: khyed kyi mkhyen rab bskal pa'i me 'dra bas //
NK024(ya)001:3618: sems kyi mun sel sgron me bdag la stsol //
NK024(ya)001:3619: mgon po mchog dang shin tu ldan gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:3620: sems can don la bskul ba mi 'tshal yang //
NK024(ya)001:3621: sdug bsngal rang bzhin dbang du bdag gyur pas //
NK024(ya)001:3622: skyob pa'i spyan sngar gdung bas gsol ba 'debs //
NK024(ya)001:3623: gang zhig pha dang ma la slong na yang //
NK024(ya)001:3624: shin tu skyo ngal med pa de bzhin du //'gro ba'i don brtson mdzad pa khyed lags kyis //
NK024(ya)001:3625: tshe rabs kun tu bdag gi skyabs mdzod cig /
NK024(ya)001:3627: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams mtha' yas mu med
NK024(ya)001:3628: pa na dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs
NK024(ya)001:3629: rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK024(ya)001:3630: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab cing brjod kyis mi
NK024(ya)001:3631: langs pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal zhing gus pas
NK024(ya)001:3632: skyabs su mchi'o // bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:3633: zhal nas gsungs pa'i chos dkon mchog 'jig rten dang
NK024(ya)001:3634: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas
NK024(ya)001:3635: pa'i chos bsam gyis mi khyab pa la phyag 'tshal
NK024(ya)001:3637: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyi thugs kyi sras su
NK024(ya)001:3638: gyur pa dge 'dun rnams la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs
NK024(ya)001:3639: su mchi'o // dkon mchog rnams la mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3645: dngos su 'byor pa dang yid kyis sprul pa'i mchod
NK024(ya)001:3646: pa'i sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab pa phul bas
NK024(ya)001:3647: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:3648: / sems can 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas
NK024(ya)001:3649: gzung 'dzin rang ga mar zhen pa'i dbang gis nyon
NK024(ya)001:3650: mongs pa 'phel zhing rgyas pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:3651: ngan song gi rgyur gyur cing /
NK024(ya)001:3652: mtho ris dang thar pa'i sgrib par gyur pa ci
NK024(ya)001:3653: mchis pa thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:3654: /'di ltar bgyis pa'i dge ba sems can thams cad
NK024(ya)001:3655: dang thun mong du bsngo bar bagyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:3656: de ltar bsngosa pas sems can thams cad kyis bla
NK024(ya)001:3657: na med pa'i byang chub rin po che myur du
NK024(ya)001:3659: gnas skabs su tshe ring nad med pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3661: dge ba sgrub pa la bar chad med pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3662: phrin las phun sum tshogs pa bsgrub nus par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3663: sangs rgyas sku gsum mnyes pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK024(ya)001:3664: chos nyid mi 'gyur bden pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK024(ya)001:3665: dge 'dun mi phyed 'dun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:3666: ji ltar bsngo ba smon lam 'grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:3669: cha gsum gyi mgron dang po ni /
NK024(ya)001:3670: rang rta mgrin du gsal ba'am dkyil 'khor gyi gtso
NK024(ya)001:3671: bo yang gnas gyur te der shes pa'i nga rgyal
NK024(ya)001:3672: gyis / h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3675: cha gsum gyi mchod pa kha gsos la bsang chu'i dri chab 'thor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3676: swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+he d+har+m+aa si ti h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3678: a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:3680: a las mchod pa byin brlab gong ltar byas /
NK024(ya)001:3682: b+h+aum las rin po che'i snod du a las byung
NK024(ya)001:3683: ba'i lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod rdzas rnams dwangs
NK024(ya)001:3684: shing thogs pa med pa bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK024(ya)001:3685: gyur / ar+g+ham sogs kyi sngags rgyas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:3686: gtor ma brtag pa bzhis byin gyis brlab dgos par
NK024(ya)001:3687: cha gsum dpal sdom ma las bshad pas chos nyid
NK024(ya)001:3688: rnam dag gi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:3689: swa b+h+aa wa lan gsum gyis sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:3690: nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:3691: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo lan gsum gyis spel /
NK024(ya)001:3692: bdud rtsi thal sbyor gyi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:3693: a mri ta lan gsum gyis bdud rtsir bsgyur /
NK024(ya)001:3694: rgya chen shugs ldan 'od kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:3695: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te /
NK024(ya)001:3697: lan gsum gyis thob pa'i nus ldan du bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:3699: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:3700: zhes pa nas gyur shog gi bar brjod /
NK024(ya)001:3702: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK024(ya)001:3703: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs rnams kyis //
NK024(ya)001:3704: sangs rgyas kun la mchod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3705: sems can kun la phan gdags phyir //
NK024(ya)001:3706: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //'jig rten khams ni ma lus kun //
NK024(ya)001:3707: de dag thams cad ci rigs par //
NK024(ya)001:3708: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur shog /
NK024(ya)001:3709: ces byin gyis brlab la mgron 'gugs pa ni nang gi lha snam la byon par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:3710: sarba ka ri sarba sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3711: tshangs pa brgya byin rgyal chen lha dang klu //
NK024(ya)001:3712: gnod sbyin dri za lto 'phye lha ma yin //
NK024(ya)001:3713: mkha' lding grul bum srin po mi'am ci //
NK024(ya)001:3714: sems can gang dag bde gshegs sras rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:3715: nor med phung po dpal bzhes kun gshegs bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:3716: badz+ra am gu sha a kar+sha ya sarba d+hi ta
NK024(ya)001:3717: rash+ta ya gan+d+har+b+ha a ti pa ta ye h+aum dzah
NK024(ya)001:3718: bi ru d+ha k+aa ye kur ban+d+he a ti pa
NK024(ya)001:3719: ta ye h+aum dzah bi ru pak+sha ye n+aa ga
NK024(ya)001:3720: a ti pa ta ye h+aum dzah bee sh+ra ba
NK024(ya)001:3721: na a ti pa ta ye h+aum dzah brah+ma ne
NK024(ya)001:3722: h+aum dzah in+d+ra a h+aum dzah ag+na ye h+aum dzah
NK024(ya)001:3723: ya ma ye h+aum dzah n+airti t+ya ye h+aum dzah
NK024(ya)001:3724: wa ru na ye h+aum dzah w+aa ya we h+aum
NK024(ya)001:3725: dzah ku be r+aa ya h+aum dzah i sh+aa na
NK024(ya)001:3726: ye h+aum dzah pyi thi w+ai a ti pa ta
NK024(ya)001:3727: ye h+aum dzah zhes bkug ste mchod yon 'bul ba
NK024(ya)001:3729: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK024(ya)001:3730: tshur gshegs chos skyong mgon po rnams //
NK024(ya)001:3731: mchod yon bzhes nas 'di nyid du //
NK024(ya)001:3732: mchod pas bdag la dgyes par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:3733: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+ha ra
NK024(ya)001:3734: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa nam ga ga
NK024(ya)001:3735: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3736: rnam lnga 'bul ba ni phyag rgyar bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:3737: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:3738: lha rdzas bzang po'i bdug spos 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3739: chos skyong mgon po rnams la 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:3740: bstan pa bsrung phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3741: badz+ra d+h+au pe sogs gong ltar 'bul zhes pa dkrol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3742: p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3743: gtsang zhing gtsang mar lha rdzas bzang po'i me tog 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3744: chos skyong mgon po bstan pa bsrung phyir badz+ra push+pe
NK024(ya)001:3745: p+au dza me g+ha gtsang zhing gtsang mar lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:3747: chos skyong mgon po bstan pa bsrung phyir badz+ra +aa
NK024(ya)001:3748: lo ke p+au dza me g+ha gtsang zhing gtsang mar
NK024(ya)001:3749: lha rdzas bzang po'i dri chab 'di //
NK024(ya)001:3750: chos skyong mgon po bstan pa bsrung phyir badz+ra gan+d+he
NK024(ya)001:3751: p+au dza me g+ha gtsang zhing gtsang mar lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:3753: chos skyong mgon po bstan pa bsrung phyir badz+ra nee
NK024(ya)001:3754: wid+ya p+au dza me g+ha gtsang zhing gtsang mar lha
NK024(ya)001:3756: chos skyong mgon po bstan pa bsrung phyir badz+ra shap+da
NK024(ya)001:3757: p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na
NK024(ya)001:3759: rol mo'i sngags badz+ra g+han+de ra ni ta zhes sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:3760: mchod pa sprin gyi gzungs na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya sogs brjod /
NK024(ya)001:3761: bstod cing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3762: ri rgyal lhun po'i phyogs bzhi nas //
NK024(ya)001:3764: spyan mi bzang dang rnam thos sras //'khor dang bcas la mchod pa 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:3765: bdag gi re ba bsgrub tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:3766: dbang po rdo rje 'chang ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3767: lha yi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK024(ya)001:3768: shar phyogs gdon gyi tshogs bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:3769: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:3770: me ste sreg bya za ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3771: drang srong rgyal po shar lho gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de gshin rje be con 'chang ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3772: ma mo'i rgyal po lho phyogs gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de bden dang bral ba legs ldan lha //
NK024(ya)001:3773: srin po'i rgyal po sna tshogs gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de zhags pa thogs pa chu yi lha //
NK024(ya)001:3774: bden pa bsrung ba nor gyi bdag /
NK024(ya)001:3775: nub phyogs gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de rlung ste srog kyang 'dzin pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3776: tshig bsrung gdon gyi bdag po ste //
NK024(ya)001:3777: nub byang gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de gnod sbyin lag na dbyug to thogs //
NK024(ya)001:3778: nor bsrung gdon gyi bdag po ste //
NK024(ya)001:3779: byang phyogs don gyi mchod cing bstod de dbang dang ldan pa 'dren pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:3780: bgegs kyi rgyal po gdon gyi bdag /
NK024(ya)001:3781: byang shar gdon gyi mchod cing bstod de 'og gi klu ste sa yi bdag /
NK024(ya)001:3782: sa 'dzin lag pa chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:3783: dam tshig shes ba'i mchod cing bstod de steng gi lha rnams thams cad dang //
NK024(ya)001:3784: nyi ma zla ba gza' chen po //
NK024(ya)001:3785: gza' dang rgyu skar bcas pa la //
NK024(ya)001:3786: mchod cing bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:3787: d+hi ta rash+t+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3788: bi ru d+ha ka ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3789: bi ru bak+sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3790: bee sh+ra wa na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3796: wa ru na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3797: w+aa ya we ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3798: ku be r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3799: i sh+aa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3805: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK024(ya)001:3806: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ud+ga te s+pha ra na i
NK024(ya)001:3807: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3808: zhes lan gsum mam bdun gyis gtor ma 'bul lo
NK024(ya)001:3809: //'dir yi ge rnying pa rnams la mtshan sngags ma
NK024(ya)001:3810: gtogs gtor sngags nges par chad skyon 'dug pas 'di
NK024(ya)001:3811: ltar 'thad / bsngo zhing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:3812: tshad ma mchis pa'i mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3813: yon tan gyi mgron tshangs pa dang brgya byin /
NK024(ya)001:3814: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:3819: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:3820: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon pany+tsi ka dang /
NK024(ya)001:3821: btsun mo dpal ldan ha ri ka dang /
NK024(ya)001:3822: sras 'phrog ma'i bu lnga brgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:3823: rdo rje rigs kyi srung ma thugs dam can gtsang
NK024(ya)001:3824: mar gnas pa rnams la mchod pa 'bul ba ni
NK024(ya)001:3830: cang shes kyi rta la sogs pa 'dod pa'i yon
NK024(ya)001:3831: tan phun sum tshogs pa ma tshang ba med pa
NK024(ya)001:3832: bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3833: de ltar byung bas thugs brtse bas dgongs te byin gyis brlabs nas bzhes su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:3836: de ltar phul bas bdag cag rnams kyi mchod pa'i yo byad dman pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3837: rgyu rkyen ma tshogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3838: brjod pa ma dag pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3839: ting nge 'dzin mi gsal ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:3840: spyod lam bag med pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3841: le lo dang snyoms las su gyur pa ci mchis
NK024(ya)001:3842: pa thams cad srung ma dam tshig can khyed rnams
NK024(ya)001:3843: kyi spyan sngar mthol lo bshags so //
NK024(ya)001:3844: de ltar mthol zhing bshags nas bdag cag dpon slob
NK024(ya)001:3845: yon bdag 'khor bcas rnams kyi sngon gyi las las
NK024(ya)001:3846: gyur kyang rung / 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung /
NK024(ya)001:3847: 'jig rten 'dir yang nad mang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:3849: sems kyi sdug bsngal thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3851: gnod pa'i bgegs la sogs pa bsam pa ngan pa sbyor ba rtsub pa byed pa thams cad dang /
NK024(ya)001:3854: ltas ngan pa thams cad zlog cing zhi bar mdzad du sol /
NK024(ya)001:3855: gzhan yang 'byung po mi dang mi ma yin pa /
NK024(ya)001:3856: sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK024(ya)001:3857: gdug pa'i sems dang ldan pa /
NK024(ya)001:3858: drag shul gyi sems dang ldan pa de dag thams
NK024(ya)001:3859: cad bzlog cing gdul ba dang zhi zhing bsgyur bar
NK024(ya)001:3860: mdzad du gsol / gal te zhi bas 'dul du
NK024(ya)001:3861: ma 'tshal na gang la gang 'tshams pa'i chad pas
NK024(ya)001:3862: mdzad du gsol / bcad pa dang / bskrad cing gzir ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:3863: bsdigs shing dpa' bkong bar mdzad du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:3864: srung ma dam tshig dang mthun stobs can khyed rnams kyi mnga' 'og tu ma 'dus pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3865: sde rigs su ma gtogs pa gang yang ma mchis
NK024(ya)001:3866: pas de dag thams cad zhi ba dang 'dul bar
NK024(ya)001:3867: mdzad du gsol / mdor na nyes pa'i skyon thams
NK024(ya)001:3868: cad byang zhing dag pa dang legs pa'i yon tan
NK024(ya)001:3869: thams cad 'phel zhing rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:3871: gtor ma bar pa bsang ba dang bden sbyangs gong bzhin bya /
NK024(ya)001:3873: yang mchod pa gsol bsang sbyang byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:3874: gtor ma bar pa dang bsil gtor gnyis brtag pa bzhis brlab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:3875: bdag gi bsam pa'i stobs dang ni /
NK024(ya)001:3876: sogs kyi bden sbyangs byin gyis brlab pa rnams gong bzhin bya /
NK024(ya)001:3877: phyi'i khor yug la mgron 'gugs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3878: sarba ka ri sarba sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3879: pad+m+aan+ta kri ta badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:3880: lha dang klu dang gnod sbyin lto 'phye grul //
NK024(ya)001:3881: nam mkha' lding dang 'dab bzang lus srul po //
NK024(ya)001:3882: dri za srin po gdon gyi rigs rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:3883: gang dag sa la gnas pa'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK024(ya)001:3884: bdag gi pus mo sa la btsugs nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:3885: thal sbyar khyed rnams la yang gsol 'debs kyi //
NK024(ya)001:3886: bu smad bcas shing g.yog 'khor tshogs bcas rnams //
NK024(ya)001:3887: gnas 'dir phan gdags slad du 'dir gshegs shig /
NK024(ya)001:3888: e h+ye hi lo ka k+aa ra ya /
NK024(ya)001:3900: sa pa ri w+aa ra sa m+aa ya a n+ri
NK024(ya)001:3901: su tri pre du dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes bkug la
NK024(ya)001:3902: / de wa gan+d+he b+h+yah n+aa ga gan+d+he b+h+yah yak+sha
NK024(ya)001:3903: gan+d+he b+h+yah rak+sha sa gan+d+he b+h+yah gan+d+har+b+ha gan+d+he b+h+yah a
NK024(ya)001:3904: su ra gan+d+he b+h+yah ga ru da gan+d+he b+h+yah kin+na
NK024(ya)001:3905: ra gan+d+he b+h+yah ma ho r+aa ga gan+d+he b+h+yah ma
NK024(ya)001:3906: nu sh+ya gan+d+he b+h+yah a ma nu sh+ya gan+d+he b+h+yahs+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:3907: / h+aa / zhes dri cha ba kyi mchod yon phul /
NK024(ya)001:3909: bar 'dir mchod pa lnga dang gtor ma gong bzhin du 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:3910: zhes gsungs pas mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:3921: a ma nu sh+ya sa ba ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham /
NK024(ya)001:3928: shap+da pra t+ai ts+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:3930: de wa n+aa ga zhes sogs rang sngags kyi mjug tu /
NK024(ya)001:3931: a ma nu sh+ya sa pa ri w+aa ra na
NK024(ya)001:3932: mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu khe
NK024(ya)001:3933: b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ud+ga te s+pha ra na i mam
NK024(ya)001:3934: ga ga na kham gri h+na dam ba lin+ta ye
NK024(ya)001:3935: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes lan bdun nam gsum gyis phul /
NK024(ya)001:3937: na mo mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma bar pa 'di
NK024(ya)001:3938: 'bul zhing bsngo ba'i gnas su gyur pa mtho srid
NK024(ya)001:3939: pa'i rtse mo man chad nas na rag dmyal ba
NK024(ya)001:3940: yan chad du 'gro ba rigs drug /
NK024(ya)001:3942: skye ba rnam pa bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can snying
NK024(ya)001:3943: rje'i mgron du gyur pa thams cad la 'bul lo
NK024(ya)001:3947: de ltar bsngosa pas lha ltung ba'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK024(ya)001:3948: lha ma yin 'thab rtsod kyi sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:3950: byol song gcig la gcig 'tshe ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:3951: yi dwags bkres skom gyi sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:3952: dmyal ba tsha grang gi sdug bsngal las thar nas
NK024(ya)001:3953: bde 'gro mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar gyur
NK024(ya)001:3954: cig / gzhan yang long ba rnams gzugs mthong bar
NK024(ya)001:3955: gyur cig /'on pa rnams rna bas sgra thos par
NK024(ya)001:3956: cig / gyur cig / dig pa rnams smra shes par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3957: zha bo rnams 'gro shes par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3958: gcer bu rnams gos rnyed par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3959: dbul po rnams nor rnyed par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3960: ltogs pa rnams zas rnyed par gyur cig /'jigs pa rnams skyabs rnyed par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3961: nad pa rnams nad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3962: sbyin pa dam pa sems kyi rgyan du gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3963: sems kyi yo byad du gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3964: don gyi mchog tu gyur cig /'di ltar mchod sbyin
NK024(ya)001:3965: gyi gtor ma 'di la brten nas bdag cag gi
NK024(ya)001:3966: gnas skabs su nad dang gnod pa zhi zhing tshe
NK024(ya)001:3968: sems can gyi sgrib pa gnyis byang /
NK024(ya)001:3969: tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs nas bla na med pa'i
NK024(ya)001:3970: byang chub rin po che myur du thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:3971: cig /'byung po gang dag ri rab steng gnas dang
NK024(ya)001:3972: // dga' ba'i tshal dang lha yi khang pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3973: shar nub ri dang nyi zla'i khyim rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:3974: ri bo kun la gang dag gnas pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3975: chu bo kun dang chu bo'i mdo rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:3976: rin chen gnas na lhag par gang gnas dang //
NK024(ya)001:3977: mtsho dang rdzing bu lteng ka ngogs rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:3978: g.ya' chu bsil ma can la gnas pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3979: grong dang phyugs lhas grong khyer stong pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3980: khang stong dag dang lha yi khang pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3981: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten gnas dag dang //
NK024(ya)001:3982: dka' thub gnas dang glang chen bres dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:3983: rgyal po'i dkor khang dag na gnas pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3984: lam 'phrang rgyan srang dang ni bzhi mdo dang //
NK024(ya)001:3985: gang dag lam po che dang shing gcig dang //
NK024(ya)001:3986: dur khrod chen po nags tshal chen po dang //
NK024(ya)001:3987: seng ge dred dang gcan gzan gnas dag dang //'brog chen 'jigs su rung bar gang gnas dang //
NK024(ya)001:3988: gang dag gling mchog dag na gnas pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3989: lhun po dur khrod dag na gnas pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:3990: rab tu dgyes shing mgu bar gyur nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:3991: phreng ba me tog dri dang bdug pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:3992: bstod dang gtor ma mar me gus 'bul na //'di dag btung zhing legs par gsol nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:3993: bdag gi las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:3994: sems can thams cad bde gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3995: kun kyang gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK024(ya)001:3996: yang na de bzhin gshegs gsungs pa //
NK024(ya)001:3997: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3998: yang na sems can thams cad kyang //'dod yon phun sum tshogs gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:3999: bsod nams 'di yi byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:4000: byol song gcig la gcig za ba //
NK024(ya)001:4001: sdug bsngal rnams ni yongs mi 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:4002: yi dwags rnams la zas dang skom //
NK024(ya)001:4003: thogs pa med par 'byung bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:4004: sems can dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gang //
NK024(ya)001:4005: rnam pa mang po gnod pa yang //
NK024(ya)001:4006: de dag thams cad ma lus pa //
NK024(ya)001:4007: thogs pa med par zhi gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4009: lha klu gnod sbyin dri za dang //'byung po mang po gang 'khod pa //
NK024(ya)001:4010: bsam pa yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:4011: khro bo chen po'i bka' yis ni //
NK024(ya)001:4012: rang rang gnas su bde bar dengs //
NK024(ya)001:4015: gtor ma gsum pa bgegs gtor bsang sbyang brtag pa bzhis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK024(ya)001:4016: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:4017: zhes sogs kyi bden brjod byas la /
NK024(ya)001:4018: me ri'i phyi rol tu bgegs rnams 'gugs phyir /
NK024(ya)001:4019: sarba ka ri sarba sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:4020: pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:4021: khro bo la bstod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:4022: h+r+aih rgyal ba kun gyi bdag po chos kyi sku //
NK024(ya)001:4023: chos rje 'od dpag med pa rdo rje'i chos //
NK024(ya)001:4024: sbyan ras gzigs sprul h+r+aihls rngams chen sku //
NK024(ya)001:4025: rta mgrin rta skad bzhad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4026: dbang chen dbang 'dul dbang gi rgyal po ste //
NK024(ya)001:4027: dbang gi mdog dmar bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:4028: dbang chen rngams brjid nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi //
NK024(ya)001:4029: dbang mdzad dbang gi sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4030: chos nyid bdud rtsi mchog gis dbang bskur zhing //
NK024(ya)001:4031: dug gsum brten pa phung mdzad dpal 'bar ba //
NK024(ya)001:4032: gdug pa'i klu rnams brjid pa'i zhabs kyis gnon //
NK024(ya)001:4033: dug chen bdud rtsir bsgyur la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4034: rig pa'i rgyal po khro bo kun gyi rje //
NK024(ya)001:4035: byams chen rab khros khro rgyal kun gyis bskor //
NK024(ya)001:4036: stong nyid dbyings las ma g.yos mkha' dkyil nas //'jigs gzugs nyi zla 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4037: zhes bstod la h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:4038: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing
NK024(ya)001:4039: ci yang ma yin pa la ji lta bsam pa
NK024(ya)001:4041: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyis ye shes
NK024(ya)001:4042: thugs su chud cing sems can don la dgongs pa
NK024(ya)001:4043: skad cig kyang mi g.yel ba'i bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4044: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi dgongs pa bskang
NK024(ya)001:4045: zhing sems can gyi mgon skyabs mdzad par zhal gyis
NK024(ya)001:4046: bzhes pa'i bden pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:4047: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4049: bla ma dam pa'i bka' bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:4050: gdug cing sdang ba'i sems dang ldan pa'i bgegs kyi rigs thams cad skad cig la 'dir 'dus shig /
NK024(ya)001:4051: h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata /
NK024(ya)001:4052: ha la ha la h+aum h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:4053: tri yam dzah badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:4056: sarba big+h+n+aana na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi
NK024(ya)001:4057: shwa mu khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra
NK024(ya)001:4058: na i mam ga ga na kham grih+na dam ba
NK024(ya)001:4060: lan gsum gyis gtor ma sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:4062: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma tha ma 'di sbyin zhing
NK024(ya)001:4063: bsngo ba'i gnas ni bdag cag dpon slob yon mchod
NK024(ya)001:4064: 'khor bcas kyi tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas
NK024(ya)001:4065: da lta yan chad kyi lan chags bu lon gyi
NK024(ya)001:4066: mgron du gyur pa bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'i
NK024(ya)001:4067: tshogs la lus dang srog gi glud dang longs spyod
NK024(ya)001:4071: de ltar phul bas bsad pas tshe thung ba /
NK024(ya)001:4073: phrogs pas nor dbul ba'i lan chags thams cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4074: bu lon thams cad khyer bar gyur cig /'khon rtsod thams cad byang bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4075: bgegs kyi bar chad thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4076: sngar gyi gnod pa 'phro bsdus la phyin chad mi byed pa'i dam bcas pa bzhin khas long zhig /
NK024(ya)001:4077: nang mchod kyi bdud rtsi'am las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:4078: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu /
NK024(ya)001:4079: dam tshig nyams na sreg bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:4080: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub thob //
NK024(ya)001:4082: cis te dam tshig 'das na ni //
NK024(ya)001:4083: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:4084: de ma thag tu bkas nas gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:4085: bdud brgyud rigs ni brlag par byed //
NK024(ya)001:4086: de rnams kyi spyi bor rdo rje bzhag pa'i tshul bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:4087: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:4088: rdo rje chen po mchog 'dzin pa //
NK024(ya)001:4089: mgon po chen pos byin brlabs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:4090: blo ldan gang zhig 'da' ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:4091: rdo rje 'dzin pas mod la spongs //
NK024(ya)001:4092: spangs pa'i sems can chen po de //
NK024(ya)001:4093: ji snyed 'khor ba'i spyod rgyud du //
NK024(ya)001:4094: ngan song gsum du yang nas yang //
NK024(ya)001:4095: shin tu mi bzad cho nge 'debs //
NK024(ya)001:4096: bdag nyid chen po sangs rgyas bka'//
NK024(ya)001:4097: tshig las 'das na rdul phran bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4098: nga ni dbang phyug chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:4099: rgyal chen rigs bzhi nga yi g.yog /
NK024(ya)001:4100: lha srin sde brgyad nga yi bran //
NK024(ya)001:4101: dam tshig dag la 'da' mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:4102: de ltar khyod kyis shes kyis la //
NK024(ya)001:4103: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' ma bcog /
NK024(ya)001:4104: dam pa chos kyi gzhung ma dbral //
NK024(ya)001:4105: sems can dmyal ba'i rgyu ma gsog /
NK024(ya)001:4107: sngags kyi dam tshig tshul ma bshig /
NK024(ya)001:4108: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK024(ya)001:4109: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK024(ya)001:4110: rang gi sems ni yongs su dul //'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:4111: lus kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:4112: gang gi sdom pa legs pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:4113: yid kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:4114: thams cad du ni sdom pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:4115: thams cad bsrung ba'i dge slong dag /
NK024(ya)001:4116: sdug bsngal kun las nges grol lo //
NK024(ya)001:4117: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK024(ya)001:4118: dag cing gsal la rnyog pa med //
NK024(ya)001:4119: gzung du med cing brjod du med //
NK024(ya)001:4120: rgyu dang las la kun tu 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:4121: ngo bo nyid med gnas med par //
NK024(ya)001:4122: de ltar chos rnams shes gyis la //
NK024(ya)001:4123: sems can don la mnyam med byos //
NK024(ya)001:4125: zhes pas so so'i gnas su song bar bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:4126: sum+b+ha sogs khro bo'i drag sngags kyis bskrad do //
NK024(ya)001:4127: de ltar cha gsum gyi cho ga 'di rtsa bar dbang rdor ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:4129: 'byung po gang dag rnams sogs khongs su bsdus te mi gsal bar 'dug par /
NK024(ya)001:4130: spyir gsar rnying gnyis ka'i lugs la cha gsum mi 'dra ba du ma 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:4131: khyad par bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rnams las bstan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4132: sh+rad+d+ha ka ra wa rma'i rgya gzhung bzhin ngor pa
NK024(ya)001:4133: rdo rje 'chang gis mdzad pa sogs khungs che ba
NK024(ya)001:4134: 'dug mod kyang / 'dir bka' ma rang gi cha
NK024(ya)001:4135: gsum dpal sdom ma'i yig rnying sor gnas ltar bris
NK024(ya)001:4136: 'dug mod kyang / pa yin pas / deng sang
NK024(ya)001:4137: yongs grags dang tshig gong 'og mi mthun cing zur
NK024(ya)001:4138: mi 'dra ba 'ga' re 'dug pa 'di ni rang
NK024(ya)001:4139: lugs rnam dag yin phyir ma dag par go nas
NK024(ya)001:4140: gsar ma'i bsre lhad kyis bris bsub mi mdzad par
NK024(ya)001:4141: 'dug mod kyang / pa yin pas / zhu / rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:4142: de nas sngar bzhin gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:4143: pa gsal btab la sngar bzhin mchod cing bstod la
NK024(ya)001:4144: / 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab /
NK024(ya)001:4146: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK024(ya)001:4147: zhes sogs kyis gshegs gsol dang /
NK024(ya)001:4148: 'jig rten pa'i mgron rnams gshegs la zhes gsungs mod /
NK024(ya)001:4149: 'on kyang bla ma rnams kyi phyag bzhes dang gsung
NK024(ya)001:4150: rgyun la mdo dbang tshugs nas ma grol bar nyin
NK024(ya)001:4151: star gyi cho ga so so'i skabs thob kyi dus
NK024(ya)001:4152: cha gsum gtong dgos pas cha gsum dkyil 'khor ma
NK024(ya)001:4153: bsdus par bzhag kyang chog gsung ba shin tu 'thad
NK024(ya)001:4154: par snang bas / go yul shong na de bzhin bya /
NK024(ya)001:4155: gal te gnas khang sogs ma shong tshe phyag rdor
NK024(ya)001:4156: gyi dbang grub nas dkyil 'khor gnyis lhan du gshegs
NK024(ya)001:4157: gsol byas la / nyin ltar gyi cha gsum skabs
NK024(ya)001:4158: dkyil 'khor med par gtor ma bsham zhing btang bas
NK024(ya)001:4159: gsol byas la / 'grub la / de ltar bgyid
NK024(ya)001:4160: tshe cha gsum po kho na ma gtogs 'das gtor
NK024(ya)001:4161: gyi mchod gtor 'bul ba rnams mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:4162: de yang gtor ma dang lhan du mchod pa phreng tshar gcig bsham na legs shing /
NK024(ya)001:4163: 'on kyang deng sang cha gsum la mchod pa mi bsham pa 'dug mod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:4164: phyi rol gtor ma'i skabs phyag len rnam dag la
NK024(ya)001:4165: nyer spyod bsham pa'i srol yod pas legs par snang
NK024(ya)001:4166: / 'di la gtsang rong gong ra lo chen gyis /
NK024(ya)001:4167: cha gsum ni 'byung po'i dkyil 'khor yin pas rgyun
NK024(ya)001:4168: par bsham na mi 'thad cing bar gcod 'jug tshul
NK024(ya)001:4169: gsung ba thos pa khong mkhas pa chen po'i thugs
NK024(ya)001:4170: khur lci zhing mkhas par yang snang mod kyi /
NK024(ya)001:4171: 'di rigs kyi gsung shin tu mang bar snang ste /
NK024(ya)001:4172: rdo rje phur pa la yi dam du byas na
NK024(ya)001:4173: phur pa phrin las kyi lha yin pas phrin las
NK024(ya)001:4174: kyis g.yengs nas bar gcod du 'gyur bas phur pa
NK024(ya)001:4175: la yi dam gtso bor mi byed ces nges par
NK024(ya)001:4176: slob ma rnams la yang yang gdams par dngos slob
NK024(ya)001:4177: rnams kyi ngag sgros las thos /
NK024(ya)001:4178: de la dang po cha gsum 'byung po'i dkyil 'khor yin pa yang dka' ste /
NK024(ya)001:4179: don la rgyud sde'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo nas
NK024(ya)001:4180: 'khor gyi bar nyi ma dang zer gyi tshul du
NK024(ya)001:4181: dgongs pa mnyam par bzhed pa rang cag snga 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:4182: ba rnams kyi grub mtha' yin pa snyan du ma
NK024(ya)001:4183: gsan nam / cha dang po gtsang rigs kyi mgon
NK024(ya)001:4184: po rnams ni rnam pa 'jig rten pa ltar snang
NK024(ya)001:4185: yang don dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi khor yug skyong
NK024(ya)001:4186: zhing gtso bo'i zhal mthong ba sha stag yin /
NK024(ya)001:4187: cha bar pa lha klu gnod sbyin sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:4188: cha tha ma'i bgegs rigs rnams ni gong 'khod ltar don ye shes kyi cha las sprul kyang /
NK024(ya)001:4189: rnam pa 'jig rten pa kho na yin phyir gtor
NK024(ya)001:4190: ma so sor btang rjes bskrad zin pas slar zhugs
NK024(ya)001:4191: dogs kyi thugs mdzangs mi dgos pa 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:4192: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gzhon nu la skur pa
NK024(ya)001:4193: tshabs chen du song bar bsam shes kun gyis go
NK024(ya)001:4194: mod la / de yang spyir lha la bzang ngan
NK024(ya)001:4195: med kyang gang 'dul gyi skur bstan pa'i phrin las
NK024(ya)001:4196: rmad du byung ba'i rnam par 'phrul pas bar gcod
NK024(ya)001:4197: sel ba'i lhar phur pa kho na oo di ya
NK024(ya)001:4198: na'i mkhan po chen po des lan brgyar basngagasa pa
NK024(ya)001:4199: mod la / dang / der ma zad grong gseb
NK024(ya)001:4200: kyi tshes bcu ba rnams kyi kha nas kyang gsol
NK024(ya)001:4202: bal yul yang le shod kyi brag phug tu yang
NK024(ya)001:4203: dag bde chen snying po bsgrubs pa'i tshe bar gcod
NK024(ya)001:4204: bgegs rnams rdo rje phur pas bsgral phyag rgya chen
NK024(ya)001:4205: po'i dngos grub gnas der thob zer ba rlung ltar
NK024(ya)001:4206: grags mod / slob dpon chen po'i mchog gi dngos
NK024(ya)001:4207: grub sgrub pa'i tshul bstan pa'i bar gcod kyang phur
NK024(ya)001:4208: pas sel tshul bstan pa kun la grags shing grub
NK024(ya)001:4209: grags mod / / phrin las yin na zang zing
NK024(ya)001:4210: gi phrin las yin pas khyab pa de 'dra nang
NK024(ya)001:4211: pa'i chos lugs ji ltar yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:4212: spyir phrin las rnam pa bzhi zhes yongs su grags pa ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:4215: zang zing gi phrin las sogs grangs mang bar 'dug
NK024(ya)001:4216: pas bsdu dngos bzhi'i sgo nas sems can gyi don
NK024(ya)001:4217: mdzad pa'i skyes chen rnams zang zing la yang skyon
NK024(ya)001:4219: de'i zhar las bstan 'gror phan bde 'dra yang 'grub
NK024(ya)001:4220: par gsungs pas rnying ma ba rnams la mgo rmog
NK024(ya)001:4221: bcog gi dbang che'i bka' skyon mi gnang bar zhu
NK024(ya)001:4222: lags / zhes pa ni bar skabs kyi brgal lan nyams dag'i tshul du 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:4224: de nas rang nyid 'og nas 'byung ba ltar gsol
NK024(ya)001:4225: ba btab pa nas bzung ste dbang rnams rdzogs par
NK024(ya)001:4226: blangs la / zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK024(ya)001:4227: bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang blang bar dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:4228: gtso bo dang rang gi mdo dbang nos pa'i bla
NK024(ya)001:4229: ma tha mi dad par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:4230: las bum gyi chus khrus dang /
NK024(ya)001:4231: man+dala gsol gdab nas bzung ste bkra shis rdzas brgyad
NK024(ya)001:4232: kyi bar slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba bzhin
NK024(ya)001:4233: du blangs la dbang rdzas rnams rang gi spyi bor
NK024(ya)001:4234: bzhag / tshig rnams ji bzhin brjod /
NK024(ya)001:4235: bla ma'i bya ba thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bos mdzad par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:4236: mthar gtso bum gyi chus kyang bkru zhing btung /
NK024(ya)001:4239: bran du khas blangs sogs kyang bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4240: de nas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro
NK024(ya)001:4241: ba phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bskur bar byed pa
NK024(ya)001:4242: la / slob ma rnams gral la 'khod /
NK024(ya)001:4244: gleng gzhi dang dgag brgyad bshad pa'i rjes su /
NK024(ya)001:4245: de nas rang gsang bdag gi nga rgyal dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:4246: pas bgegs gtor slob ma rnams la bskor te btang
NK024(ya)001:4247: / las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:4250: zhes gsungs pa 'dir blangs te las bum gyi chus khrus bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:4251: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:4252: zhes sogs sngags dang bcas pa brjod /
NK024(ya)001:4256: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che las
NK024(ya)001:4257: grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du
NK024(ya)001:4258: las gtor ma zag pa med pa ye shes kyi
NK024(ya)001:4259: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho kha dog dri ro nus pa
NK024(ya)001:4260: phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:4261: +aah h+aum lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:4262: g.yas rdo rje khu tshur dang bcas pa'i mchog sbyin
NK024(ya)001:4263: gyi phyag rgya slob ma rnams la bskor zhing mthar
NK024(ya)001:4265: sarba big+h+nana na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi
NK024(ya)001:4266: shwa mu khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra
NK024(ya)001:4267: na i mam ga ga na kham gri h+na dam
NK024(ya)001:4270: lag pa gnyis khu tshur g.yas steng du byas la rgyab sprad pa mathe'u chung gnyis sbrel /
NK024(ya)001:4271: mdzub mo gnyis brkyang ba h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya snying gar bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:4273: rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal
NK024(ya)001:4274: ldan bla ma dam pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK024(ya)001:4275: dang / sangs rgyas kyi bka' chos kyi dge 'dun
NK024(ya)001:4276: gyi gsang sngags dang rig sngags dang gzugs sngags dang
NK024(ya)001:4277: snying po phyag rgya rnam pa dag pa'i khyad par
NK024(ya)001:4278: du yang bcom ldan 'das gsang ba'i bdag po phyag
NK024(ya)001:4279: na rdo rje'i lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:4281: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlab kyis deng 'dir
NK024(ya)001:4282: rdo rje'i slob ma rnams la dbang bskur bar byed
NK024(ya)001:4283: pa la bar du gcod par rtsom pa'i bgegs kyi
NK024(ya)001:4284: rigs gang yin pa de dag thams cad la rgyud
NK024(ya)001:4285: sde dang mthun pa'i gtor ma 'dis tshims shing mgu
NK024(ya)001:4286: bar gyis la rang rang gi gnas su song zhig
NK024(ya)001:4287: / gang dag mi 'gro zhing bar du gcod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:4288: tshogs de dag thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK024(ya)001:4289: cad kyi mthu stobs las byung ba'i khro bo'i rdo
NK024(ya)001:4290: rje rab tu 'bar ba 'dis mgo bo tshal ba
NK024(ya)001:4292: so lugs mtshams gcod kyi tshig snga ma bsgyur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:4295: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas /
NK024(ya)001:4296: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:4297: thams cad thugs rjes bkang zin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:4298: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK024(ya)001:4300: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:4301: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:4302: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4304: phyag rdor gyi sngags dang sum+b+ha brjod /
NK024(ya)001:4306: yungs thun gyis bsdigs shing rol mo drag po bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4307: bla ma la la gsar mar khrus thog mar bya de nas bgegs gtor gtong /
NK024(ya)001:4308: rnying mar de gnyis go ldog dgos zer yang gsar
NK024(ya)001:4309: ma'i dbang rnams la khrus ma gtogs bgegs gtor mi
NK024(ya)001:4310: gtong zhing / gal te gtong ba rnams kyang rnying ma'i rgyas 'gebs su snang la /
NK024(ya)001:4311: dbye ba phyes mdog de yang ti thug rigs 'agre'o //
NK024(ya)001:4312: de nas man+dala gyi me tog bkye zhing thams cad
NK024(ya)001:4313: kyi nas phud man+dala steng du 'bab phyir phud bsdus
NK024(ya)001:4315: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:4316: don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK024(ya)001:4317: par bya / de'i ched du 'dir 'dus pa chen
NK024(ya)001:4318: po mdo yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor chen por
NK024(ya)001:4319: smin byed kyi dbang zab mo mnyan te don tshul
NK024(ya)001:4320: bzhin du nyams su blang snyam pa byang chub kyi
NK024(ya)001:4321: mchog tu sems bskyed pa sngon du btang ste gsan
NK024(ya)001:4322: par bya / 'tshal / de la thog mar chos
NK024(ya)001:4323: nyan pa'i kun tu spyod pa rnams gal che bar
NK024(ya)001:4324: par bya / 'tshal / gda' ste / de yang
NK024(ya)001:4325: bdag cag gi ston pa bcom ldan 'das thub pa
NK024(ya)001:4326: sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod pa na
NK024(ya)001:4327: rgyal bu zla bar gyur pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:4328: bram ze chos smra ba las 'di ltar thos te /
NK024(ya)001:4329: rab tu dma' ba'i stan la 'dug /
NK024(ya)001:4330: dul ba'i dpal ni rab tu bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:4331: dga' dang ldan pa'i mig gis blta //
NK024(ya)001:4332: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4333: gus pa bskyed cing rtse gcig btud //
NK024(ya)001:4334: rab tu dang la dri med yid //
NK024(ya)001:4335: nad pa sman pa'i tshig mnyan bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4336: rim gro bskyed de chos nyon cig /
NK024(ya)001:4338: gu ru pad+ma'i man ngag las /
NK024(ya)001:4339: mig gi dbang po chos smra'i zhal la blta //
NK024(ya)001:4340: rna ba'i dbang po ma yengs gsung la nyan //
NK024(ya)001:4341: yid kyi dbang po tshig zung don la brtag /
NK024(ya)001:4344: dge slong dag legs par rab tu nyon la yid la gzung zhig dang /
NK024(ya)001:4345: ngas khyod la bstan par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4346: zhes gsungs pa ltar gus pas nyan dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:4347: de'i mi mthun phyogs snod kyi dri ma drug kyang spang dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:4349: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK024(ya)001:4350: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK024(ya)001:4351: phyi rol rnam g.yeng nang bsdus dang //
NK024(ya)001:4352: skyo ba nyan pa'i dri ma yin //
NK024(ya)001:4355: rtogs pa thams cad legs par bsdus nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:4356: shin tu bsam pa bzang po ldan pas nyon //
NK024(ya)001:4357: brjed ngas blo la rdo rje sems dpa' sogs //
NK024(ya)001:4358: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis byin mi rlob //
NK024(ya)001:4359: ces gsungs pa ltar sgo gsum legs par bsdams te gzhan du ma yengs par gsan dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:4360: gsan bya'i chos ni zhes 'brel dgod /
NK024(ya)001:4361: rtsa bar gsungs pa'i de nas zab cing rgya che
NK024(ya)001:4362: ba'i chos bshad de zhes dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi sgrub
NK024(ya)001:4363: mchod kyi dbu na 'dug pa de 'dir blangs na
NK024(ya)001:4365: de yang rtsa ba ji bzhin par bshad na rig
NK024(ya)001:4366: 'dzin gong ma rnams kyi gsung rgyun byin rlabs kyi
NK024(ya)001:4367: mthu dpung che bas sor gnas su bris la /
NK024(ya)001:4368: 'on kyang lung khungs ma dag pa dang lung snga
NK024(ya)001:4369: phyi'i go rim ldog ste thar chags su bris pa
NK024(ya)001:4370: sogs ma dag pa rnams dag par bcos shing gzhan
NK024(ya)001:4371: rtsa ba sgra ji bzhin par bris pa la /
NK024(ya)001:4372: de yang 'o skol 'khor ba khrag gi rgya mtsho
NK024(ya)001:4373: lta bu'i nang na sdug bsngal gyi rba klong dpag
NK024(ya)001:4374: tu med pa la longs spyod cing zhen /
NK024(ya)001:4375: bya ba ma yin pa la mngon par zhen pa ni bshang pa'i srin bu dang 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:4376: 'dod yon la mngon par chags pa ni lan tsh+wa'i chu dang 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:4377: ci byas sdug bsngal la spyod pa ni rgya mo'i gzan dang 'dra ste /
NK024(ya)001:4378: de ltar 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin la bde ba skad cig kyang med de /
NK024(ya)001:4380: mi gtsang ba la dri zhi ma med bzhin 'gro lnga dag na bde ba med //
NK024(ya)001:4383: 'gro ba 'di dag ming dang gzugs kyi 'dam la chags //
NK024(ya)001:4384: rlung gi 'khor lo lta bu'i 'khor ba'i 'khor lor 'khyams //
NK024(ya)001:4385: zhes gsungs so //'khor ba'i gnas na'ang thams cad sdug bsngal gyi rgyu la longs spyod de /
NK024(ya)001:4388: dud 'gro la gcig la gcig za /
NK024(ya)001:4392: de thams cad la thun mong du skye 'chi'i sdug
NK024(ya)001:4393: bsngal bsam gyis mi khyab bo //'khor ba'i sems can
NK024(ya)001:4394: gyi tshogs de dag la bsam na sems can tsam
NK024(ya)001:4395: po'i lus mthong na mi lus thob pa med pa
NK024(ya)001:4396: tsam / kha 'thor ba'i tshogs mthong na mi lus thob pa srid pa tsam ste /
NK024(ya)001:4397: de ltar slob dpon zhi ba lhas /
NK024(ya)001:4398: gang tshe dge spyad skal ldan yang //
NK024(ya)001:4399: dge ba bdag gis ma byas na //
NK024(ya)001:4400: ngan song sdug bsngal kun rmongs pa //
NK024(ya)001:4401: de tshe bdag gis ci byar yod //
NK024(ya)001:4402: dge ba dag kyang ma byas la //
NK024(ya)001:4403: sdig pa dag kyang nyer bsags na //
NK024(ya)001:4404: bskal pa bye ba brgya yang ni //
NK024(ya)001:4406: de nyid phyir na bcom ldan gyis //
NK024(ya)001:4407: rgya mtsho cher g.yeng gnya' shing gi //
NK024(ya)001:4408: bu gar rus spal mgrin chud ltar //
NK024(ya)001:4409: mi nyid shin tu thob dkar gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:4411: dal 'byor 'di ni rnyed pa shin tu dka'//
NK024(ya)001:4412: skyes bum don grub thob par gyur pa la //
NK024(ya)001:4413: gal te 'di la phan pa ma bsgrubs na //
NK024(ya)001:4414: phyis 'di yang dag 'byor pa ga la 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:4415: ji ltar mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum na //
NK024(ya)001:4416: glog 'gyur skad cig bar snang ston pa ltar //
NK024(ya)001:4417: de bzhin sangs rgyas mthu yis rgya lam na //'jig rten bsod nams blo gros thang 'ga' 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:4418: zhes dal 'byor gyi mi lus shin tu thob par dka' bar gsungs la /
NK024(ya)001:4419: gal te mi lus thang gcig thob srid kyang dge
NK024(ya)001:4420: ba ma bsags na don med stong log yin te
NK024(ya)001:4422: mi yi lus kyang thob mi 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:4423: mi lus thob par ma gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:4424: sdig pa 'ba' zhig dge ba med //
NK024(ya)001:4426: nam 'chi'i tshe la nges pa med de /
NK024(ya)001:4428: byas dang ma byas mi sdod pas //
NK024(ya)001:4429: na dang mi na kun gyis kyang //
NK024(ya)001:4430: glo bur tshe la yid mi brtan //
NK024(ya)001:4431: thams cad bor te chas dgos par //
NK024(ya)001:4432: bdag gis de ltar ma shes na //
NK024(ya)001:4434: tshe ma tshor bar zad pa yang /
NK024(ya)001:4435: nyin mtshan sdod pa yongs med par //
NK024(ya)001:4437: snon pa gud na yod med na //
NK024(ya)001:4439: bdag ni mal na 'dug bzhin du //
NK024(ya)001:4440: gnyer bshes rnams kyis mtha' bskor yang //
NK024(ya)001:4441: srog 'chad pa yi tshor ba dag /
NK024(ya)001:4442: bdag nyid gcig pus myong bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:4443: gshin rje'i pho nyas zin pa la //
NK024(ya)001:4444: gnyen gyis ci phan bshes ci phan //
NK024(ya)001:4445: de tshe bsod nams skyabs gcig na //
NK024(ya)001:4446: de yang bdag gis ma bsten to //
NK024(ya)001:4447: zhes gsungs pas 'chi ba rjes su dran dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:4448: nad med nyi ma 'di lta bur //
NK024(ya)001:4449: zas bcas 'tshe ba med kyang ni //
NK024(ya)001:4450: tshe ni skad cig bslu ba ste //
NK024(ya)001:4451: lus ni thang gcig brnyan po bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4453: de ring kho na mi 'chi zhes //
NK024(ya)001:4454: bde bar 'dug pa rigs ma yin //
NK024(ya)001:4455: zhes pas 'chi ba ma dran na gang bya ba chos su mi 'gyur te /
NK024(ya)001:4457: 'di ni sang bya 'di ni thang gcig 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:4458: bya //'di ni de ring bya zhes skye bo sems
NK024(ya)001:4459: byed na // gshin rje be con lag thogs zur gyis blta ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:4460: mig rtsa dmar khros ma rangs gad mo re snyam 'debs //
NK024(ya)001:4461: sos ka me tog rgyas pa'i dus 'di 'byung 'gyur zhing //
NK024(ya)001:4462: zla ba gsal ba mtshon pa'i ston dus 'di 'byung zhes //
NK024(ya)001:4463: skye bo thams cad dga' 'gyur bdag gi tshe 'di ni //
NK024(ya)001:4464: zad par 'gyur zhes shin tu mi dgar 'gyur ba med //
NK024(ya)001:4466: nges 'byung chen pos dal 'byor gyi snying po blangs
NK024(ya)001:4467: pa'i phyir tshogs gnyis bsags pa la 'bad dgos te
NK024(ya)001:4469: 'jig rten sdug bsngal ji snyed kun //
NK024(ya)001:4470: de kun mi dge byas las byung //
NK024(ya)001:4471: lha mi'i bde ba ji snyed kun //
NK024(ya)001:4472: de kun bsod nams bsags las thob //
NK024(ya)001:4473: bsod nams bsags pas bde ba thob //
NK024(ya)001:4474: de phyir yang dang yang du bsag /
NK024(ya)001:4476: de ltar du 'chi ba mi rtag ba'i gsal 'debs dang /
NK024(ya)001:4478: bde 'gro mtho ris dang dge ba bcu'i phan yon dang /
NK024(ya)001:4479: mi dge ba bcu'i nyes dmigs dang /
NK024(ya)001:4480: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal dang /
NK024(ya)001:4481: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa'i dad pa bskyed
NK024(ya)001:4482: pa la sogs chos zab cing rgya che ba bshad
NK024(ya)001:4483: cing / rgyud snod du rung ba'i nges shes bskyed la /
NK024(ya)001:4484: khyad par theg pa'i rim pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4486: yang sgos chos 'di'i bka' babs tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:4487: bla ma brgyud pa'i rim pa bshad de spro ba bskyed par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4490: bye brag snga 'gyur gyi chos khyad par 'phags tshul /
NK024(ya)001:4491: khyad par bka' ma'i chos kyi babs tshul sogs blo gros yangs par byas te 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:4492: de ltar mi nus na 'di'i dbu na bzhugs pa'i bla ma brgyud pa'i tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:4493: brgyud pa de las byung ba'i man ngag gi sbyi don rnams bklags so //
NK024(ya)001:4494: de ltar bka' srol bzang po 'dir 'jug pa la /
NK024(ya)001:4495: nang du 'dus la gleng gzhi bshad pa 'dir skabs su babs pas /
NK024(ya)001:4496: de la dang po gleng gzhi ni sangs rgyas ye
NK024(ya)001:4497: shes rin po che'i gab pa'i dbang le drug gi
NK024(ya)001:4498: dang por / spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi dang //
NK024(ya)001:4501: slob ma rnams la dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad par bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:4502: de'ang rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:4503: 'dod pa khams kyi gnas rigs 'di na bram ze'i
NK024(ya)001:4504: slob dpon dung gi phreng ba can zhes bya ba
NK024(ya)001:4505: / gos su dung gi phreng ba gyon pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK024(ya)001:4506: slob ma rgyal bu zhig yod de /
NK024(ya)001:4507: de la bram zes slob sbyang du byas pas rig
NK024(ya)001:4508: pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas par gyur pas rgyal bu'i
NK024(ya)001:4509: bsam pa la / da ni bdag kyang shes pa mang po dang ldan /
NK024(ya)001:4510: bram ze 'di min pa gong na med pas 'di gong du mi btang snyam nas /
NK024(ya)001:4511: bram ze la rgun chang blud de brgyal ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:4513: lce lcags kyus drangs te bcad /
NK024(ya)001:4514: lus rus sbal gyi khrag gis byug ste bud med mang pos mnan /
NK024(ya)001:4515: sgyid pa bcad de bzhag pas re zhig na bram
NK024(ya)001:4516: ze brgyal ba sangs nas rtsa na su yod snyam
NK024(ya)001:4518: blta bsam pa las mig med /
NK024(ya)001:4519: langs par bsam pas sgyid pa med /
NK024(ya)001:4520: bud med mang pos mnan pas dran pa nyams /
NK024(ya)001:4521: lus chu lbur dang rkong pas gang bar gyur pas /
NK024(ya)001:4522: des bsam pa 'di ltar sdug bsngal zhing nyams thag pa 'di sngon las yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:4523: gzhan phrag dog gis byas pa yin brtags pas rgyal bus byas par rig nas smod bor ba /
NK024(ya)001:4524: rgyal bu khyod la nga de tsam du drin che
NK024(ya)001:4525: yang 'di lta bu byed pa khyod skye ba gcig
NK024(ya)001:4526: gi tshe lus la mdze dang /
NK024(ya)001:4533: nad rnam pa drug gis thebs shing /
NK024(ya)001:4534: lus la sha za mo stong gi tshang bca' ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:4535: mig long zhing ngag lkugs pa dang yan lag zha zhing 'gro mi shes par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4536: de nas tshe 'phos nas ngan song gsum rim par
NK024(ya)001:4537: brgyud de dmyal bar skyes nas tshe rabs grangs med
NK024(ya)001:4538: par 'phags pa'i 'bral bu mi thob cing byang chub
NK024(ya)001:4539: kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4540: ces smod pa byas pas rgyal bu de yang myur
NK024(ya)001:4541: du tshe 'phos nas rang gi nyes byas kyi rnam
NK024(ya)001:4542: smin dang bram ze'i smod pa 'doms pa'i dbang gis
NK024(ya)001:4543: sems can lus srul po gcer bu can zhes bya
NK024(ya)001:4544: bar skyes te / lus la nad drug gis thebs /
NK024(ya)001:4545: sha za mo stong gi tshang bcas /
NK024(ya)001:4548: rkang pa zha ste sdug bsngal bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4549: de nas tshe 'phos nas dmyal khams bcu drug gi
NK024(ya)001:4550: kha brgyud nas bskal pa grangs med par 'phags pa'i
NK024(ya)001:4552: byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur pa la thug pa na /
NK024(ya)001:4553: bcom ldan 'das nyid kyi thugs ka nas dpal phyag na rdo rje phyungs nas bka' nod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:4554: khyod song la 'dod khams 'di na sems can lus
NK024(ya)001:4555: srul po can zhes tshe snga ma slob dpon la
NK024(ya)001:4556: ngan sems byas pa'i rnam smin nyams su myong ba
NK024(ya)001:4557: ste / de lta bu byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams la thug cing sdug bsngal la /
NK024(ya)001:4558: tshe 'phos nas dmyal bar lhung ba ni las gzhan
NK024(ya)001:4559: gyi rnam smin la thar srid kyang slob dpon la
NK024(ya)001:4560: ngan sems byas pa'i rnam smin shin tu sbyang dka'
NK024(ya)001:4561: bas lag na rdo rje khyod song la cho ga
NK024(ya)001:4562: zab mo'i byin rlabs mchog dbang 'di rnams bskur la
NK024(ya)001:4563: mtho ris kyi gnas su skyel bar gyis shig ces
NK024(ya)001:4564: bka' stsal to // lag na rdo rje yi rangs te bcom ldan 'das slar gsol pa /
NK024(ya)001:4565: bcom ldan 'das dbang rnams kyi rang bzhin bshad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:4567: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK024(ya)001:4568: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe //
NK024(ya)001:4569: rgyal srid 'bangs kyis phul bas na //
NK024(ya)001:4570: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:4571: sa bdag rgyal por gnas pa bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4572: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK024(ya)001:4573: lha dang lha min 'khor bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:4574: dbang bskur rdzas kyis mnga' gsol bas //
NK024(ya)001:4575: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:4576: phyag rgya gsang ba'i gnas bsrung ste //
NK024(ya)001:4577: bdud rtsi bum pas sdig rnams bkrus //
NK024(ya)001:4578: phreng ba cod pan tshul khrims dang //
NK024(ya)001:4579: rnam lnga'i thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK024(ya)001:4580: me long 'khor lo dung rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:4581: sna bdun 'khor los stegs btsugs te //
NK024(ya)001:4582: ral gri shes rab mda' gzhu dang //
NK024(ya)001:4583: seng ge nyi zla lta bu dang //
NK024(ya)001:4584: mtha' yas bkra shis rdzas brgyad byin //
NK024(ya)001:4585: bden pa'i bka' brjod bden brdar dang //
NK024(ya)001:4586: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
