NK024(ya)001:4587: rten 'brel rdzas rnams bsham nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:4588: dbang mchog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:4590: de nas phyag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i
NK024(ya)001:4591: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:4592: gshegs pa rnams sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:4593: rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya bcings te /
NK024(ya)001:4594: sems can lus srul po can gyi gnas lngar bkod
NK024(ya)001:4595: pas sha za mo stong gi gnas kyang byer ro
NK024(ya)001:4596: // de nas 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:4597: gis byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams su gyur
NK024(ya)001:4598: pa la thug pa sos nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:4599: snying po can du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK024(ya)001:4600: de nas dam pa rnams kyi thugs rje'i byin rlabs
NK024(ya)001:4601: kyi bdud rtsi bum pas dbang bskur nas lus mi
NK024(ya)001:4602: bde ba rnams bkrus nas dag par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4603: me tog phreng ba'i dbang bskur bas tshul khrims kyi
NK024(ya)001:4604: phreng ba zhig ral yongs su rdzogs nas ngan song
NK024(ya)001:4605: nas yongs su bzlog pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK024(ya)001:4606: to // cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum
NK024(ya)001:4607: na gnas pa'i bsam sbyor ngan pa'i bag chags dang
NK024(ya)001:4609: de nas gser gyi thur ma'i dbang bskur bas ma
NK024(ya)001:4610: rig pa'i ling tog gi thibs po phyungs nas gsal
NK024(ya)001:4611: bar gyur to // me long gis chos thams cad
NK024(ya)001:4612: gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma lta bu mthong ngo
NK024(ya)001:4613: bar gyur to // // gser gyi 'khor los rdzu
NK024(ya)001:4614: 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan nas khams gsum thams
NK024(ya)001:4615: cad du 'gro nus par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4616: dung gis tshangs ba'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4617: rgya gram gyis phyogs bcu nas sngags 'chang rnams kyis rtag tu bsrung bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4618: de nas rin po che sna bdun mkha' la brgyud mar byung ste 'khor lo //
NK024(ya)001:4624: glang po che rnams kyi dbang bskur bas phyir mi
NK024(ya)001:4625: ldog pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po sprin phung
NK024(ya)001:4627: de la ye shes kyi ral gri dang /
NK024(ya)001:4628: thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i mda' gzhu dang /
NK024(ya)001:4629: brjod pa seng ge myur ba'i gzugs brnyan rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:4630: dbang bskur bas skad cig ma la sangs rgyas te
NK024(ya)001:4631: / bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po zhes bya bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4632: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis legs
NK024(ya)001:4633: zhes bstod nas nyi ma dang zla ba phyag tu
NK024(ya)001:4634: phul ma thag tu nyi mas skye 'gro ma lus
NK024(ya)001:4635: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la ye shes
NK024(ya)001:4636: kyi 'od zer chen po dus mtha' med par shar
NK024(ya)001:4637: nas dro zhing 'jam par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4638: zla bas ni stong gsum gyi mun pa thams cad
NK024(ya)001:4639: dus gcig tu bsal nas rnam pa thams cad du
NK024(ya)001:4640: bsil zhing snang bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:4641: de nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi go 'phang chen po rdzogs par gyur te /
NK024(ya)001:4642: thams cad nas thams cad du bkra shis shing grub pa'i rdzas su gsungs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4647: gang zag dag pa gsal zhing rig pa'i glang po dang /
NK024(ya)001:4648: mkhyen pa'i dpal la sogs te sbyin pa'i gnas su
NK024(ya)001:4649: bskyed pa'i phyir bkra shis kyis mnga' gsol nas gzhan
NK024(ya)001:4650: la phan pa'i don du tshigs su bcad de bstod
NK024(ya)001:4651: pa / de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa dgyes pa che //
NK024(ya)001:4652: rdo rje bdag ni gtan du ma btang zhig /
NK024(ya)001:4653: yungs kar dngos grub rdzas kyis bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnams 'joms shing //
NK024(ya)001:4654: zho yis rnam par rgyas byed ting 'dzin bcud kyis 'tsho ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:4655: d+aurbasa dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan zhing //
NK024(ya)001:4656: li khris lha mo mang po dbang du sdud par byed par shog /
NK024(ya)001:4657: me long gis ni chos kun gzugs brnyan lta bur rtogs pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:4658: dung gis 'jig rten gsum du chos kyi grags pa thob gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:4659: g+hi wam gis ni dug gsum zhi byed chos srog mang po 'tsho ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:4660: bil bas mtshungs med bla med byang chub snying po thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:4662: bkra shis rdzas kyis mnga' gsol nas so so'i yon
NK024(ya)001:4663: tan ji skad gsungs pa bzhin bkra shis par gyur
NK024(ya)001:4664: to // de lta bas na gzhan gyi sdig pa mtshams med pa lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:4666: log pa brgyad la sogs pa rnams 'dag pa lta ci smos /
NK024(ya)001:4667: bla ma la brnyas pa byas pa'i rnam smin yang
NK024(ya)001:4668: dbang bskur ba'i phrin las khyad par can gyis 'dag
NK024(ya)001:4669: par 'gyur pa ni khyad par rmad du byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:4670: phrin las te / don chen po dang ldan par
NK024(ya)001:4671: thugs la dgongs te spro ba chen po mdzod cig
NK024(ya)001:4672: phrin las te / / de dag ni dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4673: de nas dbang de dag bskur yang mi chags pa'i gegs brgyad bshad par bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:4675: dper na chu rang bzhin gyi rnam par dwangs pa
NK024(ya)001:4676: la glo bur du rnyog ma byung na mi gsal
NK024(ya)001:4677: ba'am / 'byung chen ltos kyi nam mkha' rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:4678: gyis rnam par dag kyang glo bur sprin dang khu
NK024(ya)001:4679: nas sgrib na mi gsal ba bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:4680: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag cing gsal
NK024(ya)001:4681: yang glo bur gyi rnam rtog gam bag chags kyis
NK024(ya)001:4683: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub dang //
NK024(ya)001:4684: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:4685: dper na rgya mtsho dwangs pa la //
NK024(ya)001:4686: nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan 'byung ba yang //
NK024(ya)001:4687: rnyog pa chu yis gegs 'gyur bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:4688: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:4689: rnam pa brgyad du 'byung bar bshad //
NK024(ya)001:4691: sngon 'byung ston pa slob dpon la //
NK024(ya)001:4692: bka' cog brnyas pa byed pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:4693: dbang dang dngos grub dang po'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:4694: zhes pas bla ma ni sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:4695: dngos grub 'byung ba'i rtsa ba lags pas bka' la brnyas pa spang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4696: bla med rdo rje 'gro ba'i spun //'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na //
NK024(ya)001:4697: dbang dang dngos grub gegs gnyis pa //
NK024(ya)001:4698: zhes pas mched grogs la gdung sems cher bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4699: byang chub lam la 'dud med cing //
NK024(ya)001:4700: thar pa 'dren pa'i lha spong ba //
NK024(ya)001:4701: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs gsum pa //
NK024(ya)001:4702: zhes pas don dam byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK024(ya)001:4703: kun rdzob byang chub kyi sems ma spong zhig /
NK024(ya)001:4704: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK024(ya)001:4705: thag pa gcod pa gegs bzhi pa //
NK024(ya)001:4707: sems can blos mi btang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4708: gsang sngags gsang ba'i longs spyod rnams //
NK024(ya)001:4709: yongs la sbyin pa lnga pa'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:4711: snod kyis ma smin pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4712: zab pa'i ma smin pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4713: chos kyis ma smin pa'i gang zag ni snod du
NK024(ya)001:4714: mi rung bas gsang sngags kyi don ma ston cig
NK024(ya)001:4715: pa'o // thar lam ston la 'dud med cing //
NK024(ya)001:4716: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:4718: dbang bskur ba'i bla ma la mos gus med pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4719: phyag rten la ser sna ma byed cig /
NK024(ya)001:4720: gzu lum dbang med las la spyod //
NK024(ya)001:4721: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs bdun pa //
NK024(ya)001:4722: zhes pas bla ma la bka' lung ma thob par
NK024(ya)001:4723: gzhan la ston pa la sogs pa gzu lum ras
NK024(ya)001:4724: chod ma byed cig /'dod pa khe grags lhur len
NK024(ya)001:4725: cing // gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ni //'di ni brgyad pa'i gegs su bstan //
NK024(ya)001:4727: 'dod pa khe grags lhur ma len par sngags kyi
NK024(ya)001:4728: dam tshig rin po che dang 'dra ba 'di ma
NK024(ya)001:4729: spong zhig / nyams pa 'di dag su spong ba //
NK024(ya)001:4730: dngos grub dbang gi snod du bshad //'di ltar khyod kyis rab brtan na //
NK024(ya)001:4731: bu khyod nang par dri byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:4732: dkyil 'khor drung du legs par nyol //
NK024(ya)001:4733: zhes pas gegs brgyad po de dag shes par byas la nyes pa de dag las bzlog par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4734: de dag gis bar skabs su 'phros don gyi bshad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4736: mi go ba rnams rgyas par bkrol te bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:4737: sogs slob ma rnams go ba legs par rnyed par
NK024(ya)001:4739: de ltar phan yon de dag dang ldan zhing nyams
NK024(ya)001:4740: pa'i rgyu de rnams spong ba'i slob ma yongs su
NK024(ya)001:4742: de la yang bskur byed rdo rje slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:4743: nyan byed slob ma'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:4744: ji ltar bya ba'i cho ga'i mtshan nyid dang gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:4747: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:4748: gnyen ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK024(ya)001:4750: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu bsten //
NK024(ya)001:4751: zhes gsungs pa la 'bru gnyer ba'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:4752: ston pa ni 'di lta bu'i lam ston pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4755: ting nge 'dzin gyi mdzod a nu /
NK024(ya)001:4756: spyod pa'i mdzod ma h+aa yo ga gsum dang ldan pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:4757: yang na lta ba bden gnyis dbyer med mngon sum du rtogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:4758: ting nge 'dzin spros bcas mthar phyin pa /
NK024(ya)001:4759: dam tshig sbyin kun dang ldan zhing khyad par sgrub
NK024(ya)001:4760: pa'i don las mi 'da' bas lta spyod sgom gsum
NK024(ya)001:4762: chu bo rdzogs pa ni dbang bzhi'i chu bo ma nyams par rdzogs par bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4763: gnyen ldan ni phyi dgra bgegs kyi bar gcod bzlog pa /
NK024(ya)001:4764: nang nyon mongs lam du long zhing bde sdug ro snyoms pa /
NK024(ya)001:4765: snying rje dang phan sems kyis slob bu rjes su 'dzin nus pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4766: rgyud ni rgyud sde mtha' dag la mkhas shing don khrol ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:4767: las ni phrin las rnam pa bzhi la mkhas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4768: man ngag ni bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag dang ldan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:4769: drod 'chang ni nyams myong gi drod 'chang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:4778: drod de gong du bshad pa'i yon tan brgyad dang ldan zhing 'chang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:4780: rnal 'byor pa gang zag spros pa mthar phyin pas dang ldan nas /
NK024(ya)001:4781: zag med la sbyor nus pa'i ston pa de shin tu bsten par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:4782: de ltar yin tshul lam rim gyi mchan bu sogs las kyang shes par nus so //
NK024(ya)001:4783: gzhan yang mdo rgyud nas gsungs pa'i spyi bye brag
NK024(ya)001:4784: gi mtshan nyid de dag dang ldan pa zhig bsten
NK024(ya)001:4785: par bya'o // gnyis pa slob ma'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK024(ya)001:4787: thos bsam sgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:4788: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis zung //
NK024(ya)001:4789: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la brtan //
NK024(ya)001:4790: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:4791: zhes gsungs pas de la yang cung zad 'bru gnyer na /
NK024(ya)001:4792: thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab zab mo la
NK024(ya)001:4793: bloo rab tu sbyangs pa'i dngos po thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:4794: de kho na nyid mthong bas na shes rab kyi
NK024(ya)001:4795: mig dang ldan pa'i skyes bu rnams kyis zung zhig
NK024(ya)001:4796: dang / snod kha sbub zhabs brdol sogs kyi skyon dang bral zhing yon tan dang ldan pa /
NK024(ya)001:4797: ngang chu bo chen po'i rgyun ltar ring ba /
NK024(ya)001:4798: tshul dge slong gsar bu ltar zhib pa /
NK024(ya)001:4799: bsam pa rin po che gser ltar bzang ba /
NK024(ya)001:4800: blo ri rab ltar brtan zhing mi 'gyur ba /
NK024(ya)001:4801: lus dang longs spyod chos phyir 'phangs pa med par
NK024(ya)001:4802: gtong phod pa'i slob ma la zab mo'i chos sbyin
NK024(ya)001:4803: par bya'o // zhes 'grel byed mkhan po dag gis bshad pas de lta bu'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:4804: gzhan yang gsung rab zab mo las bshad pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:4805: gyi mtshan nyid kun ldan nam phyogs 'dra tsam zhig
NK024(ya)001:4806: nges par dgos / gsum pa ji ltar bya ba'i
NK024(ya)001:4807: cho ga'i mtshan nyid ni spyir rgyud sde so so'i
NK024(ya)001:4808: sgos bka' lta bu'i tshe rang rang gi lugs rnams
NK024(ya)001:4810: de yang gong ma 'og mar 'brel mi rung la /
NK024(ya)001:4811: 'og ma gong mar bkral chog par mkhas pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:4812: bzhed pas 'dir rgyud sde gong ma dang 'brel bas
NK024(ya)001:4813: na gong mas 'og ma zil gyis gnon pa ste
NK024(ya)001:4814: / zur hwam rin po che'i lha thems las /
NK024(ya)001:4815: blor shong thams cad ye shes sku //
NK024(ya)001:4816: rgyud lung phyag len bshad mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:4818: sngon 'gro'i dkyil 'khor 'di gnyis spyod rgyud las gsungs
NK024(ya)001:4819: kyang phyag len phal cher gong ma dang mthun tshabs
NK024(ya)001:4820: che zhing / de yang spyod rgyud kho na ltar na thems yig las /
NK024(ya)001:4821: bdag nyid dam tshig mdun ye shes //'dres dang gsum ka mchod pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:4823: bdag dam tshig pa'i nga rgyal dang /
NK024(ya)001:4824: mdun bskyed la dam ye gnyis te gsum du gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:4825: gong mar bkral ba ltar yang de nyid las /
NK024(ya)001:4826: bum dang tsa ka dkyil bla ma //
NK024(ya)001:4827: thams cad lhar gsal mchod bzlas la //
NK024(ya)001:4828: phyi snod 'jig rten kun gzhal yas //
NK024(ya)001:4829: nang bcud skye 'gro kun lha mnyes //
NK024(ya)001:4830: lha yi rang snang mchod rdzas zhes //
NK024(ya)001:4831: lha thugs rang grol mchod pa'i tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:4833: gong ma kho na ltar bkral ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:4834: 'dir sngon 'gro phyag na rdo rje ngan song gnas
NK024(ya)001:4835: 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor 'di nyid la brten nas theg
NK024(ya)001:4836: pa'i rim pa'i dbang 'dir 'jug pa'i sgo gsang bdag
NK024(ya)001:4837: gi dkyil 'khor nas byas pas phyag na rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:4838: gsang ba thams cad kyi mdzod 'dzin pa yin pa
NK024(ya)001:4839: dang / lam 'di yang rdo rje theg pa gtso
NK024(ya)001:4840: bor byas te bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi srol chen
NK024(ya)001:4841: po'i gzhung lam yin no zhes ston par byed pa'i
NK024(ya)001:4842: dang / rtags yin no // mdor na sngon chad
NK024(ya)001:4843: bstan pa spyi dang khyad par snga 'gyur gyi bstan
NK024(ya)001:4844: pa rin po che dbyar mtsho ltar 'phel zhing gdul
NK024(ya)001:4845: bya rnams kyang dad brtson shes rab dang ldan phyir
NK024(ya)001:4846: dang / rtags yin no // / gong ma rnams
NK024(ya)001:4847: kyi yig rnying du chog khrigs de dag mdor bstan
NK024(ya)001:4848: gyis shes bar nus pa byung na'ang deng sang de
NK024(ya)001:4849: las ldog pa'i phyir tshig tshogs kyi dka' ba la
NK024(ya)001:4850: ma bsam par slob dpon gyi bgyi 'os rnams kyang
NK024(ya)001:4851: rang gzhung dang mi 'gal ba'i cho ga rgyas par
NK024(ya)001:4852: dang / rtags yin no // / grub khul yin / slob ma'i ngo skal ni /
NK024(ya)001:4853: man+dala me tog bcas thal mo //
NK024(ya)001:4854: nyan sogs 'dod pas gsol gsum btab //
NK024(ya)001:4855: ces 'byung bas na bla ma dang gsang ba'i bdag
NK024(ya)001:4856: po tha mi dad pa la sngon 'gro phyag na
NK024(ya)001:4857: rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur zab
NK024(ya)001:4858: mo zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul nas /
NK024(ya)001:4859: dang po gsol ba gdab pa ni 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4860: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK024(ya)001:4861: brtse bas dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK024(ya)001:4862: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK024(ya)001:4863: de ring rab tu stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:4864: zhes pa'i gsol ba lan gsum btab /
NK024(ya)001:4866: de nas bla ma'i rjes su thams cad kyi mgrin
NK024(ya)001:4867: gcig tu zhes pa tsam las phyag 'tshal bar ma
NK024(ya)001:4868: gsungs kyang / sgrol chen bsam grub rdo rje'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:4869: bzhes zur hwam thams cad mkhyen pa'i zin bris las
NK024(ya)001:4870: brda sprod dang bcas te gsungs pa legs par mthong
NK024(ya)001:4871: gsungs kyang / ste 'di ltar / bdag gzhan thams
NK024(ya)001:4872: cad kyi thams cad du lus ngag yid gsum gyi
NK024(ya)001:4873: mi dge ba byas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:4874: byed 'gyur gyi sdig sgrib sbyang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:4875: 'phags pa'i skyes bu chen po rnams kyi sku gsung
NK024(ya)001:4876: thugs gsum dge ba mdzad pa'i byin rlabs rnams thob
NK024(ya)001:4877: pa'i slad du lus ngag yid gus pas phyag bgyi
NK024(ya)001:4878: ba dang lhan cig 'di'i rjes zlos kyang mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4880: khams gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:4881: bu bzhin skyob pa'i thugs mnga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:4882: sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin sku //
NK024(ya)001:4883: bla med mgon la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4884: zhes bla ma la phyag btsal /
NK024(ya)001:4885: bcom ldan phyag na rdo rje ni //
NK024(ya)001:4888: rdo rje bsnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4889: zhes yi dam gsang ba'i bdag po dang /
NK024(ya)001:4890: las kyi gnod sbyin chen po ni //'jigs su rung ba'i cha byad can //
NK024(ya)001:4891: thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //'jigs byed khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4892: zhes gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje sogs chos skyong dang /
NK024(ya)001:4893: ston pa bla med sangs rgyas rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:4894: skyob pa bla med dam chos rin po che //'dren pa bla med dge 'dun rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:4895: bla med dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4896: zhes dkon mchog spyi phyag dang /
NK024(ya)001:4897: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK024(ya)001:4898: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:4899: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK024(ya)001:4900: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:4901: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:4902: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:4903: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK024(ya)001:4904: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:4905: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK024(ya)001:4906: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK024(ya)001:4907: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK024(ya)001:4908: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK024(ya)001:4909: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK024(ya)001:4910: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:4911: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK024(ya)001:4912: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:4913: zhes pa yan lag brgyad pas phyag byas la 'dug go //
NK024(ya)001:4914: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:4915: mdun gyi nam mkhar gsang ba'i bdag po'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:4916: la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK024(ya)001:4917: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong srung ma'i
NK024(ya)001:4918: tshogs sprin 'thibs pa ltar bzhugs pa la /
NK024(ya)001:4919: skyabs su 'gro ba dang smon pa sems bskyed pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4920: phyogs dus kun nas brtse bar bzhugs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:4921: bla ma dkon mchog thams cad dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:4922: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs kyi mchog rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:4923: byang chub bar du bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:4924: bdag gis sbyin sogs bgyis pa'i bsod nams kyis //'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas myur thob bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:4927: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK024(ya)001:4928: yang dag byang chub bskyed mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:4929: de bzhin bla med byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:4930: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:4932: de nas slar yang dmigs kyis phye nas phyi nang
NK024(ya)001:4933: gsang ba de kho na'i yul la nan tan du
NK024(ya)001:4935: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun gsum la skyabs su mchi /
NK024(ya)001:4936: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro gsum la chos sku
NK024(ya)001:4937: longs sku sprul sku gsum la rang sems stong gsal
NK024(ya)001:4938: chos kyi sku la bla ma sangs rgyas rin po
NK024(ya)001:4940: da ni kun dril nas slar yang skyabs su 'gro zhing thun mong ma yin pa'i gsol gdab ni /
NK024(ya)001:4941: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK024(ya)001:4942: byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK024(ya)001:4943: dkon mchog gsum dang yi dam lha //
NK024(ya)001:4944: bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:4945: dbang bskur dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:4946: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:4948: skyabs sems kyi go rim 'di rnams 'chol ba 'dra
NK024(ya)001:4949: zhig 'dug kyang skyon cher med cing gzhung ltar du
NK024(ya)001:4953: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na'i skyabs su 'gro ba sogs kyis rgyud dag par byas nas /
NK024(ya)001:4954: dbang dngos la mchog dbang bcu drug bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:4956: thog mar ngan song gnas 'dren gyi phyag na rdo
NK024(ya)001:4957: rje g.yon sdigs mdzub bsgrengs pa'i sku de bla mar
NK024(ya)001:4958: sgom zhing slob ma'i mgor bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:4959: de yang dbang mchog rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:4960: ngan song gsum dang rigs drug ka'i bag chags dag par byas te /
NK024(ya)001:4961: bu dmyal ba'i yi ge duhr sgom /
NK024(ya)001:4963: na raka shud+he tsak+shu pra be sha a a /
NK024(ya)001:4965: 'od 'phros pas sdig sgrib sbyangs zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:4966: thugs 'dun dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4967: khyed rang rnams kyi mdun gyi nam mkhar da ltar
NK024(ya)001:4968: gyi rdo rje slob dpon 'di nyid tha mal pa
NK024(ya)001:4969: ma yin pa gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo
NK024(ya)001:4970: rje g.yas rdo rje 'phyar zhing g.yon sdigs mdzub bsgrengs
NK024(ya)001:4971: pa khyer rang rnams kyi mgo bor bzhag pa zhig
NK024(ya)001:4973: de'i ngang nas khyed rang rnams kyi tshe rabs su
NK024(ya)001:4974: nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi las bsags pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:4975: gis dmyal bar skye 'gyur gyi las ngan gyi rang
NK024(ya)001:4976: gzugs yi ge duhnaga po zhig tu sgoms mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4977: de la slob dpon gyi phyag rgya bsdams shing bden
NK024(ya)001:4978: pa brjod de mthar phyag rgya phral zhing dkrugs pas
NK024(ya)001:4979: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis duhyiga rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:4980: med par sbyangs pas dmyal bar skye ba'i sdig sgrib
NK024(ya)001:4981: thams cad byang bar gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:4982: slob dpon gyis phyag rgya rdo rje phyir bsdams bcas la /
NK024(ya)001:4984: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK024(ya)001:4985: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing
NK024(ya)001:4986: khams mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa
NK024(ya)001:4987: dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis rigs
NK024(ya)001:4988: kyi bu 'di rnams kyi rgyu nyon mongs pa zhe
NK024(ya)001:4989: sdang dang rkyen srog gcod pa la sogs kyis dmyal
NK024(ya)001:4990: bar skye ba'i sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:4991: thams cad skad cig la byang bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4992: slar gang nas kyang mi ldang bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:4993: na raka shud+d+he tsak+shu pra be sha a a /
NK024(ya)001:4994: zhes phyag rgyal bkrol la sprug go //
NK024(ya)001:4996: phyag rdor la dad pa dang gsol ba 'debs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:4997: de ltar dmyal bar skye ba'i las ngan de nyid /
NK024(ya)001:4998: bla mas phyag na rdo rje'i mthus zad par byas pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:5000: kun nas mun bsal bde dga' bskyed pa'i mthu bzang 'di ko su yi mthu snyam ste //
NK024(ya)001:5001: gyen du bltas na nam mkha'i dkyil na phyag na rdo rje 'bar ba bzhugs mthong nas //
NK024(ya)001:5002: rab tu dga' ba'i shugs kyis sdig dang bral nas de dang lhan cig 'grogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:5003: ces gsungs pa'i phyir rtse gcig tu dad pas gsol ba 'debs shing /
NK024(ya)001:5004: stobs bzhi tshang ba'i sgo nas bshags sdom gyi slad du 'di'i rje zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:5005: kye ma kye hud gang nas byon //'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyongs shig /
NK024(ya)001:5006: dbang mchog rgyal pos bsgral du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:5007: slan chad mi 'chab mi bgyid do //
NK024(ya)001:5009: bla ma chas gos sngon po dang ldan pas slob bu'i lag tu rdo rje gtad de /
NK024(ya)001:5010: rigs kyi bu khyod 'dir shog cig /
NK024(ya)001:5011: rang gis nyams dang zlas nyams pas //
NK024(ya)001:5012: na raka dmyal bar lhung ba las //
NK024(ya)001:5013: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:5014: zhes rdo rjes gral du drangs sngon du basngagasa pa'i yungs kar gyis slob ma rnams la brab cing /
NK024(ya)001:5015: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga ta he du h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:5017: ram yam kham zhes brjod pas /
NK024(ya)001:5018: bla ma'i thugs las 'phros pa'i me rlung chus kyang sbyangs pa'i dmigs pa bya /
NK024(ya)001:5019: a zhes brjod pas stong pa nyid du dag par mos /
NK024(ya)001:5021: slar yang sngar bzhin bden pa tshar gcig brjod do //'di la phyag rgya bsdam sprug sogs mi bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5022: rtsa ba dang zur hwam rin po che'i zin bris su yi dwags dang /
NK024(ya)001:5023: dud 'gro'i gnas sbyong gi sngags tsam dang 'don pa
NK024(ya)001:5024: bsgyur tshul tsam las ma gsungs pas lag len bde
NK024(ya)001:5026: bla ma sngar bzhin gsang bdag tu gsal ba'i mdun
NK024(ya)001:5027: du slob ma rnams tshe rabs su nyon mongs pa
NK024(ya)001:5028: 'dod chags kyi las bsags pa'i dbang gis yi dwags
NK024(ya)001:5029: su skye 'gyur gyi rang gzugs yi ge pre dmar
NK024(ya)001:5031: de la sngar bzhin slob dpon gyis bden brdar phyag
NK024(ya)001:5032: rgya 'ching 'grol sogs byas pas phyag rgya'i 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:5033: gyis pre yig rang bzhin med par sbyangs pas yi
NK024(ya)001:5034: dwags su skye ba'i sdig sgrib thams cad sbyangs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5035: mos pa mdzod / phyag rgya bcas la /
NK024(ya)001:5037: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sogs sngar ltar la /
NK024(ya)001:5038: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams kyi rgyu 'dod chags dang
NK024(ya)001:5039: rkyen ma sbyin pa len pa sogs kyis yi dwags
NK024(ya)001:5040: su skye ba'i sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:5041: thams cad skad cig la byang bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5042: slar gang nas kyang sogs rigs 'gre /
NK024(ya)001:5043: pre ta ka tsak+shu pra be sha a a /
NK024(ya)001:5045: dad pas gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5046: kye ma kye hud sogs kyi rjes zlos /
NK024(ya)001:5047: rigs kyi bu khyod 'dir shog cig /
NK024(ya)001:5048: rang gis nyams dang zlas nyams dang //
NK024(ya)001:5049: yi dwags gnas su ltung ba las //
NK024(ya)001:5050: skyob phyir dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:5051: zhes rdo rjes gral du drang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5052: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ga te he du h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:5053: ces yungs kar gyis brab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5056: slar yang bden brjod tshar gcig bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5057: yang sngar bzhin slob ma rnams tshe rabs su nyon
NK024(ya)001:5058: mongs pa gti mug gi las bsags pa'i dbang gis
NK024(ya)001:5059: dud 'gror skye 'gyur gyi rang gzugs yi ge tri
NK024(ya)001:5060: smug nag zhig tu sgoms mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:5063: phyogs bcu zhes sogs sngar ltar /
NK024(ya)001:5064: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams kyi rgyu gti mug dang
NK024(ya)001:5065: rkyen log lta sogs kyis dud 'gror skye ba'i sa
NK024(ya)001:5066: bon bag chags dang bcas pa skad cig la byang
NK024(ya)001:5068: slar gang nas kyang sogs rigs 'gre /
NK024(ya)001:5069: tri tir+ya ga te tsak+shu pra be sha a a /
NK024(ya)001:5071: dad pas gsol btab kyi rjes zlos dang /
NK024(ya)001:5072: gral du drang ba'i tshigs bcad /
NK024(ya)001:5073: rigs kyi bu khyod 'dir shog cig /
NK024(ya)001:5074: ces pa'i rkang pa gsum pa /
NK024(ya)001:5075: byol song gnas su ltung ba las //
NK024(ya)001:5077: rdo rjes gral du drang ba /
NK024(ya)001:5080: a dang bden brjod gnyis pa sogs 'agre'o //
NK024(ya)001:5081: de yang bla ma phyag rdor du gsal ba rten gyi stobs /
NK024(ya)001:5082: phyag rgya 'ching 'grol bden brjod 'od zer gyis sbyang ba sogs rnam par sun 'byin pa'i stobs /
NK024(ya)001:5083: dad pas gsol btab gnyen po kun tu spyod pa'i stobs /
NK024(ya)001:5086: a sogs kyis sbyangs pa sor chud pa'i stobs te bzhi ka legs par tshang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:5087: ngan song gnas 'dren gyi cho ga dngos gnas sbyong
NK024(ya)001:5088: 'di nyid gzhan las khyad par shin tu 'phags par
NK024(ya)001:5089: snang ngo // de dag gi zhar la nga rgyal
NK024(ya)001:5090: phrag dog ser sna rdzun tshig sogs kyi sgrib pa
NK024(ya)001:5091: sbyang ba'i phyir ngan song spyi gcod du /
NK024(ya)001:5092: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga ti pa
NK024(ya)001:5093: ri sho d+ha na r+aa dza ya ta th+aa ga
NK024(ya)001:5094: ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:5096: sho d+ha ne shod+ha ne sarba p+aa pam bi sho
NK024(ya)001:5097: d+ha ne shud+d+he bi shud+d+he sarba karma a wa ra
NK024(ya)001:5100: nang sems mi 'khrug cing sangs rgyas mi bskyod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5101: thugs rjes zhing khams rnam par dag par skye ba'i
NK024(ya)001:5102: phyir / na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:5103: mo kam ka ni kam ka ni /
NK024(ya)001:5104: ro tsa ni ro tsa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5105: tro ta ni tro ta ni /
NK024(ya)001:5106: t+r+aa sa ni t+r+aa sa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5107: pra ti ha na pra ti ha na /
NK024(ya)001:5108: sarba karma pa ram pa r+aa ni me sarba sat+w+aa n+aany+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:5109: zhes pas ngan song gnas 'dren no //'di la rtsa
NK024(ya)001:5110: bar mi gsal yang snga ma'i 'gros kyi bzlas yungs
NK024(ya)001:5112: rtsa bar de nas dbu rgyan thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5113: de nas lag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs nas /
NK024(ya)001:5114: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK024(ya)001:5115: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcings te gnas lngar gtugs pas
NK024(ya)001:5116: sha za mo stong gi tshang dkrogs nas byer ba
NK024(ya)001:5117: de bzhin du dbang bskur te /
NK024(ya)001:5119: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan yab sras kyis 'di
NK024(ya)001:5120: la phyag rgya bcas te dbang bskur ba las tsakli
NK024(ya)001:5121: mi dgos gsung / zhes pa'i mchan bu 'dug cing rnam snang thig le dbang gi rgyud las kyang /
NK024(ya)001:5122: phyag rgyas gsang ba'i gnas srung ste //
NK024(ya)001:5123: zhes gsungs pas de ltar 'thad par sems pas lag pa rdo rje sdams pa las gung mo gshibs /
NK024(ya)001:5124: mthe bong dang mathe'u chung gnyis brkyang ba spyi bor bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:5125: mi bskyod pa yab yum gyi sngags /
NK024(ya)001:5128: de nyid las mdzub mo dang srin lag pad+ma 'dra bar byas te /
NK024(ya)001:5129: rnam snang yab yum gyi phyag rgya dpral bar bzhag la rnam snang yab yum gyi sngags /
NK024(ya)001:5132: de nyid las mdzub mo dang srin lag rin po che 'dra bar byas te /
NK024(ya)001:5133: rna ltag g.yas su bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:5136: mthe bong dang mathe'u chung so sor mnyam la lhag ma thams cad brkyang ba ltag par bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:5137: a mi de wa h+r+aih r+aa ga ra ti h+r+aih
NK024(ya)001:5138: de nyid g.yon phyogs su yo bar byas te ltag
NK024(ya)001:5140: a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah ta ra ta ri +aah
NK024(ya)001:5141: de'i rjes su 'jam dbyangs yab sras kyi mchan bur
NK024(ya)001:5142: 'di ni dbu rgyan dngos su sbyin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:5144: rin po che dngos sam bris pa'i dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:5145: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan 'dis //
NK024(ya)001:5146: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun 'dus pa //
NK024(ya)001:5147: gzi brjid rig sngags rgyal ba'i dbu //
NK024(ya)001:5148: bu khyod gtsug na nor bu 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:5149: rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK024(ya)001:5150: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:5151: rigs kyi bu la dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:5152: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal po'i dbang dam pa thob
NK024(ya)001:5153: par gyur cig / de nas gsang ba'i rten thogs
NK024(ya)001:5154: la zhes gsungs pa ni gsang bdag dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:5155: gtso bo'i sku thogs te dbang bskur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:5156: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso //
NK024(ya)001:5157: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:5158: gsang ba gsang chen yang gsang ni //
NK024(ya)001:5159: bdag por khyod ni dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:5160: bud+d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo /
NK024(ya)001:5161: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK024(ya)001:5162: cad kyis rigs kyi bu la gsang ba'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:5163: bas byang chub kyi myu gu skams pa sos nas
NK024(ya)001:5164: byang chub kyi snying po can du gyur nas /
NK024(ya)001:5165: gsang ba'i bdag po'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5166: badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum phata kyis g.yas su rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:5167: g.yon du dril bu byin no //
NK024(ya)001:5168: de nas rnam rgyal bum pa thogs la /
NK024(ya)001:5169: rin chen sna tshogs rgyu las byung /
NK024(ya)001:5170: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:5171: shes rab yum gyi bum pa 'dis //'gro don mchog gi dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:5172: bud+d+ha ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK024(ya)001:5174: rigs kyi bu la bum pa'i dbang bskur bas nad
NK024(ya)001:5175: rnams byang zhing dag nas rang sems spros pa bral
NK024(ya)001:5176: nas ye shes rnam pa lnga dang ldan pas 'gro
NK024(ya)001:5177: ba'i don chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du byed pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:5180: me tog gi phreng ba thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5181: byang chub yan lag me tog 'thor /
NK024(ya)001:5182: khams gsum btsun pa'i bdag po ste //
NK024(ya)001:5183: bde gshegs mchod pa thob pa dang //'gro don byed par dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:5185: rigs kyi bu la me tog thod kyi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:5186: bas tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs te sgrib gnyis byang
NK024(ya)001:5187: ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5189: ye shes bdag nyid cod pan ni //
NK024(ya)001:5190: klu gdug gnod pas mi bardzida zhing //'khor ba'i nyes pas mi gos pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5191: rgyan mchog dam pas dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:5192: badz+ra sat+w+aa a b+hi mam sa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:5193: rigs kyi bu la cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:5194: mya ngan las 'das kyang khams gsum du gnas nas
NK024(ya)001:5195: srid pa gsum gyi sdug bsngal thams cad dang bral
NK024(ya)001:5196: bar gyur cig / thur ma thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5197: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK024(ya)001:5198: ma rig ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK024(ya)001:5199: bu khyod kyi ni mi shes pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5200: ling thog rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK024(ya)001:5201: tsak+shu tsak+sh+au dz+ny+aa na tsak+shu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:5203: rigs kyi bu la thur ma rnam pa lngas dbang
NK024(ya)001:5204: bskur bas ma rig pa'i ling thog bsal te spyan
NK024(ya)001:5205: lnga dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5207: chos rnams gzugs brnyan lta bu ste //
NK024(ya)001:5208: rten 'brel mthun la snang ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:5209: brjod med rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK024(ya)001:5210: don dam chos nyid brjod par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5211: badz+ra +aa dar+sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:5213: rigs kyi bu la me long gi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:5214: chos thams cad gzugs brnyan ltar du rten 'brel sgyu
NK024(ya)001:5215: mar mthong ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:5219: brjod pa'i don du mthu bkod nas //
NK024(ya)001:5220: gzhan don 'di las phan bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:5221: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:5222: tsakra rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:5223: rigs kyi bu la 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas rdzu
NK024(ya)001:5224: 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan pas khams gsum kun
NK024(ya)001:5225: tu bgrod cing 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po thob
NK024(ya)001:5226: par gyur cig / dung thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5227: chos dung rgyas pa bus nas ni /
NK024(ya)001:5228: 'jig rten sems can skal can la //
NK024(ya)001:5229: gnyid bsal sdig sbyangs chos thob pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5230: skyob pa mgon po'i tshangs skad sgrog /
NK024(ya)001:5231: b+h+ra ma w+aa ka a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:5232: rigs kyi bu la dung gi dbang bskur bas chos
NK024(ya)001:5233: ston pa la tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:5234: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5235: rdo rje rgya gram thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5236: rdo rje 'di ni sna tshogs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5237: las rnams rgya mtsho'i dbang bskur gyis //
NK024(ya)001:5238: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //'gro ba'i don la 'bad par gyis //
NK024(ya)001:5239: b+hi shwa badz+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:5240: rigs kyi bu la rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang
NK024(ya)001:5241: bskur bas phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i rigs
NK024(ya)001:5242: sngags 'chang grub pa rnams kyis rtag tu bsrung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:5243: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5244: rgyal srid sna bdun thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5245: bsod nams dpal las legs grub pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5246: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun 'di //'gro ba'i bde legs 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:5247: phyogs bcur dge bcu bskor bar gyis //'khor lo'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:5248: bskur bas sangs rgyas kyi sa la nges par lung
NK024(ya)001:5249: bstan pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5250: btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi nges pa'i don dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5251: dmag dpon gyi dbang bskur bas phas kyis rgol ba zil gyis gnon par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5252: blon po'i dbang bskur bas blo dang brtson 'grus su ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5253: rta mchog gi dbang bskur bas mi gnas pa'i dbyings su thogs med du bgrod nus par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5254: glang po'i dbang bskur bas rigs drug than pa'i gnas su 'dren nus par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5255: nor bu'i dbang bskur bas bsam pa yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i yon tan thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5264: rigs kyi bu la rin po che sna bdun gyi
NK024(ya)001:5265: dbang bskur bas phyir mi ldog pa'i 'khor los sgyur
NK024(ya)001:5266: ba'i dbang phyug dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5268: lag tu sbyin pas dug gsum gyi 'khrul pa rgyun
NK024(ya)001:5269: bcad de bag chags thams cad rtsa ba nas dag
NK024(ya)001:5270: par gyur cig / mda' gzhu thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5271: mda' gzhu lag tu sbyin pas thabs shes zung du
NK024(ya)001:5272: 'brel nas ye shes dag pa'i rtse mor gnas par
NK024(ya)001:5273: gyur cig / seng ge thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5274: brjid pa'i seng ge shin tu myur ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:5275: gzugs can mchog 'di lag tu sbyin pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:5276: gsung rab rgya mtsho kun gyi sgra sgrogs te //
NK024(ya)001:5277: log pa'i phyogs kun zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK024(ya)001:5278: badz+ra sing ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:5279: rigs kyi bu la brjid pa seng ge'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:5280: bas gsung rab rgya mtsho'i sgra sgrogs pas log pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5281: phyogs zil gyis gnon pa'i sangs rgyas thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:5283: steng phyogs mnga' mdzad thugs rje nyi ma brdal //
NK024(ya)001:5284: brtse bas mun sel thugs rje zla ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:5285: stong gsum mun pa dus gcig bsal nas ni //'jig rten kun tu snang ba bskyed par shog /
NK024(ya)001:5286: s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:5288: rigs kyi bu la nyi zla'i dbang bskur bas skye
NK024(ya)001:5289: 'gro ma lus pa'i sems kyi rgyud la ye shes
NK024(ya)001:5290: kyi 'od shar nas khams gsum gyi mun pa thams
NK024(ya)001:5291: cad skad cig la sel ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK024(ya)001:5292: par gyur cig / bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad rim bzhin thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:5293: gsang bdag bstan pa rgyas pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:5294: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:5295: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK024(ya)001:5296: gsang ba rab tu sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:5297: yungs kar rdo rjes bgegs tshogs 'dul //
NK024(ya)001:5298: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs can //
NK024(ya)001:5299: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:5300: byin rlabs mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:5301: zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:5302: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK024(ya)001:5303: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:5304: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:5305: durbasa tshe 'di 'phel bar byed pa ste //'chi med rdo rje tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK024(ya)001:5306: sdug bsngal skye shi'i rtsa ba rgyun bcad de //
NK024(ya)001:5307: bkra shis des kyang tshe 'di brtan gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5308: li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin can //
NK024(ya)001:5309: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:5310: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:5311: bkra shis des kyang chos srid brtan gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:5312: dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrog pa'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:5313: yon tan rgya mtsho'i mchog tu bdag gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:5314: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5315: bkra shis des kyang tshig gi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:5316: g+hi wam dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK024(ya)001:5317: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:5318: nyon mongs zug rdu med par gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:5319: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK024(ya)001:5320: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK024(ya)001:5321: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du bdag gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:5322: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5323: bkra shis des kyang don gyi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:5324: bilba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK024(ya)001:5325: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:5326: bkra shis de ni 'gro bas thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:5327: ces mchog dbang bcu drug rdzogs par bskur nas /
NK024(ya)001:5328: rjes su bum chus kyang bkru btung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:5329: zhes gsungs pas slar yang rnam rgyal gyi chus khrus bya zhing khar btung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:5331: de nas lam 'khyer bzhi la theg pa chen po'i skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya /
NK024(ya)001:5332: dbang gi dam tshig gegs brgyad bsrung ba dbang mchog dbang bcu drug /
NK024(ya)001:5334: snying po n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra bzlas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:5335: zhes gsungs pas de dag gi don rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5336: de la don rnam pa bzhi las dang po theg chen gyi skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya /
NK024(ya)001:5337: spyir mdo rgyud bstan bcos mtha' dag nas rgyas par bshad pa bsam gyis mi khyab mod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:5338: 'dir brgyud pa'i bla ma gong ma dag gi gsung
NK024(ya)001:5339: dang sbyar na skabs su babs shing byin rlabs kyi
NK024(ya)001:5341: mkhas shing grub brnyes glan ban bsod nams mgon po'i
NK024(ya)001:5342: chog khrigs kyi yig rnying las byung ba ma nyams
NK024(ya)001:5343: par bkod pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK024(ya)001:5344: skyabs su 'gro ba la don drug gis ston par byed de /
NK024(ya)001:5345: gang la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5347: tshul lam thabs ji ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:5348: dngos gzhi dbye ba dang bcas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5349: skyabs su ma song ba'i skyon nam nyes dmigs dang /
NK024(ya)001:5351: de la dang po gang la skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:5352: yul dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:5353: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK024(ya)001:5354: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5355: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5356: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5357: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5359: rig pa 'dzin pa dang bcas pa rnams ni skyabs su 'gro ba'i yul lo //
NK024(ya)001:5360: gnyis pa gang gis 'gro na rten gyi gang zag /
NK024(ya)001:5363: dad pa gsum dang ldan zhing skyabs su 'gro ba'i yul de rnams kyi yon tan dran pa /
NK024(ya)001:5364: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob par 'dod cing /
NK024(ya)001:5365: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal la 'jigs pa'i gang zag de rnams skyabs su 'gro ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:5366: tshul lam thabs ji ltar skyabs su 'gro snyam na /
NK024(ya)001:5367: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi gang zag gis chos bzhi ldan gyi sgo nas 'gro dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:5370: las dang las kyi rnam smin la 'dzem zhing /
NK024(ya)001:5371: las rgyu 'bras kyi chos la yid ches pa /
NK024(ya)001:5372: dus rtag tu bla ma bsten zhing bla ma la gus pa /
NK024(ya)001:5373: des bstan pa'i chos la the tshom mi za ba dang bzhi yin te /
NK024(ya)001:5374: de ltar yang mdo sde khang bzang rtse mo las /
NK024(ya)001:5375: dad pa'i sngon 'gro ma ltar bskyed pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:5376: dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad bskyed pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:5377: log pa'i sbyor bas mi phyed rtag tu bzung //
NK024(ya)001:5378: dge ba'i mchog ni yid ches stobs las byung //
NK024(ya)001:5379: theg chen don mkhas bla ma bsten byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:5380: smras pa'i don la the tshom mi za ba //
NK024(ya)001:5381: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhing mchog shin tu nye //
NK024(ya)001:5383: dngos gazhi'am dbye ba'i dbang du byas na don gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:5388: sangs rgyas la skyabs su song nas 'jig rten rang
NK024(ya)001:5389: rgyud pa'i lha la skyabs su mi 'gro ste spang
NK024(ya)001:5390: / chos la skyabs su song nas sems can thams
NK024(ya)001:5391: cad la 'tshe ba'i sems spangs te phan gdags pa
NK024(ya)001:5392: 'ba' zhig gi sems su byas la gnod pa'i sems
NK024(ya)001:5393: / spang / dge 'dun la skyabs su song nas mi log lta can dang /
NK024(ya)001:5395: sdig sems can rnams spang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5396: de dag mi ldan zhing spang bar ma byas na skyon nam nyes dmigs ni /
NK024(ya)001:5397: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i khongs su mi chud pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5398: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK024(ya)001:5399: rig 'dzin dang rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyis byin gyis brlab par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5400: 'dul sdom dang dam tshig rnams kyi rten med par 'gyur ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5401: tshe 'dir bsam pa mi 'grub cing mthar 'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:5402: sdug bsngal gyi rgyur 'gyur ba'i phyir spang bya de
NK024(ya)001:5403: dag dus rtag tu dran par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5405: thun mong spyi'i blang bya dang /
NK024(ya)001:5406: khyad par gyi blang bya gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:5407: dang po ni dus rtag tu bya ba dang spyod pa ci dang ci byed rung /
NK024(ya)001:5408: na tsha dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa'i rkyen ci dang ci byung rung /
NK024(ya)001:5409: phyogs gang dang gang du 'gro rung /
NK024(ya)001:5410: tha na zas kham cig tsam za'ang /
NK024(ya)001:5411: dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan 'ba' zhig yid la dran par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5412: khyad par du phye ba'i blang bya ni sangs rgyas la skyabs su song nas /
NK024(ya)001:5413: mchod pa'i rten du bzhengs pa lugs su blug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5415: ris su bris pa la sogs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten gang na 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:5416: de dag thams cad la dad cing gus par bya /
NK024(ya)001:5417: chos la skyabs su song bas glegs bam dang /
NK024(ya)001:5418: po ti la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5419: mdo sde rgyud sde la sogs pa thams cad la dad cing gus par bya /
NK024(ya)001:5420: dge 'dun la skyabs su song nas dge slong dang /
NK024(ya)001:5423: tshangs par spyod pa la sogs pa de dag thams cad la dad cing gus par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5424: de ltar dkon mchog gsum po de dag la gus par bya dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan yang /
NK024(ya)001:5426: dkon mchog gsum spangs tshangs par spyad pa dge med 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5429: sdom pa kun la yod mod kyang //
NK024(ya)001:5430: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK024(ya)001:5431: ces gsungs pa'i phyir blang bya de dag dus rtag tu dran par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5432: de dag dang ldan pa'i gang zag gis skyabs su
NK024(ya)001:5433: 'gro ba'i cho ga dngos la 'jug par 'tshal te
NK024(ya)001:5437: mthar thug de kho na nyid kyi skyabs su 'gro ba dang bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:5438: dang po ni dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa
NK024(ya)001:5439: gsum gyis 'gro ba sems can thams cad la skyob
NK024(ya)001:5441: de ltar yang mdo khang bu brtsegs pa las /
NK024(ya)001:5442: sangs rgyas lta bu'i ston pa med //
NK024(ya)001:5443: chos dang 'dra ba'i skyob pa med //
NK024(ya)001:5444: dge 'dun lta bu'i zhing sa med //
NK024(ya)001:5445: des na gsum la bsnyen bkur bya //
NK024(ya)001:5448: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK024(ya)001:5449: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //'gro ba'i bla mar mchod par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:5450: de la rtag tu gus phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:5452: de dag la bslab par bya ba ni mdun gyi
NK024(ya)001:5453: nam mkha' la dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa
NK024(ya)001:5454: gsum dang / phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5455: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs rnams dang
NK024(ya)001:5456: gsum dang / / rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5457: yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5458: rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:5460: rig 'dzin rig pa 'dzin pa rnams mdun gyi nam
NK024(ya)001:5461: mkha' la sprin phung gtibs pa bzhin du bzhugs par
NK024(ya)001:5462: bsgoms nas rang gi lus dang longs spyod la sogs
NK024(ya)001:5463: pa thams cad kyang phangs pa med par da lta
NK024(ya)001:5464: spyan drangs pa de rnams la phul /
NK024(ya)001:5466: 'jig rten gyi khams kyi rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5467: mchod pa'i sprin phung bsam gyis mi khyab pas bkang nas phul te /
NK024(ya)001:5468: dus 'di nas bzung nas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ma
NK024(ya)001:5469: thob kyi bar du dkon mchog rin po che rnam
NK024(ya)001:5470: pa gsum po shes so snyam bgyi ba de dag
NK024(ya)001:5473: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha la skyabs su 'gro ba yin te /
NK024(ya)001:5474: de la bla ma'i skyabs su 'gro ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:5476: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas pas //
NK024(ya)001:5477: slob dpon gnyan par shes par bya //
NK024(ya)001:5480: bla ma dang ni rdo rje 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:5481: tha dad par ni mi lta'o //
NK024(ya)001:5483: dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:5484: skal pa dus gsum thams cad du //
NK024(ya)001:5485: dkon mchog gsum po mchod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:5486: srog chags bye ba'i tshe skyabs pas //
NK024(ya)001:5487: tshe 'dir sangs rgyas mi thob ste //
NK024(ya)001:5488: yon tan rgya mtsho'i bla ma la //
NK024(ya)001:5489: dad pa'i yid kyis mchod byas na //
NK024(ya)001:5490: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub ni //
NK024(ya)001:5495: tshogs kyi slob dpon tshogs kyi bdag /
NK024(ya)001:5496: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dbang dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:5499: 'jig rten shes legs slob dpon te //'jig rten slob dpon 'jigs pa med //
NK024(ya)001:5500: mgon skyabs 'jig rten yid gcugs pa //
NK024(ya)001:5501: skyabs dang skyob pa bla na med //
NK024(ya)001:5505: rtag tu ri mor bya ba'i 'os //
NK024(ya)001:5506: bkur 'os brjed par bya ba'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:5507: phyag byar 'os pa bla ma'i rab //
NK024(ya)001:5510: nyan thos bye ba phrag brgya mchod pa bas //
NK024(ya)001:5511: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma dam pa la //
NK024(ya)001:5512: bsnyen bkur byas pa'i bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:5514: mkha' 'gro zil gnon gyi rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:5515: dus gsum sangs rgyas rtag tu mchod pa bas //
NK024(ya)001:5516: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i bla ma dam pa la //
NK024(ya)001:5517: ba spu'i khung bur snum gyi thigs gcig gis //
NK024(ya)001:5518: bku mnye byas pa'i bsod nams khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:5521: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK024(ya)001:5522: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:5523: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK024(ya)001:5524: nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5527: chos kun mi shes ma rtogs kyang //
NK024(ya)001:5528: dam par gyur pa'i bla ma la //
NK024(ya)001:5529: bkur sti rim gro cher byas na //'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las brgal 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5530: ci phyir zhing rab gshin pa la //
NK024(ya)001:5531: sa bon btab na rgyas 'phel bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:5532: bsod nams dam pa'i zhing mchog la //
NK024(ya)001:5535: dpal bde mchog sdom pa 'byung ba'i rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:5536: mchod pa thams cad yongs spangs te //
NK024(ya)001:5537: bla ma mchod pa yang dag brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:5538: de mnyes pas ni kun mkhyen pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5539: ye shes mchog ni thob par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5540: zhes gsungs pas bla ma la skyabs su 'gro ba shin tu gal che bar gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:5541: yang yi dam gyi lha la skyabs su 'gro ba yang gal che zhing /
NK024(ya)001:5542: lha ma bsgom na skyon yod pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:5544: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5545: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5546: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK024(ya)001:5547: kyom pa ngan song gsum du skye //
NK024(ya)001:5548: bla med 'gro ba'i rgyun nas bcad //
NK024(ya)001:5549: rigs chad nyid du gnas par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:5550: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:5551: lha spangs na dge ba ci spyad kyang don med par 'gyur ba yin la /
NK024(ya)001:5552: yang yi dam gyi lha tshogs rnams dang dus gsum
NK024(ya)001:5553: rgyun du ma bral bar bsgoms pas yon tan bsam
NK024(ya)001:5554: gyis mi khyab pa 'byung bar gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:5555: lha yi sku nyid gsal bsgoms na //
NK024(ya)001:5557: de nyid chu zla'i tshul shes na //
NK024(ya)001:5559: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor na //
NK024(ya)001:5562: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha la skyabs su 'gro bar bya ba ni nang gi skyabs 'agro'o //
NK024(ya)001:5564: lta sgom spyod 'bras bzhi'i ngang la gnas pa la'ang
NK024(ya)001:5565: skyabs su 'gro bar shes par gsungs pa yin te
NK024(ya)001:5566: / lta ba dbyings ye shes dbyer med /
NK024(ya)001:5567: sgom pa ting nge 'dzin bsran tshugs /
NK024(ya)001:5568: spyod pa bdag gzhan don grub /
NK024(ya)001:5570: de'i ngang las mi 'da' mi yengs /
NK024(ya)001:5571: mi 'gyur bar nyams su len pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:5572: mthar thug de kho na nyid ni gzhi gnas lugs /
NK024(ya)001:5576: de las mi 'da' bar nyams su len pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:5577: de ltar skyabs su song ba'i yon tan ni /
NK024(ya)001:5578: 'dul sdom thams cad kyi rten du 'gyur ba'i yon tan dang /
NK024(ya)001:5579: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i sde tshan du tshud pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5580: mi dang mi ma yin pa rnams kyi gnod pas mi tshugs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5581: lam log par mi 'gyur zhing ngan song gsum du mi skye ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5582: bsam pa thams cad yid bzhin du grub pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:5583: bla ma dkon mchog gis byin gyis brlab par 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:5584: ba la sogs te de ltar yon tan du ma
NK024(ya)001:5585: dang ldan pa'i phyir skyabs su 'gro ba'i sdom pa
NK024(ya)001:5586: la gnas pa shin tu'ang gal che bar gsungs so
NK024(ya)001:5587: // zhes gsungs pa ltar skyabs 'gro'i sdom pa lam du 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:5588: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa dbang gi dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:5589: gegs brgyad bsrung ba ni gong du sngon 'gro'i chos
NK024(ya)001:5590: bshad kyi skabs su rgyas par gsungs pa ltar lam
NK024(ya)001:5591: du 'khyer ro // dbang mchog dbang bcu drug bskur
NK024(ya)001:5592: ma thag pa ltar grangs nges par byas nas lha
NK024(ya)001:5593: gsang pa'i bdag po phyi nang gsang gsum gyi sku
NK024(ya)001:5594: mdog phyag mtshan rgyan cha rnams skabs bstun gyi dbye
NK024(ya)001:5595: ba phyed par byas te lam du 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:5597: n+ai lam b+ha ra d+ha ra badz+ra p+aa ni r+aa dz+ny+aa pa ya ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:5598: zhes brgya stong nas bdun nam gsum gyi bar mi chag par bzla zhing lam du 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:5599: de lta bu'i lam 'khyer rnams tshul bzhin du bgyid snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:5600: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK024(ya)001:5601: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyid //
NK024(ya)001:5603: gsang ba'i bdag po'i dbang bskur rdzogs par thob pa'i gtang rag gi yon du man+dala phul /
NK024(ya)001:5604: lus longs spyod dus gsum gyi dge rtsa thams cad
NK024(ya)001:5605: 'bul lo cha shas nas longs spyod pa dang slob
NK024(ya)001:5606: mar bzung du gsol snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK024(ya)001:5607: / deng nas brtsams te bdag bran du //
NK024(ya)001:5608: khyod la bdag ni 'bul lags kyis //
NK024(ya)001:5609: khyod kyi slob mar bzung ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:5610: cha yis kyang ni spyad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:5612: des rang gzhan gyi don rgya chen po 'grub pa
NK024(ya)001:5613: yin pa dge ba sems can la bsngo bar zhu
NK024(ya)001:5615: slob ma rnams rang gnas su btang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:5616: de nas dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos te /
NK024(ya)001:5625: ba lin+ta sarba p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:5627: mchod pa'i sprin gyi sngags kyis mchod nas /
NK024(ya)001:5628: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK024(ya)001:5629: byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:5630: gsang bdag 'phags pa gos sngon can //'khor bcas ma lus phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:5631: rdo rje sems dpa'i yig brgya lan gsum gyis lhag chad kha bskang /
NK024(ya)001:5632: ma 'byor ba dang nyams pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:5633: zhes sogs kyi tshigs su bcad pas bzod par gsol /
NK024(ya)001:5634: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor mi bsdu na cha gsum
NK024(ya)001:5635: dkyil 'khor dang dkyil 'khor gnyis ka la bkod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5636: tsakli'i lha rnams la brtan bzhugs kyi phyir me tog
NK024(ya)001:5637: 'thor zhing / 'dir ni gzugs dang lhan cig tu //'gro ba'i don du bzhugs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:5638: nad me tshe dang dbang phyug dang //
NK024(ya)001:5639: mchog rnams legs par stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:5640: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:5642: tsakli med pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha gzhan rnams dang bum pa'i lha la dmigs te //
NK024(ya)001:5643: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK024(ya)001:5644: khyod kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:5645: rjes su mthun pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:5646: sangs rgyas yul du gshegs nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:5647: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:5648: a ham yu ti dzahbadz+ra muh zhes lag gnyis kha
NK024(ya)001:5649: phyir bstan pa bsnol bas se gol gtogs pas cha
NK024(ya)001:5650: gsum bsdu na dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi lha rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:5651: ye shes pa bum pa'i lha dang bcas pa chos
NK024(ya)001:5654: mi bsdu na gsang bdag dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams
NK024(ya)001:5655: kyi ye shes pa bum pa'i lha dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:5657: bdag bskyed kyi ye shes pa yang badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:5658: rdul tshon kyang dbang ldan nas bzung rdo rjes gshig la bsdu'o //
NK024(ya)001:5659: mthar dge ba bsngo zhing rgyun spyod bya /
NK024(ya)001:5660: de'i rjes su nub mo slar yang zhi khro'i phrin las rgyas pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:5662: gzhan du na bka' brgyad spyi bka' dang sgos bka'i
NK024(ya)001:5663: dkyil 'khor gang yang rung ba'i las gzhung la brten
NK024(ya)001:5664: nas legs ldan lcam dral sogs chos srung rnams la
NK024(ya)001:5665: mchod gtor 'bul / gong du bshad pa'i ye shes
NK024(ya)001:5666: dang 'jig rten gyi ma mor mdos gtor bskang ba
NK024(ya)001:5667: sogs kyang ci nus su bgyis pa'i mthar /
NK024(ya)001:5668: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i cho ga bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:5670: dpon slob tshogs la rol gtor ma btang /
NK024(ya)001:5671: lhag mas 'byung po tshim par byas /
NK024(ya)001:5672: zhes gsungs pa ltar las gzhung gang yin ltar chad lhag med par bya /
NK024(ya)001:5674: yo byad lhag ma gsog na'ang de'i nyin mo 'dzom par bsag go //
NK024(ya)001:5675: de yan chad sngon 'gro'i cho ga'o //
NK024(ya)001:5677: yo byad rnams 'dzom par bsag dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:5678: 'di yan chad sngon 'gro yin pas nyin gcig la tshang bar grub na legs /
NK024(ya)001:5679: gal te nyi ma thung ba lta bu'i skabs cis
NK024(ya)001:5680: kyang mi grub par byung nas bzung yan lag zhag
NK024(ya)001:5681: gcig dang / de man chad la gcig ste zhag gnyis la nges par grub par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5682: mdo dbang nyin byed mkha' la dbang 'char ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:5683: snga ltas sa yi cho ga'i skya rengs dang //
NK024(ya)001:5684: gsang bdag dbang gi thun mtshams dang po'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:5685: lhan cig shar bas gdul bya'i pad+ma 'dzum //
NK024(ya)001:5686: rgyal kun gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin mthu stobs bdag /
NK024(ya)001:5687: phyag rdor dbang bskur rgyu skar grangs mang yang //
NK024(ya)001:5688: ngan song gnas 'dren cho ga'i 'od stong can //
NK024(ya)001:5689: sdug bsngal mun 'joms rgyud don 'di nyid tsam //
NK024(ya)001:5690: smin byed zab mo'i sgo 'phar rab 'byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5691: thabs mkhas ngo mtshar phrin las dpal 'bar ba //
NK024(ya)001:5692: bla ma yi dam dbyer med 'khor lo'i mgon //
NK024(ya)001:5693: deng nas byang chub bar du bdag srungs shig /
NK024(ya)001:5694: ces pa ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////de nas dngos gzhi'i cho ga la /
NK024(ya)001:5697: dang po yan lag gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:5699: de la dbang gi chu bo bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:5700: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK024(ya)001:5701: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK024(ya)001:5703: thog mar yan lag gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5710: de la dang po lha mi'i theg pa'i sgrub khrigs la /
NK024(ya)001:5711: dkyil 'khor bsham khungs mchod pa bsham //
NK024(ya)001:5712: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:5713: dpang skong khrus byas sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:5714: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzegs thub pa bsgom //
NK024(ya)001:5715: gsol gdab sdom pa dus khrims dpog /
NK024(ya)001:5716: rin chen ldan pa'i bum pa la //
NK024(ya)001:5717: bdag 'jug rin chen chos bshad dang //
NK024(ya)001:5718: ka smad lha dbang lam 'khyer bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:5719: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang //
NK024(ya)001:5720: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyir dgos //
NK024(ya)001:5721: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:5722: zhes don sum cus bstan no //
NK024(ya)001:5725: dang po dkyil 'khor bsham pa la dgongs pa gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:5729: dang po cho ga 'dzugs pa nas bla ma yi
NK024(ya)001:5730: dam mkha' 'gro chos skyong gzhi bdag la mchod gtor
NK024(ya)001:5731: bsham / tshogs dang zas phud phul /
NK024(ya)001:5732: khyad par e yam ram kham zhes nam mkha' rlung
NK024(ya)001:5733: me chu rnams mas brtsegs su chags pa'i chu'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:5735: gnyis pa tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa'i rta babs la lha mi'i theg pa sgom pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:5736: gsum pa lha mi'i dkyil 'khor sgos su bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:5737: zhes gsungs pa'i don gsum gyis bstan pa las /
NK024(ya)001:5738: dang por sngon 'gro'i skabs nas nye bar brtsams te /
NK024(ya)001:5741: srog bslu rgya gzug lam 'phrang bsal //
NK024(ya)001:5742: tsh+wa tsh+wa chu gtor la sogs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:5743: chos spyod skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sogs //
NK024(ya)001:5744: dge tshogs dpung bskyed bsngo ba bya //
NK024(ya)001:5746: bya ba gang dag gang byed pa'i sngon du 'gro
NK024(ya)001:5747: ba dge ba'i las dpung cher bskyed na las de
NK024(ya)001:5748: mthar phyin la bsam don tshul bzhin grub pa rgyal
NK024(ya)001:5750: tshogs bsags pa las bde ba 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:5751: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir 'bum lnga 'don pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5752: 'bum lnga'i ngos 'dzin tshul mkhas pa dag gi gsung rab las /
NK024(ya)001:5753: sku'i 'bum dkon mchog brtsegs pa chos kyi rnam grangs 'bum las bsdus pa ltung bshags /
NK024(ya)001:5754: gsung gi 'bum myang 'das zhal chems 'bum las bsdus pa 'da' kha ye shes /
NK024(ya)001:5755: thugs kyi 'bum sher phyin stong phrag brgya pa las bsdus pa sher snying /
NK024(ya)001:5756: yon tan gyi 'bum phal po che smon lam 'bum las bsdus pa bzang spyod /
NK024(ya)001:5757: phrin las kyi 'bum lang+kara gshegs pa srin po 'bum
NK024(ya)001:5758: btul ba'i tshul las bsdus pa rnam 'joms zhes rgyas
NK024(ya)001:5759: bsdus gnyis 'byung ba ltar spro na /
NK024(ya)001:5771: sems can 'chi nges pa'i srog bslu ba dang lam 'phrang bzo ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:5772: tsh+wa tsh+wa gdab pa dang chu gtor gtong ba sogs la 'bad dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:5773: sngon 'gro la nan cher byas pas bar chad 'byung mi srid pa yin gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:5774: gzhan yang nyin re bzhin zhi khro'i phrin las tshogs
NK024(ya)001:5775: dang bcas pa re bya zhing chos srung la mchod
NK024(ya)001:5776: gtor bsngo zhing phrin las bcol ba dang cha gsum
NK024(ya)001:5779: lam du dkyil 'khor sgom tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:5780: de ltar bri ba'i tshul gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:5782: e las nam mkha' dang yam las rlung ram las
NK024(ya)001:5783: me kham las chu rnams mas rim gyis chags pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5784: chu'i dkyil 'khor la lha mi dgod pa ni sa
NK024(ya)001:5785: mtshams zhes bshad pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:5786: bka' gter gyi phur pa rnams la srid pa'i phur
NK024(ya)001:5787: pa zhes pa dbal la ngan song gnas bcu nas
NK024(ya)001:5788: rgya mdun 'og mar lha mi sogs 'dod khams /
NK024(ya)001:5789: changs bzung smad la gzugs khams /
NK024(ya)001:5791: rgya mdud gong ma dkyil 'khor du bzhed pa dang chos mtshungs /
NK024(ya)001:5792: gnyis pa lam du dkyil 'khor sgom tshul ni tshogs
NK024(ya)001:5793: chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi rta babs dang po
NK024(ya)001:5794: la lha mi'i theg pa'i lha rnams sgom pa yin
NK024(ya)001:5797: thog ma rang nas dbus su a nu yo ga
NK024(ya)001:5798: tshogs chen 'dus pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sngon
NK024(ya)001:5799: 'gro'i chos rnams tshang ba byas te /
NK024(ya)001:5800: thig gdab tshom bu bkod de /
NK024(ya)001:5801: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams 'khor du bkod pa la /
NK024(ya)001:5805: lho nub tu byang chub sems dpa'/
NK024(ya)001:5807: nub byang du u pa ya /
NK024(ya)001:5808: byang du ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul khro bo /
NK024(ya)001:5809: byang shar du ma h+aa yo ga sgyu 'phrul zhi ba /
NK024(ya)001:5810: steng du rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i dkyil 'khor bri ba'i lugs dang /
NK024(ya)001:5811: yang na shar lhor lha mi /
NK024(ya)001:5814: byang shar du byang chub sems dpa' rnams byed pa'i lugs gnyis su bshad /
NK024(ya)001:5815: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK024(ya)001:5816: nub dang po la sngon 'gro dang /
NK024(ya)001:5817: gnyis pa lha mi nyan rang rnams gcig tu dril nas dbang bskur ba'i lho nub tu lha mi /
NK024(ya)001:5819: zur gcig tu rang rgyal zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:5820: dbus su tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor yod pa 'dra
NK024(ya)001:5821: yang byed pa'i gsal kha ma byung bas tshogs chen
NK024(ya)001:5822: a nu'i skabs su rgyas par 'chad rtsis su mngon
NK024(ya)001:5823: / zur lugs la theg pa 'og ma rnams la
NK024(ya)001:5824: re re bzhin du sa mtshams kyi dgod tshul dang
NK024(ya)001:5825: / / tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor la sgom tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:5826: bri ba'i dkyil 'khor dang gsum du bzhed de /
NK024(ya)001:5828: gsum pa lha mi'i dkyil 'khor sgos su bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:5833: phyi'i rgya mtsho'i gling bcu gnyis la /
NK024(ya)001:5838: phyi'i lcags ri la gling bzhi bye ba phrag brgya'i thig 'god do //
NK024(ya)001:5840: mi 'khrugs pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dab brgyad dbus sngo /
NK024(ya)001:5843: dus bzang gi dkyil 'khor gsum 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog /
NK024(ya)001:5848: dus gsum sangs rgyas dang dkon mchog gsum gyi dkyil 'khor pad+ma brgyad ldan dbus ser /
NK024(ya)001:5849: 'dab ma sna tshogs pa ste de rnams sgo rta babs yod med gang 'os bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5851: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan yab sras kyi bla dpe'i mchan bur /
NK024(ya)001:5852: tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor la rtsa ba spyi khyab kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:5853: bye brag so so'i dkyil 'khor gnyis zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:5854: gnyis pa la yang gnyis kyi ri rab gling bzhi
NK024(ya)001:5855: dang bcas pa la gling bzhi lha mo'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:5856: zhes rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:5857: bye brag la bzhir gsungs te mi 'khrugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:5858: dus bzang gi dkyil 'khor gsum mdzad pas yongs dril dkyil 'khor lnga ste /
NK024(ya)001:5859: rig 'dzin rje'i gsan yig dang dngos slob o rgyan pa'i gsan yig gnyis tshig mthun par /
NK024(ya)001:5860: lha mi'i theg pa la lnga ste /
NK024(ya)001:5861: ngan song sbyong ba kun rig rnam snang /
NK024(ya)001:5862: las sgrib gcod pa mi 'khrugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:5863: nad kyi bskal pa zhi byed tshes brgyad sman bla /
NK024(ya)001:5864: mtshon gyi bskal pa zhi byed nya'i snang ba mtha' yas /
NK024(ya)001:5865: mu ge'i bskal pa zhi byed stong gi sh+aakya thub pa dang lnga'o //
NK024(ya)001:5867: snga ma rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang phyi ma bzhi po bye brag gi dkyil 'khor bzhir nges la /
NK024(ya)001:5868: rgyal dbang mchog gi gsan yig tu gong du bshad pa'i lnga la bye brag gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:5869: de rnams gcig tu dril ba lha nyer lnga ma
NK024(ya)001:5870: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor te drug tu bzhed pa ni
NK024(ya)001:5871: / rig 'dzin rje dpon slob kyi gsan yig la yang de ltar 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:5872: zur lugs dang kahthoga lugs gnyis kar bsdu na gcig
NK024(ya)001:5873: dril gyi dkyil 'khor re re las bye brag gi
NK024(ya)001:5874: dkyil 'khor rnams mi mdzad pa'i lugs yin /
NK024(ya)001:5875: kahthoga lugs kyi bla ma 'dra'i thob yig tu dkyil 'khor bdun 'dug pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:5877: dus bzang gsum so sor re re /
NK024(ya)001:5878: dus gsum sangs rgyas la bsdoms te gcig /
NK024(ya)001:5879: dkon mchog gsum la bsdoms te gcig rnams 'dod pa yin mod /
NK024(ya)001:5880: 'dir rang lugs zur lugs kyi rtsa ba la zhib
NK024(ya)001:5881: mor dpyad cing gong ma'i zin bris rnams kyi don
NK024(ya)001:5882: bsdus na lha mi la dkyil 'khor rgyas par phye
NK024(ya)001:5884: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor ri rab gling bzhi ma /
NK024(ya)001:5885: bye brag gi dkyil 'khor mi 'khrugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:5886: dus bzang gi lha gsum la dkyil 'khor re re /
NK024(ya)001:5887: dus gsum sangs rgyas la gtso bo go 'pho ba'i dkyil 'khor re re /
NK024(ya)001:5888: dkon mchog gsum las sangs rgyas dang /
NK024(ya)001:5889: dge 'dun gnyis la gtso bo thub chen dang /
NK024(ya)001:5890: chos la yum chen po ste dkyil 'khor gsum /
NK024(ya)001:5891: gcig dril lha nyer lnga ma ste bcu gnyis su 'gyur la /
NK024(ya)001:5892: de yang dkyil 'khor lnga ni med thabs med la /
NK024(ya)001:5893: rgyas par na bcu gcig /'bring lnga bdun gang rigs /
NK024(ya)001:5894: tha ma rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang lha nyer lnga ma gang rigs bri dgos par the tshom med /
NK024(ya)001:5895: ji ltar bri ba ni thog mar rgyas pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK024(ya)001:5896: dang po rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gling bzhi lha mi'i
NK024(ya)001:5897: dkyil 'khor 'di la thig rtsa zur pa zhig yod
NK024(ya)001:5898: pas / de yang rgyud thig gi cha chen bcu drug gdab /
NK024(ya)001:5899: dang po dang gnyis pa'i thig /
NK024(ya)001:5900: lnga pa phan chad du mnan nas btab pas nang du thig ro mi yong ba'i khyad yod /
NK024(ya)001:5901: nang thig gi dang po zlum por bskor ba pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:5902: gnyis pa cha bzhir bgos pa ri rab /
NK024(ya)001:5903: gsum pa cha phran phyed tshad kyi bdun du btang
NK024(ya)001:5904: ba mtha' nas zlum por cha chung gcig bskor ba
NK024(ya)001:5905: lcags ri dang / de'i nang du mtsho gling ngo //
NK024(ya)001:5907: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK024(ya)001:5909: tshon ni lte ba dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:5910: de'i phyir phyogs mdog gi pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:5911: de'i phyir ri rab shar dkar /
NK024(ya)001:5914: byang ser ba cha chung bdun gyi bcad rnams ser po byas pa ni gser ri bdun dang /
NK024(ya)001:5915: bar rol mtsho bdun sngon po /
NK024(ya)001:5916: de'i phyir lcags ri sngon po cha chung gcig zlum
NK024(ya)001:5917: por bskor ba'i nang gi phyogs bzhir rgya mtsho ri
NK024(ya)001:5918: rab kyi mdog dang mtshungs pa'i nang du gling bzhi
NK024(ya)001:5919: gling phran brgyad ni shar zlum po che ba dbus
NK024(ya)001:5920: dang g.yas g.yon du chung ba re re dkar po
NK024(ya)001:5921: / de bzhin du lhor sog kha gsum sngo /
NK024(ya)001:5922: nub tu zla gam gsum dmar po /
NK024(ya)001:5923: byang du gru bzhi gsum ser po /
NK024(ya)001:5924: so sor yul ljongs dang khang bzang gi rnam pa bri'o //
NK024(ya)001:5925: khor yug sngon po'i phyir rtsig pa dkar /
NK024(ya)001:5929: ljang ba nang rim bzhin nam /
NK024(ya)001:5941: lha mtshan ni 'dab bzhi'i dbus su rnam snang dang /
NK024(ya)001:5942: shar gling gi lha gsum gyi mtshan ma shar gling
NK024(ya)001:5943: dbus su brgya byin yab yum dang nang du blta
NK024(ya)001:5944: ba'i g.yas su mnga' gzhug pa /
NK024(ya)001:5945: g.yon du pho nya'i mtshan ma mngon rtogs ltar bkod /
NK024(ya)001:5946: de bzhin du gling gzhan rnams kyang phyogs kyi gling
NK024(ya)001:5947: gsum po so so dang rgyal chen bzhi sgo bzhir
NK024(ya)001:5949: kahthoga lugs lte bar 'dab ma bcu gnyis la lha
NK024(ya)001:5950: bkod srol 'dug cing glan ban gyis kyang 'dam khar
NK024(ya)001:5951: gsungs / sgo rdzogs mi byed na dbus su pad 'dab bzhi pa zhig /
NK024(ya)001:5952: de'i phyir ri rab nas lcags ri'i bar bri zhing dbus su rnam snang dang /
NK024(ya)001:5953: pad 'dab bzhis phyogs bzhir rgyal po bzhi bkod na 'thad par mthong /
NK024(ya)001:5954: lha gzhan rnams gling bzhi gling phran la bkod par bshad /
NK024(ya)001:5955: mdun bskyed dus gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid tshang ba'i
NK024(ya)001:5956: nang du ri gling rnams sgom dgos pa'i phyir sgo
NK024(ya)001:5958: ma bris kyang skyon cher med de /
NK024(ya)001:5960: de rnams sgo rta babs yod med gang bde bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:5962: gnyis pa mi 'khrugs pa'i dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi dbus sngo /
NK024(ya)001:5967: rtsig ljang khyams sgo phan chad spyi ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:5968: dus bzang gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bkral ba'i dbang du
NK024(ya)001:5969: byas te dkyil 'khor gsum pa mu ge'i bskal pa
NK024(ya)001:5970: zhi byed gnam stong gi lha bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya
NK024(ya)001:5972: bzhi pa mtshon gyi bskal pa zhi byed bco lnga nya'i lha snang ba mtha' yas kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:5973: lnga pa nad kyi bskal pa zhi byed tshes brgyad
NK024(ya)001:5974: kyi lha sman bla'i dkyil 'khor te dkyil 'khor gsum
NK024(ya)001:5975: ka dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog rtsig ljang
NK024(ya)001:5980: dus gsum sangs rgyas dang dkon mchog gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bkral ba ltar na /
NK024(ya)001:5981: dkyil 'khor drug pa mar me mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:5982: bdun pa thub dbang gi dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:5984: dgu pa sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:5986: bcu gcig pa dge 'dun gyi dkyil 'khor te drug po thams cad lte ba ser /
NK024(ya)001:5989: khyams sgo rta babs pad rdor me ri sogs rigs 'agre'o //
NK024(ya)001:5990: bcu gnyis pa gcig dril gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:5991: 'di gong bzhin rgyas par bris na der tshang bas
NK024(ya)001:5992: mi dgos kyang bsdus par byed na gcig dril gyi
NK024(ya)001:5993: dkyil 'khor bla ma'i man ngag bzhin 'di ltar bris
NK024(ya)001:5994: te / ri rab gser ri rol mtsho gling bzhi
NK024(ya)001:5995: gling phran khor yug dang bcas pa'i phyir sgo rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:5996: yod med gang bde'i lte ba pad 'dab bzhi pa'i
NK024(ya)001:5999: lho nub byang gsum du dus bzang gi lha gsum /
NK024(ya)001:6000: ri rab gling bzhi gling phran rnams la rgyal chen bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6002: pho nya mngag gzhug rnams bkod pa'i lha nyer lnga ma'i lugs 'di 'doms che zhing 'thad par mngon /
NK024(ya)001:6003: zur lugs kahthoga gnyis ka'i lugs la bsdu na rtsa
NK024(ya)001:6004: ba'i dkyil 'khor la basngagasa pa tsam mdzad 'dug kyang
NK024(ya)001:6005: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la rnam snang dang /
NK024(ya)001:6008: pho nya mngag gzhug rnams ma gtogs mi 'khrugs pa
NK024(ya)001:6009: dang dus bzang gi lha gsum med phyir chad skyon
NK024(ya)001:6010: du 'dug pas dkyil 'khor gcig tu bsdu na phyi
NK024(ya)001:6012: dkon mchog gsum la bsdus pa'i tshe dngos su lha
NK024(ya)001:6013: gnas med kyang de dag la don gyi tshang ba
NK024(ya)001:6014: yin no / 'bring po dkyil 'khor lngar dbye na rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:6016: dus bzang gi lha'i dkyil 'khor gsum ste lnga'o //'bring
NK024(ya)001:6017: po bdun du byed na gong gi lnga'i steng dus
NK024(ya)001:6018: gsum sangs rgyas bsdoms par dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab brgyad
NK024(ya)001:6019: pa gcig dang / dkon mchog gsum bsdoms pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dab brgyad pa gcig ste bdun no //
NK024(ya)001:6020: bsdus pa'i lugs ni gcig dril gyi dkyil 'khor las 'phros te gong du bshad zin to //
NK024(ya)001:6021: rtsa ba'i sa bcad sum cu'i skabs /
NK024(ya)001:6022: dkyil 'khor bsham khrus mchod pa bsham //
NK024(ya)001:6024: dang po dkyil 'khor bsham pa rgyas par bshad zin /
NK024(ya)001:6025: gnyis pa khrus zer ba 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:6026: rtsa bar sa bcad gnyis pa 'chad skabs /
NK024(ya)001:6029: theg pa'i dang po bcu drug mgon //
NK024(ya)001:6030: zhes pa mi chos bcu drug po 'di 'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:6031: dang ngan song las skyob pa'i mgon du bstan no
NK024(ya)001:6033: de ltar na khrus zer ba dang skang rtang las
NK024(ya)001:6034: zer ba gnyis ka yi ge ma dag pa'i skyon
NK024(ya)001:6035: te / mdo dbang gi rtsa ba dbang rin chen
NK024(ya)001:6036: skas gdang zhes pa las khungs kyi lung drangs pas
NK024(ya)001:6037: mi chos bcu drug lha mi'i nyams len gyi rtsa
NK024(ya)001:6038: bar 'dug pas de la khungs byas shing /
NK024(ya)001:6039: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK024(ya)001:6040: khungs ni 'khrul snang rtsad gcod nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las gsungs par bshad /
NK024(ya)001:6041: de ltar na dkyil 'khor bsham khrus zer ba bsham khungs dang /
NK024(ya)001:6042: skang rtang las zer ba skas gdang las zhes pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:6045: tsh+wa tsh+wa dkar zhal ston pa'i mi grangs sam so
NK024(ya)001:6046: so'i lo grangs dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' skor du bzhag
NK024(ya)001:6047: / bsnyen sngags kyi rab gnas bya /
NK024(ya)001:6049: bum pa rin po che sman 'bru sna dri bzang
NK024(ya)001:6050: dang lha khrus me long la byas pa'i chu blug
NK024(ya)001:6051: / kha rgyan mgul chings gzungs thag dang bcas pa'i mchu bla ma la bstan pa bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:6052: gtso bo lha lnga'i snying po brgya rtsa bzlas la pho brang du 'god ces dang /
NK024(ya)001:6063: dkyil 'khor de rnams ji ltar bsham tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:6065: de'i mdun nas brtsams te g.yas skor gyis mi 'khrugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6068: dkon mchog gsum sogs bskor te thams cad kyi mdun phyogs gcig tu bstan no //
NK024(ya)001:6069: tsh+wa tsh+wa dkyil 'khor thams cad la mi bskor bar
NK024(ya)001:6070: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la bskor ba'i phyag len yod
NK024(ya)001:6071: / dkyil 'khor gcig las med na de gar bskor /
NK024(ya)001:6072: tsh+wa tsh+wa'i grangs ni slob ma mang du yod na mi grangs sam /
NK024(ya)001:6073: nyung na slob ma'i lo grangs byed /
NK024(ya)001:6074: dkyil 'khor so so'i lha gnas su 'jim pa lta
NK024(ya)001:6075: bu'i rten byed la lha tsaka rnams smyug thur la
NK024(ya)001:6076: bcings te btsugs / rgya bod kyi yi ge sogs dbang rdzas rnams kyang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:6078: rgya bod kyi yi ge'i dbang rten gsung /
NK024(ya)001:6079: tsh+wa tsh+wa thugs rten yin zhes gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:6080: dkyil 'khor so so'i mthar mtshams 'dzin nas bzung chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i mchod pa g.yas skor dang /
NK024(ya)001:6081: dkon mchog spyi gtor dkar zlum dkar gsum mngar gsum gyis brgyan pa bzang ba re re yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:6082: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu bdun par /
NK024(ya)001:6083: rin chen ldan pa'i bum pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:6084: rgyal rigs ma nyams pa la gser dngul gyi bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:6087: rin po che bcug la bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:6088: zhes gsungs pa'i don slob ma rgyal rigs la dbang bum rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:6089: rigs nyams la sogs phal la rdza bum yin 'dra
NK024(ya)001:6090: yang de 'dra'i dbye ba dka' bas na rtsa ba'i
NK024(ya)001:6091: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:6092: bum pa dri bzang gi chu dang bum rdzas nyer
NK024(ya)001:6093: lnga'i bcud ldan rten khyad par can la khrus gsol
NK024(ya)001:6094: ba'i khrus chu dang bcas pa blug /
NK024(ya)001:6095: dar dkar ser gang rigs kyis mgul chings kha rgyan
NK024(ya)001:6096: dung chos rdo rje gzungs thag dang bcas pa bsham
NK024(ya)001:6097: / gzhan yang sdom rten ston pa'i sku'i mdun du mchod pa'i khyad par rgya che ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:6098: zhi khro chos srung gi gtor ma rnams la kha bsos /
NK024(ya)001:6099: cha gsum gyi gtor ma gsar pa /
NK024(ya)001:6100: slob mar dbang gi sngon 'gro'i bgegs gtor sogs ma tshang ba med par bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:6102: bzhi pa rab gnas ni rten 'brel rab gnas bya /
NK024(ya)001:6104: mchod pa bsham pa'i skabs bsnyen sngags kyi rab gnas bya /
NK024(ya)001:6105: zhes gsungs pa dang don gcig pas gong du phyag
NK024(ya)001:6106: rdor skabs bshad pa ltar gyi ting nge 'dzin dang
NK024(ya)001:6107: bcas rdor dril 'dzin pas dkyil 'khor so so'i lha
NK024(ya)001:6108: sngags kyis 'go mnan pa'i rten 'brel snying po bzlas
NK024(ya)001:6109: pa'i me tog dkyil 'khor gnas khang mchod rdzas thams
NK024(ya)001:6110: cad la 'thor zhing rab gnas bya /
NK024(ya)001:6112: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:6113: dpang skong khrus bya sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:6115: chog gzhung dngos thar pa chen po'i mdor ngos bzung zhing /
