NK024(ya)001:6116: yang na dpang skong phyag rgya pa'i mdo klag par
NK024(ya)001:6117: gsungs pas sa bcad lnga pa chog gzhung dang 'og
NK024(ya)001:6118: gi dpang skor gnyis sbyar dgos shing dpang skong sa
NK024(ya)001:6119: bcad lnga pa'i khongs su 'du bas zur du mi
NK024(ya)001:6121: lnga pa ni thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:6122: rtogs pa chen po'i dpang skong phyag rgya ba'i cho ga gzhung bsrang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:6124: bla ma gong ma mkhyen pa'i spyan dang ldan pa
NK024(ya)001:6125: de dag gis tshig rigs de tsam la brten nas
NK024(ya)001:6126: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi sgrub mchod dang /
NK024(ya)001:6127: mdo sde klog pa sogs mdzad pa the tshom med
NK024(ya)001:6128: kyang deng sang cho ga zur du mi gsal gshis
NK024(ya)001:6129: dkyil 'khor bshams te dbang bskur la 'jug pa ma
NK024(ya)001:6130: gtogs sgrub mchod dang mdo sde klog pa sogs mi
NK024(ya)001:6131: mdzad pa mang bas lag len 'khrul pa sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:6132: 'dug cing / kahthoga lugs la sgrub mchod mdzad srol dang /
NK024(ya)001:6133: thar pa chen po'i chog gzhung sngags kyi cho ga 'dra ba zhig 'dug mod /
NK024(ya)001:6134: 'on kyang bdag mdun bum gsum par bka' ma zhig
NK024(ya)001:6135: lan gsum 'don pa lta bu'i the tshom gyi gzhir
NK024(ya)001:6136: 'dug pas 'dir gong ma'i gsung rab la brten nas
NK024(ya)001:6137: bshad par bya'o // de la dang po bla ma
NK024(ya)001:6138: dge slong yin na rang nyid kyis rten gyi drung
NK024(ya)001:6139: du 'og gi nyan thos kyi cho ga'i skabs na
NK024(ya)001:6140: yod pa'i gso spyong de nyid blangs /
NK024(ya)001:6141: dge bsnyen dang sngags pa yin na lha mi'i dus
NK024(ya)001:6142: khrims yan lag brgyad pa cho ga 'di ga'i 'og
NK024(ya)001:6143: nas 'byung ba ltar bsnyen gnas gso sbyong gi tshul
NK024(ya)001:6144: du blangs / dge bsnyen gyi bsnyen gnas la gso sbyong gi ming btags su rung ste /
NK024(ya)001:6145: bu ston thams cad mkhyen pas /
NK024(ya)001:6146: 'di dge bsnyen rnams kyi dge ba'i rtsa ba gso
NK024(ya)001:6147: zhing sdig pa sbyong bas dge bsnyen gyis tshes brgyad
NK024(ya)001:6148: sogs la rtag tu bsrung dgos shing dge bsnyen gyi
NK024(ya)001:6149: gso sbyong yin pas gso sbyong /
NK024(ya)001:6151: cho ga dngos la bdag mdun bum gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:6152: thog mar mchod pa byin rlabs phyag rdor skabs ltar
NK024(ya)001:6153: bya zhing rol mo'i sngags dang mchod pa'i sprin gyi
NK024(ya)001:6155: bdag sogs 'gro ba ma gyur nam mkha'i mtha' dang
NK024(ya)001:6156: mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad dus deng nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:6157: ste ji srid byang chub snying po la mchis kyi
NK024(ya)001:6158: bar du rje btsun rtsa ba dang brgyud par bcas
NK024(ya)001:6159: pa'i dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams la skyabs
NK024(ya)001:6160: su mchi'o // yi dam dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK024(ya)001:6161: rnams la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams
NK024(ya)001:6162: la dam pa'i chos rnams la 'phags pa'i dge 'dun
NK024(ya)001:6163: rnams la lan gsum sogs brjod /
NK024(ya)001:6164: skyabs sems thun mong gi slad du /
NK024(ya)001:6167: sems can thams cad bde ba dang bde ba'i rgyu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:6168: sogs tshad med bzhi lan gcig bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:6170: 'og gi sa bcad bcu gnyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6171: bcu dgu pa gnyis kyi don ltar na thub pa bsgom par gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:6172: ston pa ni lha mi thams cad kyi skyabs su gyur phyir rigs pas brtags kyang mi 'gal mod /
NK024(ya)001:6173: 'on kyang rnam pa lha mi'i theg pa ltar snang
NK024(ya)001:6174: yang don sngags lam kho na yin pas gcig dril
NK024(ya)001:6175: gyi dkyil 'khor bdag bskyed du byed pa yig rnying
NK024(ya)001:6176: mtha' dag las gsungs shing phyag len du yang mdzad
NK024(ya)001:6179: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che las
NK024(ya)001:6180: grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi rgyan
NK024(ya)001:6181: rta babs mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:6182: dbus su ri rab shar dkar /
NK024(ya)001:6188: gling phran khor yug dang bcas pa'i lte bar pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:6189: 'dab ma bzhi pa'i dbus su nyi zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:6190: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das kun rig rnam par snang
NK024(ya)001:6191: mdzad zhal bzhi dang sku mdog dkar ba byang chub
NK024(ya)001:6192: mchog gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil krung du
NK024(ya)001:6193: bzhugs pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan
NK024(ya)001:6194: pa / shar gyi 'dab mar bcom ldan 'das rdo
NK024(ya)001:6195: rje mi 'khrugs pa sngon po g.yas sa gnon g.yon
NK024(ya)001:6196: mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya'i steng na gser gyi rdo
NK024(ya)001:6198: lhor ston pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po gser mdog can sa gnon mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:6199: nub tu sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas dmar po mnyam gzhag gi steng na tshe bum can /
NK024(ya)001:6200: byang du sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal
NK024(ya)001:6201: po mthing kha g.yas mchog sbyin gyis a ru ra
NK024(ya)001:6202: dang g.yon mnyam gzhag gi steng du bdud rtsis gang
NK024(ya)001:6204: bzhi ka'ang sprul sku'i cha byad chos gos rnam pa
NK024(ya)001:6205: gsum dang ldan cing mtshan dpes spras pa zhabs gnyis
NK024(ya)001:6206: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs shing zhal dbus
NK024(ya)001:6207: su phyogs pa'o // shar gling du brgya byin yab yum mngag gzhug pho nya dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:6208: lho gling du tshangs pa yab yum mngag gzhug pho nya dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:6209: nub gling du khyab 'jug yab yum mngag gzhug pho nya dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:6210: byang gling du dbang phyug yab yum mngag gzhug pho nya dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:6212: thams cad kyang rang rang gi rgyan cha lugs sku mdog phyag mtshan dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:6213: de dag thams cad kyi spyi bor /
NK024(ya)001:6214: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum gis mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6215: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:6216: rgyar bcas te snyan gsan dbab cing mdun gyi nam
NK024(ya)001:6217: mkhar spyan drangs / dzahh+aum bam hohs ye shes pa gzhug /
NK024(ya)001:6218: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra a r+g+ham /
NK024(ya)001:6227: chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK024(ya)001:6228: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:6229: ting nge 'dzin ldan phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:6230: phyag 'tshal bcom ldan kun rig la //
NK024(ya)001:6231: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK024(ya)001:6232: thugs rjes rtag tu mya ngan mi 'da' bar //
NK024(ya)001:6233: mtha' yas 'gro ba'i don grub lhur mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:6234: bcom ldan mi 'khrugs pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:6235: rnam dag sku mnga' mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK024(ya)001:6236: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:6237: grags pa 'jig rten bkram nas lham me ba //
NK024(ya)001:6238: mgon po khyod nyid la ni phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:6239: sh+loo ka 'og ma 'di tog gzungs ltar bris pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:6240: 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK024(ya)001:6241: kun rtog ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:6242: ting 'dzin chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:6243: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK024(ya)001:6244: thugs rje kun la snyoms pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:6245: mtshan tsam thos pas ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal sel //
NK024(ya)001:6246: dug gsum nad sel sangs rgyas sman gyi bla //
NK024(ya)001:6247: bee d+aur+ya yi 'od la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:6248: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:6249: zhing rdul kun gyi grangs snyed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:6250: lus btud pa yi rnam kun tu //
NK024(ya)001:6251: mchog tu dad pas bstod par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:6253: lha so so'i thugs kar zla ba la gnas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:6254: sa bon h+aum yig gi mthar sngags kyi phreng ba
NK024(ya)001:6255: sku mdog dang mthun pas bskor ba las 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:6257: tshur 'dus bdag la thim bas dngos grub thob par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:6259: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga te pa
NK024(ya)001:6260: ri sho d+ha na r+aa dza ya ta th+aa ga
NK024(ya)001:6261: ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:6263: sho d+ha ne sho d+ha ne sarba p+aa pam bi
NK024(ya)001:6264: sho d+ha ne shud+d+he bi shud+d+he sarba karma a wa
NK024(ya)001:6265: ra na bi shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:6268: kam ka ni kam ka ni /
NK024(ya)001:6269: ro tsa ni ro tsa ni /
NK024(ya)001:6270: tro ta ni tro ta ni /
NK024(ya)001:6271: t+r+aa sa ni t+r+aa sa ni /
NK024(ya)001:6272: pra ti ha na pra ti ha na /
NK024(ya)001:6273: sarba karma pa ram pa r+aa ni me sarba sa t+wa n+aany+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:6275: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:6277: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih sman blar /
NK024(ya)001:6279: b+hee sha dz+ye b+hee sha dz+ye ma h+aa b+hee sha
NK024(ya)001:6280: dz+ye b+hee sha dz+ye r+aa dza sa mud+ga te s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:6281: h+aa / de rnams ci nus su bzlas /
NK024(ya)001:6283: bdag bskyed gzhal yas khang lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu nas rang la thim par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6284: bum bskyed ni bum dbang gi dus rnam snang 'od
NK024(ya)001:6285: du zhu ba'i bum pas slob bu la zhes gsungs
NK024(ya)001:6286: pas gtso rkyang bskyed pa 'dra zhig 'dug mod kyang
NK024(ya)001:6287: / yo byad bsham pa'i skabs gtso bo lha lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:6288: snying po brgya rtsa bzlas la pho brang du 'god
NK024(ya)001:6289: / / ces gsungs pa ltar na gtso bo lnga bskyed dgos par gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:6290: bla ma rnams kyang de ltar bzhed pas /
NK024(ya)001:6291: bum pa swa b+h+aa was sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:6292: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du b+h+r+aum yig
NK024(ya)001:6293: zhu ba las byung ba'i rin po che'i bum pa
NK024(ya)001:6294: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang gzhal yas khang par
NK024(ya)001:6295: gyur pa'i dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte
NK024(ya)001:6296: bar pad zla'i gdan la bcom ldan 'das kun rig
NK024(ya)001:6297: rnam par snang mdzad ces pa nas /
NK024(ya)001:6299: zhes pa'i bar bdag bskyed ltar gtso bo lha lnga sgom /
NK024(ya)001:6301: mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum gis mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6302: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes pa nas /
NK024(ya)001:6303: spyan 'dren mchod bstod kyi bar gong bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:6304: gzungs thag blangs la rang gi thugs ka nas sngags
NK024(ya)001:6305: kyi phreng ba gzungs thag la brten nas song ba
NK024(ya)001:6308: sku'i cha las bdud rtsi'i rgyu babs pas bum pa
NK024(ya)001:6309: gang bar bsam zhing gong gi lha lnga'i snying po
NK024(ya)001:6310: brgya rtsa re bzlas mthar mchod bstod byas te dung
NK024(ya)001:6311: chos kyi chu phul bas lha rnams zhu bar bsam
NK024(ya)001:6312: mo // las bum bskyed chog 'dir gsal kha ma
NK024(ya)001:6313: byung yang phyag rdor dbang gi skabs bsgrubs pa des
NK024(ya)001:6314: 'thus par byed dam yang na gong bzhin 'dir yang
NK024(ya)001:6315: mo // bsgrub bo // mdun bskyed ni /
NK024(ya)001:6316: dkyil 'khor so so ltar sgrub mchod bya dgos zhes bla ma rnams gsungs bas /
NK024(ya)001:6317: thog mar rgyas pa dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa ltar bskyed pa'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:6318: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+hahsarba d+ha r+m+aahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:6319: dkyil 'khor rnams mi dmigs te stong par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6320: stong pa'i ngang las sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK024(ya)001:6321: gnas pa'i b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs las
NK024(ya)001:6322: grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa
NK024(ya)001:6323: / gtso bo'i kha dog can gyi rtsig pa nang du byas pa'i rim pa lnga pa /
NK024(ya)001:6325: rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pas kun nas mdzes pa /
NK024(ya)001:6326: mda' yab sngon po phyir 'phyang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:6327: pu shu dkar po pad+ma phyed pa'i dbyibs can gyen du langs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6328: nang ka ba brgyad dang ldan pa'i steng gdung gis
NK024(ya)001:6329: bteg pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa rdo rje dang
NK024(ya)001:6330: rin po che'i tog gis spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:6331: sgo bzhir ka ba bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs rim
NK024(ya)001:6332: pa bzhi la gnas pa'i bum pa bre chos kyi
NK024(ya)001:6333: 'khor gdugs dang tog gis spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:6334: phyi rol gyi 'dod snam la mchod pa'i lha mos bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:6335: khor yug tu sna tshogs pad+ma rdo rje'i ra ba
NK024(ya)001:6336: 'od zer gyi phreng ba kun na 'phro ba'i nang
NK024(ya)001:6340: byang ljang pa'i dkyil 'khor bcu gcig tu gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6341: rtsa bar lha lam 'khyer gyi dus lha rnams kyi mngon rtogs bshad cing sgrub mchod dpang skong dang /
NK024(ya)001:6342: thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa'i mdos chog gzhung gi go bcad pa zhig 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:6343: 'dir sgrub mchod gsar du sgrigs pas 'og gi lha lam 'khyer gyi mngon rtogs rnams 'dir blangs so //
NK024(ya)001:6344: dkyil 'khor dang po lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ri bo mchog rab /
NK024(ya)001:6349: gser ri rol mtsho bdun gyis bskor ba'i mtha' lcags
NK024(ya)001:6350: ri sngon pos bskor ba'i nang gi khyams rgya mtshor
NK024(ya)001:6351: gyur pa'i steng shar gling gsum zla gam dkar /
NK024(ya)001:6352: lho gling gsum sog kha sngo /
NK024(ya)001:6353: nub gling gsum zlum po dmar /
NK024(ya)001:6354: byang gling gsum gru bzhi ser /
NK024(ya)001:6355: ri rab kyi steng du pad+ma 'dab bzhi dbus dang shar dkar /
NK024(ya)001:6358: byang ljang ba'i lte bar zur lugs rtsa bar lha lam 'khyer skabs seng ge'i khri bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:6360: lha mi nyan rang khri gdan la //
NK024(ya)001:6361: seng ge mi 'os pad zlar bshad //
NK024(ya)001:6362: ces gsungs pas bla ma'i man ngag btsan bar byas te /
NK024(ya)001:6363: pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan la bcom ldan 'das kun
NK024(ya)001:6364: rig rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po byang
NK024(ya)001:6365: chub mchog gi phyag rgya can rdo rje'i skyil mo
NK024(ya)001:6366: krung gis bzhugs pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan
NK024(ya)001:6367: gyis brgyan pa'o // shar gling dbus mar brgya byin
NK024(ya)001:6368: dkar po g.yas rdo rje gdengs pa la g.yon nor
NK024(ya)001:6369: bu las mchod sbyin ster ba la /
NK024(ya)001:6370: dbang mo go bo rgyud mang bsnams pas g.yon nas brten pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6371: g.yas kyi gling du mngag gzhug pa 'gro ba'i yid 'ong ljang gu g.yas ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6372: g.yon gling du pho nya myur ba'i shugs can sngon po g.yas mdung rtse gsum pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6373: lho'i gling gi dbus su tshangs pa ser po g.yas spyi blugs 'dzin pa la /
NK024(ya)001:6374: tshangs ma gun+d+he 'dzin pas g.yon nas brten pa /
NK024(ya)001:6375: g.yas su mngag gzhug pa lta na sdug ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6376: g.yon na pho nya mgyogs byed dmar po pad dkar dang skar mda' 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6377: nub gling gi dbus su khyab 'jug sngo nag 'khor lo 'dzin pa la /
NK024(ya)001:6378: dpal lha mo gsal shing 'dzin pas g.yon nas brten pas /
NK024(ya)001:6379: g.yas su mngag gzhug pa rdo rje bde ba dkar mo mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6380: g.yon du pho nya rdo rje sde dpon ljang ser 'khor lo 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6381: byang gling gi dbus su dbang phyug chen po dmar po rtse gsum 'dzin pa la /
NK024(ya)001:6382: dkar bzlog ma pad+ma 'dzin pas g.yon nas brten pa /
NK024(ya)001:6383: g.yas su mngag gzhug pa ded dpon nag po mdung thung 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6384: g.yon du pho nya drang srong khros pa dmar po mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6385: thams cad kyang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6386: sgo bzhir yul 'khor bsrung dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6387: 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri gdengs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6388: spyan mi bzang dmar po sbrul zhags bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:6389: rnam thos sras ser po ne'u le 'dzin pa bzhi ka go mtshon dang ldan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6390: gzhan yang stong gsum bye ba phrag brgya'i rten dang brten pa thams cad kyang gsal bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6391: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa mi 'khrugs pa'i kyil 'khor gyi dbus sngon po pad+ma 'dab brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:6395: byang ljang ba'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la zhing
NK024(ya)001:6396: sbyong gi lha bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi 'khrugs
NK024(ya)001:6397: pa sngon po g.yas sa gnon g.yon mnyam bzhag gi
NK024(ya)001:6398: steng na rdo rje 'dzin pa sprul sku'i cha byad
NK024(ya)001:6399: can mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil krung gis
NK024(ya)001:6400: bzhugs pa'o //'dab ma bzhi la shar du rnam snang
NK024(ya)001:6401: dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:6402: lhor rin 'byung ser po mchog sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:6403: nub tu snang mtha' dmar po mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:6404: byang du don grub ljang gu skyabs sbyin mdzad pa sprul sku'i cha lugs can /
NK024(ya)001:6405: shar lhor spyan ma dkar mo spyan gyis mtshan pa'i 'khor lo //
NK024(ya)001:6406: lho nub tu m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:6407: nub byang du gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:6408: byang shar du sgrol ma ljang gu ut+pala 'dzin pa rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:6409: sgo bzhir lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6410: dkyil 'khor gsum pa gnam stong gi lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:6411: gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog lte ba
NK024(ya)001:6412: ser por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:6413: / gnam stong gi lha ston pa bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:6414: sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu
NK024(ya)001:6415: / g.yas sa gnon / g.yon mnyam gzhag gi steng
NK024(ya)001:6416: na lhung bzed bsod snyoms kyi zas kyis khengs shing
NK024(ya)001:6418: chos gos rnam pa gsum dang mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6419: dus bzang gi dkyil 'khor gsum gyi 'khor mi bskyod
NK024(ya)001:6420: pa sogs rigs bzhi'am sgeg sogs bzhi gang bder mdzad
NK024(ya)001:6421: pa las phyi ma legs pas /
NK024(ya)001:6422: shar gyi 'dab mar sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6423: lhor phreng ba sngon mo phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6424: nub tu klu ma dmar mo pi wang brdung ba /
NK024(ya)001:6425: byang du gar ma ljang gu gar pad bsgyur ba /
NK024(ya)001:6427: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa bco lnga'i lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:6428: dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog lte ba dmar
NK024(ya)001:6429: por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la nya'i
NK024(ya)001:6430: lha bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag tu med
NK024(ya)001:6431: pa sangs rgyas sna ba mtha' yas sku mdog pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:6432: r+aa ga'i lhun po ltar dmar ba'i phyag gnyis mnyam
NK024(ya)001:6433: gzhag gi steng na 'chi med tshe'i bum pa bsnams
NK024(ya)001:6434: pa / chos gos gsum dang mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6439: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6440: dkyil 'khor lnga pa tshes brgyad lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:6441: dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog lte ba sngon
NK024(ya)001:6442: por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la tshes
NK024(ya)001:6443: brgyad lha sangs rgyas sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od
NK024(ya)001:6444: kyi rgyal po sku mdog mthing kha g.yas pa mchog
NK024(ya)001:6445: sbyin gyi mthil na a ru ra /
NK024(ya)001:6446: g.yon mnyam gzhag gi steng na bdud rtsi'i lhung bzed
NK024(ya)001:6447: bsnams pa chos gos gsum dang mtshan dpes spras pa
NK024(ya)001:6448: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6449: phyogs bzhir sgeg phreng glu gar ma bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6450: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6451: dkyil 'khor drug pa 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:6452: 'khor gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte
NK024(ya)001:6453: ba ser por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan
NK024(ya)001:6454: la 'das pa'i sangs rgyas mar me mdzad gser mdog
NK024(ya)001:6455: don dam pa'i chos ston pas rten 'brel gyi phyag
NK024(ya)001:6456: rgya mdzad pa / chos gos gsum dang mtshan dpes
NK024(ya)001:6457: spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa
NK024(ya)001:6458: rgya mdzad pa / / phyogs kyi 'dab bzhir sgeg phreng glu gar ma /
NK024(ya)001:6459: mtshams bzhir shar lhor spos ma dud kha bdug spos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6460: lho nub tu push+pe ma dkar mo me tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6461: nub byang du mar me ma dmar skya mar me 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6462: byang shar du dri ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6463: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6464: dkyil 'khor bdun pa da ltar sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:6465: 'khor gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte
NK024(ya)001:6466: ba ser por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan
NK024(ya)001:6467: la da lta'i sangs rgyas ston pa mnyam med sh+aakya'i
NK024(ya)001:6468: rgyal po gser mdog can sa gnon mnyam gzhag gi
NK024(ya)001:6470: chos gos gsum dang mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6471: 'dab ma brgyad la phyogs bzhir sgeg phreng glu gar ma bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6472: mtshams bzhir spos me tog mar me dri chab 'dzin pa'i lha mo bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6473: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6474: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa ma 'ongs sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:6475: 'khor dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte ba
NK024(ya)001:6476: ser por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:6477: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas byams pa mgon po gser mdog
NK024(ya)001:6478: can gdul bya rjes su 'dzin pas mchog sbyin spyi
NK024(ya)001:6479: blugs can / chos gos dang mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6480: 'dab ma brgyad la phyogs bzhir sgeg sogs bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6481: mtshams bzhir spos ma sogs bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:6482: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6483: dkyil 'khor dgu pa sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:6484: dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte ba ser
NK024(ya)001:6485: por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la sangs
NK024(ya)001:6486: rgyas rnam par snang mdzad dkar po byang chub mchog
NK024(ya)001:6488: shar du mi bskyod pa sngon po mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:6489: lhor rin 'byung ser po mchog sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:6490: nub tu snang mtha' dmar po mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:6491: byang du don grub ljang gu skyabs sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:6492: mtshams bzhir spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo /
NK024(ya)001:6493: m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:6494: gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:6495: sgrol ma ljang gu ut+pala 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6496: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6497: dkyil 'khor bcu pa dam chos kyi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:6498: dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte ba ser
NK024(ya)001:6499: por gyur pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la dam
NK024(ya)001:6500: chos dkon mchog gi ngo bo yum chen mo shes
NK024(ya)001:6501: rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma gser mdog can
NK024(ya)001:6502: zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:6503: g.yas 'og ma chos 'chad dang g.yon 'og ma glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6504: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6505: pad 'dab brgyad la shar du sh+aaka thub ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:6506: lhor sgra dbyangs ser po mchog sbyin mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:6507: nub tu mya ngan med mchog dmar skya mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:6508: byang du mtshan legs ser po mi 'jigs sbyin dang mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:6509: byang shar du sman bla sngon po mchog sbyin gyis
NK024(ya)001:6510: a ru ra dang mnyam gzhag steng na lhung bzed
NK024(ya)001:6511: can / shar lhor gser bzang ser po chos 'chad can /
NK024(ya)001:6512: lho nub tu chos bsgrags dkar dmar chos 'chad can /
NK024(ya)001:6513: nub byang du mngon mkhyen dmar po mchog sbyin mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:6514: brgyad ka'ang chos gos sum ldan mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil krung can /
NK024(ya)001:6515: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6516: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa dge 'dun gyi dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:6517: gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon lte ba
NK024(ya)001:6518: ser por gyur pa'i dbus su thub dbang ser po
NK024(ya)001:6520: chos gos gsum dang mtshan dpes spras pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:6521: 'dab ma brgyad kyi phyogs bzhir byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun /
NK024(ya)001:6522: shar du spyan ras gzigs dkar po pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6523: lhor byams pa ser po klu shing gi me tog
NK024(ya)001:6524: sdong bu dang bcas pa ril pa sbyi blugs kyis
NK024(ya)001:6526: nub tu phyag rdor ljang gu g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6527: byang du 'jam dbyangs dmar ser glegs bam dang ral
NK024(ya)001:6528: gri 'dzin pa byang chub sems dpa'i cha lugs can
NK024(ya)001:6529: no // mtshams bzhir nyan thos kyi dge 'dun shar lhor sh+aa ri'i bu /
NK024(ya)001:6530: lho nub tu mood+gala gyi bu /
NK024(ya)001:6532: byang shar du kun dga' bo rnams nyan thos kyi cha lugs lhung bzed dang 'khar gsil 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:6533: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:6534: rgyas par na dkyil 'khor bcu gcig po 'di bzhin
NK024(ya)001:6535: yin mod kyang gal te 'bring po dkyil 'khor lnga
NK024(ya)001:6536: ma dang bdun ma gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:6537: 'bring po dkyil 'khor lnga ma ltar na rtsa ba'i
NK024(ya)001:6538: dkyil 'khor dang mi 'khrugs pa dus bzang gsum so
NK024(ya)001:6539: sor phral ba rnams mngon rtogs gong bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:6540: dus gsum sangs rgyas dang dkon mchog gsum de dag
NK024(ya)001:6541: la don gyis tshang bas med pa yin no //'bring
NK024(ya)001:6542: po dkyil 'khor bdun ma ltar na rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:6543: 'khor dang mi 'khrugs pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis dus bzang
NK024(ya)001:6544: gi dkyil 'khor gsum so sor kha phral te dkyil
NK024(ya)001:6545: 'khor lnga'i mngon rtogs rgyas pa ltar la /
NK024(ya)001:6546: drug pa dus gsum sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor bsdoms te lte dbus su thub dbang /
NK024(ya)001:6549: 'dab ma brgyad la sgeg sogs lha mo brgyad dang /
NK024(ya)001:6550: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi sogs gong ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:6551: bdun pa dkon mchog gsum gyi dkyil 'khor yang bsdoms te lte dbus su thub dbang /
NK024(ya)001:6552: mdun du yum chen mo gtso bo la zhal bstan
NK024(ya)001:6553: pa 'khor du theg pa che chung gi dge 'dun
NK024(ya)001:6554: sgom tshul gong ltar ro //'on kyang 'bring po'i lugs
NK024(ya)001:6555: gnyis rnam grangs tsam du bshad kyi /
NK024(ya)001:6556: gzhan du na rgyas pa'i tshe dkyil 'khor bcu gcig kho na 'thad cing /
NK024(ya)001:6557: de yang zur lugs rtsa bar dkyil 'khor de rnams
NK024(ya)001:6558: kyi grangs nges bshad tshul gong du dkyil 'khor bri
NK024(ya)001:6559: tshul 'chad skabs rtsa ba nas lung drangs pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:6560: yin la / 'khor rnams kyi nges pa ni zur lugs rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:6561: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:6562: zhes pa tsam las ma gsungs kyang zur lugs kyi yi ge rnying pa dag las btus shing /
NK024(ya)001:6563: mngon rtogs rnams gsal bar bris pa yin pas rang
NK024(ya)001:6564: gzhung dang mi 'gal zhing shin tu 'thad par yod
NK024(ya)001:6565: / de tsam ma lcogs na dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis
NK024(ya)001:6566: su grangs nges pa'i tshe gcig dril gyi dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:6567: ram drug du byed pa'i tshe drug pa /
NK024(ya)001:6568: shin tu bsdus na dkyil 'khor gcig po 'di kho
NK024(ya)001:6569: nar tshang ba zur dang kahthoga gnyis ka bzhed pa
NK024(ya)001:6570: de nyid sgom pa'i tshul ni rten gzhal yas khang
NK024(ya)001:6572: 'on kyang dkyil 'khor bcu gcig tu gyur zer ba la /
NK024(ya)001:6574: dkyil 'khor dang po lha mi'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su zhes pa la /
NK024(ya)001:6575: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su ri bo
NK024(ya)001:6576: mchog rab ces pa nas gtso bo bskyed pa'i bar
NK024(ya)001:6577: gong gi rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:6578: 'dab bzhi'i shar du bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi 'khrugs pa sngon po zhes sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:6579: lhor bcom ldan 'das sman gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po zhes sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:6580: nub tu bcom ldan 'das mgon po tshe dpag tu med pa snang ba mtha' yas zhes sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:6581: byang du ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa zhes sogs kyis mi 'khrugs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6582: dus bzang gsum gyi gtso bo'i mngon rtogs rnams len /
NK024(ya)001:6583: shar gling dbus mar brgya byin dkar po zhes pa
NK024(ya)001:6584: man chad rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang po ltar ro
NK024(ya)001:6585: // de ltar na lag len du spro na rgyas pa dkyil 'khor bcu gcig dang /
NK024(ya)001:6586: bsdu na 'di kho na bzhin nges par bya dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:6587: lha tshogs de rnams kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:6589: thus kar h+aum sngon pos mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6590: rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:6591: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes snyan gsan phab la rdo rje dril bu 'dzin pas /
NK024(ya)001:6592: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:6593: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK024(ya)001:6594: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:6595: bcom ldan 'khor bcas 'dir ni shegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6596: bcom ldan bskal pa grangs med du ma rung //'gro la brtse phyir thugs rje rnam sbyangs shing //
NK024(ya)001:6597: smon lam rgya chen dgongs pa yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:6598: khyod bzhed 'gro don mdzad dus 'di lags na //
NK024(ya)001:6599: de phyir chos dbyings pho brang lhun grub nas //
NK024(ya)001:6600: rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs sna tshogs ston mdzad cing //
NK024(ya)001:6601: mtha' yas sems can tshogs rnams bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:6602: yongs dag 'khor dang bcas rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6603: chos rnams kun gyi dbang phyug gtso //
NK024(ya)001:6604: btso ma gser gyi mdog 'dra zhing //
NK024(ya)001:6605: nyi ma las lhag gzi brjid che //
NK024(ya)001:6606: dad pas spyan ni drang bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:6607: zhi zhing thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:6608: dul zhing bsam gtan sa la bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:6609: chos dang ye shes chags bral ba //
NK024(ya)001:6610: kun tu mi zad nus par ldan //
NK024(ya)001:6611: tshul spyon tshur spyon zhi bdag lha //
NK024(ya)001:6612: thub pa skyes mchog thams cad mkhyen //
NK024(ya)001:6613: shin tu legs byas gzugs brnyan ni //
NK024(ya)001:6614: mchod pa'i 'dir ni gshegs su gsol //'dir ni gzugs
NK024(ya)001:6615: dang lhan cig tu //'gro ba'i don du bzhugs nas
NK024(ya)001:6616: kyang // nad med tshe dang dbang phyug dang //
NK024(ya)001:6617: mchog rnams legs par stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6618: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes nam mkhar spyan drangs te bzhugs pa la /
NK024(ya)001:6619: bcom ldan 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:6620: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK024(ya)001:6621: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:6622: thugs la dgongs shing gnang bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:6623: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:6624: tshur gshegs 'dir ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6625: bdag la mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6626: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ga ga na sa ma ya h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:6627: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+ri ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:6628: zhes mchod yon dang sku khrus phul /
NK024(ya)001:6629: pad+ma ka ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:6638: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:6641: zhes so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas mdun bskyed kyi rten la ye shes pa bcug go //
NK024(ya)001:6642: dpang skong phyag rgya pas cho ga gzhung bsrang bar
NK024(ya)001:6643: gzhung las gsungs phyin skabs 'dir phyag 'tshal ba'i don
NK024(ya)001:6645: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:6647: bdag nyid myur du mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK024(ya)001:6649: mchod pa 'bul ba la byin rlabs gong du song bas 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:6650: spos mar me rnams spar zhing thal mo sbyar nas /
NK024(ya)001:6651: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK024(ya)001:6652: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:6653: bdag gis gus par bshams pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:6654: ji snyed rgyal ba sras dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:6655: de snyed rnams la bdag 'bul na //
NK024(ya)001:6656: thugs rje mnga' ba khyod rnams kyis //
NK024(ya)001:6657: ci bde bar ni bzhes nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:6658: sems can don kun mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:6659: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza
NK024(ya)001:6660: me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma
NK024(ya)001:6661: ye h+aum / gar skor sngon du 'gro bas so
NK024(ya)001:6662: so'i phyag rgya bcas pa'i mthar se gol gtogs pa
NK024(ya)001:6663: 'di man chod kyi mchod phreng kun la rigs 'agre'o
NK024(ya)001:6664: ye h+aum / // rab 'byams me tog bdag gis
NK024(ya)001:6665: ji snyed de snyed thugs rje ci bde sems can
NK024(ya)001:6666: sarba ta th+aa ga ta push+pe rab 'byams bdug spos
NK024(ya)001:6667: ye h+aum / // sogs / sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+h+au pe rab 'byams snang gsal sogs /
NK024(ya)001:6668: sarba ta th+aa ga ta +aa lo ke rab 'byams dri chab sogs /
NK024(ya)001:6669: sarba ta th+aa ga ta gan+d+he rab 'byams zhal zas sogs /
NK024(ya)001:6670: sarba ta th+aa ga ta nee wi d+ya rab 'byams
NK024(ya)001:6671: rol mo bdag gis ji snyed de snyed thugs rje
NK024(ya)001:6672: ci bde sems can sarba ta th+aa ga ta shap+da
NK024(ya)001:6673: p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na
NK024(ya)001:6676: d+harma ra ni ta sogs dril bu rgyun chags su dkrol zhing dbul lo //
NK024(ya)001:6677: rgyas par spro na rin chen sna bdun dang 'dod
NK024(ya)001:6678: yon drug sogs 'og nas 'byung ba'i dkyil chog rnams
NK024(ya)001:6681: dang po rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor /
NK024(ya)001:6682: chos dbyings ye shes rnam par dag /
NK024(ya)001:6683: ces pa'i sh+lo ka gcig dang /
NK024(ya)001:6685: thub dbang la rnam dag sku mnga'/
NK024(ya)001:6686: sman blar thugs rje kun la snyoms mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:6687: 'od dpag med la 'dod chags rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:6689: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas mar me mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:6690: ma byon sangs rgyas byams pa mgon //
NK024(ya)001:6691: da lta'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub //
NK024(ya)001:6692: dus gsum sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:6694: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:6695: thams cad mkhyen pa ston pa po //
NK024(ya)001:6696: bsod nams yon tan rgya mtsho'i zhing //
NK024(ya)001:6697: de bzhin gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:6698: dag pa 'dod chags bral ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:6699: dge bas ngan song las grol zhing //
NK024(ya)001:6700: gcig tu don dam mchog gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:6701: zhi gyur chos la grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK024(ya)001:6702: bslab pa dag la rab tu gus //
NK024(ya)001:6703: zhing gi dam pa yon tan zhing //
NK024(ya)001:6704: dge 'dun la yang zhes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6705: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK024(ya)001:6707: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK024(ya)001:6709: grwa yi phyogs ni kun tu yang //
NK024(ya)001:6710: rigs kyi yum bzhi'i skur bstan pa //
NK024(ya)001:6711: lha mo spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK024(ya)001:6712: dkar mo sgrol ma khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:6714: mtshan legs rin chen dpal dang gser bzang dang //
NK024(ya)001:6715: mya ngan med mchog chos bsgrags mngon mkhyen dang //
NK024(ya)001:6716: sman gyi bla dang sh+aakya'i rgyal po sogs //
NK024(ya)001:6717: bde bar gshegs pa brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:6719: sgeg mo phreng ba de bzhin glu //
NK024(ya)001:6720: gar ma mchod pa'i lha mo dang //
NK024(ya)001:6721: spos ma me tog mar me ma //
NK024(ya)001:6722: dri yi lha mo khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:6723: sgo bzhi'i dbus su legs bzhugs shing //
NK024(ya)001:6724: dad sogs ngo bo rnam dag pa //
NK024(ya)001:6725: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril //
NK024(ya)001:6726: sgo srung rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:6728: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:6730: mdun bskyed kyi bzlas pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:6735: snang ba mtha' yas la pad+ma a mi de wa /
NK024(ya)001:6736: mar me mdzad dang byams pa la sh+aakya ma sbyar ba'i mu ne /
NK024(ya)001:6737: yum chen mor shes rab snying po'i sngags rnams cung zad bzla zhing dkyil 'khor rnams gsal btab /
NK024(ya)001:6738: slar yang sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham p+aa d+yam zhes sogs kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:6739: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:6741: cho ga gzhung du thar pa chen po'i mdo bklag par gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:6742: slob dpon gyis 'don par nus na skabs 'dir 'don /
NK024(ya)001:6743: de yang mdo 'di rgya nag 'gyur du 'dug pas rgya gar skad med la /
NK024(ya)001:6745: 'phags pa thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa 'gyod tshangs kyi sdig sbyangs te /
NK024(ya)001:6746: sangs rgyas su bsgrub pa rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
NK024(ya)001:6747: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la
NK024(ya)001:6748: phyag 'tshal lo //'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus
NK024(ya)001:6749: gcig na bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab kyi grong
NK024(ya)001:6751: zhes pa nas rdzogs byang gi bar shog bu drug
NK024(ya)001:6752: cu re 'dren tsam yod pa de nyid ma tshang
NK024(ya)001:6753: ba med par bklag /'don par ma nus na 'og
NK024(ya)001:6754: tu slob ma 'dus ma thag chos bkram ste 'ur
NK024(ya)001:6755: 'don du bklag / bsdoms tshig tu drug pa cha
NK024(ya)001:6756: gsum dgos par gsungs pa bzhin 'dir babs pas kha
NK024(ya)001:6757: sang gi cha gsum dkyil 'khor bsdus ma tshar na
NK024(ya)001:6758: mchod gtor bsham ste byin rlabs gong ltar byas te
NK024(ya)001:6760: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK024(ya)001:6761: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:6763: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor 'das gtor 'bul ba sngon
NK024(ya)001:6764: du 'gro bas bgegs skrod kyi sum+b+ha'i bar bya zhing
NK024(ya)001:6766: dkyil 'khor bsdus zin na 'das gtor mi 'bul zhing
NK024(ya)001:6767: cha dang po'i mchod gtor brlab pa nas bzung gzhung
NK024(ya)001:6768: bzhin btang ngo // des sa bcad lnga pa dang drug pa song nas /
NK024(ya)001:6769: bdun pa khrus yin 'dug na'ang gab 'khrugs yin phyir /
NK024(ya)001:6770: bco brgyad pa bdag 'jug dang bcu dgu pa rin chen 'dir blang dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:6772: bco brgyad pa bdag 'jug ni sngar dbang thob pa'i bla ma la yid kyis blangs /
NK024(ya)001:6773: bsnyen gnas sngar blangs dus la blangs kyang bskyar ma ma bskyar yang skye /
NK024(ya)001:6776: ngang sgom dang lam 'khyer yang bskyar ma bzang du 'agro'o //
NK024(ya)001:6777: zhes gsungs pa'i don bdag 'jug blang dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:6779: rdo rje slob dpon khyim pa yin na bsnyen gnas
NK024(ya)001:6780: sam gso sbyong gi ming 'dogs shing lha mi'i theg
NK024(ya)001:6781: pa nas bshad pa'i dus khrims bsnyen gnas yan lag
NK024(ya)001:6783: sum ldan la theg pa chen po'i gso sbyong gi
NK024(ya)001:6784: ming 'dogs shing cho ga nyan thos kyi skabs na
NK024(ya)001:6785: yod pa de yin pas gsar ma'i don zhags nas
NK024(ya)001:6788: theg chen gso sbyong gi cho ga nyan thos kyi skabs na yod pa mi rigs pa min te /
NK024(ya)001:6790: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:6791: cho ga nyan thos lugs bzhin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:6793: 'di la pan chen gser mdog can pas dge slong
NK024(ya)001:6794: gis theg pa chen po'i gso sbyong blang du mi
NK024(ya)001:6795: rung ba'i rigs pa phra mo gtong bar mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:6796: / kun mkhyen bsod nams seng ge'i lung rigs kyis
NK024(ya)001:6797: tshar bcad pa ltar 'dir yang don la gnas shing
NK024(ya)001:6798: bla mas gong du blangs zin pa des khyab /
NK024(ya)001:6799: 'jug sgo ni chos spyod bcu yin par lam 'khyer
NK024(ya)001:6800: las bshad pas rtag par nyams su blang byar 'dug
NK024(ya)001:6801: / ngang sgom ni spyir thos bsam gyis dpyad de
NK024(ya)001:6802: rgyud la ngo 'phrod par yod pas khyab mod kyang
NK024(ya)001:6803: lam 'dir so sor ngang sgom bshad pa ltar bla
NK024(ya)001:6805: lam 'khyer bzhi la theg pa lta ba bsrung bya
NK024(ya)001:6806: sgom pa bzhi yin pa 'og tu rgyas par 'chad
NK024(ya)001:6807: / lha sngags lam 'khyer ni sgrub mchod skabs rgyas par bstan zin to //
NK024(ya)001:6808: bdag 'jug blang ba ni las bum gyi chus khrus
NK024(ya)001:6809: bya zhing man+dala gsol btab nas bzung slob ma la
NK024(ya)001:6810: ji ltar dbang bskur ba bzhin tshang mar blangs /
NK024(ya)001:6811: gso sbyong cho ga'i sngon du blangs zin pas bdag 'jug skabs len mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:6813: bcu dgu pa rin chen ni /
NK024(ya)001:6814: bdag sh+aakya thub pa'i nga rgyal byas te snang srid
NK024(ya)001:6815: kyi bcud thams cad bsdus la bdag gi spyi bor
NK024(ya)001:6816: bstim pas rin po che 'bar bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:6818: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dkon mchog mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyi 'od zer rang la bstim /
NK024(ya)001:6819: lha la rjes su gnang ba zhu /
NK024(ya)001:6821: sems can gyi dgos 'dod thams cad skong ba'i yi
NK024(ya)001:6822: ge'i rnam par rang la thim pas chos thams cad
NK024(ya)001:6823: rang lugs lhun grub tu 'byung ba de bzhin gshegs
NK024(ya)001:6824: pa rnams kyis byin gyis brlab par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:6826: kahthoga lugs su sgyu 'phrul ltar rig pa'i me tog
NK024(ya)001:6827: dor ba sogs mdzad 'dug pas mdo sgyu sems sogs
NK024(ya)001:6828: theg pa gong 'og thams cad kyi lha sta gon
NK024(ya)001:6829: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor yod pas mi 'gal mod /
NK024(ya)001:6830: 'dir ni de bzhin byed pa gzhung las kyang ma gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:6831: dkyil 'khor de rnams da lta med pas skabs su
NK024(ya)001:6832: ma babs phyir de'i dod du sa bcad bcu dgu
NK024(ya)001:6833: pa 'di kho nas 'thus par sems shing /
NK024(ya)001:6834: de yang rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu gnyis pa las
NK024(ya)001:6835: kyang thub pa sgom par gsungs pa bzhin bdag 'jug
NK024(ya)001:6836: grub nas rang thub pa'i nga rgyal bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:6837: de las 'od zer 'phros snang srid kyi bcud thams
NK024(ya)001:6838: cad bsdus bdag gi spyi bor bstim pas dbang rtags
NK024(ya)001:6839: rin po che 'bar bas gtsug tor gyi rtser mtshan
NK024(ya)001:6841: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad la mchod pa phul /
NK024(ya)001:6842: tshur 'dus byin rlabs thams cad 'od kyi rnam par
NK024(ya)001:6843: rang la thim pas slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:6846: sems can gyi dgos 'dod thams cad skong bar byas /
NK024(ya)001:6847: tshur 'dus 'od zer rgya bod kyi yi ge'i rnam
NK024(ya)001:6848: par rang la thim par bsam la gnas lugs kyi
NK024(ya)001:6849: ngang du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:6850: de yan chad slob dpon gyi bya ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:6851: slob ma'i bya ba ni sa bcad bdun pa nas
NK024(ya)001:6852: brtsams te yin pas slob ma rnams bos te gral
NK024(ya)001:6854: drug pa khrus ni bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus byas la gos gsar pa gyon par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:6855: zhes gsungs pa yi ge nor ba'i skyon gyis sa
NK024(ya)001:6856: bcad bdun pa chad 'dug cing sdoms kyi dbang du
NK024(ya)001:6857: byas na drug pa cha gsum dang bdun pa khrus
NK024(ya)001:6859: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:6860: zhes sogs sngags dang bcas te las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:6861: 'dir mi gsal yang spyi khyab tu bgegs gtor mdzad srol 'dug pas bgegs gtor bsham /
NK024(ya)001:6862: bla ma las kyi lha gang yin gyi nga rgyal
NK024(ya)001:6863: gyis gtor ma bsang sbyang byin brlab sngags bsngosa bden
NK024(ya)001:6864: brdar bka' bsgo sogs phyag rdor dbang gi skabs bzhin
NK024(ya)001:6865: la / phyag rdor gyi tshab tu khyad par du
NK024(ya)001:6866: yang 'jin rten lha mi'i theg pa'i dkyil 'khor lha
NK024(ya)001:6867: tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK024(ya)001:6869: bka' bsgo'i tshig rkang dang po /
NK024(ya)001:6872: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu tshar rjes /
NK024(ya)001:6873: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:6874: don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK024(ya)001:6875: par bya / de'i ched du 'dir 'dus pa chen
NK024(ya)001:6876: po'i dkyil 'khor du smin byed kyi dbang bskur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:6877: dang po yan lag gi dkyil 'khor las 'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:6878: lha mi'i theg pa'i sgor zhugs shing /
NK024(ya)001:6879: lam de'i smin grol rnams tshul bzhin du nyan te
NK024(ya)001:6880: sems can gyi don bgyid snyam pa byang chub kyi
NK024(ya)001:6881: mchog tu sems bskyed pa sngon du btang ste gsan
NK024(ya)001:6882: 'tshal / zhes thugs bskyed phog cing chos nyan par
NK024(ya)001:6883: gdams pa sogs spyi bshad rgyas bsdus skabs sbyar bgyis
NK024(ya)001:6884: 'tshal / pa'i mthar / 'dir theg pa'i khyad par
NK024(ya)001:6885: ni slob dpon chen po dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:6887: chen bi ma la mi tra'i bzhed par mngon par
NK024(ya)001:6889: nges par legs pa'i theg pa gnyis su gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:6890: dang po mngon mtho'i theg pa ni lha mi'i theg pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:6892: dge bcu sgrub cing mi dge spong byed pa //'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:6893: zhes gsungs pas mi dge bcu spong zhing dge bcu sgrub pa rgyu dang lam /
NK024(ya)001:6894: lha mi'i go 'phang ni 'bras bu yin /
NK024(ya)001:6895: de yang spyod ba sdus las /
NK024(ya)001:6896: sems can dang po'i las can rnams //
NK024(ya)001:6897: dam pa'i don la 'jug pa la //
NK024(ya)001:6898: thabs 'di rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK024(ya)001:6899: skas kyi rim pa lta bur gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:6900: zhes gsungs pa'i skas gdang 'og ma dang chos mtshungs pa lha mi'i theg pa yin cing /
NK024(ya)001:6901: de'i lam gyi 'jug sgo bsnyen gnas sam rnying ma rang skad la dus khrims dang /
NK024(ya)001:6902: gtan khrims kyi gso sbyong sbyin pa sogs kyi sgo nas bslab dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:6904: dang por gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:6906: de yang thog mar rtsa ba'i sdoms tshig don sum
NK024(ya)001:6907: cus bstan pa'i sa bcad drug pa cha gsum yan
NK024(ya)001:6908: chad la bcu bdun pa bsnan cing /
NK024(ya)001:6909: 'og nas sa bcad bco brgyad pa bdag 'jug dang
NK024(ya)001:6910: bcu dgu pa rin chen gnyis kyang blangs te khyon
NK024(ya)001:6911: sdoms don dgu ni slob dpon kho na'i bya bar
NK024(ya)001:6912: 'dug pas gong du lhag chad med tsam du grub
NK024(ya)001:6913: pa yin / slob ma'i bya ba la don tshan bdun pa khrus nas ston par byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6914: bgegs bskrad gzhung nas mi gsal yang /
NK024(ya)001:6915: glan ban bsod nams mgon pos /
NK024(ya)001:6916: lha'i nga rgyal gyis bgegs bskrad ces gsungs pas khrus dang bgegs skrod gnyis grub pa der gda'/
NK024(ya)001:6918: brgyad pa sdom rten la gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:6919: mdo dbang thos pa'i shes rab la dbang bskur byed du gzhug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6920: bsam pa'i shes rab la bshad par byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6921: sgom pa'i shes rab la khrid du byed pa dang gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:6922: dbang bskur mjug chog dang bcas pa tsakli'i yin /
NK024(ya)001:6924: skabs 'dir phyag rten gang yod ngan song las nges par 'byung ba'i blos 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:6925: zhes gsungs pa'i don sdom rten gyi gzhi 'am rgyu
NK024(ya)001:6926: slob ma'i thos bsam sgom gsum gyi shes rab yin
NK024(ya)001:6927: la / de yang thos pa'i shes rab la dbang bskur te smin par byas /
NK024(ya)001:6928: bsam pa'i shes rab la bshad pa byas te gtan la phab /
NK024(ya)001:6929: sgom pa'i shes rab la ngang sgom dang lam 'khyer
NK024(ya)001:6930: gyi khrid bskyang ba dang gsum yin pas der shes
NK024(ya)001:6931: dgos / sdom pa zhu ba'i rten nam phyag rten
NK024(ya)001:6932: ni 'dir phyag rten gang yod nges 'byung gi blos
NK024(ya)001:6934: glan ston gyis kyang sdom rten ci rigs pa bla ma la 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:6935: zhes gsungs pas phyag rten ci rigs kyang phul grub cing /
NK024(ya)001:6936: khyad par man+dala 'bul ba ni theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi khyad chos yin /
NK024(ya)001:6939: bla ma 'jig rten skyong ba de sems can la
NK024(ya)001:6940: brtse bas zhing khams la dbang sgyur ba'i phyir slob
NK024(ya)001:6941: mas brtsig go // zhes gsungs pa spyir theg dman
NK024(ya)001:6942: la khri stan che mtho sogs spang byar gsungs kyang
NK024(ya)001:6943: chos smra ba po la bkur sti chen pos khri
NK024(ya)001:6944: stan bsham pa theg pa che chung thams cad la
NK024(ya)001:6945: mas brtsig go // bshad cing / slob mas bla
NK024(ya)001:6946: ma la bkur sti bya ba'i phyir chos ston pa'i
NK024(ya)001:6949: bcu pa rgyan ni zhing khams la dbang mdzad pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:6950: mnga' gsol ba'i phyir rgyan mdzes shing brjid par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:6951: zhes gsungs pas bla ma rab tu byung ba yin
NK024(ya)001:6952: na dri ma med pa'i chos gos rnam pa gsum
NK024(ya)001:6954: dge bsnyen nam rig sngags 'chang ba'i rten can yin
NK024(ya)001:6955: kyang rang rang gi rgyan gos phun sum tshogs pas
NK024(ya)001:6958: bcu gcig pa khrir 'dzeg pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:6959: lhas gnang bar bsam la lus skyil krung dang tshugs thub par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:6960: zhes gsungs pa ni dkon mchog gsum gyi gnang ba thob pa'i blo dang /
NK024(ya)001:6961: gzhan yang dkon mchog la gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:6962: bdud tshar bcad cing 'khor la byams pas khyab par bya ba la sogs bya dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:6963: dam pa'i chos pad+ma dkar po las /
NK024(ya)001:6964: gtsang zhing yid du 'ong ba'i sa phyogs su //
NK024(ya)001:6965: yangs pa'i stan ni rab tu bshams bting ste //
NK024(ya)001:6966: bzang po'i tshon gyis legs par kha bsgyur ba //
NK024(ya)001:6967: chos gos gtsang ma de ni rab bgos nas //
NK024(ya)001:6968: rdul gzan nag po de bzhin bshams byas nas //
NK024(ya)001:6969: sham thabs che tshad legs par rab bgos nas //
NK024(ya)001:6970: bcos bu'i ras rnams sna tshogs legs bting ba //
NK024(ya)001:6971: rkang rten bcas pa'i khri la rab 'dug cing //
NK024(ya)001:6972: rkang pa legs par bkrus te stegs 'dzegs nas //
NK024(ya)001:6973: gdong dang bzhin gyi mdangs ni rab snum zhing //
NK024(ya)001:6974: chos kyi bstan de la ni rab 'dug nas //
NK024(ya)001:6975: sems can lhags pa rtse gcig gyur rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:6976: gtam mang rnam pa sna tshogs nye bar ston //
NK024(ya)001:6977: dge slong dag dang dge slong ma rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:6978: dge bsnyen rnams dang dge bsnyen ma dag dang //
NK024(ya)001:6979: rgyal po dag dang rgyal bu rnams la yang //
NK024(ya)001:6980: mkhas des rtag tu phrag dog med par ni //
NK024(ya)001:6981: sna tshogs don ldan snyan pa'i gtam yang ston //
NK024(ya)001:6982: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:6983: blo gros rgya mtshos zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:6985: sha ma sha ma ba ti /
NK024(ya)001:6996: m+aa la p+aa na ye khu khu re /
NK024(ya)001:7002: a mu khi sha mi ta ni /
NK024(ya)001:7003: sarba gra h+aa ban+d+ha n+aa ni /
NK024(ya)001:7005: sarba pa ra pra bir+d+ha na /
NK024(ya)001:7006: bi mug ta m+aa ra p+aa sha s+tha pa ta /
NK024(ya)001:7009: sarba m+aa ree su tsa ri ta p+aa da pa ri shud+d+h+ya bi gats+tshan+tu sarba m+aa ra karma ni /
NK024(ya)001:7010: sngags 'di bu ston chos 'byung du 'dug pa mdo
NK024(ya)001:7011: dngos dang cung zad ma mthun pas 'dir mdo rang
NK024(ya)001:7012: nas btus so // phan yon ni de nyid las /
NK024(ya)001:7013: sngags kyi tshig 'di dag sngon du byas te chos
NK024(ya)001:7014: kyi gtam byed na de'i khor yug dpag tshad brgyad
NK024(ya)001:7015: tshun chad du bdud dang bdud kyi rigs kyi lha
NK024(ya)001:7016: rnams mig gis mi rtsol bar bya ba'i las kyi
NK024(ya)001:7018: gang dag 'ong ba de dag kyang bar chad byed par mi nus so //
NK024(ya)001:7019: zhes gsungs pas khrir 'dzeg pa'i 'phros las gdams ngag zab mo 'di rnams kyang nges par bya dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7021: bcu gnyis pa thub pa sgom pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:7022: dge bcu 'khor los sgyur ba rgyal po'i khrims yin /
NK024(ya)001:7023: de'ang bstan pa dang lha mi'i gtso bo ston pa sangs rgyas yin /
NK024(ya)001:7024: de la lha mi'i 'khor bzhi yod pas de bsgoms nas bsnyen gnas sogs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:7025: zhes gsungs pa'i don chos kyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal khrims dge bcu sgrub dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:7026: de yang thub pa'i bstan pa dang ston pa yin
NK024(ya)001:7027: pas da ltar gyi chos ston pa'i bla ma la
NK024(ya)001:7028: tha mal par mi blta bar ston pa thub pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7029: dbang po la 'khor rnam pa bzhis bskor ba dngos
NK024(ya)001:7030: yin snyam pa'i mos gus bgyid dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:7031: bla mas kyang thub pa'i ting nge 'dzin brtan po dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:7033: dgra bcom pa sa ga'i lhas /
NK024(ya)001:7034: ston pa dang ni dge bdun bcas //'jig rten gsum snang khyab bdag yin //
NK024(ya)001:7036: de yang 'jig rten lha mi'i theg pa'i skabs 'dir
NK024(ya)001:7037: bsnyen gnas dang bslab bya tsam 'thad cing dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:7038: bar mi rigs so zhes log par rtog pa yod
NK024(ya)001:7039: srid kyang / 'dir ni gtso bo rdo rje theg
NK024(ya)001:7040: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga dang 'brel bar dbang
NK024(ya)001:7041: srid kyang / bskur zhing / de'i 'jug sgor 'jig
NK024(ya)001:7042: rten pa rnams dge bcu'i lam las rim gyis drangs
NK024(ya)001:7043: te rdzogs chen a ti yo ga'i bar du 'khrid
NK024(ya)001:7044: par byed pa'i phyir thabs sam /
NK024(ya)001:7045: rgyu rkyen du lam mas 'dzeg gis ston par byed pa'i thabs zab mo yin /
NK024(ya)001:7046: de bzhin du dkyil 'khor gyi lha rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:7047: 'khor gyi gtso bo dang yum chen mo tsam ma
NK024(ya)001:7048: gtogs gzhan phal cher gyi gtso bo sprul sku lta
NK024(ya)001:7049: bu mang bar yod pa la log par smra na
NK024(ya)001:7051: gsar ma la yang bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i
NK024(ya)001:7052: dkyil 'khor la bskal bzang gi sangs rgyas stong sprul
NK024(ya)001:7053: sku'i cha byad du bzhugs par bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:7055: byams pa mgon po zhal gsum phyag bzhi pa'i rjes
NK024(ya)001:7056: gnang sogs bshad pa de dag dang chos mtshungs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7057: phyir ro // mdor na 'jig rten dang mthun pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:7058: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dkyil 'khor bcu sogs la
NK024(ya)001:7059: sngags lugs dang 'brel ba'i sgrub mchod smin rgyas su
NK024(ya)001:7060: grub pas / 'dir slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal
NK024(ya)001:7061: du gyur pa bla ma dang ston pa thub pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7062: dbang po tha mi dad pa la 'jig rten lha
NK024(ya)001:7063: mi'i dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba zhu
NK024(ya)001:7065: bcu gsum pa gsol ba gdab pa'i slad du snyim
NK024(ya)001:7066: pa me tog dang bcas te thal mo sbyar te
NK024(ya)001:7068: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK024(ya)001:7069: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnam sbyong ba //
NK024(ya)001:7070: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen mchog /
NK024(ya)001:7071: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin gsol //
NK024(ya)001:7073: rtsa bar zhes me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:7074: mtho ris kyi legs smon dang /
NK024(ya)001:7076: zhes gsungs pa'i don 'dir 'jig rten pa rnams tshe
NK024(ya)001:7077: 'di'i bde 'bras kho na don du gnyer ba yin
NK024(ya)001:7078: pas de lta bu'i blo spangs de mi dge ba'i
NK024(ya)001:7079: rgyu las byung ba'i ngan 'gro'i g.yang sa bzod par
NK024(ya)001:7080: dka' ba'i me dong lta bu'i nang nas thar pa
NK024(ya)001:7081: la nges par 'byung 'dod kyi blo dang /
NK024(ya)001:7082: mtho ris legs smon gyi rgyu dge bcu spyad pa'i 'bras bu lha dang /
NK024(ya)001:7083: khyad par mya ngan las 'das pa sgrub snyam pa'i smon sems dung ba bskyed mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7085: bcu bzhi pa sdom pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:7086: skyabs 'gro dpang por gsol nas sdom pa'i tshul khrims ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:7089: bco lnga pa dus khrims bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7090: bcu drug pa de lta bu'i sdom pa 'bogs pa'i cho ga dang gsum gyis gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:7091: de yang cho ga 'khrugs sdebs ma byas pas go
NK024(ya)001:7092: dka' ba dang cho ga ma tshang ba sogs legs
NK024(ya)001:7093: par bcos te 'chad par bya ba la /
NK024(ya)001:7095: bco lnga pa dus khrims ni nya stong tshes brgyad de /
NK024(ya)001:7096: de'ang sku gsung thugs kyi rten bkram /
NK024(ya)001:7099: tsog pur 'dug la ngan song las thar ba'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:7100: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du lha mi'i theg pa la
NK024(ya)001:7102: zhes gsungs pas dang po gtan khrims ni rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu bzhi pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:7103: slob ma rnams mchil lham phud /
NK024(ya)001:7104: khrus byas te sdom rten ston pa'i sku dang rang
NK024(ya)001:7105: la phyag gsum gsum 'tshal zhing tsog pur 'dug tu
NK024(ya)001:7108: de yang shes rab brgya pa las /
NK024(ya)001:7109: mi yi chos lugs legs spyad na //
NK024(ya)001:7110: lha yul 'grod pa thag mi ring //
NK024(ya)001:7111: lha dang mi yi them skas la //'dzegs na thar pa gam na 'dug /
NK024(ya)001:7112: ces gsungs pa ltar lha mi'i theg pa 'dir 'jug
NK024(ya)001:7113: sgo bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa zhig len dgos la
NK024(ya)001:7114: / de yang khyad par cung zad phye na /
NK024(ya)001:7116: bsnyen gnas so so thar pa'i lugs //
NK024(ya)001:7117: gtso cher nyan thos gzhung lugs yin //
NK024(ya)001:7118: zhes gsungs pa'i nyan thos lugs la yang bye brag tu smra ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7119: mdo sde pa'i lugs gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:7121: bye brag smra ba'i bsnyen gnas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7122: dge slong las len gang zag ni //
NK024(ya)001:7123: gling gsum skyes pa bud med las //'gro ba gzhan la sdom pa bkag /
NK024(ya)001:7124: ces gsungs pas na len yul yang dge slong zhig la nges par len /
NK024(ya)001:7125: rten yang sgra mi snyan pa ma yin pa'i gling gsum du skyes pa'i skyes pa bud med de /
NK024(ya)001:7127: za ma ma ning sgra mi snyan //
NK024(ya)001:7128: mtshan gnyis ma gtogs mi rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:7129: sdom min sdom pa'ang de bzhin la //
NK024(ya)001:7133: mdo sde pa rnams dud 'gro sogs //'gro ba gzhan la'ang skye bar bshad //
NK024(ya)001:7134: blang ba'i yul yang dge bsnyen sogs //
NK024(ya)001:7135: gang yang rung las blang bar bshad //
NK024(ya)001:7136: ces gsungs pas mdo sde pa'i lugs su len yul yang dge slong kho na mi dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7137: gnas 'jog gis zhus pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:7140: rab tu byung ba cho ga shes pa zhig gi gam du song ste /
NK024(ya)001:7143: khyim bdag mgon med zas sbyin gyis rang gi 'khor
NK024(ya)001:7144: 'bangs rnams bsnyen gnas la bkod par gsungs pa'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:7145: na / dge slong ngam dge bsnyen gso sbyong la
NK024(ya)001:7146: gnas pa sdom pa dag pa 'bogs pa'i cho ga
NK024(ya)001:7148: rten ni klu gzhon nu tsam pa zhes bya ba
NK024(ya)001:7149: dus bzang la yan lag brgyad kyi bsnyen gnas bsrung
NK024(ya)001:7150: ba sogs bshad pas klu sogs dud 'gro dang 'gro
NK024(ya)001:7151: ba gzhan la yang skye bar bshad /
NK024(ya)001:7152: de bzhin du theg pa che chung gi bsnyen gnas kyi cho ga la yang khyad par yod de /
NK024(ya)001:7154: nyan thos rnams kyi cho ga yang //
NK024(ya)001:7156: zhes gsungs pas skyabs 'gro rtsom byed du byas nas gang zag gzhan la rten nas len dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7158: don yod zhags pa'i rtog pa las /
NK024(ya)001:7159: bsnyen gnas rang gis len pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:7160: cho ga sems bskyed 'dra bar gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:7161: zhes gsungs pas rten gyi drung du dang po nyid nas rang gis blangs chog par bshad /
NK024(ya)001:7162: mdor na de lta bu'i spyir bshad pa rnams ngos zin par byas nas 'dir ni /
NK024(ya)001:7163: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis bzung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:7164: cho ga nyan thos lugs bzhin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:7165: so sor thar pa rigs brgyad po //
NK024(ya)001:7166: byang sems so sor thar par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:7167: zhes gsungs pa ltar spyir theg chen dang /
NK024(ya)001:7168: khyad par sngags lam dang 'brel ba'i bsnyen gnas kyi
NK024(ya)001:7169: cho ga nyan thos lugs ltar len par byed dgos
NK024(ya)001:7170: shing / de yang rnying ma rang lugs kyi cho
NK024(ya)001:7171: ga 'dir gtan khrims lha mi'i theg pa'i lugs ltar
NK024(ya)001:7172: shing / len pa dang / dus khrims bsnyen gnas
NK024(ya)001:7173: yan lag brgyad pa len tshul gnyis yod pa'i dang
NK024(ya)001:7174: shing / len pa dang / po ni / cho
NK024(ya)001:7175: ga'i 'gros la dpags na phal cher spyod pa rtsa
NK024(ya)001:7176: bzhi 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen du ming 'dogs su rung
NK024(ya)001:7178: de'i rgyu mtshan mi dge bcu spong ba la phal
NK024(ya)001:7179: cher spyod pa'i dge bsnyen du bu ston thams cad
NK024(ya)001:7181: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa brgyad par /
NK024(ya)001:7182: rdzun gyi tshig ni zlog pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:7183: de yi skyon ni gzhan las kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7184: gang phyir lus ngag mi dge las //
NK024(ya)001:7185: ldog pa yid kyi dge las so //
NK024(ya)001:7186: de phyir brnab sems gnod pa'i sems //
NK024(ya)001:7187: lta las ldog rnams grub pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:7188: zhes pa'i lung yang 'dren par mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:7189: 'on kyang dbang gi skabs 'dir zhu mkhan gyi gang
NK024(ya)001:7190: zag gis nges par bsrung nus mi nus la ltos
NK024(ya)001:7191: pa'i dbang du mi mdzad par sngags sdom ltar spyi
NK024(ya)001:7193: deng sangs dbang bskur thob tshad kyis sngags sdom mtshan
NK024(ya)001:7194: nyid pa srung mi thub pas skyon med 'dra snyam
NK024(ya)001:7195: zhing / tshul bzhin srung sdom thub na legs pa lta ci smos /
NK024(ya)001:7196: de ltar gtan khrims len pa la /
NK024(ya)001:7198: bsnyen gnas kun la yod mod kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7199: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK024(ya)001:7201: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK024(ya)001:7202: thar pa 'dod pa rnams kyi skyabs //
NK024(ya)001:7203: zhes gsungs pas dkon mchog gsum dpang por gsol nas len dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:7204: de lta bu'i skyabs yul gyi dkon mchog ngos 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:7205: lugs mang zhing so sor thar pa'i lugs bye mdo
NK024(ya)001:7206: gnyis la yang skyabs yul ngos 'dzin tshul mi 'dra
NK024(ya)001:7207: mod kyang / 'dir theg dman spyi lugs kyi dkon mchog gsum ni /
NK024(ya)001:7208: sangs rgyas su byed pa'i chos sangs rgyas mi slob
NK024(ya)001:7209: pa'i lam bden chos sku dang gzugs sku gnyis kyi
NK024(ya)001:7210: bdag nyid / chos myang 'das so sor brtags 'gog /
NK024(ya)001:7211: dge 'dun du byed pa'i chos slob mi slob kyi
NK024(ya)001:7212: lam bden gzugs sku dang bcas pa rnams yin par
NK024(ya)001:7213: gsungs la / mtshon byed du kun rdzob brdar btags
NK024(ya)001:7214: pa'i sangs rgyas ston pa'i sku gzugs sdom rten du
NK024(ya)001:7215: bzhugs dgos par gzhung 'dir yang gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:7217: dga' ston dus tshe sku gzugs ni //
NK024(ya)001:7218: rgan po'i gong du rtag tu bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:7219: ces gsungs pas sdom rten ston pa'i sku dang dkyil
NK024(ya)001:7220: 'khor gyi gtso bo rnams la ston pa dngos kyi
NK024(ya)001:7222: chos ni lung rtogs gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:7223: rtogs pa'i chos lam du sgrub pa /
NK024(ya)001:7224: lung gi chos lam gyi 'jug sgom /
NK024(ya)001:7225: sdom pa 'bogs pa'i las kyi cho ga rnams yin pa la dngos su tshang /
NK024(ya)001:7226: dge 'dun ni dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor gyi lha rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:7227: khyad par dge 'dun gyi dkyil 'khor la rigs gsum mgon po dang /
NK024(ya)001:7229: mchog zung rab 'byor kun dga' bo ste /
NK024(ya)001:7230: theg pa che chung gi dge 'dun rnams ting nge
NK024(ya)001:7231: 'dzin gyis bskyed cing spyan drangs te mngon sum du
NK024(ya)001:7232: bzhugs pas tshang zhing gang zag gzhan las khyad par
NK024(ya)001:7233: 'phags / gzhan yang sdom gnas kyi bla ma yang dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7234: dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa brgyad par /
NK024(ya)001:7235: sdom gnas bla ma mkhas pa la //
NK024(ya)001:7236: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir na cho ga brda sprod pa yang bdag gis bgyid /
NK024(ya)001:7237: de ltar dkon mchog gsum bla ma dang bcas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7238: drung du sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:7239: las thar par bya ba'i phyir skyabs sangs rgyas la
NK024(ya)001:7240: de'i thabs ston pa'i ston pa zhu /
NK024(ya)001:7241: chos mi gnas pa'i myang 'das la skyabs dngos /
NK024(ya)001:7242: dge 'dun la de sgrub pa'i grogs zhus te deng
NK024(ya)001:7243: phyin chad skyabs gzhan spangs la mi dge bcu spong
NK024(ya)001:7244: sems kyi gtan khrims ji srid 'tsho'i bar du len
NK024(ya)001:7246: sdom pa thob 'dod kyi blos dungs pa bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:7247: zhes gsungs pas thob 'dod kyi blo dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:7248: bcu drug bsdom pa dpog pa ni sngar chos 'brel med na btsun pa zhes brjod dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:7251: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:7252: ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis dam pa
NK024(ya)001:7253: rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //'dod
NK024(ya)001:7254: chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la skyabs
NK024(ya)001:7255: su mchi'o // tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK024(ya)001:7256: bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du lha mi'i theg pa la gnas par btsun pas bzung du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:7257: gnyis pa'i yang rjes zlos mdzod byas la gnyis pa bskyar /
NK024(ya)001:7259: brjod pa gsum pa'i mthar slob dpon gyi bzung du gsol bya /
NK024(ya)001:7260: zhes gsungs pas gsum pa'i skabs su cho ga 'di
NK024(ya)001:7261: la cha gsum du yod pa'i dge 'dun la skyabs
NK024(ya)001:7262: su mchi'o yan chad skyabs brjod pa /
NK024(ya)001:7263: lha mi'i theg pa la gnas par yan chad bdag brjod pa /
NK024(ya)001:7264: btsun pas bzung du gsol zhes gzhan brjod pa yin
NK024(ya)001:7265: pas bdag brjod rdzogs pa dang sdom pa skye zhing
NK024(ya)001:7266: de'i tshe nged kyang slob dpon du 'gyur ba yin
NK024(ya)001:7267: pas btsun pa zhes mi brjod par slob dpon gyi
NK024(ya)001:7268: bzung du gsol zhes brjod dgos pas de yid la
NK024(ya)001:7269: zhog la gsum pa'i yang rjes zlos mdzod byas la
NK024(ya)001:7270: gsum pa bya / slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK024(ya)001:7272: de nas bslab pa brjod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:7273: des sdom pa thob pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:7274: thob kyang ma bsrung na nyes dmigs chen po yod pas bsrung dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7275: bsrung lugs dgra bcom pa rnams kyis mi dge ba
NK024(ya)001:7276: bcu po yid kyis spangs nas lus ngag gi de
NK024(ya)001:7277: las slar log pa bzhin du bdag gis kyang mi
NK024(ya)001:7278: dge bcu yid kyis spangs te lus ngag gis slar
NK024(ya)001:7279: ldog par bgyid snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos lan gcig
NK024(ya)001:7280: mdzod / slob dpon dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:7281: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis lha mi'i theg pa la zhugs te /
NK024(ya)001:7282: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7283: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7284: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7291: log par blta ba la sogs pa mi dge ba bcu spangs te /
NK024(ya)001:7292: mi dge ba bcu las slar log pa de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK024(ya)001:7293: mi dge ba bcu spangs te mi dge bcu las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:7294: sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyi rjes
NK024(ya)001:7295: su slob pa'i lha mi'i theg pa bzang po la
NK024(ya)001:7299: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK024(ya)001:7302: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa /
NK024(ya)001:7303: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:7304: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:7305: tshangs gnas la sogs rim par skye ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:7306: zhes gsungs pas de lta bu'i lam la slob pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos lan gcig mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7308: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po de dag gi lha mi'i theg par zhugs te /
NK024(ya)001:7309: bsam gtan dang snyoms 'jug gi sems bsgrubs te /
NK024(ya)001:7310: bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa brnyes pa de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang /
NK024(ya)001:7314: btang snyoms tshad med pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7315: bsam gtan gyi sems rtog dpyod bral ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7317: gnas te 'phags pa'i bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa thob par bagyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:7318: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po rnams kyi rjes su slob bo //
NK024(ya)001:7321: slob dpon gyis thabs yin no //
NK024(ya)001:7324: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bco lnga pa bsnyen gnas nyid yin te /
NK024(ya)001:7325: byams pa lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:7326: bcu bzhi dang ni bco lnga dang //
NK024(ya)001:7327: de bzhin zla gcig tshes brgyad dang //
NK024(ya)001:7328: cho 'phrul gyi ni zla ba la //
NK024(ya)001:7329: yan lag brgyad legs mnyam gzhag cing //
NK024(ya)001:7330: bsnyen gnas gso sbyong byas nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:7333: zla ba yar gyi tshes brgyad dang //
NK024(ya)001:7334: cho 'phrul gyi ni zla ba la //
NK024(ya)001:7335: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad bsrungs na //
NK024(ya)001:7338: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK024(ya)001:7339: ko'u shi ka de skad ma zer cig /
NK024(ya)001:7340: tshig rkang snga ma gsum gong bzhin la tha mar /
NK024(ya)001:7342: zhes gsungs pas dus khrims 'di nyid mchog tu basngagasa /
NK024(ya)001:7344: ji srid 'tsho dang nyin zhag tu //
NK024(ya)001:7345: sdom pa yang dag blang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:7346: zhes gsungs pas na thog mar ji srid 'tsho'i bar
NK024(ya)001:7347: gyi zla ba byung ngo cog gi dus bzang gsum
NK024(ya)001:7348: por bsnyen gnas bya bar khas blangs shing phyis dus
NK024(ya)001:7349: bzang de gsum la bsnyen gnas len pa'i tshe tho
NK024(ya)001:7350: mar 'dir blangs pa'am thob pas go bcad de slar
NK024(ya)001:7351: sdom pa len mi dgos pa ni ma yin te
NK024(ya)001:7352: / dper na cho 'phrul zla ba'i tshes gcig nas
NK024(ya)001:7353: bco lnga'i bar bsrung yang zhag re bzhin len dgos
NK024(ya)001:7354: / la / de ltar len pa'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:7355: theg dman ltar na gzhan las len cing /
NK024(ya)001:7356: theg chen la rang gis blangs chog par gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:7357: de yang theg dman bye brag tu smra ba'i lugs
NK024(ya)001:7358: la thog mar gzhan las len pa'i dgos pa ni
NK024(ya)001:7359: / slar len pa'i tshe gzhan las nges par blang
NK024(ya)001:7360: dgos kyang dus kyi khyad par zas zos nas blangs
NK024(ya)001:7361: kyang sdom pa skye ba'i khyad yin la /
NK024(ya)001:7362: 'on kyang zas de gung tshigs lta bu ma yin par snga dro'i tsha ba lta bu yin /
NK024(ya)001:7363: de lta yin pa'i shes byed /
NK024(ya)001:7365: gang gi tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas la gnas par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:7366: zhes sngon yang dag par blangs pa byas pa des ni zas zos nas kyang nod par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:7367: gzhan las nod par bya yi //
NK024(ya)001:7368: bdag nyid las ni ma yin te //
NK024(ya)001:7370: de yang slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mi ltar bsnyen gnas
NK024(ya)001:7371: yan lag brgyad pa ji srid 'tsho'i bar bsrung ba
NK024(ya)001:7372: la go mi'i dge bsnyen zhes grags kyang /
NK024(ya)001:7373: lugs de ni thams cad yod par smra ba'i lugs
NK024(ya)001:7374: la ma grags shing gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs yin
NK024(ya)001:7375: te / mnga' ris pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:7376: 'di brgyad ji srid 'tsho yi bar bsrungs na //
NK024(ya)001:7377: go mi'i dge bsnyen yin kyang yod smra'i min //
NK024(ya)001:7378: gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed //
NK024(ya)001:7380: bu ston gyis sa ston sde pa'i lugs yin yang gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:7381: 'dir ni de lta bu'i gtan khrims ma yin par
NK024(ya)001:7382: dus khrims ltar yin te nyin zhag gcig 'das ma
NK024(ya)001:7383: thag sdom pa gtong bas na /
NK024(ya)001:7384: bsnyen gnas mtshan mo 'das pa na //
NK024(ya)001:7386: mdo sde pa yi lugs bzhin du //
NK024(ya)001:7387: ji ltar 'dod tshe len na yang //
NK024(ya)001:7388: nang par phan chad srung ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:7389: bsam pa med phyir sdom pa btang //
NK024(ya)001:7390: de yi phyir na 'bul mi dgos //
NK024(ya)001:7391: zhes gsungs pas don bsdu na bye brag tu smra
NK024(ya)001:7392: ba'i lugs la bsnyen gnas nges par gang zag gzhan
NK024(ya)001:7394: mdo sde pa'i lugs su dang por gzhan las nges
NK024(ya)001:7395: par len la phyis rten gyi drung du rang gis
NK024(ya)001:7397: theg chen lugs la dang po nas kyang rten kho
NK024(ya)001:7398: na'i drung du blangs pas skye bar bshad pas de
NK024(ya)001:7399: dag ma 'dres par shes dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:7400: de phyir da res theg dman gyi lugs ltar thog mar slob dpon gyi drung du len /
NK024(ya)001:7401: slar slob dpon 'byor na bye brag tu smra ba ltar slob dpon las len la /
NK024(ya)001:7402: ma 'byor na mdo sde pa bzhin cho ga 'di ltar rten gyi drung du len /
NK024(ya)001:7403: yang na gsar ma ba rnams don zhags las gsungs zhes 'chad la /
NK024(ya)001:7404: rang lugs nyan thos kyi skabs na yod pa'i cho
NK024(ya)001:7405: ga de nyid rten gyi drung du len pa ste
NK024(ya)001:7406: / de gsum ji ltar bde ba ltar len par bya dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7407: de yang kun spyod stan dma' bar 'dug cing rgyan gsar pa mi gdags dus nyin zhag phrugs gcig /
NK024(ya)001:7408: cho ga slob dpon gyi rjes zlos tshig gsal la brjod pa dag pa lan gsum bgyid dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7410: dma' bar 'dug smras bzla pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:7411: mi brgyan nam ni langs bar du //
NK024(ya)001:7412: bsnyen gnas yan lag tshang bar ni //
NK024(ya)001:7413: nang par gzhan las nod par bya //
NK024(ya)001:7414: zhes gsungs pas don yid la 'jog dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:7416: gnam stong ni gso sbyong mi thub pa na tshes gcig la'ang rung ste /
NK024(ya)001:7418: nya nas gnam stong gi bar la tshes gang yang
NK024(ya)001:7419: rung ba gcig chad na'ang gnam stong gi ngo bo
NK024(ya)001:7420: de nyid yin no zhes skyabs 'gro byas nas /
NK024(ya)001:7421: zhes gsungs pas skyabs 'gro da lta song ma thag
NK024(ya)001:7422: pa yin na'ang gtan khrims dang dus khrims cho ga
NK024(ya)001:7423: tha dad pas slar yang skyabs 'gro bya dgos te
NK024(ya)001:7424: sngar bshad pa bzhin skyabs 'gro'i don dran par bya
NK024(ya)001:7425: / de'i ched du bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa len snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7427: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:7428: ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis dam pa
NK024(ya)001:7429: rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //'dod
NK024(ya)001:7430: chags dang 'bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la tshogs
NK024(ya)001:7431: rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la bdag ming 'di zhes
NK024(ya)001:7432: bya ba ji srid 'tsho'i bar gyi zla ba byung
NK024(ya)001:7433: ngo cog gi nya dang gnam stong dang tshes brgyad
NK024(ya)001:7434: la bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad par btsun pas bzung
NK024(ya)001:7436: gnyis pa 'i yang rjes zlos gyis byas la gnyis pa bya /
NK024(ya)001:7437: gsum pa dum bu gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:7438: dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o yan chad skyabs brjod pa /
NK024(ya)001:7439: bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad par zhes pa bdag brjod pa /
NK024(ya)001:7440: btsun pas bzung du gsol gzhan brjod pa yin pas
NK024(ya)001:7441: skyabs brjod bdag brjod gnyis rdzogs rjes khyod kyi rgyud
NK024(ya)001:7443: nged slob dpon du 'gyur bas de dus thob shes
NK024(ya)001:7444: bskyed pa dang de'i tshe nged kyang slob dpon du
NK024(ya)001:7445: 'gyur bas slob don zhes brjod dgos pas de yid
NK024(ya)001:7446: la zhog la gsum pa'i yang rjes zlos gyis byas
NK024(ya)001:7449: de rjes bslab pa brjod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:7450: des bsnyen gnas dus khriims kyi sdom pa thob pa yin la /
NK024(ya)001:7451: de thob pas mi chog bsrung dgos shing bsrung lugs
NK024(ya)001:7452: dgra bcom pa rnams kyis spang bya brgyad po yid
NK024(ya)001:7453: kyis spangs te lus ngag gis slar log pa bzhin
NK024(ya)001:7454: du bdag gis kyang dus bzang po gsum la bsnyen
NK024(ya)001:7455: gnas kyi spang bya brgyad char gtogs dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:7456: yid kyis spangs te lus ngag gi slar ldog snyam
NK024(ya)001:7457: pa dgos shing de lta bu'i bslab pa brjod pa
NK024(ya)001:7458: 'di la rjes zlos lan gsum nges par bya dgos
NK024(ya)001:7460: de ltar lan gnyis lan gsum du'o //
NK024(ya)001:7461: zhes 'byung bas 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7462: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chen
NK024(ya)001:7463: po rnams kyis zla ba byung ngo cog gi nya
NK024(ya)001:7465: gnam stong la srog gcod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7466: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7467: mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7470: bcos pa'i chang myong par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK024(ya)001:7475: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7478: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas spangs te /
NK024(ya)001:7479: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas za ba las slar
NK024(ya)001:7480: log pa de bzhin du yan lag brgyad pa 'dis
NK024(ya)001:7481: bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gi rjes
NK024(ya)001:7482: su slob bo // rjes su sgrub bo //
NK024(ya)001:7484: lan gsum song nas thabs legs gong bzhin bya /
NK024(ya)001:7486: gsol btab sdom pa dus khrims dbog /
NK024(ya)001:7487: ces gsungs pa'i sdom pa gtan khrims /
NK024(ya)001:7488: dus khrims bsnyen gnas dpog ces pas cho ga dngos
NK024(ya)001:7489: bstan pa'i shugs las bslab bya 'bogs pa yang bstan
NK024(ya)001:7491: de ltar gtan khrims dang dus khrims kyi rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:7492: can 'chal tshul gyi rgyun 'gog par byed pa sdom
NK024(ya)001:7493: pa'i tshul khrims de lta bu'i bsrung tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:7494: spyir dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su song ba'i bslab byar /
NK024(ya)001:7496: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs 'gro ba //
NK024(ya)001:7497: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen te //
NK024(ya)001:7498: nam du'ang lha ni gzhan dag la //
NK024(ya)001:7499: skyabs su song ba ma yin no //
NK024(ya)001:7500: dam pa'i chos la skyabs 'tshol na //'tshe zhing gnod pa'i sems dang bral //
NK024(ya)001:7501: dge 'dun la yang skyabs song ba //
NK024(ya)001:7502: mu stegs gzhan la phyag mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:7505: gang zhig gsum la skyabs 'gro ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:7506: dge bsnyen nyid du dam bcas pas //
NK024(ya)001:7507: skyabs ni gsum po bsrung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:7508: mu stegs kun la gus pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:7510: zhes gsungs pa ltar bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7511: sangs rgyas la skyabs song gi bslab byar 'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:7512: gyi lha sogs la phyag mchod mi bya zhing lha
NK024(ya)001:7513: rten gyi sar slebs na'ang se gol gyi sgras sad
NK024(ya)001:7514: par byas te / chos rnams thams cad rgyu las byung //
NK024(ya)001:7516: brtsam par bya zhing dbyung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:7517: zhes sogs kyi tshigs bcad kyi sgo nas chos bshad la phan gdags /
NK024(ya)001:7518: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gzugs dang thugs rten gang
NK024(ya)001:7519: mthong yang gus par bya zhing tha na byis pas
NK024(ya)001:7520: rtse mor byas pa la yang rim gro bskyed dgos
NK024(ya)001:7522: ji ltar bde gshegs sku gzugs shing las kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7523: bgyis pa ci 'dra'ang rung ste mkhas pas mchod //
NK024(ya)001:7525: chos la skyabs song gi bslab byar sems can la gnod 'tshe spong /
NK024(ya)001:7526: dam pa'i chos mi spong zhing theg pa che chung
NK024(ya)001:7527: drang nges ji ltar snang yang bzang ngan du mi
NK024(ya)001:7528: blta / chos smra ba la bkur sti dang ci gsung bsgrub /
NK024(ya)001:7529: des bstan pa'i dam pa'i chos la thos bsam sgom
NK024(ya)001:7530: pa 'chad nyan sogs ci nus su bya zhing de
NK024(ya)001:7531: dag gi mi mthun phyogs spong /
NK024(ya)001:7532: glegs bam nas yi ge nyis 'brel gyi bar du gus pas bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7534: yi ge nyis 'brel dkon mchog gsum gyi mtshan //
NK024(ya)001:7536: dge 'dun la skyabs song gi bslab byar /
NK024(ya)001:7537: grogs mu stegs can dang mi 'grogs /
NK024(ya)001:7540: dge 'dun bzhir longs pa yan chad dam rgyun zhugs
NK024(ya)001:7541: sogs 'phags pa'i gang zag gcig yan chod la gus
NK024(ya)001:7543: tshul khrims 'chal ba la yang mi brnyas shing /
NK024(ya)001:7544: gus pa'i sgo nas dge 'dun rjes su dran pa bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7546: nga yi dge sbyong tshul khrims 'chal gyur kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7547: mu stegs phal pa rnams kyi do ma yin //
NK024(ya)001:7549: thun mong du skyes bu dam pa bsten /
NK024(ya)001:7550: dam pa'i chos nyan tshul bzhin yid la bya /
NK024(ya)001:7553: sdom pa ci nus su len /
NK024(ya)001:7554: sems can la snying rje sgom /
NK024(ya)001:7555: dkon mchog mchod pa la brtson par slob bo //
NK024(ya)001:7556: gzhan yang jo bo chen po'i bzhed srol /
NK024(ya)001:7557: srog dang bya dag'i phyir du dkon mchog gsum mi spang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7558: dgos gal ji ltar che yang skyabs 'gro las mo
NK024(ya)001:7559: bon rtsis gsum sogs kyi thabs gzhan mi 'tshol ba
NK024(ya)001:7560: dang / dus kyi mchod pa mi gcog pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7561: rang gzhan thams cad skyabs 'gro'i lam la 'god pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7562: gar 'gro yang phyogs de'i sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal
NK024(ya)001:7563: zhing gus pa'i sgo nas 'gro ba dang lnga yin
NK024(ya)001:7564: te / pan chen gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:7565: srog dang bya dgar dkon mchog gsum mi spang //
NK024(ya)001:7566: dgos gal che yang thabs gzhan mi 'tshol zhing //
NK024(ya)001:7567: dus mchod mi bcag rang gzhan skyabs 'gror 'god //
NK024(ya)001:7568: gar 'gro'i phyogs kyi sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:7569: lnga rnams thun mong bslab byar jo bo bzhed //
NK024(ya)001:7571: mdor na de lta bu'i bslab bya gtso bo nyams pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7574: smra shes don go'i mi'i drung du skyabs 'gro gtong 'dod kyi bsam pas dkon mchog gsum 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:7575: bdag lha gzhan la brten par bzung du gsol //
