NK024(ya)001:7576: bdag mu stegs can du bzung du gsol zhes pa lta bur phul ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7577: shi 'phos na gtong bas shi na ma gtogs gzhan
NK024(ya)001:7578: gtong rgyu snga ma rnams kyi sgo nas btang na
NK024(ya)001:7579: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi drung du bshags la slar
NK024(ya)001:7580: blang ngo // de ltar skyabs song gi phan yon bsam las 'das zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7581: mdor bsdu na nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i lugs kyi
NK024(ya)001:7582: mngon mtho dang nges legs kyi yon tan thams cad
NK024(ya)001:7583: kyi gzhi rten skyabs song kho na las byung ba
NK024(ya)001:7584: yin te / mdo sde rgyan las /
NK024(ya)001:7585: sna tshogs 'jig 'gyur 'jig tshogs kun dang theg pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:7586: ngan song rnam mang sdug bsngal thabs min song ba rnams //
NK024(ya)001:7587: skye dang 'chi ba nyon mongs las rnams kun las bsrung //
NK024(ya)001:7588: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gtan khrims kyi bslab byar mi dge ba bcu spong zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7589: de'i ldog pa dge bcu ci nus su sgrub tshul shes par sla mod /
NK024(ya)001:7590: 'on kyang 'og tu lam 'khyer skabs cung zad 'chad la /
NK024(ya)001:7591: de yang srog gcod ni mi gsod pa /
NK024(ya)001:7592: ma byin len ni kar+sha pa ni bzhi char tshang ba brku ba /
NK024(ya)001:7593: rdzun ni mi chos bla ma'i rdzun smra /
NK024(ya)001:7594: mi tshangs spyod ni log g.yem ste bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:7595: nyams na bshags pa sngon du 'gro bas bskyar la blangs /
NK024(ya)001:7596: skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya phra mo las 'das pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7597: mi ma yin gsod pa sogs kyis mtshon pa'i cung
NK024(ya)001:7598: zad phra ba bzhi byas na nyes pa de dang
NK024(ya)001:7599: rigs mthun ma byung ba gcig la bshags /
NK024(ya)001:7600: mi dge ba gzhan drug po blangs pa'i phyogs mthun yin pas sdam dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7601: rtsa ba bzhi dug gsum gang rung gi sbyor bas khyad med la /
NK024(ya)001:7602: srog gcod zhe sdang gis mthar phyin pas de dang
NK024(ya)001:7603: phyogs mthun tshig rtsub gnod sems ma sbyin len no
NK024(ya)001:7604: //'dod log 'dod chags kyis mthar phyin par byed pas
NK024(ya)001:7606: rdzun dug gsum gang rung gis thar phyin par byed pas phyogs mthun phra ma tshig 'khyal lo //
NK024(ya)001:7607: de rnams dang skyabs 'gro la yang dag lta ba
NK024(ya)001:7608: dgos pas phyogs mthun log lta rnams nges par bsdam
NK024(ya)001:7609: par bya dgos / de ltar bslab pa'i gzhi mang
NK024(ya)001:7610: po'i srung sdom la 'jigs te sdom pa mi len
NK024(ya)001:7611: pa rnams 'jug pa'i don du phal cher spyod pa
NK024(ya)001:7612: rtsa bzhi 'dzin pa'i dge bsnyen zhes gsungs kyang don
NK024(ya)001:7613: du mi dge bcu po thams cad bsrung dgos pas
NK024(ya)001:7614: ldog pa dge bcu sgrub par shugs kyis bstan te
NK024(ya)001:7615: par bya dgos / / 'dir rang lugs gtan khrims
NK024(ya)001:7616: su 'dod pa'i rgyu mtshan yang sangs rgyas pa'i grub
NK024(ya)001:7617: mthar 'jug pa'i rtsa ba yin pa'i phyir na de
NK024(ya)001:7618: par bya dgos / / ltar du 'dod / de
NK024(ya)001:7619: dag kyang gong gi skyabs sdom 'bul bas mtshon te
NK024(ya)001:7622: ma ning du gyur pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7623: log ltas dge rtsa chad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7624: rtsa ba bzhi rags sdom dngos gzhi rdzogs na gtong bas /
NK024(ya)001:7625: shi 'phos dang ma ning gnyis ma gtogs gzhan rnams
NK024(ya)001:7626: la bshags sdom byas la bskyar te blang dgos te
NK024(ya)001:7627: / sdom pa slar yang blang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:7628: de 'dra'i gang zag nyid las so //
NK024(ya)001:7629: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ltung ba byung na las sgrib sbyang don du phung po gsum pa'i mdo dang /
NK024(ya)001:7630: 'phags pa sgo drug pa'i gzungs nyin mtshan gyi dus mtshams drug tu 'don dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:7632: rtsa ba yan lag kyang gang thub pa bsrung zhing
NK024(ya)001:7633: blang du rung la dus kyang nya stong brgyad gsum
NK024(ya)001:7635: de yang rtsa ba nyams na gzhi nas bskyar /
NK024(ya)001:7636: yan lag nyams pa bshags pas 'dag go //
NK024(ya)001:7637: sbyor dngos rjes bsam pa bzhi las rjes ma tshang na nyes pa na smad pa zhes pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:7639: de'i steng du thos bsam sgom gsum dang sbyin sogs ci nus kyis 'bad par bya dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7640: dus khrims bsnyen gnas yan lag brgyad pa'i bslab byar
NK024(ya)001:7641: gang zag tha ma 'dod pa dang nyes spyod gnyis
NK024(ya)001:7642: ka las dben par spyod mi nus pa'i rigs can
NK024(ya)001:7643: de dben pa gnyis la sbyar ba'i don du gsungs
NK024(ya)001:7644: shing / dgra bcom pa dang nye bar gnas byed kyi phyir /
NK024(ya)001:7645: ji srid 'tsho ba pa'i sdom pa gtan khrims dang
NK024(ya)001:7646: nye bar gnas byed kyi phyir na spang bya yan
NK024(ya)001:7647: lag brgyad spong bar khas len dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:7648: yan lag brgyad ni rtsa ba bzhi spong ba tshul khrims kyi yan lag bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:7649: chang spong ba bag yod kyi yan lag /
NK024(ya)001:7650: mal che mtho gnyis gcig tu bsdoms /
NK024(ya)001:7651: gar sogs phreng sogs gcig tu bsdoms /
NK024(ya)001:7652: phyi dro'i kha zas te 'di gsum brtul zhugs kyi yan lag dang brgyad yin te /
NK024(ya)001:7653: pan chen gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:7654: rtsa bzhi spong ba tshul khrims yan lag bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:7655: chang spong bag yod yan lag mal che mtho //
NK024(ya)001:7656: gar phreng la sogs phyi dro'i kha zas gsum //
NK024(ya)001:7657: brtul zhugs yan lag bsnyen gnas sdom pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:7658: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir mdor na gzhan la gnod pa
NK024(ya)001:7659: spangs pa'i yan lag tu srog gcod dang ma byin
NK024(ya)001:7660: len / rang gzhan gnyis ka la gnod pa spang ba'i yan lag tu 'khrig pa'i chos /
NK024(ya)001:7661: nyams pa phyir gso ba'i yan lag tu rdzun /
NK024(ya)001:7662: dran pa mi rmongs pa'i yan lag tu chang /
NK024(ya)001:7663: mi nyams pa dran shes brtan pa'i yan lag tu gar sogs phreng sogs /
NK024(ya)001:7665: dus min gyi kha zas rnams spong dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:7666: dge tshul la gar sogs phreng sogs tha dad du byed kyang /
NK024(ya)001:7667: 'dir gcig tu byed pa'i rgyu mtshan rab byung la rtsed mo //
NK024(ya)001:7669: bsog 'jog gnyis tshul dang mi mthun pas tha dad du byas zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7670: 'das na ltung ba gnyis bshags dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7671: bsogs 'jog gi rtsa ba gser dngul len pa yin pas de yang spang dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7672: khyim pa la de ltar ma yin pas gser dngul
NK024(ya)001:7673: len pa ma bkag cing gar sogs las 'das kyang
NK024(ya)001:7674: ltung ba gcig bshags pas chog par bstan pa'i don
NK024(ya)001:7676: gser dngul len pa yang spong bar 'dod na spangs
NK024(ya)001:7677: la gong gi bslab bya brjod pa'i skabs su de
NK024(ya)001:7680: yang na yan lag bcu pa la khri stan mthon po dang /
NK024(ya)001:7683: 'on kyang bsnyen gnas yan lag bcu pa zer ba kun la ma grags shing /
NK024(ya)001:7684: khri stan mthon po ni brtul zhugs kyi yan lag
NK024(ya)001:7685: mal che mtho tshang bas zur du mi dgos la
NK024(ya)001:7686: / gser dngul len pa spong ba yang don la
NK024(ya)001:7687: brtul zhugs kyi yan lag kho nar 'agro'am snyam zhing
NK024(ya)001:7688: / / de ltar na dge tshul dang zlos skyon du 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:7689: rtsa ba'i tshig rigs la 'dul ba mi shes pa 'dras bsre lhad kyi skyon yin 'dra zad /
NK024(ya)001:7690: yan lag brgyad pa kho na klan ka nyung zhing legs par mngon par de ltar bya /
NK024(ya)001:7691: de dag len tshul gong du legs par bshad zin pa ltar ma 'dres par shes dgos /
NK024(ya)001:7692: de ltar len pa'i cho ga 'di tshig rigs yongs
NK024(ya)001:7693: grags dang ma mthun yang snga 'gyur bka' ma'i rang
NK024(ya)001:7694: lugs yin pas byin rlabs dang ldan phyir legs shing
NK024(ya)001:7695: / slar dus bzang gsum la sdom pa len pa'i tshe cho ga rigs 'di ltar byung na rab /
NK024(ya)001:7696: de min nyan thos kyi cho gar 'byung rgyu'i theg pa chen po'i gso sbyong ngam /
NK024(ya)001:7697: yang na spyi ltar blangs kyang 'gal ba med /
NK024(ya)001:7698: skyabs 'gro nas srog gcod spong ba sna gcig spyod
NK024(ya)001:7699: pa'i dge bsnyen sogs de'i rigs 'gres kyi rang gang
NK024(ya)001:7700: 'dod re len tshe cho ga kha spos pas 'grub
NK024(ya)001:7701: / spyir bstan du dus bzang gsum la bsnyen gnas
NK024(ya)001:7702: srung bar khas blangs pas nam 'tsho'i bar dus bzang
NK024(ya)001:7703: gsum la nges par len dgos kyang dmigs gsal de
NK024(ya)001:7704: gsum gang rung la blangs kyang mi 'gal te /
NK024(ya)001:7706: rtsa ba yan lag kyang gang thub pa srung zhing
NK024(ya)001:7707: blang du rung la dus kyang nya stong brgyad gsum
NK024(ya)001:7710: mdor na 'phral yun gyi blang dor mtha' dag la legs par 'bad dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:7711: khrims kyi tshul khrims skyon med cing //
NK024(ya)001:7712: tshul khrims rnams par dag dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:7713: rlom sems med pa'i tshul khrims kyis //
NK024(ya)001:7714: tshul khrims pha rol phyin rdzogs shog /
NK024(ya)001:7715: ces bsgrub bya la me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:7716: zhar byung rtsod pa spang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:7718: nya dang gnam stong tshes brgyad la //
NK024(ya)001:7719: lha sgom tha dad ma byas na //
NK024(ya)001:7720: bsnyen gnas srung du mi 'dod zer //'di yang re zhig brtag par bya //
NK024(ya)001:7721: zhes gsungs pa rang lugs nya'i lha 'od dpag med /
NK024(ya)001:7722: gnam stong gi lha sh+aaka thub /
NK024(ya)001:7723: tshes brgyad sman blar bshad pas phyogs sngar mdzad dam snyam na ma yin te /
NK024(ya)001:7724: kun mkhyen bsod nams seng ges /
NK024(ya)001:7725: de'i phyogs snga bka' gdams bya yul bar ngos bzung zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7728: 'on kyang gsang sngags lugs byed na //
NK024(ya)001:7729: yi dam bsgoms pa bsod nams che //
NK024(ya)001:7730: theg pa chen po las byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:7731: so sor thar pa bshad kyis nyon //
NK024(ya)001:7732: zhes gsungs pa ltar nya stong brgyad gsum sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:7733: de gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i dus chen la
NK024(ya)001:7734: / bsnyen gnas bsrung pa'i steng sngags lugs ltar lha de gsum bsgom zhing bzlas pa byed pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:7735: yang na gzhan gang yang rung ba'i bsgom bzlas bgyis
NK024(ya)001:7736: na phan yon che bar gsungs pas theg chen so
NK024(ya)001:7737: thar gyi lugs yin par rtsod pa med /
NK024(ya)001:7738: 'on kyang dus bzang gsum la bsnyen gnas bsrung phyin
NK024(ya)001:7739: lha ma bsgom kyang chog cing dus bzang gsum la
NK024(ya)001:7740: sangs rgyas gsum gyi smon lam gyi mthus phan yon
NK024(ya)001:7741: 'byung bar rang lugs dri ma med pa'i gzhung 'di
NK024(ya)001:7743: stong la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas thub pa'i smon lam
NK024(ya)001:7744: gyi mthu las mu ge'i bskal pa las thar ba
NK024(ya)001:7745: dang / nya la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas snang ba
NK024(ya)001:7746: mtha' yas kyi smon lam gyi mthu las mtshon gyi
NK024(ya)001:7747: bskal pa las thar pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7748: tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas sman bla'i smon lam gyi mthus las rmi lam mtshan ngan /
NK024(ya)001:7751: nad kyi bskal pa las thar bar gsungs pa'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:7752: na bsnyen gnas bsrungs pa kho nas phan yon 'byung
NK024(ya)001:7753: zhing bsgom bzlas ma byas na bsnyen gnas nyams par
NK024(ya)001:7755: des na lha sgom ma byas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:7756: bsnyen gnas nyams par 'gyur ba med //
NK024(ya)001:7758: 'di la pan chen gser mdog can pa sh+aakya mchog ldan gyis /
NK024(ya)001:7759: gsang sngags lugs kyi bsnyen gnas la //
NK024(ya)001:7760: yi dam sgom pa mchog yin na //
NK024(ya)001:7761: lha de bdag mdun gang yin brtag /
NK024(ya)001:7762: bdag bskyed yin na bya rgyud kyi //
NK024(ya)001:7763: rang rkang bdag bskyed med de ci //
NK024(ya)001:7764: mdun bskyed yin na rnam rgyal sogs //
NK024(ya)001:7765: ma bskyed gong du gso sbyong gi //
NK024(ya)001:7766: sdom pa len par mdzad de ci //
NK024(ya)001:7768: kun mkhyen go bo rab 'byams pa bsod nams seng ges /
NK024(ya)001:7769: gzhung gi dgongs pa ma lon pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7770: dri ba thug med du 'gyur ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:7771: mtha' gnyis la skyon brjod pa mi 'thad pa gsum gyis rtsod pa zlog zin kyang /
NK024(ya)001:7772: zhwa dpe lhwam bkab kyi 'dir yang de 'dra'i rtsod
NK024(ya)001:7773: pa 'byung srid pas rtsod par 'dod pa rnams dri
NK024(ya)001:7774: lan sdom gsum 'khrul spong du gzigs shig /
NK024(ya)001:7775: pan chen gser mdog can pa mkhas grub tshad ma
NK024(ya)001:7776: yin 'dra yang rtog ge ba rgan po sngags lam
NK024(ya)001:7777: la zhugs ma thag pa kun gzhi bden grub kyi
NK024(ya)001:7778: nga rgyal brtan po 'dzin pa'i rang mdangs kyi gsang
NK024(ya)001:7779: sngags la rtog dpyod mang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7780: lhag par dge slong gis theg chen gso sbyong blangs
NK024(ya)001:7781: na bsnyen rdzogs kyi sdom pa 'jig ces pa gdul
NK024(ya)001:7782: bya'i rgyud kyi nyams len rgyun gcod pa nan tar
NK024(ya)001:7784: de la kun mkhyen bsod nams seng ges /
NK024(ya)001:7785: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:7786: zhes sogs kyis dgos pa rgya chen po yin tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:7787: dgos pa de ltar na sems bskyed lan cig thob nas slar nos pa dgos pa med tshul /
NK024(ya)001:7788: bla med kyi dbang thob cing sdom pa la gnas
NK024(ya)001:7789: pa'i sngags pas rgyud sde 'og ma'i dbang bskur nod
NK024(ya)001:7790: pa'i tshe bla med kyi sngags sdom 'jig tshul sogs
NK024(ya)001:7791: rig pas dgags pa la rjes su yi rang lan
NK024(ya)001:7792: brgyar 'phel / gser mdog can pa'i dgongs bzhed chos dbyings bsngosa rgyu'i dge rtsar sgrub bzhed dang /
NK024(ya)001:7793: dkar nag zang thal du bzhed 'dod dang /
NK024(ya)001:7794: byin rlabs smin byed kyi skor bzhed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:7795: phyag rgya chen po'i sgra don lag pa'i sgra don
NK024(ya)001:7796: du sgrub grogs mdzad pa til+li te lor bsgrub pa
NK024(ya)001:7797: dang / n+aa ro ta pa'i bzhed lugs sogs mang bas /
NK024(ya)001:7798: rje karma pa chos grags rgya mtsho'i mkhyen brtse nus
NK024(ya)001:7799: pa zang zing dang bcas pa'i byin rlabs kyis sa
NK024(ya)001:7800: skya pa'i grub mtha' dgongs pa'i phugs su mi bzhed
NK024(ya)001:7801: 'dra zhing / 'on kyang gser mdog can pas grub
NK024(ya)001:7802: mtha' sa kar gang mdzad kyang rang rang gi sngon
NK024(ya)001:7803: gyi smon lam btsan pa ma gtogs rang lugs la
NK024(ya)001:7804: ma ltos kyang gser thur du sa lugs kyi zhar
NK024(ya)001:7805: la rnying mar yang 'bri gung dpal 'dzin gyis rang
NK024(ya)001:7806: bzo'i dgag sgrub sna tshogs byas pa'i ngang bgros bskyar
NK024(ya)001:7807: 'dra zhing / zlos mdzad de / sngar 'gyur gyi
NK024(ya)001:7808: bstan pa rin po cher gnod pa byung ba la
NK024(ya)001:7809: bya ba skal bzang chos rje dang /
NK024(ya)001:7810: mnga' ris pan+di ta pad+ma dbang rgyal sogs kyang phyogs
NK024(ya)001:7811: 'di la shin tu mi 'thad pa'i tshul gyi gsung
NK024(ya)001:7812: thor bu ba 'dra snang bas rang gzhan gyi rig
NK024(ya)001:7813: pa rnon por rlom pa 'ga' lugs 'di'i rjes su
NK024(ya)001:7814: 'brangs te log par rtog par mi bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7815: khyad par theg chen gso sbyong rten las len par
NK024(ya)001:7816: bdag mdun gang yin brtag pa mi dgos kyang dogs
NK024(ya)001:7818: dge slong gi sdom pa rgyud ldan gyi gang zag
NK024(ya)001:7819: gis theg chen sems bskyed kyis kun nas slangs te
NK024(ya)001:7820: theg chen gso sbyong byas par sdom pa snga ma
NK024(ya)001:7821: la tho reg gang yang mi yong zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7822: bya spyod sogs rgyud sde 'og ma'i cho ga sgrub
NK024(ya)001:7823: pa la phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag tu 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:7824: pa'i thabs la dgos med the tshom gyis gso sbyong
NK024(ya)001:7825: 'dor ba sogs ti thug rigs 'gre nam yang mi
NK024(ya)001:7826: mdzad par snying nas gdams pa 'di la /
NK024(ya)001:7827: bden rdzun phyogs su ma lhungs pa'i mkhas grub tshad ma rnams kyis dpyad par zhu /
NK024(ya)001:7828: des 'jig rten lha mi'i theg pa'i 'jug sgo tshar nas dbang dngos la /
NK024(ya)001:7830: nyi shu pa chos bshad pa ni lha 'di rnams
NK024(ya)001:7831: ni lha kun gyi phyi mo yin pas dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:7833: mi dge ba las ngan 'gro dang /
NK024(ya)001:7834: mi g.yo ba'i las kyi khams gong ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:7835: dkon mchog gsum la dad pas chos kyi rgyal po thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:7836: zhes gsungs pa'i don dbang dngos la 'jug par byed pa la /
NK024(ya)001:7837: bum dbang sogs lha mi'i mtho ris kyi chas su 'jug pa'i dbang /
NK024(ya)001:7838: yi ge'i dbang la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:7839: rgya yig dbyangs gsal gyi dbang dang /
NK024(ya)001:7841: lha dbang dang bzhir yod pa las /
NK024(ya)001:7842: lha dbang yi ge'i dbang sogs theg pa kun gyi
NK024(ya)001:7843: phyi mo yin pas dbang de rnams thob cig dam
NK024(ya)001:7844: tshig la gnas na mtho ris dang /
NK024(ya)001:7845: mi dge ba spyad na ngan song /
NK024(ya)001:7846: mi g.yo ba'i las kyis khams gong ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:7847: dkon mchog gsum la dad pas chos kyi rgyal po
NK024(ya)001:7848: thob pa'i rgyu byed pas na mi dge spong zhing
NK024(ya)001:7849: dge ba la nan tan bya dgos zhes spro ba
NK024(ya)001:7851: nyer gcig pa ka kha bum pa'i dbang ni /
NK024(ya)001:7852: rgya yig dang bod yig cha gnyis su byung ba'i rgya yig kun bzang /
NK024(ya)001:7853: bod yig thub pa rang dang bum pa tsakli la thim /
NK024(ya)001:7854: bla ma dang tsakli las mar me gcig las gnyis chad lta bu byung /
NK024(ya)001:7855: slob ma la thim pas dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung bar bsam zhing rim pas thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:7856: zhes gsungs pas de'i don ni /
NK024(ya)001:7857: khyed rang rnams tha mal par blta bas dbang bskur yang mi chags te /
NK024(ya)001:7858: seng ge'i 'o ma snod ngan du blug pa dang
NK024(ya)001:7859: mtshungs pa'i phyir na rang gi lhag pa'i lha gang
NK024(ya)001:7860: yang rung ba'am rnam par snang mdzad lta bu'i nga
NK024(ya)001:7862: de'i ngang nas phyogs bcu'i bde bar gshegs pa'i byin
NK024(ya)001:7863: rlabs thams cad rgya yig dang bod yig gi rnam
NK024(ya)001:7864: par byon te / de yang dbyangs gsal rgya yig gi rnam pa kun bzang dang /
NK024(ya)001:7865: ka kha bod yig gi rnam pa thub par byas te /
NK024(ya)001:7866: bla ma dang bum pa dbang rten gyi tsakli rnams la thim dbang rnams bskur ba'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:7867: dbang rdzas so so bla ma dang dbang rten las
NK024(ya)001:7868: mar me gcig las gnyis chad lta bur byung ste
NK024(ya)001:7869: / khyed rang rnams la thim pas dgos 'dod thams cad yid bzhin du 'grub par sgom mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7870: gzhung du thog mar cod pan byung yang /
NK024(ya)001:7871: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan yab sras kyi bla dper /
NK024(ya)001:7872: thog mar rnam rgyal bum pas dbang bskur zhing rigs
NK024(ya)001:7873: bdag gis rgyas gdab pa'i tshul du cod pan gyis
NK024(ya)001:7874: dbang bskur bar gsungs pa ltar slob dpon gyi bum
NK024(ya)001:7875: pa thogs la / bum pa 'di ni bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:7876: 'das rnam par snang mdzad lha lnga 'od du zhu
NK024(ya)001:7877: ba las byung ba'i bum pa'i chu rgyun gyis slob
NK024(ya)001:7878: bu la spyi bo nas dbang bskur bas lus kyi
NK024(ya)001:7880: las nyon bag chags kyi dri ma thams cad dag /
NK024(ya)001:7881: chu'i lhag ma yar lud pa las rnam par snang mdzad kyis dbu brgyan pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7883: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis rlabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:7884: rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:7885: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma thams cad
NK024(ya)001:7886: byang zhing dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:7887: bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:7888: zhes spyi bor bzhag cing bum chu blud do //
NK024(ya)001:7889: rigs bdag rnam snang gtso bor gyur pa'i rigs lngas dbang bskur ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7891: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rin po che'i cod
NK024(ya)001:7892: pan gyi dbang bskur bas rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad
NK024(ya)001:7893: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:7894: / de yang sngon bdag cag gi ston pa yum
NK024(ya)001:7895: sgyu 'phrul ma'i lhums su zhugs pa'i tshul bstan pa
NK024(ya)001:7896: 'i tshe yum gyi phyag gis sems can nad pa
NK024(ya)001:7897: gang la reg pa'am rtsa nyag gcig sbyin pas kyang
NK024(ya)001:7898: thams cad nad med cing bde ba dang ldan par
NK024(ya)001:7900: 'dir yang yum gyi phyag gi dbang bskur bas yon
NK024(ya)001:7901: tan de lta bu'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK024(ya)001:7903: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la yum gyi phyag gis
NK024(ya)001:7904: reg cing dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:7905: thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:7906: gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa lhums su zhugs
NK024(ya)001:7907: pa'i tshe gangs ri'i ngos nas seng ge'i phru gu
NK024(ya)001:7909: ser skya'i grong khyer la bskor ba byed pa'i dge
NK024(ya)001:7910: mtshan bzang po ltar seng ge'i phrug gu zung zhig
NK024(ya)001:7911: gi dbang bskur bas rgol ba 'joms pa'i rten 'byung
NK024(ya)001:7912: gi dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:7914: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la seng phrug zung gcig
NK024(ya)001:7915: gi dbang bskur bas rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil
NK024(ya)001:7916: gyis gnon pa'i dbang dang ldan pa thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:7917: cig / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa lhums
NK024(ya)001:7918: su zhugs pa'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe glang po che'i
NK024(ya)001:7919: phru gu rnams kyang ser skyar lhags te snga ma
NK024(ya)001:7920: ltar bkra shis kyi mtshan ma bstan pa bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:7921: glang po'i phru gu'i dbang bskur bas 'jig rten gyi
NK024(ya)001:7922: 'dren par 'gyur ba'i dbang thob par mos pa mdzod
NK024(ya)001:7924: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la glang po che'i phru
NK024(ya)001:7925: gu zung gcig gi dbang bskur bas 'jig rten thams
NK024(ya)001:7926: cad 'dren pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:7927: gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa bltams pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:7928: na bza' ka shi ka'i ras dri ma med pa
NK024(ya)001:7929: gsol ba ltar ras gos kyi dbang bskur bas mkhyen
NK024(ya)001:7930: cha gsal la ma 'dres pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:7932: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la na bza' ka shi
NK024(ya)001:7933: ka'i ras kyi dbang bskur bas mkhyen pa'i ye shes
NK024(ya)001:7934: gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK024(ya)001:7935: cig / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa la
NK024(ya)001:7936: lha klu rnams kyi khrus gsol ba ltar bum chus
NK024(ya)001:7937: dbang bskur zhing khrus byas pas dri ma thams cad
NK024(ya)001:7938: dag pa'i dbang thob pa'i slar yang rnam rgyal gyi
NK024(ya)001:7941: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:7942: bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma
NK024(ya)001:7943: thams cad byang zhing dag pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:7944: cig / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa sh+aakya
NK024(ya)001:7945: rnams kyi don thams cad grub par mtshan gsol ba
NK024(ya)001:7946: ltar ming gis dbang bskur bas gzhan don 'grub pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7948: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la ming gi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:7949: bas shes bya'i ye shes la thogs pa med pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7950: gzhan don 'grub pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:7951: /'dir skya ming lta bur gang 'thad re spro na
NK024(ya)001:7952: gdags / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa sh+aakya'i
NK024(ya)001:7953: rgyal po bzang pos rgyan gyis brgyan par byas pa
NK024(ya)001:7954: bzhin rgyan gyi bye brag gi dbang bskur bas gzhan
NK024(ya)001:7955: skabs su yid 'phrog cing mthar thug mngon par shes
NK024(ya)001:7956: pa 'i dbang thob pa'i na mo /
NK024(ya)001:7957: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rgyan gyi bye brag
NK024(ya)001:7958: gi dbang bskur bas 'gro ba thams cad kyi sems
NK024(ya)001:7959: shes pa'i dbang dang ldan pa thob par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:7960: / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pas yig dpon
NK024(ya)001:7961: kun gyi bshes gnyen sogs yi ge'i tshul gyis 'dul
NK024(ya)001:7962: ba'i mdzad pa bstan pa bzhin yig shing gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:7963: bskur bas gnas skabs su dam pa'i chos la 'jug
NK024(ya)001:7964: sgo bri klog mthar phyin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:7965: mthar thug chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang thob pa'i na mo /
NK024(ya)001:7966: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la yig shing gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:7967: bskur bas chos kyi sgra sgrog pa'i dbang dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:7968: par gyur cig / gzhon nu don thams cad grub
NK024(ya)001:7969: pas sh+aakya'i tshogs rnams sgyu rtsal gyis 'dul bar mdzad
NK024(ya)001:7970: pa bzhin mda' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas gnas skabs su
NK024(ya)001:7972: mthar thug bdud sde'i g.yul las rgyal ba'i dbang thob pa'i na mo /
NK024(ya)001:7973: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la gnam ru zung gcig
NK024(ya)001:7974: gi dbang bskur bas snyan pa'i sgra sgrog cing bdud
NK024(ya)001:7975: dpung 'dul ba'i 'phongs rtsal dang ldan par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:7976: / gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa btsun mo'i
NK024(ya)001:7977: 'khor gyis rol pa'i ma dzad pa bstan pa bzhin
NK024(ya)001:7978: btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas gnas skabs su rigs mi
NK024(ya)001:7979: / nub cing / mthar thug thabs dang shes rab
NK024(ya)001:7980: kyi sgo nas 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang thob pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7981: / nub cing / na mo / phyogs bcu rigs
NK024(ya)001:7982: kyi bu la btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas bstan pa'i
NK024(ya)001:7984: ji ltar 'dul ba de bzhin du 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:7986: de ltar dbang bcu gcig po des lha mi mtho ris su chas su bcug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:7987: zhes gsungs pas mtho ris kyi dpal la spyood par
NK024(ya)001:7988: chas de rnams dang ldan dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan gyi
NK024(ya)001:7989: phyir ro //'di yang rgya che rol pa sogs gsung
NK024(ya)001:7990: rab las 'byung ba'i gleng gzhi dang sbyar te bshad
NK024(ya)001:7991: pas dang ba 'dren zhing dad pa 'phel ba'i rgyur
NK024(ya)001:7992: bsam ste gleng gzhi mdo tsam bris pa yin la
NK024(ya)001:7993: / rgyas par spro na zhib tu phye la 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:7994: de la dgos pa yod de /
NK024(ya)001:7995: byang chub mchog gi rjes su rab mos shing //
NK024(ya)001:7996: lan cig tsam yang dad pa skyes pa na //
NK024(ya)001:7997: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:7999: de 'dra'i dgos pa ma shes par dbang bskur yang
NK024(ya)001:8000: log rtog 'phel bas dgos don rgya cher rtogs dgos
NK024(ya)001:8001: shing / rgyu mtshan 'di la brten nas lam gyi
NK024(ya)001:8002: dkri tshul 'di yang gzhan las khyad par du 'phags
NK024(ya)001:8003: pa'i nges shes rnyed par 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:8004: de rjes yi ge dbang bskur ba la dmigs pa gong du bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK024(ya)001:8005: rdzod byed kyi tshig thams cad yi ge'i phyi mo
NK024(ya)001:8006: 'di rnams las 'byung ba'i phyir dbang bskur ba yin
NK024(ya)001:8007: pas thog mar dbyangs gsal rgya yig ltar bris pa
NK024(ya)001:8009: rgya yig gi ka smad thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:8010: a ni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK024(ya)001:8011: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK024(ya)001:8012: ka ni bya ba'i ye shes te //
NK024(ya)001:8013: las kyis thams cad grol bar bshad /
NK024(ya)001:8014: kha ni khyab par byed pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8015: mi dmigs thams cad grol bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:8016: ga ni don du 'gyur ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8017: yul med thams cad grol bar ston //
NK024(ya)001:8018: g+ha ni gnas pa'i sgo yin te //
NK024(ya)001:8019: gcig tu ma nges grol bar ston //
NK024(ya)001:8020: nga ni 'dzin pa med pa'i sgo //'dzin yul thams cad grol bar ston //
NK024(ya)001:8021: tsa ni 'gag pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8022: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8023: tsha ni 'da' ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8024: bral ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8025: dza ni ma byung ba yi sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8026: mi gnas pas ni thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8027: dz+ha ni rnyog ma med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8028: dri ma dag pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8029: na ni spyod dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8030: bya ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8031: ta ni nga rgyal med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8032: ngo bo med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8033: tha ni sgyu rtsal med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8034: byed pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8035: da ni 'dren pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8036: rtsod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8037: d+ha ni slu ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8038: sgyu ma thams cad grol bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:8039: na ni kun tu gyur pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8040: g.yo ba skyob pas las rnams grol //
NK024(ya)001:8041: ta ni tha snyad med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8042: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8043: tha ni rten dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8044: gnas pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8045: da ni gtong dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8046: len pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8047: d+ha ni rang bzhin med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8048: mtshan nyid med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8049: na ni yul dang bral ba'i sgo //'dzin pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8050: pa ni nges par 'byung ba'i sgo //'gag pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8051: pha ni dngos po med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8052: cir yang med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8053: ba ni brjod pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8054: smra ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8055: b+ha ni rdul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8056: rtog pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8057: ma ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8058: zhen pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8059: ya ni dri ma med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8060: gos pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8061: wa ni rgyu rkyen med pa'i sgo //'bras bu med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8062: ra ni rkyen dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8063: dor ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8064: la ni blang ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8065: yon tan med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8066: sha ni spros pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8067: zhi bas thams cad grol bar byed /
NK024(ya)001:8068: sha ni khur dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8069: lci ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8070: sa ni yang dag gsang ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8071: nges pa thams cad grol bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:8072: ha ni rgyu dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8073: rkyen dang bral bas thasama cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8074: k+sha ni khams dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8075: mtshan nyid med pas grol bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:8076: a +aa ni ma skyes ye shes yin //
NK024(ya)001:8077: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK024(ya)001:8078: i +ai ni mthong ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8079: gzugs dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8080: u +au ni thos pa med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8081: sgra dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8082: e ee ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8083: dri dang bral bas grol bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:8084: o oo ni tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK024(ya)001:8085: reg dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8087: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK024(ya)001:8088: zhes brjod cing dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:8089: de nas bod yig gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:8090: sngon lo ts+aa ba sangs rgyas ye shes kyi 'phags
NK024(ya)001:8091: yul wa ra n+aa sir sgra bsgyur nyi shu rtsa
NK024(ya)001:8092: gcig la mkhas pa +aa tsa r+ya gsal ba'i rgyan
NK024(ya)001:8093: dang / rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge dang /
NK024(ya)001:8094: bal po ba su d+ha ra rnams la 'dus pa
NK024(ya)001:8095: chen po'i dbang bskur gsan pa'i tshe lha mi'i theg
NK024(ya)001:8096: pa'i gnas skabs kyi ka med kyi dbang la /
NK024(ya)001:8097: rgya yig lnga bcu'i dbang bskur gyin 'dug pa la /
NK024(ya)001:8098: bod na thon mi sam+b+ho tas bsgyur ba'i yi ge sum cu yod ces zhus pas /
NK024(ya)001:8099: bod la yi ge sum cu yod pa'i dbang khyod kyis bskur zhig /
NK024(ya)001:8100: ces gsungs pas bod yig gi dbang rnams sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:8101: ye shes kyi gsung yin zhing phyag len yang de
NK024(ya)001:8102: man chod du dar ba las 'phags yul na med
NK024(ya)001:8103: la / spyir 'gro ba rnams la rang rang gi
NK024(ya)001:8104: dbang po dang 'tshams par chos ston par mdo rgyud
NK024(ya)001:8105: la / las gsungs shing / rgya gar gyi bla
NK024(ya)001:8106: ma pan+di ta'i gsung gi gnang ba thob pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:8107: lo ts+aa ba grub pa brnyes pas mdzad pa yin
NK024(ya)001:8108: pas na yid ches kyi gnas yin la /
NK024(ya)001:8109: rgya yig gi dbang bskur ba bzhin bod yig gi
NK024(ya)001:8110: dbang yang bskur bar byed pas na sngar bshad pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8111: dmigs pa rnams kyang gsal 'debs par mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:8114: ka ni dbang byed sgrol ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:8115: zhes pas khams gsum sems can la dbang byed cing nyon mongs pa sgrol bar byed pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:8116: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku don gyi gsung gzugs
NK024(ya)001:8117: brnyan 'byung ba'i tshig gi sgra 'dis kyang sems can
NK024(ya)001:8118: thams cad dbang du byed cing nyon mongs pa las
NK024(ya)001:8119: sgrol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:8120: kha ni khams gsum kun gyi rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:8121: zhes pas khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi rgyan du 'byung ba yin te /
NK024(ya)001:8122: de'i byin rlabs kyis don gyi gsung sgra snyan tshig
NK024(ya)001:8123: 'di sems can gyi rgyan du gyur te 'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:8124: las sgrol pa'i dbang dang ga ni ma chags dag
NK024(ya)001:8125: par mdzad // ces pas dus gsum du chos sku
NK024(ya)001:8126: bde ba chen po ci la'ang ma chags shing rnam
NK024(ya)001:8127: par dag pa yin pas de'i byin rlabs chos sku'i
NK024(ya)001:8128: gsung 'dis kyang 'gro ba rnams ci la yang ma
NK024(ya)001:8129: chags shing rnam par dag pa'i dbang dang nga ni
NK024(ya)001:8131: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK024(ya)001:8132: po mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing
NK024(ya)001:8133: mtshan ma las rgyal ba'i byin rlabs kyis sems can
NK024(ya)001:8134: thams cad chos dbyings mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las
NK024(ya)001:8135: ma g.yos shing mtshan ma las rgyal ba'i dbang dang
NK024(ya)001:8136: ca ni gnyis med don rtogs te //
NK024(ya)001:8137: zhes pa dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK024(ya)001:8138: po de mtshan ma dang mtshan med gnyis su med
NK024(ya)001:8139: pa'i byin rlabs kyis sems can mtshan 'dzin gnyis su
NK024(ya)001:8140: med pa'i dbang dang cha ni thabs dang shes rab
NK024(ya)001:8141: ste // zhes pa chos sku bde ba chen po
NK024(ya)001:8142: las thabs shes gnyis med kyi sprul pa ji snyed
NK024(ya)001:8143: cig byu nga nas 'gro ba'i don byed de /
NK024(ya)001:8144: de'i byin rlabs kyis thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i dbang dang ja ni chos sku dag par mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:8145: ces pas chos sku bag chags kyis ma gos shing
NK024(ya)001:8146: rnam par dag pa'i byin rlabs kyis bu rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:8147: rgyud bag chags kyis ma gos shing dag pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:8148: dang nya ni chos nyid gdar sha gcod //
NK024(ya)001:8149: ces pa chos nyid rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang 'dra
NK024(ya)001:8150: ba la rig pa'i ye shes rlabs dang 'dra bas
NK024(ya)001:8151: gdar sha gcod pa'i byin rlabs kyis bu rnams chos
NK024(ya)001:8152: nyid rgya mtsho las rig pa ye shes kyi byin
NK024(ya)001:8153: rlabs la dbang ba'i dbang dang ta ni mkhas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8154: 'od zer can // zhes pa chos kyi sku las
NK024(ya)001:8155: thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i byin rlabs kyis bu
NK024(ya)001:8156: rnams kyi sems la snying rje'i 'od zer 'byung pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8157: dbang dang tha ni dkon mchog 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:8158: zhes pa drug gsum gyi chos sku bde ba chen
NK024(ya)001:8159: po la dgongs pa zab mo 'byung ba de'i byin
NK024(ya)001:8160: rlabs kyis chos sku'i dgongs pa zab mo'i ye shes
NK024(ya)001:8161: rtogs pa'i dbang dang da ni rgyu 'bras gnyis med
NK024(ya)001:8162: la // zhes pa chos sku bde ba chen po
NK024(ya)001:8163: la rgyu 'bras kyi chos gnyis su med pa'i byin
NK024(ya)001:8164: rlabs kyis chos kyi 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol
NK024(ya)001:8165: te mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang bde ba'i dbang dang
NK024(ya)001:8166: na ni sdug bsngal med pas bde //
NK024(ya)001:8167: zhes pa chos sku bde ba chen po las bde
NK024(ya)001:8168: ba'i ngang rgyun du 'byung ba'i byin rlabs kyi 'khor
NK024(ya)001:8169: ba'i sdug bsngal gtan nas spong ba'i dbang dang pa
NK024(ya)001:8170: ni thams cad bskyed par byed //
NK024(ya)001:8171: ces pa chos sku bde ba chen po rig pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8172: ye shes bskyed pa'i byin rlabs kyis gsung 'di mthong
NK024(ya)001:8173: ba tsam gyis gzhan rig bskyed pa'i dbang dang pha
NK024(ya)001:8174: ni pha rol phyin la gnas //
NK024(ya)001:8175: zhes pas chos sku 'khor ba'i pha rol tu phyin
NK024(ya)001:8176: pa la mi gnas pa'i sa la gnas pa'i byin
NK024(ya)001:8177: rlabs kyis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mthar phyin nas mya
NK024(ya)001:8178: ngan las 'das pa'i dbang dang ba ni bde ba
NK024(ya)001:8179: chen po ste // zhes pas chos sku bde ba
NK024(ya)001:8180: chen po mnyam pa nyid kyi byin rlabs kyis dngos
NK024(ya)001:8181: po dang mtshan ma thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi
NK024(ya)001:8182: dbang dang ma ni srid gsum yongs kyi ma //
NK024(ya)001:8183: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po yongs kyi
NK024(ya)001:8184: gzhi mar gyur pa'i byin rlabs kyis srid pa gsum
NK024(ya)001:8185: las rgyal zhing kun gyi gzhi rten du gyur pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8186: dbang dang tsa ni 'du 'bral med pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:8187: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po sku dang
NK024(ya)001:8188: ye shes stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa
NK024(ya)001:8189: 'du 'bral med pa'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku dang
NK024(ya)001:8190: 'du 'bral med pa'i dbang dang tsha ni don dam
NK024(ya)001:8191: lus la rdzogs // zhes pas don dam chos kyi
NK024(ya)001:8192: sku ni rgyu dang 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs
NK024(ya)001:8193: su rdzogs pa yin te de'i byin rlabs kyis chos
NK024(ya)001:8194: sku'i rgyu 'bras thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:8195: dang dza ni bar ma'i lus la gnas //
NK024(ya)001:8196: zhes pas chos sku las thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung
NK024(ya)001:8197: ba'i byin rlabs kyis thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8198: dbang dang wa ni mya ngan thams cad 'dul //
NK024(ya)001:8199: zhes pa sa chos sku bde ba chen po'i ngang
NK024(ya)001:8200: las 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i byin
NK024(ya)001:8201: rlabs kyis 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8202: dbang dang zha ni gzhal yas khang chen po //
NK024(ya)001:8203: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po thams cad
NK024(ya)001:8204: kyi gnas yin pa'i byin rlabs kyis gzhal yas khang
NK024(ya)001:8205: bde ba chen po'i dbang dang za ni skye med
NK024(ya)001:8206: chos la 'phags // zhes pas chos thams cad rgyu
NK024(ya)001:8207: rkyen las ma skyes pa'i byin rlabs kyis chos nyid
NK024(ya)001:8208: gsal ba'i ye shes ma rig pa'i mun pa sel
NK024(ya)001:8209: ba'i dbang dang 'a ni goms pa'i tshogs la rtson
NK024(ya)001:8210: chos la 'phags // // zhes pas gsung gi tshogs
NK024(ya)001:8211: rang bzhin med pa'i sgra sgrog pa'i dbang dang ya
NK024(ya)001:8212: ni mthar byed pho nya'i bdag /
NK024(ya)001:8213: ces pas gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis kyi 'gro ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8214: don byed pa'i dbang dang ra ni spyod byed yul
NK024(ya)001:8215: la dbang // zhes pas ye shes kyis bcad par
NK024(ya)001:8216: bya ba'i yul nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i dbang dang
NK024(ya)001:8217: la ni mnyam nyid sprul pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:8218: zhes pas chos nyid mnyam pa nyid la sprul pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8219: sku byung nas sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:8220: dang sha ni snang byed mkha' la shar //
NK024(ya)001:8221: zhes pas chos kyi sku la ye shes kyi rol
NK024(ya)001:8222: pa shar nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang
NK024(ya)001:8223: sa ni 'khor ba'i rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:8224: zhes pas thugs la phyag mtshan sna tshogs byung nas
NK024(ya)001:8225: 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang ha ni thabs
NK024(ya)001:8227: zhes pas bde ba chen po'i dbyings nas thabs mkhas
NK024(ya)001:8228: pa'i mdzad spyod bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gro ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8229: don mthar phyin pa'i dbang dang a ni skye med
NK024(ya)001:8230: chos kyi dbyings // zhes pas rgyu rkyen dang bral
NK024(ya)001:8231: ba'i dbyings nas 'gro ba'i don la ma 'gags par
NK024(ya)001:8232: 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK024(ya)001:8233: chos kyi dbyings // cig / nyer gnyis pa lha dbang ni /
NK024(ya)001:8234: de nas lha dbang gi slad du khyed rang rnams
NK024(ya)001:8235: dbang bskur byed kyi lha de dang de'i nga rgyal
NK024(ya)001:8236: rim pa ltar gsal ba la /
NK024(ya)001:8237: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mar me gcig las gnyis chad ltar so sor thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:8238: rnam snang dang tshes kyi lha rnams rim pa bzhin thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:8240: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK024(ya)001:8241: gtso bo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:8242: kun rig rnam par snang mdzad ngan song thams cad
NK024(ya)001:8243: sbyong zhing mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul ster ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:8245: sarba bid a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK024(ya)001:8247: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK024(ya)001:8248: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku mngon par dga' ba'i zhing
NK024(ya)001:8249: khams na bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa sku mdog
NK024(ya)001:8251: g.yon mnyam gzhag mdzad pa'i sku mthong ba'am /
NK024(ya)001:8253: de dran pa tsam gyis sdig sgrib dang ngan 'gro
NK024(ya)001:8254: thams cad sel zhing mtho ris dang thar pa thob
NK024(ya)001:8255: par mdzad pa de'i dbang mchog thob na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8256: mchod 'os rnams kyis mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK024(ya)001:8257: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku stong gi lha rgyal ba
NK024(ya)001:8258: sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu
NK024(ya)001:8259: g.yas sa gnon / g.yon mnyam gzhag lhung bzed can
NK024(ya)001:8260: gang yin pa de nyid kyi sngon sbyin pa'i bsod
NK024(ya)001:8261: nams thob pa las bsngosa te /
NK024(ya)001:8262: bdag mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa na bdag
NK024(ya)001:8263: gi 'khor rnam bzhi 'tsho bas mi brel bar smon
NK024(ya)001:8264: lam grub pa'i byin rlabs kyis stong la bsnyen gnas
NK024(ya)001:8265: bsrungs pas phyogs dus gnas skabs thams cad du mu
NK024(ya)001:8266: ge'i bskal pa las thar pa'i dbang mchog dam pa
NK024(ya)001:8267: thob na mo / mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas
NK024(ya)001:8268: dam pa lha mi'i gtso bo sprul pa'i sku nya'i
NK024(ya)001:8269: lha snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po mnyam
NK024(ya)001:8270: gzhag tshe bum can de nyid kyis thos bsam sgom
NK024(ya)001:8271: pa'i shes rab kyi bsod nams thob pa las bsngosa
NK024(ya)001:8272: thob na mo / te / bdag mngon par rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:8273: par sangs rgyas pa na bdag gi 'khor rnams kyis
NK024(ya)001:8274: bde ba can gyi zhing khams su phyir mi ldog
NK024(ya)001:8275: pa'i 'phags pa thob par smon lam 'grub pa'i byin
NK024(ya)001:8276: rlabs kyis nya la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas phyogs dus
NK024(ya)001:8277: thams cad du mtshon gyi bskal pa las thar pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8278: dbang mchog dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8279: mchod 'os rnams kyi mcho gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK024(ya)001:8280: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku tshes brgyad kyi lha sman
NK024(ya)001:8281: gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po sku mdog
NK024(ya)001:8282: mthing kha g.yas mchog sbyin a ru ra /
NK024(ya)001:8283: g.yon mnyam gzhag lhung bzed can /
NK024(ya)001:8284: smon lam gyi mthu las gang gis bdag gi mtshan lan bdun brjod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8286: tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas phyogs dus thams cad du rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8291: nad kyi bskal pa las thar ba'i dbang mchog dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8292: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam par gyur pa /
NK024(ya)001:8293: nyi ma shar ba shar gyi phyogs /
NK024(ya)001:8294: shar phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK024(ya)001:8295: gang zag chos ldan skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:8296: dri za'i rgyal po yul 'khor srung gi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8297: mchod 'os rnams kyi nyi ma 'phel ba lho yi phyogs /
NK024(ya)001:8298: lho phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK024(ya)001:8299: gang zag chos ldan skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:8300: grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8301: mchod 'os nyi ma bgrod pa nub kyi phyogs /
NK024(ya)001:8302: nub phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK024(ya)001:8303: gang zag chos ldan skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:8304: klu'i rgyal po mig mi bzang gi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8305: mchod 'os nyi ma dbus nas lhun po byang /
NK024(ya)001:8306: byang phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK024(ya)001:8307: gang zag chos slad na skyong bar 'dzam bu'i gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK024(ya)001:8308: gnod sbyin rgyal po rnam thos sras kyi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8309: mchod 'os shar na lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang
NK024(ya)001:8310: btsun mo 'gro ba sems can thams cad la bde
NK024(ya)001:8311: ba ster ba de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8312: mchod 'os shar gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa 'gro
NK024(ya)001:8313: ba kun gyi yid du 'ong ba skye 'gro'i nyon
NK024(ya)001:8314: mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo
NK024(ya)001:8315: / mchod 'os shar gling g.yon na pho nya rab
NK024(ya)001:8316: tu myur ba'i shugs can ngan song gsum gyi sdug
NK024(ya)001:8317: bsngal las sgrol ba de'i dbang dam pa na mo
NK024(ya)001:8318: / / mchod 'os lho 'dzam bu'i gling na lha
NK024(ya)001:8319: tshangs pa dang btsun mo tshangs ma 'dod khams kyi
NK024(ya)001:8321: 'khor ba gyod khrims dang 'dra ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8322: mchod 'os lho gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa 'gro
NK024(ya)001:8323: ba'i yid du 'ong ba nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod
NK024(ya)001:8324: pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8325: mchod 'os lho gling g.yon na pho nya myur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:8326: shugs can ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal las sgrol
NK024(ya)001:8327: ba de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8328: mchod 'os nub na lha khyab 'jug btsun mo dpal
NK024(ya)001:8329: lha mo phrin las kyis kun tu khyab pa de'i
NK024(ya)001:8331: mchod 'os nub gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:8332: rje bde bas nyon mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:8334: mchod 'os nub gling g.yon na pho nya rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:8335: ded dpon 'gro ba la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK024(ya)001:8336: ba de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8337: mchod 'os byang na lha dbang phyug chen po dang
NK024(ya)001:8338: btsun mo dka' thub zlog ma dug gsum 'joms par
NK024(ya)001:8339: byed pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8340: mchod 'os byang gling g.yas na mngag gzhug pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:8341: rje rnon po 'gro ba'i nyon mongs pa gcod par
NK024(ya)001:8342: mdzad pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:8343: mchod 'os byang gling g.yon na pho nya drang srong
NK024(ya)001:8344: khros pa'i cha byad can 'gro ba kun la rnam
NK024(ya)001:8345: par snang ba de'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:8346: cig / ces sum cu rtsa drug po bskur bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:8347: de ltar lha dbang yan chod du sa bcad nyer gnyis yod pa song nas //
NK024(ya)001:8348: lam 'khyer bzhi'i dang po nyer gsum pa theg pa
NK024(ya)001:8349: lam 'khyer la nang gses kyi dang po theg pa
NK024(ya)001:8354: drug pa 'bras bu ste drug tu phye /
NK024(ya)001:8356: nyer lnga pa snying po lam 'khyer /
NK024(ya)001:8357: nyer drug pa bslab bya lam 'khyer te mdor na lam 'khyer la dgur yod pa'i dang po ni /
NK024(ya)001:8359: nyer gsum pa lam 'khyer la bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:8360: theg pa lam 'khyer lha mi'i theg pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:8362: de lta bu'i theg pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK024(ya)001:8364: dang po 'jug sgo chos spyod bcu ste /
NK024(ya)001:8366: yi ge 'dri mchod sbyin pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:8367: nyan dang klog dang 'dzin pa dang //'chad dang kha ton byed pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:8368: de sems pa dang sgom pa ste //'di bcu chos
NK024(ya)001:8369: kyi sgo mo ste //'dren pa rnams kyi gshegs shul
NK024(ya)001:8371: zhes gsungs pas yi ge 'dri ba /
NK024(ya)001:8372: glegs bam la mchod pa 'bul ba /
NK024(ya)001:8373: glegs bam sbyin par gtong ba /
NK024(ya)001:8374: dam pa'i chos nyan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8380: sgom pa ste chos spyod bcu la rtag par 'bad dgos /
NK024(ya)001:8383: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:8385: lus can dag gi las rnams ni //
NK024(ya)001:8386: bskal pa brgyar yang chud mi za //
NK024(ya)001:8387: tshogs shing dus la bab pa na //'bras bu nyid du smin par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8392: bsrung bya ni sgo gsum gyi mi dge ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:8394: lus kyi las ni rnam gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:8395: ngag gi las ni bzhi yin te //
NK024(ya)001:8396: yid kyi rnam pa gsum po dag /
NK024(ya)001:8397: mi dge bcu ni spang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:8399: zhes gsungs pas de lta bu'i lta ba rgyu 'bras
NK024(ya)001:8400: de nyid bsrung bya mi dge bcu spong tshul dang
NK024(ya)001:8404: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa gsum lus kyi las /
NK024(ya)001:8411: log lta gsum yid kyi las /
NK024(ya)001:8412: de yang bskyed pa'i gzhi ni /
NK024(ya)001:8413: dbu ma rin chen phreng ba las /
NK024(ya)001:8414: chags dang zhe sdang gti mug gsum //
NK024(ya)001:8415: des bskyed las ni mi dge ba //
NK024(ya)001:8418: gnod sems gsum zhe sdang gis bskyed cing rdzogs par byed /
NK024(ya)001:8421: brnab sems gsum 'dod chags kyis bskyed cing rdzogs par byed /
NK024(ya)001:8422: log lta gti mug gis bskyed cing rdzogs par byed /
NK024(ya)001:8425: ngag 'khyal rnams dug gsum gis bskyed cing rdzogs par byed pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:8427: gsod dang gnod sems tshig rtsub bo //
NK024(ya)001:8428: zhe sdang gis ni mthar phyin byed //
NK024(ya)001:8429: log g.yem brnab sems ma byin len //
NK024(ya)001:8430: chags pa yis ni rdzogs par byed //
NK024(ya)001:8431: log par lta ba gti mug gis //
NK024(ya)001:8432: lhag ma gsum gyis rdzogs par 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:8434: de ltar bskyed pa'i las de rnams spyad pa'i 'bras bu la //
NK024(ya)001:8437: bdag po'am dbang gi 'bras bu ste bzhi las /
NK024(ya)001:8438: gnas skabs ni rin chen phreng bar /
NK024(ya)001:8439: gsod pa yis ni tshe thung 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8440: brkus pa yis ni longs spyod 'phongs //
NK024(ya)001:8441: byi bo byed pa'ang dgra dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:8442: rdzun du smras pas bskur pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:8443: phra ma yis ni bshes dang dbye //
NK024(ya)001:8444: rtsub po nyid kyis mi snyan thos //
NK024(ya)001:8445: ma 'dres pa yis tshig mi btsun //
NK024(ya)001:8446: brnab sems yid la re ba 'joms //
NK024(ya)001:8447: gnod sems 'jigs pa sbyin par bshad //
NK024(ya)001:8448: log par lta bas lta ngan nyid //
NK024(ya)001:8449: ces gsungs pa gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu'am mthong chos kyi 'bras bur grags la /
NK024(ya)001:8450: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bur myong ba rgyu mthun dang /
NK024(ya)001:8451: byed pa rgyu mthun gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:8454: gal te mir skyes kyang mi dge bcu kho nar spyod par skye bar bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:8455: mthar thug gi 'bras bu ni chen pos dmyal ba /
NK024(ya)001:8458: bdag po'i 'bras bu ni phyi rol gyi yul la smin te /
NK024(ya)001:8459: tha na dud 'gror skyis kyang r+ts+wa chu dkon zhing ches sdug bsngal ba'i rigs rnams yin par bshad /
NK024(ya)001:8460: de'i ldog pa dge ba bcu ni la la dag chos spyod bcu dang gcig par smra yang /
NK024(ya)001:8461: de rnams gsung rab kyi go don tsam yang ma chags pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:8462: chos spyod bcu ni gong du theg pa'i ngo bo'i skabs bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK024(ya)001:8463: dge ba bcu ni lus kyi sgo nas srog mi gcod /
NK024(ya)001:8466: ngag gi sgo nas rdzun mi smra /
NK024(ya)001:8470: yid kyi sgo nas brnab sems mi bya /
NK024(ya)001:8473: de yang bskyed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK024(ya)001:8475: ma chags zhe sdang gti mug med //
NK024(ya)001:8476: des bskyed pa ni dge ba yin //
NK024(ya)001:8477: zhes gsungs pas zhe sdang med pas srog gcod /
NK024(ya)001:8479: gnod sems las ldog /'dod chags med pas ma byin len /
NK024(ya)001:8482: gti mug med pas log lta las ldog /
NK024(ya)001:8483: gsum ga med pas rdzun phra ma ngag 'khyal rnams
NK024(ya)001:8484: las ldog /'bras bu yang gnas skabs mthar thug rgyu
NK024(ya)001:8486: gnas skabs sam myong ba rgyu mthun ni /
NK024(ya)001:8487: srog gcod spangs pas tshe ring ba sogs gong gi 'gros kyis shes par nus pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:8488: byed pa rgyu mthun ni mir gyur na dge bcu la goms 'dris spyod par skye ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:8492: tha mas dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob par bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:8493: de'i rkyen lha mi mtho ris kyi yul du skye
NK024(ya)001:8494: bas bdag po'i 'bras bu ni phyi rol gyi yul
NK024(ya)001:8495: la smin te / mir skyes kyang yul phun sum tshogs par skye ba lta bu'o //
NK024(ya)001:8496: de ltar rgyu sngon song gi 'bras bu mthar thug gnyis kyis mi dge bas ngan 'gro /
NK024(ya)001:8497: dge bas mtho ris su skye bar 'gyur te /
NK024(ya)001:8500: mi dge las ni sdug bsngal kun //
NK024(ya)001:8501: de bzhin ngan 'gro thams cad do //
NK024(ya)001:8504: sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal ngan song gsum /
NK024(ya)001:8505: 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal lha dang lha ma yin mi gsum gyi 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:8506: 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal spyi mthun du snang ba dang gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:8509: yang sos thig nag bsdus 'joms dang //
NK024(ya)001:8511: tsha ba rab tsha mnar med brgyad //
NK024(ya)001:8513: chu bur chu bur brdol ba can //
NK024(ya)001:8514: a chu so tham kyi hud pa //
NK024(ya)001:8516: zhes sdug bsngal gyi rnam pa de lta bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:8517: de rnams kyi tshe'i tshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:8519: yang sos la sogs drug rim bzhin //'dod lha'i tshe dang nyin zhag mnyam //
NK024(ya)001:8520: zhes gsungs pas tsha ba'i bar dang /
NK024(ya)001:8521: rab tu tsha phyed mnar med ni //
NK024(ya)001:8523: zhes gsungs pas rab tsha la bar bskal phyed /
NK024(ya)001:8524: mnar med la bar bskal lo //
NK024(ya)001:8526: til rdzang nas ni lo brgya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:8527: til cig phyungs pas zad gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:8528: chu bur can gyi tshe yin te //
NK024(ya)001:8529: gzhan gyi tshe ni nyi shus bsgyur //
NK024(ya)001:8530: zhes grang dmyal gyi tshe tshad dang /
NK024(ya)001:8531: tsha dmyal dang 'dab 'byor du nye 'khor ba rnams gnas te /
NK024(ya)001:8536: ral gri lo ma'i nags tshal rnams te /
NK024(ya)001:8538: brgyad po kun la lhag bcu drug /
NK024(ya)001:8539: de dag gi ni ngos bzhi na //
NK024(ya)001:8540: me mar mur dang ro myags dang //
NK024(ya)001:8541: spu gri lam sogs chu bo yin //
NK024(ya)001:8543: de yang spu gri'i lam sogs kyi sogs khongs nas mtshon cha'i rigs su gcig pas bsdus te /
NK024(ya)001:8545: shal ma li'i sdong po rnams bstan /
NK024(ya)001:8546: chu bo zhes pas thal tshan gyi chu bo rab med bstan pa yin zhes gsung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:8547: nyi tshe ba ni bshes springs las /
NK024(ya)001:8548: kha cig lcags las byas pa'i zangs chen du //
NK024(ya)001:8549: spyi'i tshugs 'bras kyi cung beng bzhin du 'tshed //
NK024(ya)001:8551: de bzhin gzhan dag khro chu bzhus pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:8552: khu ba 'bar ba 'khrigs pa btung bar bgyid //
NK024(ya)001:8554: gzhan yang 'dul lung nas gsungs pa'i thag pa lta bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:8556: gtun lta bu sogs rang rang gi rgyu sngon song
NK024(ya)001:8557: gi 'bras bu sna tshogs mtha' gcig tu ma nges
NK024(ya)001:8559: mdor na de 'dra'i sdug bsngal bzod par dka' ba'i dpe ni /
NK024(ya)001:8561: 'di na nyin gcig mdung thung sum brgya yis //
NK024(ya)001:8562: rab tu drag btab sdug bsngal gang lags pa //
NK024(ya)001:8563: des ni dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal chung ngu'i yang //'ol yang mi bgyi char yang mi phod do //
NK024(ya)001:8565: de bzhin du yi dwags kyang phyi'i sgrib pa can zhes zas skom mi rnyed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8566: nang gi sgrib pa can zhes pa zas skom ngan
NK024(ya)001:8567: ngon rnyed kyang slar yang sdug bsngal du 'gyur ba
NK024(ya)001:8568: dang / sgrib pa can gyi sgrib pa can nam zas skom gyi sgrib pa can /
NK024(ya)001:8570: mkha' la rgyu ba byings na gnas pa sogs mang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:8572: yi dwags la rigs drug cu rtsa bzhi yod par gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:8573: sdug bsngal yang bshes springs las /
NK024(ya)001:8574: yi dwags rnams la sos ka'i dus su ni //
NK024(ya)001:8575: zla ba'ang tsha la dgun ni nyi ma'ang grang //
NK024(ya)001:8576: ljon shing grib ma med 'gyur 'di dag gis //
NK024(ya)001:8577: ltas pa tsam gyis klung yang skams par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8578: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:8580: zla ba nyin zhag gi lnga brgya //
NK024(ya)001:8581: zhes gsungs pas mi'i zla ba la yi dwags kyi zhag gcig tu brtsis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8583: nyes par spyad pa'i las kyi zhags pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:8584: sra bas bcings pa'i lus can kha cig ni //
NK024(ya)001:8585: lnga stong dag dang khrir yang 'chi mi 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8586: zhes gsungs pa ni mi lor brtsis pa'i tshe tshad do //
NK024(ya)001:8587: dud 'gro yang rgya mtsho'i byings na gnas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8588: gling bar gyi mun pa na gnas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8589: kha 'thor pa sogs so sor las mthun gyi sdug bsngal mang la /
NK024(ya)001:8590: klu yang dud 'gror bsdu bas na tshe'i tshad kyang
NK024(ya)001:8591: 'jog po la sogs bskal par yang gnas pa dang
NK024(ya)001:8592: / de bzhin du la la lo mang po dang /
NK024(ya)001:8593: la la zhag gcig tsam la 'chi ba sogs mtha' yas te /
NK024(ya)001:8595: dud 'gro rnams mchog ring bskal pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:8597: sdug bsngal ni bshes springs las /
NK024(ya)001:8598: dud 'groo'i skye gnas na yang gsod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:8599: bcing dang rdeg sogs sdug bsngal sna tshogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:8600: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:8601: de ltar sdug bsngal gyi sdug bsngal bstan nas //
NK024(ya)001:8602: gnyis pa 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal ni /
NK024(ya)001:8603: mi la skye rgas na 'chi'i sdug bsngal bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:8607: skyes pa'i mtha' ma 'chi ba sogs rang re rnams
NK024(ya)001:8608: kyis myong bas grub cing tshe'i tshad kyang de dang
NK024(ya)001:8609: mtshungs / lha ma yin rnams lha'i dpal 'byor la
NK024(ya)001:8610: phrag dog gis brtag par 'thab rtsod kho nas brel
NK024(ya)001:8612: 'dod lha rnams bde skyid longs spyod phun sum tshogs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:8614: stan la mi dga' me tog phreng rnying dang //
NK024(ya)001:8615: gos la dri ma chags dang lus las ni //
NK024(ya)001:8616: sngon chad med pa'i rdul 'byung zhes bya ba //
NK024(ya)001:8617: mtho rus 'chi 'pho sbran byed snga ltas lnga //
NK024(ya)001:8619: drang srong rgyas pas zhus pa'i mdo las gsungs pa'i nye ba'i 'chi ltas lnga sogs byung ste /
NK024(ya)001:8620: 'pho ltung gi sdug bsngal che bar gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:8622: brgya byin 'jig rten mchod 'os gyur nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:8623: lam gyi dbang gis phyir yang sa steng lhung //'khor
NK024(ya)001:8624: los sgyur rgyal nyid du gyur nas kyang //'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:8625: dag tu yang bran nyid du 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8626: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa rnams 'gyur ba'i sdug bsngal yin /
NK024(ya)001:8627: gzugs dang gzugs med kyi lha la'ang bya nam mkha'
NK024(ya)001:8628: la 'phur ba slar yang sa la lhungs pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:8629: sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin las ma 'das par bshad
NK024(ya)001:8630: / khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal ni /
NK024(ya)001:8633: lag mthil spu nyag bzhag pa na //
NK024(ya)001:8634: mi bde ba dang sdug bsngal med //
NK024(ya)001:8635: de nyid mig tu bcug pa na //
NK024(ya)001:8636: mi bde ba dang sdug bsngal bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:8637: byis pa lag mthil 'dra ba yis //'du byed sdug
NK024(ya)001:8638: bsngal spu mi rtogs //'phags pa mig dang 'dra ba
NK024(ya)001:8639: yis //'di dag gzigs nas thugs phyung mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:8640: ces dpe don sbyar te bshad pa'i khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal ni /
NK024(ya)001:8641: 'dod pas tshims pa med pa'i sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:8642: skye shis sun pa med pa'i sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:8643: las la zin pa med pa'i sdug bsngal dang gsum
NK024(ya)001:8644: yin par 'chad pa'i dang po ni bshes springs las
NK024(ya)001:8645: / re res rgya mtsho bzhi bas lhag pa yi //'o ma 'thung ste da dung so so yi //
NK024(ya)001:8646: skye bo'i rjes su 'brang ba'i 'khor ba pas //
NK024(ya)001:8647: de bas ches mang snyed cig btang 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:8651: re re'i bdag nyid rus pa'i phung po ni //
NK024(ya)001:8652: lhun po mnyam pa snyed cig 'das gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:8653: ma yi thug mtha' rgya shug tshig gu tsam //
NK024(ya)001:8654: ri lur bgrangs kyang sa yi lang mi 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:8657: zhing pa rnams lo re bzhin zhing las mi zin pa /
NK024(ya)001:8658: tshong pa rnams kyang rtag par tshong mi zin pa
NK024(ya)001:8659: lta bus mtshon rang rang gi las kyi mtha' ma
NK024(ya)001:8660: shi'i bar du mi zin pa lta bu'o //
NK024(ya)001:8661: de ltar sdug bsngal gsum ni mi dge ba'i las
NK024(ya)001:8662: kyi mthar thug rdzogs byed kyi 'bras bu yin la
NK024(ya)001:8663: / dge ba'i las kyi mthar thug gam rdzogs byed
NK024(ya)001:8664: kyi 'bras bu ni gong du bshad pa ltar ro
NK024(ya)001:8665: / // mdor na chos kyi snying po las 'bras
NK024(ya)001:8666: kho na zab cing mi bslu bar yid ches dgos
NK024(ya)001:8668: las rnams bskal pa brgyar yang ni //
NK024(ya)001:8669: chud mi za bar tshogs dang dus //
NK024(ya)001:8670: rnyed na lus can rnams la ni //'bras bu dag tu 'gyur ba nyid //
NK024(ya)001:8672: blang dor bya tshul mdor bsdu na /
NK024(ya)001:8673: so sor thar pa'i tshigs su bcad pa las /
NK024(ya)001:8674: sdig pa ci yang mi bya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:8675: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad //
NK024(ya)001:8676: ces gsungs pa ltar yongs 'dzin dam pa bsten nas
NK024(ya)001:8677: phra zhing phra ba'i las 'bras la blang dor zhib
NK024(ya)001:8679: yid ches pa'i phyir du mdo sde zab mo rnams klog cing bsam par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:8680: rtsa ba'i sa bcad theg pa lam 'khyer las lta
NK024(ya)001:8681: ba dang bsrung bya'i 'phros don bye brag tu bshad
NK024(ya)001:8682: zin to // bzhi pa ting 'dzin ni /
NK024(ya)001:8686: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:8687: tshangs gnas la sogs rim par skye ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:8690: spyir tshad med bzhi bsgoms pas tshangs gnas bzhir skyo ba'i rgyu ste /
NK024(ya)001:8691: rgyud sde las tshangs pa'i gnas pa bzhi sgom par gsungs pa yin la /
NK024(ya)001:8694: sems can rnams la brtse ba can //'phrad dang bral ba'i dgongs pa can //
NK024(ya)001:8695: mi 'bral ba yi dgongs pa can //
NK024(ya)001:8696: phan bde dgongs khyod la phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:8698: sems can rnams la brtse ba can //'phrad dang zhes
NK024(ya)001:8699: pa yan chad bde ba dang 'phrad 'dod kyi byams
NK024(ya)001:8700: pa tshad med / bral ba'i dgongs pa can ni
NK024(ya)001:8701: sdug bsngal dang bral 'dod kyi snying rje tshad med
NK024(ya)001:8702: pa tshad med / / mi 'bral ba'i dgongs pa
NK024(ya)001:8703: can ni bde ba dang ldan pa rnams mi 'bral
NK024(ya)001:8704: bar 'dod pa'i dga' ba tshad med /
NK024(ya)001:8705: phan bde dgongs ni nye ring gi mtha' gnyis su
NK024(ya)001:8706: ma lhung ba ste btang snyoms tshad med yin par
NK024(ya)001:8707: bshad pas mngon mtho'i rgyu tshad med pa bzhi yin
NK024(ya)001:8708: la / de ltar sgom dgos par bshes springs las /
NK024(ya)001:8709: byams dang snying rje dge dang dga' ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:8710: btang snyoms rtag tu yang dag sgoms mdzod cig /
NK024(ya)001:8713: tshangs dang 'od gsal dag dang dge rgyas dang /
NK024(ya)001:8714: 'bras bu che lha rnams dang skal mnyam thob //
NK024(ya)001:8716: rgyas par ni byang sdom gyi skabs su 'brel bar sems so //
NK024(ya)001:8718: rtsa bar dge ba bcu ci nus kyis bsgrub ste /
NK024(ya)001:8719: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa //'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:8721: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong du rgyas par bshad zin pa ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:8724: 'bras bu ni lha mi'i go 'phang thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:8725: zhes gsungs pa'i don shes par sla bas ma spros so //
NK024(ya)001:8726: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer bzhi pa lha lam 'khyer ni /
NK024(ya)001:8727: rtsa bar mngon rtogs 'dir skabs su bshad mod kyang
NK024(ya)001:8728: gong du bdag mdun sgrub mchod kyi skabs su rgyas
NK024(ya)001:8729: par bshad zin pas der lta zhing /
NK024(ya)001:8730: 'on kyang slob ma rnams lha ngo 'phrod par bya
NK024(ya)001:8731: ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor so so'i lha rnams mngon rtogs
NK024(ya)001:8733: mdor na deng nas lha de rnams dran zhing de dag gi bka' las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:8734: nyer lnga pa snying po lam 'khyer ni /
NK024(ya)001:8735: rnam snang gi rtsa rig durga /
NK024(ya)001:8736: mi 'khrugs pa'i las sgrib rnam sbyong kam ka ni /
NK024(ya)001:8738: snang ba mtha' yas kyi gzungs la rtsa bar pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:8739: ta kri ta bshad kyang pad+ma mthar byed ces khro
NK024(ya)001:8740: bo'i sngags su 'dug pas 'dir spyi ltar du pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:8742: sman bla'i b+hee sha dz+ye rnams ci nus su bzla zhing /
NK024(ya)001:8744: sngags mi shes na skyabs 'gro bya'i zhes gsungs pas
NK024(ya)001:8745: snying po phal cher lha'i mtshan nas 'bod pa'i tshul
NK024(ya)001:8746: yin pas sngags mi shes na mtshan nas bos te
NK024(ya)001:8747: skyabs su 'gro bar byas kyang chog ste /
NK024(ya)001:8748: rdo rje gur gyi rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:8749: mkha' 'gro ma dang rang btsun mo //
NK024(ya)001:8750: mngon sum du ni bya ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:8751: sngags ni snyan gsan dbab par brjod //
NK024(ya)001:8752: dper na skyes bu la la dag /
NK024(ya)001:8753: skad kyi nga ros bos pa na //
NK024(ya)001:8755: de bzhin de bzhin gshegs kun gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:8757: lha de rnams kyi mtshan nas brjod cing skyabs su mchi'o phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:8758: zhes pa lta bu sbyar te brjod pas snying po lam 'khyer gyi go chod /
NK024(ya)001:8761: bslab bya ni mi chos bcu drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:8763: dkon mchog gsum la dad pa skyo ngal med par byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8764: don dam par dam pa'i chos btsal ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8765: gtsug lag bzang po la mkhas par slob pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8766: ci la'ang dran cing tshod zin par bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8767: ma bcol ba'i las la gtogs 'dod mi byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8768: mig mtho sar blta zhing gong ma rnams kyi rjes snyed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8769: dus gsum gyi pha ma la drin lan slan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8770: phu nu dang pha tshan nang du shong yangs che ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8771: rim pas rgan pa la bkur sti bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8772: khyim tshes la byams par bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8773: gnyer grogs kyi dge bshes la dka' las kyi phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8774: srid kyis 'brel ba'i nye ring la chab gang mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8775: rig byed bzo la mkhas pas gzan la phan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8776: ltos pa'i mi drin gyis skyabs 'og tu gzhug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:8777: ngan byed kyi gros bkag la rgyal khams bde yangs kyi gros gzhi 'ding ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:8778: las mtha' chos la gtad de phyi mar bu smad kyis byang chub kyi gzhi thob par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:8779: de ltar gang nus khas len du gzhug go //
NK024(ya)001:8780: zhes gsungs pas na 'di rnams skye bo spyi mthun
NK024(ya)001:8781: kho na la nye bar mkho zhing bslab bya'i do
NK024(ya)001:8782: ther 'dug pas de dag thams cad dam /
NK024(ya)001:8783: gang nus la slob par bya dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:8784: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer bdun pa la nang gses kyi phye na drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:8787: gnas chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram /
NK024(ya)001:8788: ston pa thub pa chen po /
NK024(ya)001:8789: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' don grub /
NK024(ya)001:8792: dgos pa 'jig rten pa'i bya ba las 'das pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:8793: de'ang mtshan nyid kyi theg pa la mtshams sbyor ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:8795: gang gis gang la ci phyir gang dgos pa //'di ni lha mi'i theg pa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK024(ya)001:8799: nyer brgyad pa ngang sgom ni /
NK024(ya)001:8800: khrid du byed na ming ngang sgom chung ngu /
NK024(ya)001:8802: dpe gar spyin la sbrang ma zin pa lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:8803: shes pa snga phyi'i 'khrul thag chod pa gnad /
NK024(ya)001:8804: sems nang du zin pa srog /
NK024(ya)001:8805: phyi snang ba 'phrang ste gol ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:8806: de'ang dang por rten can la bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:8807: de nas ci la'ang rten mi bca'/
NK024(ya)001:8810: sems rang sor ma dkrogs pa'i ri dwags ltar ram /
NK024(ya)001:8812: 'ben phigs pa'i mda' lta bur bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:8813: zhib tu bkrol na bag gsar ltar lus glod /
NK024(ya)001:8814: gar sbyin sbrang ma lta bur dbugs glod /
NK024(ya)001:8815: snga phyir mi 'khrul ba sems glod pa de 'gyu ba nang du zin pa'i sems kyi rang gzugs /
NK024(ya)001:8816: stong nyid ngos zin pa srog /
NK024(ya)001:8817: sems yul du snang ba khams gsum sa dgu ste 'phrang /
NK024(ya)001:8818: rang snang stong pa'i rtsal du shar ba de stong
NK024(ya)001:8819: pa'i rang gzugs su ma shes pas chags sdang gi
NK024(ya)001:8820: blang dor byas pas ngan song gsum du skye ba
NK024(ya)001:8821: gol ba'o // de'ang lam rim las /
NK024(ya)001:8822: 'jig rten dang po bsam gtan bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:8825: zhes pas sa gcig pa 'dod khams dang /
NK024(ya)001:8826: gzugs khams bsam gtan dang po /
NK024(ya)001:8830: snyoms 'jug gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi ste dagu'o //
NK024(ya)001:8831: sems dwangs gsal 'dzin med sa dgur bskyed kyang mi 'ching ste /
NK024(ya)001:8834: zhen med chos sku spyod par bshad //
NK024(ya)001:8835: des ni lha mi'i ngang sgom bstan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:8837: de rnams kyi don ni brgyud pa rin po che 'di'i lugs la /
NK024(ya)001:8838: rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po yab sras kyi
NK024(ya)001:8839: mdo dbang khrid du 'chad pa'i dgongs pa zhes zla
NK024(ya)001:8840: ba gsum tsam nges par mdzad pa'i rgyun 'dug pa
NK024(ya)001:8841: dang / lam 'di yang bstan pa yongs rdzogs kyi
NK024(ya)001:8842: nyams len du 'dug pas gsung rab thams cad gdams
NK024(ya)001:8843: par 'char bzhin byed pa gal che bas dpon slob
NK024(ya)001:8844: gnyis kas rnam g.yeng rgyun bcad de dbang khrid sbrags
NK024(ya)001:8846: deng sang ni spyir gal chung chos su byed pa'i
NK024(ya)001:8847: dbang gis dam pa'i chos la thos 'dun chung ba
NK024(ya)001:8848: dang / gal te thos par 'dod pa rnams kyang
NK024(ya)001:8849: thob lo dang thob grags go skam la thig pas
NK024(ya)001:8850: bsnun pa lta bu des go gcod par mthong bas
NK024(ya)001:8851: mang du smras kyang dgos pa chung ngur bas te
NK024(ya)001:8852: dang / / bu ston rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:8853: bdag gi chos min smra ru chos dang 'gal //
NK024(ya)001:8854: chos bzhin byas na bod rnams dgra ru ldang //
NK024(ya)001:8855: ci yang ma smras kun gyis blun zhes brnyas //
NK024(ya)001:8856: kye ma da ni bdag gis ji ltar bya //
NK024(ya)001:8857: zhes gsungs pa'i don kho na'i thog tu bab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:8858: 'on kyang bla ma dang chos la the tshom med
NK024(ya)001:8859: pa'i dad 'dun che zhing 'khor ba las nges par
NK024(ya)001:8860: 'byung 'dod dang byang chub kho na don du gnyer
NK024(ya)001:8861: na chos kyi rtsa ba sems kho na 'dul dgos
NK024(ya)001:8862: te / rang gi sems ni yongs su dul //'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:8865: khyod kyi thugs dul mdzod cig bcom ldan gyis //
NK024(ya)001:8866: sems ni chos kyi rtsa ba lags par gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:8867: zhes gsungs pas thabs du ma'i sgo nas sems thog tu phebs pa zhig gal che bar gda' zhing /
NK024(ya)001:8868: chos kyi dgos pa rang rgyud 'dul ba las gzhan med pas /
NK024(ya)001:8869: de yang gdams ngag khyad par can la rag las shing ji ltar bya na /
NK024(ya)001:8871: dang po rten can la bzhag de nas ci la'ang rten mi bca'/
NK024(ya)001:8872: zhes gsungs pas dben par lus rnam snang gi chos bdun dang ldan pas /
NK024(ya)001:8873: rang gi mdun du rde'u dang shing bu la sogs
NK024(ya)001:8874: che chung 'tshams pa mig la mi gnod pa'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:8876: rnam rtog gi 'phro 'du nyung ba'i phyir bzo dbyibs sna tshogs ma yin pa zhig bzhag ste /
NK024(ya)001:8877: las dang po'i skabs 'dir sems dus gsum gyi rtog pa'i 'phro 'du thams cad cham skyur la /
NK024(ya)001:8878: mig gzhan du mi 'gyur zhing yid mig lhan cig tu dmigs rten gyi steng du lhod kyis 'jog /
NK024(ya)001:8879: de ltar bzhag pa'i tshe rnam rtog gi 'phro 'du ji ltar 'dug legs par brtags la /
NK024(ya)001:8880: mang por 'phro na dmigs rten gyi steng du hril
NK024(ya)001:8881: bsdus la lhod kyis bzhag /'phro 'du nyung na dran
NK024(ya)001:8882: pa'i rgya bskyed la grims par byas te blta /
NK024(ya)001:8883: des skyo na dmigs rten la ched kyis mi blta bar shes pa rang babs su lhod de 'jog /
NK024(ya)001:8884: yang rten can du 'jog pa sogs res mos kyi sgom /
NK024(ya)001:8885: mdor na mdo sde las bshad pa'i sems gnas du
NK024(ya)001:8886: ma'i sgo nas kyang zhi gnas kyi gnas cha btsal
NK024(ya)001:8887: / 'di nas sgom gyi gzhi bcas te mthar rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:8888: chen a ti yo ga'i dbang gi tshe lta ba
NK024(ya)001:8889: ngo sprod pa yin pas legs par bsgom mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:8891: las dang po par sems gnas kyi rgyas bshad mang
NK024(ya)001:8892: na mgo 'khor te sgom gyi gegs byed pas dmigs
NK024(ya)001:8894: mkhas pa'i rigs la lung rigs kyi sgo nas so
NK024(ya)001:8895: so'i rigs dang sbyar ba'i bcad sgom gyi bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:8896: byed pa'o // de yan chod kyi 'jig rten lha mi'i theg pa'i 'jug sgo bsnyen gnas dang /
NK024(ya)001:8897: dngos gzhi dbang khrid thams cad legs par grub pa
NK024(ya)001:8898: yin pas de las bshad pa'i bslab bya sogs legs
NK024(ya)001:8899: par srung snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:8902: deng nas brtsams te sogs rjes chos gsum phyag rdor ltar bya /
NK024(ya)001:8903: de'i dge ba sems can la bsngo bar zhu /
NK024(ya)001:8904: bsod nams 'di yis thams cad gzigs pa nyid //
NK024(ya)001:8907: de nas gong du bstan pa'i cho gas cha gsum btang /
NK024(ya)001:8908: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod bstod bya /
NK024(ya)001:8910: 'jam dbyangs yab sras kyi mchan bur /
NK024(ya)001:8911: rjes ye d+har bzlas shing shis pa brjod /
NK024(ya)001:8913: mchod pa bsang sbyang mchod bstod yig brgya brjod /
NK024(ya)001:8916: spyod lam ci bder bya gsung /
NK024(ya)001:8917: zhes 'byung bas cha gsum gong du grub pas 'dir mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:8918: dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:8919: mdun bskyed sgrub mchod skabs kyi mchod phreng rgyas pa'am
NK024(ya)001:8920: bsdu na sngags mchod dang bstod pa yang rgyas bsdus
NK024(ya)001:8921: des rigs 'gre / rdo rje sems dpa'i yi ge brgya pa lan gsum gyis lhag chad kha bskang /
NK024(ya)001:8922: ma 'byor ba dang nyams pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:8923: zhes sogs kyi tshigs su bcad pas bzod par gsol /
NK024(ya)001:8924: tsakli yod pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i ye shes pa rnams tsaklira brtan bzhugs kyi slad du /
NK024(ya)001:8925: 'dir ni gzugs dang lhan cig tu //
NK024(ya)001:8926: zhes sogs kyi tshigs bcad dang /
NK024(ya)001:8927: su pra tish+tha'i sngags kyis me tog gtor zhing brtan par bzhugs /
NK024(ya)001:8928: dam tshig pa rnams dang rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor rten med pa'i lha rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:8929: khyod kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:8930: ces sogs kyi tshigs bcad dang lhan du se gol gtog cing gshegs gsol bya /
NK024(ya)001:8931: slob dpon gyi rdo rjes dbang ldan nas brtsam ste tshon rnams bsdu /
NK024(ya)001:8933: bdag bskyed kyi ye shes pa yang badz+ra muh sa gshegs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:8934: nyer dgu pa smon lam ni /
NK024(ya)001:8935: rtsa bar thog mar bkra shis dang mjug tu bsngo smon byung kyang smon lam 'dir len /
NK024(ya)001:8937: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK024(ya)001:8938: zhes gsungs pas bzang po spyod pa la sogs pa'i smon lam rnam par dag pa btab /
NK024(ya)001:8939: sum cu pa bkra shis ni /
NK024(ya)001:8940: rtsa bar bkra shis brjod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:8941: ston mchog dam pa sogs gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:8942: stong chen rab 'joms nas gsungs pa ltar /
NK024(ya)001:8943: ston mchog dam pa lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK024(ya)001:8944: sangs rgyas phyag 'tshal deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:8945: sems can gang dag 'gro dang mi 'gro ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:8946: de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:8947: zhi ba chags bral lha mi'i mchod 'os pa //
NK024(ya)001:8948: chos la phyag 'tshal sems can gang dag de dag
NK024(ya)001:8949: thams cad tshogs kyi mchog rab lha mi'i mchod 'os
NK024(ya)001:8950: pa // dge 'dun phyag 'tshal sems can gang dag de dag thams cad deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:8952: gzhan yang bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa ci rigs brjod cing /
NK024(ya)001:8953: rten 'brel snying pos me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:8955: nub mo zhi khro'i phrin las tshogs bskang bya ba sogs snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK024(ya)001:8956: legs byas mngon mtho'i khang brtsegs dam pa der //
NK024(ya)001:8957: lha mi'i lam gyi them skas la brten nas //
NK024(ya)001:8958: bgrod byed cho ga'i nor bu grangs mang po //
NK024(ya)001:8959: khrigs chags srad bur brgyus 'di dpyod ldan rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:8960: gang zhig mchog dman bar ma'i skye bo kun //
NK024(ya)001:8961: nges legs rin chen gling der rab bkri ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:8962: bsnyen gnas sa bon dge bcu'i drod gsher gyis //
NK024(ya)001:8963: byang chub 'bras bur smin byed thabs 'di zab //'di phyi'i gtan 'dun grub ste dkon mchog gsum //
NK024(ya)001:8964: lhag pa'i lhar brten chos spyod bsags sbyangs kyi //
NK024(ya)001:8965: bzlas brjod zhi lhag zung 'jug ting 'dzin sogs //
NK024(ya)001:8966: rnam mang lam gyi 'jug tshul 'di rmad byung //
NK024(ya)001:8967: zhes bya ba ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad
NK024(ya)001:8968: pa'o////de nas gnyis pa nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor sgrub
NK024(ya)001:8970: dkyil 'khor bya zhing mchod pa bsham //
NK024(ya)001:8971: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:8972: dpang skor khrus byas sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:8973: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzeg ston pa bsgom //
NK024(ya)001:8974: tshul khrims ldan pa'i bum dbang la //
NK024(ya)001:8975: gso sbyong tshul khrims btsun chas lha //
NK024(ya)001:8976: gsol gdab sdom pa bslab bya dpog /
NK024(ya)001:8977: chos bshad dbang bskur dang lam 'khyer //
NK024(ya)001:8978: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang //
NK024(ya)001:8979: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyir dgos //
NK024(ya)001:8980: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:8981: zhes don sum cus bstan pa'i dang po dkyil 'khor la gsum yin te /
NK024(ya)001:8983: dang po dkyil 'khor lo gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:8985: e yam ram wam lam zhes pas mkha' rlung me
NK024(ya)001:8986: chu sa'i dkyil 'khor rim brtsegs kyi sa'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:8988: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi thems brgyad kyi
NK024(ya)001:8989: gnyis pa yan chad la nyan thos rgyu la gnas
NK024(ya)001:8990: pa / rgyan gyi rta babs gnyis pa man chad
NK024(ya)001:8991: la nyan thos 'bras bu la gnas pa 'god pa'o
NK024(ya)001:8992: pa / // gsum pa bri ba la lnga ste /
NK024(ya)001:8993: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa gnyis dang nang du 'dab bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:8998: de rnams kyi lte ba ser /
NK024(ya)001:9003: 'du shes bcu ldan nyan thos rnams //
NK024(ya)001:9006: de'i don ni gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gnas tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:9008: de ltar bri ba'i tshul dang gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po gzhi'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK024(ya)001:9009: 'byung ba rim brtsegs kyi sa'i dkyil 'khor la nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor gnas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9010: gnyis pa ni tshogs chen 'dus pa'i rta babs brgyad
NK024(ya)001:9011: kyi gnyis pa la nyan thos rgyu dang 'bras bu
NK024(ya)001:9012: la gnas pa rnams rim pa bzhin 'god do //
NK024(ya)001:9013: gsum pa bris pa'i dkyil 'khor ni rtsa bar lnga
NK024(ya)001:9014: gsungs kyang 'dra mnan pa'i tshe 'dab bzhi pa gnyis
NK024(ya)001:9015: dang / nang du 'dab bzhi de'i phyir brgyad pa
NK024(ya)001:9016: nyis sbrags yod pa gnyis te bzhir nges kyang lha
NK024(ya)001:9017: lam 'khyer gyi dus gtso bor ston pa la dus
NK024(ya)001:9019: dus chen gyi lha gsum ste drug gis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor gcig kyang bshad pas lngar 'gyur /
NK024(ya)001:9020: kahthoga pa rnams kyi zin bris su snga ma bzhi bri bya yin la /
NK024(ya)001:9021: phyi ma 'di tshogs zhing gi dkyil 'khor yin pas mi 'dra zer /
NK024(ya)001:9022: zur lugs kahthoga lugs gnyis ka'i dkyil 'khor rnying pa
NK024(ya)001:9023: rnams la nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor dbus su pad
NK024(ya)001:9024: 'dab bzhi'i phyir brgyad yod pa gcig kho na bris
NK024(ya)001:9025: 'dug la / de mtshungs kahthoga rdor bzang gi chog khrigs su yang bshad mod /
NK024(ya)001:9026: 'on kyang rtsa ba'i sa bcad dang po'i nang sems gsum pa bris pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:9027: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bco brgyad pa lha gnyis go
NK024(ya)001:9028: bstun na gtso bo thams cad ni ston pa kho
NK024(ya)001:9029: na la / bri char 'dab bzhi pa gnyis bshad
NK024(ya)001:9030: pa'i dang po sh+aa ri bu dang mood+gala gyi bu
NK024(ya)001:9031: rab byung khyim pa bzhis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:9032: gnyis pa 'khor rnam bzhis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:9033: gsum pa bri char nang du 'dab bzhi de'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:9034: brgyad de'i phyir yang brgyad ces pa ni nang gi
