NK024(ya)001:9035: 'dab bzhi la dgra bcom pa phyir 'ong phyir mi
NK024(ya)001:9038: phyi mar sprul pa brgyad rnams /
NK024(ya)001:9039: bzhi pa dang lnga par bri char 'dab ma bcu drug bya /
NK024(ya)001:9041: zhes gsungs pa'i bcu drug pa dang po mchog bcu drug /
NK024(ya)001:9042: gnyis par gnas brtan bcu drug rnams yin par 'khrul pa med /
NK024(ya)001:9043: 'dir ni rang lugs gtso bor bgyis na /
NK024(ya)001:9044: zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aakya 'byung gnas kyi lhan thems su /
NK024(ya)001:9045: nyan thos la yang gtso bo ni //
NK024(ya)001:9046: spyir na dus gsum sangs rgyas dang //
NK024(ya)001:9047: khyad par bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong //
NK024(ya)001:9048: zhes dkyil 'khor dang po gtso bo ston pa la
NK024(ya)001:9049: dus chen po lha gsum dang dus bzang gi lha
NK024(ya)001:9050: gsum ste drug la sangs rgyas stong gis bskor ba
NK024(ya)001:9051: / gnyis pa bde bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK024(ya)001:9052: dge slong dge bsnyen pho mo bshad /
NK024(ya)001:9053: gsum pa dge 'dun mchog bcu drug /
NK024(ya)001:9054: bzhi pa 'khor brgyad sprul rang rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:9055: lnga pa mchod dang gnas brtan sbrags //
NK024(ya)001:9056: zhes gsungs pa'i dang po go sla la /
NK024(ya)001:9057: gnyis pa la 'dab bzhi dbus su thub dbang dang /
NK024(ya)001:9058: phyogs bzhir dge slong pha ma dang dge bsnyen pha ma ste bzhis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:9059: gsum pa mchog bcu drug ni thub dbang la mang du thos pa'i mchog kun dga' bo /
NK024(ya)001:9060: shes rab can gyi mchog sh+aa ri'i bu /
NK024(ya)001:9061: rdzu 'phrul can gyi mchog mood+gala gyi bu /
NK024(ya)001:9062: 'dri zhing lan 'don pa rnams kyi mchog rab 'byor /
NK024(ya)001:9063: lha'i mig dang ldan pa'i mchog ma 'gags pa /
NK024(ya)001:9064: bslab pa la gus pa'i mchog 'char ka /
NK024(ya)001:9066: khyim pa dad par byed pa'i mchog rta thul te mchog brgyad dang /
NK024(ya)001:9068: 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchog ba lang bdag /
NK024(ya)001:9069: sbyangs pa'i yon tan la gnas pa rnams kyi mchog 'od srungs /
NK024(ya)001:9070: bslab pa la gus pa'i mchog sgra gcan 'dzin /
NK024(ya)001:9071: mtshan dper ldan pa'i mchog gcung dga' bo //
NK024(ya)001:9072: rgyal ba'i bka' la gus pa'i mchog ming chen /
NK024(ya)001:9073: dbul ba sel ba'i mchog nor sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:9074: chos smra ba rnams kyi mchog gam yon sbyong ba'i
NK024(ya)001:9075: mchog gang po sogs rang rgyud pa brgyad bsdoms pas
NK024(ya)001:9076: mchog bcu drug gis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor yin kyang
NK024(ya)001:9077: / deng sang phyag bzhes su dkyil 'khor gsum pa
NK024(ya)001:9078: 'di la 'dab bzhi'i dbus su ston pa dang 'dab
NK024(ya)001:9082: rgyun zhugs bzhis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor du mdzad pas 'og tu rgyas par 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:9083: bzhi pa la 'khor brgyad ni zung bzhi ya brgyad
NK024(ya)001:9084: ces grags pa'i zung bzhi ni gong gi mchog brgyad
NK024(ya)001:9085: dang / ya brgyad ni rang rgyud pa brgyad yin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9086: de dag la sprul pa dang rang rgyud kyi khyad par yod pas na /
NK024(ya)001:9087: bzhi pa 'khor brgyad sprul rang rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:9089: 'on kyang skyes bu zung bzhi ya brgyad po spyi ltar na /
NK024(ya)001:9093: dgra bcom pa bzhi la zung bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:9094: ya brgyad ni de la nang gses phye ba'i rgyun zhugs la zhugs pa dang gnas pa gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:9095: phyir 'ong la zhugs pa dang gnas pa gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:9096: phyir mi 'ong la zhugs pa dang gnas pa gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:9097: dgra bcom pa la zhugs pa dang gnas pa gnyis su bshad pas /
NK024(ya)001:9098: 'dir dgra bcom pa 'ba' zhig la zung bzhi ya
NK024(ya)001:9099: brgyad du btags 'dug pa yang dpyad par bya zhing
NK024(ya)001:9100: mchog brgyad kyang spyi dang mi mthun par byung ngo
NK024(ya)001:9101: // bri char phyag len du 'dab brgyad nyis sprag gi nang ma la sprul pa brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:9102: phyi ma la rang rgyud pa brgyad mdzad srol yod /
NK024(ya)001:9103: lnga pa ni thub dbang la gong gi nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:9104: bcu drug gi steng gnas brtan bcu drug kyang bkod
NK024(ya)001:9105: pas 'khor sum cu so gnyis kyis bskor ba'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:9106: 'khor du bshad / de lta bu'i gnas brtan yang /
NK024(ya)001:9108: gnas brtan bcu drug rnying ma ltar //
NK024(ya)001:9109: thams cad 'khar gsil lhung bzed mthun //
NK024(ya)001:9110: gsar ma jo bo rje ltar dang //
NK024(ya)001:9111: mtshan bzhi mi 'dra bcu gsum mthun //
NK024(ya)001:9113: gnas brtan b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms len dang gcig /
NK024(ya)001:9117: 'das pa zhes bya ste dus ldan dang lnga /
NK024(ya)001:9118: b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha gser can dang drug /
NK024(ya)001:9119: lam po che ba dang bdun /
NK024(ya)001:9123: zur gyi gshegs sam zur gyi shes zhes pa nags
NK024(ya)001:9124: na gnas pa'am gnas na gnas pa dang bcu gcig
NK024(ya)001:9125: / ma pham pa dang bcu gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:9126: shing kun pa dang bcu gsum /
NK024(ya)001:9127: shing shun can dang bcu bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:9128: ba lang skyong dang bco lnga ni dge slong snam sbyar can yin la /
NK024(ya)001:9129: bcu drug pa tsun+da ni dge tshul snam sbyar med pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9130: dge bsnyen d+harma pha la'am d+harma ta ni khyim pa'i cha byad can dang bcu bdun las /
NK024(ya)001:9131: jo bo rje'i gnas brtan ltar na shing kun pa /
NK024(ya)001:9135: sbed byed ces sam bde byed bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:9138: rdo rje mo'i bu zhes bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:9139: phyag mtshan yang so sor gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:9144: rdo rje mo'i bu bzhi'i mtshan la shing kun pa /
NK024(ya)001:9147: tsun+da zhes btags pa ma gtogs yongs grags dang 'dra bar snang yang /
NK024(ya)001:9148: bya pa skal bzang pa'i mdzad pa 'khrul med dang
NK024(ya)001:9149: pan chen byams gling pa'i gnas bcu'i rtogs pa gnyis
NK024(ya)001:9150: mthun par / sbed byed pa ba lang bdag /
NK024(ya)001:9151: shing shun can ba ku lar bshad 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:9152: rig 'dzin yol mo ba yang 'di ltar bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:9153: rdo rje mo'i bu dge tshul tsun+da snga 'gyur phyogs
NK024(ya)001:9154: bzhed pa 'dra yang mdo las rdo rje mo'i bu
NK024(ya)001:9155: dang dge tshul tsun+da gleng gzhi tha dad du byung
NK024(ya)001:9156: bas gcig tu byas na klan ka 'byung nye zhing
NK024(ya)001:9157: / gleng gzhi dang sbyar na gser be'u /
NK024(ya)001:9158: ba lang bdag yin 'dra zhing 'dug mod /
NK024(ya)001:9159: 'on kyang 'dir bla ma gong ma rnams kyi gsung
NK024(ya)001:9160: la 'khrul pa mi mnga' bas bsgyur bkod ma bde
NK024(ya)001:9161: zhing lugs 'di 'thad ldan du bsgrub par nus pa
NK024(ya)001:9162: dag mchis na ljags rkyong bar rigs so //'on kyang
NK024(ya)001:9163: deng sang zur lugs dang kahthoga lugs gnyis ka la
NK024(ya)001:9164: gnas brtan rnams kyi mngon rtogs mi gsal zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9165: tsun+da dang d+har+m+aa ta gnyis gnas brtan bcu drug tu
NK024(ya)001:9166: 'dren dgos pa sogs 'dra min sna tshogs 'dug kyang
NK024(ya)001:9167: / phyogs 'dir mkhas pa 'ga' zhig pad 'dab bcu drug la gnas brtan bcu drug dang /
NK024(ya)001:9168: shar lho'i grar tsun+da dge tshul /
NK024(ya)001:9169: byang shar gyi grar d+ha r+m+aa ta dge snyen rnams
NK024(ya)001:9170: bshad pa legs par mthong ste de bzhin du 'og
NK024(ya)001:9171: gi dkyil chog tu yang bris so //
NK024(ya)001:9172: phyag mtshan rang lugs la thams cad 'khar gsil lhung bzed /
NK024(ya)001:9173: yongs grags la phyag mtshan mi 'dra ba so sor
NK024(ya)001:9174: byed pa jo bo rje'i lugs yin par bshad 'dug
NK024(ya)001:9175: kyang / ngos zin pa'i khyad kyis phyi ma ltar legs par mngon zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9176: 'di rnams kyi gleng gzhi sogs kyang 'og tu rgyas pa 'chad par spro'o //
NK024(ya)001:9177: mdor na rang lugs kyi 'thad pa dang bcas sngon du bshad nas /
NK024(ya)001:9178: bri bya dngos phyag len ji lta bar bris na zlos pa'i skyon med cing 'thad par mthong bas /
NK024(ya)001:9180: dang po pad+ma mdzes tshon 'dab drug /
NK024(ya)001:9181: gnyis pa dang gsum pa 'dab bzhi phyogs mdog /
NK024(ya)001:9182: bzhi pa 'dab brgyad nyis rim mdzes tshon /
NK024(ya)001:9183: lnga pa la nang du 'dab brgyad de'i phyir 'dab ma bcu drug pa mdzes tshon /
NK024(ya)001:9184: lnga ga lte ba ser khyams phyogs tshon /
NK024(ya)001:9185: rtsig pa nang nas ser mthing dmar ljang dkar ba'am ljang gu /
NK024(ya)001:9186: sgo rta babs pad rdor sogs snga ma rnams dang
NK024(ya)001:9187: mthun no //'og gi chog gzhung ltar lha gnas su
NK024(ya)001:9188: tshon spungs kyis mtshan ma dgod /
NK024(ya)001:9189: de yang sa bcad kyi dbang du byas na dang po gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gnas tshul /
NK024(ya)001:9190: gnyis pa lam du dkyil 'khor sgom tshul gyi shugs bstan las de ltar bri tshul bstan no //
NK024(ya)001:9192: gsum pa mchod pa bsham pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9193: sku gsung thugs kyi rten dang /
NK024(ya)001:9203: chu tshags la sogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:9207: dkyil 'khor lnga ga sbreng tshar du bsham /
NK024(ya)001:9209: sku gsung thugs kyi rten bsham zhes par /
NK024(ya)001:9211: sku rten dbus su sh+aaka thub dang //'dab ma bzhi la 'khor rnam bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:9212: bcu drug 'dab la mchog bcu drug /
NK024(ya)001:9213: gsung gi rten la glegs bam bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:9214: thugs rten rdo rje dril bu dgod //
NK024(ya)001:9215: ces gsungs pas lnga ga'i dbus su ston pa'i sku
NK024(ya)001:9216: bris 'bur gang rigs bsham zhing bris sku tsakli smyug
NK024(ya)001:9217: thur la bcings te btsugs shing /
NK024(ya)001:9218: spro na thugs rten du rdor dril yang bkod /
NK024(ya)001:9219: gzhan yang lha gnas so sor tsakli zhal nang bstan du smyug thur la bcings te btsugs /
NK024(ya)001:9220: gsung rten glegs bam gzhan mi shong yang sman bla'i
NK024(ya)001:9221: skabs sman mdo'i glegs bam bzhugs pa dang chos mtshungs
NK024(ya)001:9222: par sman mdo dang shes rab snying po /
NK024(ya)001:9223: sdud pa lta bu'i glegs bam yang bzhugs /
NK024(ya)001:9224: dkyil 'khor so so'i mthar mtshams 'dzin nas bzung chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i mchod pa g.yas skor dang /
NK024(ya)001:9225: gzhan yang mchod pa'i khyad par gang 'byor rgya cher bsham /
NK024(ya)001:9226: dkon mchog spyi gtor dkar zlum dkar gsum mngar gsum
NK024(ya)001:9227: gyis brgyan pa bzang po re re yang 'das gtor
NK024(ya)001:9229: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu bzhi pa bum pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9232: bya ma bum du chu bo chen po nas blangs
NK024(ya)001:9233: pa'i chus rten gsum me long gi ngos su khrus
NK024(ya)001:9234: gsol la / slar bum par blug ste lha rnams kyi thugs rje'i bdud rtsir bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:9235: zhes bum bskyed mi dgos par khrus gsol gyi chus bum chus dod byed pa lta bur gsungs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:9236: sa bcad bzhi par bum bzlas sogs bstan cing 'og tu bum dbang yang bshad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:9237: kahthoga lugs su bum bskyed kyang tshul bzhin gsungs 'dug pas /
NK024(ya)001:9238: spyir nyan rang byang sems sogs la dbang gi tha
NK024(ya)001:9239: snyad med kyang 'dir sgo 'byed dus nas sngags lam
NK024(ya)001:9241: dbang gi tha snyad yod phyin bum bskyed kyang mi 'thad pa ma yin mod /
NK024(ya)001:9242: 'on kyang zur lugs kho na ltar lha ma bskyed
NK024(ya)001:9243: kyang khrus bum gyi dod lta bur bzlas dmigs tsam
NK024(ya)001:9244: byas na gzhung dang mi 'gal zhing legs pa 'dra
NK024(ya)001:9245: bas cho ga dngos 'og tu ston la /
NK024(ya)001:9246: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po
NK024(ya)001:9247: che bum pa dri bzang gi chu dang bum rdzas
NK024(ya)001:9248: rten khrus kyi chu 'og nas ston /
NK024(ya)001:9249: dar dmar ser gang rigs kyis mgul chings kha rgyan dung chos rdor gzungs dang bcas pa bsham /
NK024(ya)001:9250: sdom rten ston pa'i sku gzugs kyi spyan sngar mchod pa gang rgyas dang /
NK024(ya)001:9251: zhi khro dang chos srung gi gtor ma rnams kha gsol /
NK024(ya)001:9253: dbang gi sngon 'gro'i bgegs gtor yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:9254: gzhan yang 'og tu dgos pa'i slob ma dang grangs mnyam pa'i bla gos /
NK024(ya)001:9260: gzhan yang 'khar gsil spu gri sogs kyang dgos /
NK024(ya)001:9261: ma 'byor na bla gos sogs kyang dbang rdzas ltar re res 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:9262: rdor dril rol mo sogs mchod rdzas dang /
NK024(ya)001:9263: man+dala me tog dang bcas pa yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:9265: bzhi pa rab gnas ni rang thub pa bsgom zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:9266: bum bzlas bshad rjes phyogs thams cad du ku shas
NK024(ya)001:9267: gtor bas rten dang mchod pa'i ma dag pa bsang
NK024(ya)001:9268: / so so'i ye shes pa thim pas dag cing bzang ba phun sum tshogs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:9269: zhes pa'i don gzhan 'og tu shes la /
NK024(ya)001:9270: 'dir rdor dril dang bcas te rten 'brel snying po bzla zhing me tog phyogs kun tu gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:9272: lnga pa ni chog gzhung sman bla'i mdo chog dang gnas brtan bcu drug gi cho ga'o //
NK024(ya)001:9273: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi don rgyas par phye na
NK024(ya)001:9274: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi thog mar mchod pa byin
NK024(ya)001:9275: gyis brlab pa'i sngon du sa gzhi byin brlab ni
NK024(ya)001:9276: / thams cad du ni sa gzhi dag /
NK024(ya)001:9277: gseg ma la sogs med pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:9278: lag mthil ltar mnyam bee d+aur+ya'i //
NK024(ya)001:9279: rang bzhin 'jam por gnas gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:9281: mchod pa byin brlab dngos ni /
NK024(ya)001:9282: bsang sbyang nas bzung mchod pa'i sprin gyi gzungs 'don pa'i bar phyag rdor gyi skabs ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9283: de rjes skyabs 'gro sems bskyed tshad med bzhi sogs lha mi'i theg pa ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9284: dang po bdag bskyed ni rtsa ba'i sa bcad bzhi par /
NK024(ya)001:9285: rang thub par sgom zhes gsungs par kahthoga lugs su
NK024(ya)001:9286: bdag mdun bum gsum gar dkyil 'khor rgyas par sgom
NK024(ya)001:9287: tshul 'dug kyang / 'dir bdag bskyed la thub pa
NK024(ya)001:9288: gtso rkyang dang bum bskyed la gzhung ltar dmigs bzlas
NK024(ya)001:9289: tshul 'dug kyang / / mdun bskyed bris pa bzhin gsal btab na legs par go bas /
NK024(ya)001:9292: stong ba'i ngang las pam las pad+ma dang a las zla ba'i gdan la /
NK024(ya)001:9293: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog
NK024(ya)001:9294: gser btso ma'i mdog lta bu zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK024(ya)001:9295: / g.yas sa gnon dang g.yon mnyam gzhag mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:9296: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa chos
NK024(ya)001:9297: gos rnam pa gsum dang ldan zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9298: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang dpe byad
NK024(ya)001:9299: bzang po brgyad cus spras pa'i spyi bor dkar po
NK024(ya)001:9302: h+aum las 'od zer 'phros 'og min nas rang 'dra'i
NK024(ya)001:9303: ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK024(ya)001:9304: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham /
NK024(ya)001:9312: rnam dag sku mnga' mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK024(ya)001:9313: ye shes rgya mtsho gser gyi lhun po 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:9314: grags pa 'jig rten bkram nas lham me ba //
NK024(ya)001:9315: mgon po khyod nyid la ni phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9317: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:9319: mjug tu gong ltar mchod bstod bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9321: lha mi'i theg par gtso bo lnga bskyed bzlas gzhung las gsal ba ltar rgyas par phye yod la /
NK024(ya)001:9322: 'dir ni rtsa ba las gzungs chu bsgrub pa tsam las ma bshad pas 'brel chags pa ltar /
NK024(ya)001:9324: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che las
NK024(ya)001:9325: grub pa'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i nang
NK024(ya)001:9326: du chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis gang ba'i steng
NK024(ya)001:9327: dung zhal gyi nang du a las zla ba'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:9328: 'khor gyi steng du rten 'brel snying po'i sngags kyi
NK024(ya)001:9329: phreng ba kha dog dkar po g.yas su 'khyil bar
NK024(ya)001:9331: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+ha w+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK024(ya)001:9332: te sh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+h+aa d+ai
NK024(ya)001:9333: ma h+aa sh+ra ma nah lan bdun bzlas pas sngags
NK024(ya)001:9334: phreng las 'od zer dkar po 'phros 'jig rten gyi
NK024(ya)001:9335: khams thams cad lha'i bdud rtsir zhu /
NK024(ya)001:9336: tshur 'dus bum par thim pas bum pa'i chus sems
NK024(ya)001:9337: can gyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri ma thams
NK024(ya)001:9338: cad dag par byed cing nus pa phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:9339: pa sgrub pa'i nus ldan du gyur /
NK024(ya)001:9340: de nas gzungs thag la bzung ste rten 'brel snying po'i sngags brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:9341: mthar dung chos kyi chu bum par blug ste /
NK024(ya)001:9342: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor sngags phreng dang bcas pa 'od
NK024(ya)001:9343: du zhu nas bum chu la thim par bsam mo
NK024(ya)001:9344: // las bum ni gong du bshad pa ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:9345: yang na 'di 'dra'i rigs la khrus bum gyi dod
NK024(ya)001:9346: kho na yin pas spros pa chung na las bum
NK024(ya)001:9347: gyi gong 'di khas chod pas khrus dbang thams cad
NK024(ya)001:9349: de nas bum chu phyogs thams cad du gtor zhing
NK024(ya)001:9350: rten 'brel snying po brjod pas rten dang mchod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9351: ma dag pa'i dri ma thams cad bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:9352: so so'i ye shes pa thim pas dag cing bzang ba phun sum tshogs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:9353: gsum pa mdun bskyed sgrub pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9355: sman bla'i mdo chog dang gnas bcu'i cho gas 'thus par gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:9356: 'on kyang dkyil 'khor so so dang mthun pa'i sgrub
NK024(ya)001:9357: mchod zhig ma byung na rnam pa mi gsal zhing
NK024(ya)001:9358: / kha skong lta bur sman bla dang gnas bcu'i cho ga byas na legs par mthong bas /
NK024(ya)001:9359: dang por dkyil 'khor so so'i sgrub mchod las /
NK024(ya)001:9360: rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9362: stong ba'i ngang las sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK024(ya)001:9363: gnas pa'i b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna tshogs las
NK024(ya)001:9364: grub pa'i gzhal med khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa
NK024(ya)001:9365: ser mthing dmar ljang dkar po'i rtsig pa lnga'i steng
NK024(ya)001:9367: rin po che'i d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang zhing mda' yab dang pu shus brgyan cing /
NK024(ya)001:9368: nang ka ba brgyad dang ldan pa'i steng rdo rje'i
NK024(ya)001:9369: gdung bzhis bteg pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:9370: rje dang rin po che'i tog gis spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:9371: sgo bzhir ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs bang rim bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:9372: bum pa bre chos 'khor gdugs tog dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:9373: phyi rol tu 'dod yon gyi snam bu la mchod
NK024(ya)001:9374: pa'i lha mo rnams kyis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:9375: phyi'i khor yug tu sna tshogs pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:9377: 'od zer gyi phreng ba kun nas 'phro ba'i nang gi khyams dbus sngo /
NK024(ya)001:9381: byang ljang ba'i dkyil 'khor lngar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:9384: bco brgyad pa lha ni gtso bo ston pa sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9385: dus bzang gi lha lha mi ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:9386: khyad par dus chen po'i lha 'das pa'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:9387: thams cad kyi sku tshab sangs rgyas mar me mdzad
NK024(ya)001:9388: don dam pa'i chos ston pas rten 'brel gyi phyag
NK024(ya)001:9389: rgya / da ltar gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:9390: sku tshab rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa skye 'gro thugs
NK024(ya)001:9391: rjes skyong bas sa gnon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9392: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku tshab
NK024(ya)001:9393: mgon po byams pa gdul bya rjes su 'dzin pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9394: mchog sbyin spyi blugs skyabs sbyin klu shing can no
NK024(ya)001:9395: //'dir dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi gtso bo thub pa
NK024(ya)001:9396: / 'khor ni g.yas su sh+aa ri'i bu /
NK024(ya)001:9408: de'i phyir de dag las gyes pa'i sprul pa brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:9409: de'i phyir rang rgyud pa brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:9410: yang mdun nas rim pas mchog bcu drug ni /
NK024(ya)001:9412: sh+aa ri'i bu rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:9417: koon+di n+ya rin chen sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:9427: kun kyang dbu reg zhabs rjen rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs can no //
NK024(ya)001:9428: yang gnas brtan bcu drug ni phyogs re rer bzhi bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:9429: shar nas rim pas b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms pa /
NK024(ya)001:9446: kun kyang dgra bcom pa 'khar gsil lhung bzed 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9448: d+har+m+aa ta la dge bsnyen no //
NK024(ya)001:9449: zhes gsungs pa'i khungs bkod pa ni rtsa ba'i tshig mi chad pa'i ched yin la /
NK024(ya)001:9450: gzhan legs bshad du mas 'di rnams kyi don legs par gtan la phab bo //
NK024(ya)001:9451: brten pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9452: dkyil 'khor dang po dus gsum sangs rgyas dang dus
NK024(ya)001:9453: chen gsum gyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su pad+ma 'dab
NK024(ya)001:9454: ma drug pa'i lte bar rin po che'i khri dang
NK024(ya)001:9456: thub dbang sh+aakya'i rgyal po ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:9457: 'dab ma drug pa pad zla'i gdan re re'i shar
NK024(ya)001:9458: du mar me mdzad ser po don dam pa'i chos
NK024(ya)001:9459: ston pas rten 'brel gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:9460: shar lhor sh+aakya thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:9461: lho nub tu byams pa ser po g.yas mchog sbyin dang spyi blugs /
NK024(ya)001:9462: g.yon skyabs sbyin dang klu shing can /
NK024(ya)001:9463: nub tu nya'i lha snang ba mtha' yas dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:9464: nub byang du tshes brgyad kyi lha sman bla mthing
NK024(ya)001:9465: kha mnyam gzhag gi steng na bdud rtsi'i lhung bzed
NK024(ya)001:9466: bsnams pa / byang shar du gnam stong gi lha
NK024(ya)001:9467: thub pa ser po bdud 'dul gyi phyag rgya can
NK024(ya)001:9468: bsnams pa / no // de'i phyir sgo nang gi
NK024(ya)001:9469: khyams la pad zla'i gdan la thub pa 'khor ba
NK024(ya)001:9470: 'jig nas mos pa snang mdzad bar gyi bskal pa
NK024(ya)001:9471: bzang po'i sangs rgyas stong rtsa phyag rgya rigs lnga
NK024(ya)001:9472: sogs sna tshogs par mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:9473: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang mtshan dpes spras pa sprul
NK024(ya)001:9474: sku chags bral gyi rnam pa can chos gos rnam
NK024(ya)001:9476: dkyil 'khor dang po 'dir kahthoga lugs kyi zin bris zhal shes mar /
NK024(ya)001:9477: 'dab ma drug gi dbus su thub dbang /
NK024(ya)001:9478: shar nas rim pa bzhin mar me mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:9483: mos pa rnams bskyed par gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:9484: rnam gzigs dang mos pa gnyis dus chen dang dus
NK024(ya)001:9485: bzang gnyis kar mi 'dug pas dpyad dka' ba dang
NK024(ya)001:9486: / de yang tshogs zhing du spyan drangs te yan
NK024(ya)001:9487: lag bdun pa 'bul ba tsam las mi 'dri ba'i
NK024(ya)001:9489: zur lugs kahthoga lugs gnyis kar de 'dra'i bshad khungs mi 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:9490: khyad par zur lugs kyi gsan yig rnams su dkyil
NK024(ya)001:9491: 'khor dang po'i gtso bo ston pa la dus bzang
NK024(ya)001:9492: gi lha gsum dang dus gsum sangs rgyas la sangs
NK024(ya)001:9493: rgyas stong gi 'khor gyis bskor ba bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:9494: 'on kyang rtsa ba'i sa bcad bco brgyad pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:9495: du byas na dkyil 'khor dang por sh+aa ri'i bu
NK024(ya)001:9496: dang / moong+gala rab byung khyim pa bzhi yang na 'khor rnam pa bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:9497: yang na gang zag zung bzhi sogs 'chad tshul mang bar snang yang /
NK024(ya)001:9498: 'dir 'khor dang po'i mchog zung ni mchog brgyad kyi nang du gtogs shing /
NK024(ya)001:9499: gzhan rnams 'og tu 'byung bas dus chen dang dus bzang gi lha zur lugs kho na dang /
NK024(ya)001:9501: lha thems kyi dgongs pa ltar bkod pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9502: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa 'khor rnam bzhis bskor ba'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:9503: 'khor pad 'dab bzhi pa'i dbus su seng khri pad
NK024(ya)001:9504: zla'i gdan la thub dbang ser po sa gnon mnyam
NK024(ya)001:9505: gzhag /'dab ma bzhi la 'khor rnam pa bzhi ste
NK024(ya)001:9506: gtso bo'i g.yas lho'i 'dab mar dge slong /
NK024(ya)001:9507: g.yon byang gi pad+mara dge slong ma /
NK024(ya)001:9508: mdun shar gyi 'dab mar dge bsnyen pha /
NK024(ya)001:9509: rgyab nub kyi pad+mara dge bsnyen ma ste dge slong
NK024(ya)001:9510: pha ma gnyis chos gos gsum ldan 'khar gsil can
NK024(ya)001:9511: dang / dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis khyim pa'i cha lugs can no //
NK024(ya)001:9512: dkyil 'khor gsum pa skyes bu zung bzhis bskor ba'i
NK024(ya)001:9513: dkyil 'khor 'dab ma bzhi pa'i dbus su seng khri
NK024(ya)001:9514: pad zla'i gdan la thub dbang ser po sa gnon
NK024(ya)001:9515: mnyam gzhag can / 'dab ma bzhi la g.yas su dgra bcom pa /
NK024(ya)001:9518: rgyab tu rgyun zhugs rnams rab tu byung ba'i cha
NK024(ya)001:9519: lugs chos gos rnam pa gsum dang ldan zhing 'khar
NK024(ya)001:9520: gsil dang lhung bzed bsnams pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9521: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa mchog bcu drug gis bskor ba'i
NK024(ya)001:9522: dkyil 'khor 'dab brgyad nyis sprag gi dbus su seng
NK024(ya)001:9523: khri pad zla'i gdan la thub dbang ser po sa
NK024(ya)001:9525: 'dab brgyad nang mar shar nas rim pa bzhin kun dga' bo bsil g.yab /
NK024(ya)001:9526: sh+aa ri'i bu rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:9531: koon+di n+ya rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:9532: rta thul phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //'di rnams la zung
NK024(ya)001:9533: bzhi ya brgyad dam mchog brgyad dam sprul pa brgyad
NK024(ya)001:9535: phyi rol gyi 'dab ma brgyad la rang rgyud pa brgyad ni nye ba 'khor lhung bzed /
NK024(ya)001:9536: ba lang bdag me sgron gsal shing /
NK024(ya)001:9540: ming can chan pa ste spu gri /
NK024(ya)001:9541: nor 'dzin rin po che'i rkyal pa ste ne'u le /
NK024(ya)001:9542: gang po nor bu 'dzin pa ste bcu drug po
NK024(ya)001:9543: thams cad kyang dbu reg zhabs rjen chos gos rnam
NK024(ya)001:9544: pa gsum dang ldan pa'o //'di'i 'dab ma brgyad pa
NK024(ya)001:9547: bzhi pa 'khor brgyad sprul rang rgyud //'khor brgyad pad+ma 'dab brgyad sbrag /
NK024(ya)001:9549: dkyil 'khor lnga pa mchog dang gnas brtan sbrags pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9550: dbus su pad zla'i gdan la thub dbang ser po
NK024(ya)001:9552: nang gi 'dab ma brgyad la mchog brgyad ni gong
NK024(ya)001:9553: du bshad pa'i sprul pa brgyad de shar nas g.yas
NK024(ya)001:9554: skor du / kun dga' bo bsil g.yab /
NK024(ya)001:9555: sh+aa ri'i bu rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:9560: koon+di n+ya rin po che'i sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:9562: de'i phyir 'dab ma bcu drug la 'phags pa'i gnas
NK024(ya)001:9563: brtan chen po bcu drug ni shar nas g.yas skor
NK024(ya)001:9564: du gnas brtan chen po yan lag 'byung spos phor
NK024(ya)001:9565: dang rnga yab / ma pham pa mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9566: nags na gnas g.yas sdigs mdzub dang g.yon rnga yab /
NK024(ya)001:9568: rdo rje mo'i bu sdigs mdzub dang rnga yab /
NK024(ya)001:9569: bzang po chos 'chad dang mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9570: gser be'u rin chen zhags pa /
NK024(ya)001:9571: b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha gser can mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9575: b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms len g.yas glegs bam dang g.yon lhung bzed /
NK024(ya)001:9576: lam bstan g.yas chos 'chad dang g.yon glegs bam /
NK024(ya)001:9577: klu'i sde 'khar gsil dang bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:9579: mi phyed pa byang chen mchod rten 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9580: yang na thams cad g.yas 'khar gsil dang /
NK024(ya)001:9582: thams cad kyang tshangs par spyod pa'i cha lugs can
NK024(ya)001:9583: chos gos rnam pa gsum dang ldan pa sbyangs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9584: yon tan la mkhas pa'i tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9585: shar lho'i grar tsun+da dge tshul chos gos can snam sbyar med pa 'khar gsil lhung bzed 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:9586: byang shar gyi grar d+har+m+aa ta dge bsnyen chas rnga
NK024(ya)001:9587: yab dang bum pa 'dzin cing sprul pa'i stag dang
NK024(ya)001:9588: bcas pa snang ba mtha' yas mdun na bzhugs pa'o
NK024(ya)001:9589: // gnas bcu rtsa bar b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod
NK024(ya)001:9590: snyoms len gyi thog drangs te rim bzhin 'god tshul
NK024(ya)001:9591: gsung pa don la khyad par med phyin 'dir sbyi
NK024(ya)001:9592: // dang bstun no // rgyal chen bzhi zur lugs yig snar yod med sna tshogs 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:9594: sgo la rgyal chen bzhis bsrung ba //
NK024(ya)001:9595: rgyal dang sems dpas gnyer gtad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9596: sangs rgyas bstan pa'i sgor zhugs tsam //
NK024(ya)001:9597: thams cad bsrung ba'i chos skyong ni //
NK024(ya)001:9598: theg pa dgu ka la mtshungs shing //
NK024(ya)001:9599: khyad par theg rer chos skyong re //
NK024(ya)001:9600: yod pas de bsten de 'bras thob //
NK024(ya)001:9601: ces gtan tshigs bzang po'i lung gis grub pas 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:9602: shar sgor yul 'khor bsrung dkar po rgyud mang /
NK024(ya)001:9603: lho sgor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:9604: nub sgor spyan mi bzang dmar po mchod rten dang sbrul zhags /
NK024(ya)001:9605: byang sgor rnam thos sras ser po rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:9606: de ltar gnas brtan 'di rnams kyi mngon par rtogs
NK024(ya)001:9607: pa bsgom pa dang bris 'bur du bzhengs pa la
NK024(ya)001:9608: phan pa'i legs bshad 'di ltar yang snang ste /
NK024(ya)001:9609: rig 'dzin yol mo ba chen pos mdzad pa'i gnas brtan phyag mchod kyi sbyar byang gi skabs las /
NK024(ya)001:9610: 'dir gtso bo cog sgar ba rnams kyis bskul ba
NK024(ya)001:9611: ltar sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rgyas pa'i rten 'brel
NK024(ya)001:9612: du bgyis shing / sku gzugs ri mor bgyi ba
NK024(ya)001:9613: la yang phan 'dogs par 'dod pa'i ched du byas
NK024(ya)001:9614: du bgyis shing / pa yin te / da lta
NK024(ya)001:9615: gnas brtan gyi bris sku 'dri ba mang yang tshul
NK024(ya)001:9616: dang mthun pa ma mthong ste /
NK024(ya)001:9617: 'di lta bu'i dgos pa khyad par can rnams ni ma thos /
NK024(ya)001:9621: dar yol bzhi zhes dgos ched med pa'i thos pa
NK024(ya)001:9622: bon gyer gyis bslus bgres po rgas nad kyis nyam
NK024(ya)001:9623: thag pa'i dbyibs can du tshems dral ba /
NK024(ya)001:9624: spyan 'bras kyi bkrag nyams pa lta bur 'dri ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:9625: gnas g.yog ces gang mi sdug cing bkra mi shis pa'i nyams su 'dri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:9626: 'jig rten spyi dang khyad par sbyin bdag la 'bras bu phyin ci log tu 'byin nges shing /
NK024(ya)001:9627: gzhan yang bya rgod phung po'i ri bo na zhes
NK024(ya)001:9628: pa la rtog brtags kyi bya rgod kyi gzugs 'dri
NK024(ya)001:9629: ba dang / sing ga la yi gling zhes par seng ge bris pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:9630: 'phags pa'i gnas brtan ma pham pa zhes pa'i mdun
NK024(ya)001:9631: du mtsho ma pham bris pa sogs mthong ba ni
NK024(ya)001:9632: / bkod pa mkhan nam bris mkhan nyid blun chen
NK024(ya)001:9633: du khas len tshigs so //'o na ji ltar du
NK024(ya)001:9634: / 'bri na / sku rnams kyang mdzes brjid dpa' ba'i rnams su 'dri la /
NK024(ya)001:9635: gnas g.yog rnams phyag mtshan 'bul mkhan gyi dbyibs su 'dri zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9636: de med pa rnams la dge slong gi 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:9637: lam phran bstan la dge slong ma'i 'khor 'dri na
NK024(ya)001:9638: skabs su babs par bdag cag kho na sems so
NK024(ya)001:9639: // gzhan yang rgan bzhi sogs kyi ngag 'khyal las /
NK024(ya)001:9640: lam bstan dang lam phran bstan phu nu yin pa
NK024(ya)001:9641: la rgan gzhon go log par bris pa yang mthong
NK024(ya)001:9642: ngo // de las gzhan du thang ju'i rgyal pos
NK024(ya)001:9643: za 'og gi na bza' sna tshogs phul pa'i lo
NK024(ya)001:9644: ngo // rgyus yod cing / si thang gi rgyu mtshan yang yod mod /
NK024(ya)001:9645: 'on kyang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa chags bral gyi
NK024(ya)001:9646: sku la gos sbu gu can lhab lhub tu bgos
NK024(ya)001:9647: pa dang / chos gos gsum gyis dben par 'dri
NK024(ya)001:9648: ba ni chos 'dul ba'i bstan pa la cung zad
NK024(ya)001:9650: rgya nag lugs yin ces rgya gar pa'i gnas brtan
NK024(ya)001:9651: chen po rnams bod mi rgan gog gi dbyibs su
NK024(ya)001:9652: 'dri ba 'di mu dur hor gyi chos lugs sam
NK024(ya)001:9653: ci zhig / gzhan yang ha shang ni thang ju'i
NK024(ya)001:9654: rgyal po'i pho nya yin pa la sbyin bdag tu
NK024(ya)001:9656: da lta'i mkhas par 'dod pa rnams phyogs 'dzin gyi dbang gis gzhan 'gog pa'i tshe blo rno zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9657: spyir grags pa'i 'khrul tshabs chen po 'di 'dra lta
NK024(ya)001:9658: bu la bag la nya gnyid pa 'ba' zhig ste
NK024(ya)001:9659: / pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi sku'i cha byad la dgos
NK024(ya)001:9660: pa khyad par can yod bzhin yang 'di ci zhes
NK024(ya)001:9661: / 'khu zhing / gong gi 'khrul pa 'di lta bu la ji mi snyam mo //
NK024(ya)001:9662: bdag ni 'phags pa gnas brtan rnams sbyangs yon la
NK024(ya)001:9663: gnas pa'i tshul du bris na 'brel ba dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:9664: par rjes su rtogs shing gcig tu smra'o //
NK024(ya)001:9665: chur lhungs bcal bu'i sgrar rmongs ri bong gis //
NK024(ya)001:9666: rab bsgrags gtam gyi rjes zhugs gcan gzan tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:9667: mu cor rgyu dang lag rjes 'god mthong tshe //
NK024(ya)001:9668: gdong lnga'i bdag po gtan tshigs ral pa rngom //
NK024(ya)001:9670: lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:9672: thugs kar h+aum sngon pos mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:9673: rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas la badz+ra sa
NK024(ya)001:9674: ma ya dzah zhes snyan gsan phab ste spyan 'dren
NK024(ya)001:9675: ni spos btul zhing rdo rje dril bu 'dzin pas
NK024(ya)001:9676: / mnga' ris pan chen gyi gsung rab gnas kyi
NK024(ya)001:9677: cho ga ye shes snying po'i 'od zer las gsungs
NK024(ya)001:9678: / pa 'di ltar // bcom ldan 'das de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:9679: gshegs pa dgra bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9680: sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa la sogs pa phyogs bcu
NK024(ya)001:9681: dus gsum du bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK024(ya)001:9682: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK024(ya)001:9683: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad
NK024(ya)001:9685: de dag gi thugs rje chen po dang byin gyis
NK024(ya)001:9686: brlabs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa mnga' zhing 'gro
NK024(ya)001:9687: ba'i don du smon lam khyad par can mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:9688: las drangs te bdag cag la sogs pa 'gro ba
NK024(ya)001:9689: mang po skyob pa'i slad du mgon skyabs su gsol
NK024(ya)001:9690: nas spyan 'dren cing mchis na mchod pa'i tshogs sbyar
NK024(ya)001:9691: ba'i pho brang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir gshegs shing gdan
NK024(ya)001:9692: 'dzom pa chen po mdzad de byin gyis brlab par
NK024(ya)001:9693: ci gnang / ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:9694: bdud sde dngos rnams bcom ldan bcom ldan bskal pa
NK024(ya)001:9695: grangs med du ma ru //'gro la smon lam khyed
NK024(ya)001:9696: bzhed de phyir rdzu 'phrul mtha' yas yongs dag chos
NK024(ya)001:9697: rnams kun gyi dbang phyug gtso //
NK024(ya)001:9698: btso ma nyi ma dad pas zhi zhing thugs rje
NK024(ya)001:9699: che dul zhing chos dang kun tu tshur spyon thub
NK024(ya)001:9700: pa shin tu mchod pa'i zhes lha mi'i skabs ltar
NK024(ya)001:9701: dang / gshegs byon skye bri med pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:9702: ji ltar smon bzhin yod pa ltar //
NK024(ya)001:9703: dkar po 'char ba'i tshul bzhin du //'jig rten skyob phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9704: pan chen rin po che'i rab gnas las //
NK024(ya)001:9705: phyogs dus kun nas skyabs gsum bka' sdod bcas //
NK024(ya)001:9706: nyon mongs 'gro la mkhyen brtses rab dgongs te //
NK024(ya)001:9707: dpag med zhing nas thogs med rdzu 'phrul gyis //'dir gshegs mchod sprin rgya mtsho'i dbus bzhugs 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:9708: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad dang //
NK024(ya)001:9709: shes rab me 'bar nyon mongs mtsho skem byed //
NK024(ya)001:9710: rnam grol bsod nams zhing du bka' sdod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:9711: phyogs bcu'i nyan thos dge 'dun bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:9712: bstan pa spel ba'i slad du spyan 'dren gyis //'gro ba'i don du mchod phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9713: gnas brtan phyag mchod spyi ltar gnas bcu spyan 'dren ni /
NK024(ya)001:9714: 'gro ba'i mgon po sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK024(ya)001:9715: sangs rgyas bstan pa gang gi phyag tu bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9716: gsung rab rin chen sgrom gyi kha 'byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:9717: dgra bcom gnas brtan chen po bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:9718: dam chos spel ba'i slad du spyan 'dren na //'gro ba'i don du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9719: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes nam mkhar spyan drangs te bzhugs pa la /
NK024(ya)001:9720: bcom ldan 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:9721: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK024(ya)001:9722: bdag la mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:9723: thugs la dgongs shing gnang bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:9724: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:9725: tshur gshegs 'dir ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9726: bdag la mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //'di nyid du ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9727: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ga ga na sa ma ya h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:9728: rnam bum gyi chus me long gi ngos su khrus bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:9729: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:9730: lha rnams kyis ni khrus gsol ltar //
NK024(ya)001:9731: lha yi de bzhin de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang de sras la //
NK024(ya)001:9732: rin chen bum pa mang po spos kyi chus //
NK024(ya)001:9733: yid 'ongs legs par gang ba'i glu dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:9734: rol mor bcas pa du mas sku khrus gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9735: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:9736: de'i khrus chu slar yang bum par blug go //
NK024(ya)001:9737: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK024(ya)001:9738: gtsang la dri rab bgos pas sku phyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:9739: de nas de la kha dog legs bsgyur ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:9740: na bza' shin tu dri zhim dam pa 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:9741: srab 'jam yangs pa lha yi gos //
NK024(ya)001:9742: mi shigs rdo rje'i sku nyid la //
NK024(ya)001:9743: mi phyed dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK024(ya)001:9744: bdag kyang rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:9746: rin chen du ma las grub seng ge'i khri //
NK024(ya)001:9747: yid 'phrog sna tshogs gos kyis bkab pa'i steng //
NK024(ya)001:9749: brtse bas dgongs te ci bder bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:9750: pad+ma ka m+aa la ye s+t+wam zhes gdan phul /
NK024(ya)001:9757: badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:9759: badz+ra +aa be sha +aah zhes so so'i phyag rgya
NK024(ya)001:9760: dang bcas te mdun bskyed kyi rten so sor ye
NK024(ya)001:9763: bdun pa ni dpang skong gi yan lag bdun pa bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9764: zhes gsungs pa skabs 'dir babs pas /
NK024(ya)001:9765: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9767: bdag nyid myur du mngon par sangs rgyas shog /
NK024(ya)001:9769: mchod pa 'bul ba ni byin rlabs gong du song
NK024(ya)001:9770: bas 'dir dkyil 'khor rnams kyi bdug spos dang mar
NK024(ya)001:9772: tshigs bcad rnams la thal mo sbyor zhing sngags kyi tshe so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:9773: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK024(ya)001:9774: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:9775: zhes sogs lha mi'i skabs ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9777: rin chen bdun 'bul ba'ang 'og nas 'byung ba'i cho ga rnams nas blang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:9779: gtso bo rnams la tog gzungs nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK024(ya)001:9780: rnam dag sku lnga mchog tu gzugs bzang ba //
NK024(ya)001:9782: dkyil 'khor dang po'i 'khor gyi dus gsum sangs rgyas la /
NK024(ya)001:9783: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas mar me mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:9785: dus bzang gsum gyi bco lnga'i lhar /
NK024(ya)001:9788: thugs rje kun la snyoms mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:9792: mthun pa'i dge tshogs smon lam rmad byung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:9793: spyad pa spyod tshe na yang mched gyur la //
NK024(ya)001:9794: bskal bzang gcig la mdzad pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:9795: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas stong la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:9796: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa dang gsum pa bzhi pa rnams kyi 'khor thun mong dang /
NK024(ya)001:9797: spyir dkon mchog gsum la dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:9798: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:9799: zhes sogs sh+lo ka gsum gyis bstod /
NK024(ya)001:9800: bye brag tu gnas brtan rnams la /
NK024(ya)001:9801: sangs rgyas sprul pa dgra bcom 'phags pa'i tshogs //'gro ba'i don du bstan pa skyong mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:9802: dkon mchog gsum dngos gnas brtan bcu drug la //
NK024(ya)001:9803: phyag 'tshal bstan pa rgyas par byin gyis rlobs //
NK024(ya)001:9805: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:9807: mdun bskyed kyi bzlas pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:9808: lam 'khyer skabs su byung ba ltar bdag bskyed bzhin
NK024(ya)001:9809: spyi khyab tu mu ne'i 'dzab ci rigs par bazla'o
NK024(ya)001:9810: // rtsa ba'i sa bcad lnga par sman bla'i mdo
NK024(ya)001:9811: chog dang gnas bcu'i cho gas gzhung byed gsungs pa
NK024(ya)001:9812: // / rgyas par spro na kho bo'i rnam 'dren
NK024(ya)001:9813: rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen pos mdzad pa'i
NK024(ya)001:9814: bde gshegs bdun gyi mchod pa'i chog sgrigs yid bzhin
NK024(ya)001:9816: bsdu na mkhan po'i mdo chog ji bzhin pa skabs
NK024(ya)001:9817: 'dir bya'o //'di gnyis la mtshams sbyor dang phyag len
NK024(ya)001:9818: gyi khyad par mtha' chod cing dmigs phyed pa sogs
NK024(ya)001:9819: yid bzhin dbang rgyal kho na legs shing /
NK024(ya)001:9820: don mkhan po'i mdo chog las gzhan du med pas khyad par med par sems /
NK024(ya)001:9821: de gnyis gang byed kyang gtor ma bsngo ba rnams ma byung yang 'thus shing 'og tu 'chad la /
NK024(ya)001:9822: mthar chags su bgyis kyang 'gal ba med par shes so //
NK024(ya)001:9823: gnas brtan bcu drug gi cho ga rnam grangs mang bar yod par grags kyang /
NK024(ya)001:9824: pan chen byams gling pa'i gsung zhig mthong ba ha cang mang pa'i skyon dang /
NK024(ya)001:9825: gnyags ban rnam rgyal bzang pos mdzad pa'i khyer bde
NK024(ya)001:9826: zhing khungs che ba 'dug kyang lung rgyun yod med
NK024(ya)001:9827: kyang ma shes pas 'dir sgrub mchod rgyas par grub
NK024(ya)001:9828: pas ma byung kyang chad pa'i skyon med la /
NK024(ya)001:9829: 'on kyang gzhung tshig yal bar mi 'dor phyir shin
NK024(ya)001:9830: tu bsdu na phyag mchod tsam gyis 'thus 'dra bas
NK024(ya)001:9831: / 'dir rig 'dzin yol mo pan+di ta bstan 'dzin nor bu'i gsung bzhin bkod pa ni 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:9832: na mo bud+d+ha bo d+hi sa t+wa b+h+yah bsam yas gzhal med khang rgyas gan+d+ho lar //
NK024(ya)001:9833: rin chen myu gu bkra ba'i 'dab ldan khri //
NK024(ya)001:9834: pad zlar rab 'gying bde gshegs rgyal pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:9835: mtshan dpe'i gzi byin 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9836: te se'i rir bzhugs gnas brtan yan lag 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:9837: lha dang lha min gnod sbyin gyis phul snod //
NK024(ya)001:9838: spos phor rnga yab legs 'dzin dgra bcom 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9839: stong dang sum brgyas bskor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9840: u shi ra yi tshal gnas ma pham pa //
NK024(ya)001:9841: ting 'dzin mi g.yo mnyam gzhag phyag rgyas 'gying //
NK024(ya)001:9842: brgya phrag dgra bcom tshogs kyis mdun bdar te //
NK024(ya)001:9843: rgyal gsung bstan pa spel la lo ma bdun pa'i 'khri shing nags na gnas //
NK024(ya)001:9844: phyag g.yas zhi ba'i sdigs mdzub g.yon rnga yab //
NK024(ya)001:9845: seng ldeng nags par rab basngagasa dgra bcom 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9846: stong dang bzhi bzlas bskor la zangs gling gnas bzhugs dgra bcom dus ldan ni //
NK024(ya)001:9847: lha dang lha mos gus phul rna cha 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:9848: stong dang brgya phrag rang 'dra'i 'dus par bcas //
NK024(ya)001:9849: lha mi'i yon gnas gyur la sing ga la yi gling bzhugs s+aa ra na //
NK024(ya)001:9850: rdo rje mo yi bur grags sdigs mdzub dang //
NK024(ya)001:9851: dri zas phul ba'i rnga yab legs 'dzin 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9852: dgra bcom stong rtsa bskor la chu bo ya mun na'i ngogs bzang po'i mtshan //
NK024(ya)001:9853: phyag g.yas chos 'chad phyag rgya g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:9854: nyon mongs med cing dgra bcom zag med 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9855: stong dang nyis brgyas bskor la ka smi rir bzhugs 'phags pa gser be'u //
NK024(ya)001:9856: klu rnams kyis phul rin chen zhags pa 'dren //
NK024(ya)001:9857: brgya phrag lnga pa'i dgra bcom che rnams kyis //
NK024(ya)001:9858: lus btud sri zhus bsten la ba lang spyod gling 'od zer 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:9859: yongs bzung b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha gser can phyag /
NK024(ya)001:9860: mnyam gzhag phyag rgyas rab bcings dgra bcom pa //
NK024(ya)001:9861: bdun brgyas yongs su bskor la sgra mi snyan bzhugs 'phags pa ba ku la //
NK024(ya)001:9862: rin chen gter gyi ne'u le phyag na bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:9863: dad pas grol ba rnams kyi mchog gcig 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9864: dgra bcom dgu brgyas bskor la pri yang kur gnas
NK024(ya)001:9865: ston sras sgra gcan 'dzin //'chi med sgeg mos legs
NK024(ya)001:9867: stong dang brgya phrag gcig gi grangs snyed 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9868: yongs 'dzin mang pos bkur la bya rgod phung po'i rir gnas lam phran bstan //
NK024(ya)001:9869: bsam gtan la chags mnyam gzhag phyag rgya mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:9870: gzhan sems bsgyur ba rnams kyi mchog gcig 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9871: stong dang drug brgyas bskor la lus 'phags gling bzhugs seng ge'i sgra sgrog pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:9872: mchog gyur b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms len //
NK024(ya)001:9873: glegs bam lhung bzed legs bsnams dgra bcom pa //
NK024(ya)001:9874: stong phrag 'khor gyis bskor la sum rtsen gnas bzhugs 'phags pa lam bstan ni //
NK024(ya)001:9875: phyag g.yas chos 'chad g.yon na glegs bam 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:9876: dgra bcom chen po dgu brgya'i grangs snyed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:9877: yongs bskor lha yi bla mar yul dbus ngos yangs
NK024(ya)001:9878: rir gnas klu yi sde //'khar gsil dang ni rigs
NK024(ya)001:9880: bum pa bzang po legs bsnams dgra bcom 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9881: stong dang nyis brgyas bskor la bi hu la yi rir bzhugs sbed byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:9882: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i gsung rab glegs bam bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:9883: mtshan gzhan ba lang bdag ces dgra bcom 'khor //
NK024(ya)001:9884: stong dang bzhi brgyas bskor la gangs can rir bzhugs gnas brtan mi phyed pa //
NK024(ya)001:9885: rgyal bas rab gnang byang chen mchod rten 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:9886: snying rje chen gnas yongs kyi mchog gcig pu //
NK024(ya)001:9887: dgra bcom stong gis bskor la rim gro par mngags dge bsnyen d+ha r+m+aa ta //
NK024(ya)001:9888: ral pa'i thod bcings snang ba mtha' yas gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:9889: rnga yab bum par bcas thogs bde gshegs bka'i //
NK024(ya)001:9890: khur 'dzin sprul par bcas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9891: rab brjid dpa' ba'i chas ldan yul 'khor bsrung //'phags skyes mig mi bzang dang rnam thos bu //
NK024(ya)001:9892: rgyud mang ral gri sbrul zhags rgyal mtshan bcas //
NK024(ya)001:9893: sde bcas bstan pa bsrung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:9894: mchod 'os rnams la gus pas phyag bgyis shing //
NK024(ya)001:9895: phyag 'os mchod pa'i dge legs char bzang pos //
NK024(ya)001:9896: bslab gsum nor ldan dge 'dun rgya mtsho'i sde //
NK024(ya)001:9897: thub bstan dbyar gyi lang tshor rab 'phel shog /
NK024(ya)001:9899: skyes thob shes rab rgya mtsho'i me long 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:9900: mang du thos pa'i nor mang gsal min mod //
NK024(ya)001:9901: sbyangs pa'i cho ga med la shes bya yi //
NK024(ya)001:9902: gzugs brnyan sna tshogs gsal ba 'di cir sems //
NK024(ya)001:9903: e wam cog sgar 'dus pa'i sprin //
NK024(ya)001:9904: stug por rgyas las thag pa che'i //
NK024(ya)001:9905: chos sgra dbyar gyi rnga bo che //
NK024(ya)001:9906: sgrog la bar chad med gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:9907: de ltar gnas brtan bcu drug ni dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i 'khor du yod la /
NK024(ya)001:9908: sman bla bde gshegs bdun gyi gtso bee d+aur+ya 'od
NK024(ya)001:9909: kyi rgyal po dkyil 'khor dang po'i pad 'dab la
NK024(ya)001:9910: bzhugs shing gzhan lhag ma drug dang phyogs skyong sogs
NK024(ya)001:9912: gsang sngags ltar na mgron thabs kyi lha dang /
NK024(ya)001:9913: 'dir sdom rten dang dkyil 'khor rnams kyi steng gi
NK024(ya)001:9914: nam mkha' sogs su tshogs zhing lta bur spyan drangs
NK024(ya)001:9915: pa yin pas mdo chog tshul bzhin btang bas phun
NK024(ya)001:9916: sum tshogs pa'i yan lag go //
NK024(ya)001:9918: drug pa gsum la rdo rje sems dpa'i tshab tu sh+aaka thub sgom gzhan 'dra'o //
NK024(ya)001:9919: zhes gsungs pa cha gsum dkyil 'khor bsdus ma tshar
NK024(ya)001:9920: na dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rdor sems thub par
NK024(ya)001:9921: gnas bsgyur te mchod gtor byin rlabs gong ltar byas
NK024(ya)001:9923: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK024(ya)001:9924: zhes sogs dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bor 'das gtor 'bul ba nas bgegs skrod sum+b+ha'i bar bya /
NK024(ya)001:9925: dkyil 'khor bsdus zin na 'das gtor bsngo mi dgos
NK024(ya)001:9926: shing dkyil 'khor so so'i 'das gtor rnams ni mchod
NK024(ya)001:9928: des na cha dang po'i mchod gtor byin brlab nas gsum pa'i bgegs skrod bar dkyus bzhin btang ngo /
NK024(ya)001:9929: 'di'i khongs su phyogs skyong gzhi bdag sogs 'du bas
NK024(ya)001:9930: gong du sman bla'i skabs gtor bsngo ma byas kyang
NK024(ya)001:9932: skabs 'dir bdag 'jug blangs te khrus man+dala gsol btab
NK024(ya)001:9933: nas bzung dbang rnams slob ma la ji ltar bskur
NK024(ya)001:9935: dge tshul dge slong gi sdom pa ni blang mi dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:9936: dbang dngos ni bla ma dge slong yin na chos
NK024(ya)001:9937: gos gsum legs par gyon te rang thub par bsam
NK024(ya)001:9939: slob ma yang rab byung dang khyim pa gang yin kyang khrus legs par byas te /
NK024(ya)001:9940: rang rang gi chas bzang po dang ldan pas 'dus te gral la 'khod /
NK024(ya)001:9942: brgyad pa ni bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:9943: zhes gsungs pa ltar slob dpon gyis /
NK024(ya)001:9944: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:9945: zhes sogs sngags dang bcas te rnam bum ma ma las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:9946: dbang gi phyir bgegs gtor mdzad srol 'dug pas /
NK024(ya)001:9947: gtor ma bsang sbyang byin brlabs sngags bsngosa bden brdar
NK024(ya)001:9948: bka' bsgo sogs phyag rdor dbang gi skabs bzhin la
NK024(ya)001:9949: / bden brdar skabs khyad par du yang dkon mchog
NK024(ya)001:9950: rin po che rnam pa gsum gyi dkyil 'khor lha
NK024(ya)001:9951: tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK024(ya)001:9956: man+dala me tog bkye bsdu byas rjes /
NK024(ya)001:9957: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:9958: don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin
NK024(ya)001:9960: de'i che du 'dir 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:9961: yan lag nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sgor zhugs te
NK024(ya)001:9962: smin grol rnams tshul bzhin nyams su blangs te sems
NK024(ya)001:9963: can thams cad kyi don bgyid snyam pa byang chub
NK024(ya)001:9964: kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed pa sngon du btang ste
NK024(ya)001:9965: gsan 'tshal / thugs bskyed phog cing nyan par gdams pa sogs 'brel dgod /
NK024(ya)001:9967: u rgyan chen po dang bi ma las /
NK024(ya)001:9968: mngon par mtho ba'i theg pa dang nges par legs pa'i theg pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:9969: de yang so so thar pa las /
NK024(ya)001:9970: brtsam par bya zhing dbyung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:9971: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya //
NK024(ya)001:9972: zhes gsungs pa'i brtsam par bya ba ni dge bsnyen /
NK024(ya)001:9973: dbyung bar bya zhes bas dge tshul /
NK024(ya)001:9974: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya zhes yongs su
NK024(ya)001:9975: rdzogs pa'i dge slong ste tshul gsum rim par bshad
NK024(ya)001:9976: cing / lam der zhugs nas klog pa thos bsam dang /
NK024(ya)001:9977: spong ba bsam gtan lhur byas nas nyon mongs pa
NK024(ya)001:9978: sogs dgra rnams bcom ste rnam byang bsgrub dgos pas
NK024(ya)001:9979: / 'dam bu'i khyim na glang chen bzhin //'chi bdag sde chen gzhom par bya //
NK024(ya)001:9981: tshul des nges legs kyi 'bras bu ster bar nus pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:9982: gang zhig rab tu bag yod par //
NK024(ya)001:9984: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs te //
NK024(ya)001:9985: sdug bsngal tha mar byed par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:9987: gzhan yang rigs brgya dbye ba las /
NK024(ya)001:9988: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spong byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:9989: ye shes bcu drug chas sbyangs rab zhi ba //
NK024(ya)001:9990: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim par sbyangs nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:9991: nyon mongs dgra rnam zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK024(ya)001:9993: de lta bu'i nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa la /
NK024(ya)001:9994: bstan pa spyi'i lugs la gang zag gi rigs dang sbyar ba'i so thar rigs bdun gang rigs sam /
NK024(ya)001:9995: tshigs gsum rim nod kyi dge slong gi dngos por
NK024(ya)001:9996: bsgrubs te lam la tshul bzhin du ci nus kyi
NK024(ya)001:9997: bslab cing 'bras bu sgrub pa las gzhan du med
NK024(ya)001:9998: kyang / 'dir theg pa'i yang rtse snga 'gyur dang /
NK024(ya)001:9999: khyad par 'dus pa mdo'i lugs la theg pa gong
NK024(ya)001:10000: mas 'og ma zil gyis gnon pa'i dgongs pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:10001: // spyir sngags lam kho na ltar smin grol gyis
NK024(ya)001:10002: khog phub pa'i khongs nas bye brag tu theg pa
NK024(ya)001:10003: 'og ma rnams kyi lam gyi rim pa yang tshang
NK024(ya)001:10004: la ma nor bar ston pa'i lam srol rmad du
NK024(ya)001:10006: 'dir nyan thos kyi dkyil 'khor du smin byed kyi dbang dang sdom pa sogs 'byung ba lags shing /
NK024(ya)001:10007: de yang spyir sgrub khrigs sum cus bstan pa yin
NK024(ya)001:10008: kyang 'khrugs sdebs sna tshogs su gyur pa rnams bsgrigs
NK024(ya)001:10010: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu gsum pa yan chad kyi
NK024(ya)001:10011: brgyad pa dang dgu pa tsam ma gtogs slob dpon
NK024(ya)001:10013: phal cher chad lhag med tsam du grub pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:10014: de yang sa bcad brgyad pa khrus bya ba slob
NK024(ya)001:10015: ma 'dus te bya dgos pa yang grub ma thag
NK024(ya)001:10016: yin / dgu pa ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:10017: sdom pa zhu ba'i yon dngos po dag pa gcig 'bul lo //
NK024(ya)001:10018: zhes gsungs pas 'byor na tshogs rdzogs shing tshul khrims
NK024(ya)001:10019: mthar phyin pa'i rten 'brel yod pas zang zing gi
NK024(ya)001:10020: dngos po gang rung dbul zhing ma 'byor na man+dala
NK024(ya)001:10021: gyi cho ga 'og nas 'byung bas des khyab par
NK024(ya)001:10022: gda'/ rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu pa nas bcu gsum pa'i bar ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:10023: bcu pa ni khru gang las lhag pa'i steng du
NK024(ya)001:10024: mi rung yang 'dir chos 'chad pas khri'i steng du
NK024(ya)001:10025: 'dug par bya'o // bcu gcig pa rgyan gyi mchog tshul khrims yin pas hrul yang btsun chas bgo /
NK024(ya)001:10026: 'dzom na bzang po kho na mchog tu mdzes pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:10027: bcu gnyis pa khri ni gzhan gyi tshogs rdzogs shing
NK024(ya)001:10028: chos kyi che ba 'byin pas de la 'dzeg pa'o
NK024(ya)001:10029: // bcu gsum pa ston pa bsgoms pas rang bzhin gyi blo 'gyur byin rlabs 'byung ste /
NK024(ya)001:10030: ser mo tsam zhig gyon pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:10031: ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya //
NK024(ya)001:10033: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir sa bcad bcu pa'i don chos smra ba khri la 'dug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10034: bcu gcig pa rab byung gi chas bya dgos pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10035: bcu gnyis pa khrir 'dzeg pa sogs kyang yul dus
NK024(ya)001:10036: dang bstun pa'i bcas mi stongs tsam grub pa 'dir
NK024(ya)001:10037: gda'/ bcu gsum pa ston pa sgom pa ni 'dir
NK024(ya)001:10038: gsang sngags mos pa lam byed dang 'brel ba yin
NK024(ya)001:10039: pas chos smra ba bdag kyang tha mal gyi rnam
NK024(ya)001:10040: par nam yang mi blta zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10041: bstan pa'i bdag po ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:10042: 'das mtshan dang dpe byad kyis legs par brgyan cing
NK024(ya)001:10043: mthong na mi mthun pa med pa 'od zer gyi
NK024(ya)001:10044: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa'i dbus na bzhugs pa mngon sum
NK024(ya)001:10045: lta bur mos gus dung ba skyed de blo 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:10047: bcu bzhi pa bum pa bca' tshul gsungs pa ni
NK024(ya)001:10048: bzhi pa rab gnas dang 'brel mtshungs su bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:10049: ltar de gnyis sdebs te legs par grub zin /
NK024(ya)001:10050: de mtshungs bdag mdun gyi sgrub mchod sogs kyang smin rgyas su grub /
NK024(ya)001:10051: bdag 'jug blang ba ni gzhung 'dir dngos bstan du gsal ba ma byu nga yang /
NK024(ya)001:10052: glan ban gyi chog khrigs su de nas ru bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK024(ya)001:10053: sh+aaka thub la bden pa bzhi'i dbang zhus la /
NK024(ya)001:10054: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdag 'jug kyang grub pas /
NK024(ya)001:10055: des na skabs 'dir bla ma dang ston pa thub
NK024(ya)001:10056: pa'i dbang po gnyis su med pa la nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:10057: kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba zhu
NK024(ya)001:10059: rtsa bar bcu dgu pa gsol ba gdab pa la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:10062: dang po ni sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs /
NK024(ya)001:10064: dge 'dun gsum la phyag gsum gsum byas la dkon mchog gsum du mos gus bya /
NK024(ya)001:10065: gnyis pa ni bla ma thub par bsgoms pa'i dbu'i
NK024(ya)001:10066: gtsug tor du nor bu 'od 'phro ba las rang
NK024(ya)001:10067: gi 'dod rgu 'byung bar bsam ste thal mo sbyar
NK024(ya)001:10068: te / kun mkhyen ye shes kyis gsol ba lan gsum gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:10069: zhes gsungs pa 'dir len dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:10070: de la yang nyan thos rang gzhung ltar dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10071: theg chen kha skong ltar kun mkhyen ye shes kyis
NK024(ya)001:10072: gsol ba 'debs pa gnyis su bshad pa'i dang por
NK024(ya)001:10073: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog rnams
NK024(ya)001:10074: la mos gus rtse gcig pas yan lag lnga ldan
NK024(ya)001:10075: gyi phyag lan gsum mdzad pa zhu /
NK024(ya)001:10076: zhes brda' sprad de sangs rgyas la phyag gsum bya /
NK024(ya)001:10077: yang mdo'i glegs bam dngos dang /
NK024(ya)001:10078: lha tshogs 'di rnams kyi thugs rgyud la bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:10079: 'gog bden rnam byang gi chos dkon mchog la dmigs
NK024(ya)001:10080: pa 'i phyag gsum mdzad par zhu /
NK024(ya)001:10081: zhes chos la phyag gsum bya /
NK024(ya)001:10082: yang dkyil 'khor 'dir bzhugs pa'i dge 'dun dkon mchog
NK024(ya)001:10083: rnams la dngos mtshungs kyi dad pa chen pos phyag
NK024(ya)001:10085: zhes dge 'dun la dmigs pa'i phyag gsum bya /
NK024(ya)001:10086: des ni nyan thos rang gzhung ltar gsol ba gdab pa'i dod yin la /
NK024(ya)001:10087: gnyis pa theg chen nas kha bskang pa'i gsol gdab
NK024(ya)001:10088: bya ba'i slad du slob dpon bdag nyid ston pa
NK024(ya)001:10089: dngos su gsal ba'i gtsug tor gyi nor bu 'od
NK024(ya)001:10090: zer kun nas 'phro ba de nyid las rang gi
NK024(ya)001:10091: 'dod rgu thams cad 'byung bar bsam zhing snyim pa
NK024(ya)001:10092: me tog dang bcas te thal mo sbyar te gsol
NK024(ya)001:10093: ba 'debs pa 'di rjes zlos lan gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10094: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK024(ya)001:10095: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnam sbyong ba //
NK024(ya)001:10096: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen gter //
NK024(ya)001:10097: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin gsol //
NK024(ya)001:10100: bco lnga pa gso sbyong ni dkon mchog gi rten
NK024(ya)001:10101: gyi drung du mchod pa dang yan lag bdun pa
NK024(ya)001:10102: byas te zhes gsungs pas mchod pa ni 'byor pa
NK024(ya)001:10103: dang bstun nas 'di ltar bsham pa lags shing /
NK024(ya)001:10104: bzhengs te phyag bya ba dang bstun yan lag bdun
NK024(ya)001:10105: pa tshig rjes don dran rnam par dag pa zhig
NK024(ya)001:10106: mdzad par zhu / slob dpon gyis byang drangs te /
NK024(ya)001:10107: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:10108: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i zhes sogs bya /
NK024(ya)001:10109: 'dir gso sbyong ni nyan thos kyi theg pa'i skabs
NK024(ya)001:10110: 'dir tshul gsum blang dgos pas dge bsnyen gyi tshul
NK024(ya)001:10111: khrims kyi dod lta bu gsar ma ltar na don
NK024(ya)001:10113: 'dir rang gzhung dri ma med pa las ji ltar 'byung ba ltar brjod dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:10114: gzhung las dgongs gsol ma gsungs pa bla ma rnams
NK024(ya)001:10115: phyag len la mdzad pas 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum
NK024(ya)001:10117: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang bya chub
NK024(ya)001:10118: sems dpa' thams cad dang slob dpon bdag la dgongs
NK024(ya)001:10119: su gsol / ji ltar de bzhin gshegs pa dgra
NK024(ya)001:10120: bcom pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rta
NK024(ya)001:10126: rang gi don rjes su thob pa /
NK024(ya)001:10127: srid pa kun tu sbyor ba yongs su zad pa /
NK024(ya)001:10129: legs pa rnam par grol ba'i thugs /
NK024(ya)001:10130: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can de dag gis /
NK024(ya)001:10131: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10132: phan par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10133: grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10134: nad med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10135: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10136: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:10137: bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang
NK024(ya)001:10138: chub rtogs par bya ba'i phyir gso sbyong nges par
NK024(ya)001:10139: mdzad pa de bzhin du bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi
NK024(ya)001:10140: bas kyang / dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid
NK024(ya)001:10141: sang nyi ma ma shar gyi bar du'am ji srid
NK024(ya)001:10142: cho ga ma grub kyi bar du gso sbyong nges
NK024(ya)001:10144: rtsa bar gsal kha ma byung yang 'di lan gsum mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:10145: de nas bslab pa brjod pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos kyang mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10146: deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:10147: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi spyad cing //
NK024(ya)001:10148: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK024(ya)001:10149: skyon mi mang po nyer bsten pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:10150: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:10151: khri stan che mtho mi bya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:10152: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK024(ya)001:10153: dri dang phreng ba rgyan dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:10154: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:10155: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK024(ya)001:10156: srog gcod la sogs mi byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:10157: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs spong //
NK024(ya)001:10158: bla med byang chub myur thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:10160: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:10161: ces lan gsum brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK024(ya)001:10163: tshul khrims rnam dag gi gzungs 'di nyer gcig gam brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10164: zhes gsungs pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10169: pad+ma bib+hu shi ta b+hu dza /
NK024(ya)001:10172: a wa lo ki te h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:10173: zhes tshig gzhan gyis bar ma chod par bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:10174: de ltar theg pa chen po'i gso sbyong 'dis skabs 'dir dge bsnyen gyi dod dang /
NK024(ya)001:10175: slad kyi dge slong nas khyim pa yan chad thams
NK024(ya)001:10176: cad thun mong gi spyod yul yin pas cho 'phrul
NK024(ya)001:10177: dang sa ga sogs dus tshigs khyad par can rnams
NK024(ya)001:10179: khyad par rten gyi drung du rang gis blangs chog
NK024(ya)001:10180: par gsungs pas de bzhin du phyag len la thebs
NK024(ya)001:10181: par mdzod / de rjes ltung ba spyi bshags 'di
NK024(ya)001:10182: sdom ldan gyi bshags pa dang gso sbyong gi dod
NK024(ya)001:10183: par mdzod / yin la / nyams chag byung na
NK024(ya)001:10184: lugs 'dir bskyar chog kyang 'di yin par gsungs shing
NK024(ya)001:10185: skabs 'dir bshags sdom gyi dod yin te /
NK024(ya)001:10187: yang na so sor thar pa'i sdom pa la rtsa
NK024(ya)001:10188: ba'i ltung ba byung na lhag ma gang yod phul
NK024(ya)001:10189: la rtsa ba nas bskyar bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10190: yan lag gi nyes pa phra rags gang yang ngo shes par byas te /
NK024(ya)001:10192: sbed sems med par ltung ba la ltung bar ngo
NK024(ya)001:10193: shes shing dran pas nya stong la sogs pa la
NK024(ya)001:10194: spyi bshags byas pas nyams chag thams cad sor chud
NK024(ya)001:10195: cing gso / sgrib pa dag pa /
NK024(ya)001:10196: rang bzhin gyi dge ba gso zhing sdig pa sbyong ba ste thams cad kyis thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:10197: zhes gsungs pas thal sbyar mdzad de tshig don rjes
NK024(ya)001:10198: dran gyi sgo nas 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum mdzad
NK024(ya)001:10199: / bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po la
NK024(ya)001:10200: sogs pa phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK024(ya)001:10201: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10202: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10203: bdag sh+aakya'i dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi bas rtsa
NK024(ya)001:10204: bar 'di bzhin gsungs pa dge slong gi dbang du
NK024(ya)001:10205: byas kyis / gzhan du rang dge tshul yin na sh+aakya'i dge tshul /
NK024(ya)001:10206: dge bsnyen yin na sh+aakya'i dge bsnyen /
NK024(ya)001:10207: gang yang ma yin na bdag ming 'di zhes brjod dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:10208: tshe 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas tha ma da lta la thug gi bar du /
NK024(ya)001:10213: yid kyi sgo nas sdig pa mi dge ba bcu bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10214: mtshams med lnga bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10215: de dang nye ba lnga bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10216: so sor thar pa'i sngom pa dang 'gal ba bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10217: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa dang 'gal ba bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10218: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig dang 'gal ba bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10219: dkon mchog gsum la gnod pa'i lam bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10220: dam pa'i chos spangs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10221: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun la skur pa btab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10222: pha dang ma la ma gus pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10223: mkhan po dang slob dpon la ma gus pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10224: grogs tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams la ma
NK024(ya)001:10225: gus pa la sogs te mdor na mtho ris dang
NK024(ya)001:10226: thar pa'i gegs su gyur cing /
NK024(ya)001:10227: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi rgyur gyur pa'i nyes
NK024(ya)001:10228: ltung sdig sgrib kyi tshogs ci mchis pa de dag
NK024(ya)001:10229: thams cad bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po
NK024(ya)001:10230: la sogs pa phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:10231: dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi spyan sngar mthol
NK024(ya)001:10234: slan chad kyang sdom par bgyid lags so //
NK024(ya)001:10235: mthol zhing bshags na bdag bde ba la reg par gnas par 'gyur gyi /
NK024(ya)001:10240: zhes gsungs pas thabs legs bya /
NK024(ya)001:10242: bcu drug pa tshul khrims ni /
NK024(ya)001:10243: lha mi yul gyi chos lugs dang /
NK024(ya)001:10244: rgyal ba'i lung gi chos lugs 'dul ba mdo sde mngon pa las 'byung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:10245: zhes gsungs pa ni rgyas par 'og tu 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:10246: bcu bdun pa btsun chas ni /
NK024(ya)001:10247: rab tu byung ba la 'os pa rnams dge bsnyen gyis kyang mos rten du bcang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10248: zhes gsungs pa yang go sla /
NK024(ya)001:10249: bco brgyad pa lha dang bcu dgu pa gsol gdab gnyis gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:10250: skabs 'dir dge tshul dang dge slong gi sdom pa 'bogs dgos pa'i dang po ni /
NK024(ya)001:10252: nyi shu pa sdom pa zhu ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:10253: dge bsnyen dge tshul dge slong gsum las mtha' ma gzhan du'o //
NK024(ya)001:10255: khyad par dge bsnyen la bar chad dri ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10257: mkhan por 'du shes bskyed mi dgos //
NK024(ya)001:10258: dge tshul dge slong la dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:10259: skabs 'dir dge tshul gyi bar chad dri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:10260: bar chad yod med dri pas yin pa la yin pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10261: ma yin pa la ma yin zhes lan drang por thob ces brjod /
NK024(ya)001:10262: ces gsungs pa'i don kahthoga lugs la 'dul ba ltar dge bsnyen sgrub chog 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10263: 'dir zur lugs kho na bzhin dge bsnyen theg chen gso sbyong gis go bcad /
NK024(ya)001:10264: tshigs gsum gyi thog mar bar chad dri dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:10265: so thar kho na'i tshe bar ma rab byung dang
NK024(ya)001:10266: dge tshul la yang mkhan slob grogs dan dus go
NK024(ya)001:10267: slob dpon kha skongs ji tsam 'os pa dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:10268: pa'am / yang na mkhan slob sogs sbrags mar byed dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:10269: bsgrub bya yang gsum las lhag pa dus gcig tu
NK024(ya)001:10270: mi rung ba sogs rgyas bsdus skabs sbyar gyi lag
NK024(ya)001:10271: len bshad gzhi sogs mang yang /
NK024(ya)001:10272: 'dir mkhan slob kyi dod kho bo yin la /
NK024(ya)001:10273: dge 'dun ni gang zag phal pa'i las gral las
NK024(ya)001:10274: ches khyad par du gyur pa ston pa nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:10275: kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mngon sum du dkyil
NK024(ya)001:10276: 'khor 'dir bzhugs pa lags pas khyed rnams kyang gzhan
NK024(ya)001:10277: du bslab pa nod pa las kyang ches mchog tu
NK024(ya)001:10278: gyur cing skal ba bzang ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:10279: bsgrub bya yang grangs nges med pas 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:10280: cho ga dngos ni kah thog lugs su dge tshul
NK024(ya)001:10281: dang dge slong yang gdams ngag brjod pa sogs tshang
NK024(ya)001:10282: ma 'dul ba sor bzhag bzhin mdzad 'dug pa rnam
NK024(ya)001:10283: pa gcig tu legs par snang zhing skye la nyes
NK024(ya)001:10285: phyogs gcig na 'dir sngags lugs kyi cho ga mdo
NK024(ya)001:10286: lugs dang cha 'dra tsam ma gtogs mdo lugs dngos
NK024(ya)001:10288: so thar kho na'i las 'chags pa dang go chod pa yang cung mi yong ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10289: gdul bya yang sna tshogs su 'dus gshis bslab pa
NK024(ya)001:10290: la tshul bzhin bslab nus pa dka' bas 'dul ba
NK024(ya)001:10291: sgra ji bzhin par byas na nyes med phun tshogs
NK024(ya)001:10292: mi yong ba'i steng gzhan gyi klan ka yang 'byung
NK024(ya)001:10293: nye ba dang bstan par yang mi phan zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10294: mdo sngags 'dres pa'i lag len yang 'tshol ba sna
NK024(ya)001:10295: tshogs byung dogs pas des na 'dir zur lugs kho
NK024(ya)001:10296: na ltar so thar dang cha 'dra tsam byas bas
NK024(ya)001:10297: 'thus par go // so thar skabs mdo rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:10298: dang po'i mkhan po nyid kyis bar chad dris nas yongs su dag pa la skabs dabye'o //
NK024(ya)001:10299: zhes thog mar bar chad dris //
NK024(ya)001:10300: de nas bstan pa la rim bzhin 'jug phyir thog mar dge bsnyen du bsgrubs /
NK024(ya)001:10301: de'i rjes su zhu ba dang mkhan por gsol btab gtsug phud 'breg pa /
NK024(ya)001:10302: rtags cha lugs bsgyur ba rnams song nas bar ma rab byung dang /
NK024(ya)001:10303: de'i rjes su tshigs snga ma dge tshul du sgrub pa /
NK024(ya)001:10304: de nas tshigs phyi ma bsnyen rdzogs su sgrub pa yin kyang 'dir bar chad dris nas /
NK024(ya)001:10305: dge bsnyen ni gong du song ba'i theg chen gso sbyong gis go bcad de /
NK024(ya)001:10306: de man cha 'dra tsam mdzad srol ltar /
NK024(ya)001:10307: dang por bar chad dri bar byed dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:10308: des na nged kyis dris pa 'di rnams la ma yin nam zhes pa'i dus /
NK024(ya)001:10310: khyod mu stegs can ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10312: lo bco lnga ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10313: ma lo bco lnga lon pa bya rog skrod mi nus pa ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10314: ma bya rog skrod nus pa lo bdun ma lon pa ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10315: ma pha mas ma gnang ba ma ma pha mas
NK024(ya)001:10316: ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba ma yin
NK024(ya)001:10317: ma nad pa ma dge slong ma sun phyungs pa
NK024(ya)001:10318: ma yin nam / brku thabs su gnas pa ma
NK024(ya)001:10319: tha dad du gnas pa ma gnas par mi bya
NK024(ya)001:10320: ba ma za ma ma ma ning ma sprul pa
NK024(ya)001:10321: ma dud 'gro ma mu stegs can zhugs pa ma
NK024(ya)001:10322: ma yin nam / ma bsad pa / pha bsad pa /
NK024(ya)001:10325: de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi khrag phyungs pa /
NK024(ya)001:10326: pham par 'gyur ba'i ltung ba bzhi las gang yang rung ba byung ba ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10327: rgyu las bzlog pa'i chad pa khas mi len pa la gnas nas phyungs pa /
NK024(ya)001:10333: rgyal pos ma gnang ba yul thag mi ring ba /
NK024(ya)001:10340: byang gi sgra mi snyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:10341: mtshan lan gsum du gyur pa /
NK024(ya)001:10343: sdig sdig lta bu'i mtshan nyid can /
NK024(ya)001:10344: gling gzhan du skyes pa'i tshul byad mi 'dra ba ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10346: khyod bar chad dang mi ldan pas bstan pa'i snod du rung bar 'dug pas /
NK024(ya)001:10347: bdag gis khyod rab tu byung bar bgyi /
NK024(ya)001:10348: zhes skabs dabye'o zhes gsungs pas de ltar na khyed
NK024(ya)001:10349: rnams bar chad dang mi ldan par rtogs te snod
NK024(ya)001:10350: du rung bar shes nas rab tu byung bar skabs
NK024(ya)001:10352: gos ster slob dpon la sprad do //
NK024(ya)001:10353: slob dpon gyis bar chad dag gam dri /
NK024(ya)001:10354: dag zhe na las byed pa'i dge slong la gtad de dge 'dun la zhu ba byas /
NK024(ya)001:10355: dge 'dun gyis gnang nas gal te yongs su dag na'o //
NK024(ya)001:10357: gtsug phud breg par spro'am dri /
NK024(ya)001:10359: slob dpon gyis bslab pa 'bogs par gsol te sdom pa dbog /
NK024(ya)001:10361: rgan pas dus go bar byed pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:10362: 'dir slob mkhan gnyis dang dge tshul gsum dril nas
NK024(ya)001:10363: mkhan pos dge tshul du slob ma tshar bar byed
NK024(ya)001:10364: pa'i lugs so // sdom pa dngos la gsum ga tshang dgos pa la /
NK024(ya)001:10365: 'dir mkhan po la sangs rgyas su mos /
NK024(ya)001:10366: de'i bka' lung gi tshig dang mthan pa'i don yid la rjes su bzung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10367: rang rjes zlos lan gsum gyi tha ma la bslab
NK024(ya)001:10368: sdom tshul khrims thob shes kyi sems la gdeng brtan
NK024(ya)001:10369: po dang / grogs dge 'dun dngos dang tsakli'i gzugs
NK024(ya)001:10370: rnams kyis kyang bar chad yongs su dag par nges
NK024(ya)001:10371: po dang / shing / sdom pa mthar phyin pa la sngo ba'i bdun ldan du nges pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:10373: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i don bzhin bya dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:10374: 'on kyang cho ga rnams cung zhig 'khrugs 'dug pa phyag len bzhir bsdebs pa la /
NK024(ya)001:10375: thog mar zhu ba bya dgos shing de yang 'dul
NK024(ya)001:10376: ba nas rgyas bsdus kyi dbye sgo sna tshogs kyang
NK024(ya)001:10378: bla mas bzhengs te dkyil 'khor la phyag gsum byas te /
NK024(ya)001:10380: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams gsan du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10381: tshe dang ldan pa 'di rnams mkhan po bdag las rab tu dbyung bar 'tshal te /
NK024(ya)001:10382: khyim pa gos dkar po can skra dang kha spu ma bregs pa las /
NK024(ya)001:10383: legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul ba las rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal te /
NK024(ya)001:10384: tshe dang ldan pa 'di rnams rab tu 'byung bar 'tshal zhing skra dang kha spu bregs nas /
NK024(ya)001:10385: gos ngur smrig bgos te yang dag pa kho nar
NK024(ya)001:10386: dad pas khyim nas khyim med par mkhan po bdag
NK024(ya)001:10388: de yang bar chad kyi chos rnams yongs su dag go zhes khong rnams nyid mchi na /
NK024(ya)001:10390: zhes lan gsum zhus pa'i mthar ston pa nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:10391: kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pas gal te yongs su
NK024(ya)001:10392: dag na'o // zhes gsungs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:10393: mkhan por gsol ba btab pa gzhung nas mi gsal bas mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10394: gtsug phud 'breg tshul gsungs pa skabs 'dir babs pas /
NK024(ya)001:10395: bla mas mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya bsgrub bya'i spyi bor bcings te /
NK024(ya)001:10396: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya ba gtsug phud breg par spro'am zhes dri zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10397: spro lags zhes lan btab pa'i mthar gtsug phud re
NK024(ya)001:10398: bregs shing sdom rten ston pa'i sku la phul te
NK024(ya)001:10399: / bstan pa la dga' ba'i lha rnams dgyes pa khyad par can bskyed par mdzad du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10401: 'dul bar skabs 'dir khrus dgos kyang 'dir gong du song bas 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:10402: rtsa bar gos ster gsungs pa gtod tshigs las chog
NK024(ya)001:10403: ltar brjod na legs par mthong bas de'i tshul ni
NK024(ya)001:10404: bsgrub bya rnams kyi phrag g.yon par gding ba dang
NK024(ya)001:10405: sham thabs bla gos rnams bltabs te bkal /
NK024(ya)001:10406: thog mar dpon slob gnyis ka'i phyag gis chos gos steng 'og tu gzung la /
NK024(ya)001:10407: 'di stod du rgyun du gyon par byed pa'i chos
NK024(ya)001:10408: gos bla gos zhes bya ba khyim pa dang mu
NK024(ya)001:10409: stegs can las rtags khyad par du gyur /
NK024(ya)001:10410: dge sbyong gi dran pa gso /
NK024(ya)001:10413: rlung dang nyi ma la sogs pa'i tsha grang gi reg pa las skyob pa'i gos su gnang /
NK024(ya)001:10414: sham thabs gtad la 'di smad kyi nang du gyon par byed pa'i mthang gos zhes bya ba /
NK024(ya)001:10416: ngo tsha ba'i gnas las skyo ba /
NK024(ya)001:10417: sbrang bu la sogs pa'i reg pa bsrung /
NK024(ya)001:10418: khyim pa dang mu stegs can las rtags khyad par du gyur /
NK024(ya)001:10419: dge sbyong gi dran pa gso ba'i gos yin /
NK024(ya)001:10420: rgya gar na rung ba'i tshon gsum la kha dog
NK024(ya)001:10421: ngan par byed pas rgyags pa dang dregs pa 'joms
NK024(ya)001:10423: ston pas kyang stod g.yogs smad g.yogs 'di lta bu
NK024(ya)001:10424: bsnams nas lam la bslabs shing sangs rgyas nas rjes
NK024(ya)001:10425: 'jug rnams la'ang gos 'di lta bu gnang ba yin
NK024(ya)001:10426: pas / stod g.yogs smad g.yogs 'di lta bu gyon nas sems dul ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10427: zhi bar byed dgos pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:10429: 'di lhung bzed bya ba khyim pa'i kha phor /
NK024(ya)001:10431: rab byung dman pa gzhan las snod dpyad kyi rtags khyad par can du gyur pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:10432: 'di zas kyis 'gengs pa bzhin du rang gi shes rgyu yon tan gyis 'geng /
NK024(ya)001:10433: 'di'i nang nas zas la longs spyod pa bzhin du chos la longs spyod /
NK024(ya)001:10434: mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i bsod snyoms spyod pa'i snod du ston pas gnang ba yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:10437: 'di gding ba bya ba khyim pa'i dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:10439: phal cher ma nyams pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10440: dge 'dun gyi r+ts+wa'i gdan ma gtogs pa gnas mal
NK024(ya)001:10441: la longs spyod pa'i dus su 'dis skyabs nas longs
NK024(ya)001:10444: 'di chu tshags bya ba sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa snying rjes rab tu phye ba yin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10445: so sor thar pa'i sdom pa gzhan la gnod pa
NK024(ya)001:10446: gzhir bcas las bzlog pa yin pas sems can thams
NK024(ya)001:10447: cad la gnod pa spang dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10448: khyad par du chu 'di 'brel che 'byung nye /
NK024(ya)001:10449: nang dang nub tu dgos pas chu la srog chags yod med legs par brtags nas /
NK024(ya)001:10450: srog chags med pa ma rnyed na 'dis btsags nas
NK024(ya)001:10451: longs spyod pa'i don du gnang ba yin pas chu
NK024(ya)001:10453: des mtshon nas yo byad gang la'ang srog chags la mi gnod pa bya dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10456: de nas smad kyi sham gos dang /
NK024(ya)001:10461: lhung bzed sogs bla mas phyag nas gnang zhing mkho ba'i yo byad rnams gtad de /
NK024(ya)001:10462: zhes gsungs pa 'khar gsil gtod pa'i phyag bzhes so
NK024(ya)001:10463: thar la yang mi 'dug pas 'og tu dbang gi
NK024(ya)001:10465: gzhan rnams gong du song ba ltar ro //'dul bar
NK024(ya)001:10466: smon lam bzhi 'debs pa'i srol yod pa 'dir rang
NK024(ya)001:10467: gzhung ltar byas na legs shing /
NK024(ya)001:10468: rtsa bar bden pa'i rjes su zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:10469: bsgrub bya rnams la me tog 'thor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10471: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa'i byin gyis rlabs
NK024(ya)001:10472: kyis tshe dang ldan pa 'di rnams kyi tshul khrims
NK024(ya)001:10474: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK024(ya)001:10475: shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK024(ya)001:10476: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang /
NK024(ya)001:10477: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:10478: ces thams cad kyis mthun gyur brjod /
NK024(ya)001:10480: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyis mthun gyur mdzad par mos so //
NK024(ya)001:10481: de nas bsgrub bya rnams gos tshags legs par bcas
NK024(ya)001:10482: te stan gding ba'i steng nas dkyil 'khor gyi ston
NK024(ya)001:10483: pa dge 'dun dang bcas pa la dmigs pa'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:10484: gsum dang / mkhan por phyag gsum btsal te tsog
NK024(ya)001:10485: pur gding ba'i steng du thal mo bsnol la 'dug
NK024(ya)001:10486: gsum dang / ste / bar ma rab tu byung ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:10487: mkhan pos khyed rnams rab tu byung ba'i bsam pa skyes pa de legs te /
NK024(ya)001:10488: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:10489: rgyal srid mchil ma'i thal ba bzhin spangs nas //
NK024(ya)001:10490: dben par 'dong ste dgon par gnas byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:10491: nyon mongs spangs nas bdud ni bcoms nas su //
NK024(ya)001:10492: byang chub rdul med 'dus ma byas 'tshang rgya //
NK024(ya)001:10494: de yang barje ba gsum dgos pa'i rtags cha lugs barje ba ni grub /
NK024(ya)001:10495: bsam pa barje ba ni 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi
NK024(ya)001:10496: rang bzhin du shes pa la spong sems yang dag
NK024(ya)001:10497: pa dgos te / de las thar pa'i skyabs dkon
NK024(ya)001:10498: mchog gsum la ston pa dang skyabs dngos zla grogs
NK024(ya)001:10499: zhus nas myang 'das sgrub cing skabs 'dir theg pa
NK024(ya)001:10500: thun mong ba'i skabs nyan rang sangs rgyas gsum gang
NK024(ya)001:10501: du sems bskyed kyang chog par gsungs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10502: bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:10503: cho ga nyan thos lugs bzhin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:10505: sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas thob par bya /
