NK024(ya)001:10506: de'i phyir du khyim spangs te rab tu byung ngo snyam pa ni bsam pa barje ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:10507: ming spo ba rtsa ba las ma gsungs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10508: spyir barje ba gsum gyi skabs gsungs pas ming btags
NK024(ya)001:10509: na phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag tu 'gyur bas
NK024(ya)001:10510: ming spo bar 'dod na chos ming ci rigs btags
NK024(ya)001:10511: / mi spo na rang ming nas smos te bar
NK024(ya)001:10512: ma rab tu byung ba'i slad du 'di'i rjes zlos
NK024(ya)001:10516: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK024(ya)001:10517: rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su
NK024(ya)001:10518: mchi'o //'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos
NK024(ya)001:10519: la tshogs rnams kyi mchog dge 'dun la sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:10520: sh+aakya thub pa / sh+aakya seng ge /
NK024(ya)001:10522: gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i rjes su bdag rab tu dbyung bar 'tshal te /
NK024(ya)001:10523: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba khyim pa'i rtags spong
NK024(ya)001:10524: zhing rab tu byung ba'i rtags yang dag par len
NK024(ya)001:10525: to / mkhan pos bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10526: brjod pa gsum gyi tha mar mkhan pos thabs yin no //
NK024(ya)001:10527: slob mas legs so brjod do //
NK024(ya)001:10528: des bar ma rab tu byung ba'i dod yin /
NK024(ya)001:10530: de nas gnang ba sbyin pa ni dngos dang yid
NK024(ya)001:10531: kyis dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i gnas brtan dge slong
NK024(ya)001:10532: rnams kyis gal te yongs su dag na'o //
NK024(ya)001:10535: gong du zhu ba'i skabs su legs par grub zin pas 'dir mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10536: de nas dge tshul du sgrub par byed pa la /
NK024(ya)001:10538: de nas mkhan po'am mkhan pos gtad pa'i slob dpon gyi chos bshad ni /
NK024(ya)001:10539: zhes gsungs pa'i don so thar lugs la mkhan slob
NK024(ya)001:10540: tha dad pa'i tshe 'di man slob dpon gyi las
NK024(ya)001:10541: yin pa la dgongs te gsungs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10542: da res mkhan slob sbrags ma yin pas bsgrub bya
NK024(ya)001:10543: rnams dkyil 'khor la bzhugs pa'i ston pa gnas brtan
NK024(ya)001:10544: dge slong dang bcas pa rnams la phyag gsum dang
NK024(ya)001:10545: / mkhan por phyag gsum btsal te sngar bzhin 'dug tu bcug /
NK024(ya)001:10546: chos 'dul bar 'gal rkyen bzhi spong zhing mthun rkyen
NK024(ya)001:10547: lnga tshang sogs kyi bshad pa mdzad srol yod kyang
NK024(ya)001:10548: / de 'dra'i bshad pa bya mi dgos shing 'dir rtsa ba ltar bshad na 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:10549: tshe dang ldan pa khyed rnams 'khor ba las yid byung /
NK024(ya)001:10550: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bsam pa brtan pos 'khor
NK024(ya)001:10551: ba'i sdug bsngal las grol nas sangs rgyas kyi go
NK024(ya)001:10553: de'i ched du dge tshul gyi sdom pa thang lhod
NK024(ya)001:10554: med par gtsang mar bsrungs la sangs rgyas kyi gdung
NK024(ya)001:10555: gsob par bya snyam pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod byas
NK024(ya)001:10556: la / mkhan po dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10557: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:10558: ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:10559: mchog sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //'dod chags dang
NK024(ya)001:10560: bral ba rnams kyi mchog chos la tshogs rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:10561: mchog dge 'dun la mkhan po dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10562: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:10563: nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dge tshul du mkhan
NK024(ya)001:10567: bslab pa brjod pa'i don du 'di rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10569: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis srog gcod pa spangs te /
NK024(ya)001:10570: srog gcod pa las slar log pa de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:10571: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas
NK024(ya)001:10572: bzung nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa
NK024(ya)001:10573: spangs te / srog gcod pa las slar log par bgyid do //
NK024(ya)001:10574: yan lag dang po 'dis bdag sngon gyi 'phags pa
NK024(ya)001:10575: dgra bcom pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes
NK024(ya)001:10576: su bslab bo // rjes su sgrub bo //
NK024(ya)001:10578: gzhan yang 'phags pa dgra bcom pa de dag gis
NK024(ya)001:10579: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du ma byin par len pa
NK024(ya)001:10580: dang / mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10583: bcos pa'i chang myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK024(ya)001:10588: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10591: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK024(ya)001:10592: gser dngul len pa las spangs te gser dngul len
NK024(ya)001:10593: pa las slar log pa de bzhin du bdag ming
NK024(ya)001:10594: 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung nas
NK024(ya)001:10595: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du ma byin par len pa
NK024(ya)001:10596: dang / mi tshangs par spyod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10599: bcos pa'i chang myos par 'gyur ba bag med pa'i gnas dang /
NK024(ya)001:10602: rol mo'i sgra dang spos nyug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:10603: rgyan dang kha dog 'chang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10606: dus ma yin pa'i kha zas dang /
NK024(ya)001:10607: gser dngul len pa spangs te gser dngul len pa las slar log par bagyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:10608: yan lag phyi ma 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
NK024(ya)001:10609: pa de dag gi bslab pa la rjes su bslab
NK024(ya)001:10616: dus go ni ma byung yang 'thus shing spro na
NK024(ya)001:10617: 'og tu bsnyen rdzogs kyi skabs su yod pas der
NK024(ya)001:10618: blta'o // dge tshul du bsgrub pa tshar ro //
NK024(ya)001:10619: de nas bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i cho ga la mkhan
NK024(ya)001:10620: pos 'di skad brjod do //'di bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:10621: cho ga'i dod tsam bgyi ba la /
NK024(ya)001:10622: so thar lugs la sbyor dngos rjes gsum gyi dang
NK024(ya)001:10623: por yo byad tshags 'dzud dang dkon mchog gsum mngon
NK024(ya)001:10625: gnyis pa mkhan po mngon gyur /
NK024(ya)001:10626: gsum pa yo byad mngon gyur /
NK024(ya)001:10627: bzhi pa yongs dag mngon gyur phyir gsang ston bsko zhing des las bya ba /
NK024(ya)001:10628: lnga pa gsol ba mngon gyur /
NK024(ya)001:10629: drug pa slar yang dge 'dun gyi nang du yongs dag mngon gyur bya ba ste drug /
NK024(ya)001:10631: rkyen bzhi'am 'gal rkyen bzhi spangs mthun rkyen lnga dang ldan pas mngon gyur bcu tshang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:10632: khyad par dgu pa gsol ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10633: bcu pa las mngon gyur gyis cho ga dngos ston /
NK024(ya)001:10634: mjug chog gnyis kyi dang po thob pa dus go ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10635: gnyis pa gdams ngag bcu gcig sogs kyi sgo nas 'chad dgos kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10636: 'dir de 'dra'i zhib cha ma bshad cing /
NK024(ya)001:10637: kho bos mkhan slob sprags ma sogs yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:10638: dang po mchog gsum mngon gyur dang /
NK024(ya)001:10639: gnyis pa mkhan po mngon gyur sogs shugs kyis tshang /
NK024(ya)001:10640: gsum pa yo byad mngon gyur ni /
NK024(ya)001:10643: skabs der bsam pa bdag dge tshul bsnyen par rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:10644: pa dge slong thob par smon pas snam sbyar dang
NK024(ya)001:10645: / dge slong gi rtags sbyin me tog bkram la
NK024(ya)001:10646: gtor zhing chas su bcug ste r+ts+wa dang gding ba
NK024(ya)001:10647: / la bzhag la / zhes gsungs mod kyang spyi ltar yo byad mngon gyur 'dir bya dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:10648: de yang bla gos mthang gos gding ba chu tshags
NK024(ya)001:10649: sogs bar ma rab byung gi sngon du song ma
NK024(ya)001:10650: thag pa yin pas ma dgos shing bsnyen rdzogs dngos
NK024(ya)001:10651: la de gnyis byin rlabs dang cho ga mi 'dra
NK024(ya)001:10653: da lam rtsa bar snam sbyar tsam gsungs pas rtsa ba bzhin bgyis pas chog par sems pas /
NK024(ya)001:10656: mkhan pos 'grengs te bsgrub bya'i phrag g.yon du snam
NK024(ya)001:10657: sbyar bkal ba sogs gong ltar byas la 'di'i rjes
NK024(ya)001:10660: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i chos gos bgyis lags
NK024(ya)001:10661: pa rung ba spyad par 'os pa 'di chos gos
NK024(ya)001:10662: snam sbyar du byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:10663: lan gsum mthar thabs legs bya /
NK024(ya)001:10664: snam sbyar yod na kun gyis gyon /
NK024(ya)001:10665: lhung bzed la rtsa bar dbang gi dus bseg par
NK024(ya)001:10666: dang sbrags pa zhig dang lhung bzed rkyang pa zhig
NK024(ya)001:10667: byung ba'i rkyang pa de la byin brlab kyang 'byung
NK024(ya)001:10668: bas / de nyid 'dir len pa la dgongs pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:10669: bla mas lhung bzed dkyil 'khor phyogs su bstan te /
NK024(ya)001:10671: dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i lhung bzed 'di mi che'am /
NK024(ya)001:10679: ston pa dge 'dun dang bcas pa rnams kyis lhung
NK024(ya)001:10680: bzed mi che mi chung ran mdzes ma chag ma
NK024(ya)001:10681: gas mi skya lhung bzed bzang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:10683: lhung bzed 'byor zhing bsgrub bya nyung na re re nas bya /
NK024(ya)001:10684: bsgrub bya mang zhing lhung bzed nyung na thun mong
NK024(ya)001:10685: du dge slong 'di rnams kyi lhung bzed 'di zhes
NK024(ya)001:10686: sogs sbyar te lan gcig gis 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:10687: de nas bsgrub bya'i lag tu lhung bzed gtad de /
NK024(ya)001:10688: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa mngon par
NK024(ya)001:10689: rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa de'i zhal zas kyi bya
NK024(ya)001:10690: ba byed pa'i lhung bzed 'di dge slong khyod la
NK024(ya)001:10691: zas kyi snod du gtad pas khyed kyis zas kyi
NK024(ya)001:10694: rtsa bar chas su bcug ste r+ts+wa dang gding ba la bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:10695: ces gsungs pas pha gu dmigs bsal ma byung bas mi dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:10696: gding pa'i 'og tu 'byor na ku sha dang /
NK024(ya)001:10697: ma 'byor na r+ts+wa phal pa rgya gram du bcings pa'i rtse gnyis phyir bstan nas bcug /
NK024(ya)001:10698: bsgrub bya rnams chos gos rnam gsum legs par gyon te /
NK024(ya)001:10699: dkyil 'khor dang mkhan por phyag gsum gsum btsal te tsog pur thal sbyar gyis 'dug tu bcug la /
NK024(ya)001:10700: mkhan pos des yo byad mngon gyur song /
NK024(ya)001:10701: bzhi pa yongs dag mngon gyur la gsang ston bskos te /
NK024(ya)001:10702: des las bya ba sogs kyi thog mar ltung thun
NK024(ya)001:10703: byin rlabs dang gnas la blo mthun sogs bya dgos
NK024(ya)001:10704: par / kahthoga lugs su so thar tshul bzhin bris
NK024(ya)001:10705: 'dug kyang so thar dngos gnas sgra ji bzhin pa
NK024(ya)001:10706: skabs su babs mi babs sna tshogs snang bas /
NK024(ya)001:10707: las thams cad kyi mngon du 'gro ba ltung thun byin rlabs dang gnas la blo mthun gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:10708: gsang ston bsko ba sogs bgyid ma dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10709: yongs dag mngon gyur phyir bar chad dri ba zur
NK024(ya)001:10710: lugs rtsa bar mdo tsam gsungs pa de bzhin gyis
NK024(ya)001:10712: kho bos gsang ston gyi tshul du dri ba bgyid /
NK024(ya)001:10714: dge slong ltar bar chad dri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:10715: 'phags pa gcig dge slong bcu dang mnyam par gsungs
NK024(ya)001:10716: pas 'phags pa sde snod 'dzin pa gcig la'ang brten
NK024(ya)001:10718: dge slong phal pa yul dbus dang mtha' 'khob tu lnga las gnang ba thob dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:10719: 'dir mkhan slob dge 'dun gyi gtso bo sangs rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:10721: chos cho ga'i tshig rnams bka' yin pas gus par mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10722: khyod ma 'dzem par byos la yin pa la yin smros /
NK024(ya)001:10723: ma yin pa la ma yin smros shig /
NK024(ya)001:10725: skyes pa'i dbang po dang ldan nam /
NK024(ya)001:10727: khyod kyi chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed tshang ngam /
NK024(ya)001:10728: khyod kyi pha ma gson nam /
NK024(ya)001:10730: khyod kyi pha mas gnang ngam /
NK024(ya)001:10733: rnyed btson can ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10734: rtsod pa can ma btsongs pa ma rgyal pos bkrabs
NK024(ya)001:10735: pa ma rgyal po la gnod pa'i las byed pa
NK024(ya)001:10736: rgyal po la gnod pa'i las byas sam /
NK024(ya)001:10737: byed du bcug pa ma chos rkun par grags pa
NK024(ya)001:10738: ma za ma ma ma ning ma dge slong ma
NK024(ya)001:10739: sun phyungs pa rku thabs su gnas pa ma tha
NK024(ya)001:10740: dad du gnas pa ma gnas par mi bya ba
NK024(ya)001:10741: ma mu stegs can ma mu stegs can zhugs pa
NK024(ya)001:10742: ma pha bsad pa ma ma bsad pa ma dgra
NK024(ya)001:10743: bcom pa bsad pa ma dge 'dun gyi dbyen byas
NK024(ya)001:10744: pa ma de bzhin gshegs pa la ngan sems kyi
NK024(ya)001:10745: khrag phyungs pa ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10746: sprul pa ma dud 'gro ma khyod la la la'i
NK024(ya)001:10747: bu lon mang yang rung nyung yang rung cung zad
NK024(ya)001:10750: khyod bsnyen par rdzogs nas 'jal nus sam /
NK024(ya)001:10751: khyod sngar rab tu byung ba ma yin nam /
NK024(ya)001:10753: khyod la pham par 'gyur ba bzhi las ltung ba
NK024(ya)001:10754: gang yang rung ba zhig byung ba ma yin nam
NK024(ya)001:10756: khyod 'bab pa na bslab pa legs par phul lam /
NK024(ya)001:10758: lhag ma phul nyes pa bshags la dge tshul byas la slar dri /
NK024(ya)001:10760: ji ltar khyod da lta rab tu byung ba yin nam dri /
NK024(ya)001:10762: tshangs par spyod pa legs par spyad dam /
NK024(ya)001:10765: lnga pa gsol ba mngon gyur dang drug pa dge
NK024(ya)001:10766: 'dun gyi nang du bar chad dri ba yongs dag
NK024(ya)001:10768: des sbyor ba'i chos rnams song nas dngos gzhir so
NK024(ya)001:10769: thar lugs kyi bshad pa rnams btang snyoms su bzhag
NK024(ya)001:10770: ste / gsol ba dang gzhi'i las kyis bsnyen par rdzogs dgos pas des na /
NK024(ya)001:10771: khyed rang rnams dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i dkon mchog
NK024(ya)001:10772: gsum dge 'dun dang bcas pa la sems dang ba'i
NK024(ya)001:10773: sgo nas sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs
NK024(ya)001:10775: de'i don du ji srid 'tsho'i bar du bsnyen par
NK024(ya)001:10776: rdzogs pa'i sdom pa blangs la ma nyams par srung
NK024(ya)001:10777: snyam pa rtse gcig tu mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10780: mkhan po stan la 'dug bzhin pas dkyil 'khor phyogs
NK024(ya)001:10781: su 'dud pa dang bcas te spyod lam zhi bas
NK024(ya)001:10785: chos smra ba'i 'phags pa'i dge slong mkhan slob la
NK024(ya)001:10786: sogs pa dge 'dun grangs dang mtshan nyid tshang ba
NK024(ya)001:10787: thams cad tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bya
NK024(ya)001:10788: ba rnams la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10789: tshe dang ldan pa ming 'di zhes bgyi ba rnams dge slong du bzung du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:10793: des dngos gzhi'i cho ga grub /
NK024(ya)001:10794: mjug chog gnyis kyi dang po thob dus go ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:10795: thur ma sor bzhi pas grib tshod bcal te nges par byas nas mkhan pos /
NK024(ya)001:10796: de yang rtsa bar rgan pas dus go bar bya /
NK024(ya)001:10798: de ma thag tu grib tshod rig par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10799: zhes gsungs pa'i don bzhin so thar skabs bsnyen bkur gyi gnas dang /
NK024(ya)001:10802: go zhing rig par bya ba'i dus /
NK024(ya)001:10803: rig par byas pa'i phan yon dang lngar gsungs pa'i rgyas bshad ma spros shing /
NK024(ya)001:10805: dang po bsnyen bkur gyi gnas zhes bya ba bslab
NK024(ya)001:10806: pa rgan pa gong du bkur 'os rnams yin la
NK024(ya)001:10807: / gnyis pa bsnyen bkur gyi gnas ma yin pa
NK024(ya)001:10808: ni bslab pa gzhon pa rnams dang khyim pa sogs
NK024(ya)001:10809: / yin / gsum pa bsnyen bkur rang gi ngo
NK024(ya)001:10810: bo ni phyag dang ldang ba bsnyen bkur 'bul ba
NK024(ya)001:10812: bzhi pa go zhing rig par bya ba'i dus ni
NK024(ya)001:10813: lo tshigs shes par bya ba'i phyir lo brjod dgos
NK024(ya)001:10819: dbyar ring po ste lnga las che ge yin /
NK024(ya)001:10820: de yang phyogs 'dir sbyangs pa rnams la bshad mi
NK024(ya)001:10821: dgos kyang lugs 'di thun mong gi spyod yul du
NK024(ya)001:10822: song bas dus 'chol gyi dogs nas /
NK024(ya)001:10823: zla ba bcu pa'i tshes bcu drug nas lo 'go
NK024(ya)001:10824: bzung ba'i bcu gcig pa'i bco lnga bar zla gcig
NK024(ya)001:10825: / de zhin du rigs 'gres pa'i dgun zla bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:10828: dbyar thung du nyin zhag gcig /
NK024(ya)001:10829: dbyar ring po la nyin zhag gcig gis ma tshang ba'i zla ba gsum rnams yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:10831: de la yang yar ngo mar ngo gnyis yod pa las che ge /
NK024(ya)001:10832: de la tshes bcu bzhi'am bco lnga yod pa las che ge /
NK024(ya)001:10833: de la nyin mo'i cha bcu gcig dang mtshan mo'i
NK024(ya)001:10834: cha brgyad de nyer gnyis yod pa las che ge
NK024(ya)001:10835: / mtshan mo yin na skar khongs 'di tsam /
NK024(ya)001:10836: nyin mo yin na dus tshod skyes bu 'di dang rkang pa 'di yin ces brjod /
NK024(ya)001:10837: de yang thur ma kho rang la skyes bu zer /
NK024(ya)001:10838: skyes bu de la rkang pa bzhi yod pas thur ma'i gri mas gar sleb par skyes bu zer /
NK024(ya)001:10839: de la tsam yod brtsi ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:10840: de ltar grib tshod 'di lta bu'i dus su gnas
NK024(ya)001:10841: 'di zhes bya bar dkon mchog gsum gyi drung du
NK024(ya)001:10842: tshigs gsum rim can du nod pa yin pas bsnyen
NK024(ya)001:10843: bkur gyi gnas dang gnas ma yin pa rnams la
NK024(ya)001:10844: bsnyen bkur spang blang tshul bzhin gyis /
NK024(ya)001:10846: spang blang tshul bzhin byas pas sangs rgyas thob pa'i rgyur 'gyur pas phyag len la thebs par mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:10848: rtsa ba'i sa bcad sum cu so gcig pa bslab bya dbog pa yin la /
NK024(ya)001:10849: gzhan du gdams ngag bcu gcig brjod pa yin kyang /
NK024(ya)001:10850: 'dir rang gzhung gis 'thus pas gsan pas khyab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:10852: des ni dkon mchog gsum gyi byin rlabs kyis sdom
NK024(ya)001:10853: pa rgyud la skye bas thams cad kyis dge slong
NK024(ya)001:10854: du gyur pa'i mos pa byas pas bskyed rim brtan
NK024(ya)001:10855: pa lhar mthong ba bzhin te /
NK024(ya)001:10856: dge slong gi bslab bya zhib tu bstan mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:10857: mdor bsdus te bshad na dge slong gi chos bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:10861: mtshang 'bru yang slar mi 'bru bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10863: nyer gnyis pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:10865: bden bzhi dang sbyar shes dgos pas sdig pa 'khor ba'i chos rgyu kun 'byung shes par bya /
NK024(ya)001:10866: de'i 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi skyon spang bar bya /
NK024(ya)001:10867: dge ba thar pa thob pa'i rgyu lam sgom par bya /
NK024(ya)001:10868: 'bras bu 'gog pa'i yon tan mngon du bya /
NK024(ya)001:10871: des tshul khrims rnam par dag pa thob pa yin
NK024(ya)001:10872: pas dge slong du gyur snyam dga' ba bsgom pa
NK024(ya)001:10873: dang mkhan po la phyag gsum btsal te bka' drin
NK024(ya)001:10875: gos byin pa'i skabs ltar me tog gtor zhing bden brjod smon lam bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:10876: de lta bu'i sdom pa 'bogs tshul ni phyogs 'dir
NK024(ya)001:10877: bla ma phal cher rig sngags 'chang ba sha stag
NK024(ya)001:10878: tu byon pas 'dul ba la cung zhig thugs 'dris
NK024(ya)001:10879: chung bas zur lugs 'dir phyag bzhes rnams cung zad
NK024(ya)001:10880: 'khrugs 'dug pa las cho ga bzhin bsdebs yod cing
NK024(ya)001:10881: / kahthoga lugs su ha cang thal zhing drags nas
NK024(ya)001:10882: las chog sor gnas bris 'dugs par rten nang so
NK024(ya)001:10883: 'jam dbyangs pa sogs kyi klan ka yod pa'i rgyu
NK024(ya)001:10885: phyag len 'di zhib rtsing ran par yod pas so
NK024(ya)001:10886: thar kho na bzhin byas pa'i nyes pa med cing
NK024(ya)001:10887: / cho ga gal che ba rnams chad skyon med par yod /
NK024(ya)001:10888: 'on kyang lugs 'di'i dge slong gi go nges par
NK024(ya)001:10889: chod kyang 'dul ba sor gnas kyi dge slong gi
NK024(ya)001:10891: 'dod na tshigs gsum rnam dag brgyud pa gzhan las
NK024(ya)001:10892: tshul bzhin blang dgos pa snying la bcang bar bya'o
NK024(ya)001:10894: nyer gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni rdzas dbang thogs te zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:10895: mchan bur badz+ra rat+na bum dbang 'dir bya gsung /
NK024(ya)001:10896: mu ne dang a b+hi shiny+tsa mam bum pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:10897: bskur bas chu btung bden bzhi'i go 'phang thob bo
NK024(ya)001:10898: // zhes gsungs pas skabs 'dir 'og gi bum dbang 'dir blangs te /
NK024(ya)001:10900: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK024(ya)001:10901: rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:10902: nyon mongs pa bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i
NK024(ya)001:10903: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:10904: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:10905: zhes brjod cing bum dbang bskur zhing bum chu sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:10906: de nas rdzas dbang gi thog mar snam sbyar thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:10907: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa yang
NK024(ya)001:10908: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa mngon
NK024(ya)001:10909: par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po sh+aakya
NK024(ya)001:10910: seng ge sh+aakya'i gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:10911: na bza' ngur smrig gi chos gos 'di mkhan po
NK024(ya)001:10913: khyod kyis 'phangs shing gces pa'i tshad ni mig 'bru ltar gyis la /
NK024(ya)001:10914: mi 'bral ba'i tshad ni sha dang rus pa ltar gyis la gyon zhig /
NK024(ya)001:10915: khyod kyi gos kyi bya ba kyis la bag yod par spyod cig /
NK024(ya)001:10917: dkon mtshog gsum gyi bka' bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:10918: bcom ldan 'das kyi na bza' ngur smrig gi rgyal
NK024(ya)001:10919: mtshan 'dis skal ldan rigs kyi bu rnams la dbang
NK024(ya)001:10920: bskur bas tshe rabs kun tu ngo tsha khrel yod
NK024(ya)001:10921: kyi gos gyon te tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i
NK024(ya)001:10922: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:10923: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:10926: rigs kyi bu la bcom ldan 'das kyi 'khar gsil
NK024(ya)001:10927: lhung bzed kyi dbang bskur bas mtshon dang mu ge'i
NK024(ya)001:10928: bskal pa las thar pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK024(ya)001:10929: gyur cig / mu ne lha dbang ni dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:10930: nas sku gzugs rnams rim gyis blangs te spyi bor
NK024(ya)001:10931: gyur cig / bzhag cing / gtso bo'i sku thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:10932: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK024(ya)001:10933: dus gsum sangs rgyas ji snyed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:10934: bcom ldan gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas //'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:10935: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK024(ya)001:10936: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:10937: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bdag med de //
NK024(ya)001:10938: sdug kun spangs nas 'gog lam lhag bcas dang //
NK024(ya)001:10939: lhag med dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK024(ya)001:10940: sarba sa ni sa ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:10942: rigs kyi bu la 'gro ba'i gtso bo skye rgu'i
NK024(ya)001:10943: bla ma thub pa chen po'i dbang bskur bas tshe
NK024(ya)001:10944: rabs kun tu sangs rgyas mthong ba dang mi 'bral
NK024(ya)001:10945: ba dang / dam pa'i chos thos pa dang mi 'bral ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:10946: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun dang rtag tu mi 'bral ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:10948: nyan thos bcu drug rim bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:10950: rigs kyi bu la kun dga' bo'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:10951: sangs rgyas kyi zhabs 'bring rtag tu byed pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:10952: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:10954: rigs kyi bu la sh+aa ri'i bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:10955: shes rab can gyi mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:10956: pa mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:10957: rigs kyi bu la moong+gala gyi bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:10958: rdzu 'phrul mchog gi dbang mu ne na mo sogs
NK024(ya)001:10959: / rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa rab 'byor gyi
NK024(ya)001:10960: dbang bskur bas dri zhing lan ldon pa mchog gi
NK024(ya)001:10962: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa ma 'gags pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:10963: bskur bas lha'i mig mchog gi mu ne na mo
NK024(ya)001:10964: sogs / rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa 'char ka'i
NK024(ya)001:10965: dbang bskur bas khyim bdag dad pa bskyed pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:10967: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa koon+di n+ya'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:10968: bas thos grol snga ba mchog gi mu ne na
NK024(ya)001:10969: mo sogs / rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa rta
NK024(ya)001:10970: thul gyi dbang bskur bas spyod lam mdzes pa mchog
NK024(ya)001:10971: gi mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:10972: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa nye ba 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:10973: dbang bskur pas 'dul ba 'dzin pa mchog gi mu
NK024(ya)001:10975: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa ba lang bdag gi
NK024(ya)001:10976: dbang bskur bas 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchog
NK024(ya)001:10977: gi mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:10978: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa 'od srungs chen po'i
NK024(ya)001:10979: dbang bskur bas sbyangs pa'i yon tan che ba mchog
NK024(ya)001:10980: gi mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:10981: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa sgra gcan 'dzin gyi
NK024(ya)001:10982: dbang bskur bas bslab pa la gus pa mchog gi
NK024(ya)001:10984: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa gcung dga' bo'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:10985: bskur bas mtshan dang dpe byad mchog gi mu ne
NK024(ya)001:10986: na mo sogs / rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK024(ya)001:10987: ming can gyi dbang bskur bas rgyal ba'i bka' la
NK024(ya)001:10988: gus pa mchog gi mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:10989: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa nor sbyin 'dzin gyi
NK024(ya)001:10990: dbang bskur bas dbul ba sel ba'i mchog gi mu
NK024(ya)001:10992: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa gang po'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:10993: bas yon sbyong ba mchog gi mu ne na mo
NK024(ya)001:10994: sogs / rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa gnas brtan
NK024(ya)001:10995: chen po b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms len gyi
NK024(ya)001:10996: rgyal ba'i bstan pa gnas kyi bar du skyong bar
NK024(ya)001:10997: mdzad pa'i dbang bskur bas dam pa chos kyi chab
NK024(ya)001:10998: srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:10999: sogs / / ces pa gnas brtan re re bzhin du sbyar ba 'gre /
NK024(ya)001:11006: b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha gser can dang /
NK024(ya)001:11015: 'phags pa gnas brtan chen po rnams kyis rgyal ba'i
NK024(ya)001:11016: bstan pa gnas kyi bar du skyong bar mdzad pa'i
NK024(ya)001:11017: dbang bskur bas dam pa chos kyi chab srid 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:11018: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:11020: bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i bag
NK024(ya)001:11021: chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i dbang mu ne na
NK024(ya)001:11022: mo sogs / rigs kyi bu la ming gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:11023: bskur bas shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med
NK024(ya)001:11024: pa'i dbang mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:11025: shing rta la sogs pa 'khor los sgyur rgyal bdag
NK024(ya)001:11026: po'i dbang bskur bas gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur zhing
NK024(ya)001:11028: sdug bsngal sun phyungs pa'i dbang mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:11029: chibs kyi dbang bskur bas rtag tu rab tu byung
NK024(ya)001:11030: zhing nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba las grol ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:11032: shan ral gri'i dbang bskur bas 'khrul pa'i dra ba gcod pa'i dbang mu ne na mo sogs /
NK024(ya)001:11033: gseg par gyi dbang bskur bas bdag dang 'gro ba'i
NK024(ya)001:11034: don mthar phyin par rdzogs pa'i dbang mu ne na
NK024(ya)001:11035: mo sogs / na bza' ngur smrig gi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:11036: bas 'khor ba'i gdung ba las skyob pa'i dbang mu
NK024(ya)001:11038: bkra shis pa'i rdzas sbrang rtsi'i dbang bskur bas 'bras
NK024(ya)001:11039: bu phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang mu ne na mo
NK024(ya)001:11040: sogs / 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:11041: mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba'i dbang mu ne na
NK024(ya)001:11042: sogs / mo sogs / r+ts+wa gding ba'i rdzas kyi
NK024(ya)001:11043: dbang bskur bas bkra shis thob cing bar chad kyis
NK024(ya)001:11044: mi tshugs pa'i dbang mu ne rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:11045: de nas snying po'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:11046: bdag lhar sgom mdun gyi dkyil 'khor la sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:11047: su dmigs te 'od zer spro bsdu bya zhing nad
NK024(ya)001:11048: gdon sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:11050: khyed rang rnams dbang bskur ba'i rkyen gyis ston pa
NK024(ya)001:11051: bcom ldan 'das kyi skur lam gyis gyur pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:11052: pa mdzod / de'i ngang nas bdag las 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:11053: 'phros mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi sku
NK024(ya)001:11054: gsung thugs la mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK024(ya)001:11055: 'od zer tshur 'dus bdag la thim pas sgo gsum
NK024(ya)001:11056: gyi nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad zhi ba'i mos
NK024(ya)001:11058: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:11061: chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong tshang ba'i snying po'i
NK024(ya)001:11062: dbang bskur bas chos thams cad kyi mdzod 'dzin pa'i
NK024(ya)001:11063: dbang dam pa tho par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:11064: mu ne zhes brjod de bum pa'i chus kyang khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:11066: zhes gsungs pas slar yang gong bzhin bum dbang bskur zhing 'thung khrus byed du bcug /
NK024(ya)001:11067: rtsa bar me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:11068: zhes gsungs pas 'og nas 'byung ba'i bkra shis 'dir yang blangs te sbyar /
NK024(ya)001:11069: de nas ngang sgom bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:11070: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer bzhi pa yin cing /
NK024(ya)001:11071: de la yang nang gses kyi phye na dang po
NK024(ya)001:11072: ngang sgom la gsum gyi dang po sngon 'gro shes
NK024(ya)001:11073: pa bcu dang / dngos gzhi gdams ngag ye shes ngang sgom /
NK024(ya)001:11074: de lam du 'khyer thabs gsum gyi bsdus /
NK024(ya)001:11075: lam 'khyer la bzhi ste theg pa lam 'khyer /
NK024(ya)001:11079: de'i dang po theg pa lam 'khyer la phye na /
NK024(ya)001:11086: de yang nyams su len tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:11087: bshad pas lta sgom gtan la dbab ste /
NK024(ya)001:11089: dngos gzhi ye shes ngang sgom /
NK024(ya)001:11090: lha dang snying po lam 'khyer tshul khrims rnams nyams su len dgos pas /
NK024(ya)001:11091: thog mar rtsa ba ltar bshad na gong gi sa
NK024(ya)001:11092: bcad rnams kyis dmigs phyed par byas te ma yengs
NK024(ya)001:11093: par gsan mdzod / de yang rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:11094: nye bzhi pa ngang sgom la gsum gyi dang po sngon 'gro shes pa bcu ni /
NK024(ya)001:11095: sdug bsngal mi dge bar shes /
NK024(ya)001:11098: 'phags lam yan lag brgyad myang 'das kyi rgyur shes /
NK024(ya)001:11099: bzod pa shes pa ni chags sdang rmongs gsum zad nas sku gsung thugs su shes /
NK024(ya)001:11100: mi dge ba shes pa ni ga bur ltar phan gnod nges pa med par shes /
NK024(ya)001:11101: chos shes pa ni sgyu ma lta bur shes /
NK024(ya)001:11102: rjes su shes pa ni phung khams skye mched rten 'brel sgyu mar shes /
NK024(ya)001:11103: kun rdzob shes pa ni 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi chos thams cad kun rdzob ste thabs su shes /
NK024(ya)001:11104: gzhan sems shes pa ni dad 'dun gdams ngag dang
NK024(ya)001:11105: smon lam gyi mthus sems sogs bcu shes pa'o //'phags
NK024(ya)001:11115: yang dag pa'i lta ba la gsum /
NK024(ya)001:11116: mi rtog pa'i ye shes gzhi mi 'gyur ba'i dngos grub dang /
NK024(ya)001:11117: rjes la skyes pa'i ye shes rgyud la skyes pa'i
NK024(ya)001:11118: lam phyin ci ma log pa'i ye shes yongs grub
NK024(ya)001:11119: dang / sprul pa'i ye shes 'bras bu ma dag
NK024(ya)001:11120: pa'i ye shes dang 'bras bu dag pa 'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:11121: las 'das pa'i ye shes gsum mo //
NK024(ya)001:11122: yang dag pa'i rtog pa ni ye shes gsum po la yang dang yang du rtog pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11123: yang dag pa'i ngag ni sems can thams cad la chos dge ba bcu rtag tu smra ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:11124: yang dag pa 'i lam mtha' ni thams cad du
NK024(ya)001:11125: las dge ba spyod pa mi dge ba spong ba'o
NK024(ya)001:11126: //'tsho ba ni dam pa'i chos 'tshol ba dang rtsol
NK024(ya)001:11127: ba cher byed / dran pas bso //
NK024(ya)001:11128: ting nge 'dzin la nang du yang dag par 'jog par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:11129: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i ye shes ngang sgom ni /
NK024(ya)001:11130: de nas dbang brtan pa'i phyir gsal gdab pa ni
NK024(ya)001:11131: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le yungs kar
NK024(ya)001:11132: tsam zhig sgom / de la shes pa gtad pas thig le je cher 'phel /
NK024(ya)001:11133: snang srid thams cad keng rus kyi dkyil 'khor du bsam /
NK024(ya)001:11134: de yang yul rang rgyud pa la brten na chags
NK024(ya)001:11135: sdang rmongs gsum skye bas nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgyu
NK024(ya)001:11136: yin / de'i mthus sdug bsngal myong ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:11137: de'i gnyen por yul mi sdug pa de sgoms pas chags sdang mi dge kun 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:11138: nyon mongs pa rtsa ba nas bcad pas 'bras bu sdug bsngal rang bzhin gyis 'gag /
NK024(ya)001:11139: de ka 'gog pa dang lam bden yin no //
NK024(ya)001:11141: theg pa lam 'khyer ni nyan thos kyi theg pa /
NK024(ya)001:11142: de la dang po 'jug sgo ni sdug bsngal /
NK024(ya)001:11146: de dag phye na bden chung bcu drug de ni spong byed ye shes bcu drug go //
NK024(ya)001:11147: kun 'byung gi bden pa 'khor ba'i rgyu /
NK024(ya)001:11148: sdug bsngal gyi bden pa 'khor ba'i 'bras bur shes nas spong /
NK024(ya)001:11150: lam gyi bden pa 'das pa'i 'bras bur shes nas sgrub /
NK024(ya)001:11151: de la phye na bden chung bcu drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:11159: bdag med do //'gog pa la 'gog pa /
NK024(ya)001:11167: de dag la spong byed ye shes bcu drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:11168: dang po la kun 'byung shes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11169: kun 'byung shes pa'i chos shes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11171: bzod pa la shes pa'i chos shes pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11173: gnyis pa ni de'i don la mi skrag pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11175: bzhi pa ni de'i don la mi skrag pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11177: de yang rigs brgyad dbye ba las /
NK024(ya)001:11178: bden bzhi'i don rtogs rab tu spong byed cing /
NK024(ya)001:11179: ye shes bcu drug chas sbyangs rab zhi ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:11180: rgyun zhugs la sogs rim pas sbyangs nas ni /
NK024(ya)001:11181: nyon mongs dgra rnams zhi ba'i sa ru 'gro //
NK024(ya)001:11183: lta ba gang zag gi bdag med rtogs /
NK024(ya)001:11184: chos kyi bdag dang bcas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11185: gang zag gi bdag la gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:11186: rang bzhin lhan skyes gang zag gi bdag dang /
NK024(ya)001:11187: ched du byas pa'i gang zag gi bdag go //
NK024(ya)001:11189: phung po lnga yi rgyu la bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:11190: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i bdag ces bya //
NK024(ya)001:11192: de la brten nas mu stegs lta rnams 'jug /
NK024(ya)001:11193: so so skye bo phung po lnga'i rgyun la blos rnam par ma phye /
NK024(ya)001:11195: de la brten nas mu stegs kyi phyin ci log
NK024(ya)001:11196: tu brtags pa'i bdag rang bzhin med par rtogs pa'o
NK024(ya)001:11197: // gnyis pa chos kyi bdag la gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:11200: gzung yul la bdag ma grub ste rang bzhin med
NK024(ya)001:11201: pa yin kyang nyan thos blo chung bas mu stegs
NK024(ya)001:11202: chad par gol gyi dogs nas rdul phra rab tu
NK024(ya)001:11203: yod par 'dod / de la mdo sde pa dang
NK024(ya)001:11204: bye brag pa gnyis rdul gyi gnas lugs rtsom tshul
NK024(ya)001:11205: yod par 'dod / ma mthun te / mdo sde
NK024(ya)001:11206: pa po ti'i shog bu'am 'bru'i phung po ltar reg
NK024(ya)001:11208: bye brag pa g.yag rnga'am ne sing ltar skor ba bar bcas su 'dod /
NK024(ya)001:11210: 'di ltar snang ba 'di ni sgyu ma tsam //
NK024(ya)001:11211: yang dag nyid la yod pa ma yin te //
NK024(ya)001:11212: shin tu chad ltar gyur na mi rung bas //
NK024(ya)001:11213: nyan thos byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan //
NK024(ya)001:11215: nang 'dzin pa'i sems la bdag ma grub ste /
NK024(ya)001:11216: kun gzhi mtha' bral du gnas pa yin kyang /
NK024(ya)001:11217: nyan thos pa blo chung bas kun gzhi gsangs te
NK024(ya)001:11218: skad cig ma skye 'gag dang bcas par 'dod ces
NK024(ya)001:11221: len dang rnam par shes pa zab cing phra //
NK024(ya)001:11222: sa bon thams cad chu bo'i rgyun bzhin 'bab //
NK024(ya)001:11223: bdag tu rtog par gyur na mi rung zhes //
NK024(ya)001:11224: nyan thos byis pa rnams la ngas ma bstan //
NK024(ya)001:11226: gzung yul phyi rol rdul du grub /
NK024(ya)001:11227: 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma bden pa bzhi la nges pa'i rten can zhes /
NK024(ya)001:11228: mdo sde pa dang bye brag gnyis //
NK024(ya)001:11229: phyi rol rdul la rtsod byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:11231: bsrung ba'i tshul khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:11233: blo rab kun 'byung spyi 'khor ba'i rgyur shes nas
NK024(ya)001:11234: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa sogs gnyen
NK024(ya)001:11235: po sgo drug gi sgo nas tshogs drug bkag nas
NK024(ya)001:11238: sems bskyed rgya chung bas spyod pa gzhan don spyad
NK024(ya)001:11239: kyang rang don la dmigs pas gzhan phan snying rje
NK024(ya)001:11241: spyod pa rgyal len rang thar 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:11242: zhes so //'bras bu ni skyes bu zung bzhi ya brgyad do //
NK024(ya)001:11243: lha lam 'khyer ni dus gsum sangs rgyas sam bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa sgom pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:11244: snying po ni mu ni bzlas pa'o //'dug tshul ni
NK024(ya)001:11245: blo phebs pa dang sdug gtam gtong ba lta bu'o
NK024(ya)001:11246: // bslab bya lam 'khyer mi dge ba bcu spong /
NK024(ya)001:11247: dgra dang nyon mongs pa tsher ma ltar spong /
NK024(ya)001:11248: dge bcu sman dang kha zas ltar len /
NK024(ya)001:11249: de'ang thun mong du 'du shes bcu ste /
NK024(ya)001:11250: srog gcod pa la btsan dug lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK024(ya)001:11251: gos la rma dkris lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK024(ya)001:11252: nyon mongs pa la dug sprul lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK024(ya)001:11253: kha zas la rgan rgon bu sha za ba lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK024(ya)001:11254: rnyed bkur la rgya dang rnyi lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK024(ya)001:11255: bla ma dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che
NK024(ya)001:11256: lta bu'i chos la lam bzang po lta bu'i sangs
NK024(ya)001:11257: rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i tshul khrims
NK024(ya)001:11258: la rgyan lta bu'i chos nyid mngon du gyur pa
NK024(ya)001:11259: la mun khung du sgron me btegs pa lta bu'i
NK024(ya)001:11261: de dag dbang rdo rje zam pa las gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:11263: gnas wa ra n+aa si'i bsil khang /
NK024(ya)001:11265: 'khor mchog brgyad dam bcu drug sogs /
NK024(ya)001:11266: chos bden bzhi nyan thos kyi theg pa /
NK024(ya)001:11267: dgos pa mu stegs rtag chad rang rgyud par 'dod pa las grol ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:11268: gang du gang la gang gis bstan //
NK024(ya)001:11269: ci phyir dgos pa bcas pa ste //'di ni nyan thos 'gag drug yin //
NK024(ya)001:11271: de rnams kyi don nyams su ji ltar blang snyam na rgyas bshad rnams gong gis shes la /
NK024(ya)001:11273: sngon 'gro shes pa bcu'i dang po bden bzhi'i tshul gyis te /
NK024(ya)001:11274: sdug bsngal thams cad mi dge ba'i rgyu las byung bar shes te spang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11275: kun 'byung sems kyi nyon mongs 'khor bar shes te spang ba'i thabs bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11276: 'gog bden ni sdug bsngal 'gog par shes te mngon du bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11277: lta ba rtog pa ngag las kyi mtha' 'tsho ba
NK024(ya)001:11278: rtsol ba dran pa ting nge 'dzin te 'phags lam
NK024(ya)001:11279: yan lag brgyad myang 'das kyi rgyu lam du shes
NK024(ya)001:11286: chags sdang rmongs gsum zad par shes pas sku gsung thugs su shes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11287: mi dge ba rgyu dang 'bras bur shes pas bya
NK024(ya)001:11288: bzhag thams cad ga bur ltar phan gnod nges pa
NK024(ya)001:11290: chos thams cad sgyu ma lta bur shes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11291: sgyu ma de yang phung khams skye mched phyi nang
NK024(ya)001:11292: gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung bar shes pa dang
NK024(ya)001:11293: / 'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kun rdzob ste thabs su shes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11294: dad 'dun gdams ngag smon lam gyi mthus gzhan sems shes pa sogs shes pa bcu la bslab /
NK024(ya)001:11295: 'di'i khongs su nyan thos kyi lam thams cad 'du
NK024(ya)001:11296: yang rim bzhin nyams su len phyin sngon 'gro'i ming
NK024(ya)001:11297: btags pa yin / dngos gzhi ye shes ngang sgom zhes dngos gzhir byed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:11298: dbang brtan pa'i phyir gsal gdab pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:11299: de yang gzhung gzhan las ba ran ta'i sgra las rus pa yin par bshad de /
NK024(ya)001:11300: rang gi smin mtshams su rus pa'i thig le yungs kar tsam zhig sgom /
NK024(ya)001:11301: de la shes pa rtse gcig tu gtad pas je
NK024(ya)001:11302: cher 'phel bas rang gi lus dang phyi rol snang
NK024(ya)001:11303: srid thams cad keng rus su gyur par bsam mo
NK024(ya)001:11304: //'di'i dgos pa ni bud med sogs yul mdzes pa
NK024(ya)001:11305: la brten nas chags sdang rmongs gsum skye bas des
NK024(ya)001:11306: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgyu byas ngan 'gro'i sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:11308: rgyu sdug bsngal 'gog cing lam bden sgrub phyir gdams ngag 'di ltar du sgom dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:11309: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK024(ya)001:11310: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le yungs kar tsam zhig sgom /
NK024(ya)001:11311: de la shes pa gtad pas thig le je che
NK024(ya)001:11312: je che la rang gi lus keng rus kyi rang
NK024(ya)001:11313: bzhin du bsam / de dang cha mthun par snang
NK024(ya)001:11314: srid thams cad keng rus kyi dkyil 'khor du bsam
NK024(ya)001:11315: bzhin du bsam / / de yang dgos pa ci
NK024(ya)001:11316: yod na da lta'i lus 'di nyid yul rang rgyud
NK024(ya)001:11317: pa la brten nas nyon mongs pa chags sdang rmongs
NK024(ya)001:11318: bzhin du bsam / / gsum skye ste / nyon mongs pa 'khor ba'i rgyu yin /
NK024(ya)001:11319: des 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi bden pa myong ba
NK024(ya)001:11320: yin te de'i gnyer por rus pa'i 'khor la yul
NK024(ya)001:11321: mi sdug pa sgoms pas nyon mongs pa chags sdang
NK024(ya)001:11322: mi skye / kun 'byung gis nyon mongs pa rtsad
NK024(ya)001:11323: nas bcad pas 'bras bu sdug bsngal rang bzhin gyis
NK024(ya)001:11324: 'gog pa de ka lam gyi bden pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:11326: spyir nyan thos kyi theg pa'i skabs 'dir slob dpon sgeg pa'i rdo rjes /
NK024(ya)001:11327: nyan rang gnyis gzhi spong ba'i gnyen po ste /
NK024(ya)001:11328: nyon mongs dug lnga dang dug gsum dgra dang tsher ma ltar spong bar gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:11329: khyad par 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa sgom pa gtso che bas /
NK024(ya)001:11330: keng rus kyang mi sdug pa'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK024(ya)001:11331: 'dul ba las kyang bcom ldan 'das kyis dge slong
NK024(ya)001:11332: rnams la 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa
NK024(ya)001:11334: ha cang mi sdug bsgom nan ches pas rang gi
NK024(ya)001:11335: lus la mi gtsang ba'i 'du shes skyes te dge
NK024(ya)001:11336: slong mang po srog dang bral pa'i lo rgyus kyang
NK024(ya)001:11337: yod cing / de ltar mi sdug pa'i sgom tshul mang yang don bsdu na spyir bshes spring las /
NK024(ya)001:11338: lus mtha' thal ba mthar skam mthar 'bral zhing //
NK024(ya)001:11339: mtha' mar mi gtsang snying po ma mchis pa //
NK024(ya)001:11340: rnam par 'jig dengs myags par 'gyur ba ste //
NK024(ya)001:11341: so sor gyes chos can du mkhyen par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:11343: khyad par du bud med la chags pa ldog phyir mi sdug pa sgom tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:11345: gzhan gyi chung ma mi lta mthong na yang //
NK024(ya)001:11346: na tshod mthun par ma dang bu mo dang //
NK024(ya)001:11347: sring mo'i 'du shes bskyed bgyi chags gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:11348: mi gtsang nyid du yang dag bsam par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:11350: gdams ngag tu bud med la mi lta zhing gal te mthong na yang /
NK024(ya)001:11351: rang las rgan pa ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:11352: mnyam pa tsam la sring mo /
NK024(ya)001:11353: gzhon pa la bu mor 'du shes bskyed de chags pa las ldog cing /
NK024(ya)001:11354: des kyang ma ldog na mi sdug pa bsgom par bya gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:11355: de ltar mi sdug pa sgom tshul yang /
NK024(ya)001:11357: bud med gzhon nu'i lus ni logs shig tu //
NK024(ya)001:11358: dri nga ba dang sgo dgu dod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:11359: mi gtsang kun snod 'dra ba dgang dka' dang //
NK024(ya)001:11360: pags pas g.yogs par brgyan yang logs shig gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:11361: zhes gsungs pa ltar sgom dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:11362: de ltar 'dod sred la chags pa'i dbang gis 'khor bar 'khyams pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:11364: 'dod pa rnams ni phung ba bskyed pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:11365: rgyal ba'i dbang pos kim pa'i 'bras ltar gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:11366: de dag spang bgyi de yi lcags sgrog gis //'khor ba'i btson rar 'jig rten 'di dag bcings //
NK024(ya)001:11367: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'dod pa spang thabs rgyud la 'byor nges par bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:11368: de yang chags sogs nyon mongs pa rnams goms na gnyen pos ldog dka' ba'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:11369: thog ma nyid nas dran shes legs par bsten cing 'bur 'joms su bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:11371: nyon mongs goms na gnyen pos ldog dka' bas //
NK024(ya)001:11372: dran shes skyes bus gnyen po'i mtshon bzung ste //
NK024(ya)001:11373: chags sogs nyon mongs dang por skye ma thag /'bur 'joms byed pa rgyal sras lag len yin //
NK024(ya)001:11374: zhes gsungs pa gnad du che'o //
NK024(ya)001:11375: lha lam 'khyer ni dus gsum sangs rgyas dang bcom ldan sh+aaka thub sgom /
NK024(ya)001:11376: snying po lam 'khyer mu ne bzla bar gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:11377: lha sgom par 'dod pa'i tshe spyir dus gsum sangs
NK024(ya)001:11378: rgyas dang khyad par bdag cag gi ston pa sh+aakya
NK024(ya)001:11381: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:11383: phan yon khyad par 'dir dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:11384: dus gsum sangs rgyas dang bskal bzang sangs rgyas stong
NK024(ya)001:11385: rtsa sogs ni sangs rgyas kyi yon tan gyi phung
NK024(ya)001:11386: po gzhal bar dka' zhing brjod las 'das pa yin
NK024(ya)001:11388: 'khor gyi nyan thos rnams ni spyir yon tan gyi phung po mtshungs pa med cing /
NK024(ya)001:11389: khyad par mchog bcu drug gi thog mar 'phags pa
NK024(ya)001:11390: kun dga' bo ni ston pa'i zhabs 'bring du rtag
NK024(ya)001:11391: par gnas shing bka' thams cad kyi sdud pa po
NK024(ya)001:11392: mang du thos pa'i mchog tu gyur la /
NK024(ya)001:11393: gsol ba btab na mang du thos pa'i mchog tu
NK024(ya)001:11394: 'gyur ro //'phags pa sh+aa ri'i bu dang moong+gala gyi
NK024(ya)001:11395: bu gnyis mchog zung du grags shing sh+aa ri'i bu
NK024(ya)001:11396: la gsol ba btab na 'jam dbyangs dang mi gnyis
NK024(ya)001:11397: pa'i mkhyen rab mtshungs pa med pa thob pa dang
NK024(ya)001:11398: / de bzhin du moong+gala bu la gsol ba btab
NK024(ya)001:11399: pas kyang gsang bdag lta bu'i mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul
NK024(ya)001:11401: gnas brtan rab 'byor ni 'dri zhing lan ldon pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pas /
NK024(ya)001:11402: de la gsol ba btab pas rgol bas tshugs pa
NK024(ya)001:11403: med pa'i rnam dpyod kyi spobs pa phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:11405: gnas brtan ma 'gags pa ni lha'i mig dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:11406: pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pas de la gsol ba btab
NK024(ya)001:11407: na / chos dang ye shes lha'i mig sha dang
NK024(ya)001:11408: mngon par shes pa'i spyan lnga thob par 'gyur ro
NK024(ya)001:11409: //'phags pa 'char ka bslab pa la gus pa'i mchog
NK024(ya)001:11410: tu basngagasa pa de la gsol ba btab na tshul
NK024(ya)001:11411: khrims rnam par dag pa dang ldan par 'gyur ro
NK024(ya)001:11412: na / // gnas brtan kun shes koon+di n+ya ni
NK024(ya)001:11413: mtha' 'khob 'dul ba'i mchog tu basngagasa pa de la
NK024(ya)001:11414: gsol ba btab pas gdul dka' ba rnams kyang 'dul
NK024(ya)001:11415: ba'i mthu thob bar 'gyur ro //'phags pa rta thul
NK024(ya)001:11416: khyim pa dad par byed pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pa
NK024(ya)001:11417: de la gsol ba btab pas mos ldan rnams dad
NK024(ya)001:11418: pas rjes su 'dzin pa'i mthu thob par 'gyur ro
NK024(ya)001:11419: //'phags pa nye ba 'khor 'dul ba 'dzin pa'i mchog
NK024(ya)001:11420: tu basngagasa pa de la gsol ba btab pas 'dul
NK024(ya)001:11421: ba rnam par dag pa 'dzin nus par 'gyur ro
NK024(ya)001:11422: //'phags pa ba lang bdag 'gog pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:11423: gyi mchog tu basngagasa pa de la gsol ba btab
NK024(ya)001:11424: pas ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo du ma la dbang
NK024(ya)001:11426: gnas brtan 'od srungs chen po sbyangs yon la gnas
NK024(ya)001:11427: pa rnams kyi mchog tu basngagasa pa de la gsol
NK024(ya)001:11428: ba btab pas sbyangs pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis la
NK024(ya)001:11429: slob nus par 'gyur ro //'phags pa sgra gcan 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:11430: la gsol ba btab pa'i phan yon ni 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:11431: 'byung ngo //'phags pa gcung dga' bo mtshan dper ldan
NK024(ya)001:11432: pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pa de la gsol ba btab
NK024(ya)001:11433: pa'i mthus mtshan bzang dpe byad dang ldan par 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:11434: ro //'phags pa ming chen rgyal ba'i bka' la gus
NK024(ya)001:11435: pa'i mchog tu basngagasa pa de la gsol ba btab
NK024(ya)001:11436: pa'i mthus thub pa'i gsung rab dri ma med pa
NK024(ya)001:11437: rnams thos shing 'dzin nus par 'gyur ro //'phags pa
NK024(ya)001:11438: nor sbyin 'dzin dbul ba sems pa'i mchog tu basngagasa
NK024(ya)001:11439: pa de la gsol ba btab pa'i mthus chos ldan
NK024(ya)001:11440: gyi 'tsho ba don yod pa'i phyir rnyed bkur phun
NK024(ya)001:11441: sum tshogs pa thob par 'gyur ro //'phags pa gang
NK024(ya)001:11442: po chos smra ba'i mchog gam yon sbyong ba'i mchog
NK024(ya)001:11443: tu basngagasa pa ltar chos smra ba'i spobs pa dang
NK024(ya)001:11444: yon gnas dam pa thob par 'gyur ro //'di rnams
NK024(ya)001:11445: kyi rtogs brjod rgyas par bshad na ha cang yig
NK024(ya)001:11446: tshogs la 'jigs te bzhag go //'phags pa'i gnas brtan
NK024(ya)001:11447: bcu drug gleng gzhi dang sbyar te cung zad bshad
NK024(ya)001:11448: na / gnas brtan yan lag 'byung 'di rgyal po'i khab tu 'khrugs /
NK024(ya)001:11449: bstan pa la rab tu byung zhing bsnyen par rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:11450: te dgra bcom pa'i 'bras bu mngon du mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:11451: la lha rnams kyis rnga yab dang lha ma yin
NK024(ya)001:11452: dang gnod sbyin gyis spos phor phul bas spos dri
NK024(ya)001:11453: tshor tshad la tshul khrims kyi dri bsrung bzang ba
NK024(ya)001:11454: 'byung zhing kun gyi yid du 'ong ba dang nad
NK024(ya)001:11455: dang sdug bsngal zhi bar 'gyur la /
NK024(ya)001:11456: rnga yab las mchod sprin spros te sangs rgyas sras bcas la mchod par mdzad cing /
NK024(ya)001:11457: rnga yab gang la g.yabs pa'i sems can thams cad
NK024(ya)001:11458: kyi nyon mongs pa sa bon dang bcas pa zhi
NK024(ya)001:11459: ba dang / nad dang sdug bsngal thams cad las
NK024(ya)001:11460: thar bar 'gyur bas gsol ba btab na de 'bras
NK024(ya)001:11462: ma pham pa mnyan yod du 'khrungs pa sogs snga
NK024(ya)001:11463: ma ltar la 'di'i mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mthong
NK024(ya)001:11464: reg dran pas / tshul khrims dag cing 'phel ba
NK024(ya)001:11465: dang dpal dang grags pa dang ting nge 'dzin brgya
NK024(ya)001:11466: stong dpag tu med pa thob par bshad pa bzhin
NK024(ya)001:11467: gsol ba btab na don 'grub bo //
NK024(ya)001:11468: nags na gnas pa mnyan yod du 'khrungs shing 'di'i
NK024(ya)001:11469: phyag gi sdigs mdzub gang la gtad pa de 'byung
NK024(ya)001:11470: bzhi'i gnod pa dang 'dre srin lha klu gnod sbyin
NK024(ya)001:11471: gtum po rnams kyi gdug pa zhi nas bka' la
NK024(ya)001:11472: nyan pa dang / rnga yab g.yabs pa'i rlung gis
NK024(ya)001:11473: reg pa dang yid la dran pas sdig pa 'dag
NK024(ya)001:11474: nyan pa dang / / bdag med gnyis dang bden
NK024(ya)001:11475: gnyis rtogs par 'gyur bas yon tan dran cing gsol
NK024(ya)001:11476: ba btabs pas de bzhin 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:11478: 'di'i phyag mtshan mthong reg dran pa las sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:11479: byang sems kyi spang rtogs thob cing 'khor mang po
NK024(ya)001:11480: 'du ba dang / sa bcu la gnas shing phyir mi ldog pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11481: zhi lhag zung du 'brel bar 'gyur bas gsol ba btab pas de bzhin du lhun gyis grub bo //
NK024(ya)001:11482: rdoo rje mo'i bu mnyan yod pa yin cing sdigs
NK024(ya)001:11483: mdzub gang la gtad pa'i skye bo de mthong reg
NK024(ya)001:11484: dran pas ma dad pa'i rgol ba bzlog ste byang
NK024(ya)001:11485: chub tu nges par byed cing /
NK024(ya)001:11486: rnga yab mthong reg yid la byed pa des ye
NK024(ya)001:11487: shes dang dbang phyug dang mtshan dpe dang lus las
NK024(ya)001:11489: de phog pa'i sems can thams cad byang chub la
NK024(ya)001:11490: 'god par nus pa'i phan yon dang ldan par byin
NK024(ya)001:11491: gyis brlab pas gus pas gsol ba btab par bya'o
NK024(ya)001:11492: // bzang po ser skyar 'khrungs shing chos 'chad kyi
NK024(ya)001:11493: phyag rgya mthong bas theg pa che chung gi chos
NK024(ya)001:11494: thams cad shes shing ci bsam 'grub /
NK024(ya)001:11496: mnyam gzhag mthong bas ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo du ma dang mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul thob /
NK024(ya)001:11498: sangs rgyas kyi zhing mang po nyul bar nus /
NK024(ya)001:11500: rgol ba thams cad tshar bcad de gdul byar 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:11501: pa sogs bshad pas de ltar 'dod pas rtse gcig
NK024(ya)001:11502: tu gsol ba 'debs pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:11504: phyag mtshan rin chen zhags pa mthong reg dran pas mi brjed pa'i dran pa thob /
NK024(ya)001:11505: sangs rgyas byang sems kyis gsungs pa'i chos thams cad thos /
NK024(ya)001:11506: gzugs dang spobs pa dang dbang phyug phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:11507: par thob par gsungs pas gsol ba btab cing gus
NK024(ya)001:11508: par bya'o // b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha gser can mnyan yod du 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11509: 'di'i mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya su'i mdun du bcas ma thag ngan 'gro las thar zhing /
NK024(ya)001:11510: dga' bde ye shes dkar po'i yon tan thams cad
NK024(ya)001:11511: rgyas par 'gyur bar gsungs pas yon tan rjes su
NK024(ya)001:11512: dran te gsol ba btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11513: ba ku la mnyan yod du 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11514: phyag gi ne'u le sus mthong reg dran pas 'dod
NK024(ya)001:11515: yon lnga phun sum tshogs shing phar phyin drug rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:11516: pa dang / chos nyid kyi bden pa mthong ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11517: byams pa dang snying rje skyes par 'gyur bar bshad pas de bzhin du gsol ba btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11518: sgra gcan 'dzin ni ston pa'i sras ser skyar 'khrungs
NK024(ya)001:11519: te phyag mtshan cod pan mgo la bzhag pa'am mthong
NK024(ya)001:11520: reg dran pas dgra bcom zhing sangs rgyas kyi gsung
NK024(ya)001:11522: sangs rgyas sras bcas kyi byin gyis rlob par bshad pas de ltar mos te gsol ba btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11523: lam phran brtan mnyan yod du 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11524: gang gis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mthong reg dran pas sems 'khrugs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11526: dug gsum dang ngan sems zhi zhing dbang po dul
NK024(ya)001:11527: ba dang rkyen ngan pa'i gdon zhi ba sogs 'byung
NK024(ya)001:11528: bar bshad pas / de ltar yid la smon pas rtse gcig tu gsol ba gdab bo /
NK024(ya)001:11529: b+ha ra d+h+wa tsha bsod snyoms len rgyal po'i khab tu 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11530: 'di'i glegs bam mthong reg dran tshad 'on long lkug myos 'khrul pa zhi zhing /
NK024(ya)001:11534: zab pa phra ba'i shes rab thob cing /
NK024(ya)001:11535: lhung bzed kyang bum pa bzang po dang 'dra bar
NK024(ya)001:11536: brlabs te mthong reg dran tshad la dgos 'dod thams
NK024(ya)001:11538: lha'i bde ba thams cad 'byung bas de ltar yid
NK024(ya)001:11539: la smon bzhin gsol ba btab pas 'bras bu 'byung
NK024(ya)001:11541: lam bstan ni lam phran bstan gyi phu bo yin phyir mnyan yod pa /
NK024(ya)001:11542: chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya mthong reg thams cad chos kyi blo gros kyi sa thob /
NK024(ya)001:11543: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra thos pa dang mi 'bral /
NK024(ya)001:11544: yang dag pa'i lta ba dang ldan /
NK024(ya)001:11545: log lta thams cad zil gyis gnon /
NK024(ya)001:11546: sangs rgyas mthong ba dang mi 'bral ba rnams tshe rabs thams cad du thob par 'gyur /
NK024(ya)001:11547: glegs bam mthong reg dran pas shes rab dang /
NK024(ya)001:11552: theg chen gyi chos dang mjal ba sogs bshad pas
NK024(ya)001:11553: de ltar 'byung phyir gus pas gsol ba gdab bo
NK024(ya)001:11554: // klu'i sde byang phyogs pad+ma'i grong khyer du 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11555: 'dir sems can gyi don du bum pa bzang po bsgrubs te /
NK024(ya)001:11556: de mthong reg dran pas dgos rgu 'byung zhing lha'i
NK024(ya)001:11557: bdud rtsi'i chus sdig sgrib thams cad 'khrud pa dang
NK024(ya)001:11558: 'khar gsil gyi sgra thos pas nad dang sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:11559: dang nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu thams cad zhi zhing
NK024(ya)001:11560: dkon mchog gsum la mi 'phrog pa'i dad pa thob
NK024(ya)001:11561: pa sogs 'byung bas yon tan yid la dran cing
NK024(ya)001:11562: gus pas 'dod don gsol ba gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11563: sbed byed pa wa ra n+aa sir 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11564: mthar gnas pa rnams kyi mchog tu bstan cing /
NK024(ya)001:11565: phyag mtshan gyi glegs bam mthong reg dran pas rig pa'i gnas lnga la mkhas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11566: nyon mongs pa thams cad zhi ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11567: chos kyi rgyal por dbang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11568: yang dag pa'i shes rab dang ldan /
NK024(ya)001:11569: rgyal ba'i sras kyi thu bor 'gyur bar bshad pas
NK024(ya)001:11570: de bzhin du yon tan yid la dran cing gsol
NK024(ya)001:11571: ba gdab bo // mi phyed pa rgyal po'i khab tu 'khrungs /
NK024(ya)001:11572: phyag gi mchod rten sus mthong reg dran tshad don thams cad 'grub /
NK024(ya)001:11574: bde legs kyi dpal thams cad thob /
NK024(ya)001:11575: sdig pa thams cad dag par 'gyur ba sogs bshad pa de bzhin mos pas gsol ba btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11576: tsun+da ni phyogs 'dir gnas bcur grangs te rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:11577: mo'i bu dang gcig pa'i bshad khungs 'dug pas dgos
NK024(ya)001:11578: pa khyad par can zhig yod 'dra yang /
NK024(ya)001:11579: spyi ltar na mgar ba'i bu dge tshul tsun+da zhes
NK024(ya)001:11580: ston pa mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba
NK024(ya)001:11582: khong dang lhan cig par rgyal ba rnams mya ngan
NK024(ya)001:11583: las mi 'dab bar gsol ba brtse gcig tu btab
NK024(ya)001:11584: bo // dge bsnyen d+har+m+aa ta la rgya gar gyi gleng gzhir mi 'byung yang /
NK024(ya)001:11585: ri bo rtse lngar gnas brtan rnams bzhugs pa'i gnas
NK024(ya)001:11586: g.yog tu sprul pa yin cing phyag dar sogs mdzad
NK024(ya)001:11587: pa'i tshe srog chags ma rungs pas 'tshe ba na
NK024(ya)001:11588: sprul pa'i stag pus mo g.yas pa las sprul par
NK024(ya)001:11589: 'dod cing / nyin re bzhin sangs rgyas snang ba
NK024(ya)001:11590: mtha' yas sprin gseb nas nam mkhar spyan drangs shing
NK024(ya)001:11591: bzhugs pa sogs spang rtogs kyi yon tan khyad par
NK024(ya)001:11592: can mnga' ba yin pas gus par bya zhing gsol
NK024(ya)001:11593: 'dod cing / ba gdab bo // mdor na 'phags
NK024(ya)001:11594: pa'i gnas brtan chen po 'di dag ni spang rtogs
NK024(ya)001:11595: kyi yon tan ston pa dang mnyam par bzhugs shing
NK024(ya)001:11596: 'dod cing / ba gdab bo // / ston pa
NK024(ya)001:11597: sangs rgyas kyis gnas brtan chen po khyed rnams ji
NK024(ya)001:11598: srid mgon po ma pham pa rdo rje gdan du
NK024(ya)001:11599: sangs rgyas nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba de
NK024(ya)001:11600: srid du mya ngan las mi 'da' bar nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:11601: kyi cha lugs 'dis sems can thams cad kyi don
NK024(ya)001:11602: du sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa skyongs shig ces bka'
NK024(ya)001:11603: 'dod cing / ba gdab bo // / bsgos pa
NK024(ya)001:11604: bzhin / yang dag pa'i mtha' mngon du mi mdzad
NK024(ya)001:11605: par dzam bu'i gling du sku gsung thugs kyis gdul
NK024(ya)001:11606: bya sna tshogs dang rgyal ba'i bstan pa skyong bar
NK024(ya)001:11608: rang cag rnams la lhag par thugs rje che zhing
NK024(ya)001:11609: gsol ba btab na mngon sum du mjal te gsung
NK024(ya)001:11610: gi bdud rtsis tshim par mdzad pa'i lo rgyus kyang
NK024(ya)001:11611: mang bar snang bas byin rlabs myur zhing gnas brtan
NK024(ya)001:11612: re re'i yon tan gyi phung po brjod par ga
NK024(ya)001:11613: la nus kyang bye brag gi gdul bya skyong tshul
NK024(ya)001:11614: gong du mdo tsam bshad pa ltar nges par bya
NK024(ya)001:11615: zhing / yid ches kyi dad pa brtan pos rtag
NK024(ya)001:11616: par thugs rje bskul zhing phyag mchod la 'bad par
NK024(ya)001:11617: byas na 'di phyi'i don thams cad yid bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:11619: bslab bya ni theg pa lam 'khyer gyi sa bcad
NK024(ya)001:11620: bzhi pa tshul khrims lam 'khyer dang spyir bslab bya
NK024(ya)001:11621: lam 'khyer gnyis 'byung ba'i tshul khrims lam 'khyer ni
NK024(ya)001:11622: / rtsa bar bsrung ba'i tshul khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:11623: zhes bshad pas tshul ldan yin na ci nus kyis slob cing /
NK024(ya)001:11624: 'on kyang 'dir thun mong ba'i gdul bya mang bas ji bzhin slob mi nus pa la dgongs nas /
NK024(ya)001:11625: spyir lus kyi las srog gcod /
NK024(ya)001:11634: log lta ste mi dge ba bcu spong /
NK024(ya)001:11635: so thar dngos la sdom pa gzugs can yin phyir
NK024(ya)001:11636: lus ngag las skye bar 'dod pas lus kyi las
NK024(ya)001:11637: gsum dang ngag gi las bzhi ste bdun spangs pa
NK024(ya)001:11638: la spong bdun gyi tshul khrims zer yang 'dir thun
NK024(ya)001:11639: mong ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK024(ya)001:11640: lus kyi sdom pa legs pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:11641: ngag gi sdom pa legs pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:11642: yid kyi sdom pa legs pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:11643: thams cad du ni sdom pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:11644: thams cad bsrung ba'i dge slong dag /
NK024(ya)001:11645: sdug bsngal kun las nges grol lo //
NK024(ya)001:11647: spyir gong du bshad pa ltar 'du shes bcu ste
NK024(ya)001:11648: srog gcod pa la btsan dug za ba lta bu'i
NK024(ya)001:11650: gos la rma dkris lta bu'i 'du shes te rma
NK024(ya)001:11651: dkris dang bral na rma chud zos par 'gyur ba
NK024(ya)001:11652: ltar chos gos rnam gsum sogs legs par gyon te
NK024(ya)001:11654: nyon mongs pa la dug sprul lta bu'i 'du shes
NK024(ya)001:11655: te reg pa tsam dang dpyad pas phung bar bsam
NK024(ya)001:11656: ste spong / kha zas la bu'i sha za ba
NK024(ya)001:11657: lta bu'i 'du shes byas te sred pa mi bya
NK024(ya)001:11658: ste spong / / rnyed bkur la rgya dang rnyi
NK024(ya)001:11659: lta bu'i 'du shes kyis 'thums par dogs te 'byol
NK024(ya)001:11660: ste spong / / / bla ma dkon mchog la
NK024(ya)001:11661: nor bu rin po che lta bu'i 'du shes bzhag
NK024(ya)001:11662: ste mchod cing gus pas gsol ba btab /
NK024(ya)001:11663: chos la lam bzang po lta bu'i 'du shes bskyed de legs par sbyong zhing 'bad par bya /
NK024(ya)001:11664: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser bzang po lta
NK024(ya)001:11665: bu'i 'du shes ltar dkon zhing bzang la rnyed pa
NK024(ya)001:11666: don ldan du mos te gus par bya zhing lam
NK024(ya)001:11667: la bslab / tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i 'du
NK024(ya)001:11668: shes bzhag ste gces spras tshags dang ldan par bya
NK024(ya)001:11669: la bslab / / chos nyid mngon sum du gyur
NK024(ya)001:11670: ba la mun khung du sgron me bteg pa'i 'du
NK024(ya)001:11671: shes bskyed de ting nge 'dzin la brtson par bya
NK024(ya)001:11672: ba dang bcu la bslab pas nyis brgya lnga bcu
NK024(ya)001:11673: rtsa gsum gyi tshul khrims kyang der 'du ba yin
NK024(ya)001:11674: la bslab / / / theg pa lam 'khyer sogs
NK024(ya)001:11675: gong du rtsa bar bstan pa ltar yin pas de
NK024(ya)001:11677: de ltar lam sbyangs pas zung bzhi ya brgyad kyi
NK024(ya)001:11678: 'bras bu mngon du byed pa ni nyan thos kyi
NK024(ya)001:11679: gdams ngag bshad pa yin pas gdams ngag ngang sgom
NK024(ya)001:11680: sogs la nan tan du mdzod cig /
NK024(ya)001:11681: des nyan thos kyi theg pa'i 'jug sgo tshul gsum
NK024(ya)001:11682: gyi sdom pa'i dngos gzhi dbang khrid thams cad legs
NK024(ya)001:11684: de las bshad pa'i sdom pa sogs legs par bsrung snyams pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:11685: gtso bos ji ltar lan gsum /
NK024(ya)001:11688: bsod nams 'di yis sogs bsngo ba rnams snga ma dang 'dra'o //
NK024(ya)001:11690: de nas slar yang mchod de /
NK024(ya)001:11693: bla ma la yon phul zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK024(ya)001:11694: dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos te byin
NK024(ya)001:11695: rlabs dang mchod bstod gong bzhin rgyas bsdus skabs sbyar
NK024(ya)001:11696: bya / rdo rje sems dpa'i yig brgya lan gsum gyis lhag chad bkang /
NK024(ya)001:11697: ma 'byor ba dang nyams pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:11698: zhes sogs kyis bzod par gsol /
NK024(ya)001:11699: tsakli yod pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i ye shes pa rnams la brtan bzhugs kyi ched du /
NK024(ya)001:11700: 'dir ni gzugs dang zhes sogs kyi tshigs bcad dang /
NK024(ya)001:11701: su pra ti sh+tha'i sngags kyis me tog gtor /
NK024(ya)001:11702: dam tshig pa rnams dang rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor rten med pa'i lha rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:11703: khyod kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:11704: ces sogs kyi tshigs bcad dang lhan du se gol gtog cing gshegs gsol bya /
NK024(ya)001:11705: rdo rjes dbang ldan nas brtsam ste tshon rnams bsdu zhing thig shul dbyi /
NK024(ya)001:11706: bdag bskyed kyi ye shes pa badz+ra muhs gshegs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:11707: sum cu pa bsngo ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:11708: nyer dgu pa bkra shis gnyis go ldog par snang bas thog mar bsngo ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:11709: rtsa bar dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK024(ya)001:11710: zhes gsungs pas bzang spyod sogs smon lam rnam par dag pa btab /
NK024(ya)001:11711: sum cu pa ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:11713: sangs rgyas rabs bdun gyi bkra shis brjod par gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:11714: bcom ldan rnam par gzigs ni rgyal rigs gzi brjid can //
NK024(ya)001:11715: tshe lo brgyad khri'i dus na grong khyer gnyen drung du //
NK024(ya)001:11716: po ta la yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11717: bkra shis phun sum tshogs pas deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:11718: bde gshegs gtsug tor can ni rgyal rigs rdzu 'phrul can //
NK024(ya)001:11719: tshe lo bdun khri'i dus na ka ni'i grong khyer du //
NK024(ya)001:11720: pun+da ri ka'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11721: bkra shis phun sum rgyal ba thams cad skyob ni rgyal rigs blo gros can //
NK024(ya)001:11722: tshe lo drug khri'i dus na grong khyer mnyan yod du //
NK024(ya)001:11723: shing mchog s+aa la'i drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11724: bkra shis phun sum thub pa 'khor ba 'jig ni stobs ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:11725: tshe lo bzhi khri'i dus na grong khyer bde ldan du //
NK024(ya)001:11726: shi ri sha yi drung du mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11727: bkra shis 'dren pa gser thub bslab pa mchog ldan bram ze'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:11728: tshe lo sum khri'i dus na grong khyer mdzes ldan du //
NK024(ya)001:11729: u dum+wa ra'i shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11730: bkra shis skyob pa 'od srungs bram ze bla med yod tan can //
NK024(ya)001:11731: tshe lo nyis khri'i dus na wa ra n+aa si ru //
NK024(ya)001:11732: nya gro ta yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11733: bkra shis 'gro mgon sh+aakya thub pa rgyal rigs brtson 'grus can //
NK024(ya)001:11734: tshe lo brgya pa'i dus na ser skya'i grong khyer du //
NK024(ya)001:11735: a shwat+tha yi shing drung mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:11736: bkra shis phun sum tshog pa des kyang deng 'dir bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:11737: mdo las sangs rgyas rabs bdun gyi bkra shis gsungs
NK024(ya)001:11738: pa dang cung zad ma mthun kyang snga 'gyur gyi
NK024(ya)001:11739: 'gyur khyad yin 'dra snyam rang sor bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:11740: gzhan yang bkra shis kyi tshigs bcad ci rigs brjod cing me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:11741: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i cho ga'o //
NK024(ya)001:11742: nub mo zhi khro'i phrin las tshogs bskang sogs kyang snga ma bzhin bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:11743: so thar gzhung brgya'i tsan+dana nags klung nas //
NK024(ya)001:11744: dag pa'i tshul khrims dri ngad brgyar 'thul ba //
NK024(ya)001:11745: las kyi cho ga'i dri bzhon gyis drangs pas //
NK024(ya)001:11746: gdul bya'i yid dbang tshim bya ngo mtshar rmad //
NK024(ya)001:11747: gnas skabs so so thar pa'i lam bsten nas //
NK024(ya)001:11748: nges pa don gyi dge slong rdo rje 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:11749: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor shar ba'i gzi 'od kyis //
NK024(ya)001:11750: bgrang yas rgyu skar zil gyis gnon dang mtshungs //
NK024(ya)001:11751: thub dbang gnas brtan chen po 'khor dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:11752: sngags rgya ting 'dzin ldan pa'i cho ga yin //
NK024(ya)001:11753: dkyil 'khor 'khor lor mngon sum bzhugs pa'i drung //
NK024(ya)001:11754: dbang bskur tshul khrims legs nod skal bzang dpyid //
NK024(ya)001:11755: ces pa yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i sgrub khrigs la /
NK024(ya)001:11756: dkyil 'khor bsham khungs mchod pa bsham //
NK024(ya)001:11757: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:11758: dpang skong khrus byas sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:11759: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzeg ston pa bsgom //
NK024(ya)001:11760: gsol gdab sdom pa bslab bya dbog /
NK024(ya)001:11761: dka' thub ldan pa'i bum dbang lha //
NK024(ya)001:11762: bkra shis khrims chas drang srong lha //
NK024(ya)001:11763: chos bshad dbang bskur lam 'khyer bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:11764: theg pa lha snying bslab bya dang //
NK024(ya)001:11765: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyir dgos //
NK024(ya)001:11766: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:11767: zhes pas don so gcig nang gses dang bcas pa'i /
NK024(ya)001:11768: dang po dkyil 'khor la don gsum gyis bstan te /
NK024(ya)001:11769: dang po gzhi'i dkyil 'khor gnas tshul la tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs las /
NK024(ya)001:11770: 'byung ba lnga ri rab gcig tu 'dres pa'i gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i me ri 'dod khams /
NK024(ya)001:11772: pad+ma gzugs med de zhes gsungs so //
NK024(ya)001:11773: gnyis pa sgom pa ni them 'og mar nyan thos /
NK024(ya)001:11776: bse ru la dbus gru bzhi sked nyag /
NK024(ya)001:11778: ne tso'i chung ba las pad+ma 'dab bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:11780: tshogs spyod che 'bring la rang rgyud pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11781: sprul pa'i 'dab ma bcu gnyis pa gnyis so //
NK024(ya)001:11782: thams cad kyi lte ba ser /
NK024(ya)001:11785: sgo rta babs sogs spyi dang 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:11786: phyi'i khyams su dpag bsam shing rtsa ba /
NK024(ya)001:11791: nam mkha' rlung me chu sa dus kyi kha dog dang /
NK024(ya)001:11792: ma rig pa sogs rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi mtshan ma dgod do //
NK024(ya)001:11793: zhes gsungs pas sa bcad dang po bstan pa de nyid phyag bzhes su ji ltar bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:11794: zur lugs rtsa ba'i dgongs pa ltar na bse ru lta bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:11795: ne tso lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:11796: ne tso'i tshogs spyod la rang rgyud pa dang sprul
NK024(ya)001:11797: pa'i gnyis te gsum mam bzhi tsam las ma gsungs
NK024(ya)001:11799: rang lugs kyi bla ma'i gsan yig rnams su rang rgyal la dkyil 'khor lngar gsungs te /
NK024(ya)001:11804: tshogs spyod che chung bsdoms pa ste lngar gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:11805: de yang gsung rab spyi skad la bse ru lta
NK024(ya)001:11806: bu ni gcig pur gnas pa yin pas gcig pur
NK024(ya)001:11807: spyod pa zer / ne tso lta bu ni mang
NK024(ya)001:11808: du 'dus shing gnas pa yin pas tshogs na spyod
NK024(ya)001:11809: spyod pa zer / pa zer / kahthoga lugs la
NK024(ya)001:11810: bse ru dang ne tso lta bu re re ste
NK024(ya)001:11812: glan ban bsod nams mgon po sogs bsdoms te gcig tu bzhed pa yang 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:11813: mdor na bse ru ne tso gnyis sam gcig dril tsam gyis 'thus par snang yang /
NK024(ya)001:11814: zur hwam sh+aaka 'byung gi lha thems dang /
NK024(ya)001:11815: rig 'dzin rje'i dngos slob u rgyan pa sogs kyi lngar bshad pa bzhin bris kyang chog mod /
NK024(ya)001:11816: phyag len 'jug pa bde phyir bse ru ne tso gnyis su bsdus na legs shing /
NK024(ya)001:11817: de yang rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi mtshan ma ni khyams su bkod la /
NK024(ya)001:11818: rang rgyal bcu gnyis kyi thugs rgyud la rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi don gnas phyir /
NK024(ya)001:11819: rten 'brel don la brten gnas phyir //
NK024(ya)001:11821: 'phags pa rang rgyal de rnams gcig pur gnas pa'i tshe bse ru lta bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:11822: 'dus te gnas pa'i tshe ne tso lta bur btags
NK024(ya)001:11823: pa yin pas ne tso lta bu'i khongs su tshogs
NK024(ya)001:11824: spyod che 'bring gi sprul pa dang rang rgyud kyang
NK024(ya)001:11825: 'dus so //'on kyang tshogs spyod che 'bring gi sprul
NK024(ya)001:11826: pa dang rang rgyud pa gnyis nyan thos kyi skabs
NK024(ya)001:11827: kyi mchog bcu drug dang gcig par bshad 'dug pas
NK024(ya)001:11828: spro na de bzhin du phye la /
NK024(ya)001:11829: bsdu na snga ma song bas 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:11830: dkyil 'khor rgyas par phye na mdun bskyed sgrub mchod
NK024(ya)001:11831: skabs kyang cung zad mi bde bas 'dir gnyis su
NK024(ya)001:11832: bsdus na mi 'gal zhing legs la phyag len yang
NK024(ya)001:11834: bse ru lta bu la dbus su gru bzhi ser po rked nyag /
NK024(ya)001:11835: de phyir 'dab ma dmar po'am mdzes tshon bcu gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:11836: ne tso lta bu'i lte ba ser /
NK024(ya)001:11838: de'i phyir 'dab brgyad gsungs kyang phyag len du bcu
NK024(ya)001:11839: gnyis rnams dmar po'i mdzes tshon rtsig pa lnga'i kha
NK024(ya)001:11842: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i rta babs kyi khyams su dpag bsam gyi shing rtsa ba /
NK024(ya)001:11846: me tog /'bras bur bcas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11847: nam mkha' rlung me chu sa dang /
NK024(ya)001:11848: dpyid sogs dus bzhi'i kha dog gam ming bri /
NK024(ya)001:11849: phyi'i khor yug gi khyams la yang rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi mtshan ma bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:11850: ma rig pa rgan mo long ba /
NK024(ya)001:11851: 'du byed rdza mkhan rdza bzo tshul /
NK024(ya)001:11853: ming gzugs gang zag grur zhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:11856: tshor ba pus mo la mda' zug pa /
NK024(ya)001:11859: srid pa pho mo 'khrig pa spyod pa /
NK024(ya)001:11860: skye ba sbrum ma bu skye ba /
NK024(ya)001:11861: rga shi rgud pa shi ba lta bu'i mtshan ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:11862: de'i phyir khams gsum mtshon byed pad rdor me ri gsum bri'o //
NK024(ya)001:11864: gnyis pa khungs ni rtsa ba'i bstod pa las /
NK024(ya)001:11865: rten 'brel don la brten gnas pa'i //'phags pa'i rang
NK024(ya)001:11866: rgyal bcu gnyis ni //'byung dang ldog pa rab zhugs
NK024(ya)001:11868: zhes gsungs pas rtogs par sla /
NK024(ya)001:11870: gsum pa mchod pa bsham pa ni nyan thos dang mthun /
NK024(ya)001:11871: bum pa la keng rus kyi mtshan ma bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:11873: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi bsham tshul gong du bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:11874: dang 'dra bar byas te so so'i mthar snga ma
NK024(ya)001:11875: ltar mchod pa g.yas skor dang /
NK024(ya)001:11876: dkon mchog spyi gtor gyi gtor ma re yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:11877: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i dbus su ston pa'i sku bris 'bur gang bde dang /
NK024(ya)001:11878: 'dab ma bcu gnyis la rang rgyal bcu gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:11879: phyi ma'i nang gi 'dab ma bzhir 'khor rnam bzhi'i tsakli btsugs /
NK024(ya)001:11880: gsung rten dang thugs rten yang ci rigs su bshams /
NK024(ya)001:11881: bum pa ni sa bcad gsum pa dang bzhi pa
NK024(ya)001:11882: las ji ltar byung ba ltar bum rdzas bcud ldan
NK024(ya)001:11883: kha rgyan mgul chings gzungs rdor keng rus sam thod
NK024(ya)001:11885: tsan+dana dkar po brdar phye dang snag tsha bsres pas
NK024(ya)001:11886: me long la rten 'brel snying po tshar bdun bris
NK024(ya)001:11887: pa'i tshar re re la lan bdun bdun bzlas te
NK024(ya)001:11889: dkyil 'khor gnyis po gang rung gi dbus su many+dzi la bkod /
NK024(ya)001:11890: zhi khro dang chos srung gi gtor ma rnams kha gso /
NK024(ya)001:11891: cha gsum sogs sngar ltar bsham /
NK024(ya)001:11892: sngon rten gyi sku'i drung du yang mchod pa rgyas par bsham /
NK024(ya)001:11893: dbang rdzas rnams kyang sta gon bya /
NK024(ya)001:11895: bzhi pa rab gnas ni dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi dri
NK024(ya)001:11896: bzang gis byungs par bum pa ma gul chings kha
NK024(ya)001:11897: rgyan bum rdzas 'bru chus bkang ba'i gzungs thag drang
NK024(ya)001:11898: zhing mchod pa bsang sbyang byin brlab skyabs 'gro tshad
NK024(ya)001:11900: tsan+dana dkar po brdar ba'i snag tshas me long la rten 'brel snying po tshar bdun bri /
NK024(ya)001:11901: tshar re re zhing lan bdun bdun bzlas te bum pa'i khar bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:11902: der zla ba la sngags phreng dkar po las 'od
NK024(ya)001:11903: 'phros pas 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad bdud rtsi'i
NK024(ya)001:11905: tshur 'dus bum par thim par bsam zhing lag pa
NK024(ya)001:11906: g.yas pa bum pa la bkab ste sngags brgya rtsa
NK024(ya)001:11907: brgyad bzlas so // de nas me long gi chu bum par blug go //
NK024(ya)001:11908: yang sngags phreng gi 'od kyis phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:11909: byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos sogs spyan drangs rten
NK024(ya)001:11910: dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha la thim par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:11911: de nas lugs sku la sogs la dngos su khrus gsol /
NK024(ya)001:11912: ras bris po ti sogs la me long gis khrus gsol la /
NK024(ya)001:11913: de'i chus mchod rdzas thams cad la gtor te ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:11914: kha dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs par bsam zhing sngags bzlas pas byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:11915: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi don ni bdag mdun bum gsum gyi cho ga las thon pas /
NK024(ya)001:11916: thog mar sa gzhi dang mchod pa byin brlab /
NK024(ya)001:11917: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi sgom pa rnams snga ma dang 'dra bar bya /
NK024(ya)001:11918: bdag bskyed ni kah thog lugs su dkyil 'khor yongs
NK024(ya)001:11919: rdzogs su mdzad 'dug pa rgyas pa'i yan lag tu
NK024(ya)001:11921: 'dir nyan thos kyi skabs ltar thub pa gtso rkyang
NK024(ya)001:11922: gi bdag bskyed bzlas pa mu ne dang rten 'brel
NK024(ya)001:11923: snying po cha mnyam ste bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:11924: bum bskyed ni rab gnas dus su gzungs sgrub kho
NK024(ya)001:11925: na bshad kyang mchan bur bum nang du thub pa
NK024(ya)001:11927: de'i tshul ni thog mar bum pa bsangs sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:11928: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las bum pa tshad dang
NK024(ya)001:11929: mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang du
NK024(ya)001:11930: pad zla'i gdan la thub dbang ser po sa gnon
NK024(ya)001:11931: mnyam bzhag can chos gos sum ldan mtshan dpes spras
NK024(ya)001:11932: pa'i spyi bor / mgrin par +aah thugs kar h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:11934: 'og min nas rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa
NK024(ya)001:11935: m+aa dzahdzah hum bam hoh pad+ma ka ma la ye
NK024(ya)001:11936: s+t+wam / ma h+aa mu ne ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:11937: rnam dag sku mnga' mas bstod /
NK024(ya)001:11938: gzungs thag nas bzung ste mu ne ci rigs par bzlas /
NK024(ya)001:11939: bum pa'i steng gi me long la dmigs te zla
NK024(ya)001:11940: ba la gnas pa'i sngags kyi phreng ba dkar po
NK024(ya)001:11941: las 'od 'phros / snang srid thams cad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du zhu /
NK024(ya)001:11942: tshur 'dus bum par thim par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:11943: lag g.yas bum pa la bkab pa'am bkab pa'i tshul byas te ye d+har+m+aa brgya rtsa bzlas /
NK024(ya)001:11944: me long bkrus pa'i chu bum par blug /
NK024(ya)001:11945: slar yang bum nang gi lha'i thugs kar zla ba la gnas pa'i sngags phreng las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:11946: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas byang sems nyan thos rang rgyal
NK024(ya)001:11947: thams cad spyan drangs te bum par thim par bsams
NK024(ya)001:11948: la ye d+har+m+aa ci rigs bzlas /
NK024(ya)001:11949: mchod bstod sngar bzhin byas te thub pa 'od du zhu ba bum chur gyur par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:11950: las bum yang snga ma ltar sgrub pa'i rnam bum gyis kyang 'thus so //
NK024(ya)001:11962: bcu bzhi pa sdom pa yan chad nyan thos dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:11964: rtsa ba'i sa bcad kyi dbang du byas na khri
NK024(ya)001:11965: dang khrir 'dzeg pa gnyis tha dad yin kyang 'dir
NK024(ya)001:11967: sa bcad lnga pa nas bcu bzhi pa'i bar nyan
NK024(ya)001:11968: thos dang mthun pas gong bzhin bgyis pas chog par
NK024(ya)001:11969: sems kyang / mdun bskyed skabs dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i khyad par dang /
NK024(ya)001:11970: cho ga yang cung zad mi 'dra ba 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:11972: de nas dkyil 'khor bskyed la zhes gsungs pa'i don ltar mdun bskyed bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:11973: rnam bum gyi chus dkyil 'khor dang gnas khang mchod
NK024(ya)001:11974: rdzas rnams la gtor zhing rten 'brel snying po bzlas
NK024(ya)001:11975: bas ma dag pa sbyangs shing mchod pa'i yo byad
NK024(ya)001:11976: rnams kha dog dri ro nus pa phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:11977: pa dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:11979: stong pa'i ngang las sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte ba
NK024(ya)001:11980: la gnas pa'i b+h+aum las rin po che sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:11981: las grub pa'i gzhal med khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi
NK024(ya)001:11982: pa ser mthing dmar ljang dkar ba'i rtsig pa lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:11983: steng na pha gu ser po rin po che'i d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:11984: ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang zhing mda' yab
NK024(ya)001:11986: nang ka ba brgyad dang ldan pa'i steng rdo rje'i
NK024(ya)001:11987: gdung bzhis bteg pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:11988: rje dang rin po che'i tog gis spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:11989: sgo bzhir ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs
NK024(ya)001:11990: bang rim bzhi pa bum pa bre chos 'khor gdugs
NK024(ya)001:11991: tog dang bcas pa'i phyi rol tu 'dod yod kyi
