NK024(ya)001:11992: snam bu la mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis bskor
NK024(ya)001:11993: ba / phyi'i khor yug tu sna tshogs pad+ma rdo
NK024(ya)001:11994: rje'i ra ba 'od zer gyi phreng ba kun nas
NK024(ya)001:11995: 'phro ba'i nang gi khyams dbus sngo shar dkar lho
NK024(ya)001:11996: ser nub dmar byang ljang ba'i dang por dbus gru
NK024(ya)001:11997: bzhi rked nyag gi phyir 'dab ma bcu gnyis dang
NK024(ya)001:11998: ba / / phyi mar nang 'dab ma bzhi de'i phyir bcu gnyis te dkyil 'khor gnyis su gyur /
NK024(ya)001:11999: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:12000: thub pa sh+aakya'i rgyal po gser mdog mtshan dpes spras
NK024(ya)001:12001: pa sa gnon mnyam gzhag can chos gos rnam pa
NK024(ya)001:12002: gsum dang ldan pa 'od zer kun nas 'phro ba
NK024(ya)001:12003: mthong na mi mthun pa med pa'i bdag nyid du
NK024(ya)001:12004: gyur / dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi 'dab ma bcu gnyis
NK024(ya)001:12005: por shar nas rim bzhin 'phags pa rang rgyal bcu
NK024(ya)001:12006: gyur / gnyis ni / 'jigs med rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:12007: snang ba brtsegs pa rin po che 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:12008: dpa' bo 'dul ba rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK024(ya)001:12009: nyon mongs gdung sel bsil yab /
NK024(ya)001:12010: shes rab mgyogs chen zla tshes /
NK024(ya)001:12014: bse ru lta bu mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:12015: ri rgyal rin po che'i snye ma /
NK024(ya)001:12016: seng ge lta bu rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12017: yid myur rnga yab bsnams shing thams cad kyang tshangs
NK024(ya)001:12018: par spyod pa'i cha lugs can gtsug tor cung zad
NK024(ya)001:12019: dang bcas pa'o // dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i nang gi
NK024(ya)001:12020: 'dab ma bzhi'i lho byang du dge slong pha ma
NK024(ya)001:12021: gnyis rab tu byung ba'i cha lugs 'khar gsil lhung
NK024(ya)001:12022: dang bcas pa'o // bzed 'dzin cing / shar nub
NK024(ya)001:12023: tu dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis khyim pa'i cha lugs
NK024(ya)001:12024: dang bcas pa'o // bzed 'dzin cing / can no
NK024(ya)001:12025: // gnyis ka'i sgo bzhir shar du yul 'khor srung
NK024(ya)001:12026: dang bcas pa'o // bzed 'dzin cing / can no // / lhor 'phags skyes po /
NK024(ya)001:12028: byang du rnam thos sras rnams bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12029: lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:12031: thugs kar h+aum sngon pos mtshan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:12032: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK024(ya)001:12033: spos btul zhing rdor dril 'dzin pas /
NK024(ya)001:12036: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK024(ya)001:12037: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK024(ya)001:12038: thugs rjes dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:12039: ye d+ha r+m+aa he tu pra b+ha w+aa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK024(ya)001:12040: te sh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:12042: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:12044: ye shes pa 'jug pa'i bar nyan thos bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:12047: gnas mchog gzhal yas pho brang 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:12048: rin chen pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:12049: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:12050: e d+har+m+aa phyag 'tshal ba ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:12051: dkon mchog bla med rin chen gsum //
NK024(ya)001:12052: sku ni rten cing 'brel ba'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:12054: thugs ni rten 'brel thams cad mkhyen //
NK024(ya)001:12055: sku gsung thugs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:12057: skabs 'dir dpang skong phyag brgya pa tshar gcig 'don /
NK024(ya)001:12058: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi mchod phreng ni /
NK024(ya)001:12059: spos mar me rnams spar zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12062: lha rdzas dam pa'i mchod yon 'di //
NK024(ya)001:12063: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:12064: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba yi //'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK024(ya)001:12065: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:12066: ye d+har+m+aa bud+d+ha d+harma sam g+ha sa pa ri w+aa
NK024(ya)001:12067: ra ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu
NK024(ya)001:12068: dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:12069: rten cing lha rdzas dam pa'i bdug spos 'di //
NK024(ya)001:12070: bla med rten cing 'gro ba thugs rjes ye d+har+m+aa
NK024(ya)001:12071: bud+d+ha d+h+au pe rten cing lha rdzas dam pa'i me
NK024(ya)001:12072: tog 'di // bla med rten cing 'gro ba thugs
NK024(ya)001:12073: rjes ye d+har+m+aa bud+d+ha push+pe rten cing lha rdzas dam
NK024(ya)001:12075: bla med rten cing 'gro ba thugs rjes ye d+har+m+aa
NK024(ya)001:12076: bud+d+ha +aa lo ke rten cing lha rdzas dam pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12077: dri mchog 'di // bla med rten cing 'gro ba
NK024(ya)001:12078: thugs rjes ye d+har+m+aa bud+d+h+aa gan+d+he rten cing lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:12080: rten cing 'gro ba thugs rjes ye d+har+m+aa bud+d+ha nee
NK024(ya)001:12081: wi d+ya rten cing lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo
NK024(ya)001:12082: 'di // bla med rten cing 'gro ba thugs rjes
NK024(ya)001:12083: ye d+har+m+aa bud+d+h+aa d+har+m+aa sam g+ha sa pa ri w+aa
NK024(ya)001:12084: ra shap+da pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu
NK024(ya)001:12085: dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:12087: rnam dag sku mnga' sogs thub bstod dang /
NK024(ya)001:12088: rten 'brel don la brten gnas pa'i //'phags pa rang
NK024(ya)001:12089: rgyal bcu gnyis ni //'byung dang ldog la rab zhugs
NK024(ya)001:12090: pa'i // rang rgyal rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:12091: bstod par 'os pa zhes sogs kyis spyir bstod /
NK024(ya)001:12092: bzlas pa mu ne dang rten 'brel snying po ci rigs bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:12093: sman bla'i mdo chog dang gnas bcu'i cho ga byed
NK024(ya)001:12094: par gsung pas grub na phun sum tshogs pa'i yan
NK024(ya)001:12095: lag yin pas nyan thos ltar bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12096: ma grub kyang 'dir dkyil 'khor la dmigs bsal med pas chad pa'i skyon med dam snyam /
NK024(ya)001:12099: rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK024(ya)001:12100: ji srid cho ga ma grub bar //
NK024(ya)001:12101: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:12102: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK024(ya)001:12105: rgyal ba dgra rgyal bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:12106: bden par gsungs pa de la sdig med cing //
NK024(ya)001:12107: lhar bcas lha min gyis rtag mchod pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:12108: bden pa de yis deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:12109: ye d+har+m+aa dam chos bdud rtsi thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:12110: zhal nas gsung pa bsil ba'i ro 'di yis //
NK024(ya)001:12111: nyon mongs 'bar ba'i me yis gdungs pa yi //'gro ba'i sdug bsngal rtag tu zhi byed shog /
NK024(ya)001:12112: ye d+har+m+aa 'byung po gang dag 'dir ni lhags gyur tam //
NK024(ya)001:12113: zhes pa nas shog cig bar brjod /
NK024(ya)001:12114: ye d+har+m+aa zhes pas me tog phyogs thams cad du gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:12115: cha gsum yang nyan thos skabs ltar btang /
NK024(ya)001:12116: 'og tu slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba bzhin bdag 'jug kyang blang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:12117: de nas slob ma nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sgor
NK024(ya)001:12118: zhugs te sdom par ldan pa rnams bos te gral
NK024(ya)001:12120: khrus bgegs gtor man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu sogs snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:12121: bla mas sems can thams cad kyi don du sangs rgyas thob par bya /
NK024(ya)001:12122: de'i ched du 'dir 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag gi
NK024(ya)001:12123: dkyil 'khor rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i sgor zhugs te
NK024(ya)001:12124: smin grol gyi don tshul bzhin du nyams su blangs
NK024(ya)001:12125: te sems can gyi don bgyid snyam pa byang chub
NK024(ya)001:12126: kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed pa mngon du btang ste
NK024(ya)001:12127: gsan 'tshal / gsan bya'i chos ni 'dir rang rgyal
NK024(ya)001:12128: gyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug par byed pa la slob
NK024(ya)001:12129: dpon gyi bgyi bar 'os pa dkyil 'khor bri ba
NK024(ya)001:12130: nas sgrub mchod bdag 'jug gi bar du legs par
NK024(ya)001:12131: gsan 'tshal / song / bye brag tu nyan rang
NK024(ya)001:12132: gi theg pa'i lugs la brgyad pa khrus bya ba
NK024(ya)001:12133: gsan 'tshal / song / dang / dgu pa sdom rten gyi yon 'bul ba /
NK024(ya)001:12134: bcu pa bla ma'i khri'i khyad par dang de la 'dzeg tshul /
NK024(ya)001:12135: bcu gcig pa rgyan ni tshul khrims yin pas rab tu byung ba'i chas bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:12136: bcu gnyis pa ston pa sgom pa ni bla ma
NK024(ya)001:12137: tha mal par mi lta bar ston pa dngos dang
NK024(ya)001:12138: mtshungs par lta dgos pa sogs kha sang nyan thos
NK024(ya)001:12139: kyi cho ga'i skabs nas ji ltar bshad pa las
NK024(ya)001:12140: gzhan du med pas de bzhin du gsal 'debs pa
NK024(ya)001:12141: dang / bcu gsum pa gsol ba gdab pa ni da lta 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:12142: bcu bzhi pa sdom pa yang nyan thos dang mthun
NK024(ya)001:12143: pa yin par kha sang rgyas par song ba des
NK024(ya)001:12145: bco lnga pa bslab bya ni bzod pa 'bring yan nyan thos ltar /
NK024(ya)001:12146: 'bring nas nyan rang so sor 'byed pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12147: zhes gsungs pas rtogs par sla /
NK024(ya)001:12149: bcu drug pa bum dbang ni /
NK024(ya)001:12150: dka' thub shor nas rdzu 'phrul nyams 'gro ba ltar
NK024(ya)001:12151: dka' thub ldan pas dbang bskur dgos pa'i phyir sdig
NK024(ya)001:12156: ces gsungs pas sdig bshags kyi don ltung ba spyi bshags bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12157: gso sbyong blangs pas sdom pa gong 'phel du 'gyur bas /
NK024(ya)001:12158: de da lta nyid du mngon du 'gyur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12159: de bzhin du ye d+har gyi bzlas pa dang khrus
NK024(ya)001:12160: bkra shis sogs kyang dbang gi skabs su zhar la
NK024(ya)001:12162: bcu bdun pa khrims ni drang srong gi brtul zhugs smra bcad dang rdzu 'phrul lo //
NK024(ya)001:12163: zhes gsungs pa lung las kyang rang sangs rgyas rnams
NK024(ya)001:12164: ni lus kyis chos ston zhing ngag gis chos mi
NK024(ya)001:12166: lus kyi sgo nas stod na me 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:12167: smad nas chu 'brub pa sogs tshul sna tshogs kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba yin /
NK024(ya)001:12169: bco brgyad pa khrims chas ni rab byung yin yang snam sbyar dang 'khar gsil med do //
NK024(ya)001:12172: bcu dgu pa lha ni kun gyi gtso bo thub pa yin la /
NK024(ya)001:12173: rang rgyal rnams kyang bslab sbyangs mthar phyin pas smon pa yid bzhin 'grub cing /
NK024(ya)001:12174: blo che chung gis bse ru ne tso gnyis su byung la /
NK024(ya)001:12175: ye shes gcig pas gtso bo gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12176: rten 'brel la grangs rigs mang yang gtso bo bcu
NK024(ya)001:12177: gnyis su 'dus pas grangs bcu gnyis su nges pa'o
NK024(ya)001:12178: // zhes gsungs pas lam la bslab pa'i tshe blo che chung gis gcig pu dang /
NK024(ya)001:12179: tshogs spyod gnyis yod kyang nyams len gyi gnad gcig pa'i tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:12180: rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs 'byung lugs ldog tu bsgoms pas rten 'brel thams cad der 'du tshul lo //
NK024(ya)001:12182: nyi shu pa chos bshad pa ni brjod pa sgrar
NK024(ya)001:12183: bcas rnam g.yeng gi skyon rig pas smra ba bcad
NK024(ya)001:12185: zhes gsungs pas ngag gi chos mi ston pa'i rgyu mtshan gsungs pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:12186: de ltar lam der 'jug par byed pa la theg
NK024(ya)001:12187: pa 'di'i lugs la 'jug sgo sdom pa dang dngos
NK024(ya)001:12189: des na bla ma dang thub pa'i dbang po gnyis
NK024(ya)001:12190: su med pa la rang rgyal gyi kyil 'khor du
NK024(ya)001:12191: 'jug cing dbang bskur ba zhu ba'i yon du man+dala
NK024(ya)001:12192: phul / de ltar man+dala phul nas bcu gsum pa
NK024(ya)001:12193: gsol ba gdab pa nyan thos dang 'dra bar gsungs
NK024(ya)001:12194: phul / pa'i phyir / lugs der nyan thos rang gzhung dang /
NK024(ya)001:12195: theg chen kha skong gi lugs gnyis su bshad pas /
NK024(ya)001:12196: dang por dkon mchog gsum la phyag bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:12197: dkyil 'khor na bzhugs pa'i gtso bo sangs rgyas la dmigs pa'i phyag gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:12198: de nas thugs rgyud la bzhugs pa'i chos la dmigs pa'i phyag gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:12199: de nas rang rgyal gyi dge 'dun rnams la dmigs pa'i phyag gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:12201: gnyis pa ni bla ma ston pa sangs rgyas dngos
NK024(ya)001:12202: su gsal ba'i gtsug tor gyi nor bu 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:12203: kun nas 'phro ba de nyid las 'dod rgu 'byung
NK024(ya)001:12204: bar mos te snyim pa me tog dang bcas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12207: kun mkhyen ye shes srid pa'i de rig gtso bos
NK024(ya)001:12208: 'dir sdig bshags dang gso sbyong bya bar gsungs pa
NK024(ya)001:12209: yin pas sdig bshags kyi don du 'di'i rjes zlos
NK024(ya)001:12210: lan gsum mdzod / bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:12211: chen po la sogs pa zhes sogs kyi ltung ba
NK024(ya)001:12212: spyi bshags nyan thos skabs ltar tshar gsum dang mjug
NK024(ya)001:12214: de rjes gso sbyong blang ba'i sngon du bzhengs te
NK024(ya)001:12215: phyag 'tshal zhing yan lag bdun pa tshar gcig gsung
NK024(ya)001:12216: bar zhu zhes mtshams sbyar na /
NK024(ya)001:12217: ji snyed su dag phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na //
NK024(ya)001:12218: zhes sogs tshar gcig gi bar phyag bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12219: de nas gral la 'dug ste gso sbyong blang ba'i slad du 'di'i rjes zlos lan gsum mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:12220: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK024(ya)001:12221: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:12222: zhes sogs nas tshul khrims rnam dag gi gzungs kyi bar snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:12223: des sbyor ba'i chos rnams legs par grub nas /
NK024(ya)001:12225: kah thog lugs la nyan rang gi skabs su yang
NK024(ya)001:12226: sgyu 'phrul ltar phan nus kyi dbang rnams bskur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:12227: srol 'dug na'ang / 'dir zur lugs ltar bgyis pas lag len tshang zhing bde bas de ltar na /
NK024(ya)001:12229: nyer gcig pa dbang bskur ba ni rdzas dang lha dbang rim pas thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:12230: gyur shog dang ye d+har+m+aa thams cad kyis brjod par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12231: zhes gsungs pas gyur shog ni bla mas gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:12232: ces gsungs res kyis slob mas shog cig zer dgos
NK024(ya)001:12233: shing / de bzhin du rten 'brel snying po byung
NK024(ya)001:12234: res kyis dpon slob thams cad mgrin gcig tu gsung
NK024(ya)001:12235: shing / bar zhu / rnam rgyal bum pa thogs la /
NK024(ya)001:12238: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin po che
NK024(ya)001:12239: rnam pa gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis rigs
NK024(ya)001:12240: kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK024(ya)001:12241: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags thams cad byang zhing dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:12242: ye d+har+m+aa bum dbang bskur chu 'thung khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:12244: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la ming gi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:12245: bas shes bya la ma rmongs pa rang sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:12246: kyi dbang dam pa thob par ye d+har+m+aa na mo
NK024(ya)001:12247: / phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la shes rab ral
NK024(ya)001:12248: gri'i dbang bskur bas 'khrul pa'i d+r+wa ba thams cad
NK024(ya)001:12249: gcod pa'i dbang ye d+ha r+m+aa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12250: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la na bza' ngur smrig
NK024(ya)001:12251: gi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba las
NK024(ya)001:12252: skyob pa'i dbang ye d+ha r+m+aa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12253: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la bkra shis pa'i rdzas
NK024(ya)001:12254: sbrang rtsi'i dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum tshogs
NK024(ya)001:12255: pa'i dbang ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12256: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la r+ts+wa gding ba'i rdzas
NK024(ya)001:12257: kyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis thob cing bar chad
NK024(ya)001:12258: gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa'i dbang ye d+har+m+aa na
NK024(ya)001:12259: mo / phyogs bcu nang gi skye mched bcu gnyis ni /
NK024(ya)001:12260: ma rig rgan mo long ba ste //'du byed rnam shes rdza mkhan spre'u //
NK024(ya)001:12261: ming gzugs gru ste skye mched grong //
NK024(ya)001:12262: reg pa 'o byed nang gi na //
NK024(ya)001:12263: tshor ba pus mor mda' zug 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:12266: srid pa sbrum ma bu skye 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:12267: rga shi rgud dang shi ba 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:12268: nang gi phyi yi rten 'brel drug /
NK024(ya)001:12269: snga ma drug nang de lhag phyi //
NK024(ya)001:12270: de las bcu gnyis phyi rten 'brel //
NK024(ya)001:12271: mkha' rlung me chu sa khams lnga //
NK024(ya)001:12272: dus kyi 'gyur dang drug phyi'i nang //
NK024(ya)001:12273: rgyu dang 'brel ba drug ces bya //
NK024(ya)001:12274: sa bon myu gu sdong po dang //
NK024(ya)001:12275: lo ma me tog 'bras bu drug /
NK024(ya)001:12277: phyi nang rgyu rkyen rten 'brel rnams //
NK024(ya)001:12278: lugs 'byung lugs ldog mngon gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:12279: yid bzhin bde ba mchog thob shog /'dir tsaklira rang
NK024(ya)001:12280: rgyal gyi sku gzugs bri srol 'dug kyang don sa
NK024(ya)001:12281: lam gyi dbang ma gtogs lha dbang ma yin par
NK024(ya)001:12283: bse ru dang ni ne tso lta bu yi //'bras bu la sogs phyi yi rten 'brel dang //
NK024(ya)001:12284: ma rig la sogs nang gi rten 'brel dang //
NK024(ya)001:12285: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spangs byas shing //
NK024(ya)001:12286: lugs ldog 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras rab bsgrubs nas //'jig
NK024(ya)001:12287: rten pa dang nyan thos rang sa drug /'das nas
NK024(ya)001:12288: rang sangs rgyas kyi sar phyin shog /
NK024(ya)001:12290: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu khyod la rten 'brel gyi
NK024(ya)001:12291: dbang bskur bas yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi sa
NK024(ya)001:12292: thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:12293: ye d+har+m+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:12295: dkyil 'khor nas sku gzugs rnams rim par blangs te dbang bskur zhing 'di skad do //
NK024(ya)001:12296: bcom ldan gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas //'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:12297: ye d+har+m+aa a b+hi na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12298: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rang rgyal bse ru
NK024(ya)001:12299: lta bu dang ne tso lta bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:12300: gcig bur bsam gtan la gnas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:12301: tshogs spyod kyi grogs la brten te bsam gtan mthar
NK024(ya)001:12302: phyin nas yid bzhin bde ba mchog gi dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:12305: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas rdo
NK024(ya)001:12306: rje 'jigs byed rdo rje rtse dgu pa'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:12307: bas 'khor ba skrag par byed pa'i dbang ye a
NK024(ya)001:12308: b+hi na mo / phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la
NK024(ya)001:12309: rang sangs rgyas snang ba brtsegs pa rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:12310: dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin rab tu snang ba'i
NK024(ya)001:12311: dbang ye a b+hi na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12312: phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas dpa'
NK024(ya)001:12313: bo 'dul ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:12314: bas srid pa bsnyil ba'i ye a b+hi na mo
NK024(ya)001:12315: / phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:12317: gdung ba sel ba'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12318: gdung ba sel ba'i ye a b+hi na mo phyogs
NK024(ya)001:12319: bcu shes rab mgyogs chen gyi dbang bskur bas shes
NK024(ya)001:12320: rab rtsal dang ldan pa'i ye a b+hi na mo
NK024(ya)001:12321: / phyogs bcu rdzu 'phrul chen ston gyi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:12322: bas sprul pa'i cho 'phrul dang ldan pa'i ye a
NK024(ya)001:12323: / b+hi na mo / phyogs bcu gdung ba sel
NK024(ya)001:12324: ba'i dbang bskur bas dug lnga 'dul ba'i ye a
NK024(ya)001:12325: / b+hi na mo / b+hi na mo / phyogs
NK024(ya)001:12326: bcu sgra chen po'i dbang bskur bas gsung gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:12327: phyug gi dbang ye a b+hi na mo /
NK024(ya)001:12328: phyogs bcu bse ru lta bu'i dbang bskur bas ting
NK024(ya)001:12329: nge 'dzin rtse gcig tu gyur ba'i ye a b+hi
NK024(ya)001:12330: na mo / phyogs bcu ri'i rgyal po'i dbang pos
NK024(ya)001:12331: dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i rlung gis mi bskyod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12333: phyogs bcu seng ge lta bu'i dbang bskur bas 'jigs
NK024(ya)001:12334: pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ye a b+hi na
NK024(ya)001:12335: mo / phyogs bcu rigs kyi bu rnams la rang
NK024(ya)001:12336: sangs rgyas yid myur ba'i dbang bskur bas ting nge
NK024(ya)001:12337: 'dzin rdzu 'phrul myur ba'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK024(ya)001:12338: mo / gyur cig / ces pas dbang bskur te /
NK024(ya)001:12339: slar yang bum pas dbang bskur khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12340: zhes gsungs pas gong bzhin du dbang bskur zhing bum chu 'thung khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12341: de nas lam 'khyer bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:12342: theg pa lha snying po bslab bya rnams lam du 'khyer zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12344: des na rtsa bar nyer gnyis pa lha lam 'khyer
NK024(ya)001:12345: ni gtso bo sh+aakya thub pa ser po sa gnon
NK024(ya)001:12346: mnyam gzhag dang g.yas g.yon bse ru ne tso rab
NK024(ya)001:12347: byung gi tshul thal mo sbyar ba /
NK024(ya)001:12348: rang rgyal bcu gnyis ni 'jigs med rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12350: dpa' bo 'dul ba rdo rje rtse lnga /
NK024(ya)001:12351: nyon mongs gdung sel bsil g.yab /
NK024(ya)001:12352: shes rab mgyogs chen zla tshes /
NK024(ya)001:12356: bse ru lta bu mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:12357: ri rgyal rin chen snye ma /
NK024(ya)001:12358: seng ge lta bu rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12359: yid myur rnga yab bsnams pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12360: zhes gsungs pas 'di rnams bsdu na rang thub par
NK024(ya)001:12361: bsgoms pa'i 'khor du bse ru ne tso gnyis rab
NK024(ya)001:12362: byung thal sbyar du bsgoms bas chog /
NK024(ya)001:12364: nyer gsum pa snying po ni /
NK024(ya)001:12366: zhes 'byung bas rten 'brel snying po ci nus bgrang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:12368: nyer bzhi pa dbang lam 'khyer ni rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi dbang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:12369: zhes gsungs pa gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:12371: nyer lnga pa theg pa rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:12372: de la 'jug sgo phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:12373: de'ang rdzas g.yung drung shug pa'i 'bras bu las shes te /
NK024(ya)001:12374: 'bras bu de ci las byung brtags pas me tog las byung /
NK024(ya)001:12378: de sa bon la thug ste rgyu dang 'brel pa drug go //
NK024(ya)001:12385: dus kyis mi rtag par bsgyur nas byung bar shes
NK024(ya)001:12386: te phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis so //'di rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:12387: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor du 'bri ba'i rgyu mtshan yang
NK024(ya)001:12388: de yin no // phra ba bag chags kyi tshul du 'khor bar 'dod /
NK024(ya)001:12389: de yang nyan thos bye brag pa'i tshogs lam pa
NK024(ya)001:12390: dang mnyam par sbyangs nas sbyor lam bzod 'bring nas
NK024(ya)001:12391: rigs bya ste / rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs 'byung lugs ldog ste sgom pa ni dmigs rten /
NK024(ya)001:12392: shes rab che bas dur khrod du phyin nas keng
NK024(ya)001:12393: rus kyi phung po la brtags pas shi ba las
NK024(ya)001:12394: byung bar shes / de na ba las /
NK024(ya)001:12406: de gang las byung brtags pas ma rnyed de /
NK024(ya)001:12407: stong par rtogs pas thams cad stong nyid du shes te /
NK024(ya)001:12408: rga shi nas lugs ldog tu rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK024(ya)001:12409: bka' shul du stong nyid re bsgoms pas lugs ldog
NK024(ya)001:12411: rgyu snga ma la brten nas 'bras bu phyi ma
NK024(ya)001:12412: 'byung ba la ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar
NK024(ya)001:12413: brtags pas 'gro ba'i rgyur shes so //
NK024(ya)001:12415: dang po brgyad dang dgu nyon mongs //
NK024(ya)001:12416: gnyis pa bcu pa las yin te //
NK024(ya)001:12417: lhag ma bdun ni bsdug bsngal lo //
NK024(ya)001:12419: dang po brgyad dang dgu pa rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:12420: gnyis pa bcu pa rkyen yin no //
NK024(ya)001:12423: de'ang tshe dum bu gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:12424: rgyu rkyen 'bras gsum dang 'phel 'grib lngar 'dod de /
NK024(ya)001:12425: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis po dngos su 'khor ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:12427: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul shes nas /
NK024(ya)001:12428: dngos po'i gzugs la thogs pa med par 'jug /
NK024(ya)001:12429: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtog /
NK024(ya)001:12431: nyer drug pa lta ba gang zag gi bdag med
NK024(ya)001:12432: rtogs pa'i steng du chos kyi bdag phyogs gcig la
NK024(ya)001:12433: bdag med par rtogs pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:12434: de gzung yul dang 'dzin sems gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:12435: gzung yul rdul phran rang bzhin med par stong pa nyid du rtogs /
NK024(ya)001:12436: 'dzin pa'i shes pa skad cig ma skye 'gag dang bcas pa nyan thos ltar 'dod /
NK024(ya)001:12437: lha mo dri ma med pa lung bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:12438: 'dzin pa'i sems ni ma spangs te //
NK024(ya)001:12439: gzung bya'i yul ni rnam rtog bcom //
NK024(ya)001:12440: rang rgyal gyi ni lta ba ste //
NK024(ya)001:12441: nyan thos pa las khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:12443: nyer bdun pa bsrung bya tshul khrims ni nyan thos dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:12444: nyer brgyad pa ti nge 'dzin ni rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs ldog tu sgom pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:12446: ma rig pa dang sred len gsum /
NK024(ya)001:12447: snga ma'i dus te rgyu ru 'dod //'du byed dang ni srid pa gnyis //
NK024(ya)001:12448: da lta'i dus te rkyen du 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:12449: rnam shes ming dang skye mched drug /
NK024(ya)001:12450: reg pa dang ni tshor ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:12451: skye ba rga shi bdun po ni //
NK024(ya)001:12453: nyer dgu pa spyod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:12456: bar nas rlung g.yo ba sogs rdzu 'phrul ya ma zung bstan nas rigs mthun du don mdzad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12458: ngag gi rdo rje yi ge med //
NK024(ya)001:12459: lus kyi rdo rje snang byed nas //
NK024(ya)001:12460: brjod med sprul pa'i chos ston pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12463: rang sangs rgyas kyi dgra bcom pa rang byang chub thob pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12465: gnas ri bo bya rkang can /
NK024(ya)001:12467: 'khor nyan thos dbang po rno ba /
NK024(ya)001:12469: dgos pa lugs 'byung lugs ldog gis 'khor 'das dbyer med du rtogs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12470: so gnyis pa dbang de chags shing bstan pa'i phyir ngang sgom gdams ngag gsal gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:12471: rang gi spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam zhig /
NK024(ya)001:12472: de las khru gang gis mtho bar dkar po sran ma tsam zhig ba sam /
NK024(ya)001:12473: thig le dmar po de la shes pa gtad pas
NK024(ya)001:12474: je cher 'phel snang srid thams cad dmar lam gyis
NK024(ya)001:12475: song bar bsam / dmar po de chags pa'i rang bzhin lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK024(ya)001:12476: yang dkar po la shes pa gtad pas je cher snang srid thams cad dkar lam song bar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:12477: de lugs ldog mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos yin
NK024(ya)001:12478: dkar dmar gnyis po de 'dres nas spyi bo nas
NK024(ya)001:12479: mar babs / snying gi dkyil du thim nas rang
NK024(ya)001:12480: gi sems dang dbyer med du 'dres pas 'khor 'das
NK024(ya)001:12481: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang la bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:12482: de rnams kyi don sgom pa ni lha dang snying
NK024(ya)001:12483: po lam 'khyer rtsa ba nas ji ltar bshad pa
NK024(ya)001:12484: ltar la / ngang sgom gdams ngag gsal 'debs 'di'i dmigs khrid kyi dngos gzhi yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:12485: rang gi spyi bor lugs 'byung 'khor ba chags pa'i rang bzhin thig le dmar po sran ma tsam /
NK024(ya)001:12486: de las khru gang gis mtho bar lugs ldog mya
NK024(ya)001:12487: 'das kyi rang bzhin thig le dkar po sran ma
NK024(ya)001:12488: tsam zhig bsam / thig le dmar po de la shes pa gtad pas je cher 'phel /
NK024(ya)001:12489: snang srid thams cad dmar lam gyis song bar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:12490: yang dkar po la shes pa gtad pas je cher 'phel /
NK024(ya)001:12491: snang srid thams cad dkar lam gyis song bar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:12492: mthar thig le dkar dmar gnyis gcig tu 'dres nas
NK024(ya)001:12493: spyi bo nas mar babs te snying gi dkyil du
NK024(ya)001:12494: thim nas rang sems dang dbyer med du 'dres par
NK024(ya)001:12495: bsam / 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du blo lhod kyis bskyur la bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:12496: glan ston gyi chog khrigs su lha rje sh+aaka mgon
NK024(ya)001:12497: ni de gcig pu la yang zhag gsum sgom skad
NK024(ya)001:12498: gsungs pas bla ma gong ma rnams dmigs rkang de
NK024(ya)001:12499: tsam la yang nan tan du mdzad pas ngo mtshar
NK024(ya)001:12500: gyi gnas so // lta sgom ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par ni /
NK024(ya)001:12501: dur khrod kyi bam ro'am keng rus la brtags pas /
NK024(ya)001:12502: de shi ba las byung bar shes /
NK024(ya)001:12503: de gang las byung brtags pas na ba la byung bar shes /
NK024(ya)001:12504: de bzhin du brtags pas de rgas pa las /
NK024(ya)001:12515: de ma rig pa las byung bar shes shing /
NK024(ya)001:12516: mthar ma rig pa la brtags pas gang nas kyang
NK024(ya)001:12517: ma byung gang du yang ma grub pa stong par
NK024(ya)001:12518: rtogs / de rnams dpe gang dang 'dra na /
NK024(ya)001:12519: ma rig pa rgan mo long ba lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12522: ming dang gzugs gang zag grur zhugs pa lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12523: skye mched drug grong khyer lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12524: reg pa 'o byed pa lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12525: tshor ba pus mo la mda' zug pa lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12526: sred pa 'o thug 'thung ba lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12527: len pa me tog 'thu ba lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12528: srid pa pho mo 'khrig pa spyod pa lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12529: skye ba bud med bu skye ba lta bu /
NK024(ya)001:12530: rga shi ro lta bu dang 'dra bar shes /
NK024(ya)001:12531: de bzhin du 'bras bu la brtags pas /
NK024(ya)001:12534: de sngong po'am myu gu las /
NK024(ya)001:12535: de rtsa ba'am sa bon las byung bar shes pa
NK024(ya)001:12536: ni rgyu la brten nas 'brel ba drug tu shes
NK024(ya)001:12537: / de yang rgyu rkyen ji ltar na nam mkhas go phye /
NK024(ya)001:12542: de yang dbyar dgun ston dpyid dus bzhis bsgyur bas
NK024(ya)001:12543: myu gu nas 'bras bu'i bar mi rtag par 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:12544: bas / rkyen gyis 'brel ba drug dang bcu gnyis su shes /
NK024(ya)001:12545: dpe de bzhin du rang gi tshe snga phyi da
NK024(ya)001:12546: lta gsum rgyu rkyen 'bras bu gsum la 'phel 'grib
NK024(ya)001:12548: de zhin du sbyar te phyi nang gi las thams
NK024(ya)001:12549: cad rten 'brel du 'char bar rtogs shing shes pas
NK024(ya)001:12551: lta ba gang zag gi bdag med dang phyi gzung yul stong par rtogs /
NK024(ya)001:12552: nang gi 'dzin sems nyan thos bzhin 'dod pas bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs te /
NK024(ya)001:12553: lha mo dri ma med lung bstan pa'i mdo lung gong du gsungs pa des shes la /
NK024(ya)001:12554: 'on kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK024(ya)001:12555: dbu ma la mkhas pa'i slob dpon zla ba grags
NK024(ya)001:12556: pa rang rgyal gyis bdag med gnyis ka rtogs par
NK024(ya)001:12557: bzhed / de ltar lta ba bdag med phyed dang gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:12558: sgom pa rten 'brel bcu gnyis lugs 'byung lugs ldog
NK024(ya)001:12559: tu bsgoms pas 'bras bu rang byang chub thob par
NK024(ya)001:12560: 'gyur zhing / bslab bya ni nyan thos dang mthun par lam du 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:12561: de ltar ngang sgom gdams ngag gsal 'debs lha dang
NK024(ya)001:12562: snying po lam 'khyer dang rten 'brel bcu gnyis sgom
NK024(ya)001:12563: tshul sogs dmigs thun du bcad de nyams su len
NK024(ya)001:12564: par mdzod / des rang rgyal gyi smin grol rnams
NK024(ya)001:12565: legs par grub pa yin pas tshul bzhin du bslab
NK024(ya)001:12566: bya rnams bsrung snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:12567: gtso bos ji ltar sogs dam tshig bsdus te khas blangs /
NK024(ya)001:12570: dge ba bsngo ba sogs snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:12572: so gsum pa mchod cing gtor ma bsdu gshegs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:12573: dkyil 'khor bsdus te mi rtog pa sgom mo //
NK024(ya)001:12574: zhes gsungs pa'i don dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos te byin gyis brlab nas /
NK024(ya)001:12576: gzhan ma bzod gsol bsdu chog gi bar nyan thos ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:12578: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12579: zhes gsungs 'dir blangs te bzang spyod sogs bsngo smon bya /
NK024(ya)001:12581: so gcig pa bkra shis ni /
NK024(ya)001:12582: de nas me tog so sor bkram ste rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK024(ya)001:12583: shin tu brgal dka' 'khor ba'i mtsho las brgal //
NK024(ya)001:12584: bsod nams ye shes dpag yas tshogs gnyis rdzogs //'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig de bzhin gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:12585: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:12586: skye rga na 'chi rtag tu mtha' dag spangs //
NK024(ya)001:12587: ma rig mun pa 'joms pa'i sgron me'i tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:12588: dmigs pa'i mtha' spangs lam gyi bde 'gror zhugs //
NK024(ya)001:12589: bkra shis rang don spangs shing gzhan don lhur len
NK024(ya)001:12590: pa //'dod pa'i yon tan lta ba rgyang bsrings te
NK024(ya)001:12591: // dad dang brtson 'grus 'grogs mchog byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:12592: bkra shis snyigs dus smon lam dbang gis sku sprul nas //
NK024(ya)001:12593: shin tu nyon mongs gdul dka' 'dul mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:12594: thabs mkhas thugs rje cher mnga' rkang gnyis gtso //
NK024(ya)001:12595: bkra shis des kyang der 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:12596: ces brjod la me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:12597: gzhan yang bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa ci rigs brjod par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12599: nub mo zhi khro'i phrin las tshogs bskang sogs kun
NK024(ya)001:12600: la sbyor shes par bya'o //'khor 'das lam gyis bsdus
NK024(ya)001:12602: phyi nang rgyu 'bras rten cing 'brel bar 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:12603: tshul bzhin legs shes bdag med rtogs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:12604: ting 'dzin sgo brgya'i lam la slob 'di mtshar //
NK024(ya)001:12605: ma lus 'gro rnams thar par 'dren pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:12606: brjod pa sgrar bcas rnam g.yeng skyon rig nas //
NK024(ya)001:12607: stod nas me 'bar smad nas chu 'brub sogs //
NK024(ya)001:12608: rmad byung lus kyi sprul pas gdul bya 'dul //
NK024(ya)001:12609: nyan rang lam gyi theg skas la 'dzegs nas //
NK024(ya)001:12610: rin chen byang chub sems kyi khang brtsegs su //
NK024(ya)001:12611: gsang sngags phyi nang theg pa'i rgyal srid mchog /
NK024(ya)001:12612: thob 'dod lam gyi 'jug sgo 'di bzung zhig /
NK024(ya)001:12613: ces bya ba yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad
NK024(ya)001:12614: pa'o////byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor la sa bcad spyir
NK024(ya)001:12615: bco lnga dang / nang gses bzhi bcu tsam gyis bstan pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:12617: dkyil 'khor mchod bsham lha tshogs bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:12618: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum btang /
NK024(ya)001:12619: dpang skong khrus byas sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:12620: rgyan ldan khrir 'dzeg ston pa sgom //
NK024(ya)001:12621: gsol gdab sdom pa bslab bya dbog /
NK024(ya)001:12622: chos bshad dbang bskur lam 'khyer bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:12623: theg pa lha snying bslab bya la'ang //
NK024(ya)001:12624: theg dag lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyir dgos //
NK024(ya)001:12625: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:12626: zhes pa'i dang po dkyil khor la gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:12629: dang po dkyil 'khor gyi sa mtshams ri rab kyi
NK024(ya)001:12630: kha khyer mu tig dang nor bu bkram pa'i brag
NK024(ya)001:12632: lam du dkyil 'khor sgom tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:12634: gnyis pa sgom pa ni rta babs bang rim bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12636: ji ltar bri ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:12638: gsum pa bri ba ni dkyil 'khor bcu ste /
NK024(ya)001:12639: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:12641: nang 'dab bzhi lha snam can gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:12643: phyi 'khor lo rtsibs bcur pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi bzhi gru chad lha snam can gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:12644: nang 'dab brgyad phyi lho byang drag po'i rtsibs drug
NK024(ya)001:12645: la 'dab brgyad pa re re gru chad lha snam
NK024(ya)001:12646: can dang / nang 'dab brgyad kyi phyir yang 'dab
NK024(ya)001:12647: brgyad che ba'i nang du 'dab brgyad re re ste
NK024(ya)001:12648: can dang / / shar nub tu gnyis gnyis so //'dab bzhi dmar /
NK024(ya)001:12653: gru chad dang lha snam phyogs mdog /
NK024(ya)001:12654: sgo rta babs khor yug sogs spyi dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:12655: zhes gsungs pa de nyid lag len du ji ltar
NK024(ya)001:12656: bya ba ni sngon rabs kyi dkyil 'khor rnams la
NK024(ya)001:12657: / lha mi nyan rang byang sems kri yog sde
NK024(ya)001:12658: gsum man chad la bshad gzhi sna tshogs kyang lag
NK024(ya)001:12659: len du dkyil 'khor re re byed pa mang bar
NK024(ya)001:12660: / 'dug mod / 'dir gzhung bzhin rgyas par phye ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:12661: khyad par byang sems skabs 'dir zur lugs khams lugs
NK024(ya)001:12662: gnyis ka la dkyil 'khor bcu byed par gsungs pa
NK024(ya)001:12663: grangs shin tu mthun cing lha rnams cung zhig mi
NK024(ya)001:12665: 'dir zur lugs gtsang mar bya ba la /
NK024(ya)001:12667: gnyis pa nang du pad+ma dmar po 'dab bzhi can /
NK024(ya)001:12669: bzhi pa 'dab brgyad bshad pa phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:12670: kyi lha gnas yin par steng 'og gi sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:12671: kyi lha gnas ma bshad pa yin snang bas lag
NK024(ya)001:12672: len du 'dab bcu mdzes tshon can /
NK024(ya)001:12674: drug pa 'dab bzhi dmar po gru chad bzhi lha snam dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:12676: brgyad pa gnyis dbus su ling tshe dgus rdo rje'i gdung ltar bcad pa'i /
NK024(ya)001:12677: phyir mtshon cha 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bcu pa shar nub gnyis su lhag re dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:12678: tshangs thig 'debs dus shar nub kyi thig rtsibs bar
NK024(ya)001:12679: du 'gro zhing lho byang gi thig rtsibs rtser 'gro
NK024(ya)001:12680: ba / rtsibs re re'i nang pad+ma dmar po 'dab
NK024(ya)001:12681: bzhi re gru chad dang lha snam gong ltar ro
NK024(ya)001:12682: ba / // dkyil 'khor dgu pa dbus su 'dab
NK024(ya)001:12683: brgyad mdzes tshon gyi phyir mtshon cha 'khor lo ser
NK024(ya)001:12684: po rtsibs drug pa rtsibs re re'i steng du 'dab
NK024(ya)001:12686: gru chad dang lha snam gong ltar ro /
NK024(ya)001:12687: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i dbus su kah thog lugs la
NK024(ya)001:12688: ling tshe dgu byed par gsungs kyang zur lugs la
NK024(ya)001:12689: nang du 'dab brgyad dang phyir pad+ma 'dab bcu mdzes
NK024(ya)001:12690: tshon gyi 'dab ma re re dbus su 'dab brgyad
NK024(ya)001:12692: gru chad glo 'bur gong bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:12693: rtsig pa'i kha dog ni dkyil 'khor dang po /
NK024(ya)001:12700: bcu pa rnams nang nas rim pa bzhin ser mthing dmar ljang dkar ba /
NK024(ya)001:12701: gsum pa nang nas dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ba /
NK024(ya)001:12702: dgu pa nang nas sngo ser dmar ljang dkar ba'i rtsig pa lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:12703: bcu po thams cad kyi go sar ser /
NK024(ya)001:12705: gru chad dang lha snam phyogs mdog can /
NK024(ya)001:12713: pad rdor me ri rnams spyi dang mtshungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:12714: lha mtshan dkyil chog ltar sku mdog dang mthun pa'i tshon spungs bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12716: gnyis pa mchod pa bsham pa ni rgyan bla bre sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:12717: me tog la sogs dang rol mo sta gon bya /
NK024(ya)001:12718: bum pa mgul chings sogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:12719: mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang rdzas /
NK024(ya)001:12720: cha gsum la sogs pa bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:12722: dkyil 'khor dang po nas bcu pa'i bar go rim
NK024(ya)001:12723: ma nor bar byas pa'i lha gnas su tsakli rnams
NK024(ya)001:12724: btsugs / tsa kli med pa rnams lha mtshan yod phyir stong par bzhag pas kyang 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:12725: mchod pa dkon mchog spyi gtor yang dkyil 'khor so
NK024(ya)001:12726: sor bsham dgos phyir mchod pa tshar bcu dang gtor
NK024(ya)001:12731: rgyal mtshan sogs kyang 'byor na tshogs gnyis gsog phyir mdzes par bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:12732: bum pa bcud ldan kha rgyan mgul chings dar dmar
NK024(ya)001:12733: ser gang rigs sam kha dog sna tshogs pas brgyan
NK024(ya)001:12734: pa gzungs rdor dung chos bcas pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:12735: dbus gang bder many+dzi'i steng du bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:12736: snga 'gyur lugs la rdzas dbang rnams 'byor na dngos
NK024(ya)001:12737: bshams kho na mdzad par 'dug pa kun la go
NK024(ya)001:12738: bar bya dgos / cha gsum dang dbang gi sngon 'gro'i bgegs gtor /
NK024(ya)001:12739: zhi khro chos srung gi mchod gtor kha bsos te snga ma bzhin du nyer bsdogs dang /
NK024(ya)001:12740: sdom rten ston pa'i sku drung du mchod pa 'bur dod kyi rgyas par bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:12741: jo bo yab sras sogs byang sdom mchod pa bzang
NK024(ya)001:12742: ngan gyi khyad par las skye tshul sogs gsungs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12743: phyir rtsa ba'i sa bcad kyi dkyus su lha bskyed
NK024(ya)001:12744: pa 'dug kyang bzhi pa 'dir len dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:12746: bzhi pa rab gnas gong bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:12747: zhes gsungs pas rdor dril dang bcas te me tog 'thor zhing rten 'brel snying pos rab gnas bya'o /
NK024(ya)001:12748: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa bdag mdun gyi sgrub mchod yin te /
NK024(ya)001:12750: gsum pa lha bskyed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:12751: rang nyid skyabs su 'gro ba dang sems bskyed pa byas nas /
NK024(ya)001:12755: dge ba la rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:12756: mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:12757: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba na /
NK024(ya)001:12758: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngosa te bsod nams kyi tshogs gsag go //
NK024(ya)001:12759: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir mchod pa byiin rlab dang skyabs
NK024(ya)001:12760: sems tshad med bzhi rnams snga ma bzhin byas rjes
NK024(ya)001:12761: / ji snyed su dag sogs yan lag bdun pa yid ches par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12762: de rjes bdag mdun bum gsum ni kahthoga lugs su
NK024(ya)001:12763: dkyil 'khor yongs rdzogs kyi cho ga kha bsgyur 'dug
NK024(ya)001:12765: ha cang mang skyon 'dug pas 'dir bdag bum gnyis
NK024(ya)001:12766: su gtso bo lha lnga la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:12767: kyi 'khor dang / mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor yang rdzogs bsgoms nas 'thad cing /
NK024(ya)001:12768: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu bzhi par bla ma sangs rgyas thub pa yum /
NK024(ya)001:12769: de bzhin gshegs pa bcu'i nga rgyal gyis zhes gsungs
NK024(ya)001:12770: pas gzhung don dang mthun par sems pas dang po
NK024(ya)001:12772: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che sna
NK024(ya)001:12773: tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gi nang pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:12774: 'dab bzhi lha snam dang bcas pa'i lte bar rin
NK024(ya)001:12775: po che'i khri pad zla'i gdan la mam las rang
NK024(ya)001:12776: nyid bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa ser po sa
NK024(ya)001:12777: gnon mnyam gzhag can 'dab bzhi'i shar du pam las
NK024(ya)001:12778: yum chen ser mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po
NK024(ya)001:12779: gnyis mnyam gzhag / g.yas 'og ma rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12780: g.yon 'og ma glegs bam 'dzin pa dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:12781: lhor h+aum las phyag na rdo rje sngon po rdo
NK024(ya)001:12782: rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa dar dang rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:12783: rgyan can / nub tu mam las sh+aa ri'i bu dge slong ser po 'khar gsil lhung bzed can /
NK024(ya)001:12784: byang du h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig
NK024(ya)001:12785: phyag gnyis pad+ma dang glegs bam 'dzin pa dar dang
NK024(ya)001:12786: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:12787: lha snam gyi shar stod du sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal sngo skya bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:12788: shar du dkon mchog 'byung gnas dkar po g.yas mchog sbyin gyis rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:12789: lhor mya ngan med dpal sngon po g.yas 'khor lo //
NK024(ya)001:12790: nub tu rin chen 'od 'phro dkar po g.yas mche ba /
NK024(ya)001:12791: byang du rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang gu g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12792: shar lhor pad+ma dam pa'i dpal dkar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12793: lho nub tu nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal dmar po g.yas nyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:12794: nub byang du gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal ljang gu g.yas sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12795: byang shar du ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal ser po g.yas chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:12796: nub smad du pad+mo'i dpal ser po g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12797: g.yon thams cad mnyam gzhag mdzad pa sangs rgyas sprul pa sku'i cha lugs can no //
NK024(ya)001:12798: gtso 'khor rnams kyi spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:12802: 'og min dang phyogs bcu'i zhing khams nas rang 'dra'i
NK024(ya)001:12803: ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK024(ya)001:12804: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK024(ya)001:12812: rnam dag sku mnga' smra bsam brjod med lcang lo
NK024(ya)001:12813: can gyi gnas mchog skyon gyis ma gos sogs sh+lo
NK024(ya)001:12815: dga' ba pad+mo'i dpal dang dkon mchog 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:12816: mya ngan med dpa' 'od 'phro rgyal ba'i dbang //
NK024(ya)001:12817: glang po pad+ma snang ba gdugs dam pa //
NK024(ya)001:12818: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:12819: bstod par 'os pa zhes sogs kyis bstod /
NK024(ya)001:12822: yum chen mor dbang gi skabs nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK024(ya)001:12823: d+h+ai pradz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:12825: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:12827: na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aa b+ha ga wan pra b+ha
NK024(ya)001:12828: ta th+aa ga ta ya a ba lo ki te
NK024(ya)001:12829: k+aa ru na ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:12831: +aar+ya a ba lo ki te shwa ra ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:12832: zhes gtso bo lnga'i bzlas pa ci rigs dang /
NK024(ya)001:12833: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas la thun mong du /
NK024(ya)001:12834: mu ne ci rigs bzlas mthar gong bzhin mchod bstod bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12835: bdag bskyed dbang ma tshar bar mi bsdu bar gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:12838: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i bum
NK024(ya)001:12839: pa tshad dang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:12840: pa'i nang gzhal yas khang par gyur pa'i dbus su
NK024(ya)001:12841: pad+ma 'dab bzhi lha snam dang bcas pa'i lte bar
NK024(ya)001:12842: rin po che'i khri pad zla'i gdan la mam las
NK024(ya)001:12843: bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa zhes sogs gong bzhin
NK024(ya)001:12844: bdag bskyed kho na'i rigs 'gres sbyor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12845: gzungs thag blangs te bzlas pa bya zhing bdag gi
NK024(ya)001:12846: thugs ka nas 'od zer gzungs thag la 'khril te
NK024(ya)001:12848: sku'i cha thams cad las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas
NK024(ya)001:12849: bum pa gang bar bsam zhing gong bzhin bzlas pa
NK024(ya)001:12851: yig brgya lan gsum gyis lhag chad bkang /
NK024(ya)001:12852: dung chos kyi chu blug pas lha rnams 'od du zhu ba bum chur gyur par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:12853: rtsa ba'i sa bcad brgyad pa bum par lha bskyed bzlas pa bya /
NK024(ya)001:12854: zhes pa'i mchan bur bum nang du sh+aaka thub bskyed pa dbus su gzhug gsung /
NK024(ya)001:12855: zhes pa'i dgongs pa ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:12856: las bum bskyed pa snga ma rnams dang 'dra'o //
NK024(ya)001:12859: de nas swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+ha rmahswa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:12860: zhes pas bdag dang snang ba thams cad stong par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:12861: de'i ngang las rdor sems su mos pa'i snying gar h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:12862: de las e yam ram bam lam sum rnams chad pa las /
NK024(ya)001:12863: nam mkha' rlung me chu sa ri rab kyi steng du /
NK024(ya)001:12864: b+h+r+aum rat+na bi shwa bi shud+d+he man+da la /
NK024(ya)001:12865: zhes pas rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i
NK024(ya)001:12866: gzhan yas khang gsal dwangs sgrib thogs med pa'i dbus
NK024(ya)001:12867: su zhes 'byung ba'i don rgyas par bstan pa ni
NK024(ya)001:12868: / rang bdag bskyed dus thub par bskyed pa kho nas go chod de rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na /
NK024(ya)001:12869: rdor sems la rnam 'gyur mang yang lugs 'di'i dkyil
NK024(ya)001:12870: 'khor dgu pa'i gtso bo rdor sems sngon po sa
NK024(ya)001:12871: gnon mnyam gzhag can zhig yod pa la zin bris
NK024(ya)001:12872: rnams su ngo bo thub pa rnam pa rdor sems
NK024(ya)001:12874: thub pa kho na'i nga rgyal la the tshom mi bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:12875: rnam rgyal bum pa'i chu ku shas phyogs bcur 'thor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:12878: snang ba thams cad mi dmigs te stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK024(ya)001:12879: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid thub pa rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:12880: sems dpa'i bdag nyid can du gsal ba'i snying gar
NK024(ya)001:12881: rgyu'i ye ge h+aum sngon po de las /
NK024(ya)001:12882: e yam ram bam lam sum rnams chad de 'og tu 'phros pa las /
NK024(ya)001:12883: e las nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas mthing nag gru gsum pa /
NK024(ya)001:12884: de'i steng du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu rgya gram gyi dbyibs can /
NK024(ya)001:12885: de'i steng du ram las me'i dkyil 'khor dmar po gru gsum /
NK024(ya)001:12886: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po /
NK024(ya)001:12887: de'i steng du lam las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi ser po /
NK024(ya)001:12888: de'i steng du sum las ri rab shar dkar /
NK024(ya)001:12891: byang ser ba bang rim bzhi rnams su gyur /
NK024(ya)001:12892: b+h+aum rat+na bi shwa bi shud+d+he man+dala la /
NK024(ya)001:12893: zhes pas ri rab kyi steng du rin po che
NK024(ya)001:12894: sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi
NK024(ya)001:12895: sgo bzhi rtsig pa kha dog lnga ldan gyi steng
NK024(ya)001:12896: na pha gu ser po la rin po che'i d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:12897: ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang ba mda' yab
NK024(ya)001:12899: nang ka ba brgyad dang ldan pa'i steng rdo rje'i
NK024(ya)001:12900: gdung bzhis bteg pa'i dbus phyur bur gyur pa rdo
NK024(ya)001:12901: rje dang rin po che'i tog gi spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:12902: sgo bzhir ka ba bzhi bzhis btegs pa'i rta babs
NK024(ya)001:12903: bang rim bzhi pa steng 'og gi sgo rgyan dang
NK024(ya)001:12904: ldan pa / sna tshogs rdo rje nyi dkyil pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:12905: rdo rje'i ra ba 'od zer gyi phreng ba dang
NK024(ya)001:12908: gnyis pa'i dbus su pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:12910: gnyis pa'i shar du rin po che'i khri nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la /
NK024(ya)001:12911: mam las thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:12913: dang po'i shar du pam las yum chen po ser
NK024(ya)001:12914: mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis mnyam gzhag
NK024(ya)001:12916: g.yon 'og ma po ti longs sku'i tshul can /
NK024(ya)001:12917: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i lhor h+aum las phyag na rdo rje sngon po g.yas rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12919: nub tu mam las sh+aa ri'i bu ser po dge slong 'khar gsil lhung bzed can /
NK024(ya)001:12920: byang du h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyis g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12921: g.yon po ti 'dzin pa longs sku'o //
NK024(ya)001:12923: yang yum dang thub pa gnas barjesa pas dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:12926: bzhi pa'i pad+ma 'dab ma bcu pa'i dbus dang phyogs
NK024(ya)001:12927: bcur a sing a h+r+aihls rin po che'i khri nyi
NK024(ya)001:12928: zla pad+ma'i gdan / dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i dbus su
NK024(ya)001:12929: yum chen mo dkar mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas
NK024(ya)001:12930: zla pad+ma'i gdan / mchog sbyin / g.yon pad+ma po tis mtshan pa longs sku /
NK024(ya)001:12931: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i dbus su thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:12932: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i shar du sangs rgyas dkon mchog
NK024(ya)001:12933: 'byung gnas dkar po g.yas mchog sbyin gyis rin po
NK024(ya)001:12935: lhor mya ngan med pa'i dpal sngon po g.yas 'khor lo //
NK024(ya)001:12936: nub tu rin chen 'od 'phro dkar po g.yas mche ba /
NK024(ya)001:12937: byang du rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang gu g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12938: shar lhor sangs rgyas pad+ma dam pa'i dpal dkar po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12939: lho nub tu nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal dmar po nyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:12940: nub byang du gdugs chen dam pa'i dpal ljang gu sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12941: byang shar du rin chen glang po dam pa'i dpal ser po g.yas chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:12942: steng mtshon pa'i shar stod du sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal sngo skya bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:12943: 'og mtshon pa'i nub smad du pad+ma dam pa'i dpal
NK024(ya)001:12944: ser po pad+ma bsnams pa thams cad kyang g.yon mnyam
NK024(ya)001:12946: yang thub pa dang yum gnas barjesa pas dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:12949: drug pa 'dab bzhi lha snam can gyi lnga pa'i dbus dang /
NK024(ya)001:12950: drug pa'i shar du mi las thub pa ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:12951: yang dkyil 'khor drug pa'i dbus dang /
NK024(ya)001:12952: lnga pa'i shar du d+hi las yum chen mo ser
NK024(ya)001:12953: mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis mnyam gzhag
NK024(ya)001:12954: /'og ma gnyis rdo rje dang po ti longs sku
NK024(ya)001:12955: / dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i lhor h+aum las phyag rdor sngon po rdo rje dang pad+ma longs sku /
NK024(ya)001:12956: nub tu mam las sh+aa ri'i bu dge slong ser po 'khar gsil lhung bzed /
NK024(ya)001:12957: byang du tram las spyan ras gzigs dkar po pad+ma dang po ti longs sku /
NK024(ya)001:12958: gnyis ka'i lha snam shar du h+r+aihls sangs rgyas glang po dam pa'i dpal dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12959: lhor h+r+aihls rin chen 'byung ldan ser po rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:12960: nub tu h+r+aihls pad+ma dam pa'i dpal dmar po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12961: byang du h+r+aihls ting 'dzin rgyal po ljang gu rdo rje rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:12962: bzhi ga g.yon mnyam gzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:12963: shar lhor nya las rdo rje sems ma dkar mo rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12964: lho nub tu sa las rin chen sems ma ser mo rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:12965: nub byang du ra las chos kyi sems ma dmar mo pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12966: byang shar du mi las las kyi sems ma ljang
NK024(ya)001:12967: gu rgya gram g.yon mnyam gzhag longs sku'i tshul lo
NK024(ya)001:12969: 'dir yang yum dang thub pa gnas barjesa pas dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:12972: yang ling tshe dgu'i dbus su yum chen mo /
NK024(ya)001:12973: phyogs bzhir rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:12974: 'khor lo rtsibs bcur phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas re re la byang chub sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:12975: gru chad bzhi la sgeg sogs brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:12976: khyams la sems dpa' bcu drug /'dod snams bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:12977: sgo ma bzhi ste dgu bcu rtsa gcig go //'dir
NK024(ya)001:12978: thub pas gtso byas yang dkyil 'khor gnyis su 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:12979: ro //'di dag gi sku mdog phyag mtshan sngags rnams
NK024(ya)001:12980: gong 'og tu zhib tu bstan no //
NK024(ya)001:12982: 'di'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams dbang bskur tshig steng
NK024(ya)001:12983: nas len pa las mngon rtogs zur pa med phyir
NK024(ya)001:12986: brgyad pa gnyis nang ling tshe dgu'i phyir 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bcu pa /
NK024(ya)001:12987: rtsibs re re'i nang du 'dab bzhi dang phyir gru chad lha snam can gnyis kyi /
NK024(ya)001:12988: bdun pa'i dbus su yum chen ser mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i g.yas gnyis ral gri dang mchog sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:12989: g.yon gnyis ut+pala glegs bam 'dzin pa longs sku'i tshul lo //
NK024(ya)001:12990: brgyad pa'i dbus su thub dbang ser po sa gnon
NK024(ya)001:12991: mnyam gzhag gi steng na lhung bzed dang 'khar gsil
NK024(ya)001:12992: 'chang ba'o // dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i ling tshe dgu'i
NK024(ya)001:12993: shar du sangs rgyas glang po dam po'i dpal dkar
NK024(ya)001:12994: 'chang ba'o // po rdo rje / lhor rin 'byung ser po rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:12995: nub tu pad+ma dam pa'i dpal dmar po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:12996: byang du h+r+aihls ting 'dzin rgyal po ljang gu rgya gram g.yon mnyam gzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:12997: ling tshe'i shar lhor rdo rje sems ma dkar mo rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:12998: lho nub tu rin chen sems ma ser mo rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:12999: nub byang du chos kyi sems ma dmar mo pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13000: byang shar du las kyi sems ma ljang gu rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:13001: g.yon mnyam gzhag brgyad ka longs sku'o //
NK024(ya)001:13002: rtsibs bcu'i shar rtsibs dang po'i dbus su steng gi
NK024(ya)001:13003: sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal dkar po g.yas rgyal mtshan
NK024(ya)001:13004: / de'i phyogs bzhi'i shar du bzang skyong ser po gser gyi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13005: lhor dkon mchog 'byung gnas sngon po rin chen sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:13006: nub tu dpa' bar 'gro ba dmar po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13007: byang du zla 'od gzhon nu ljang gu zla tshes /
NK024(ya)001:13008: de yang shar nub gnyis sems dpa' dang /
NK024(ya)001:13009: lho byang nyan thos kyi tshul lo //
NK024(ya)001:13010: shar rtsibs gnyis par shar phyogs kyi sangs rgyas dkon
NK024(ya)001:13011: mchog 'byung gnas dkar po g.yas mchog sbyin dang 'khor
NK024(ya)001:13012: lo // g.yon skyabs sbyin mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:13013: shar du chos kyi rgyal mtshan dkar po chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan /
NK024(ya)001:13014: lhor dbang phyug rgyal po sngon po lcags kyu /
NK024(ya)001:13015: nub tu bkod pa'i rgyal mtshan dmar po me tog /
NK024(ya)001:13016: byang du rin chen 'od 'phro ljang gu rin chen 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13019: shar lho'i rtsibs dbus sangs rgyas pad+mo dam pa'i dpal dkar ser g.yas pa nyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:13021: de'i shar du kun bzang dkar po rin chen sdong bu /
NK024(ya)001:13023: nub tu sgrib sel dmar po po ti /
NK024(ya)001:13024: byang du byams pa ljang gu klu shing dang g+hun+d+he ste spyi blugs 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13027: lho rtsibs kyi dbus su sangs rgyas mya ngan med
NK024(ya)001:13028: dpal sngon po g.yas thugs kar skyabs sbyin gyis rin
NK024(ya)001:13029: po che / g.yon mnyam gzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:13030: de'i shar du snang ba'i mchog dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13031: lhor phyag rgya'i rgyal po ser po rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:13032: nub tu spos kyi glang po dmar po 'bud dung dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:13033: byang du spobs pa brtsegs ljang gu gser g.yu'i tog dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:13036: lho nub kyi rtsibs dbus su sangs rgyas snang ba dam pa'i dpal dmar ser nyi ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13037: de'i shar du mthu chen thob dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13038: lhor sman rgyal sngon po bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:13039: nub tu yon tan snying po dmar po rin chen snye ma /
NK024(ya)001:13040: byang du mthong na dga' ljang gu klu shing can /
NK024(ya)001:13043: nub rtsibs dang po'i dbus su nub phyogs kyi sangs
NK024(ya)001:13044: rgyas rin chen 'od 'phro dmar po g.yas thugs kar
NK024(ya)001:13045: skyabs sbyin gyis pad+ma bsnams shing /
NK024(ya)001:13046: g.yon mchog sbyin pus mor brkyang ba /
NK024(ya)001:13047: de'i shar du pad+ma'i rgyal po dkar po sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:13048: lhor pad+ma dam pa sngon po pad dkar /
NK024(ya)001:13049: nub tu rdo rje mi g.yo dmar po lcags kyu /
NK024(ya)001:13050: byang du thogs med rgyal po ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13053: nub rtsibs gnyis pa'i dbus su 'og gi sangs rgyas
NK024(ya)001:13054: pad+mo dam pa'i dpal sngo nag chos 'chad kyis pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:13055: bsnams pa / de'i shar du ye shes tog dkar po tog /
NK024(ya)001:13056: lhor mya ngan med 'joms sngon po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13057: nub tu blo gros mi zad pa dmar po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13058: byang du ye shes 'od ljang gu rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13061: nub byang gi rtsibs kyi dbus su sangs rgyas gdugs mdzes dam pa'i dpal dmar ljang gdugs bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13062: de'i shar du gzhon nu rgyal mtshan dkar po ut+pala /
NK024(ya)001:13063: lhor skyes bu dam pa sngon po dung rnga yab /
NK024(ya)001:13064: nub tu seng ge sgra dmar po ku mud /
NK024(ya)001:13065: byang du mya ngan med ljang gu pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13068: byang gi rtsibs kyi dbus su sangs rgyas rgyal ba'i
NK024(ya)001:13069: dbang po ljang gu g.yas skyabs sbyin gyis nyi ma
NK024(ya)001:13070: dang / g.yon mchog sbyin gyis rdo rje can /
NK024(ya)001:13071: de'i shar du rin 'byung dkar po rin chen zur brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:13072: lhor grub pa sngon po sna tshogs rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13073: nub tu dga' ba dmar mo me long /
NK024(ya)001:13074: byang du mi g.yo ba ljang gu mnyam gzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:13077: byang shar gyi rtsibs kyi dbus su sangs rgyas glang
NK024(ya)001:13078: po dam pa'i dpal ljang gu g.yas thugs kar glegs
NK024(ya)001:13079: bam / g.yon pa mchog sbyin gyis chos gos kyi d+r+wa ba bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13080: de'i shar du phyag rdor dkar po rdo rje rtse dgu pa /
NK024(ya)001:13081: lhor spyan ras gzigs sngon po pad dkar /
NK024(ya)001:13082: nub tu nam mkha'i snying po dmar po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13083: byang du sa snying ljang gu rin po che'i myu gu bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13086: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i shar lho'i gru chad kyi nang
NK024(ya)001:13087: du sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa dang
NK024(ya)001:13088: / de'i rgyab tu spos ma dud kha spos phor 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13089: lho nub kyi gru chad la phreng ba ma sngon mo me tog gi phreng ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13090: me tog ma dkar mo me tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13091: nub byang gi gru chad la glu ma dmar mo pi wang dang /
NK024(ya)001:13092: mar me dmar mo mar me 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13093: byang shar gyi gru chad la gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:13094: dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13095: lha snam gyi khyams la shar du byams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13107: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK024(ya)001:13110: kun tu bzang po rnams phyogs kyi rang mdog can phyag mtshan sna tshogs 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13111: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo //
NK024(ya)001:13112: lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo //
NK024(ya)001:13113: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo //
NK024(ya)001:13114: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu /
NK024(ya)001:13115: 'dod snam la bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad ni
NK024(ya)001:13116: shar du lha mo dkar mo gnyis dpal be'u dang
NK024(ya)001:13117: 'khor lo / lhor ser mo gnyis pad+ma dang rgyal mtshan /
NK024(ya)001:13118: nub tu dmar mo gnyis gdugs dang bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:13119: byang du ljang gu gnyis dung dang nya 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13120: dkyil 'khor dgu pa 'dab brgyad rtsibs drug can gyi
NK024(ya)001:13121: dbus 'dab ma brgyad kyi lte bar thub pa'i ngo
NK024(ya)001:13122: bo dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sngon po sa gnon
NK024(ya)001:13123: mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13124: shar du dga' ba'i spyan dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13125: lhor yongs su dgongs pa'i rgyal po sngo ser mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13126: nub tu gser gyi 'od zer dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi rgyal po'i phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13127: byang du ting 'dzin glang po ljang gu mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13128: shar lhor zhi ba dbang po sngo skya byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13129: lho nub tu me long 'od dkar ljang gu skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13130: nub byang du yid 'ong dbyangs dmar ljang ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13131: byang shar du me long 'od dkar ljang skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13132: de'i phyi 'khor lo rtsibs drug gi rtsibs re re'i
NK024(ya)001:13133: nang du pad+ma 'dab brgyad pa re re'i byang shar
NK024(ya)001:13134: gyi rtsibs kyi dbus su thub pa chen po ser
NK024(ya)001:13135: po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:13136: de'i shar du yum chen mo ser mo zhal gcig
NK024(ya)001:13137: phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis mnyam gzhag /'og ma gnyis
NK024(ya)001:13139: shar lhor lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin sngon po go mtshon can /
NK024(ya)001:13140: lhor rnam par snang mdzad ser po mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:13141: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa snang byed dmar nag sgrom bu can /
NK024(ya)001:13142: nub tu sh+aa ri'i bu dge slong ser po bseg par can /
NK024(ya)001:13143: nub byang du byol song thub pa rnam gnon ser nag po ti can /
NK024(ya)001:13144: byang du lha min thub pa rnam rgyal mthing kha pad+ma can /
NK024(ya)001:13145: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa rab rgyal dud kha me chu bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13146: shar lho'i rtsibs kyi dbus su rnam snang dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13147: shar du zla 'od dpal dkar po sa gnon can /
NK024(ya)001:13148: lhor nyi ma'i snying po ser po mchog sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:13149: nub tu spos kyi dpal dmar po ting nge 'dzin can /
NK024(ya)001:13150: byang du sngon 'phro'i rgyal po ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13151: shar lhor rin chen rgyal dkar ser sa gnon can /
NK024(ya)001:13152: lho nub tu 'od zer dpal ser skya mchog sbyin /
NK024(ya)001:13153: nub byang du dka' thub rgyal dmar skya ting nge 'dzin can /
NK024(ya)001:13154: byang shar du gtsug tor snying po dkar ljang skyabs sbyin can no //
NK024(ya)001:13155: lho'i rtsibs kyi dbus su rin 'byung ser po mchog sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13156: shar du gser 'od 'phro dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13157: lhor bkod pa'i rgyal po ser po sa gnon can /
NK024(ya)001:13158: nub tu gser gyi gzugs dmar po ting nge 'dzin can /
NK024(ya)001:13159: byang du dpal gyi rgyal po sngon po skyabs sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13160: shar lhor snang ba brtsegs dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:13161: lho nub tu mya ngan med pa dmar ser sa gnon can /
NK024(ya)001:13162: nub byang du dga' ba'i dpal dmar ljang mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:13163: byang shar du gzi brjid dpal dkar ljang skyabs sbyin can no //
NK024(ya)001:13164: lho nub kyi rtsibs kyi dbus su sh+aakya seng ge ljang gu po ti thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13165: shar du dri med sgra dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13166: lhor dkon mchog sprin sngon po mchog sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13167: nub tu yon tan 'byung dmar po mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:13168: byang du seng ge sgra ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13169: shar lhor mdzes pa'i tog dkar ser byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13170: lho nub tu gzi brjid rgyal dmar ser mchog sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13171: nub byang du tsan+dana dpal dmar ljang mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:13172: byang shar du snying rje'i rgyal dkar ljang skyabs sbyin no //
NK024(ya)001:13173: nub byang gi rtsibs kyi dbus su snang ba mtha'
NK024(ya)001:13174: yas dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can
NK024(ya)001:13175: / shar du nges par gshegs dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13176: lhor nges par gsungs sngon po mchog sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13177: nub tu brdal ba che dmar po sa gnon /
NK024(ya)001:13178: byang du me tog dbyangs ldan ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13179: shar lhor grags pa'i dpal dmar skya byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13180: lho nub tu sprul pa'i rgyal dmar po chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:13181: nub byang du sgra dbyangs mi zad pa dmar po sa gnon can /
NK024(ya)001:13182: byang shar du sman gyi rgyal po dkar ljang skyabs sbyin mdzad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13183: byang gi rtsibs kyi dbus su bcom ldan 'das don yod grub pa ljang gu skyabs sbyin can /
NK024(ya)001:13184: shar du dge ba'i bshes gnyen dkar po byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13185: lhor ngan song sbyong ba sngon po chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:13186: nub tu kun gyi slob dpon dmar po mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13187: byang du rnam par rgyal ba ljang gu sa gnon /
NK024(ya)001:13188: shar lhor me tog bkod pa'i rgyal po ljang sngon byang chub mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13189: lho nub tu thams cad snang ljang ser chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:13190: nub byang du tsan+dana dri dmar ljang mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13191: byang shar du seng ge 'bum gzugs ljang skya sa gnon /
NK024(ya)001:13192: grwa bzhi'i nang du sgeg mo dkar mo rab tu snyem pa /
NK024(ya)001:13193: phreng ba ma ser mo phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13194: glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dren pa /
NK024(ya)001:13195: gar ma ljang gu gar byed pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13196: phyir bdug pa sngon mo spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13197: me tog ma ser mo me tog gi za ma tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13198: mar me ma dmar mo mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13199: dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13200: lha snam la shar du byams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13212: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK024(ya)001:13216: shar sgor lcags kyu ma dkar mo lcags kyu /
NK024(ya)001:13217: lho sgor zhags pa ma ser mo //
NK024(ya)001:13218: nub sgor lcags sgrog ma dmar mo //
NK024(ya)001:13219: byang sgor dril bu ma ljang gu'o //'dod snam la
NK024(ya)001:13220: shar du dpal be'u 'khor lo 'dzin pa'i lha mo
NK024(ya)001:13221: gnyis dkar / lhor pad+ma rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis ser /
NK024(ya)001:13222: nub tu gdugs dang bum pa 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis dmar /
NK024(ya)001:13223: byang du dung dang nya 'dzin pa'i lha mo gnyis ljang gu ste lha tshogs dgu bcu rtsa dagu'o //
NK024(ya)001:13224: yang dkyil 'khor bcu pa nang 'dab brgyad dang de'i
NK024(ya)001:13225: phyir 'dab ma bcu pa'i dbus su rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:13226: khri seng ge brgyad kyis bteg pa'i steng du nyi
NK024(ya)001:13227: zla pad+ma'i gdan cha gnyis kha sprod la /
NK024(ya)001:13228: dbus su d+hi pra las yum chen mo ser mo zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po mnyam gzhag dang /
NK024(ya)001:13229: 'og ma gnyis rdo rje dang glegs bam 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13230: de'i mdun zhal sprod du mam las thub pa chen po ser po sa gnon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13231: phyogs bzhir h+r+aihls glang po dam pa'i dpal rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13232: rin chen 'byung gnas ser po rin po che /
NK024(ya)001:13234: ting 'dzin rgyal po ljang gu rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:13235: bzhi ga'ang g.yon mnyam gzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:13236: shar lhor nya las rdo rje sems ma dkar mo chos 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:13237: lho nub tu sa las rin chen sems ma ser mo rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13238: nub byang du ra las chos kyi sems ma dmar mo pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13239: byang shar du mi las las kyi sems ma ljang gu rgya gram bsnams pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13240: de'i phyir shar gyi pad+ma gnyis pa'i dbus su di
NK024(ya)001:13241: las mya ngan med pa'i dpal dkar po 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:13242: // de'i shar du a las byang chub sems dpa'
NK024(ya)001:13243: chos kyi rgyal mtshan dkar po chu srin rgyal mtshan
NK024(ya)001:13244: // bsnams pa / lhor tri las dbang phyug rgyal po sngon po lcags kyu /
NK024(ya)001:13245: nub tu h+r+aihls bkod pa'i rgyal po dmar po me tog /
NK024(ya)001:13246: byang du tram las rin chen 'od 'phro ljang gu rin po che 'bar ba bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13248: lho byang nyan thos kun la 'agre'o //
NK024(ya)001:13249: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13250: lho'i pad+ma'i dbus su di las rin chen dpal sngo skya rin chen thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13251: shar du a las snang ba'i mchog dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13252: lhor h+aum las phyag rgya'i rgyal po ser po rdo rje rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:13253: nub tu tram las spos kyi glang po dmar po 'bud dung /
NK024(ya)001:13254: byang du du las spobs pa brtsegs ljang gu rin po che'i za ma tog /
NK024(ya)001:13255: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi dkar ser dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13256: nub kyi pad+ma'i dbus su di las gdugs dam pa'i dpal dmar po thugs kar pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13257: shar du h+r+aih las pad+ma'i rgyal po dkar po pad+ma'i sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:13258: lhor sa las pad+ma sems dpa' sngon po pad+ma kha 'byed pa /
NK024(ya)001:13259: nub tu h+aum las mi g.yo ba dmar po lcags kyu /
NK024(ya)001:13260: byang du a las thogs med rgyal po ljang gu ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13261: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13262: byang gi pad+ma'i dbus su di las dbang du gyur pa ljang gu nyi ma thugs kar /
NK024(ya)001:13263: shar du tram las rin chen dbang phyug dkar po rin chen zur brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:13264: lhor tram las grub pa'i dpal sngon po rdo rje rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:13265: nub tu las dga' ba ston pa dmar po me long /
NK024(ya)001:13266: byang du am las mi bskyod pa ljang gu mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13267: mtshams su yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13268: byang shar pad+ma'i dbus su di las sh+aakya seng ge ljang gu po ti thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13269: shar du ba las phyag na rdo rje dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13270: lhor h+aum las spyan ras gzigs sngon po pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:13271: nub tu tram las nam mkha'i snying po dmar po rin chen za ma tog /
NK024(ya)001:13272: byang du sa'i snying po ljang gu rin chen myu gu /
NK024(ya)001:13273: mtshams su yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13274: shar lho pad+ma'i dbus su di las chog pa'i 'od
NK024(ya)001:13275: dam pad+mo dam pa'i dpal dkar ser pad+ma bsnams pa
NK024(ya)001:13276: / shar du tram las kun tu bzang po dkar po rin chen sdong bu /
NK024(ya)001:13277: lhor las 'jam dpal gzhon nu sngon po ut+pala /
NK024(ya)001:13278: nub tu a las sgrib pa rnam sel dmar po po ti bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13279: byang du me las byams pa ljang gu g+hun+d+he'am spyi blugs 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13280: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13281: lho nub tu pad+ma dbus su di las rnam par
NK024(ya)001:13282: grol ba'i pad+mo dmar ser nyi ma thugs kar bsnams
NK024(ya)001:13283: pa / shar du pa las mthu chen thob dkar po rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:13284: lhor ham las pad+ma rgyal sngon po sman gyi bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:13285: nub tu tram las yon tan snying po dmar po rin chen nyi ma /
NK024(ya)001:13286: byang du a las mthong na dga' ba ljang gu klu shing lo ma /
NK024(ya)001:13287: mtshams su yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13288: nub byang du pad+ma'i dbus su di las bdud rtsi rgyal ba dmar ljang g.yas gdugs kyis 'gebs pa /
NK024(ya)001:13289: shar du a las gzhon nu rgyan dkar po ut+pala /
NK024(ya)001:13290: lhor h+aum las skyes bu dam pa sngon po 'bud dung /
NK024(ya)001:13291: nub tu h+r+aihls seng ge sgra dmar po ku mu da /
NK024(ya)001:13292: byang du h+aum las mya ngan gsal ljang gu spyan gsal bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13293: mtshams bzhir yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13294: shar gyi pad+ma dang po steng gi pad+ma'i dod kyi
NK024(ya)001:13295: dbus su di las dga' ba'i dpal dkar po rgyal
NK024(ya)001:13296: mtshan / shar du h+aum las bzang skyong dkar po bum pa /
NK024(ya)001:13297: lhor tram las dkon mchog 'byung gnas sngon po rin chen sgrom bu /
NK024(ya)001:13298: nub tu h+r+aih las dpa' bar 'gro ba dmar po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13299: byang du a las zla 'od gzhon nu ljang gu zla tshes /
NK024(ya)001:13300: mtshams su yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13301: nub kyi pad+ma gnyis pa 'og gi pad+ma'i dod kyi
NK024(ya)001:13302: dbus su di las pad+ma dam pa'i dpal sngon po
NK024(ya)001:13303: pad+ma chos 'chad / shar du tram las ye shes tog dkar po tog bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13304: lhor a las mya ngan kun sel sngon po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13305: nub tu ha las blo gros mi zad pa dmar po po ti /
NK024(ya)001:13306: byang du a las ye shes 'od zer ljang gu rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:13307: mtshams su yum bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK024(ya)001:13308: grwa bzhi'i nang gi shar lhor sgeg mo dkar mo me long /
NK024(ya)001:13309: lho nub tu phreng ba ma ser mo me tog gi phreng ba /
NK024(ya)001:13310: nub byang du glu ma dmar mo pi wang /
NK024(ya)001:13311: byang shar du gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur ba /
NK024(ya)001:13312: shar lho'i grwa'i phyir bdug spos ma dud kha spos khang /
NK024(ya)001:13313: lho nub tu me tog ma dkar mo me tog /
NK024(ya)001:13314: nub byang du mar me ma dmar mo mar me /
NK024(ya)001:13315: byang shar du dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:13316: lha snam la shar du brgya byin ser po rdo rje 'dzin pa glang po che la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13317: shar lhor me lha dmar po bgrang phreng 'dzin pa ra skyes la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13318: lhor gshin rje sngon po dbyug to bsnams pa ma he la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13319: lho nub tu srin po smug nag ral gri 'dzin pa ro langs la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13320: nub tu chu lha dkar po sprul zhags bsnams pa chu srin la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13321: nub byang du rlung lha ljang gu ba dan 'phyar ba sha ba la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13322: byang du nor bdag ljang gu dbyug to 'dzin pa rta la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13323: byang shar du dbang ldan dkar po rtse gsum 'dzin pa khyu mchog la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13324: shar stod du tshangs pa gdong bzhi pa dkar po me tog 'dzin pa ngang pa la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13325: nub smad du sa'i lha mo ser mo bum pa 'dzin pa phag la zhon pa /
NK024(ya)001:13326: shar sgor yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wang /
NK024(ya)001:13327: lho sgor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri /
NK024(ya)001:13328: nub sgor spyan mi bzang dmar po mchod rten dang sbrul zhags /
NK024(ya)001:13329: byang sgor rnam thos sras ser po rgyal mtshan dang ne'u le 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13330: dkyil 'khor bcu po'i sangs rgyas sprul sku rnams mtshan dpes spras pa /
NK024(ya)001:13331: longs sku sems dpa' dang sems ma rnams dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:13332: sems dpa' rab tu byung ba rnams dge slong gi cha lugs dang ldan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:13333: gtso 'khor de rnams kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:13335: thugs kar h+aum sngon pos mtshan pa de las 'od zer 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:13336: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rab 'byams rgya mtsho nas rgyal
NK024(ya)001:13337: ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad badz+ra sa ma
NK024(ya)001:13338: ya dzahdzah rtsa ba'i sa bcad bzhi par rab gnas
NK024(ya)001:13339: gong du song / lnga pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:13341: lnga pa cho ga gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13343: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK024(ya)001:13344: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK024(ya)001:13345: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK024(ya)001:13347: thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13349: de nas spos dang rdo rje dril bu sogs rol mo dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:13351: chos nyid dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med kyang //
NK024(ya)001:13352: gzhi dang lam dang rnam pa thams cad mkhyen //
NK024(ya)001:13353: bdag med stong pa don dam yang dag mtha'//
NK024(ya)001:13354: yum chen pha rol phyin ma gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13355: bcom ldan bskal pa grangs med du ma ru //'gro la brtse phyir thugs rje rnam sbyangs nas //
NK024(ya)001:13356: khyed bzhed 'gro don mdzad pa 'di lags kyis //
NK024(ya)001:13357: ston pa 'khor dang bcas nas gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13358: shar phyogs rin chen yod pa'i zhing khams nas //
NK024(ya)001:13359: bde gshegs rin chen 'byung ldan 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:13360: lho phyogs mya ngan med pa'i bde gshegs mya ngan
NK024(ya)001:13361: med pa nub phyogs bde dang ldan pa'i bde gshegs
NK024(ya)001:13362: rin chen 'od 'phro byang phyogs rgyal ba can gyi
NK024(ya)001:13363: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po shar lho snying po
NK024(ya)001:13364: byang chub bde gshegs pad+mo dpal mnga' lho nub rdul
NK024(ya)001:13365: tshogs bral ba'i bde gshegs nyi ma snang ba nub
NK024(ya)001:13366: byang dbang du gyur pa'i bde gshegs gdugs mchog dam
NK024(ya)001:13367: pa byang shar ting 'dzin brgyan pa'i ting 'dzin glang
NK024(ya)001:13368: po dpal mnga' 'og phyogs pad+ma can gyi bde gshegs
NK024(ya)001:13369: pad+ma dpal nyid steng phyogs 'jig rten mdangs dag'i zhing
NK024(ya)001:13370: khams nas // bde gshegs dga' ba dpal gyi 'khor bcas gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:13371: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:13372: zhes pas spyan drangs la gdan 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13373: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje'i ngang //
NK024(ya)001:13374: nyon mongs mi spong gos pa med //
NK024(ya)001:13375: ma chags rang bzhin dag pas na //
NK024(ya)001:13376: mnyam nyid ngang du bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13377: pho brang gzhal yas dam pa 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:13378: thugs rjes dgongs pa'i phrin las rnams //'gro don rdzogs mdzad de bzhin du //
NK024(ya)001:13379: yun ring brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13380: pad+ma a sa ni tish+tha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:13382: smra bsam brjod med ces pa nas //
NK024(ya)001:13385: rnam dag sku mnga' zhes pa'i sh+lo ka dang /
NK024(ya)001:13386: zhing bcur sku khyab zab yangs gsung sgra can //
NK024(ya)001:13387: ji lta ji snyed thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs //
NK024(ya)001:13388: dus kun rnam bzhi phrin las lhun grub pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:13389: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:13390: gdul bya'i zhing du 'gro don rdzogs mdzad phyir //
NK024(ya)001:13391: mi bsnyel thugs rjes 'khor ba mthar la gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:13392: thabs mkhas thugs rjes 'gro don lhur mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:13393: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:13394: chos dbyings ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK024(ya)001:13395: bde gshegs mchod sprin skur sprul pa //
NK024(ya)001:13396: lha mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:13397: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung mdzad cing //
