NK024(ya)001:13398: so so'i bgegs rnams 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:13399: phyogs skyong rgya chen phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:13403: rol mo'i bye brag du ma dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:13404: bla med dkon mchog gsum po dang //
NK024(ya)001:13405: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:13406: yid 'ong mchod sprin thams cad dang //
NK024(ya)001:13407: rol mo sil snyan 'phan gdugs dang //
NK024(ya)001:13408: bla bre rgyal mtshan lhab lhub dang //
NK024(ya)001:13409: me tog phreng ba bdug pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:13410: mar me dri chab zhal zas sogs //
NK024(ya)001:13411: mchod sprin sna tshogs phyoogs bcur 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:13412: sna tshogs rig pa'i bden pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:13413: dngos 'byor yid kyis sprul pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:13414: sangs rgyas zhing khams rab 'byams su //
NK024(ya)001:13415: bla med mchod pa'i sprin 'byung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:13416: yon tan dpag med thams cad kyi //
NK024(ya)001:13417: zhabs la spyi bos gtug gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:13419: 'jig rten 'di dag 'jig rten gzhan dag na //
NK024(ya)001:13420: mchod par 'os pa'i gzugs sgra dri dag dang //
NK024(ya)001:13421: ro dang reg bya thugs dang mi 'gal ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:13422: gtsang dang ma nyams sman gyi mchog gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:13423: chu gtsang bsil dang me tog khyad par can //
NK024(ya)001:13424: dbyibs legs dri zhim kha dog sna tshogs 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:13425: tsan+dana ga bur gur gum sbyar ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:13426: so sor bsres pa'i gtor ma ji snyed pa //
NK024(ya)001:13427: nyi zla ltar gsal rin chen 'bar ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:13428: sgron ma rab gsal mar me mdzes pa'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:13429: gla rtsi hu lu ka sogs legs sbyar dri //
NK024(ya)001:13430: sku mdzes don du byi dor byug pa'i rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:13431: sman dang bcud dang shing 'bras dam pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:13432: yul rigs 'tsho ba rnams kyang legs par 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:13433: sgra snyan dbyangs dang sil snyan rol mor bcas //
NK024(ya)001:13434: rin chen bdun dang rin chen gzhan rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:13435: bkra shis rdzas brgyad gzhan yang bkra shis rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:13436: bdag gi lus ngag yid bcas khyed la 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:13437: rgyal ba sras bcas thugs rjes brtser dgongs la //'gro rnams bde bar bya phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13439: gzhan yang mchod bstod kyi rigs gzhan nas 'byung ba
NK024(ya)001:13440: bzhin rgyas par byas la gong bzhin cha gsum yang
NK024(ya)001:13441: btang ngo // mdun bskyed la dmigs pa'i bzlas pa cung zad bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13443: de dag gi snying po rim bzhin dkyil 'khor dang po dang /
NK024(ya)001:13444: gnyis pa'i lha sngags ni mu ne dang /
NK024(ya)001:13445: di pra ba ye ya di pra dung pra ni
NK024(ya)001:13446: bi shud+d+he b+h+ya d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu b+ha ga wan dzahh+aum
NK024(ya)001:13447: bam hoh a la la hoh a mri a ra
NK024(ya)001:13448: hi dza h+aum / badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:13449: na mah sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam /
NK024(ya)001:13450: b+ha ga wan pra sa ta th+aa ga t+ya b+hi sha ya swa b+h+aa wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13451: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te ka ru nam m+aa ra ya badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13455: di pradz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa h+aum d+harma d+h+aa tu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13456: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu pu ra ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13457: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13458: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na tri thi sa ga pa ri bi sa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13459: sarba ta th+aa ga ta su d+ya bi la ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13460: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13461: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13464: drug pa de dag gi sngags kyang rim pa bzhin du gtso bo lha gong dang 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:13465: k+sh+au ban a tse nan sarba bud+d+ha nam mrga bi sha ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13466: omo rat+na bi lo ka ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13467: pad+ma bi shwa d+ha ni shud+d+he siti nam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13468: pa ti pa ma ti pra sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13469: badz+ra sa s+t+wa dzi ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13470: rat+na dzi rat+na ba ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13471: pad+ma dzi pad+ma hi sho d+ha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13472: karma dzi karma hri she de s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13476: bcu pa gsum gyi gtso bo yab yum gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:13479: 'khor sems dpa' bzhi bcu'i sngags rim pa bzhin du /
NK024(ya)001:13480: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam d+har+m+aa ke tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13481: ke tu shwa r+aa dza s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13482: pad+ma pa la pad+ma da ra s+w+aa rat+na b+ha tra
NK024(ya)001:13483: ta rat+na a tsi ya ra na a tra a
NK024(ya)001:13484: lo ka tsa ra mu tsa bra ba ta pra
NK024(ya)001:13485: ti r+aa dza no pra ti ban kun ti d+har+m+aa
NK024(ya)001:13486: hri to ya ba ti ka m+aa la tsa pad+ma
NK024(ya)001:13487: da ra badz+ra a k+sho b+h+yo a mo ga r+aa
NK024(ya)001:13488: dza da ra rat+na sha ra da ra karma si
NK024(ya)001:13489: ti da ra ru ti a dar+sha da ra a
NK024(ya)001:13490: k+sho sa ma ya da ra badz+ra tsan+da ro sha
NK024(ya)001:13491: ni a ba lo ki te shwa ra ya a
NK024(ya)001:13492: kar+sha gar+b+he k+shi ti garba rat+na da ra sa man+ta
NK024(ya)001:13493: rat+na da ra many+dzu sh+r+ai ku m+aa ra mum sa
NK024(ya)001:13494: na sarba bi shwa d+ha ni mee tri ma h+aa
NK024(ya)001:13495: ma ti bi mu ge mrga la da ra ka
NK024(ya)001:13496: ru na b+ha dra da ra gu na hri to
NK024(ya)001:13497: ya ba rat+na a ma ki ti sa na da
NK024(ya)001:13498: ku m+aa ra da ra bu ling a tsan na
NK024(ya)001:13499: sing ha hri shang ka badz+ra tsak+shu da ra sa
NK024(ya)001:13500: la pra ba le rat+na swa b+h+aa wa da ra
NK024(ya)001:13501: shum ram ga me sa ti tsan dra pra b+ha
NK024(ya)001:13502: ku m+aa ra dz+ny+aa na ke tu pra ti sarba
NK024(ya)001:13503: sho ga na ga ti ma ti phu ba ri
NK024(ya)001:13504: dz+ny+aa na pra ba b+ha ta da ra s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:13511: thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa'i mdo dang /
NK024(ya)001:13513: dpang skong phyag brgya pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13514: sman gyi bla'i mdo chog dang /
NK024(ya)001:13515: gnas brtan bcu drug gi gsol 'debs la sogs pa
NK024(ya)001:13516: pad+ma stong ldan gyi lha tshogs la tshogs gsog pa
NK024(ya)001:13517: dang sgrib pa gnyis sbyang ba'i cho ga thams cad
NK024(ya)001:13521: 'phags pa thar pa chen po phyogs su rgyas pa 'gyod tshangs kyi sdig sbyangs te /
NK024(ya)001:13522: sangs rgyas su bsgrub pa rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
NK024(ya)001:13523: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:13524: zhes sogs bklag /'don par mi nus na 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:13525: slob ma 'dus ma thag tu 'ur 'don du bklag
NK024(ya)001:13526: go // de bzhin du dpang skong phyag rgya pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13528: gnas brtan phyag mchod kyang spro na nyan rang gi
NK024(ya)001:13529: skabs bzhin bya'o //'og nas 'byung ba ltar bdag 'jug
NK024(ya)001:13530: kyang blang ngo // de nas slob ma rnams 'dus te /
NK024(ya)001:13532: bum par lha bskyed bzlas pa byas te dpon slob kun khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:13533: zhes gsungs pas bum bzlas gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:13534: khrus ni las bum mam khyad par rnam bum gyi chus bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:13535: khrus dang bgegs gtor btang ba rnams gong dang 'dra zhing /
NK024(ya)001:13536: bgegs skrod kyi bden brdar la khyad par du phyogs
NK024(ya)001:13537: bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang slob mar bcas pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:13541: rgyal ba sras bcas dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:13543: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu grub rjes /
NK024(ya)001:13544: sems can thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya /
NK024(ya)001:13545: de'i ched du theg pa chen po byang chub sems
NK024(ya)001:13546: dpa'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas sdom pa blangs la
NK024(ya)001:13547: dbang bskur dang smin grol gyi gdams pa rnams tshul
NK024(ya)001:13548: bzhin nyams su blangs sems can gyi don bagyi'o snyam
NK024(ya)001:13549: pa byang chub kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed pa gsal
NK024(ya)001:13551: gnas bya'i chos ni 'dir theg chen byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa sgor 'jug pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:13552: 'di ni gzhan lam rmad du byung zhing khyad par du ches 'phags pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:13554: yon tan shin tu rgya chen byang chub shing bskyed phyir //
NK024(ya)001:13555: bde dang sdug bsngal chen po zhi ba thob bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:13556: bdag dang gzhan la phan bde'i byed pa 'bras bu'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:13557: rigs mchog de ni rtsa ba bzang po lta bu yin //
NK024(ya)001:13559: de yang dal 'byor gyi mi lus 'di la brten
NK024(ya)001:13560: nas bsgrub dgos pas 'di nyid thar pa'i lam brten
NK024(ya)001:13561: bla na med pa'i yin te /
NK024(ya)001:13563: bde gshegs lam bsten 'gro ba 'dren par chas gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:13564: sems kyi stobs chen mi yi rnyed pa gang yin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:13565: lam de lha dang klu yis mi rnyed lha min dang //
NK024(ya)001:13566: mkha' lding rigs 'dzin mi'am ci dang lto 'phyes min //
NK024(ya)001:13567: mi yis dngos po shin tu rnyed dka' rnyed gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:13568: don du brnag pa gang yin de ni bstun te bsgrubs //
NK024(ya)001:13571: gser 'gyur rtsi yi rnam pa mchog lta bur //
NK024(ya)001:13572: mi gtsang lus 'di blangs nas rgyal ba'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:13573: rin chen rin thang med par bsgyur bas na //
NK024(ya)001:13574: byang chub sems zhes bya ba rab brtan bzung //
NK024(ya)001:13576: mi yi gru la brten nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:13577: sdug bsngal chu bo che las sgrol //
NK024(ya)001:13578: gru 'di phyis nas rnyed dka' bas //
NK024(ya)001:13579: rmongs pa dus su gnyid ma log /
NK024(ya)001:13580: ces gsungs pa ltar brtson 'grus bskyed dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:13581: de ltar brtson 'grus bskyed dgos tshul yang bshes spring las /
NK024(ya)001:13582: mago'am gos la glo bur me shor na /
NK024(ya)001:13583: de las phyir zlog bgyi ba btang nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:13584: yang srid med par bgyi slad 'bad 'tshal te //
NK024(ya)001:13585: de bas ches mchog dgos pa gzhan ma mchis //
NK024(ya)001:13586: zhes gsungs pa bzhin bya dgos la /
NK024(ya)001:13587: de yang thog mar yongs 'dzin dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK024(ya)001:13588: zhig las byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yang dag
NK024(ya)001:13589: par blangs te theg pa chen po'i lam la legs
NK024(ya)001:13590: par bslab dgos pa yin pas 'dir byang chub sems
NK024(ya)001:13591: dpa'i dkyil 'khor du sems bskyed blang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13593: grol byed kyi gdams pa ster ba sogs skabs su babs pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:13594: de yang spyir sdom pa skye ba'i rten gang zag
NK024(ya)001:13595: gi khyad par las dbu sems gang rung gi cho
NK024(ya)001:13596: ga la brten nas len dgos kyang /
NK024(ya)001:13597: 'dir dbu ma lugs kho na 'brel chags shing khams
NK024(ya)001:13598: lugs su dbu sems gnyis ka'i sdom pa 'bogs chog
NK024(ya)001:13599: 'dug pa rnam pa gcig tu nyan rang gi lam
NK024(ya)001:13600: sngon du grub zin la dgongs pa yin 'dra yang
NK024(ya)001:13601: / zur lugs su gnyis ka mi mdzad cing /
NK024(ya)001:13602: khyad par 'dir dbang dang sprel dgos pas thog mar
NK024(ya)001:13603: dkyil 'khor bri ba nas bdag 'jug gi bar du
NK024(ya)001:13604: rtsa ba'i sa bcad dang po nas /
NK024(ya)001:13605: brgyad pa'i bar du legs par grub pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:13607: dgu pa sdom rten ni gzhan don du tshogs rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:13608: sgrib pa sbyang pa'i phyag rten bzang po 'bul lo
NK024(ya)001:13609: // zhes 'byung ba sbyir gsang sngags lugs la byin
NK024(ya)001:13610: rlabs 'jug pa'i sgo yin pas dbang gi yon sogs
NK024(ya)001:13611: 'byor stobs dang bstun pa'am med kyang bstsal te bya
NK024(ya)001:13612: // dgos shing / khyad par thugs bskyed kyi skabs
NK024(ya)001:13613: 'dir dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang slob
NK024(ya)001:13614: pa lam gyi gnas skabs su zang zing gi dngos
NK024(ya)001:13615: po ci 'byor re thugs bskyed kyi yon du dbul
NK024(ya)001:13616: bar mdzad pa'i tshul ni mdo sde bskal bzang sogs
NK024(ya)001:13618: bdag cag gi ston pas kyang de bzhin gshegs pa
NK024(ya)001:13619: sh+aakya thub pa chen po la kham sa'i bum pa
NK024(ya)001:13623: de bzhin gshegs pa khyed sku ci 'dra dang //'khor dang sku tshe'i tshad dang zhing khams sogs //
NK024(ya)001:13624: de bzhin mtshan mchog bzang po ci 'dra ba /
NK024(ya)001:13625: de 'dra kho nar bdag kyang 'gyur bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:13626: ces smon lam btab ste thugs bskyed pa lags pas /
NK024(ya)001:13627: 'dir bla ma la ci 'byor ba'i yon nges par 'bul dgos /
NK024(ya)001:13629: bla ma'i khri brtsig go zhes gsungs pa yang grub /
NK024(ya)001:13631: bla ma byang chub kyi sems dang ldan pas khri la 'dug ste ston pa sgom mo //
NK024(ya)001:13632: zhes gsungs ba gong du bdag bskyed song ba des khyab par 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:13633: khyad par chos thams cad stong nyid du shes pa'i shes rab dang /
NK024(ya)001:13634: 'gro rnams bde la 'god 'dod kyi brtse ba /
NK024(ya)001:13635: slob ma rnams la byang sems skye 'dod gsum dgos pa kho bo'i go skal yin no //
NK024(ya)001:13637: bcu gcig pa dkon mchog gi rten dang mchod pa
NK024(ya)001:13638: bshams la dge ba'i bshes gnyen la ston pa dngos
NK024(ya)001:13640: sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las bsgral te sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'god par bya /
NK024(ya)001:13641: de'i ched du byang chub sems mchog blang snyam pas
NK024(ya)001:13642: bla ma la phyag btsal te yon dang man+dala phul
NK024(ya)001:13643: te / zhes 'byung bas bla ma tha mal pa
NK024(ya)001:13644: ma yin par ston pa dngos kyi 'du shes bzhag
NK024(ya)001:13645: te / ste / de yang sems can thams cad pha mar ma gyur pa med /
NK024(ya)001:13646: pha ma byas res kyi drin can sha stag yin
NK024(ya)001:13647: pas 'di rnams 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho
NK024(ya)001:13648: chen po las bsgral bar bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:13650: nye du 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho'i khongs su chud gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:13651: klong gi nang du ltung ba lta bu snang bzhin du //
NK024(ya)001:13652: skye shi 'phos bo ngo ma shes pa de bor nas //
NK024(ya)001:13653: gal te gcig thar byed na de las khrel bor med //
NK024(ya)001:13655: sems can pha ma yin pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK024(ya)001:13657: re re'i bdag nyid rus pa'i phung po ni //
NK024(ya)001:13658: lhun po snyam pa snyed cig 'das gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:13659: ma yi thug mtha' rgya shug tshig gu tsam //
NK024(ya)001:13660: ril bur bgrangs kyang sa yis lang mi 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:13661: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes dgongs pas 'dir sems can
NK024(ya)001:13662: thams cad 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rgya mtsho chen
NK024(ya)001:13663: po las bsgral te sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'god
NK024(ya)001:13664: par bya / de'i phyir du byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa blang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13666: grol byed kyi gdams pa zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul nas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:13667: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu gcig pa'i nang gses bzhi pa gsol ba gdab pa yin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:13669: thal mo sbyar la 'di skad du zhes gsungs pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13670: kye rigs kyi bu bdag la dus gsum gyi de
NK024(ya)001:13671: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i
NK024(ya)001:13672: lam skyabs gsum sngon du 'gro ba can byang chub
NK024(ya)001:13673: kyi mchog tu sems bskyed pa stsal du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:13674: zhes lan gsum gsol gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:13675: slob dpon gyis nus pa ji lta ba bzhin du sbyin no //
NK024(ya)001:13677: sems bskyed blang bar bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13678: mnga' ris pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:13679: bskal bzang 'gro ba'i 'dren pa thub chen des //
NK024(ya)001:13680: bya rgod phung sogs theg chen rigs can la //
NK024(ya)001:13681: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod dpag yas gsungs //'jam dbyangs bka' bsdus klu sgrub sogs kyis bkral //
NK024(ya)001:13682: zhi ba lhas spel zab mo lta ba'i lugs //
NK024(ya)001:13683: byams pas bka' bsdus thogs med sku mched bkral //
NK024(ya)001:13684: jo bo rjes spel rgya chen spyod pa'i srol //
NK024(ya)001:13685: pad+ma'i ring lugs n+aa gardzu na mthun //
NK024(ya)001:13686: ngo bo byams dang snying rjes rgyud brlan cing //
NK024(ya)001:13687: gzhan gyi don du byang chub thob 'dod pas //
NK024(ya)001:13688: sgo gsum nyes pa spong ba'i sems dpa' 'o //
NK024(ya)001:13689: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir lugs gnyis kyi klu sgrub lugs dang snga 'gyur phyogs mthun par bzhed cing /
NK024(ya)001:13690: de la yang dbu sems kyi khyad par ni gong du mdo tsam smos pa ltar /
NK024(ya)001:13692: ji ltar 'bras kyi sa bon ni //
NK024(ya)001:13693: grang pa'i yul du mi skye ba //
NK024(ya)001:13694: de bzhin sems tsam pa yi yang //
NK024(ya)001:13695: sems bskyed sdig can la mi skye //
NK024(ya)001:13696: ji ltar nas kyi sa bon ni //
NK024(ya)001:13697: grang dro gang du'ang skye ba ltar //
NK024(ya)001:13698: de bzhin dbu ma'i sems bskyed kyang //
NK024(ya)001:13699: sdig pa yod med kun la skye //
NK024(ya)001:13703: des na sems tsam pa yi lugs //
NK024(ya)001:13704: gal te sems bskyed de 'dod na //
NK024(ya)001:13705: thog mar so so thar pa long //
NK024(ya)001:13706: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod slobs //
NK024(ya)001:13707: dad cing sgrub par nus gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:13708: phyis nas sems bskyed sdom pa long //
NK024(ya)001:13709: ci ste sems can thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:13711: cho ga 'khrul pa med pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:13712: dbu ma pa yi gzhung bzhin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:13714: phyi ma 'di don che zhing khyad par sngags kho na dang 'brel chags gshis /
NK024(ya)001:13718: bir+wa pa sogs rgya gar gyi grub chen phal cher 'di kho na bzhed par snang /
NK024(ya)001:13719: de ltar len tshul ni pan chen pad+ma dbang rgyal gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:13720: len tshul sdom gnas dge ba'i bshes gnyen la //
NK024(ya)001:13721: theg chen snod gyur dad ldan slob ma yi //
NK024(ya)001:13722: yan lag bdun mthar smon 'jug stabs gcig tu //
NK024(ya)001:13723: len nyid rang gzhan dga' ba bsgom pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:13724: zhes gsungs pa dang skabs 'di'i cho ga shin tu
NK024(ya)001:13725: mthun cing 'di la yang rgyas bshad mang mod kyi
NK024(ya)001:13727: de yi rtsa ba snying rjer 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:13729: sdug bsngal can gyi sems can mthong thos las snying rje drag po dang /
NK024(ya)001:13730: bla ma dkon mchog la dang ba'i dad pa /
NK024(ya)001:13731: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan thos pas thob 'dod kyi dad pa /
NK024(ya)001:13732: las 'bras la nges pa thob pa'i yid ches kyi dad pa ste dad pa rnam pa gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:13733: 'khor ba 'di sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du shes
NK024(ya)001:13734: shing de las thar 'dod kyi blo yang rang gcig
NK024(ya)001:13735: pu zhi bde don gnyer ma yin pas gzhan don
NK024(ya)001:13736: du sangs rgyas bgyid snyam pa sogs gsal gdab dgos
NK024(ya)001:13737: shing / de yang rtsol ba drag pos sgrub dgos tshul gong du bshad pa ltar yin /
NK024(ya)001:13739: gsar ma ba rten sgrub pa'i man+dala tshom bu lnga
NK024(ya)001:13740: pa bshams la thog mar dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i mdo
NK024(ya)001:13741: las gsungs pa'i ltung bshags sngon du btang rjes /
NK024(ya)001:13742: gdams ngag gi bshad pas gsal btab la /
NK024(ya)001:13743: man+dala tshom bu la brten pa'i dkon mchog rnams la phyag dang mchod phreng /
NK024(ya)001:13744: bshags pa sogs sngon du bya bar bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:13746: de nas yan lag bdun pa rgyas bsdus gang rung byas la zhes gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:13747: pan chen gyi sdom gsum du /
NK024(ya)001:13748: yan lag bdun mthar smon 'jug stabs gcig tu //
NK024(ya)001:13749: zhes gsungs pa yang 'di la dgongs pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:13750: de na tshom bu'i man+dala gyi dod du kho bos
NK024(ya)001:13751: sgrub mchod legs par bgyis zin pa'i dkyil 'khor bcu
NK024(ya)001:13752: po 'di rnams la dkon mchog rin po che rnam
NK024(ya)001:13753: gsum ma tshang ba med par mngon sum du bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:13755: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i zhing khams rab 'byams rgya mtsho
NK024(ya)001:13756: na rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa bzhug pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:13757: kyang yid kyis legs par gsal btab ste /
NK024(ya)001:13758: de rnams la thog mar lus ngag yid gsum gus pa'i phyag 'tshal ba ste yan lag dang po /
NK024(ya)001:13759: mchod pa la yang rnam grangs bsam gyi mi khyab kyang /
NK024(ya)001:13760: 'dir dang po dbyangs kyi yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgras bstod dbyangs kyis mchod pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13765: zhal zas la sogs pa'i nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:13778: dung la sogs pa'i rol mo'i khyad par dang /
NK024(ya)001:13784: nor bu'i bye brag sogs 'jig rten na srid do
NK024(ya)001:13785: cog gi dngos po bdag pos bzung ba dang ma
NK024(ya)001:13786: bzung ba'i tshogs ji snyed dang /
NK024(ya)001:13787: bdag gis bshags pa'i mchod pa'i tshogs 'di dag lhan
NK024(ya)001:13788: cig par kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa'i sprin phung
NK024(ya)001:13789: lta bur nam mkha'i khams thams cad phyur bur bkang
NK024(ya)001:13790: nas 'bul ba ste yan lag gnyis pa /
NK024(ya)001:13791: lus ngag yid gsum chags sdang rmongs pa'i dbang du
NK024(ya)001:13792: gyur te sdig pa mi dge ba'i las ci bsags
NK024(ya)001:13793: pa thams cad 'gro ba kun gyi sdig dang lhan
NK024(ya)001:13794: cig tu rten de rnams kyi drung du dug 'thungs
NK024(ya)001:13795: pa lta bu'i 'gyod sems kyis bshags shing phyin chad
NK024(ya)001:13796: srog la babs kyang mi bgyid snyam pa'i sdom sems
NK024(ya)001:13797: dang / de ltar bgyis pa la brten nas sor
NK024(ya)001:13798: chud de dag cing byang bar bya ba sogs stobs
NK024(ya)001:13799: bzhi tshang ba'i tshul gyis bshags pa ste yan lag
NK024(ya)001:13800: dang / gsum pa dang / phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba
NK024(ya)001:13801: sras bcas nyan rang so skye sogs kyi dus gsum
NK024(ya)001:13802: bsod nams kyi dngos po kun la rjes su yid
NK024(ya)001:13803: rang bar bya ba ste yan lag bzhi pa dang
NK024(ya)001:13804: dang / gsum pa dang / / rgyal ba gang
NK024(ya)001:13805: zhig chos kyi 'khor lo mi bskor bar thugs las
NK024(ya)001:13806: chung ngur bzhugs pa de dag la sems can gyi
NK024(ya)001:13807: don du chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar yang dag
NK024(ya)001:13808: par bskul ba ste yan lag lnga pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13809: gang zhig mya ngan las 'das ba'i tshul ston par
NK024(ya)001:13810: bzhed pa rnams la 'gro ba'i don du bskal pa
NK024(ya)001:13811: rgya mtshor bzhugs par gsol ba rtse gcig tu gdab
NK024(ya)001:13812: pa ste yan lag drug pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13813: de rnams kyi dge ba bla na med pa'i byang
NK024(ya)001:13814: chub tu bsngo bar bya ba ste yan lag bdun
NK024(ya)001:13815: pa rnam par dag pa zhig mdzad par zhu zhes
NK024(ya)001:13816: mtshams sbyar la / sdom rten gyi drung gi mchod
NK024(ya)001:13817: pa rnams las mar me spar zhig spos btul rol
NK024(ya)001:13818: mtshams sbyar la / mo bya zhing / bzang sbyod
NK024(ya)001:13819: nas 'byung ba bzhin yan lag bdun pa bya ste
NK024(ya)001:13820: mtshams sbyar la / mo bya zhing / / ji snyed su dag sogs brjod cing /
NK024(ya)001:13821: bde ba gshegs pa thams cad bdag gis bstod //
NK024(ya)001:13822: ces pa'i bar du phyag rgya /
NK024(ya)001:13824: me tog dam pa phreng ba dam pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:13826: rgyal ba kun la phyag 'tshal mchod par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:13827: zhes pa'i mjug tu rol chen bya /
NK024(ya)001:13828: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug dbang gis na //
NK024(ya)001:13829: zhes pa man chad slar bzhengs te phyag bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:13830: de ni gzhung gzhan las kyang sems bskyed kyi sngon du mthun rkyen tshogs bsag pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13831: 'gal rkyen sdig sgrib sbyang ba gnyis 'byung ba yang des khyab bo //
NK024(ya)001:13832: dngos gzhi la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13835: thal mo sbyar la 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13836: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:13837: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:13838: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung byang chub snying po la mchis kyi bar du /
NK024(ya)001:13840: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK024(ya)001:13841: zhi ba 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13842: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i dam chos rnams la tshogs rnams kyi mchog /
NK024(ya)001:13843: phyoogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK024(ya)001:13844: 'dun phyir mi ldog pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK024(ya)001:13846: gnyis pa sems bskyed pa la gnyis kyi smon 'jug stabs gcig tu len pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:13848: yang thal mo sbyar te 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13849: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:13850: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:13851: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK024(ya)001:13852: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:13853: 'das rnams dang / byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams kyis byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed de /
NK024(ya)001:13854: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK024(ya)001:13855: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon
NK024(ya)001:13856: par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas sems can ma bsgral
NK024(ya)001:13858: ma grol ba rnams grol ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13859: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13860: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs
NK024(ya)001:13861: su mya ngan las 'das pa'i sa la bkod pa
NK024(ya)001:13862: de bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas
NK024(ya)001:13863: kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste snying po byang chub
NK024(ya)001:13864: la mchis kyi bar du byang chub mchog tu sems
NK024(ya)001:13865: de bzhin du / bskyed de / sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13866: ma grol ba rnam grol ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13867: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13868: yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'das bar bagyi'o //
NK024(ya)001:13870: slob dpon gyi thabs yin no //
NK024(ya)001:13873: bcu gsum pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:13874: de'ang khyed rnams de ring nas byang chub sems dpar
NK024(ya)001:13875: gyur pas mi lus thob pa don can yin no
NK024(ya)001:13876: // zhes gsungs pa ni dga' ba bsgom pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:13877: de yang gnyis te rang dang gzhan las /
NK024(ya)001:13878: dang po rang dga' ba sgom pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13879: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK024(ya)001:13880: bdag gi gson pa'ang 'bras bur bcas //
NK024(ya)001:13881: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK024(ya)001:13882: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:13883: zhes lan gsum rjes zlos dang /
NK024(ya)001:13884: ji ltar gsungs pa de bzhin du dga' ba dang spro ba chen po mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13885: gnyis pa gzhan dga' ba bskyed du gzhug pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:13886: bdag gis de ltar sems bskyed pas bstan pa la
NK024(ya)001:13887: dga' ba'i lha klu thams cad dgyes pa bskyed par
NK024(ya)001:13888: mdzad du gsol snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos kyang lan
NK024(ya)001:13889: gsum mdzod / bdag gis de ring skyob pa thams cad kyi //
NK024(ya)001:13890: spyan sngar 'gro ba bde gshegs nyid dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:13891: bar du bde la mgron du bos zin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:13892: lha dang lha min la sogs dga' bar gyis //
NK024(ya)001:13894: de nas sems bskyed las mi 'da' bar dam bca' ba'i slad du 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13895: de yang bdag gis ci nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:13896: rigs dang mthun pa'i las brtsam ste //
NK024(ya)001:13897: skyon med btsun pa'i rigs 'di la //
NK024(ya)001:13898: rnyog par mi 'gyur de ltar bya //
NK024(ya)001:13901: bla ma la gus pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:13902: nag po'i chos bzhi spang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:13903: sems can blos mi btang ba la bslabs pas bsod nams dpag tu med /
NK024(ya)001:13904: dpal sbyin gyis zhus pa las /
NK024(ya)001:13905: byang chub sems kyi bsod nams gang //
NK024(ya)001:13906: gal te de la gzugs mchis na //
NK024(ya)001:13907: nam mkha'i khams ni kun bkang ste //
NK024(ya)001:13908: de bas kyang ni lhag bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:13910: de rnams kyi don rgyas par 'og tu rtsa ba'i
NK024(ya)001:13911: sa bcad bco lnga pa lam 'khyer bshad pa'i nang
NK024(ya)001:13912: gses kyi sa bcad bzhi pa bslab bya lam 'khyer
NK024(ya)001:13914: 'dir gzhung don bla ma la gus pa ni rtogs par sla /
NK024(ya)001:13915: nag po'i chos bzhi spang ba ni sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:13916: mchod 'os bslu dang 'gyod med 'gyod pa bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:13917: dam par skur 'debs 'gro la g.yo sgyu spyod //
NK024(ya)001:13918: ces bshad pa ltar spong zhing /
NK024(ya)001:13919: de las ldog pa bzhi dang du blang ba ni dkar po'i chos bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:13921: nag po'i chos bzhi spang zhing ldog pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:13922: dkar po'i chos bzhi yin pas kun tu spyad //
NK024(ya)001:13923: ces gsungs pa'i sems can blos mi gtong ba ni sems bskyed pa'i nying dgos mthar thug pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:13924: de la bsod nams 'byung tshul dpal sbyin gyis zhus pa'i mdo'i lung ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:13925: des sdom pa dang bslab bya dbog pa grub nas /
NK024(ya)001:13927: bcu bzhi pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13932: de bzhin gshegs pa bcu'i nga rgyal gyis slob ma rnams man+dala thal mo sbyar te zhes 'byung bas /
NK024(ya)001:13933: bla ma bdag bskyed kyi nga rgyal ldan bzhin pa la /
NK024(ya)001:13934: slar yang dbang gi don du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13935: gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:13936: slob dpon sangs rgyas dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13937: bden gnyis don rtogs theg chen gyi //
NK024(ya)001:13938: rgyal ba'i mdzad pa mthar phyin pa //
NK024(ya)001:13939: zab cing rgya che'i dbang rnams gsol //
NK024(ya)001:13940: zhes lan gsum gsol ba gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:13942: de nas bla mas dbang rdzas rnams rim par thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:13943: zhes gsungs shing mchan bur bum pas dbang bskur khrus bya zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:13944: thog mar bum dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:13945: bum pas dbang bskur zhing mu ne dang tad+ya th+aa
NK024(ya)001:13946: la a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum zhes btags pa bum chus
NK024(ya)001:13948: de nas lha dbang ni sku gzugs rnams rim par spyi bor bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13951: gser gyi gdog can rkang gnyis gtso //
NK024(ya)001:13952: spyan yangs mdzod spur mthing khar ldan //
NK024(ya)001:13955: sh+aakya'i rgyal pos byin gyis rlobs //
NK024(ya)001:13956: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:13959: shar phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK024(ya)001:13960: yum chen rgyan ldan rdo rje skyil //
NK024(ya)001:13961: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:13962: phyag bzhi dang po mnyam gzhag can //'og gnyis chos
NK024(ya)001:13963: 'chad po ti 'dzin //'gro ba sems can don mdzad
NK024(ya)001:13964: pa // de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:13965: d+hi pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pradz+ny+aa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:13966: d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13967: a b+hi lho phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK024(ya)001:13968: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK024(ya)001:13970: rin chen rgyan ldan sems skyil bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:13971: de yi byin rlabs dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:13972: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:13973: a b+hi nub phyogs pad+ma sh+aa ri'i bu ni gser mdog can //
NK024(ya)001:13974: rab byung 'khar gsil lhung bzed bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:13975: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:13976: b+ha ga wan pra ba ta th+aa ga ta a
NK024(ya)001:13977: ba lo ki te ka ru na ma ye s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:13978: h+aa / a b+hi byang phyogs pad+ma spyan ras gzigs dbang kun+da'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:13979: longs spyod rdzogs sku pad+ma po ti 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:13980: de yi dbang +aar+ya a wa lo ki wa ra
NK024(ya)001:13981: ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka sa ma ya s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:13982: h+aa / a b+hi gzhal yas lha snam shar phyogs su //
NK024(ya)001:13983: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK024(ya)001:13984: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la //
NK024(ya)001:13985: mchog sbyin rin chen g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13986: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yu ra ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13987: a b+hi gzhal yas lho phyogs pad zla'i steng //
NK024(ya)001:13988: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:13989: sngon po 'khor lo g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13990: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13991: a b+hi nub phyogs pad steng pad zla'i steng //
NK024(ya)001:13992: bde gshegs rin chen 'od 'phro rab tu dkar //
NK024(ya)001:13993: g.yas pa mche ba g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13994: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta tri ti sha ga pa ri b+hi shwa ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13995: a b+hi byang phyogs pad steng pad bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po sku mdog ljang //
NK024(ya)001:13996: g.yas pa pad dkar g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:13997: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi sha rat+na san ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:13998: a b+hi shar lho bde gshegs pad+ma dpal //
NK024(ya)001:13999: dung ltar pad dmar g.yon mnyam gzhag /'gro la bstan pas bag chags 'joms //
NK024(ya)001:14000: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta du ma le ka do ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14001: a b+hi lho nub pad steng bde gshegs ni //
NK024(ya)001:14002: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14003: dmar smug nyi ma g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:14004: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi mug ti mrgad ru sha ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14005: a b+hi nub byang pad zlar bde gshegs ni //
NK024(ya)001:14006: gdugs chen dam pa in+d+ra'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:14007: sna tshogs rdo rje g.yon mthil ston //
NK024(ya)001:14008: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta sur+ya bi ta la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14009: a b+hi byang shar pad zlar glang po dam pa gser ltar 'tsher //
NK024(ya)001:14011: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi d+ya bi sha ya b+ha pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14012: a b+hi steng gi bde gshegs dga' ba dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14013: sngon po rin chen bum pa g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14014: g.yon pa dkur brten skyil krung bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:14015: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14016: a b+hi 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+mo'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14017: gser mdog g.yas pa pad+ma bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14018: g.yon pa lte bar mthil phyir bstan //
NK024(ya)001:14019: de yi sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14020: a b+hi zhes pas thub pa la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba'i dbang dang //
NK024(ya)001:14021: yang yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:14022: lha bco lnga ma'i dbang ni /
NK024(ya)001:14024: phyogs bcu'i dbus su seng ge'i khri //
NK024(ya)001:14025: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:14026: dbus phyogs bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK024(ya)001:14027: sku mdog dkar gsal g.yas mchog sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:14028: g.yon na pad+ma po tis mtshan //
NK024(ya)001:14029: de yi d+hi pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14030: d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:14032: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:14033: dkar gsal mchog sbyin rin chen g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14034: g.yon pa lte bar dkur brten tshul //
NK024(ya)001:14036: lho phyogs sangs rgyas mya ngan med //
NK024(ya)001:14037: mkha' ltar phyag g.yas 'khor lo bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14038: g.yon pa dkur brten bsnyems pa'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:14041: g.yas pa mche ba g.yon dkur brten //
NK024(ya)001:14042: sangs rgyas pad zla nyi mar bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:14044: byang phyogs rgyal ba'i dbang po ni //
NK024(ya)001:14045: nyi zla pad steng sku mdog ljang //
NK024(ya)001:14046: pad dkar g.yas la g.yon dkur brten //
NK024(ya)001:14047: de yi a b+hi byang shar pad steng gser gyi mdog /
NK024(ya)001:14048: ting 'dzin glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14049: chos 'chad g.yas te g.yon dkur brten //
NK024(ya)001:14050: de yi a b+hi shar lho pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14051: dung ltar pad dkar g.yas na ste //
NK024(ya)001:14052: g.yon pa dkur brten bsnyems pa'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:14053: de yi a b+hi lho nub nyi snang dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14054: mrgad lta bu g.yas nyi ma //
NK024(ya)001:14055: g.yon pa bsnyems tshul dku la brten //
NK024(ya)001:14056: de yi a b+hi nub byang sangs rgyas gdugs dam pa //
NK024(ya)001:14057: ljang gu sna tshogs rdo rje g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14058: g.yon pa dkur brten 'gying tshul can //
NK024(ya)001:14060: steng phyogs dga' ba byed pa po //
NK024(ya)001:14061: sangs rgyas ut+pala lta bu'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:14062: bum pa g.yas la dkur brten g.yon //
NK024(ya)001:14063: de yi a b+hi 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+ma'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14064: gser mdog pad+ma dmar po g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14065: g.yon pa dkur brten thugs rje'i bdag /
NK024(ya)001:14066: de yi a b+hi yang lha lnga ma dang go dgu ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:14067: brgya nyer gcig ma'i gtso bo yab yum 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:14069: rnam dag dbus kyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK024(ya)001:14070: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub //
NK024(ya)001:14071: sa gnon mnyam gzhag bseg shang par bu can //
NK024(ya)001:14072: yum chen gser mdog ral gri mchog sbyin g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14073: g.yon pa ut+pala po ti phreng ba can //
NK024(ya)001:14074: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas phyogs mdog ting 'dzin glang //
NK024(ya)001:14075: rin 'byung pad+ma ting 'dzin rgyal po g.yas //
NK024(ya)001:14076: rdo rje chos 'chad rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:14077: thugs kar bsnams shing g.yon pa mnyam gzhag mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:14078: yum bzhi phyogs mdog rdo rje rin chen chos //
NK024(ya)001:14079: las ma bzhi po phyag mtshan yab dang mthun ///
NK024(ya)001:14080: rigs lnga yab yum 'di la thugs rjes bzung //
NK024(ya)001:14081: byin rlabs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14082: mu ne dang ga te brjod /
NK024(ya)001:14084: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dkon 'byung dkar //
NK024(ya)001:14085: mchog sbyin 'khor lo g.yon pa skyabs sbyin mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:14086: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang gu //
NK024(ya)001:14087: chos kyi rgyal mtshan chu srin rgyal mtshan can //
NK024(ya)001:14088: dbang phyug rgyal po lcags kyu 'bar ba 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14089: bkod pa'i rgyal mtshan mdzes pa'i me tog bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14090: rin chen 'od 'phro nor bu rin chen 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14091: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK024(ya)001:14092: sangs rgyas thub pa'i tshul dang sems dpa' re re yang //
NK024(ya)001:14093: rab byung tshul khrims sna tshogs tshul 'dzin pa'o ///
NK024(ya)001:14094: 'gro ba thugs rjes byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14095: sgrib sbyang dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14096: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14097: lho phyogs sangs rgyas mya ngan med dpal sngo //
NK024(ya)001:14098: skyabs sbyin thugs kar rin chen g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK024(ya)001:14099: shar lho nub byang dkar ser dmar ljang sems //
NK024(ya)001:14100: snang ba'i mchog ni phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14101: phyag rgya'i rgyal po rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14102: spos kyi glang po 'bud dung dkar po ste //
NK024(ya)001:14103: spobs pa brtsegs pa gser g.yu'i tog dang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:14104: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:14105: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul ///
NK024(ya)001:14106: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14107: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14108: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14110: skyabs sbyin thugs kar pad+ma bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14111: g.yon pa mchog sbyin pus mo'i steng //
NK024(ya)001:14112: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK024(ya)001:14113: pad+ma'i rgyal po sgrom bu ste //
NK024(ya)001:14114: pad+ma dam pa pad dkar po //
NK024(ya)001:14115: rdo rje mi g.yo lcags kyu'o //
NK024(ya)001:14116: thogs med rgyal po ral gri 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14117: sems ma rdor rin pad rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:14118: shar nub sems ma lho byang nyan thos tshul ///
NK024(ya)001:14119: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14120: byang phyogs rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang //
NK024(ya)001:14121: g.yas pa skyabs sbyin nyi ma ste //
NK024(ya)001:14122: g.yon pa mchog sbyin rdo rje can //
NK024(ya)001:14123: phyogs bzhi rin 'byung rin chen zur brgyad 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14124: grub pa sna tshogs rdo rje ste //
NK024(ya)001:14125: dga' ba ston pa me long can //
NK024(ya)001:14126: mi g.yo ba ni mnyam gzhag rgya //
NK024(ya)001:14128: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14129: byang shar glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14130: ljang gu thugs kar po ti bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14131: g.yon pa mchog sbyin chos gos 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14132: phyogs bzhi phyag na rdo rje rtse dgu ste //
NK024(ya)001:14133: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad dkar 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14134: nam mkha'i snying po za ma tog /
NK024(ya)001:14135: sa snying rin chen myu gu'o //
NK024(ya)001:14137: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14138: shar lho pad+ma dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14139: dkar ser g.yas pa nyi ma ste //
NK024(ya)001:14140: phyogs bzhi kun bzang rin chen sdong bu ste //'jam dpal gzhon nu ut+pa la lo //
NK024(ya)001:14141: sgrib pa rnam sel po ti 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14142: byams pa klu shing g+hun+d+he bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14144: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14145: lho nub snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14146: dmar ser nyi ma thugs kar bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14147: phyogs bzhi mthu chen thob ni rdo rje ste //
NK024(ya)001:14148: sman gyi rgyal po bum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14149: yon tan snying po rin chen snye //
NK024(ya)001:14150: mthong na dga' ba klu shing ngo //
NK024(ya)001:14152: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14153: nub byang gdugs mdzes dam pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14154: dmar ljang g.yas na gdugs kyis brjid //
NK024(ya)001:14155: phyogs bzhi gzhon nu rgyal mtshan ut+pala //
NK024(ya)001:14156: skyes bu dam pa dung rnga yab //
NK024(ya)001:14157: seng ge sgra ni ku mu da //
NK024(ya)001:14159: yum bzhi rdor rin pad rgya gram //
NK024(ya)001:14161: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14162: steng phyogs sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:14163: dkar po g.yas na rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14164: phyogs bzhi bzang skyong gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14165: dkon mchog 'byung gnas rin chen sgrom //
NK024(ya)001:14166: dpa' bar 'gro ba ral gri ste //
NK024(ya)001:14167: zla 'od gzhon nu zla tshes so //
NK024(ya)001:14169: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14172: phyogs bzhi ye shes tog ni tog dkar po //
NK024(ya)001:14173: mya ngan mun 'joms ral gri ste //
NK024(ya)001:14174: blo gros mi zad po ti 'o //
NK024(ya)001:14175: ye shes 'od de rdo rje bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14177: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14178: shar du glang po'i gdan khri la //
NK024(ya)001:14179: brgya byin ser po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14180: shar lhor ra skyes gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:14181: me lha dmar po bgrang phreng 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14182: lho ru ma he'i gdan la ni //
NK024(ya)001:14183: gshin rje sngon po be con 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14184: lho nub ro langs gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:14185: srin po smug nag ral gri 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14186: nub tu chu srin gdan la ni //
NK024(ya)001:14187: chu lha dkar po sprul zhags 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14188: nub byang sha ba'i gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:14189: rlung lha ljang gu ba dan 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14190: byang du rta yi gdan la ni //
NK024(ya)001:14191: gnod sbyin ljang sngon dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14192: byang shar khyu mchog gdan la ni //
NK024(ya)001:14193: dbang ldan nag po rtse gsum 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:14194: steng du ngang pa'i gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:14195: tshangs pa ser po pad+ma 'dzin //'og tu phag gi gdan la ni //
NK024(ya)001:14196: brtan ma ser mo gter bum bsnams ///
NK024(ya)001:14197: 'gro la dbang bskur mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14198: sgeg phreng glu gar me tog spos //
NK024(ya)001:14199: mar me dri chab sgo skyong bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:14200: rgyal ba mchod cing bstan pa srung //
NK024(ya)001:14201: tshad med phrin las gdul bya skyong ///
NK024(ya)001:14202: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14203: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14204: mu ne ga te a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:14205: de rnams ni lha dbang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:14207: rdzas dbang bskur ba rim pa bzhin thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:14208: zhes gsungs pas cod pan thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:14209: de yang bdag cag gi ston pas sgyu 'phrul ma'i
NK024(ya)001:14210: lhums su 'jug pa'i tshul ston par bzhed pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:14211: / rang gi cod pan byams par bcings te dga'
NK024(ya)001:14212: ldan gyi gnas rgyal mtshan mthon por rgyal tshab tu
NK024(ya)001:14213: / dbang bskur zhing / skyes bu dam pa khyod
NK024(ya)001:14214: ni nga'i 'og tu bla na med pa yang dag
NK024(ya)001:14215: par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon par rdzogs par
NK024(ya)001:14217: zhes gsungs pa ltar de ring khyod rnams la yang
NK024(ya)001:14218: cod pan spyi bor bcings te dbang bskur bas de
NK024(ya)001:14219: ltar du 'gyur bar byin gyis brlabs pa'i mos pa
NK024(ya)001:14221: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK024(ya)001:14222: dga' ldan gyi gnas nas yum sgyu ma lha mdzes
NK024(ya)001:14223: kyi lhums su gshegs pa'i tshe dbu las rin po
NK024(ya)001:14224: che'i prog zhu phud nas ma pham mgon la chos
NK024(ya)001:14225: kyi rgyal tshab tu lha rnams kyi ston par dbang
NK024(ya)001:14226: bskur ro // de bzhin du rin po che'i cod
NK024(ya)001:14227: pan gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal tshab byed
NK024(ya)001:14228: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:14230: tog gi dbu las rin chen cod pan phud //
NK024(ya)001:14231: de nyid phyag gis bu yi dbu la bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:14232: ma pham mgon po chos kyi rgyal tshab rje //
NK024(ya)001:14233: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po byed par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14234: chos kyi dbyings nas byung nas ga la bar //
NK024(ya)001:14235: sprul sku kun khyab yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK024(ya)001:14236: dang po tshogs rdzogs smon lam mthar phyin pa //'di
NK024(ya)001:14237: ni bsod nams rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis dang
NK024(ya)001:14238: po'o // de yang rgya che rol pa las //
NK024(ya)001:14239: ser skya'i grong khyer chen po de dang yul gzhan dag na skyes pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14242: bu mo su gang lha dang /
NK024(ya)001:14246: 'byung pos non pa ji snyed cig yod pa de
NK024(ya)001:14247: dag thams cad kyang byang chub sems dpa'i ma mthong
NK024(ya)001:14248: ma thag tu sos shing dran pa thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:14249: to // mi ma yin pa de dag kyang myur du gnas gzhan du 'dong bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:14250: sems can gang la la zhig nad sna tshogs kyis thebs par gyur te /
NK024(ya)001:14254: 'dus pa las byung ba'i nad kyis gnod par gyur pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14272: rkang shu la sogs pa'i nad kyis btab par gyur
NK024(ya)001:14273: pa de dag la byang chub sems dpa'i mas lag
NK024(ya)001:14274: pa g.yas pa spyi bor bzhag pa tsam gyis nad
NK024(ya)001:14276: rang rang gi gnas su 'dong bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:14277: tha na lha mo sgyu 'phrul gyis r+ts+wa nyag ma
NK024(ya)001:14278: 'ga' zhig sa las blangs te sems can nad pa
NK024(ya)001:14280: de dag des blangs ma thag tu nad med cing nyams pa med par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:14282: 'dir yang sgyu 'phrul lha mo'i phyag gis dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:14283: ba yang dgos pa de lta bu 'byung ba'i mos
NK024(ya)001:14284: pa mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dam pa tog
NK024(ya)001:14285: dkar po de yum gyi lhums na bzhugs pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:14286: pa mdzod / / yum gyi phyag gis sems can
NK024(ya)001:14287: rnams la reg cing dbang bskur bas sems can rnams
NK024(ya)001:14288: kyi na tsha dang sdug bsngal thams cad zhi bar
NK024(ya)001:14289: pa mdzod / / gyur to // de bzhin 'dir
NK024(ya)001:14290: yang yum gyi phyag gis reg cing dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:14291: nyon mongs pa dang na tsha sdug bsngal thams cad
NK024(ya)001:14293: sgyu ma lha mdzes lha yi lcam //
NK024(ya)001:14294: lha yi lus la rin chen mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:14295: nyon mongs sdug bsngal kun zhi nas //
NK024(ya)001:14296: na tsha'i sdug bsngal thar bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:14297: byin rlabs yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK024(ya)001:14298: kun la byams snyoms thugs rje che ba'i ma //
NK024(ya)001:14299: gzhan la phan mdzad don gnyis lhun gyis grub //'di
NK024(ya)001:14300: ni lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang gi bkra shis gnyis
NK024(ya)001:14301: pa'o // de yang gzhon nu don thams cad grub
NK024(ya)001:14302: pa lhums su zhugs pa dang bltams pa'i tshe gangs
NK024(ya)001:14303: ri'i ngos nas seng phrug zung cig byung ste ser
NK024(ya)001:14304: skya'i grong khyer la bskor ba byed pa'i dge mtshan
NK024(ya)001:14305: pa'o // bzhin / 'dir yang seng phrug gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:14306: bskur bas 'jigs med seng ge'i sgra bsgrags te thams
NK024(ya)001:14307: cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa
NK024(ya)001:14308: pa'o // bzhin / mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum+bi'i tshal du lhums nas bltams pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14309: seng ge'i phru gu zung cig gis bskor ba byas
NK024(ya)001:14310: shing dbang bskur bas rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil
NK024(ya)001:14311: gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14312: de bzhin du 'dir yang seng ge'i phyu gu zung
NK024(ya)001:14313: cig gi dbang bskur bas phyir rgol ba thams cad
NK024(ya)001:14314: zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:14315: seng ge'i nga ro skad chen thogs med pas //'jigs pa med pa'i sgra rnams bsgrags nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:14316: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyi sde btul te //
NK024(ya)001:14317: rgol ba'i tshogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14318: thams cad zil gnon cho 'phrul che ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:14319: yon tan kun tshang gdug pa zil gyis gnon //
NK024(ya)001:14320: che ba'i mthu stobs gzhan bas khyad par 'phags //'di
NK024(ya)001:14321: ni che btsan mthu stobs can gyi dbang gi bkra
NK024(ya)001:14322: shis gsum pa'o // de yang byang chub sems dpa'
NK024(ya)001:14323: gzhon nu don grub ser skyar gnas pa'i tshe glang
NK024(ya)001:14324: po'i phru gu rnams kyang ser skyar 'ongs te skor
NK024(ya)001:14325: ba byed pa bzhin du 'dir yang glang chen phru
NK024(ya)001:14326: gu zung gi dbang bskur bas theg chen stobs bcu'i
NK024(ya)001:14327: rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK024(ya)001:14328: shis gsum pa'o // / sngon byang chub sems dpa'
NK024(ya)001:14329: grong khyer ser skya na bzhugs pa'i tshe glang po
NK024(ya)001:14330: che'i phru gu gnyis kyi snas phyug cing dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:14331: bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14332: de bzhin du 'dir yang glang po che'i phyug gu
NK024(ya)001:14333: gnyis kyi dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:14334: thob par gyur cig /'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs ldan
NK024(ya)001:14335: zhing // theg pa bzhi yi don rtogs nas //
NK024(ya)001:14336: bye brag 'byed pa'i stobs rdzogs te //
NK024(ya)001:14337: stobs kyi pha rol phyin rdzogs shog /
NK024(ya)001:14338: mthu stobs phun tshogs ldan pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:14339: rin chen gser rgyan kun gyis spras //
NK024(ya)001:14340: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs glang po'i stobs //'di ni stobs bcu ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14341: de yang rgya che rol pa las /
NK024(ya)001:14342: de'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang mi mdzed
NK024(ya)001:14343: kyi bdag po tshangs pa gnyis mdun na 'khod de
NK024(ya)001:14344: / de gnyis kyi rim gro dam pa chen pos
NK024(ya)001:14345: lha'i gos ka shi ka'i sleb mos lus dang yan
NK024(ya)001:14346: lag thams cad kyis dran bzhin shes bzhin du byang
NK024(ya)001:14348: zhes gsungs pa ltar ka shi ka'i ras gos kyis
NK024(ya)001:14349: dbang bskur bas nyes skyon spangs shing yon tan rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:14350: pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:14351: sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum+bi'i tshal du sku bltams
NK024(ya)001:14352: pa'i tshe tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis blangs te
NK024(ya)001:14353: na bza' ka shi ka'i ras gsol te dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:14354: bas mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14355: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du na bza' ka
NK024(ya)001:14356: shi ka'i ras kyis dbang bskur bas mkhyen pa'i ye
NK024(ya)001:14357: shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:14358: dbang thob bo // cig / nyon mongs skyon spangs ka shi ka yi ras //
NK024(ya)001:14359: legs pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs te //
NK024(ya)001:14360: nyes pa'i skyon las skyob pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:14361: mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:14362: brgya byin bsod nams dag pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:14363: tshangs pa mngon shes lnga dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:14364: bdud rtsi chos 'khor zhu ba'i bdag /'di ni yon tan rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:14365: dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14367: klu'i rgyal po chen po dga' bo dang /
NK024(ya)001:14368: nye dga' bo gnyis kyang nam mkha'i dkyil nas lus
NK024(ya)001:14369: phyed phyungs te 'khod nas bsil ba dang dro ba'i
NK024(ya)001:14370: chu rgyun gnyis mngon par sprul nas byang chub sems
NK024(ya)001:14372: brgya byin dang tshangs pa dang 'jig rten skyong ba la sogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:14373: gzhan yang lha'i bu brgya stong mang po dag byang
NK024(ya)001:14374: chub sems dpa' btsas ma thag tu spos chu sna
NK024(ya)001:14375: tshogs dang / me tog sil mas lus 'khru zhing mngon par 'thor ro //
NK024(ya)001:14376: zhes 'byung ba ltar khrus chus dbang bskur bas ma
NK024(ya)001:14377: dag pa'i dri ma 'khru zhing legs lam mthar phyin
NK024(ya)001:14378: pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:14379: tsakli dang khrus bum sprags te /
NK024(ya)001:14380: sngon byang chub sems dpa' yum gyi lhums nas bltams pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14381: klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nyer dga' gnyis kyis
NK024(ya)001:14382: lho phyogs kyi chu mig rta rnga 'dzin nas bdud
NK024(ya)001:14383: rtsi'i chu blangs nas khrus gsol bas nyon mongs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14384: dri ma dag pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14385: de bzhin du 'dir yang dbang bskur bas nyon mongs
NK024(ya)001:14386: pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma dag pa'i klu rgyal
NK024(ya)001:14388: bcom ldan drin lan bsab pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:14389: sku yi dri ma yongs su bkru //
NK024(ya)001:14390: skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14391: yon tan kun ldan byang chub sems dpa'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:14392: bcom ldan rjes dran smon lam 'grub pa'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:14393: dri ma kun 'khru legs pa mthar phyin pa'i //'di
NK024(ya)001:14394: ni sku tshe ring ba'i dbang gi bkra shis drug
NK024(ya)001:14395: pa'o // rgya che rol pa las /
NK024(ya)001:14396: de ltar rgyal po zas gtsang ma de'i don bsam
NK024(ya)001:14397: pa gang yin pa de dag thams cad phun sum
NK024(ya)001:14399: rgyal po zas gtsang ma 'di snyam du bdag gi
NK024(ya)001:14400: bu gzhon nu de'i ming ji skad gdags par bya
NK024(ya)001:14401: snyam pa dang / de 'di snyam du sems te
NK024(ya)001:14402: bu 'di skyes ma thag tu bdag gi don thams
NK024(ya)001:14403: cad yang dag par grub par gyur gyis /
NK024(ya)001:14404: 'di'i ming ni don thams cad grub par gdags so snyam ste /
NK024(ya)001:14405: de nas rgyal pos byang chub sems dpa' de la
NK024(ya)001:14406: rim gro cher byas nas bu'i ming don thams cad
NK024(ya)001:14409: zhes gsungs pa ltar ming gi dbang bskur bas 'khor
NK024(ya)001:14410: 'das la dbang sgyur rgyal dbang thob pa'i mos pa
NK024(ya)001:14411: mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' bltams nas dgung
NK024(ya)001:14412: lo bdun lon pa'i tshe sh+aakya'i rigs rnams 'tshogs nas
NK024(ya)001:14413: gzhon nu don grub par ming du btags te dbang
NK024(ya)001:14414: bskur bas shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang thob
NK024(ya)001:14415: mdzod / bo // de bzhin du 'dir yang ming
NK024(ya)001:14416: gi dbang bskur bas shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14417: dbang rigs kyi bu khyod deng phyin chad //
NK024(ya)001:14418: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur bas //
NK024(ya)001:14419: gzhon nu don grub yin pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:14420: rgyal bu don kun grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14421: rgyal khrims gtsang ma rgyal bu kun 'dus pa //
NK024(ya)001:14422: lha mi kun la dbang sgyur rgyal por bskos //
NK024(ya)001:14423: kun las 'phags pa'i rgyal dbang dam pa ste //'di ni kun gyi dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14425: de yang gzhon nu don grub la skye dgu'i bdag mo chen mo go'u ta mi dang /
NK024(ya)001:14428: sh+aakya'i rgyal po bzang po sogs kyis rgyan gyi bye brag du mas brgyan te mdzes par byas /
NK024(ya)001:14429: rgyan gzhan gyis mdzes par ma gyur par gsungs pa
NK024(ya)001:14430: bzhin rgyan du ma'i dbang bskur bas yon tan rgya
NK024(ya)001:14431: mtsho'i rgyan dang ldan pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa
NK024(ya)001:14432: mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' la sru skye
NK024(ya)001:14433: dgu'i bdag mos rgyan gyi bye brag gis brgyan cing
NK024(ya)001:14434: dbang bskur bas sa rdo la byas pa'i bsam ma
NK024(ya)001:14435: no med pa phyag gis tshur stsal ba'i dbang thob
NK024(ya)001:14436: mdzod / bo // de bzhin du rgyan gyi bye
NK024(ya)001:14437: brag gi dbang bskur bas 'gro ba thams cad shes
NK024(ya)001:14438: pa dang ldan par byed pa'i mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams
NK024(ya)001:14440: legs pa'i yon tan kun tshang ye shes sku //
NK024(ya)001:14441: ma rig thar lam ma lus 'dren pa'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:14442: rtogs pa'i yon tan mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14443: yon tan kun ldan sru mos mdzes par brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:14444: legs pa kun rdzogs yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK024(ya)001:14445: che ba'i yon tan mthar phyin mi lang ste //'di ni legs brgyan dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14447: byang chub sems dpa' yi ge'i grar byon pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:14448: yig dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen zil gyis mnan te
NK024(ya)001:14449: / yi ge'i sgra las chos sgo brgya stong grangs
NK024(ya)001:14450: med pa byung ste byis pa sum khri nyis stong
NK024(ya)001:14451: byang chub tu smin par mdzad pa bzhin yig shing
NK024(ya)001:14452: gi dbang bskur bas chos kyi sgra sgrog pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:14454: sngon byang chub sems dpa' kun gyi bshes gnyen la yi ge slob pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14455: tsan+dana sprul gyi snying po'i byang shing gser gyi wam mig btags /
NK024(ya)001:14456: rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan te yi ge
NK024(ya)001:14457: slob pa'i dbang bskur bas yig dpon yang dang ngas
NK024(ya)001:14458: te lha mi'i yi ge thams cad la mkhas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14459: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du yig shing gi
NK024(ya)001:14460: dbang bskur bas chos kyi sgra sgrog pa'i tsan+dana sprul
NK024(ya)001:14462: rin chen gser gyi wam mig btags //'gro ba'i don byed yi ge'i mthu //
NK024(ya)001:14463: pha rol zil gnon kun las rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:14464: yon tan bla med yi ge'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:14465: dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14467: byang chub sems dpa' mes seng ge za 'gram gyi
NK024(ya)001:14468: gnam ru brdungs pa'i tshe sgra mngon par grags pa
NK024(ya)001:14469: la / lha dang mi brgya stong dag e ma
NK024(ya)001:14470: a la la zhes zer ba dag lha'i bu dag
NK024(ya)001:14471: la / gis / gdan las ma bzhengs rtsol ba ma mchis su //
NK024(ya)001:14472: thub pas gnam ru 'di 'dra brdungs pa las //
NK024(ya)001:14473: gdon mi 'tshal bar dgongs pa rdzogs gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:14474: bdud kyi sde bcom myur du thub par byon //
NK024(ya)001:14475: zhes basngagasa pa ltar gnam rus dbang bskur bas bdud
NK024(ya)001:14476: dpung 'joms pa'i mthu rtsal ldan pa'i dbang thob pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14477: mos pa mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' sgyu
NK024(ya)001:14478: rtsal gyi stobs 'gran pa'i tshe mes seng ge 'gram
NK024(ya)001:14479: gyi gnam ru brdungs pas sgra'i bye brag bsam gyis
NK024(ya)001:14480: mi khyab pa byung ste sgyu rtsal gyis 'dul ba'i
NK024(ya)001:14482: de bzhin du gnam ru'i dbang bskur bas snyan pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14483: sgra sgrog cing bdud dpung 'joms pa'i mthu rtsal dang
NK024(ya)001:14484: ldan pa'i snyan pa'i sgra sgrog gnam ru mchog /'gro
NK024(ya)001:14485: ba kun gyi yid tshim zhing //
NK024(ya)001:14486: gnod pa'i bdud rnams bcom nas ni //
NK024(ya)001:14487: ma rung 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:14488: thams cad kun 'dul mthu stobs phun sum tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:14489: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis pha rol zil gyis gnon //
NK024(ya)001:14490: don dang mi 'gal gdug pa zhi mdzad pa //'di ni gnam ru dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14492: de'i tshe sh+aakya lag na be con gyis rang gi
NK024(ya)001:14493: bu mo sa 'tsho ma byang chub sems dpa' la
NK024(ya)001:14494: phul lo // rgyal po zas gtsang mas kyang de
NK024(ya)001:14495: rim gyis bag mar blangs te byang chub sems dpa'
NK024(ya)001:14496: phul lo // la phul lo // de nas byang
NK024(ya)001:14497: chub sems dpa' 'jig rten dang mthun pa tsam du
NK024(ya)001:14498: bya ba'i phyir bud med brgyad khri bzhi stong gi
NK024(ya)001:14500: dga' zhing rtse la yongs su spyod pa ston to //
NK024(ya)001:14501: bud med brgyad khri bzhi stong de dag thams cad
NK024(ya)001:14502: kyi nang na sh+aakya'i bu mo sa 'tsho ma btsun
NK024(ya)001:14503: mo'i mchog tu dbang bskur bar gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:14504: zhes gsungs pa ltar btsun mo sa dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:14505: rigs mi nub cing skal ba dang 'tshams par gdul
NK024(ya)001:14506: bya 'dul ba'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:14507: sngon byang chub sems dpa' rgyal srid khab tu bzhes
NK024(ya)001:14508: pa'i tshe sh+aakya sa 'tsho ma khab tu phul te
NK024(ya)001:14509: dbang bskur bas rigs mi nub cing 'gro ba khyim
NK024(ya)001:14511: de bzhin du btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas rigs mi
NK024(ya)001:14512: nub cing ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du 'gro don
NK024(ya)001:14513: byed pa'i nor bu rin chen byi dor byas shing
NK024(ya)001:14514: gsal / sh+aakya sa 'tsho ma bkab phyar na yang //
NK024(ya)001:14515: blos mos yid gcugs dang po'i sems bskyed de //
NK024(ya)001:14516: dgos pa'i don rnams yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14517: khyim dang 'du 'dzin 'dul bar gzigs pa yi /
NK024(ya)001:14518: khab dang rgyal srid 'khor los sgyur ba'i tshul /
NK024(ya)001:14519: khams gsum khyim pa rnams kyi don mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:14520: btsun mo dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14522: byang chub sems dpa' pho brang gi shar sgor rgan po na tshod kyis gtugs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14523: lho sgor nad kyis nyam thag pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14524: nub sgor shi ba'i ro khyogs la btegs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14525: byang sgor lhas dge slong du sprul pa rnams gzigs
NK024(ya)001:14526: pas 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du mkhyen
NK024(ya)001:14527: te thar pa rab tu byung ba 'chi med kyi
NK024(ya)001:14528: 'bras bu mchog la smon pa'i tshul bstan pa de
NK024(ya)001:14529: bzhin du / shing rtas dbang bskur bas skye rga
NK024(ya)001:14530: na 'chi'i sdug bsngal sun phyungs te myang 'das kyi
NK024(ya)001:14531: yon tan mchog tu dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK024(ya)001:14532: bzhin du / / sngon byang chub sems dpa' grong
NK024(ya)001:14533: khyer gyi phyogs bzhir shing rta kha lo sgyur bas
NK024(ya)001:14534: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad mi rtag par mkhyen pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14535: bzhin du / / dbang thob bo // de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:14536: du shing rta kha lo sgyur ba'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:14537: skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal sun dbyung ba'i rgyal
NK024(ya)001:14538: srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /'gro ba'i
NK024(ya)001:14539: don mdzad 'khor los sgyur ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:14540: lha mi yongs kyi spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK024(ya)001:14541: skye shi mi rtog pa las bzlog par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14542: rgyal chen dpal 'byor longs spyod phun sum tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:14543: gling bzhi'i mtha' bskor skye rga na 'chi spongs //'khor ba'i skyon sel bde sbyin yon tan mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:14544: shing rta dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14546: 'dun pa des kyang lha tshig de thos basngagasa ldan rta pho de la smras //
NK024(ya)001:14547: sems can kha lo sgyur mchog 'di bzhud khyod ni rta skad sgrogs shing shog /
NK024(ya)001:14548: de yis dbyar gyi kha dog can de rmig pa gser gyis brgyan byas nas /
NK024(ya)001:14549: yid mi dga' bzhin yon tan rgya mtsho mnga' ba'i bcibs par dbul ba byas //
NK024(ya)001:14550: mtshan mchog mnga' zhing phan mdzad khyod kyi chibs 'di rigs bzang dge ba lags //
NK024(ya)001:14551: khyod kyi sngon chad gang dgongs smon lam de grub gyur cing gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:14552: gang dag gegs bgyid zhi bar gyur cig dgongs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14553: brtul zhugs grub gyur cig /'gro ba kun la de
NK024(ya)001:14554: dag mtho ris sa dang zhi ba sbyin gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:14555: / ces gsungs pa ltar chibs rta'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:14556: nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i dbang thob pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:14557: / pa mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' khab
NK024(ya)001:14558: nas byung ba'i tshe 'bangs mos pas chibs ngang pa
NK024(ya)001:14559: basngagasa ldan brgyan te phul bas mtshan phyed la dpag
NK024(ya)001:14560: tshad brgya 'das te rab tu byung nas nyon mongs
NK024(ya)001:14561: pa las thar ba'i dbang thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14562: de bzhin du chibs rta'i dbang bskur bas rab tu
NK024(ya)001:14563: byung zhing nyon mongs pa las grol ba'i dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:14565: gar yang thogs med brtson 'grus myur ba'i shugs //
NK024(ya)001:14566: tshangs pa brgya byin mthu chen che ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:14567: rgyal chen rigs bzhis 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:14568: thog med tshangs par spyod pa'i mthu ldan shog /'khor ba'i chos rnams mchil ma bzhin du 'dor //
NK024(ya)001:14569: nus pa ma lus dgra rnams gzhom pa'i phyir //'dod pa'i rgyu spong rnam rtog 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:14570: chibs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14572: ji ltar na gtsug phud kyang yod la rab tu byung ba zhes gsungs par yang 'gyur snyam nas /
NK024(ya)001:14573: des ral gris gtsugs phud bcad de bar snang la bor ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:14574: de sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams kyis mchod pa'i phyir blangs te /
NK024(ya)001:14575: deng sang du yang sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha rnams gtsug phud kyi dus ston byed do //
NK024(ya)001:14576: der mchod rten yang byas te deng sang mchod rten
NK024(ya)001:14577: de gtsug phud blangs pa'i mchod rten zhes ming du
NK024(ya)001:14578: chags so // zhes gsungs pa ltar gtsug phud 'breg
NK024(ya)001:14579: pa'i ral gri'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:14580: ba gcod pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:14581: sngon byang chub sems dpa' mchod rten rnam dag gi
NK024(ya)001:14582: drung du rab tu byung ba'i tshe sum cu rtsa
NK024(ya)001:14583: gsum gyi lha mdzes pa'i tog gis phyag shan phul
NK024(ya)001:14584: te dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod
NK024(ya)001:14586: de bzhin du ral gri'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs
NK024(ya)001:14587: pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod
NK024(ya)001:14589: mi shes nyon mongs rgyu rnams bcad nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:14590: bla med byang chub gnas su 'god pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:14591: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14592: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus bcoms nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:14593: bde ba'i don rtogs nags khrod dben par gnas //
NK024(ya)001:14594: bdag don lhun grub gzhan don mthar phyin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:14595: tshul khrims dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14596: bseg par byung tshul rgya rol gyi gleng gzhi dang ma mthun pas ma bris so //
NK024(ya)001:14597: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub rdzogs pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14598: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i bu yid bzhin 'byung
NK024(ya)001:14599: bas bseg shang par bu phul bas 'gro don mthar
NK024(ya)001:14601: de bzhin du bseg shang par bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:14602: 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:14603: / ser sna'i mdun pa 'grol phyir bseg shang bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14604: chog shes dgang ba sla phyi par bu bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:14605: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs byang chub nyid kyi sku //
NK024(ya)001:14606: bdag dang gzhan don mthar phyin rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14607: ma rig gnyid slong bsil byed sgra //
NK024(ya)001:14608: lhung bzed zag med yon tan snod //
NK024(ya)001:14609: zhi zhing dbang po rab dul ba //
NK024(ya)001:14610: dbang gi bkra shis bco lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14612: byang chub sems dpa' 'di snyam du bsams te /
NK024(ya)001:14613: rab tu byung bas ka shi ka'i ras gyon pa
NK024(ya)001:14614: mi rigs par mthong ste ngur smrig zhig rnyed na
NK024(ya)001:14616: lhas rngon pa ngur smrig bgos par sprul pa dang
NK024(ya)001:14617: byang chub sems dpas ka shi'i ras dang barjesa te
NK024(ya)001:14618: gsol ba'i gtam rgyud bzhin ngur smrig gi na bza'
NK024(ya)001:14619: dbang bskur bas tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:14621: sngon byang chub sems dpa' bsnyen par rdzogs pa'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:14622: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i lha'i bus na bza' ngur
NK024(ya)001:14623: smrig phul bas srid pa'i gdung ba las skyob pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14624: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du na bza' ngur
NK024(ya)001:14625: smrig gi dbang bskur bas srid pa'i gdung ba las
NK024(ya)001:14626: skyob pa'i ngan 'gro bskyab phyir na bza' chos gos
NK024(ya)001:14627: dbang thob bo // gsol // mi shes rmongs pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:14628: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas ma gos pa'i //'bras bu byang chub gnas su grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14629: bslab gsum tshul khrims sgo gsum rnam par dag /
NK024(ya)001:14630: bde ba mchog brnyes 'jigs pa'i dgra las rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:14631: rab byung dge slong rkang gnyis lha mi'i gtso /
NK024(ya)001:14632: na bza' dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14634: steng rgyas kyi sde dbon gyi grong na dga' byed ces bya ba'i bu mo legs skyes mas /
NK024(ya)001:14635: ba stong gi 'o ma lan bdun du nying khur
NK024(ya)001:14636: byas pa'i 'o thug sprang rtsi dang 'bras gsar pa
NK024(ya)001:14637: dang sbyar te gser gyi snod bkang ste byang chub
NK024(ya)001:14638: sems dpa' dka' thub kyis lus cung zad nyams pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14639: tshul bstan pa de la phul bas zas rags pa
NK024(ya)001:14640: zos ma thag tu lus kha dog bzang po rgyas
NK024(ya)001:14642: 'od 'dom gang dang bcas par gyur pa de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:14643: du 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang bskur bas mtshan
NK024(ya)001:14644: dpe rdzogs pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:14645: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i
NK024(ya)001:14646: 'gram du dka' thub lo gnyis la 'bras nyag ma
NK024(ya)001:14647: re / lo gnyis la chu thigs pa re /
NK024(ya)001:14648: lo gnyis la ci yang ma gsol ba nyid la tshor ba mi mnga' yang /
NK024(ya)001:14649: sku rid cing skams pa'i tshe grong pa'i bu mo
NK024(ya)001:14650: legs skyes mas 'o thug 'bras chan 'khar gzhong gang
NK024(ya)001:14651: phul bas sku gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar
NK024(ya)001:14652: gyur te mtshan dang dpe byad kyi dbang thob bo
NK024(ya)001:14653: // de bzhin du 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang
NK024(ya)001:14654: bskur bas sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14655: nyon mongs med pa 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:14656: zhi ba'i ngang la rab tu gnas //
NK024(ya)001:14657: bsod nams thob phyir bsngosa pa 'dis //
NK024(ya)001:14658: mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14659: zad med bdud rtsi'i chos kyi ro //
NK024(ya)001:14660: bsod nams lugs rdzogs ye shes kyi //
NK024(ya)001:14661: mtshan dpes rab brjid rgyal ba'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:14662: dbang chog bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14664: bkra shis r+ts+wa dag nga la myur du byin /
NK024(ya)001:14665: de ring nga la r+ts+was ni don chen 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14666: dpung dang bcas pa'i bdud ni bcom nas su //
NK024(ya)001:14667: byang chub dam pa zhi ba reg par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14668: gang gi ched du nga yis bskal stong du //
NK024(ya)001:14669: sbyin dang dul dang sdom dang gtong byas dang //
NK024(ya)001:14670: tshul khrims brtul zhugs dka' thub rab spyad pa //
NK024(ya)001:14671: de ni de ring nga yis thob par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14673: de ring nga la r+ts+wa sbyin byas na ni //
NK024(ya)001:14674: khyod la bsod nams stobs ni mtha' yas te //
NK024(ya)001:14675: de ni khyod kyi ngan pa'i rgyur mi 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14676: khyod kyang ston pa bla na med par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14678: bkra shis kyis r+ts+wa phul zhing 'di skad smras pa /
NK024(ya)001:14679: gal te r+ts+wa yis byang chub go 'phang dam pa 'chi med pa //
NK024(ya)001:14680: mchog gyur zhi ba lta dka' sngon gyi rgyal ba'i lam thob na //
NK024(ya)001:14681: yon tan chen po'i rgya mtsho grags pa dpag med khyod bzhes shig /
NK024(ya)001:14682: bdag gi go 'phang dam pa 'chi med thog mar 'tshang rgyar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:14683: zhes 'byung ba ltar r+ts+wa durba'i dbang bskur bas bdud
NK024(ya)001:14684: tshogs btul te sangs rgyas pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:14685: pa mdzod / sngon byang chub sems dpa' byang chub kyi shing drung du gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14686: r+ts+wa 'tshong bkra shis kyis r+ts+wa rma bya'i mgrin pa
NK024(ya)001:14687: ltar sngo ba phyag tu phul ba stan tu bting
NK024(ya)001:14688: ste bzhugs pa bdud kyi bar chad kyis mi tshugs
NK024(ya)001:14690: de bzhin du r+ts+wa durba'i dbang bskur bas bar chad
NK024(ya)001:14691: thams cad kyis mi tshugs pa'i sngon gyi drang srong
NK024(ya)001:14693: ngo mtshar r+ts+wa mchog rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:14694: nyes med legs pa mtha' dag rdzogs byed pa'i //'gro ba'i don du bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14695: mnyam nyid mi g.yo rdo rje lta bu'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:14696: ting 'dzin 'jig tshogs lta ba nyi shu 'joms //
NK024(ya)001:14697: bdud rigs tshogs btul mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:14698: r+ts+wa mchog dbang gi bkra shis bco brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14700: bcom ldan 'das sgra gcan gyi drang srong gug rdzi
NK024(ya)001:14701: ka'i gnas na bzhugs pa'i tshe spre'usa lhung bzed du
NK024(ya)001:14703: de srog chags kyis gang bas ma bzhes pa las
NK024(ya)001:14704: slar yang srog chags bsal te phul ba bzhes pa
NK024(ya)001:14705: la dga' ste gar byas pa khron par lhungs te
NK024(ya)001:14706: shi ba sgra gcan gyi bram ze'i bur skyes pa
NK024(ya)001:14707: ltar sbrang rtsis dbang bskur bas stobs mchog dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:14709: sngon bcom ldan 'das ma ga d+har bsod snyoms la
NK024(ya)001:14710: gshegs pa'i tshe spre'usa sbrang rtsi lhung bzed gang phul
NK024(ya)001:14711: bas bkra shis pa'i rdzas su mnga' brnyes par gyur
NK024(ya)001:14712: to // de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi
NK024(ya)001:14713: dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i rgyal
NK024(ya)001:14715: sbrang rtsi phul ba'i bsod nams mchog /
NK024(ya)001:14716: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:14717: bkra shis stobs mchog ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14718: stong nyid rang byung zag med snying po'i bcud //
NK024(ya)001:14719: dus gsum rgyal bas zhen med rol par mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:14720: gang gis 'di 'thungs mnyam nyid sku gsum rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:14721: rtsi mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14723: bcom ldan 'das shing sgrol rgyu'i drung du bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:14724: tshe byang phyogs kyi tsho pa ga gon dang bzang
NK024(ya)001:14725: po zhes spun gnyis lho phyogs su dong ba la
NK024(ya)001:14726: / glang bu cang shes legs skyes dang grags pa
NK024(ya)001:14727: gnyis kyi thub pa'i spyan sngar lam drangs te mthong
NK024(ya)001:14728: bas dad de sbrang rtsi dang /
NK024(ya)001:14731: der rgyal chen bzhis rin po che'i lhung bzed phul
NK024(ya)001:14732: ba ma bzhes par slar rdo'i lhung bzed phul ba
NK024(ya)001:14733: na phyi ma'i nyan thos rnams la brtse bar dgongs
NK024(ya)001:14734: te thog mar rnam thos kyi bu dang /
NK024(ya)001:14735: de nas lhag ma gsum yang bzhes shing bzhi po
NK024(ya)001:14736: yang gcig tu byin gyis brlabs te gong gi sbrang
NK024(ya)001:14737: rtsi dang / slad kyi tshong pa spun gnyis kyis
NK024(ya)001:14738: ba stong gi 'o ma nying khur 'dus pa'i zhal
NK024(ya)001:14739: zas dang sbyar te rin po che'i gzhong pa bkang
NK024(ya)001:14741: lha yi bkra shis don grub cing //
NK024(ya)001:14742: phyogs rnams bkra shis byed pa des //
NK024(ya)001:14743: khyed kyi don rnams grub gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:14744: thams cad myur du mthun par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14746: sbrang rtsi 'byung ba'i rgyal por lung bstan no //
NK024(ya)001:14747: de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas sprang rtsis dbang
NK024(ya)001:14748: bskur bas skye 'chi med pa'i dbang thob pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:14749: pa mdzod / sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes bu gyad kyi nye 'khor na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:14750: byang phyogs kyi tshong ba ga gon ta bzang pos
NK024(ya)001:14751: bu ram sbrang rtsi phul ba bzhes pa shin tu
NK024(ya)001:14752: bkra shis pa'i rdzas la mnga' bsnyes par gyur to
NK024(ya)001:14753: // de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi dbang
NK024(ya)001:14754: bskur bas skye shi med pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:14755: // cig / kun gyi snying po yon mchog dad pas phul //
NK024(ya)001:14756: mchod gnas mchog gi rab bzhes 'bras bu ni //
NK024(ya)001:14757: rgyal bar lung bstan smon lam myur thob phyir //'di dag bkra shis thog med rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:14758: yon tan rab rdzogs sangs rgyas sa la gnas //
NK024(ya)001:14759: go 'phang bla med rgyal thabs spyod pa gcig /'gro don mthar phyin 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK024(ya)001:14760: mdzad pa mthar phyin dbang mchog nyi shu pa'o //'di
NK024(ya)001:14761: yan rgya che rol pa 'gro ba 'dul ba rgyu
NK024(ya)001:14762: mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i dbang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:14763: de ltar dbang gi rim pa grub nas rtsa ba'i
NK024(ya)001:14764: sa bcad bco lnga pa lam 'khyer la nang gses
NK024(ya)001:14765: bzhi'i dang po theg pa lam 'khyer gyi rgyas bshad
NK024(ya)001:14768: gsum pa snying po ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:14770: theg pa rgyu mtshan nyid byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14771: lha yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:14772: snying po tad+ya th+aa ga te bzlas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14773: dbang mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:14774: zhes gsungs pa ltar lha sngags de rnams lam du 'khyer /
NK024(ya)001:14775: theg pa lam 'khyer drug gi dang po 'jug sgo ni /
NK024(ya)001:14776: rtsa bar 'jug sgo bden pa gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK024(ya)001:14778: sangs rgyas rnams kyi chos bstan pa //
NK024(ya)001:14779: bden pa gnyis la yang dag brten //'jig rten kun rdzob bden pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:14780: dam pa don gyi bden pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14782: kun rdzob kyi bden pa la bzhi ste mtshan gazhi'am ngo bo ni yul sna tshogs snang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:14783: de kun rdzob tu mtshon pa'i mtshan nyid ni rig pas dpyad na mi 'thad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14784: ming don nam nges tshig ni tha snyad pa'i shes
NK024(ya)001:14785: pa la snang zhing yang dag pa'i don la sgrib
NK024(ya)001:14787: gang zhig gi sems gang zhig la //
NK024(ya)001:14788: yan lag sgrib byed kun rdzob 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:14790: bzhi pa dbye na gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:14791: snang la don byed nus pa yang dag pa'i kun rdzob dang /
NK024(ya)001:14792: snang la don byed mi nus pa log pa'i kun rdzob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14793: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK024(ya)001:14794: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK024(ya)001:14795: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK024(ya)001:14796: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:14797: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba bya //
NK024(ya)001:14799: don dam pa'i bden pa la bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:14800: mtshan nyid dam ngo bo ni spros pa dang bral bar snang ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:14801: don dam du mtshon par byed pa'i mtshan nyid ni
NK024(ya)001:14802: rig pas dpyad na 'thad pa ste shes bya yin
NK024(ya)001:14804: go don nam nges tshig ni /
NK024(ya)001:14805: rig shes kyi yul yin pas don mi bslu bas dam pa /
NK024(ya)001:14806: yun ni de'i ngo bor bden pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14808: rnam grangs kyi don dam bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:14809: rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam bden pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14811: spros pa la phyogs gcig par dang bral ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:14812: skye ba la sogs bkag pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:14813: yang dag pa dang mthun phyir 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:14815: gnyis pa spros pa thams cad dang bral ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:14817: yod med ces pa 'di yang mtha'//
NK024(ya)001:14818: de phyir mtha' gnyis rnam spangs nas //
