NK024(ya)001:14819: mkha' pas dbus la gnas mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:14820: zhes pas 'di la dbu ma rang rgyud pa dang thal 'gyur ba'i 'dod lugs mang du yod de /
NK024(ya)001:14821: kun rdzob rnam dpyad dgag byar byas nas 'gegs /
NK024(ya)001:14822: don dam yongs spyod sgrub byar byas nas sgrub pa de 'jug sgo //
NK024(ya)001:14824: gnyis pa lta ba ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:14825: gnyis pa lta ba ni gang zag gi bdag gcig
NK024(ya)001:14826: dang du bral gyi rtag 'dzin gyi rang bzhin med
NK024(ya)001:14827: par rtogs la / chos kyi bdag dang gzung yul
NK024(ya)001:14828: thams cad sgyu ma ltar rtogs pas phyi rol yul
NK024(ya)001:14830: 'dzin pa'i shes pa kun gzhi mtha' bral du gnas
NK024(ya)001:14831: pa de la skad cig tu grub pa med do
NK024(ya)001:14833: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //'di ni byang chub sems dpa' yin //
NK024(ya)001:14835: gsum pa tshul khrims ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:14836: gsum pa bsrung ba'i tshul khrims ni byang chub sesama dpa' rtsa ba'i sdom pa bzhin ni /
NK024(ya)001:14837: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK024(ya)001:14838: gzhan gyis bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK024(ya)001:14839: khros pas gzhan la 'tshog pa srog /
NK024(ya)001:14840: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK024(ya)001:14841: ser sna'i chos nor ma byin len //
NK024(ya)001:14842: rnyed dang bkur stir chags pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:14843: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa log /
NK024(ya)001:14844: theg pa chen po spong byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:14845: dam chos 'drar snang ston pa rdzun //
NK024(ya)001:14847: rtsa bzhi yan lag nyi shu /
NK024(ya)001:14848: nying lag du ma rnams bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:14850: bzhi pa ting 'dzin ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:14851: ting nge 'dzin ni sgom gyi ngo bo byang phyogs so bdun te /
NK024(ya)001:14852: chos nyid du dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:14853: yang dag par spong ba bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:14855: sbyor lam du dbang po lnga /
NK024(ya)001:14857: mthong lam du byang chub yan lag bdun /
NK024(ya)001:14858: sgom lam du 'phags lam yan lag brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:14859: mthong lam du gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya /
NK024(ya)001:14860: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag go //
NK024(ya)001:14862: lnga pa spyod pa ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:14863: lnga pa sbyod pa ni bdag gces gzhan gces kyi sgo nas sems can gyi don byed pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:14864: de yang spyod pa'i rang bzhin phar phyin bzhi la spyod pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:14870: phyi yongs su gtong ba 'khor gsum yongs su dag pa 'dzin chags med pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:14872: gling bzhi legs par brgyan pa mchil ma'i thal ba 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:14873: byin nas dga' bar 'gyur gyi gling thob de ltar min //
NK024(ya)001:14875: nang yongs su gtong ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:14877: bu dang chung ma la sogs pa gtong ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:14878: mgo dang yan lag gtong zhing zhum pa'i sems med kyang //
NK024(ya)001:14879: bdog pa thams cad gtong zhing zhen med pa //
NK024(ya)001:14890: gnod pa la ji mi snyam pa /
NK024(ya)001:14891: chos la nges par sems pa /
NK024(ya)001:14892: sdug bsngal dang du len pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14896: drug pa 'bras bu ni lam lnga /
NK024(ya)001:14897: sa bcu rim par bgrod nas sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan gyi sa thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:14899: bdag med gnyis don pha rol phyin rtogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:14900: sa bcu rim gyis sgom pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK024(ya)001:14901: bden gnyis sangs rgyas go 'phang thob par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:14903: sangs rgyas dngos ni chos kyi sku yin te //
NK024(ya)001:14904: gzugs sku rnam gnyis 'gro ba'i mos rtog tsam //
NK024(ya)001:14907: gnas ni bya rgod phung po'i ri'am /
NK024(ya)001:14909: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni sangs rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:14910: 'khor byang chub sems dpa' don grub /
NK024(ya)001:14912: ci'i phyir na mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i ched du'o //
NK024(ya)001:14913: dgos pa bdud dpung bcom nas chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14915: gang gis gang du ji lta bar //
NK024(ya)001:14916: tshul dgos bcas pa rnam drug gis //'di ni byang sems 'gag drug yin //
NK024(ya)001:14919: gdams ngag gi sgom tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:14920: yul dpon yul rtsis byed pa lta bu ste /
NK024(ya)001:14921: gzhan don kho na la yongs su dmigs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14922: de yang ngang sgom gyi dbang du byas na bden gnyis kyi don sgom pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:14923: de yang kun rdzob kyi dbang du byas na /
NK024(ya)001:14925: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bskur byed dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:14926: pa ye shes chen po mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:14928: don dam par snying gi dkyil du thig le cog
NK024(ya)001:14929: sgong tsam 'od kha dog gang du'ang ma nges pa
NK024(ya)001:14931: thig le stong pa skye med par //
NK024(ya)001:14933: de la brtags pas kha dog gi rnam pa ma 'gags pa ci yang snang la /
NK024(ya)001:14934: kha dog de dag la brtags pas phyogs gcig pa
NK024(ya)001:14935: gang du'ang ma grub de bzhin du dbang bskur dang
NK024(ya)001:14936: bcas pa ma 'gags par shar yang /
NK024(ya)001:14937: don dam par gang du'ang ma dmigs chos nyid spros
NK024(ya)001:14938: pa thams cad dang bral ba ci'i ngo bor yang
NK024(ya)001:14939: ma grub par gnas pa yin no //
NK024(ya)001:14940: de ltar spros pa thams cad dang bral ba'i ngang
NK024(ya)001:14941: la ma g.yos par gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyis
NK024(ya)001:14942: gnas par bya'o // de'i rjes la kun rdzob ma
NK024(ya)001:14943: 'gags pa'i snang cha nyid yum sher phyin du lam
NK024(ya)001:14944: gyis sgom zhing spyod lam rnam bzhi lha dang mi
NK024(ya)001:14945: 'bral ba ni bden gnyis zung 'jug gi lam ste
NK024(ya)001:14946: ye shes dang sgom chen po'o //
NK024(ya)001:14947: de rnams kyi don gzhan rnams rtsa ba ltar la /
NK024(ya)001:14948: 'dir bsrung bya'i tshul khrims kyi skabs su skyabs 'gro'i
NK024(ya)001:14949: bslab bya ni lha mi'i theg pa'i skabs su rgyas
NK024(ya)001:14950: par grub / sems bskyed kyi bslab bya'i gtso bo nag po'i chos bzhi spang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:14951: dkar po'i chos bzhi sgrub tshul byang sdom tshar ma thag tu bshad zin /
NK024(ya)001:14952: 'dir gtso bo ni gzhung 'di'i lugs la sdom pa nyi shu pa khungs su mdzad pas /
NK024(ya)001:14953: des na thog mar phas pham bzhi ni /
NK024(ya)001:14954: slob dpon tsan+d+ra go mis mdzad pa'i sdom pa nyi shu par /
NK024(ya)001:14955: nyon mongs drag las byung ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:14956: sdom pa zhig par gang gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:14957: de yi nyes pa bzhi pa ni //
NK024(ya)001:14958: phas pham 'dra bar dgongs pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:14959: zhes gsungs pa'i nyes pa bzhi po gang zhe na /
NK024(ya)001:14961: rnyed dang bkur bstir chags pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:14962: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:14963: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK024(ya)001:14964: ser snas chos nor mi ster dang //
NK024(ya)001:14965: gzhan gyis bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK024(ya)001:14966: khros nas gzhan la 'tshog pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:14967: theg pa chen po spong byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:14970: bdag bstod gzhan smod ni pham pa dang po'o //
NK024(ya)001:14971: chos dang zang zing la ser sna byed pa ni gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14972: khros 'khrugs te bshad sbyangs la mi nyan par 'tshog cing brdung ba ni gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:14973: theg pa chen po'i chos spangs te chos ltar bcos
NK024(ya)001:14974: pa la mos shing gzhan la ston par byed pa
NK024(ya)001:14975: ni bzhi pa'o // de ltar yin par pan chen sdom gsum las kyang /
NK024(ya)001:14976: rnyed bkur lhag zhen bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK024(ya)001:14977: ser snas zang zing chos dang nor mi ster //
NK024(ya)001:14978: khro bas gzhan 'tshe bshad sbyang gis mi ldog /
NK024(ya)001:14979: g.yom las chos ltar bcos mos ston pa bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:14980: rtsa ltung bzhi ste 'jug pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:14982: de yang so thar gyi pham pa bzhi ni slar blang du med kyang /
NK024(ya)001:14983: 'di ni nyams na bskyar bas chog ste /
NK024(ya)001:14984: sdom pa nyi shu pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon zhi ba 'tshos mdzad pa las /
NK024(ya)001:14985: de ci byang chub sems dpas yang dag par blangs par gyur pa des 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:14986: dge slong so so thar pa'i sdom pa las pham
NK024(ya)001:14987: pa 'byung ba bzhin du tshe 'di nyid la yang
NK024(ya)001:14988: dag par blang ba'i skal pa med pa yin na
NK024(ya)001:14989: / ma yin te sdom pa slar yang blang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:14990: zhes dang gso ba'i tshul rnam grangs du mar bshad /
NK024(ya)001:14991: de ltar rtsa ltung bzhi po bshad nas /
NK024(ya)001:14992: nyes byas kyi chos bzhi bcu zhe drug bstan pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:14993: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK024(ya)001:14994: dkon mchog gsum la gsum mi mchod //'dod pa'i sems kyis rjes su 'jug /
NK024(ya)001:14995: rgan pa rnams la gus mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:14996: dris pa la ni lan mi 'debs //
NK024(ya)001:14997: mgron pos bdag gir mi byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:14998: gser la sogs pa len mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:14999: chos 'dod pa la sbyin mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15001: pha rol dang phyir bslab mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15002: sems can don la bya ba chung //
NK024(ya)001:15003: snying brtser bcas na nyes pa med //'tsho ba log
NK024(ya)001:15004: pa dang du len //'phyar zhing rab tu rgod la
NK024(ya)001:15005: sogs //'khor ba gcig tu bgrod par sems //
NK024(ya)001:15006: grags pa ma yin mi spong ba //
NK024(ya)001:15007: nyon mongs bcas kyang 'chos mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15008: gshe la lan du gshe la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:15009: khros pa rnams ni yal bar 'jog /
NK024(ya)001:15010: pha rol bshad kyi 'chags pa spor //
NK024(ya)001:15011: khro ba'i sems kyi rjes su 'jug /
NK024(ya)001:15013: le lo la sogs sel mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15014: chags pas bre mo'i gtam la brten //
NK024(ya)001:15016: bsam gtan sgrib pa spong mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15017: bsam gtan ro la yon tan blta //
NK024(ya)001:15018: nyan thos theg pa spong bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:15019: rang tshul yod bzhin de la brtson //
NK024(ya)001:15020: brtson min phyi rol bstan bcos brtson //
NK024(ya)001:15021: brtson par byas kyang de la dga'//
NK024(ya)001:15022: theg pa chen po spong bar byed //
NK024(ya)001:15023: bdag la bstod cing gzhan la smod //
NK024(ya)001:15024: chos kyi don du 'gro mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15025: de la snod dang yi ge bsten //
NK024(ya)001:15026: dgos pa'i grogs su 'gro mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15027: nad pa'i rim gro bya ba spong //
NK024(ya)001:15028: sdug bsngal sel bar mi byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:15029: bag med rnams la rigs mi ston //
NK024(ya)001:15030: byas la lan du phan mi 'dogs //
NK024(ya)001:15031: gzhan gyi mya ngan sangs mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15032: nor 'dod pa la sbyin mi byed //'khor rnams kyi ni don mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15033: gzhan gyi blo dang mthun mi 'jug /
NK024(ya)001:15034: yon tan basngagasa pa smra mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15035: rkyen du 'tshams par tshar mi gcod //
NK024(ya)001:15036: rdzu 'phrul bsdigs la sogs mi byed //
NK024(ya)001:15037: snying rje ldan zhing byams phyir dang //
NK024(ya)001:15038: sems dge ba la nyes pa med //
NK024(ya)001:15040: pan chen gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las //
NK024(ya)001:15041: nyes byas phra ba zhe drug gzhan du shes //
NK024(ya)001:15042: zhes bshad pa'i phyir ro //'di la gong du theg
NK024(ya)001:15043: pa lam 'khyer gyi sa bcad gsum pa bshad pa'i
NK024(ya)001:15044: skabs / rtsa bzhi yan lag nyi shu nying lag du ma rnams bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:15045: zhes gsungs pa'i don yin la /
NK024(ya)001:15046: sdoms tshig de rnams kyi don rgyas par 'dir bshad kyis ma lang bas /
NK024(ya)001:15047: sdom pa nyi shu'i 'grel pa rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:15048: khyad par mkhan po zhi ba 'tsho'i 'grel bshad du blta bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15049: mdor na nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK024(ya)001:15050: dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims /
NK024(ya)001:15051: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims dang gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:15052: dang po nyes spyod sdom pa'i khongs su bslab bya phal cher 'du zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15053: de yang nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo las byung ba'i
NK024(ya)001:15054: byang chub sems dpa' rgyal po la 'byung ba'i rtsa
NK024(ya)001:15055: ltung lnga / blon po la lnga /
NK024(ya)001:15056: phal pa la 'byung ba brgyad rnams rtsa ltung du
NK024(ya)001:15057: bshad pa mdo'i tshig ha cang mang bas yi ger
NK024(ya)001:15058: 'jigs te / 'dir pan chen rin po che'i sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:15059: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog dang ni chos spong las //
NK024(ya)001:15060: tshul ldan tshul 'chal khrims gcod bslab 'bebs sogs //
NK024(ya)001:15061: mtshams med las byed log lta lnga rgyal po //
NK024(ya)001:15062: grong ljongs grong khyer grong brdal yul 'khor rnams //'joms par byed pa blon por nges pa lnga //
NK024(ya)001:15063: ma sbyangs stong nyid brjod sngas nyan thos smon //
NK024(ya)001:15064: rdzogs byang phyir ldog theg dman sems bskyed dang //
NK024(ya)001:15065: so thar spangs nas theg chen slob pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:15066: nyan thos theg pas chags sogs mi ldog pas //
NK024(ya)001:15067: de log de yi 'bras bu med par byas //
NK024(ya)001:15068: phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK024(ya)001:15069: dge slong chad pas gcod 'jug sug 'bul dang //
NK024(ya)001:15070: spong pa'i longs spyod kha ton pa la sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:15071: zhi gnas 'dor bcug phal la 'byung nges brgyad //
NK024(ya)001:15074: yan lag nyes byas brgyad cu la sogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:15075: phra phyir 'dir ni ma bshad bslab btus blta //
NK024(ya)001:15076: zhes gsungs pas zhi ba lhas mdzad pa'i bslab pa kun las btus su blta bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15077: gnyis pa dge ba chos sdud ni phar phyin drug la bslab dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:15078: de yang dang po sbyin pa la zang zing /
NK024(ya)001:15081: chos te bzhir bshad kyang 'dir mi 'jigs pa dang
NK024(ya)001:15082: skyabs sbyin gnyis don gcig tu bsdus te sbyin pa
NK024(ya)001:15084: zang zing la gnyis su phye ste phyi yongs su
NK024(ya)001:15085: gtong ba zhes rgyal srid dang longs spyod sogs ster
NK024(ya)001:15086: ba / nang yongs su gtong ba zhes lus srog dang /
NK024(ya)001:15087: bu dang chung ma sbyin par gtong ba sogs yin /
NK024(ya)001:15089: gtong ba chen po zhes grags shing /
NK024(ya)001:15090: sdud pa'i lung dang sbyar ba yang gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:15092: chos sbyin ni rtogs par sla /
NK024(ya)001:15096: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims gsum gyi ngo bo yin /
NK024(ya)001:15098: gnod pa la ji mi snyam pa'i bzod pa /
NK024(ya)001:15099: chos la nges par sems pa'i bzod pa /
NK024(ya)001:15100: sdug bsngal dang du len pa'i bzod pa dang gsum /
NK024(ya)001:15104: phyir mi ldog pa'i brtson 'grus dang gsum /
NK024(ya)001:15109: 'dir theg pa lam 'khyer gyi sa bcad lnga pa spyod pa'i skabs su /
NK024(ya)001:15110: spyod pa phar phyin bzhi la slob //
NK024(ya)001:15112: bsam gtan dang shes rab ni gtso bo yin te lta sgom gyi ngo thi yin la /
NK024(ya)001:15113: gzhan bzhi po yan lag gam spyod pa'i don du bshad /
NK024(ya)001:15114: de yang bsdu na pan chen rin po che'i sdom gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:15115: dge ba chos sdud phar phyin drug slob de //
NK024(ya)001:15116: dbul ba sel phyir chos nor mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:15117: spong ba'i sems kyis tshul khrims rnam gsum spyad //
NK024(ya)001:15118: khong khro zab mo sdug bsngal bzod par bya //
NK024(ya)001:15119: go cha dge sdud gzhan phan brtson 'grus brtsams //'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i bsam gtan sgom //
NK024(ya)001:15120: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab zab mo spyad //
NK024(ya)001:15121: ces gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15122: gsum pa sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims ni bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:15124: thog mar sbyin par gdul bya rab bsdus nas //
NK024(ya)001:15125: snyan par smra ba'i gtam gyis yid rab drang //
NK024(ya)001:15126: theg pa rim dgur bkri ba don spyod de //
NK024(ya)001:15127: de dag 'dren phyir rang yang don de spyod //
NK024(ya)001:15129: de ltar byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyams na gso ba'i tshul mang yang mdor bsdu na /
NK024(ya)001:15130: pan chen gyi sdom gsum rnam nges las /
NK024(ya)001:15131: thun 'das nyams na 'phags pa nam snying la //
NK024(ya)001:15132: tho rengs gsol btab rmi lam ltung ba 'chags //
NK024(ya)001:15134: nam mkha'i snying po'i mdo lung bslab btus su drangs par /
NK024(ya)001:15135: byang chub sems dpa' las dang po pa nyes pa
NK024(ya)001:15136: dang bcas pa des tho rangs langs la shar phyogs
NK024(ya)001:15139: skya reng gi lha'i bu la gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:15141: skya reng skya reng snying rje chen po legs pa
NK024(ya)001:15142: chen po khyod 'dzam bu'i gling du shar ma thag
NK024(ya)001:15143: tu snying rjes bdag la khebs par mdzad du gsol
NK024(ya)001:15144: / nam mkha'i snying po snying rje chen po dang
NK024(ya)001:15145: ldan pa la yang bdag gi tshig gis myur du
NK024(ya)001:15146: / bskul te / thabs gang gis bdag ltung ba 'chags par 'gyur ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:15147: theg pa chen po 'phags pa la thabs dang shes
NK024(ya)001:15148: rab thob par 'gyur ba'i thabs de bdag gi rmi
NK024(ya)001:15150: zhes smros la de'i tshe gnyid legs par nyol zhig dang /
NK024(ya)001:15151: 'dzam bu'i gling 'dir skya rengs shar ma thag tu
NK024(ya)001:15152: byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po nam mkha'i
NK024(ya)001:15154: byang chub sems dpa' las dang po pa de'i rmi lam du /
NK024(ya)001:15155: de nyid du byang chub sems dpa' mi brjed pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:15156: theg pa chen po la brtan por gnas par 'gyur ro //
NK024(ya)001:15158: yang de nyid las chog gzhan sngags dang bcas pa yang bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:15160: pan chen gyi sdom gsum las /
NK024(ya)001:15161: lhag ma phung po gsum pa nyin mtshan du //
NK024(ya)001:15162: lan gsum 'don pas gzhil ba klu sgrub lugs //
NK024(ya)001:15163: zhes gsungs pa'i phung po gsum pa'i mdo ni /
NK024(ya)001:15164: drag shul can gyis zhus pa'i mdo lung bslab btus su drangs par /
NK024(ya)001:15165: nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du gtsang ba dang
NK024(ya)001:15166: gos btsang ma bgos te phung po gsum pa bklag
NK024(ya)001:15167: bar bya'o // de la phung po gsum ni sdig pa bshags pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15168: bsod nams la rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:15169: sangs rgyas la bskul ba zhes bya ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:15170: bsod nams kyi phung po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK024(ya)001:15174: sdig pa bshags pa'i nang du 'dus te /
NK024(ya)001:15175: sangs rgyas la phyag byas nas sdig pa bshags so
NK024(ya)001:15176: zhes nye ba 'khor gyis zhus pa las 'byung ngo
NK024(ya)001:15177: // gsol ba gdab pa ni bskul ba dang don gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK024(ya)001:15179: phung po gsum pa dngos ni /
NK024(ya)001:15180: dkon mchog brtsegs pa'i mdo las /
NK024(ya)001:15181: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK024(ya)001:15182: zhes sogs ltung bshags gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:15183: de nyin mtshan dus drug tu 'don no //
NK024(ya)001:15185: nyin dang mtshan mo lan gsum du //
NK024(ya)001:15186: phung po gsum pa gdon bya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:15187: rgyal dang byang chub sems bsten pas //
NK024(ya)001:15188: ltung ba'i lhag ma des zhi bya //
NK024(ya)001:15190: gzhan yang bdag gzhan mnyam pa dang barje ba'i byang
NK024(ya)001:15191: chub kyi sems sogs spyod pa rgya chen po la
NK024(ya)001:15192: bslab par bya ba'i tshul ni rgyas par byang chub
NK024(ya)001:15193: sems dpa'i sde snod rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:15196: bslab btus sogs las 'byung ba lta thos bsam gyis gtan la phab ste nyams su blang bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15197: de ltar byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rgya chen
NK024(ya)001:15198: po la bslab par 'dod pa rnams kyis lam gyi
NK024(ya)001:15199: gnad ma nor bar shes dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:15200: gnad 'phyugs na lam 'di la ma bslab par chos gzhan gyis 'tshang rgya bar mi nus te /
NK024(ya)001:15202: byang chub sems kyi gnad 'phyugs na //
NK024(ya)001:15203: chos gzhan gyis ni sangs mi rgya //
NK024(ya)001:15204: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir sngags lam gyi yang rtsa ba kho nar rig par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15205: de lta bu'i byang sems skye ba 'di nyid shin tu dka' ste /
NK024(ya)001:15207: long bas phyag dar phung po nas //
NK024(ya)001:15208: ji ltar rin chen rnyed pa ltar //
NK024(ya)001:15209: de bzhin ji zhig ltar ltas nas //
NK024(ya)001:15210: byang chub sems 'di bdag la skyes //
NK024(ya)001:15211: zhes gsungs pas long bas phyag dar gyi phung po
NK024(ya)001:15212: nas rin chen rnyed pa ltar shin tu dka' zhing
NK024(ya)001:15213: / stes legs pa'i dbang gis byang chub sems 'di rnyed pa'am skyes pa'i don yin /
NK024(ya)001:15214: de lta rnyed kyang dka' la /
NK024(ya)001:15215: rnyed pa yang don chen phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:15218: bdud rtsi'i mchog kyang 'di yin no //'gro ba'i dbul ba sel ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:15219: mi zad gter yang 'di yin no //'gro ba'i nad rab zhi byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:15220: sman gyi mchog kyang 'di yin no //
NK024(ya)001:15221: srid lam 'khyams shing dub pa yi //'gro ba'i ngal
NK024(ya)001:15222: bso'i ljon shing yin //'gro ba thams cad ngan 'gro
NK024(ya)001:15223: las // sgrol bar byed pa'i sbyi stegs yin //'gro ba'i nyon mongs gdung sel ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:15224: sems kyi zla ba shar ba yin //'gro ba'i mi shes rab rib dag /
NK024(ya)001:15225: dpyis 'byin nyi ma chen po yin //
NK024(ya)001:15226: dam chos 'o ma bsrubs pa las //
NK024(ya)001:15227: mar gyi nying khu 'byung ba yin //
NK024(ya)001:15229: byang chub sems skyes gyur na skad cig gis //'khor ba'i btson rar bcings pa'i nyam thag rnams //
NK024(ya)001:15230: bde gshegs rnams kyi sras zhes brjod bya zhing //'jig rten lha mir bcas pa'i phyag byar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:15232: 'di'i mi mthun phyogs ni khong khro ste /
NK024(ya)001:15234: bskal pa stong du bsags pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:15235: sbyin dang bde gshegs mchog la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:15236: legs spyad gang yin de kun yang //
NK024(ya)001:15237: khong khro gcig gis 'joms par byed //
NK024(ya)001:15239: khong khro thul na phyi rol gyi dgra bo thams cad choms pa yin te /
NK024(ya)001:15241: sa steng 'di dag ko g.yog tu //
NK024(ya)001:15242: de snyed ko bas ga la lang //
NK024(ya)001:15243: lhwam mthil tsam gyi ko bas ni //
NK024(ya)001:15244: sa steng thams cad g.yogs dang 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:15247: sems can mi bsrun nam mkha' bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:15248: de dag gzhom gyi yongs mi lang //
NK024(ya)001:15249: khro bo'i sems ni gcig bcom na //
NK024(ya)001:15250: dgra sde thams cad chom dang 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:15252: mdor na bslab pa bsrung bar bya ba yang sems bsrung ba kho na ste /
NK024(ya)001:15254: bslab pa bsrung bar 'dod pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:15255: rab tu bsgrims nas sems bsrungs te //
NK024(ya)001:15256: sems ni bsrung bar ma byas na //
NK024(ya)001:15257: bslab pa bsrung bar yong mi nus //
NK024(ya)001:15260: sems bsrung 'dod pa rnams la ni //
NK024(ya)001:15261: dran pa dang ni shes bzhin dag /
NK024(ya)001:15262: srog la babs kyang srungs shig ces //
NK024(ya)001:15263: bdag ni de skad 'doms par byed //
NK024(ya)001:15265: sems 'di gcig pu btul gyur na //
NK024(ya)001:15266: de dag thams cad btul bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:15267: zhes gsungs pa'i don bshes springs las kyang //
NK024(ya)001:15268: khyod kyi thugs thul mdzod cig bcom ldan gyis //
NK024(ya)001:15269: sems ni chos kyi rtsa ba lags par gsungs //
NK024(ya)001:15271: de ltar sems 'dul bar byed pa'i thabs kun rdzob
NK024(ya)001:15272: byang chub kyi sems byams pa dang snying rje sgom
NK024(ya)001:15273: zhing / don dam byang chub kyi sems zhi gnas dang lhag mthong sgom pa spyi'i lugs yin la /
NK024(ya)001:15274: bye brag tu lam 'di'i lugs la gdams ngag ngang sgom ni grol byed kyi nyams len te /
NK024(ya)001:15275: de la ye shes ngang sgom gyi dbang du byas nas bden gnyis kyi don ba sgom pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:15276: de la 'chad tshul mang yang lam 'di'i lugs la dbang rdzas gtad chog dang /
NK024(ya)001:15277: ting nge 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bskur byed dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:15278: pa ye shes chen po mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:15279: dang bcas pa ni kun rdzob bden pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:15280: don dam bden pa ni ngang sgom gyi ngo bo ste /
NK024(ya)001:15281: rang gi snying gi dkyil du thig le cog sgong
NK024(ya)001:15282: tsam 'di kha dog gang du'ang ma nges pa zhig
NK024(ya)001:15283: gsal btab cing / de la brtags te mnyam par
NK024(ya)001:15284: bzhag pas kha dog gi rnam pa ma 'gags pa
NK024(ya)001:15286: kha dog de dag la brtags pas phyogs gcig pa gang du yang ma grub pa de bzhin du /
NK024(ya)001:15287: kun rdzob kyi snang ngor dbang bskur dang dbang rdzas sogs ma 'gags par 'char yang /
NK024(ya)001:15288: don dam gang du'ang ma grub ma dmigs chos nyid
NK024(ya)001:15289: spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral ba ci'i ngo
NK024(ya)001:15290: bor yang ma grub par gnas pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:15291: de'i don la gnas pa med pa'i tshul gyi gnas par byas te mnyam par bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:15292: de ltar mnyam gzhag gi dus su bden gnyis dbyer med du gyur kyang /
NK024(ya)001:15293: de nyid lam du 'khyer tshul lam rjes thob kyi
NK024(ya)001:15294: rjes shes ma 'gags pa'i snang cha de nyid yum
NK024(ya)001:15295: sher phyin du sgom zhing spyod lam rnam bzhir snang
NK024(ya)001:15296: ba thams cad lha dang mi 'bral bar rjes thob
NK024(ya)001:15297: kyi rgyun skyong ba'i dran pas gsal gdab pa ni
NK024(ya)001:15298: / bden gnyis zung 'jug gi lam ye shes ngang
NK024(ya)001:15299: sgom yin pas mnyam rjes gnyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin
NK024(ya)001:15301: de ltar byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du byang
NK024(ya)001:15302: sdom dang dbang bskur grol byed kyi gdams pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:15303: nos pa tshul bzhin nyams su blangs te sems can
NK024(ya)001:15304: gyi don rgya chen po bgyid snyam pas 'di'i rjes
NK024(ya)001:15305: zlos mdzod / ces mtshams sbyar la dam tshig bsdus te khas blangs /
NK024(ya)001:15308: dge ba bsngo ba sogs snga ma ltar la /
NK024(ya)001:15311: de nas me tog bkram ste rol mor byas pas /
NK024(ya)001:15312: dam pa tog dkar dga' ldan pho brang dam pa ru //
NK024(ya)001:15313: ma pham mgon la rgyal tshab dam par dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:15314: zhing //'dzam gling nyid du glang chen thal kar lhums
NK024(ya)001:15315: su gshegs // bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:15316: rgyal po'i khab kyi ser skya'i grong khyer zas gtsang sras //
NK024(ya)001:15317: bud med mchog gyur g.yo sgyu spangs pa lha mdzes yum //
NK024(ya)001:15318: lhums su zla bcur bzhugs nas 'byor ldan sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:15319: bkra shis des kyang lum+bi'i tshal ni nyams dga' p+aaka sha ljon pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:15320: yal ga nas bzung bltams tshe tshangs pa brgya byin 'dus //
NK024(ya)001:15321: mkha' la gshegs te phyur por pad+ma byung gyur gang //
NK024(ya)001:15322: bkra shis des pho brang gzhal yas khang mdzes drang srong mdun bzhag nas //
NK024(ya)001:15323: mtshan ltas shis pa brjod de ston pa 'byung 'gyur zhes //
NK024(ya)001:15324: sh+aaka rigs bud med 'khor gyis bskor zhing rab tu brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:15325: bkra shis pho brang nas byung phyogs bzhir skye rga na 'chi gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:15326: mi rnams smin mdzad lha yis bteg ste mkha' la gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:15327: srid gsum rgyal phyir rab byung dbu skra mthon mthing bregs //
NK024(ya)001:15328: bkra shis lha yis rdzu 'phrul blangs nas na bza' ngur smrig phul //
NK024(ya)001:15329: nee rany+dza nar thub pa'i dka' thub lo drug rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:15330: bsam gtan nas bzhengs legs skyes mas phul 'o thug bzhes //
NK024(ya)001:15331: bkra shis pad+ma la sogs khyu mchog byang chub shing drung du //
NK024(ya)001:15332: skyil mo krung bcas mi g.yo bdud btul nas //
NK024(ya)001:15333: tho reng bdud rtsi 'chi med phun sum tshogs pa brnyes //
NK024(ya)001:15334: bkra shis wa ra n+aa sir thog mar chos kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK024(ya)001:15335: kun mkhyen ston pas lnga sde bzang la bden bzhi bstan //
NK024(ya)001:15336: lha dang mi dang lha min rnams kyang 'dus gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:15337: bkra shis nga rgyal dregs pa'i mu stegs ston pa drug btul nas //
NK024(ya)001:15338: glang chen rab myos rbad pa'i ma rungs lhas sbyin btul //
NK024(ya)001:15339: drang srong mchog dang sprel rgyal cang shes sbrang rtsis mchod //
NK024(ya)001:15340: bkra shis pad+ma lta bur skyon gyis ma gos sh+aakya'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:15341: zas gtsang sras po rgyal rigs mchog gyur 'khor los sgyur //
NK024(ya)001:15342: sku bltams gyur pas de yi mdzad pa ma lus rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:15343: bkra shis byams pa'i stobs kyis 'gro ba ma lus rab tu sgrol //
NK024(ya)001:15344: sems can thams cad smin grol zhi ba'i lam la bkod //
NK024(ya)001:15345: r+ts+wa mchog grong du mdzad pa mthar phyin dgongs pa rdzogs //
NK024(ya)001:15346: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:15347: ces brjod cing me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:15351: dge ba bla med byang chub tu bsngo'o //
NK024(ya)001:15353: dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos te byin gyis brlab la /
NK024(ya)001:15354: gong du bshad pa ltar mchod phreng dang bstod pa rgyas bsdus gang yang rung ba bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15355: bzod gsol dang dkyil 'khor bsdu ba /
NK024(ya)001:15356: bsngo smon sogs dkyil 'khor snga ma rnams kyi chog
NK024(ya)001:15357: khrigs kyi 'gros ltar bya zhing mdzad pa nyi shu'i
NK024(ya)001:15359: nub mo chog phrin tshogs bskang sogs kyang snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:15360: byang chub sems dpa' cho ga'o //
NK024(ya)001:15361: dal 'byor sa gzhir thar pa'i sa bon ni //
NK024(ya)001:15362: byang chub lam bzang drod gsher gyis bskrun te //
NK024(ya)001:15363: lam lnga sa bcu'i lo 'bras g.yur za ba //
NK024(ya)001:15364: ma lus skye rgu'i legs byas bsod nams zhing //'gro kun pha mar shes pa'i byams chen chab //
NK024(ya)001:15365: snying rje'i rba rlabs dkar pos nyer mdzes pa //
NK024(ya)001:15366: phyin drug nor bus legs gtams 'phags pa'i lam //
NK024(ya)001:15367: yan lag brgyad ldan chu klung 'di bsten cig /
NK024(ya)001:15368: gang zhig gzhan phan byang chub mchog gi sems //
NK024(ya)001:15369: rab bskyed brnag daka'i sdug bsngal khur khyer te //'gro ba'i sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa kun //
NK024(ya)001:15370: sel nus sems dpa' chen por bdag 'gyur shog /
NK024(ya)001:15371: ces pa yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////de
NK024(ya)001:15372: yan chod kyis phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa'i
NK024(ya)001:15373: smin grol gyi rim pa rnam legs par grub ste
NK024(ya)001:15374: //'di man chod nang gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i
NK024(ya)001:15375: lam gyi tshul rnams rim bzhin ston par byed pa
NK024(ya)001:15376: la / dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15377: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa gnyis su yod pa'i dang po la gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:15381: de la dang po kri ya ni /
NK024(ya)001:15382: kahthoga lugs su rnam 'joms la rigs gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:15383: rigs bzhi khro bcu sogs kyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor gcig tu mdzad cing /
NK024(ya)001:15384: pan chen ri zangs tog pa sogs kyang 'di ltar bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:15385: zur lugs la rnam 'joms kyi dmigs bsal med kyang /
NK024(ya)001:15386: phyag len bsdus pa'i phyogs su dkyil 'khor gcig tu byed pa yang 'dug mod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:15387: 'dir rtsa ba las ji ltar gsungs pa bzhin bya ba las /
NK024(ya)001:15390: kri ya'i theg pa'i cho ga ni //
NK024(ya)001:15391: dkyil 'khor mchod bsham lha tshogs bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:15392: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:15393: khrus byas nang zhugs gsol ba gdab //
NK024(ya)001:15394: sdom bzung chos bshad bslab bya dbog /
NK024(ya)001:15395: dbang bskur lam 'khyer bzhi yang bstan //
NK024(ya)001:15396: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyi dgos //
NK024(ya)001:15397: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:15398: zhes sa bcad bco brgyad nang gses dang bcas pa'i dang po dkyil 'khor la gzhi'i gnas tshul /
NK024(ya)001:15403: dang po dkyil 'khor gyi sa mtshams ri rab kyi rdo rje'i brag ri la'o //
NK024(ya)001:15406: tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor gyi shar lhor kri ya gnas par glan ston bsod nams mgon po bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:15408: khams lugs su rgyas par na rigs gsum mgon po
NK024(ya)001:15409: la sgeg sogs bzhis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor la 'dab
NK024(ya)001:15411: 'dab drug pa lte ba mi 'dra ba gsum la gtso bo rigs gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:15412: 'khor kri ya don gyi lha drug gis bskor ba gsum /
NK024(ya)001:15413: kri ya lha bco lnga ma'i dkyil 'khor gsum ste dgu /
NK024(ya)001:15414: lha nyer bdun ma'i dkyil 'khor te bcu /
NK024(ya)001:15415: yang bskal bzang gi lha snam can te bcu gcig tu byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15416: dgur byed pa gnyis su gsungs /
NK024(ya)001:15417: zur lugs rig 'dzin rje'i mchod shom pa bla ma
NK024(ya)001:15418: o rgyan pa'i gsan yig tu dkyil 'khor bdun du
NK024(ya)001:15419: bzhed kyang / 'dir zur lugs rtsa bar dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:15420: dgur gsungs pa la bla ma'i man ngag gis brgyan
NK024(ya)001:15422: de yang 'di man chod la lha sta gon kyang dgos par bshad pas /
NK024(ya)001:15423: dkyil 'khor 'og nas 'byung ba ltar bri rtsis kyi
NK024(ya)001:15424: las thig btab pa'i steng dri bzang gi chus thig
NK024(ya)001:15425: le bya zhing / pad+ma s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra man+dala zhes brjod /
NK024(ya)001:15426: dri'i thig le'i steng 'bras sam nas dkar gyi tshom bu bkod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:15427: dkyil 'khor dang po'i dbus su tshom bu bkod la /
NK024(ya)001:15430: phyogs bzhir tshom bu bkod cing /
NK024(ya)001:15433: badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih badz+ra n+air+t+ya a /
NK024(ya)001:15434: zhes brjod cing tshom bu bkod pa dang bstun lha rnams 'og gi mngon rtogs bzhin gsal btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:15435: de bzhin du dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i dbus su /
NK024(ya)001:15438: phyogs bzhi'i lha sngags gong ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:15441: zhes phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK024(ya)001:15442: phyogs bzhi'i lha sngags gong bzhin no /
NK024(ya)001:15447: zhes rigs bdag rnam snang ste tshom bu nyis sprel du bkod /
NK024(ya)001:15451: lho'i rtsibs la w+aa g+ai shwa ri mum /
NK024(ya)001:15453: nub kyi rtsibs la badz+ra ti k+sha na h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15454: zhes rdo rje rnon po dang /
NK024(ya)001:15455: byang gi rtsibs la ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15456: zhes gshin rje gshed rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:15457: sku'i mgron thabs kyi lha gsum la sta gon mi dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:15458: lha snam la tshom bu shar nub gnyis su lhag
NK024(ya)001:15459: re dang bcas te phyogs mtshams brgyad du 'god cing
NK024(ya)001:15461: gra bzhir bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad ni shar lho'i gru chad du tshom bu gnyis bkod cing /
NK024(ya)001:15462: tram mad+g+aa la de wi h+aum gnyis brjod /
NK024(ya)001:15463: de bzhin du mtshams gzhan gsum la tshom bu bkod tshul dang lha sngags gong ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:15467: a mi de wa h+r+aih zhes rigs bdag 'od dpag med gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:15468: pad 'dab bzhi'i shar du lo ki ta ri pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15472: nub tu pad+ma ta kri ta h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15474: byang du badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15476: mngon thabs kyi lha gsum mi dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:15477: lha snam gyi khro bo bcu /
NK024(ya)001:15478: gra bzhi'i bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad sogs gong ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:15481: zhes phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK024(ya)001:15483: zhes rigs bdag mi bskyod pa gnyis bkod /
NK024(ya)001:15484: rdo rje rgya gram gyi shar gyi rwa la sa man+ta b+ha d+r+ai h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15485: zhes kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK024(ya)001:15486: lho'i rwa la badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15487: zhes phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK024(ya)001:15488: nub kyi rwa la badz+ra kro ta h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15489: zhes rdo rje khro bo dang /
NK024(ya)001:15490: byang gi rwa la a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15491: zhes bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:15492: lha mgron gsum po mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:15493: lha snam la bskal bzang bcu drug dang /
NK024(ya)001:15494: khro bcu 'dam khar gsungs pas 'dir bskal bzang ni /
NK024(ya)001:15495: kahthoga lugs su yo ga nas bshad pa'i rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:15496: sems dpa' dang rgyal po sogs yin par bshad kyang
NK024(ya)001:15497: / zur lugs su shar du dpa' bar 'gro ba kun tu bzang po sogs bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:15498: lhor d+r+wa ba can sogs bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:15499: nub tu mya ngan kun 'joms sogs bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:15500: byang du byams pa sogs bzhir bshad pas 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:15501: dbang gi bskur tshig tu yang de bzhin bshad la
NK024(ya)001:15502: 'dir sta gon gyi tshe snam bu'i phyogs rer tshom
NK024(ya)001:15504: sngags ni thams cad mthun par bo d+hi sat+wa h+aum 'ba' zhig go /
NK024(ya)001:15505: khams lugs su sgo ba bshad kyang zur lugs su gsal kha med /
NK024(ya)001:15506: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsum po 'di'i gtso
NK024(ya)001:15507: bo khams lugs su rigs bdag gsum las ma bshad
NK024(ya)001:15509: rigs bdag gtsug rgyan rigs gtso dbus //
NK024(ya)001:15510: yum mdun g.yas g.yon khro bo dang //
NK024(ya)001:15511: rgyab nas pho nyas lha lnga thim //
NK024(ya)001:15512: zhes gsal bar 'byung ba bzhin 'dir bkod do //
NK024(ya)001:15521: zhes phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK024(ya)001:15522: dkyil 'khor de gsum gyi 'dab ma drug la shar
NK024(ya)001:15523: du chos nyid rnam dag gi sngags brjod cing tshom
NK024(ya)001:15524: bu bkod pa ni sh+aaka thub /
NK024(ya)001:15525: shar lhor nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags dang tshom bu ni rnam snang /
NK024(ya)001:15526: lho nub tu 'khyil pa'i sngags dang tshom bu ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK024(ya)001:15527: nub tu shugs ldan 'od kyi sngags brjod cing tshom bu ni rin 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:15528: nub byang du ye shes skar mad'i sngags brjod cing tshom bu ni don grub /
NK024(ya)001:15529: byang shar du dbang sgyur 'khor lo'i sngags dang tshom bu ni phyag rdor te /
NK024(ya)001:15530: kri ya don gyi lha drug go //
NK024(ya)001:15531: sta gon gyi lha mchod pa'i phyir mthar mchod pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs pa yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:15532: de ltar dam tshig pa bskyed tshar ma thag /
NK024(ya)001:15533: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgyas snyan gsan dbab cing /
NK024(ya)001:15534: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam bud+d+ha d+harma sam g+ha a
NK024(ya)001:15535: sa me tri sa me ma h+aa sa ma ye
NK024(ya)001:15537: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bi d+ya d+h+aa
NK024(ya)001:15538: ra p+au tsa ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:15540: pad+ma +aa sa na ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15541: zhes gdan phul te bzhugs par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:15542: 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin mchod pa byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:15543: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK024(ya)001:15544: zhes sogs sngags rgyar bcas te dbul lo //'og nas 'byung ba'i bstod pa rgyas pa'am /
NK024(ya)001:15545: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:15547: dkyil 'khor gyi lha de rnams kyi sngags kyang ci
NK024(ya)001:15548: rigs par bzlas pa'i mthar mchod bstod bsdus pa phul
NK024(ya)001:15549: zhing / yig brgya lan gsum gyis lhag chad bkang ste /
NK024(ya)001:15550: h+aum badz+ra muhzhesa sngags rgyar bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:15551: sta gon gyi lha gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:15552: rgyud sde 'og ma 'di rnams la nam mkhar mi 'degs pa'i lugs kyang 'dug pa bzhin byas so //
NK024(ya)001:15553: mchod rdzas dang tshom bu bsdu'o //
NK024(ya)001:15554: de ltar lha sta gon 'di phyag len 'jug pa
NK024(ya)001:15555: bde ba'i phyir byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:15556: bya ba zin ma thag bgyis na dkyil 'khor bri
NK024(ya)001:15557: ba sogs la mi gnod pa'i khyad par shin tu
NK024(ya)001:15558: che'o // de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:15560: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa lte ba ser dkar sngo ba gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:15561: 'dab drug pa lte ba dkar dmar mthing gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:15562: nang du 'khor lo ser po rtsibs bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:15563: de'i phyir pad+ma dmar po 'dab bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:15564: de'i phyir sngon po rgya gram can gsum mo //
NK024(ya)001:15565: sgo rta babs sogs sbyi dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:15566: rgyas par lha nyer bdun ma byed na lha snam yang bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15567: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyag len bzhin bri ba la /
NK024(ya)001:15568: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum gyi lte ba rim bzhin ser dkar sngo /
NK024(ya)001:15569: yang lte ba ser po 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:15570: lte ba dmar po pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:15571: lte ba sngon po rdo rje rgya gram can gsum la lha snam dang bcas pa /
NK024(ya)001:15572: yang 'dab drug pa lte ba dkar dmar mthing gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:15573: dkyil 'khor dgu po thams cad la rtsig pa phan spyi dang 'dra zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15574: rtsig pa'i kha dog 'og gi dkyil chog skabs bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:15590: me ri sogs spyi ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:15591: lha gnas su tshon spungs bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15592: gnyis pa mchod pa bsham pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:15595: mchod pa rnam lnga dang gtor ma cha gsum bsham /
NK024(ya)001:15602: dkyil 'khor so so'i mthar mtshams 'dzin nas bzung chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:15603: 'di man chod gsang sngags kho na yin phyir dkon
NK024(ya)001:15604: mchog sbyi gtor zhes ming mi 'dogs par 'das gtor
NK024(ya)001:15605: dkar zlum mtheb skyus bskor ba dkar gsum mngar gsum
NK024(ya)001:15606: gyis brgyan pa bku bag can te sha chang dang
NK024(ya)001:15607: ma 'dres pa'i gtsang spra dang ldan pa bsham par
NK024(ya)001:15608: bya'o // cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor ma bsdus na
NK024(ya)001:15609: mchod pa rnams gso zhing cha gsum gyi gtor ma
NK024(ya)001:15610: bya'o // gsar du bsham / bsdus zin na cha gsum gyi gtor ma bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:15611: gzhan yang rtsa ba nas gsungs pa ltar dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:15612: gyi mtha' mar mda' brgyad me long dang dar tshon
NK024(ya)001:15613: gyis brgyan pa / ral gri dang phur bu brgyad dam bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:15614: de rnams kyi bar tshon skud sna lngas phyag len
NK024(ya)001:15615: ltar 'brel shing lha gnas so sor lha tsaka kyang
NK024(ya)001:15616: btsugs / dkyil 'khor dgu po gang bde'i dbus su
NK024(ya)001:15617: many+dzi'i khar bum pa bcud ldan mgul chings kha dog
NK024(ya)001:15618: lnga'am gang mdzes 'khor lo'i mtshan ma gdags pa kha
NK024(ya)001:15619: rgyan dung chos rdor gzungs dang bcas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15620: slob dpon gyi mdun du las bum gong bzhin la
NK024(ya)001:15621: bum dar dkar ljang gang rigs can rdzas ldan phur
NK024(ya)001:15622: bu'i mtshan ma can yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:15623: gzhan yang sngon 'gro'i gtor ma gnyis dang yungs thun
NK024(ya)001:15624: gu gul sol me man+dala me tog dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:15625: dang / dbang rdzas rnams kyang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:15626: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gsum pa lha tshogs bskyed pa
NK024(ya)001:15627: ni bdag mdun bum gsum gyi cho ga'i skabs su
NK024(ya)001:15628: ston la / bzhi pa rab gnas ni /
NK024(ya)001:15632: slob dpon gyis rdor dril dang bcas te rten 'brel
NK024(ya)001:15633: snying po bzla zhing gnas khang dkyil 'khor mchod rdzas
NK024(ya)001:15634: thams cad la me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:15635: lnga pa chog gzhung ni bdag mdun bum gsum gyi cho ga ste /
NK024(ya)001:15637: lha bum du bzlas pa tshar ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:15638: las bum du khams gsum rnam rgyal dkar ljang phyag gnyis phur bu can du bskyed de /
NK024(ya)001:15639: tree lokya bi dz+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:15640: zhes bzlas te dang po khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:15641: de nas su si ti ka ra ye s+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15642: zhes pas mi tshugs shing nye reg 'thor 'thung bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15643: de nas bum chu phyogs bcur gtor zhing zhes 'byung
NK024(ya)001:15644: ba dong sprugs sogs las kyang thog mar bsang chu
NK024(ya)001:15645: brlab cing des bsang sbyang bya bar bshad pas /
NK024(ya)001:15646: las bum gyi bsang chu'i dod byas pa yin pas
NK024(ya)001:15647: 'dir sgrub cing rnam bum ni bdag bskyed tshar nas
NK024(ya)001:15648: sgrub pa de'o // de'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:15650: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du b+h+r+aum las
NK024(ya)001:15651: rin po che'i bum pa tshad dang mtshan nyid thams
NK024(ya)001:15652: cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang gzhal yas khang par
NK024(ya)001:15653: gyur pa'i dbus pad+ma dang nyi ma'i steng du h+aum
NK024(ya)001:15654: dkar ljang las khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal sku
NK024(ya)001:15655: mdog dkar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis kyis phur bu
NK024(ya)001:15656: 'dril ba khro bo'i chas dang ldan pa'i spyi bor
NK024(ya)001:15660: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:15661: kro ta r+aa dza tree lo kya bi dz+aa ya ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:15662: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrogs shing //
NK024(ya)001:15663: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:15664: dngos grub ma lus stsol ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:15665: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:15666: tree lokya bi dz+aa ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:15667: ces brgya rtsa bzlas mthar gong bzhin mchod bstod byas
NK024(ya)001:15668: la 'od du zhu ste bum pa'i chur gyur par
NK024(ya)001:15669: bsam mo // de nas bum chus rang nyid khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:15670: su si ti ka ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15671: zhes gnas rnams su nye reg dang 'thor 'thung bya /
NK024(ya)001:15672: de nas phyogs bcur gtor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15674: stong gsum kun tu dri mchog 'byung gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:15675: spos dang sman sbyar chu gtsang rgyal ba'i khrus //
NK024(ya)001:15676: ye shes sprin phung mkha' la char 'bebs pa //
NK024(ya)001:15677: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:15678: shud+d+he shud+d+he shwa d+ha na ye s+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15679: zhes bzlas la gnas khang dang dkyil 'khor mchod rdzas thams cad la gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:15680: mchod pa rnams gsum rgyal gyi sngags kyis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:15682: stong pa'i ngang las zhes sogs dkyil 'khor snga ma
NK024(ya)001:15683: rnams kyi lugs ltar sngags rgyas byin gyis brlabs shing
NK024(ya)001:15684: rol mo'i sngags dang mchod pa'i sprin gyi gzungs 'don
NK024(ya)001:15685: pa'i bar ro // skyabs sems kyi sngon du mkhyen
NK024(ya)001:15686: par gsol te sdig pa bshags pa dang skyabs su
NK024(ya)001:15687: pa'i bar ro // 'gro ba ni / rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:15690: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:15691: dus 'di nas bzung ste thog ma ma mchis pa'i bar du mi dge ba'i las bgyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15693: bgyis pa la rjes su yi rangs pa thams cad mthol lo bshags so //
NK024(ya)001:15694: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK024(ya)001:15695: bdag gi lus 'bul gyi bzhes su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:15699: bsod nams dam pa'i dpal gyi zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15700: yon tan thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK024(ya)001:15701: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag /'gro ba yongs kyi dpal mgon /
NK024(ya)001:15702: mchod gnas bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK024(ya)001:15703: cho ga snga ma rnams las 'byung ba bzhin spyi 'gro'i skyabs sems dang tshad med bzhi yang bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15704: sngon 'gro gtor ma dang po gsum rgyal gyis bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:15705: +aahh+aum lan gsum gyi byin gyis brlabs te h+aum mdzad
NK024(ya)001:15706: kyi phyag rgya bcas la las kyi khro bo bdud
NK024(ya)001:15707: rtsi 'khyil ba'i nga rgyal bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:15708: glan ston gyis badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta a mra ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:15709: ces bdud rtsi 'khyil ba sku mdog ljang gu phyag
NK024(ya)001:15710: g.yas rdo rje rgya gram bsnams pas dgra bgegs thams
NK024(ya)001:15711: cad skrod pa / g.yon gyi dril bu'i sgras gdon
NK024(ya)001:15712: bgegs thams cad dkyil 'khor chen po'i mtshams kyi nang
NK024(ya)001:15713: na 'dug sa med par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:15716: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15717: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15718: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:15719: gsang sngags dang rig sngags dang gzungs sngags dang snying po dang phyag rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:15720: lha dang drang srong rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15721: yum chen mo dang sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15722: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK024(ya)001:15727: phyag na rdo rje la sogs pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15728: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis mchod pa dang
NK024(ya)001:15729: cho ga la bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang log
NK024(ya)001:15730: 'dren glog ltar g.yo zhing rlung ltar 'tshubs pa /
NK024(ya)001:15736: log 'dren sna yo la sogs pa thams cad gtor
NK024(ya)001:15737: ma 'dis tshim par gyis la 'dir ma gnas par
NK024(ya)001:15738: dengs shig / rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu 'khrol bas /
NK024(ya)001:15740: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK024(ya)001:15741: mngag gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:15742: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:15743: bgegs kyi sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK024(ya)001:15745: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15746: na mahs man+ta badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15747: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK024(ya)001:15749: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nam /
NK024(ya)001:15750: na mo badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15751: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK024(ya)001:15753: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra nam /
NK024(ya)001:15754: na mo badz+ra kro d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15755: ma h+aa damsh+tota ka ta b+he ra w+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15756: a si mu sa la pa ra shu p+aa sha ha bud+d+h+aa s+t+wa ya /
NK024(ya)001:15757: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:15768: bi s+pho ta ya bi s+pho ta ya /
NK024(ya)001:15771: ma h+aa ga na pa ti dzi wi ta an+ta ka r+aa ya s+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15772: zhes bzlas te gu gul bdug cing yugs kar gyis brab la bskrad de mtshams bcad do //
NK024(ya)001:15777: ta th+aa ga to b+ha wa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15778: badz+roda b+hi ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:15779: zhes brjod pas rigs gsum 'khor dang bcas pa dmigs la /
NK024(ya)001:15780: zhes gsungs pa'i don rgyun bshags kyi dod yin pas
NK024(ya)001:15781: mdun gyi nam mkhar sku'i lha bcom ldan 'das rnam
NK024(ya)001:15782: par snang mdzad / gsung gi lha snang ba mtha' yas /
NK024(ya)001:15783: thugs kyi lha mi bskyod pa /
NK024(ya)001:15785: gzhan yang rigs gsum mgon po sogs de bzhin gshegs
NK024(ya)001:15786: pa sras dang bcas pa mngon sum du dmigs te
NK024(ya)001:15788: dzi na dzika sogs sngags rnams brjod cig thal mo
NK024(ya)001:15789: sbyar te tshig don dran pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang
NK024(ya)001:15791: 'jig rten dag gi phyogs kun nas //
NK024(ya)001:15792: de bzhin gshegs pa gang bzhugs dang //
NK024(ya)001:15793: dgra bcom byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK024(ya)001:15794: bdag gi ma 'tshal sdig bgyis dang //
NK024(ya)001:15795: gang yang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:15796: rjes su yi rangs bgyis la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:15797: bag med pa ni phra mo yang //
NK024(ya)001:15798: lus ngag yid kyis bgyis pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:15799: yang dang yang du mthol zhing bshags //
NK024(ya)001:15800: slan chad de ltar yongs mi bgyid //
NK024(ya)001:15801: bdag gi mi dge bgyis pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:15802: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyis mkhyen pa ltar //
NK024(ya)001:15803: bdag kyang de ltar dam baca'o //
NK024(ya)001:15804: srog chags sdug bsngal zhi bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:15805: ji srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK024(ya)001:15806: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun la //
NK024(ya)001:15807: gus pas yang dag skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:15808: deng nas mchog gi sa bon gang //
NK024(ya)001:15809: thar pa bdud rtsi'i 'bras bu smin //
NK024(ya)001:15810: shin tu bsgoms pas mchog gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:15811: dngos grub phyir ni de bskyed do //
NK024(ya)001:15812: dge ba'i las rnams gang dag kun //'di dang gzhan du bsags rnams kyi //
NK024(ya)001:15813: chos kyi longs spyod sna tshogs la //
NK024(ya)001:15814: mnyam par bzhag pas yi rang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:15815: sngon gyi rgyal ba sras bcas kyis //
NK024(ya)001:15816: smon lam ji ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK024(ya)001:15817: bdag kyang dge ba kun rtogs nas //
NK024(ya)001:15818: de bzhin du ni smon lam 'debs //'phags pa rnams kyis rjes dgongs te //
NK024(ya)001:15819: mgon ma mchis pa bdag myur du //
NK024(ya)001:15820: sangs rgyas 'grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:15822: sa lugs sogs bya rgyud la bdag bskyed dngos bstan ma bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:15823: 'dir bya rgyud kho na'i skabs ma yin cing /
NK024(ya)001:15824: spyir bla med kyi dkyil 'khor khongs su bsdus pa'i
NK024(ya)001:15825: phyir theg pa gong mas 'og ma zil gyis gnon
NK024(ya)001:15826: pa'i dgongs pa 'di rnam pa thams cad du dran
NK024(ya)001:15827: par bya ba gnad du che ba yod do //
NK024(ya)001:15829: khams lugs su cho ga'i skabs bdag mdun bum gsum gyi lha rnam 'joms rigs lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:15831: rigs gsum mgon po ste gtso 'khor dgu la /
NK024(ya)001:15834: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad sgo ba dang bcas pa kho na kha bsgyur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15835: dbang gi lha zur lugs ltar mdzad 'dug pa rgya mgo hor mjug ltar snang bas /
NK024(ya)001:15836: 'dir zur lugs ltar mdun bskyed la bris pa'i dkyil 'khor dang mthun pa'i sgom tshul /
NK024(ya)001:15837: bum bskyed la rnam bum gyi bskur tshig gi shugs bstan ltar sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:15839: bdag bskyed la ngang sgom ltar rang sku'i lha rnam
NK024(ya)001:15840: snang du bskyed pa'i gnas gsum du rigs gsum mgon
NK024(ya)001:15841: po bsgoms pas / gsung gi lha spyan ras gzigs kyi rigs bdag dang /
NK024(ya)001:15842: thugs kyi lha phyag rdor dang gnyis med du shes
NK024(ya)001:15843: pa sogs gzhung don dang mthun par rtogs pa 'di
NK024(ya)001:15844: ltar ro // swa b+h+aa was stong par sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:15845: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che'i gzhal
NK024(ya)001:15846: yas khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:15847: dbus su / pad zla'i gdan la rang nyid rnam
NK024(ya)001:15848: snang dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis mnyam gzhag gi
NK024(ya)001:15849: phyag rgya can longs spyod rdzogs sku dar dang rin
NK024(ya)001:15850: po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i spyi bor pad zla'i
NK024(ya)001:15851: steng du m+aum las 'jam dbyangs ser po zhal gcig
NK024(ya)001:15852: phyag gnyis g.yas ral gri dang g.yon ut+pala gyi steng
NK024(ya)001:15854: mgrin par pad zla'i steng du spyan ras gzigs dkar
NK024(ya)001:15855: po zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis thal sbyar
NK024(ya)001:15856: / g.yas 'og mas shel phreng dang g.yon 'og mas pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:15857: snang ba mtha' yas kyi rigs bdag can /
NK024(ya)001:15858: snying khar pad zla'i steng du phyag na rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:15859: sngon po rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub khro tshul can
NK024(ya)001:15860: / thams cad kyang dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa'i spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:15864: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa ma ya dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra ar+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:15865: lha so so'i mtshan bstod 'og nas 'byung ba'am spyi bstod kyis bstod la /
NK024(ya)001:15866: rnam snang la bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:15867: 'jam dbyangs la w+aa g+ai shwa ri /
NK024(ya)001:15868: spyan ras gzigs la ma ni /
NK024(ya)001:15869: phyag rdor la badz+ra p+aa ni bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:15870: mchod bstod gong ltar byas la bdag bskyed bsdu'o //
NK024(ya)001:15872: rnam bum gsum rgyal gyi sngags kyis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:15874: stong pa'i ngang las pad zla'i steng du b+h+aum las
NK024(ya)001:15875: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs
NK024(ya)001:15876: su rdzogs pa'i nang du pad zla'i gdan lnga'i dbus
NK024(ya)001:15877: su rnam snang dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis ting
NK024(ya)001:15879: mdun du 'od dpag med sprul sku mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:15880: g.yas su 'jam dbyangs ser po ral gri glegs bam can /
NK024(ya)001:15881: rgyab tu spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis thal sbyar /
NK024(ya)001:15882: g.yas 'og ma shel phreng dang g.yon pad dkar 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15883: g.yon du phyag rdor khro tshul rdo rje sdigs mdzub can /
NK024(ya)001:15884: rnam snang dang rigs gsum dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa'i spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:15886: thugs kar h+aum sngon pos mtshan pa /
NK024(ya)001:15888: rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra a r+g+ham sogs kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:15889: spyi dang bye brag gi bstod pas bstod la //
NK024(ya)001:15891: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer gzungs thag la
NK024(ya)001:15892: 'khril te song ba bum nang gi lha la phog
NK024(ya)001:15894: don gnyis byas tshur 'dus rgyal ba rnams kyi zag
NK024(ya)001:15895: med ye shes kyi bdud rtsi bsdus bdag la thim
NK024(ya)001:15896: / slar yang bdud rtsi gzungs thag la 'khril te
NK024(ya)001:15897: song ba'i rkyen gyis bum nang gi lha'i sku'i cha
NK024(ya)001:15898: las bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang zhing
NK024(ya)001:15899: / / de'i 'od zer gyis sems can gyi sdig sgrib dag par bsam zhing /
NK024(ya)001:15900: bdag bskyed kyi sngags rnams kyi steng 'od dpag med la a mi de wa a /
NK024(ya)001:15901: zhes pa bsnan te so sor brgya rtsa re bzlas
NK024(ya)001:15902: mthar mchod bstod dang yig brgyas lhag chad bkang ste
NK024(ya)001:15903: / +aahh+aum zhes dung chos kyi mchod yon phul ba'i
NK024(ya)001:15904: rkyen gyi ye shes pa gshegs shing dam tshig pa
NK024(ya)001:15905: bum chur gyur par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:15907: de nas rang nyid khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:15908: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sngon du song bas bdud rnam dag bya /
NK024(ya)001:15909: swa b+h+aa was bdag dang snang ba stong par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:15910: de'i ngang las mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor rnams rim pa bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:15911: zhes gsungs pa'i don khrus dang bdun rnam dag skyabs sems sogs gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:15912: 'dir dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa sgrub tshul la /
NK024(ya)001:15913: gsum pa mdun bskyed sgrub pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:15914: dkyil 'khor rnams gsum rgyal gyi sngags chus bsang /
NK024(ya)001:15916: stong pa'i ngang las 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri rab
NK024(ya)001:15917: dang bcas pa'i steng du rdo rje'i gur khang ye
NK024(ya)001:15918: shes kyi me 'bar ba yangs shing rgya che ba
NK024(ya)001:15919: rnams kyi nang du b+h+r+aum las rin po che sna
NK024(ya)001:15920: tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo
NK024(ya)001:15921: bzhi pa rgyan rta babs dang bcas pa mtshan nyid
NK024(ya)001:15922: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang po
NK024(ya)001:15924: bdun pa rnams rtsig pa nang nas ser dkar dmar ljang sngo ba /
NK024(ya)001:15927: brgyad pa rnams nang nas dkar ser dmar ljang sngo ba /
NK024(ya)001:15930: dgu pa rnams nang nas mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba'i mdog can no //
NK024(ya)001:15931: dkyil 'khor dang po'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la /
NK024(ya)001:15932: m+aum las 'jam dpal ser po g.yas ral gri g.yon ut+pala 'dzin pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:15933: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:15934: h+r+aih las spyan ras gzigs dkar po phyag dang po
NK024(ya)001:15936: 'og ma gnyis shel phreng dang pad dkar 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15937: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:15938: h+aum las phyag na rdo rje g.yas rdo rje dang
NK024(ya)001:15940: dkyil 'khor gsum ga'i shar gyi pad 'dab la h+aum las sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15941: lho'i pad 'dab la tram las phreng ba ma ser mo me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15942: nub kyi pad 'dab la h+r+aihls glu ma dmar mo pi wam 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15943: byang gi pad 'dab la +aahls gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:15945: lha bco lnga pa steng gi dbus su rnam snang /
NK024(ya)001:15948: g.yon du khro bo gshin rje gshed /
NK024(ya)001:15949: rgyab tu pho nya rnon po /
NK024(ya)001:15950: bar gyi dbus su 'od dpag med /
NK024(ya)001:15953: g.yon du khro bo rta mgrin /
NK024(ya)001:15954: rgyab tu pho nya rdo rje phur bu'o //'og gi dbus su rdo rje sems dpa'/
NK024(ya)001:15955: mdun du kun tu bzang mo //
NK024(ya)001:15956: g.yas su phyag na rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:15958: rgyab tu pho nya rdo rje khro bo //
NK024(ya)001:15959: lha nyer bdun du byed na lha snam la khro bo bcu /
NK024(ya)001:15960: gra bzhir bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad do //
NK024(ya)001:15961: yang lha snam la skal bzang bcu drug dgod pa'am gang mos su bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:15962: zhes gsungs pa'i don rnams man ngag bzhin 'di man chod du sdebs so //
NK024(ya)001:15963: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa sku'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su
NK024(ya)001:15964: m+aum las 'jam dpal ser po ral gri dang glegs
NK024(ya)001:15965: bam 'dzin pa'i spyi bor las rigs kyi bdag po
NK024(ya)001:15966: rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK024(ya)001:15967: ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:15968: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du lam las spyan ma dkar mo sbyan 'bras 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15969: lho'i rtsibs la m+aum las 'jam dbyangs ser po ral gri dang glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15970: nub kyi rtsibs la d+h+r+ai las rdo rje rnon po dkar po phur bu sgril pa /
NK024(ya)001:15971: byang gi rtsibs la ya las khro bo gshin rje
NK024(ya)001:15972: gshed smug nag be con dang sdig gadzuba mdzad pa'o
NK024(ya)001:15973: // khor yug la mgron thabs kyi lha lha mo dpal dkar mo pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15974: mdzod sprul ma dkar mo nor bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15975: tshangs pa ser po gdong bzhi pa 'khor lo 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:15976: dkyil 'khor lnga pa gsung gi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK024(ya)001:15977: su pad zla'i gdan la h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar
NK024(ya)001:15978: po zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis thal sbyar
NK024(ya)001:15979: / 'og ma gnyis kyis shel phreng dang pad dkar
NK024(ya)001:15980: 'dzin pa'i dbu gtsug tu rigs kyi bdag po 'od
NK024(ya)001:15981: dpag med dmar po sprul sku'i cha byad can ting
NK024(ya)001:15982: nge 'dzin gyi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:15983: pad 'dab bzhi'i shar du pam las gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:15984: lhor h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi thal sbyar shel phreng pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15985: nub tu h+r+aihls rta mgrin dmar po rta mgo can ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15986: byang du h+aum las rdo rje phur bu dmar po phur bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:15987: khor yug la mgron thabs kyi lha grags ldan ma dkar mo pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15988: lu gu rgyud ma ser mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:15989: lha chen ma h+aa de ba dmar po rtse gsum 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:15991: lnga pa gnyis kyi lha snam la h+aum bcu las shar stod du h+aum mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:15995: nub smad du stobs po che /
NK024(ya)001:15998: lho nub tu mi g.yo ba /
NK024(ya)001:15999: nub byang du gzhan gyis mi thub /
NK024(ya)001:16000: byang shar du khams gsum rnam rgyal te bcu po
NK024(ya)001:16001: thams cad kyang g.yas rdo rje rtse lnga dang g.yon
NK024(ya)001:16002: sdigs mdzub can khro bo'i rgyan chas brjid pa nyi
NK024(ya)001:16003: ma'i gdan la brkyang bskum gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16004: dkyil 'khor gnyis ka'i mtshams kyi gru chad bzhir tram brgyad las bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad ni /
NK024(ya)001:16005: shar lhor dus ldan ma dkar mo dpal be bsnams pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16006: pad+ma can dkar mo 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16007: lho nub tu 'jigs bral ma sngon mo pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:16008: 'od ldan ma sngon mo rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16009: nub byang du mdangs can ma dmar mo gdugs 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16010: dri med ma dmar mo bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16011: byang shar du rgyal gdung ma ljang gu dug bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:16012: yid bzang ma ljang gu gser nya 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16013: dkyil 'khor drug pa thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dbus
NK024(ya)001:16014: su pad zla'i gdan la h+aum las phyag na rdo
NK024(ya)001:16015: rje sngon po rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub khro tshul
NK024(ya)001:16016: can gyi spyi bor h+aum las rigs bdag thugs mchog
NK024(ya)001:16017: mi bskyod pa sngon po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can
NK024(ya)001:16018: / phyogs kyi rwa bzhi'i shar du m+aum las kun
NK024(ya)001:16019: tu bzang mo sngon mo rdo rje rtse gsum dang
NK024(ya)001:16021: lhor h+aum las phyag rdor sngon po rdo rje sdigs mdzub khro tshul can /
NK024(ya)001:16022: nub tu h+aum las rdo rje khro bo dkar ser rdo rje dang zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16023: byang du h+aum las bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang gu rgya gram dang bum pa bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:16024: khor yug la mgron thabs kyi lha stobs chen ma nag mo rdo rje rtse gcig pa /
NK024(ya)001:16025: rnam rgyal ma dkar mo 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16026: lha chen khyab 'jug mthing ga 'khor lo 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16027: lha snam la bcu drug las /
NK024(ya)001:16028: shar du byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bar 'gro dkar po ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16029: kun bzang dkar po rin chen 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16030: zla 'od dkar po zla ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16031: bzang skyong dkar po bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16032: lhor d+r+wa ba can sngon po 'od zer 'gyed pa /
NK024(ya)001:16033: nam mkha' mdzod sngon po rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16034: nam mkha'i snying po sngon po rdo rje rtse gsum pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16035: 'od dpag med sngon po rin chen 'bar ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16036: nub tu mya ngan kun 'joms dmar po ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16037: ye shes tog dmar po rin po che'i tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16038: spobs pa brtsegs dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16039: blo gros mi zad pa dmar po glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16040: byang du byams pa ljang gu klu shing dang spyi blugs 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16041: spos kyi glang po ljang gu dung dkar 'bud pa /
NK024(ya)001:16042: ngan song kun 'dren ljang gu lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16043: don kun grub byed ljang gu rgya gram 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16044: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:16045: m+aum las 'jam dbyangs ser po ral gri glegs bam
NK024(ya)001:16046: 'dzin pa / dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i dbus su pad
NK024(ya)001:16047: zla'i gdan la h+r+aihls spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal
NK024(ya)001:16048: gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis thal sbyar dang 'og
NK024(ya)001:16049: ma gnyis shel phreng dang pad dkar 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:16050: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i dbus su pad zla'i gdan la
NK024(ya)001:16051: h+aum las phyag na rdo rje sngon po g.yas rdo
NK024(ya)001:16052: rje dang g.yon sdigs mdzub mdzad pa khro tshul can
NK024(ya)001:16053: no // dkyil 'khor de gsum gyi phyi rol gyi
NK024(ya)001:16054: pad 'dab drug la shar du a las sbyang ba'i
NK024(ya)001:16055: lha sh+aakya thub pa dkar po sprul sku'i cha byad
NK024(ya)001:16056: can phyag gnyis thugs kar thal mo khong stong du
NK024(ya)001:16057: sbyar ba'i nang du +aahdakara po can /
NK024(ya)001:16058: shar lhor kham las spel ba'i lha rnam snang ser
NK024(ya)001:16059: po mdzod spur rin chen sgrom bu'i phyag rgya kham
NK024(ya)001:16060: sngon po can / lho nub tu dzahls sgyur ba'i
NK024(ya)001:16061: lha bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang sngon mgrin par mthe
NK024(ya)001:16062: bong bsnol te thal mo lhag ma rnams kha phyir
NK024(ya)001:16063: gyed par dzah dmar po can /
NK024(ya)001:16064: nub tu tram las thob pa'i lha rin chen 'byung
NK024(ya)001:16065: ldan ser po g.yon mdzub mo thugs kar sgreng ba
NK024(ya)001:16066: / g.yas mchog sbyin la tram ser po can /
NK024(ya)001:16067: nub byang du ha las tshims pa'i lha don yod
NK024(ya)001:16068: grub pa ljang gu g.yas khu tshur dang g.yon mchog
NK024(ya)001:16069: sbyin 'degs pa ha ljang gu can /
NK024(ya)001:16070: byang shar du dzahls dbang du byed pa'i lha phyag
NK024(ya)001:16071: na rdo rje sngon po phyag gnyis spyi bor sor
NK024(ya)001:16072: mo nang du bsnol ba dzahdamara po can no //
NK024(ya)001:16073: lha tshogs de dag kyang longs sku rnams dar dang
NK024(ya)001:16074: rin po che'i rgyan can sprul sku rnams chags bral
NK024(ya)001:16076: khro bo rnams stag lpags kyi sham thabs sprul gyis brgyan pa me 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16077: lha tshogs thams cad kyi spyi bor dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:16080: de las 'od zer 'phros pas rang bzhin gyi gnas
NK024(ya)001:16081: nas rang 'dra'i ye shes pa badz+ra sa ma ya
NK024(ya)001:16085: 'phags pa'i tshogs rnams thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:16086: mkhyen pa'i ye shes gzigs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:16089: gza' skar thams cad bkra shis /
NK024(ya)001:16090: dgra bcom thams cad zag pa zad /
NK024(ya)001:16091: sangs rgyas thams cad rdzu 'phrul che ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK024(ya)001:16092: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas pa sbyan 'dren phyag 'tshal bas gshegs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:16094: spos btul zhing rdor dril dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:16096: stobs bcu rtsal mnga' mi yi seng ge gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:16097: gti mug mun sel 'jig rten sgron ma gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:16098: nyon mongs nad sel sman pa'i rgyal po gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:16099: bdud bzhi 'joms mdzad thar pa'i lam ston gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:16100: dbang mchog rgyal po 'dir spyon phrin las mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:16102: bud+d+h+aa d+harma sam g+ha a sa me tri sa ma ma h+aa sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16103: zhes mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te /
NK024(ya)001:16104: dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgo dbye ni /
NK024(ya)001:16106: phyogs bcu rgyal yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16107: rin chen lhun grub gzhan yas khang //
NK024(ya)001:16108: dbye sdom rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK024(ya)001:16109: sri zhu'i tshul du sgo dabye'o //
NK024(ya)001:16110: badz+ra s+pho ta ga ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16111: zhes sgo phye la nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i lha rnams la mchod yon 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:16113: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:16114: tshur gshegs 'dir ni bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16115: bdag gi mchod yon bzhes nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:16116: thugs la dgongs shing gnang bar mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:16117: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+h+aa ra
NK024(ya)001:16118: p+au tsa ga ga na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:16121: rin chen ye shes gzhal yas nas //
NK024(ya)001:16122: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK024(ya)001:16123: bde gshegs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //'gro ba'i don du bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16124: pad+ma +aa sa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16125: zhes gdan so sor bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:16126: de nas mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:16127: mar me dang bdug spos rnams spar la thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:16129: rab 'byams rgya mtsho dpag med na //
NK024(ya)001:16130: mchod yon ji snyed yod pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16131: bdag gis gus par bshams pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:16132: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul /
NK024(ya)001:16133: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16134: gtsang zhig gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:16135: lha rdzas dam pa'i me tog 'di //
NK024(ya)001:16136: rgyal ba sras dang bcas la 'bul //'gro ba'i don du bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16137: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe pra t+aits+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16138: gtsang zhing lha rdzas dam pa'i bdug spos 'di /
NK024(ya)001:16139: rgyal ba 'gro ba'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa
NK024(ya)001:16140: pa ri w+aa ra d+h+aum pe gtsang zhing lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:16142: rgyal ba 'gro ba'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa
NK024(ya)001:16143: pa ri w+aa ra +aa lo ke gtsang zhing lha
NK024(ya)001:16145: rgyal ba 'gro ba'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa
NK024(ya)001:16146: pa ri w+aa ra gan+d+he gtsang zhing lha rdzas dam
NK024(ya)001:16148: rgyal ba 'gro ba'i sarba ta th+aa ta sa pa
NK024(ya)001:16149: ri w+aa ra nee wi d+ya gtsang zhing lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:16151: rgyal ba 'gro ba'i sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa
NK024(ya)001:16152: pa ri w+aa ra shap+da pra t+aitsh+tsha ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:16153: / dril bu rgyun chags su dkrol zhing /
NK024(ya)001:16154: d+harma ra ni ta sogs rol mo'i sngags kyis dbul lo //
NK024(ya)001:16156: 'dir dkyil 'khor la dngos su thub dbang med kyang /
NK024(ya)001:16157: bstan pa'i bdag po yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:16158: thog mar sangs rgyas dang chos la bstod pa sngon du gtong ba'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:16160: yon tan rin chen mang po'i tshogs mnga' zhing //
NK024(ya)001:16161: mtshan rabs ye shes yongs su dag pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:16162: gser gyi mdog can lha dang mis mchod pa //
NK024(ya)001:16163: bcom ldan lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:16164: dam chos nyi ma'i 'od zer stong 'phro bas //
NK024(ya)001:16165: skye bo srid pa'i chu bo sgrol bar mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:16166: thar pa'i lam ston 'dren pa'i theg skas mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16167: ma lus skems pa'i gtso la bde gshegs sras po'i kun mkhyen mi ldog sgrol //
NK024(ya)001:16168: thugs rje chen pos yid ni rangs gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:16169: blo can bye bar gyur pa de dag la //
NK024(ya)001:16170: rgyun mi chad par spyi bos rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:16171: mi gdung mi g.yo mnyam gzhag kyang //
NK024(ya)001:16172: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen ltar //
NK024(ya)001:16173: bsam pa tsam gyis gnas su phyin //
NK024(ya)001:16174: bltas pa tsam gyis grub par mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:16175: snang mdzad khyod la bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas ni //
NK024(ya)001:16176: sngon du bskal pa grangs med nas //'khor ba'i skyon rnams sel mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16177: las dang nyon mongs sa bon las //
NK024(ya)001:16178: dgongs nas srid pa stongs mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16179: snang mtha' yas la bcom ldan mi bskyod rdo rje ni //'jig rten 'das pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK024(ya)001:16180: lta ba rtog pa rnam bsal te //
NK024(ya)001:16182: rkyen dus ldan par byin gyis brlabs //
NK024(ya)001:16183: mi bskyod pa la dpal gyi dam pa 'jam dbyangs dpal //
NK024(ya)001:16184: ye shes sku mdzes gsung snyan zhing //
NK024(ya)001:16185: mthong thos kun dang yid mthun pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16186: gzhon nur gyur la shes rab thugs rje che ba'i mtshan //
NK024(ya)001:16187: brgya phrag bcu yi spyan gyis gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:16188: sems can kun kyi dpung dang skyabs //
NK024(ya)001:16189: rtag par brtse la rig pa'i rgyal po grub pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16190: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK024(ya)001:16192: rdo rje 'dzin la rigs kyi yum mchog sangs rgyas spyan //
NK024(ya)001:16194: phyag na thor tshugs rgyan gyis spras //
NK024(ya)001:16195: sangs rgyas mkha' 'gror rigs kyi yum chen gos dkar mo //
NK024(ya)001:16198: pad+ma mkha' 'gror rigs kyi yum chen m+aa ma k+ai //
NK024(ya)001:16200: phyag na rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16201: rdo rje mkha' 'gror dpal gyi lha mo sku mdog dkar //
NK024(ya)001:16202: chu skyes dkar po phyag na bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16203: grags ldan ma ni shel ltar dkar //'dam skyes pad+ma phyag na mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:16204: stobs chen mo ni mig sman mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16205: phyag na rdo rje rtse gcig go //
NK024(ya)001:16206: mdzod sprul ma ni zla ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:16207: phyag gis yid bzhin nor bu 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:16208: lu gu rgyud ma gser gyi mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16210: rnam par rgyal ma kun+da'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16212: gshin rje gshed po smug nag 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:16213: be con dbyug to klad la 'phyar //
NK024(ya)001:16214: khro bo'i rgyal po rta mgrin dmar //
NK024(ya)001:16216: khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang //
NK024(ya)001:16217: pho nya skra can ba mo'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16218: pho nya phur bu le brgan mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16219: rdo rje phur bu drag tu bsgril //
NK024(ya)001:16220: pho nya lcags kyu sngo zhing nag /
NK024(ya)001:16221: lcags kyus dbang du sdud pa'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:16222: pad+ma'i mdangs can seng ge chibs //
NK024(ya)001:16223: dmar po pad+ma rgyas pa can //
NK024(ya)001:16224: lha chen dmar po rtse gsum ste //
NK024(ya)001:16226: mthu stobs dbang phyug phun tshogs pa'i //'khor dang bcas la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:16230: de dag gi sngags kyang rim pa bzhin du /
NK024(ya)001:16232: bee ro tsa na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16233: a mi de ba h+r+aihs+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16234: badz+ra a k+sho b+h+yahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16235: many+dzu sh+r+ai ku m+aa ra m+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16236: a ba lo ki d+ya ka ru na ma ram h+aum dzahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16237: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16238: ru ru phu ru dz+wa la tish+tha sid+d+hi lo tsa ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16239: pan+da mi ki ta ram pa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16240: sug sme dz+ny+aa na dza h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16241: ma h+aa sh+r+ai ye tsi ri mi ri ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16243: te shan te shan s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16245: sarba d+har+m+aa ni se ta ni badz+ra si pa ra ni s+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16246: badz+ra ta badz+ra pra b+ha te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16247: ban+d+ha ban+d+ha mo ha ya badz+roda b+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16248: ban+d+ha ban+d+ha mo ha ya mo ha ya badz+roda b+ha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16249: badz+wa la dz+wa la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16250: badz+ra a k+sho ta h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:16251: khad+ga ban s+pho ta ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16252: a mri te ha na bi du na bi du
NK024(ya)001:16253: na go sa kha a mri te ma kha s+w+aa
NK024(ya)001:16254: h+aa / b+h+ra ma ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16255: ga na pa ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16257: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+har+m+aa swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:16258: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa
NK024(ya)001:16259: mu khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi
NK024(ya)001:16260: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:16261: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:16262: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta a wa lo ki te sam+b+ha ra sam+b+ha ra h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16263: dz+ny+aa na a wa lo ki te na mahs man+ta
NK024(ya)001:16264: s+pha ra na rasmi sam+b+ha wa sa ma ya ma
NK024(ya)001:16265: h+aa ma ni du ru du ru hri da ya
NK024(ya)001:16267: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam gra he shwa ra pra
NK024(ya)001:16268: b+hany+tsa dza ti ma h+aa sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:16269: / zhes pa rnams mdun bskyed la dmigs te ci rigs par bzlas so //'das gtor bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:16270: stong pa'i ngang la las rin po che'i snod du
NK024(ya)001:16271: 'dod pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs par bsam la
NK024(ya)001:16273: lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlab te lha sngags 'di
NK024(ya)001:16274: rnams la a k+aa ro btags pa lan gsum gyis
NK024(ya)001:16276: de nas cha gsum rgyas pa gong bzhin btang ngo
NK024(ya)001:16277: zhes gsungs pa gong du bshad pa ltar btang ngo
NK024(ya)001:16279: slob ma la ji ltar dbang bskur ba bzhin rang gis blang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:16280: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bdun pa khrus bya ba nas dbang dngos ston par byed de /
NK024(ya)001:16283: de nas slob bu rnams khrus byas phyag dang man+dala phul /
NK024(ya)001:16285: ji ltar bltams pa sogs brjod cing las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:16286: sngon 'gro gtor ma gnyis pa bshams pa chab kyis bran la /
NK024(ya)001:16287: slob dpon gong du bstan pa bzhin khro bo bdud
NK024(ya)001:16288: rtsi 'khyil ba g.yas rgya gram dang g.yon dril bu
NK024(ya)001:16294: bka' bsgo sogs snga ma rnams bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:16295: bden brdar la gsang sngags kri ya'i lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16298: bya rgyud kri ya'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:16299: zhes par bsgyur zhing 'khyil ba'i sngags dang sum+b+ha drag tu bya zhing yungs thun gyis brab /
NK024(ya)001:16300: gu gul gyis bdug ste bgegs bskrad do //
NK024(ya)001:16301: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu grub rjes /
NK024(ya)001:16302: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:16303: don rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang rin po
NK024(ya)001:16305: de'i ched du 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:16306: gyi dbang bskur ba'i yan lag bya ba'i rgyud kri
NK024(ya)001:16308: kri ya don gyi lha drug gi dkyil 'khor du
NK024(ya)001:16309: zhugs la smin grol gyi gdams pa blangs te sems
NK024(ya)001:16310: can gyi don bgyid snyam pas byang chub kyi mchog
NK024(ya)001:16312: gsan bya'i chos ni 'dir slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha wa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16313: pan chen bi ma la'i bzhed par /
NK024(ya)001:16314: mngon par mtho ba'i theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16315: nges par legs pa'i theg pa gnyis su bzhed pa'i phyi ma la'ang theg pa che chung gnyis las /
NK024(ya)001:16317: theg chen la gnyis te mtshan nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:16319: mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg pa ni byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod yin la /
NK024(ya)001:16320: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi theg pa la gnyis te /
NK024(ya)001:16321: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16322: nang pa thabs kyi theg pa gnyis su gsungs 'dir phyi rgyud yin /
NK024(ya)001:16323: de la yang gsum ste kri ya bya ba'i rgyud /
NK024(ya)001:16324: u pa ya spyod pa'i rgyud /
