NK024(ya)001:16325: yo ga rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang gsum las snga ma yin /
NK024(ya)001:16326: de la'ang rigs bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig bshad kyang 'dir spyi khyab yin /
NK024(ya)001:16327: de la spyir gsang sngags kyi theg pa ni rnam grangs bzhi'i sgo nas khyad par 'phags te /
NK024(ya)001:16329: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK024(ya)001:16330: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16331: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK024(ya)001:16332: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:16334: de yang 'dir gsang sngags phyi rgyud ni /
NK024(ya)001:16335: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen rab 'byams kyis /
NK024(ya)001:16336: de yang bya spyod rnal 'byor thub pa rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:16337: kri ya u pa yo ga zhes bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:16338: de dag gsang sngags phyi ste lha rnams kyang //
NK024(ya)001:16339: yab yum zung 'brel sgom par mi nus la //
NK024(ya)001:16340: sha lnga la sogs bsten par mi nus shing //
NK024(ya)001:16341: gtsang sbra kun tu spyod pas gnas pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:16342: zhes rgyud sde 'og ma gsum po spyir bshad nas bye brag tu bya rgyud dmigs bsal la /
NK024(ya)001:16343: bya bas rang nyid dman la lha nyid mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16344: rje khol tshul du bsgrubs pas dngos grub len //
NK024(ya)001:16345: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs pa ltar yin la /
NK024(ya)001:16346: 'dir 'dus pa mdo'i yan lag tu byed pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:16347: nyan rang sogs theg dman dang /
NK024(ya)001:16348: byang sems sogs mtshan nyid theg pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16349: bya spyod rnal 'byor sogs rgyud sde 'og ma thams cad bla med ltar bkral bas /
NK024(ya)001:16350: de dag gi don tshang ba tsam ma gtogs sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa ma yin la /
NK024(ya)001:16351: khyad par khams lugs su rnam 'joms kyi dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:16352: gong du bshad pa ltar la bla med kho na'i
NK024(ya)001:16354: 'dir zur lugs ltar dkyil 'khor dang po gsum rigs gsum kri ya'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:16355: bar pa gsum rigs gsum kri ya'i rigs bdag sku
NK024(ya)001:16356: gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gyis byas pa'i 'khor du
NK024(ya)001:16357: / kri ya bco lnga ma dang nyer bdun ma sogs kyi don dang mthun pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK024(ya)001:16358: phyi ma gsum rigs gsum gtso bo la kri ya
NK024(ya)001:16359: don gyi lha drug gis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor te
NK024(ya)001:16362: bdag 'jug sogs smin rgyas su grub ste slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams legs par song /
NK024(ya)001:16364: man+dala dbul zhing gsol ba gdab pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:16365: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo gnyis su
NK024(ya)001:16366: med pa la rigs gsum kri ya'i smin byed kyi
NK024(ya)001:16367: dbang rnams zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul /
NK024(ya)001:16368: sa bcad brgyad pa dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa ni
NK024(ya)001:16369: 'dir phyi 'jug nang 'jug sogs kyi dmigs bsal med
NK024(ya)001:16370: kyang / man+dala phul te dkyil 'khor khang par zhugs pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:16371: dgu pa gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16372: rtsa bar thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16374: bla ma dkon mchog gsum po rnams //'gro ba sems can don slad du //
NK024(ya)001:16375: bdag la dgongs shing gzigs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16376: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16377: yi dam gtso 'khor dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16378: lha dang byin rlabs dam tshig dang //
NK024(ya)001:16379: dbang rnams rim par bskur du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16380: zhes gsol ba lan gsum gdab bo //
NK024(ya)001:16381: de nas gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16383: yi dam dbang bskur dam tshig sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:16384: gus pas sems kyis sgrub par gyis //
NK024(ya)001:16385: nyes pa dag ni ma gos na //'bras bu dam pa thob par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:16387: de nas bcu pa sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:16388: rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzung ba'i bsam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:16390: bla med dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK024(ya)001:16391: bdag ni rtag tu skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:16392: bdag gis sangs rgyas bstan pa la //
NK024(ya)001:16393: spyi dang mi 'gal legs gnas te //
NK024(ya)001:16394: theg chen gsang sngags bya ba'i gzhung //
NK024(ya)001:16395: khyad par dam tshig bdag gis bzung //
NK024(ya)001:16396: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:16397: theg pa chen po sngags kyi lha //
NK024(ya)001:16398: don gcig gnyis med ye shes don //
NK024(ya)001:16399: yang dag nyid du bdag gis bzung //
NK024(ya)001:16400: sku yi rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK024(ya)001:16401: dam tshig sdom pa la gnas te //
NK024(ya)001:16402: sgrub pa dag kyang ci nus brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:16403: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:16404: phyi nang gsang ba'i gsung bsgrags te //
NK024(ya)001:16405: dam pa'i chos kyang ma lus bzung //
NK024(ya)001:16406: rdo rje rigs mchog dam tshig ni //
NK024(ya)001:16407: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK024(ya)001:16408: bla ma rdo rje rigs bsten bya //
NK024(ya)001:16409: mthar yas sems can don gyi phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16410: gsang sngags dam tshig bdag gis blang //
NK024(ya)001:16411: yang dag par ni bzung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:16412: byang chub sems mchog sgrub par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:16414: bcu gcig pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16416: phyi pa mu stegs pa las nang pa sangs rgyas pa khyad par 'phags shing /
NK024(ya)001:16423: de dag rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:16424: de dag las 'dir gsang sngags kyi theg pa khyad par du 'phags te /
NK024(ya)001:16426: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK024(ya)001:16427: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16428: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK024(ya)001:16429: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:16430: zhes gsungs pa ltar lam 'dir 'jug pa la spro ba khyad par can bskyed par mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:16432: kri ya'i dam tshig bcu gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:16433: bslab bya dbog ces gsungs pa /
NK024(ya)001:16434: sdom pa bsgrag pa yin pas gsan pas khyab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:16436: de ring phan chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK024(ya)001:16437: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK024(ya)001:16438: gsang sngags gzungs sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:16439: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK024(ya)001:16440: rtag tu phyag rgya chen po la //
NK024(ya)001:16441: khyad par du yang mos par bya //
NK024(ya)001:16442: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo bya //
NK024(ya)001:16443: bla ma la ni gus par bya //
NK024(ya)001:16444: lha rnams kun la sdang mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:16445: dus 'tshams rtag tu mchod pa bya //
NK024(ya)001:16446: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK024(ya)001:16447: rtag tu bla ma mchod mgron bya //
NK024(ya)001:16448: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i sems //
NK024(ya)001:16449: rab tu brtan pas nye bar bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:16450: theg pa mchog la dga' rnams kyi //
NK024(ya)001:16451: bsod nams tshogs la nan tan bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:16452: bzlas brjod byed la 'bad par bya //
NK024(ya)001:16453: gsang sngags rgyud las bstan pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:16454: dam tshig rnams kyang srung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:16455: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK024(ya)001:16456: sngags dang phyag rgya sbyin mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:16457: gsang sngags rgyud nas legs gsungs bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:16458: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:16460: zhes gsungs pa'i don cung zhig dpyad na /
NK024(ya)001:16461: dkon mchog gsum dang gsang sngags gzungs sngags kyi lha
NK024(ya)001:16462: rnams la dad pa brtan par bya ba dang po
NK024(ya)001:16463: dang / rtag tu lha'i bskyed rim phyag rgya chen po la mos par bya ba gnyis pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16464: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams dang mdza' bar bya ba ste gsum pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16465: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la gus par bya ba bzhi pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16466: lha rnams la sdang bar mi bya ba lnga pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16467: yar tshes brgyad dang skar ma rgyal la sogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16468: tshes bzang po la mchod par bya ba drug pa
NK024(ya)001:16469: dang / mu stegs byed la sogs pa'i ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod pa bdun pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16470: rtag tu bla ma mchod cing mgron gyis mnyes par bya ba brgyad pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16471: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i sems rab tu brtan pa nye bar 'jog pa dgu pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16472: theg mchog sngags la mos pa rnams kyi bsod nams
NK024(ya)001:16473: kyi tshogs spel ba'i grogs bya ba ste bcu pa
NK024(ya)001:16474: dang / bzlas brjod la 'bad par bya ba bcu gcig pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:16475: gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde las byung ba'i dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:16476: dang sdom pa'i tshogs bsrung bar bya ba ste bcu
NK024(ya)001:16477: gnyis pa dang / dam tshig med pa rnams la
NK024(ya)001:16478: sngags dang lha'i phyag rgya sogs sbyin par mi bya
NK024(ya)001:16479: ba ste bcu gsum po bya ba'i rgyud kyi dam
NK024(ya)001:16480: tshig tu legs par gsungs pa bzhin rtogs par gyis
NK024(ya)001:16481: la tshul bzhin du bslab par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:16482: de ltar dam tshig dang sdom pa'i tshogs de dag
NK024(ya)001:16483: bsrung bar nan gyis gdams shing dam la bzhag pa
NK024(ya)001:16484: dam tshig gi mna' chu blud pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16486: de nas las kyi bum pa'i chu sbyin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:16487: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK024(ya)001:16488: dam tshig 'das na bsreg par byed //
NK024(ya)001:16489: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub ni //
NK024(ya)001:16493: de nas man+dala du me tog dor te /
NK024(ya)001:16494: rigs brtag ste ming gdags so //
NK024(ya)001:16496: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha 'di rnams la rig
NK024(ya)001:16497: pa'i me tog dor ba'i mos pa dang bcas te
NK024(ya)001:16499: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16500: bdag la thugs brtser dgongs nas ni //'gro la phan phyir gtso chen gyis //
NK024(ya)001:16501: dman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:16503: zhes dkyil 'khor du me tog gtor te gang la
NK024(ya)001:16504: babs pa'i rigs ngos bzung ste gsang ming 'dogs pa'am
NK024(ya)001:16505: / yang na gsang ming 'og tu tshogs chen gyi
NK024(ya)001:16506: dkyil 'khor du btags pas 'thus phyir 'dir me tog
NK024(ya)001:16508: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:16510: lha dbab pa sogs ni gsal bar ma bshad cing phyag len du mi mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:16511: bcu gsum pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:16513: de nas lha dbang rim pa bzhin thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:16515: bum pa sbyi bor gtugs la /
NK024(ya)001:16516: zhes gsungs pas rnam rgyal bum pas dbang bskur zhing /
NK024(ya)001:16518: don dam bden pa'i chos nyid las //
NK024(ya)001:16519: mi sems pa yi mngon sum du //
NK024(ya)001:16520: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16521: rigs gsum kri ya'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:16523: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yahh+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16524: w+aa g+ai shwa ri la sogs gsum brjod /
NK024(ya)001:16526: dkon mchog gsum dang kri ya rigs gsum gyi lha
NK024(ya)001:16527: tshogs kyi byin gyis brlabs kyis rigs kyi bu la
NK024(ya)001:16529: kri ya don gyi lha drug gi dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:16531: lha dbang dngos ni tsakli rnams rim bzhin blangs te dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:16533: d+h+aih dpal gyi 'byung gnas 'jam dpal kun gyi dpal //
NK024(ya)001:16534: mtha' dag yongs la khyab pa 'jam pa'i ngang //'jam
NK024(ya)001:16535: dang dpal du grags pa 'i don dang ldan //'jam
NK024(ya)001:16536: dpal yang dag dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:16539: yon tan rgyas pas sku mdog gser dang mtshungs //
NK024(ya)001:16540: shes rab rtags su po ti ral gri bsnams //'phags pa 'jam dpal shes bya gang yin pa //
NK024(ya)001:16541: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:16542: h+r+aih dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa chos kyi sku //'gro drug sems can kun la spyan ras gzigs //
NK024(ya)001:16543: nam mkha' lta bur gyur pa'i bcu gcig zhal //
NK024(ya)001:16544: gzi brjid 'od dpag med la phyag ma ni pad+me h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16545: a b+hi thugs rje'i rtags su sku mdog zla ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:16546: ma chags skyon gyis ma gos pad+ma bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16547: spyan ras gzigs kyi bkra shis bkra shis des kyang h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16548: lcang lo can gyi gnas mchog dam pa nas //
NK024(ya)001:16549: gsang sngags rig sngags kun gyi bdag po ste //
NK024(ya)001:16550: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16551: bcom ldan rdo rje bsnams la badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16552: a b+hi chos nyid mi 'gyur rtags su sku mdog sngo //
NK024(ya)001:16553: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med rdo rje 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:16554: mthu stobs can gyi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK024(ya)001:16556: sh+aakya thub pa nyes skyon sbyong ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16557: rnam par snang mdzad yon tan spel ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16558: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba mos par bsgyur ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16559: rgyal chen shugs ldan so sor thob pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16560: don yod grub pa thams cad tshim pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16561: phyag na rdo rje dbang du byed pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:16562: lha sngags phyag rgya ting 'dzin yig 'bru drug /
NK024(ya)001:16563: rigs drug dam pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16564: a kham dzi s+w+aa h+aa dzah a b+hi /
NK024(ya)001:16565: rigs bdag sku mchog rnam snang mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:16566: nyes pa'i skyon bral sku mdog dkar //
NK024(ya)001:16567: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:16568: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /'jam dpal dbyangs ni sku yi rigs //
NK024(ya)001:16570: phyag na ral gri ut+pala bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16571: rigs kyi yum mchog sangs rgyas spyan //
NK024(ya)001:16572: dkar mo phyag na spyan 'bras bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16573: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NK024(ya)001:16574: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje rno //
NK024(ya)001:16575: lha mo dpal dang mdzod sprul ma //
NK024(ya)001:16576: lha chen tshangs pa la sogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:16577: sku yi rigs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:16579: a b+hi +aah rigs bdag gsung mchog snang mtha' yas //
NK024(ya)001:16580: thugs rje chags pas sku mdog dmar //
NK024(ya)001:16581: ting 'dzin mchog gi phyag de yi dbang mchog spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung gi rigs //
NK024(ya)001:16582: dmar po phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16583: yum chen gos dkar sku mdog dmar //
NK024(ya)001:16584: phyag na 'dam skyes dkar po bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16585: khro rgyal rta mgrin rta skad 'tsher //
NK024(ya)001:16586: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje phur //
NK024(ya)001:16587: grags ldan ma dang lu gu rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:16588: ma h+aa de wa la sogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:16589: gsung gi rigs kyi dbang a mi de ba a /
NK024(ya)001:16591: rigs bdag thugs mchog rdo rje sems //
NK024(ya)001:16592: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog sngo //
NK024(ya)001:16593: sa gnon chen po'i phyag de yi dbang mchog phyag
NK024(ya)001:16594: na rdo rje thugs kyi rigs sngon po phyag na
NK024(ya)001:16595: rdo rje bsnams // yum chen bzang mo sku mdog sngo //
NK024(ya)001:16596: phyag na rdo rje rtse gsum can //
NK024(ya)001:16597: khro bo'i rgyal po bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK024(ya)001:16598: pho nya rdo rje khro bo ste //
NK024(ya)001:16599: stobs chen ma dang rnam rgyal ma //
NK024(ya)001:16600: lha chen khyab 'jug la sogs pa //
NK024(ya)001:16601: thugs kyi rigs kyi ak+sho b+h+yah h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16603: dpa' bar 'gro dkar ral gri ste //
NK024(ya)001:16604: kun bzang gangs ltar rin chen te //
NK024(ya)001:16606: bzang skyong dung mdog bum pa can //
NK024(ya)001:16607: lho yi sems dpa' bzhi po sngo //
NK024(ya)001:16609: nam mkha' mdzod ni rin chen sgrom //
NK024(ya)001:16610: nam snying rdo rje rtse gsum can //'od dpag med ni rin chen 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:16611: nub phyogs sems dpa' byu ru'i mdog /
NK024(ya)001:16613: ye shes tog ni rin chen tog /
NK024(ya)001:16614: spobs pa brtsegs ni rin chen 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:16615: blo gros mi zad glegs bam can //
NK024(ya)001:16616: byang gi sems pa ljang gu ste //
NK024(ya)001:16617: byams pa klu shing spyi blugs can //
NK024(ya)001:16618: spos kyi glang po dung dkar 'bud //
NK024(ya)001:16621: bskal bzang sems dpa' bcu drug gi //
NK024(ya)001:16622: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16625: shar du dus ldan pad+ma can //
NK024(ya)001:16626: dkar mo dpal be'u 'khor lo bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:16629: nub tu mdangs can dri med ma //
NK024(ya)001:16630: dmar mo gdugs dang bum pa 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:16631: byang du rgyal gdung yid bzang ma //
NK024(ya)001:16632: ljang gu dung dang gser nya 'dzin //
NK024(ya)001:16633: phyogs bzhi dus bzhir bkra shis pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16634: lha mo brgyad kyi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:16635: tri mam ga la de wi a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:16636: zhes pa yan chad lha dbang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:16637: de nas rdzas dbang rnams rim par thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:16638: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la chos
NK024(ya)001:16639: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su dpal phyag na
NK024(ya)001:16640: rdo rje la rin po che sna lnga'i ri rab
NK024(ya)001:16641: kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa
NK024(ya)001:16642: dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob par gyur
NK024(ya)001:16643: to // de bzhin du rin po che sna lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:16644: ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun sum
NK024(ya)001:16645: tshogs pa dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob
NK024(ya)001:16646: to // par gyur cig / gzi brjid lhun stug ri rab mchog gi sku //
NK024(ya)001:16647: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i bang rim mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16648: thams cad gnas pa'i ri bo chen po la //
NK024(ya)001:16649: mthu stobs mi 'gyur sku rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16650: skye bzhi 'gro drug khams gsum yongs kyi srog /
NK024(ya)001:16651: kha dog mdzes ldan rin chen sna tshogs gzhi //
NK024(ya)001:16652: phyogs bzhi rigs dang dbus kyi skur bstan pa //'di ni rin chen sna lnga'i ri rab kyi //
NK024(ya)001:16653: dbang gi bkra shis le'u dang po'o //
NK024(ya)001:16654: sngon bcom ldan 'das mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin
NK024(ya)001:16655: pa'i dus su u dum+wa ra'i me tog dang sbyar
NK024(ya)001:16656: nas / dpal phyag na rdo rje la rang bzhin
NK024(ya)001:16657: gyi mchod rten dang sprul pa'i mchod rten la sogs
NK024(ya)001:16658: pas dbang bskur bas rnam par mi rtog pa chos
NK024(ya)001:16659: kyi sku thob par de bzhin du 'dir yang mchod
NK024(ya)001:16660: rten chen po'i dbang bskur bas chos kyi sku thob
NK024(ya)001:16661: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:16662: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i bang rim la //
NK024(ya)001:16663: skye 'gag med pa'i bum pa zlum pos brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:16664: chos kyi 'khor lo ma 'dres tog la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:16665: rnam par mi rtog chos sku thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16666: lta ba'i sa dang mngon par byang chub mtshungs pa mi mnga' yang //
NK024(ya)001:16667: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor dang cho 'phrul ston la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:16668: lha yul gnas gshegs ston pa dbyings su bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:16669: stobs bcu'i byin rlabs mnga' ba mchod rten dbang gi bkra shis le'u gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16670: sngon bcom ldan 'das gyad yul gyi nye 'khor na
NK024(ya)001:16671: bzhugs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK024(ya)001:16672: dpag bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas dgos 'dod thams
NK024(ya)001:16673: cad yid bzhin du 'grub par de bzhin du dpag
NK024(ya)001:16674: bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas dgos 'dod thams cad
NK024(ya)001:16675: yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:16676: gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK024(ya)001:16677: yon tan yid bzhin zad med gter dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:16678: bstan pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul yin te //
NK024(ya)001:16679: dgos pa'i don rnams yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16680: lha yi re skong dpag bsam ljon shing ltar //'phags pa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi lang ste //
NK024(ya)001:16681: re ba yid bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i rdzas //'dod
NK024(ya)001:16682: rgu'i 'byung gnas rin chen dpag bsam shing //'di ni
NK024(ya)001:16683: dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16684: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgya mtsho chen po'i gling du
NK024(ya)001:16685: gshegs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK024(ya)001:16686: rgya mtsho chen po'i dbang bskur bas skye ba med
NK024(ya)001:16687: pa'i chos zab cing rgya che ba rgyud la rtogs
NK024(ya)001:16688: par de bzhin du rgya mtsho chen po'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:16689: bas skye ba med pa'i chos zab cing rgya che
NK024(ya)001:16690: ba rgyud la rtogs par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:16691: gting dpag zab cing rgya mtsho yangs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:16692: kun tu snyoms pa'i yon tan chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:16693: skye 'gag med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK024(ya)001:16694: zab cing rgya che'i chos don rtogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16695: chos nyid rgya mtsho lta bu thugs chud pas //
NK024(ya)001:16696: zab cing ga ting dpag dka' ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK024(ya)001:16697: yid bzhin nor bu kha dog mdzes pa'i tshul //'di ni rgya mtsho dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16698: sngon bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i gdan drung na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16699: pa'i tshe dpal phyag na rdo rje la sa gzhi
NK024(ya)001:16700: chen po gnas kyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis la
NK024(ya)001:16701: byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:16702: du sa gzhi gnas kyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:16703: byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:16704: / rab tu dben pa'i gnas mchog dam pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:16705: me tog dri bsung mang po skye ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:16706: yoon tan ma lus tshang bar kun rdzogs te //
NK024(ya)001:16707: dben pa'i bkra shis 'byor pa'i gnas su shog /
NK024(ya)001:16708: me tog mdzes ldan yid 'ong brgyan pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:16709: chos kyi sgra snyan sgra skad sna tshogs sgrog /
NK024(ya)001:16710: yon tan kun ldan ston pas byin brlabs nas //
NK024(ya)001:16711: gnas gzhi dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16712: sngon bcom ldan 'das wa ra n+aa si na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16713: pa'i tshe dpal phyag na rdo rje la bdud rtsi'i
NK024(ya)001:16714: chus dbang bskur bas skye shi mi mnga' ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:16715: thob par de bzhin du bum pa'i chus dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:16716: bas skye shi med pa rdo rje sku'i dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:16717: pa bdud rtsi chu rgyun 'gro ba'i bsos kyi mchog
NK024(ya)001:16718: / nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad rnams ma lus sel //
NK024(ya)001:16719: ma rig dag byed bdud rtsi'i chu mchog ste //
NK024(ya)001:16720: skye shi med pa dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:16721: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK024(ya)001:16722: dbang bskur bum pa spyi blugs pas //
NK024(ya)001:16723: bdud rtsi'i bum pa 'dir rtsol zhig /'di ni bdud rtsi chu bo'i rgyun //
NK024(ya)001:16724: dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16726: 'dir kri ya'i bum dbang yang bya /
NK024(ya)001:16727: u pa ya'i bum dbang yang bya /
NK024(ya)001:16729: zhes gsungs pa ni kri ya dang u pa ya
NK024(ya)001:16730: gnyis rdzas dbang 'dra ba la dgongs te 'jug pa
NK024(ya)001:16731: bde ba'i phyir / dkyil 'khor gnyis ka dril te
NK024(ya)001:16732: sgrub mchod dang dbang bskur byed pa la dgongs pa
NK024(ya)001:16734: lha dang dbang gi sgrub mchod dbang bskur 'jug pa
NK024(ya)001:16735: sogs mi 'dra ba du ma yod pas tha dad
NK024(ya)001:16736: du bgyis na dngos gtsang zhing cho ga mi 'khrugs
NK024(ya)001:16738: 'dir kri ya'i bum dbang mi bya bar rdzas dbang dkyus la 'jug pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:16740: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16741: pa'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis chos zhus
NK024(ya)001:16742: pa'i rten du da ru khad kyi zar tshags phul
NK024(ya)001:16743: bas / chos sgra chen po sgrog pa'i dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:16744: pa de bzhin du da ru khad kyi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:16745: bas chos sgra chen po sgrog pa'i dbang chos kyi
NK024(ya)001:16746: rgyal srid chen po mnga' brnyes shing //
NK024(ya)001:16747: ma rig mun pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:16748: brgya byin shes pa ma lus sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16749: chos rnams thams cad go bzhin sgrog par shog /'jam mnyen reg bde dar gyi za ra tshags //
NK024(ya)001:16750: rigs kyi kha dog sna bdun shin tu mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:16751: yid 'ong legs par brgyan pa'i bkra shis rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:16752: lhab lhub dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16753: sngon bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK024(ya)001:16754: su brgya byin la chos 'khor bskor ba'i tshe rin
NK024(ya)001:16755: po che'i khri rkang phul nas bzhugs pas chos shes
NK024(ya)001:16756: pa'i rgyud la go zhing sgrog par de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:16757: rin po che'i khri rkang gi dbang bskur bas chos
NK024(ya)001:16758: ma nor bar go zhing sgrog pa'i dbang rin chen
NK024(ya)001:16760: chos sgra chen po sgrogs pa yis //'gro ba rnams kyi mi shes grol //
NK024(ya)001:16761: chos rnams go zhing sgrog par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16762: tshad med bzhi ldan 'degs byed gser gyi khri //
NK024(ya)001:16763: yon tan tshogs rdzogs rin chen sna tshogs bkram //'gro ba'i yid bzhin zad med dgos 'dod skong //
NK024(ya)001:16764: khri mchog dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16765: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK024(ya)001:16766: ba'i tshe brgya byin gyis me tog chen pos bres
NK024(ya)001:16767: pas sems can 'khor ba las bslu zhing brid pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16768: mchog tu de bzhin du me tog chun pos dbang
NK024(ya)001:16769: bskur bas 'khor ba las yid 'byung ba mdzes pa
NK024(ya)001:16770: rgyan mchog dam pa'i dbang sdug cing mdzes pa'i me
NK024(ya)001:16772: kha dog ma 'dres so sor gsal ba'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16773: sems can kun gyis blta bar 'os pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:16774: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16775: me tog chu skyes thang skyes dam pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16776: shing dang nags skyes 'bru mchog dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:16777: rin chen phreng ldan me tog chun mar 'bebs //'di ni dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16778: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab khang pa brtsegs par
NK024(ya)001:16779: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i che sum cu rtsa
NK024(ya)001:16780: gsum lha'i bu nyi 'od dam pas rnga yab kyis
NK024(ya)001:16781: g.yabs bas dgyes pa chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan
NK024(ya)001:16782: par de bzhin du rnga yab kyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:16783: dgyes pa chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i snyan
NK024(ya)001:16784: pa'i sgra rnams myur du sgrog pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:16785: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma ma lus sel //
NK024(ya)001:16786: thams cad myur du go ba'i blo thob nas //
NK024(ya)001:16787: bkra shis gzi mdangs mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16788: rgyal ba'i sku la nyes pa ma gos kyang //
NK024(ya)001:16789: dag cing gsang bar bya ba'i rnga yab 'dis //
NK024(ya)001:16790: sku yi dri ma ljan ljin dag par byed //
NK024(ya)001:16791: rnga yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16792: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16793: tshe sum cu rtsa gsum lha'i bu kun nas 'od
NK024(ya)001:16794: zer 'byung bas rdul g.yab kyis rdul g.yabs pas chos
NK024(ya)001:16795: nyid la skyon gyis ma gos par de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:16796: lha'i rdul g.yab kyi dbang bskur bas chos nyid zab
NK024(ya)001:16797: mo'i don la 'jug pa'i nyon mongs rdul rnams ma
NK024(ya)001:16799: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:16800: bag chags skyon gyi dri ma bsal ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16801: chos nyid zab mo'i don la 'jug par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16802: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang //
NK024(ya)001:16803: log rtog rdul gyi bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16804: bkra shis gtsang ma'i ras kyis sku phyi ba //
NK024(ya)001:16805: rdul g.yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16806: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal dgon pa na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16807: pa'i tshe sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu zhig
NK024(ya)001:16808: gis sbrang g.yas kyis sbrang bu g.yabs pas sems can
NK024(ya)001:16809: du 'dzin pa'i skyon las grol bar de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:16810: lha'i sbrang g.yab kyi dbang bskur bas 'dzin chags kyi
NK024(ya)001:16811: skyon las grol ba'i nyon mongs sems can ma rigs
NK024(ya)001:16812: bsal ba dang //'bras bu thar pa'i go 'phang thob
NK024(ya)001:16813: pa dang // bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs drung 'khor
NK024(ya)001:16814: ba'i phyir //'dzin chags skyon gyi dri ma dag par
NK024(ya)001:16815: pa dang // shog / drang srong chen po bsam gtan gnas pa la //
NK024(ya)001:16816: srog chags gdug pa'i gzugs brnyan bsal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:16817: rnga yab rgyal ba'i ring bsrel bskor ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16818: sbrang g.yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16819: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16820: tshe 'khor rnam bzhis bla bre bres pas nyon mongs
NK024(ya)001:16821: pa'i gdung ba zhi bar de bzhin du bla bre'i
NK024(ya)001:16822: dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i rdul gyi dri mas
NK024(ya)001:16824: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor phyir bla bre bres //
NK024(ya)001:16825: mi yi rgyal po bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:16826: dbang phyug chen po'i mnga' bdag chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:16827: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma med par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16828: dpag bsam ljon shing me tog lo 'dab rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:16829: nyi zla gza' skar mang po'i sprin gseb nas //
NK024(ya)001:16830: bkra shis bya skad mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK024(ya)001:16831: dar zab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16832: sngon bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i rir chos
NK024(ya)001:16833: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe 'khor rnam bzhis rgyal
NK024(ya)001:16834: mtshan chen po gtsugs pas che ba'i yon tan nub
NK024(ya)001:16835: pa med pa thob par de bzhin du rgyal mtshan
NK024(ya)001:16836: gyi dbang bskur bas che ba'i yon tan nub pa
NK024(ya)001:16837: med pa'i dbang lhun grub sku brnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal
NK024(ya)001:16838: mtshan te // nub dang zad med dus med sngar bzhin rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:16839: yon tan mchog gyur kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:16840: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16841: dpal brjid mdzes pas 'jig rten yongs kyi rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:16842: bdud dang mu stegs bdud dpung 'joms par byed //
NK024(ya)001:16843: rgyal ba'i sku dang dbyer med tshul gcig pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16844: rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16845: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16846: tshe 'khor rnams kyis tsha ba'i gdung skyob gdugs kyis
NK024(ya)001:16847: bkab pas tsha ba'i gdung ba zhi bar de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:16848: du gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i gdung
NK024(ya)001:16849: ba thams cad zhi ba'i dbang gdugs kyis tsha ba'i
NK024(ya)001:16851: grang zhing bsil ba'i gdugs mchog dam pa ste //'gro ba'i nyon mongs tsha gdung zhi ba'i gsos //
NK024(ya)001:16852: rims nad tsha ba'i sdug bsngal thar par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16853: ji ltar nyon mongs tsha bas gdungs pa las //
NK024(ya)001:16854: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal skyob pa ltar //'khor ba'i nyes pa sdug bsngal bsal ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16855: gdugs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bco lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16856: sngon bcom ldan 'das yangs pa can gyi grong khyer
NK024(ya)001:16857: spre'u rdzing gi 'gram khang bu brtsegs pa na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16858: pa'i tshe bram ze kham pa sngon gyi nyes pas
NK024(ya)001:16859: brdas nas nya pa rnams kyis zin pa'i nya pa
NK024(ya)001:16860: rnams 'gyod pa rjes su dran nas nya rgya che
NK024(ya)001:16861: chung phul bas nya pa lnga brgya sangs rgyas par
NK024(ya)001:16862: de bzhin du nya rgya'i rtags dar gyi lda ldi'i
NK024(ya)001:16863: dbang bskur bas ngan song skye nges kyang de las
NK024(ya)001:16864: thar te sangs rgyas pa'i dar gyi lda ldi nyon
NK024(ya)001:16866: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus yongs rdzogs nas //
NK024(ya)001:16867: ma rig 'khrul pa'i shes pa blo dag cing //
NK024(ya)001:16868: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i nad las thar par shog /'khor ba'i nyes pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16869: sdug bsngal rgya mo bkra shis rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:16870: bag chags kun dag lda ldi'i rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:16871: dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16872: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes mos tshal du bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16873: tshe khyim bdag gi bu mo bzang ldan mas a
NK024(ya)001:16874: par se'i sku rags gsol bas sku brtan pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:16875: mchog dang ldan par de bzhin du sku rags kyi
NK024(ya)001:16876: dbang bskur bas lus brtan pa'i mchog gi dri med
NK024(ya)001:16877: dag pa'i sku rags gtsang ma'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16878: khyim bdag dad pas phul ba'i sku chings 'di //
NK024(ya)001:16879: sku la bkra shis rab tu brtan pas na //
NK024(ya)001:16880: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16881: thar pa mchog gi legs par gang gsungs pa //
NK024(ya)001:16882: mi dmigs dag pa'i ye shes chos sku yi //
NK024(ya)001:16883: nyon mongs dri ma med pa'i sku brten pa //
NK024(ya)001:16884: sku rags dbang gi bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16885: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gangs can na bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16886: pa'i tshe gnod sbyin rnams kyis spos rnam lnga phul
NK024(ya)001:16890: du ru ka ste de rnams phul bas dbang po
NK024(ya)001:16891: tshim zhing bkra shis par de bzhin du spos rnam
NK024(ya)001:16892: pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas dbang tshim zhing bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:16893: pa'i dbang po tshim bya bdug pa'i spos mchog 'di
NK024(ya)001:16894: // dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa mchod pa da
NK024(ya)001:16895: nga //'gro ba ma lus dbang po kun tshim zhing
NK024(ya)001:16896: // // dri zhim 'phags pa'i sku dang ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16897: dri zhim ngad ldan yon tan phun sum tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:16898: mkha' la mchod pa'i sprin phung gtibs byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:16899: yongs su khyab pa'i bdug mchog dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:16900: tshim byed dbang gi bkra shis bco brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16901: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po na bzhugs pa'i tshe klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis tsh+wa /
NK024(ya)001:16905: til te snying po lnga phul bas chos kyi snying
NK024(ya)001:16906: po mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par de
NK024(ya)001:16907: bzhin du snying po rnam pa lngas dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:16908: tshe mi zad pa'i snying po lnga ni gsos kyi
NK024(ya)001:16909: mchog / mi zad pa yi dbyig thogs te //
NK024(ya)001:16910: legs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK024(ya)001:16911: tshe dang longs spyod 'phel bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16912: tsh+wa yis ro bsgyur mar gyis mdangs dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:16913: sprang rtsis stobs rgyas ka ras nad rnams zhi //
NK024(ya)001:16914: til gyis sdig zhi dge tshogs rnams par 'phel //
NK024(ya)001:16915: snying po dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16916: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gru 'dzin na bzhugs pa'i tshe gnod sbyin gter 'chang rnams kyis gser /
NK024(ya)001:16920: mu men te rin po che rnam pa lnga phul
NK024(ya)001:16921: bas zad mi shes pa'i dkor mdzod dang ldan par
NK024(ya)001:16922: de bzhin du rin po che rnam pa lnga'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:16923: bskur bas longs spyod zad mi shes pa'i rin chen
NK024(ya)001:16925: mi zad nor gyi mchog 'di yis //'phags pa'i nor
NK024(ya)001:16926: bdun dang ldan te //'gro ba'i dbul ba sel bar
NK024(ya)001:16927: shog / dgos pa'i nor 'byung rin chen sna tshogs mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16928: zad mi shes pa re ba skong ba'i gter //
NK024(ya)001:16929: bkres dang dbul 'phongs sdug bsngal sel byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:16930: dgos 'byung dbang gi bkra shis nyi shu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16931: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul ad+ga ma ga d+ha na bzhugs pa'i tshe rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis nas /
NK024(ya)001:16935: mon sran dre'u ste 'bru lnga phul bas mu ge
NK024(ya)001:16936: med cing bkra shis par de bzhin du 'bru lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:16937: dbang bskur bas mu ge'i bskal pa las thar pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16938: dbang rin chen 'bru mchog 'gro ba kun gyi gsos
NK024(ya)001:16939: // mu ge'i sdug bsngal kun las thar byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:16940: sbyin pas longs spyod rtag tu 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:16941: zas gos mi zad gter dang ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:16942: longs spyod tshogs chen 'byor pa kun ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:16943: gang la ci 'dod yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK024(ya)001:16944: phun sum tshogs pa dge ba'i stobs bskyed pa //
NK024(ya)001:16945: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16946: sngon bcom ldan 'das tsan+dana gyi nags su gshegs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16947: tshe gcan gzan gyi rgyal po stag gis sman b+y+aa
NK024(ya)001:16948: gri phul bas bkra shis par de bzhin du sman
NK024(ya)001:16949: stag tsher gyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:16950: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:16951: byol song gti mug kun kyang 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16952: b+y+aa gri sman mchog gcan gzan stag gis phul //
NK024(ya)001:16953: sman gyis nad rnam ma lus zhi bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16954: sems can gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16955: thabs kyis kun la cho 'phrul cir yang ston //
NK024(ya)001:16956: thugs rje chen pos gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:16957: cho 'phrul dbang gi bkra shis nyer gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16958: sngon bcom ldan 'das seng ldeng nags su gshegs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:16959: tshe gcan gzan gyi rgyal po seng ges seng gri
NK024(ya)001:16960: phul bas sman gyi mchog tu bkra de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:16961: seng ldeng tsher mas dbang bskur bas sman mchog bkra
NK024(ya)001:16962: shis seng gri sman mchog gcan gzan seng ge phul
NK024(ya)001:16963: // bcom ldan thugs rje byol song gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16964: sman mchog nad rnams kun las thar bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16965: gzi brjid 'gro mkhas 'gying ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //'gying zhing 'gying ba dud 'gro'i rgyal po ste //
NK024(ya)001:16966: sgra skad bsgrags tshe gcan gzan zil gyis gnon //
NK024(ya)001:16967: gdul legs dbang gi bkra shis nyer gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16968: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri btang bzung chen por bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:16969: pa'i tshe klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos bri ha ti
NK024(ya)001:16970: phul bas mchog gi sman bkra de bzhin du shu
NK024(ya)001:16971: dag dkar po'i dbang bskur bas sman mchog bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:16972: pa'i shu dag sman mchog klu yis phul ba ste
NK024(ya)001:16973: // bcom ldan thugs rje klu rigs gti mug kun kyang go mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16974: sman gyis nad rnams rab tu sel bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16975: rig pa'i cha ldan byang chub sems dpa' yi //'gro ba'i re skong gtsug na rin chen mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16976: thabs kyis don mdzad mthu dpung che ba'i klu //
NK024(ya)001:16977: nad sel dbang gi bkra shis nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16978: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal
NK024(ya)001:16979: na bzhugs pa'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis
NK024(ya)001:16980: ha sa de wa phul bas sman mchog gi snying
NK024(ya)001:16981: por bkra de bzhin du dbang po lag pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:16982: bskur bas sman mchog don dam pa'i dbang dbang po
NK024(ya)001:16983: lag pa brgya byin dbang pos phul //
NK024(ya)001:16984: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po lha yi sems kyang go mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16985: sman mchog nad kun rab tu zhi bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16986: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK024(ya)001:16987: longs spyod ldan pa lha dbang brgya byin mchog /
NK024(ya)001:16988: sum cu rtsa gsum lha las rnam rgyal ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:16989: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:16990: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po'i tshal du
NK024(ya)001:16991: gshegs pa'i tshe shing gi lha mo 'od 'chang mas
NK024(ya)001:16992: kan+da ka ri phul bas sman mchog snying por bkra
NK024(ya)001:16993: de bzhin du kan+da ka ri'i dbang bskur bas sman
NK024(ya)001:16994: mchog snying po'i dbang bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i
NK024(ya)001:16995: byin rlabs kyis // shing gi lha mo'i sems kyang go mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:16996: kan+da ka ri shing gi lha mos phul //
NK024(ya)001:16997: sman mchog de yis nad kun zhi bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:16998: nags tshal chen po ljon shing las //
NK024(ya)001:16999: bde dang dgos pa'i re skong ba //
NK024(ya)001:17000: lha mo 'dod pas rab tu phul //
NK024(ya)001:17001: dbang mchog bkra shis nyer drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17002: zhes pas dbang rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:17003: de ltar dbang bskur grub nas rtsa ba'i sa bcad
NK024(ya)001:17004: bcu bzhi pa lam 'khyer la nang gses bzhi ste
NK024(ya)001:17005: / theg pa lha snying bslab bya ste bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:17006: theg pa la nang gses kyi drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:17013: de la dang po'i rgyas bshad drug 'og tu 'byung la /
NK024(ya)001:17015: de nas lam 'khyer gyi theg pa kri ya /
NK024(ya)001:17017: snying po w+aa g+ai shwa ri mum /
NK024(ya)001:17020: kri ya'i dbang nyi shu rtsa drug go //
NK024(ya)001:17021: de yang theg pa'i 'jug sgo khrus dang gtsang sbra ste /
NK024(ya)001:17022: las la 'jug pa'i skabs dag tu //
NK024(ya)001:17023: lus ni sa yis dril phyis byas //
NK024(ya)001:17024: chu nang rnyog pa med zhugs te //
NK024(ya)001:17025: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du bkrus //
NK024(ya)001:17027: lta ba don dam pa'i bden pa sems dag pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17028: mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i 'di stong gsal gyi ye
NK024(ya)001:17030: de'i yon tan kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK024(ya)001:17031: de'ang yul phar snang phyi rol gyi mthong /
NK024(ya)001:17033: tshur nang nas 'char ba'am sgo gsum dug gsum /
NK024(ya)001:17034: srid gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod de /
NK024(ya)001:17035: kun rdzob snang ba rigs gsum lha //
NK024(ya)001:17036: rje dang 'dra ba gtsang mas grub //
NK024(ya)001:17037: don dam dag pa'i chos nyid do //
NK024(ya)001:17038: drug byed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:17039: mthong ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK024(ya)001:17042: sdom pa gcig gsum la sogs te rigs gsum mam bdun nam nyi shu rtsa drug tu bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:17043: rigs gsum dbang byas gsum mam bdun //
NK024(ya)001:17044: yang na nyi shu dag tu bsrung //
NK024(ya)001:17048: dam tshig pa bran du dmigs pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:17050: ye shes sems dpa' rjer dmigs te //
NK024(ya)001:17051: dam tshig sems dpa' bran du blta //
NK024(ya)001:17052: gtsang ma'i phud dkyil mchog byas nas //
NK024(ya)001:17053: dngos grub dam pa thob par 'dod //
NK024(ya)001:17055: spyod pa ni bya ba drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:17056: bza' ba zas kyi bya ba dkar gsum mngar gsum bza'/
NK024(ya)001:17057: chang sha sgog btsong bsrung ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:17058: bgo ba gos kyi bya ba ras kha tshar ma nyams pa gyon pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17059: gtsang sbra khrus kyi bya ba bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:17060: nyon mongs pa mngon du rgyu ba rags pa'i bag chags lta ba rtogs pas 'dag /
NK024(ya)001:17061: bag la nyal gyi bag chags ting nge 'dzin goms pas 'dag /
NK024(ya)001:17062: spyod lam nyams pa'i dri ma lha'i dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing ye shes pa gshegs pa 'dag /
NK024(ya)001:17063: tha mal pa'i dri ma chus 'dag pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17065: tha ma dri ma chu yis 'dag /
NK024(ya)001:17066: chu ni sngags kyis 'dag par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17068: dngos grub brten gyi bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17069: dmigs pa'i rten yi dam lha'i sku gzugs gtsang sbra
NK024(ya)001:17070: bzhengs nas byed pa'o //'jug pa dus tshod kyi bya
NK024(ya)001:17072: tshes grangs bzang po la 'jug ste //
NK024(ya)001:17073: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK024(ya)001:17074: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:17075: gza' skar shis pas blangs bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:17078: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17079: de nyid gsum dang ldan pa ste /
NK024(ya)001:17083: sngags kyi skyon bcu spangs la bazla'o //
NK024(ya)001:17085: gsang ba gsum ldan skyon bcu spangs te blangs //
NK024(ya)001:17086: mtshams med lnga dang mi dge bcu spyod dang //
NK024(ya)001:17087: sdig pa gang byas bzlas brjod byas pas 'byang //
NK024(ya)001:17088: zhes so //'bras bu rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob ste /
NK024(ya)001:17089: dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba chos sku /
NK024(ya)001:17091: rigs kyi khro bo pho nya la sogs sprul sku /
NK024(ya)001:17093: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs shing //
NK024(ya)001:17095: sangs rgyas phrin las kun rdzogs nas //
NK024(ya)001:17100: ston pa bcom ldan 'das sam phyag na rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:17103: dbang ri rab mchod rten la sogs kri ya'i dbang nyer drug /
NK024(ya)001:17104: gang gi phyir na dam tshig dang ldan pa rjes su bzung ba'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:17105: dgongs pa dbang bskur ba'i 'bras bu de dag go //
NK024(ya)001:17106: de nas dbang de brtan pa'i phyi gdams ngag lam 'khyer gsal gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17107: spyi bor thig le dkar dmar mthing gsum brtsegs mar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:17109: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:17111: tshur 'dus spyi bor thims pas 'jam dpal ser po ral gri u t+pal 'dzin par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:17113: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:17115: tshur 'dus mgrin par thim pas spyan gzigs dkar po pad+ma 'dzin par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:17117: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:17119: tshur 'dus snying khar thim pas phyag na rdo rje sngon po rdo rje 'dzin par bsgom /
NK024(ya)001:17120: de ltar sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor
NK024(ya)001:17121: sgoms nas spyod lam rnam bzhi lha gsum gyi ngang
NK024(ya)001:17123: zhes gsungs pas 'di rnams kyi don rags pa tsam
NK024(ya)001:17124: gong du bstan pa tsam gyis shes par nus pa
NK024(ya)001:17125: / 'on kyang gtso bor lam 'khyer bzhi'i theg pa ni kri ya ste /
NK024(ya)001:17126: de'i dang po 'jug sgo khrus dang gtsang sbra byas
NK024(ya)001:17127: te dbang lam 'khyer shugs bstan du 'byung ba kri
NK024(ya)001:17128: ya'i dbang nyer drug po de thob nas /
NK024(ya)001:17129: lha lam 'khyer ni yongs grags kyi rigs gsum mgon po /
NK024(ya)001:17130: de yang gang mos so so'am gcig tu nyams su len tshul gdams ngag dang sgom skabs su 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:17131: snying po ni rigs gsum mgon po gsum ga'i snying po 'bru drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:17132: 'jam dbyangs la w+aa g+ai shwa ri mum zhes 'bru drug /
NK024(ya)001:17133: spyan ras gzigs kyi yi ge drug pa ma ni pad+me h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:17134: phyag rdor gyi 'bru drug badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:17136: theg pa lam 'khyer gyi gnyis pa lta ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17137: don dam dag pa mtha' bzhi dang bral ba stong
NK024(ya)001:17138: gsal chen por rtogs pa'i mnyam gzhag gi rjes thob
NK024(ya)001:17139: tu phyi nang gi 'char sgo dug gsum srid gsum
NK024(ya)001:17140: sogs gsum chos thams cad rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17141: du 'khyer zhing / gsum pa tshul khrims sam dam
NK024(ya)001:17142: tshig rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig ni gong du sdom
NK024(ya)001:17144: sku'i dam tshig tu dam tshig dang sdom pa'i tshogs bsrung zhing bsgrub pa /
NK024(ya)001:17145: gsung pad+ma'i rigs kyi dam tshig tu phyi nang gsang ba'i dam chos bsgrag bzung bya ba /
NK024(ya)001:17146: thugs rdo rje'i rigs kyi dam tshig gsum ste /
NK024(ya)001:17149: thugs rdo rje rnams brten cing bzung ba sogs gsum
NK024(ya)001:17150: po la rgyas par phye ste bdun nam nyi shu
NK024(ya)001:17151: rtsa drug tu 'gyur ba'i tshul rnams bzung ba ni
NK024(ya)001:17152: bya rgyud kho na'i sngags sdom bsrung bya'i dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:17153: yin / bzhi pa ting nge 'dzin ni lha ye shes sems dpa' rje bo'i tshul dang /
NK024(ya)001:17154: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' bran du dmigs te mchod pa 'bul zhing dngos grub len pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:17155: lnga pa spyod pa ni bya ba drug ste /
NK024(ya)001:17156: bza' ba zas kyi bya ba sha chang sgog btsong spangs te /
NK024(ya)001:17157: de'i ldog pa dkar gsung mngar gsum bza'/
NK024(ya)001:17158: bgo ba gos kyi bya ba ras kha tshar ma nyams pa gyon /
NK024(ya)001:17159: khrus kyi bya ba la bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:17160: nyon mongs mngon rgyu'i bag chags lta bas bkru /
NK024(ya)001:17161: bag la nyal gyi bag chags ting nge 'dzin gyis bkru /
NK024(ya)001:17162: spyod lam gyi nyes dri lha gshegs dkyil 'khor bsdus pas bkru /
NK024(ya)001:17163: tha mal gyi dri ma sngags bzlas pa'i chus bkru pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17164: dngos grub rten gyi bya ba yi dam gyi bris sku'am 'bur sku gtsang sbra dang ldan par bzhengs /
NK024(ya)001:17165: 'jug pa dus tshod kyi bya ba ni yar ngo'i brgyad dang skar ma rgyal sogs yin /
NK024(ya)001:17166: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba ni de nyid gsum ldan gyi bzlas pa skyon bcu spang ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:17170: skyon bcu spang te bzlas pas mi dge bcu la sogs pa'i sdig pa 'dag go //
NK024(ya)001:17172: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa zhes bya ste dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i chos sku /
NK024(ya)001:17174: rigs gsum de gsum gyi sprul pa khro bo dang pho nya /
NK024(ya)001:17175: sprul sku'i 'bras bu skye ba bdun nas thob par bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:17176: 'gag drug ni rtsa ba ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:17177: nyams khrid kyi gtso bo ngang sgom gdams ngag gsal 'debs ni /
NK024(ya)001:17178: rang tha mal pa'i spyi bor thig le mthing kha /
NK024(ya)001:17180: de'i steng du dkar po ste sum brtsegs su bsam pa'i dang po dkar po las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:17181: sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:17182: 'phags pa'i tshogs la mchod pa phul /
NK024(ya)001:17183: tshur 'dus rang gi spyi bor thim pas spyi bor
NK024(ya)001:17184: 'jam dbyangs ser po ral gri ut+pala 'dzin pa zhig
NK024(ya)001:17185: gsal gdab / de bzhin du thig le dmar po las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:17187: tshur 'dus mgrin par thim pas rang gi mgrin par
NK024(ya)001:17188: spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa
NK024(ya)001:17189: spyi ltar bsgom / yang thig le mthing kha las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:17191: tshur 'dus rang gi snying gar thim pas rang gi
NK024(ya)001:17192: snying gar phyag rdor sngon po rdo rje sdig mdzub
NK024(ya)001:17193: can khro tshul dang ldan par gsal gdab /
NK024(ya)001:17194: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor sgom pa yin pas /
NK024(ya)001:17195: za nyal 'gro 'dug gi spyod lam bzhir lha gsum
NK024(ya)001:17196: gyi nga rgyal las mi 'da' bar bslab par mdzod
NK024(ya)001:17197: / des bya rgyud kri ya'i theg pa'i smin grol
NK024(ya)001:17198: rnams legs par grub pas dam tshig dang sdom pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17199: tshogs tshul bzhin bsrung snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK024(ya)001:17201: dam tshig khas blang gtang rag gi yon dbul ba bran du khas blang sogs rjes chos gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:17202: dge bsngo sogs snga ma ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17203: rtsa bar de nas dkyil 'khor bsdu /
NK024(ya)001:17204: zhes 'byung bas dkyil 'khor mchod pa rnams kha gsos shing byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:17205: mchod bstod bzod gsol nyer bsdu bsngo smon sogs dkyil 'khor snga ma rnams ltar bya /
NK024(ya)001:17209: bcom ldan gser mdog ri yi rgyal po 'dra //'jig rten gsum mgon 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi sku //
NK024(ya)001:17210: bde gshegs sku yi bkra shis gang lags pa //
NK024(ya)001:17211: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:17212: bcom ldan dngul mdog ri yi 'jig rten gsum mgon spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung //
NK024(ya)001:17213: bde gshegs gsung gi bkra shis des kyang bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:17214: mthing nag ri yi 'jig rten gsum mgon phyag na
NK024(ya)001:17215: rdo rje'i thugs // bde gshegs thugs kyi bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:17216: des kyang shar lho nub byang dpal be'u 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:17217: rdo rje'i thugs // dang // pad+ma rgyal mtshan gdugs bum dung dang nya //
NK024(ya)001:17218: lha mo brgyad kyi bkra shis bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:17219: ces brjod cing me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:17222: dge ba'i rtsa ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17223: zhes gsungs pa ni gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:17224: nub mo chog gzhung tshogs bskang sogs kyang snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:17226: rmad byung rdo rje theg pa'i ri dbang gi //
NK024(ya)001:17227: rtsa bar yongs 'khyil bya rgyud rgya mtsho'i 'jing //
NK024(ya)001:17228: smin grol rin chen nor bus legs gang ba //
NK024(ya)001:17229: don gnyer gdengs can tshogs kyi rol pa'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:17230: rnam dag mtho ris dbang gi chu bo'i rgyun //
NK024(ya)001:17231: yongs 'dzin tshangs pa'i ral par legs gnas pa //
NK024(ya)001:17232: gdul bya'i klungs su 'dren byed cho ga'i khrigs //
NK024(ya)001:17233: skal ldan shing rta'i rnam dpyod bdag blor 'khyil //
NK024(ya)001:17234: phyogs 'dir mos ldan blo gsal rig 'dzin tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:17235: don gnyis bdud rtsi'i dpal la spyod 'dod na //
NK024(ya)001:17236: dam gtsang lag pa'i snyim pa kha phye la //
NK024(ya)001:17237: smin grol chu bo'i rgyun 'di legs 'thung zhig /
NK024(ya)001:17238: ces pa'ang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////u pa ya'i theg pa la /
NK024(ya)001:17241: dus bzang sa btsal blang bsrung sbyangs //
NK024(ya)001:17242: sa bzung byin brlab bsnyed thig gdab //
NK024(ya)001:17243: gsol gdab dal bri mchod bsham khrus //
NK024(ya)001:17244: chos bshad dang bskyed drang phyag bya //
NK024(ya)001:17245: gzhung bsrung spyan drang mchod bstod cha gsum btang //
NK024(ya)001:17246: bum bzlas 'dzab bya sbyin sreg bya //
NK024(ya)001:17247: chos bshad sems bskyed dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:17248: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //
NK024(ya)001:17250: phyir dgos gtang rag rig dbye bya //
NK024(ya)001:17251: gshegs gsol bkra shis bsngo ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:17252: zhes don bzhi bcur nye bas bsdus pa'i /
NK024(ya)001:17253: de la dang po dus ni /
NK024(ya)001:17255: sangs rgyas kyi dus mchod la byas na bsod nams bye ba phrag brgya'i 'gyur yod de /
NK024(ya)001:17257: rgyal gyi nya la bltams shing chos la gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:17258: dgun gyi nyi ma ldog pa'i dus yin no //
NK024(ya)001:17259: rta yi yar ngo cho 'phrul che ba bstan //
NK024(ya)001:17260: mu stegs ston pa rnam gsum 'khor bcas btul //
NK024(ya)001:17261: khra zla'i nya nas zhag bcu nyer lnga las //
NK024(ya)001:17262: tshangs pa'i drang srong btul nas sngags dbang bskur //
NK024(ya)001:17263: nag pa'i brgyad nas bco lnga sangs rgyas kun //
NK024(ya)001:17264: dngos kyi dbang bskur rdo rje theg lam ston //
NK024(ya)001:17265: sa ga'i nya yi dkar nag mtshams sangs rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:17266: dpyid ka nam dang nyi ma mnyam dus yin //
NK024(ya)001:17267: chu zla'i tshes lnga tshes brgyad chos 'khor bskor //
NK024(ya)001:17268: dbyar nyi log dus me tog ug chos skye //
NK024(ya)001:17269: dbyug zla cho 'phrul chung ba mu stegs kyi //
NK024(ya)001:17270: ston pa drug btul ston ka'i nyin mtshan mnyam //
NK024(ya)001:17271: myang 'das de yi tshes brgyad nam phyed yin //
NK024(ya)001:17272: zhes pas dus de dag la 'jug par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17273: zhes gsungs kyang 'di dag la bshad tshod spyi dang
NK024(ya)001:17274: mi mthun pa 'ga' re 'dug pas dpyad par bya'o
NK024(ya)001:17275: // gnyis pa sa btsal ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17276: zhi rgyas la bkra shis pa'i sa /
NK024(ya)001:17277: drag po la gdug pa can gyi sa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17278: gsum pa sa blang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:17279: bzhi pa sa bsrung ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:17280: lnga pa sa sbyang ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:17281: drug pa sa bzung ba rnams gong ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17282: zhes gsungs pa gong du rgyas par grub phyir 'dir mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:17283: bdun pa byin gyis brlab pa ni spyi theg dgu'i
NK024(ya)001:17284: chog phrin rgyas bsdus gang yang rung bas gnas de'i
NK024(ya)001:17285: steng du srid rtse nas 'og dmyal ba'i bar gyi
NK024(ya)001:17286: gnas dang 'gro ba thams cad 'od zer gyis khyab
NK024(ya)001:17287: pa'i bskyed rdzogs brtan pa cig sgom par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17288: zhes gsungs pa spyir thog mar lnga pa sa sbyang ba'i skabs su grub zin pas des khyab bo //
NK024(ya)001:17290: byang sems kyi mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang /
NK024(ya)001:17291: kri ya'i bkra shis nyer drug /
NK024(ya)001:17292: yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa bzhi la tshang bar
NK024(ya)001:17293: byas nas u pa ya'i dbang sgos su mi byed
NK024(ya)001:17294: pa yod kyang / dka' thub rig byed theg pa yang //'di yang yul gyi gsum nyid de //
NK024(ya)001:17297: 'bring gi rab yo gas 'dul bar gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:17298: u pa cis kyang dgos so //
NK024(ya)001:17299: zhes gsungs pa'i don dka' thub rig byed kyi theg
NK024(ya)001:17300: pa la gsum yod pa'i bar ma u pa la
NK024(ya)001:17301: spyod pa'i rgyud de nyid chad du mi rung bas
NK024(ya)001:17302: bye brag tu bgyis pa legs so //
NK024(ya)001:17305: bya rgyud gtso bor byas pas u pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:17306: rnal 'byor rgyud gtso bor byas pa'i u pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17307: zhes gsungs pa ni lha thems las /
NK024(ya)001:17308: u pa yo ga spyod pa'i rgyud //
NK024(ya)001:17309: gnyis ka rgyud kyi theg pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:17310: kri ya'i zhor dang yo ga'i shugs //
NK024(ya)001:17311: yang na zur du dkyil 'khor mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:17312: ces gsungs pas bya rgyud kyi zhor du byed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:17313: yo ga'i shugs bstan du byed pa gnyis sam yang
NK024(ya)001:17314: na zur du byed pa las 'dir zur du byed
NK024(ya)001:17315: pa'o // dang po bya rgyud gtso bor byas pa'i u pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17317: phyag rdor dbang bskur ba'i rgyud dang /
NK024(ya)001:17318: rdo rje ri rab brtsegs pa'i rgyud las /
NK024(ya)001:17323: chang la sogs pa yang ma bkag /
NK024(ya)001:17324: bya rgyud dang 'gal ba ltar snang yang skyon med de //
NK024(ya)001:17326: lha rigs gsum gang byed kyang bum bzlas kyi skabs
NK024(ya)001:17327: su chur zhu bas las kyi lha gcig dgos pa
NK024(ya)001:17328: bum pa gzhan nam de nyid du khams gsum rnam
NK024(ya)001:17329: rgyal bskyed bzlas nas bar chad bsrung bar bsgo ba'o
NK024(ya)001:17330: // rigs gsum las kyi lha dang bzhi'o //
NK024(ya)001:17334: h+aum yid dran pa thugs te sgo gsum sku gsung thugs te /
NK024(ya)001:17336: sku gsung thugs su ldan pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:17337: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gi //
NK024(ya)001:17338: bdag por khyod kyis dbang bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:17340: bdag po ni ye shes rdo rje'o //
NK024(ya)001:17341: gnyis pa rnal 'byor rgyud gtso bor byas pa'i u pa ya ni /
NK024(ya)001:17345: u pa ni rigs gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:17348: ling tshe dgu'i dbus su rnam snang ser po mnyam
NK024(ya)001:17349: gzhag can shar du rdo rje sogs kyang gsungs so
NK024(ya)001:17351: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK024(ya)001:17352: sangs rgyas rgyal ba kun 'dus pa //
NK024(ya)001:17353: zhes rigs lnga tshang ba ste /
NK024(ya)001:17354: rnam snang mdzad kyi ye shes ni //
NK024(ya)001:17355: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs la gsal //
NK024(ya)001:17356: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes ni //
NK024(ya)001:17357: rnam snang mdzad kyi thugs la gsal //
NK024(ya)001:17358: zhes pas rnam snang me long /
NK024(ya)001:17362: bya grub don yod kyang slob dpon pad+ma'i sku gsum dbye ba las /
NK024(ya)001:17363: rig pa rnam snang chos sku mi bskyod pa snying po byang chub na bzhugs pa'i sku /
NK024(ya)001:17367: zhes ye shes lnga rigs lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:17368: ye shes dang rdo rje bzhir byed pas u pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17369: yang sems dpa' bzhi ltar na /
NK024(ya)001:17372: 'phro 'du ting 'dzin gsum gsal bas phyi lus dam tshig sems dpa'/
NK024(ya)001:17373: nang thugs ye shes sems dpa'i /
NK024(ya)001:17374: bar ting 'dzin sems dpa' gsum gcig tu gsal bas rdo rje sems dpa' ste /
NK024(ya)001:17375: de'i dbus su gtsang rme med par sha chang la spyod cing rdzas mchog la'ang bran pas chog pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17376: de'ang bdag bskyed mdun bskyed gnyis ka'ang sems dpa' bzhi ste /
NK024(ya)001:17378: da ni bdun pa u pa'i khrid //
NK024(ya)001:17379: lha dang bdag nyid dpon g.yog blta //
NK024(ya)001:17380: lus ngag yid gsum phyag rgya sgom //
NK024(ya)001:17393: dbus su rnam snang chos 'chad kyi steng na 'khor lo can /
NK024(ya)001:17394: shar du mi bskyod pa sa gnon rdo rje can /
NK024(ya)001:17395: lhor rin 'byung mchog sbyin rin chen can //
NK024(ya)001:17396: nub tu snang mtha' mnyam gzhag pad+ma can /
NK024(ya)001:17397: byang du don grub skyabs sbyin rgya gram can no //
NK024(ya)001:17398: kun rdo rje skyil krung chos gos can rgyan gyis spras pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17399: grwa bzhir mchod pa'i lha mo dang /
NK024(ya)001:17400: snam bu la bkra shis kyi lha mo //
NK024(ya)001:17401: khyams la dpal mgon bdun cu rtsa lnga ste /
NK024(ya)001:17405: go drug ste rgyas bsdus gang mos su bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17409: spyi spyod rgyud 'dir rnam snang la rigs lngas bskor ba'i lha lnga ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17410: rigs lnga'i steng du sgeg sogs mchod lha brgyad bsnam pas bcu gsum ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17411: bcu gsum gyi steng du bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad bsnan pas lha nyer gcig ma /
NK024(ya)001:17412: de'i steng du mgon po bdun cu rtsa lnga bsnan
NK024(ya)001:17413: pas lha go drug ma ste phye na dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17414: bzhi gsungs pa / bzhi ka dgos pa ma yin te /
NK024(ya)001:17415: rgyas par na go drug gi khongs su gong ma thams cad 'du la /
NK024(ya)001:17416: 'bring po gnyis gang bde dang bsdu na lha lnga mar 'dus pas /
NK024(ya)001:17417: lam du dkyil 'khor gcig kho nas khyab pa'i phyir /
NK024(ya)001:17418: 'dir rgyas par lha go drug ma kho na bya
NK024(ya)001:17419: ba la 'dir cho ga mi gsal ba rnams dang
NK024(ya)001:17420: / med du mi rung ba 'ga' zhig spyod rgyud
NK024(ya)001:17421: rnam par snang mdzad mngon par byang chub pa'i rgyud
NK024(ya)001:17422: kyi cho ga las blangs te /
NK024(ya)001:17423: skyabs sems mdor bsdus pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK024(ya)001:17424: na mahs man+ta badz+ra n+aam badz+ra +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:17425: bdag nyid tha mal pa'i lus spangs nas rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:17426: sems dpa'i sku zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi nang na
NK024(ya)001:17427: bzhugs shing / zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'od dang
NK024(ya)001:17428: ldan pa phyag gnyis kyi rdo rje dang dril bu
NK024(ya)001:17429: bzhugs shing / bsnams pa / dbu rgyan la sogs pa'i rgyan sna tshogs pas brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:17430: thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pa dang bcas par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:17431: thal mo khong stong du sbyar ba'i mdzub mo gnyis gung mo'i phyi nas 'khyud pa go cha'i rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17432: na mahs man+ta badz+ra n+aam badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:17433: rang gi lus la rdo rje'i go gyon par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:17434: de nas stegs bu'am zhal ba dri bzang gi chus byugs pas /
NK024(ya)001:17435: dkyil 'khor sgo rdzogs lte ba pad+ma 'dab bzhi'am 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17436: lo rtsibs bzhi pa gang bder byas pa'i phyir lha
NK024(ya)001:17437: snam dang phyi rol gyi pad+ma dang rdo rje'i ra
NK024(ya)001:17438: ba'i bar du khor yug dang bcas pa'i las thig
NK024(ya)001:17439: btab la lha gnas so sor dri bzang gi chus
NK024(ya)001:17443: dbus su tshom bu bkod cing /
NK024(ya)001:17445: rnam snang dkar po chos 'chad kyi steng na 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17446: lo bsnams pa sogs mdun bskyed ltar gsal 'debs shing
NK024(ya)001:17451: nub tu pad+ma a mi de ba h+r+aih snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK024(ya)001:17452: byang du karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a /
NK024(ya)001:17454: gra bzhi'i nang du shar lho nas badz+ra l+aa s+ye h'u /
NK024(ya)001:17457: rdo rje phreng ba ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17458: badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih rdo rje glu ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17460: rdo rje gar ma ste bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:17461: de bzhin rgyab tu tshom bu bkod cing /
NK024(ya)001:17463: rdo rje bdug spos ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17465: rdo rje me tog ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17466: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih rdo rje mar me ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:17468: rdo rje dri chab ma ste bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:17469: lha snam la phyogs rer tshom bu gnyis re bkod cing /
NK024(ya)001:17470: tram mam ga la de wi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:17471: zhes brjod pa ni bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad do //
NK024(ya)001:17472: phyi'i khor yug la mgon po bdun cu rtsa lnga'i
NK024(ya)001:17473: tshom bu bkod de dam tshig pa ji lta ba
NK024(ya)001:17474: bzhin bsam mo //'di la ye shes pa spyan drang
NK024(ya)001:17476: sngags rgyas bskyed pa tsam rnam snang mngon byang du bshad pa ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:17477: mchod pa bzhi'i dod dang po phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17479: phyag 'tshal byang chub sems khyod la //
NK024(ya)001:17481: spyod gzugs khyod dang sa dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:17482: pha rol phyin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:17483: phyag 'tshal thog mar byed khyod la //
NK024(ya)001:17485: gnyis pa phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17486: tshom bu'i mthar bshams te mchod yon gyi phyag rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17487: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na sa ma sa ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17489: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam bi shud+d+ha ga nad+d+hoda b+h+aa wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17491: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ma h+aa meer+t+ya b+h+yud ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17493: na mahs ma n+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam d+h+aarma d+h+aa tu a nu ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17495: na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK024(ya)001:17496: a ri tsa s+pha ra na a wa b+h+aa sa
NK024(ya)001:17497: ga ga nod t+aa ra b+h+yah s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17499: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam tree ya d+hi k+aa n+aam
NK024(ya)001:17500: a ra ra pa ra ra bi la de wa
NK024(ya)001:17502: zhes sogs kyi mchod pa rnams sngags rgya de dag
NK024(ya)001:17503: lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs rjes sngags rgya lan
NK024(ya)001:17505: phyag rgya de dag 'og tu 'chad do //
NK024(ya)001:17507: thal mo khong stong du sbyar ba mthe bong gnyis phye ste /
NK024(ya)001:17508: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam am a s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17509: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa sogs
NK024(ya)001:17510: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags lan gsum brjod la mchod
NK024(ya)001:17511: pa rgya chen pos mchod par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:17512: bzhi pa sgrub pa'i mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17513: byams pa dang snying rje bsgoms la /
NK024(ya)001:17514: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:17515: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sbyin stobs dang //
NK024(ya)001:17516: chos kyi dbyings kyi stobs kyis su //
NK024(ya)001:17517: sems can rnams la phan 'dod pas //
NK024(ya)001:17518: don rnams gang dag bsam pa kun //
NK024(ya)001:17519: sems can khams ni ma lus 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:17520: de dag thams cad ci rigs par //
NK024(ya)001:17521: thogs pa med par 'byung gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:17522: ces mchod pa bzhis mchod de /
NK024(ya)001:17523: sta gon la gnas par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17525: de nas bum pa dang mchod pa bsham la /
NK024(ya)001:17526: zhes 'byung ba'i bum pa bsham pa 'og tu 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:17528: gsol gdab ni spos thogs la thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:17530: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:17532: che ge mo'am slob ma'i don ched du //
NK024(ya)001:17533: sta gon la ni dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:17536: zhes zhus pas gnang ba thob par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:17538: gzhung gzhan las kyang 'di nam mkhar mi 'degs par
NK024(ya)001:17539: na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK024(ya)001:17540: a d+hish+tha na a d+hish+thi te a tsa le bi
NK024(ya)001:17541: ma le s+pha ra na pra kri te pa ri
NK024(ya)001:17542: shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa / zhes brjod pas dri'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17543: la gnas pa'i lha rnams mnyes par gyur te mi
NK024(ya)001:17544: snang bar bsam la tshom bu dang mchod pa rnams
NK024(ya)001:17545: shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa / bsdu'o // lha sta gon bsnyen pa'i cho ga'o //
NK024(ya)001:17546: slob ma sta gon 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin 'dis
NK024(ya)001:17547: blang ba'am yang na dkyus bzhin dngos ste sbrel lo
NK024(ya)001:17549: dgu pa thig gi nang ling tshe dagu'am 'dab bzhi'am rtsibs bzhi gang mos bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17550: sgo rta babs la sogs sbyi dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:17552: bcu gcig pa dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17553: rlung chen chu tshon dang rlan chen rdul tshon //
NK024(ya)001:17554: rang byung gi tshon nam med na bsgyur tshon gyis gong du bstan pa ltar bri bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17555: zhes gsungs pa'i don lte ba dkar po 'dab bzhir byed na shar sngo /
NK024(ya)001:17559: 'khor lo byed na phyogs mdog gong ltar /
NK024(ya)001:17561: lha snam dkar po rtsig pa nang nas dkar ser
NK024(ya)001:17562: dmar ljang sngo ba spyod rgyud phyogs chen gyi lhor
NK024(ya)001:17563: lta bas nang khyams shar dmar /
NK024(ya)001:17568: phyi rol gyi khor yug sngon po bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17569: lha mtshan ni mdun bskyed sgrub mchod skabs bzhin la lha gnas su tsakli bkod dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:17570: spyod rgyud skabs 'dir dmigs bsal dkyil 'khor la bris
NK024(ya)001:17571: 'bur gyi skur bkod dgos par gsungs pas gtso bo
NK024(ya)001:17572: lnga gnas so sor bkod cing lhag ma rnams la
NK024(ya)001:17574: de nas slar yang mchod pa bsham /
NK024(ya)001:17575: cha gsum dang gtor ma gzhan yang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:17576: zhes gsungs pa dkyil 'khor gyi mthar nyer spyod ni /
NK024(ya)001:17577: mchod yon dri chab me tog spos mar me zhal zas rnams bkod pa ni khyad chos dang /
NK024(ya)001:17578: mchod pa'i bum pa brgyad dam bcu drug gam gcig sogs pa yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:17579: dkyil 'khor ba la dbul ba'i gtor ma yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:17580: cha gsum gyi gtor ma gsar du bsham zhing dkyil
NK024(ya)001:17581: 'khor med na mchod pa rnams kha gsos shing bla
NK024(ya)001:17582: med kyi rgyun gtor rnams kyang kha gso /
NK024(ya)001:17583: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:17584: bum pa bcud ldan dar dkar pos dkris pa 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17585: lo'i mtshan ma can kha rgyan rdor gzungs /
NK024(ya)001:17586: dri'i dung chos dang bcas pa'ang bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:17587: slob dpon gyi mdun du las bum bcud ldan dar
NK024(ya)001:17588: dkar pos dkris pa rdo rje'i mtshan ma dgod pa
NK024(ya)001:17589: kha rgyan dang bcas pa yang nyer bsdogs bya /
NK024(ya)001:17592: de nas rdo rje dril bu thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:17593: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing /
NK024(ya)001:17594: bdud sde dngos rnams bcom ldan rnam snang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:17595: zhes pas mchod bstod la sogs pas spyan drangs la cha gsum rgyas par btang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:17596: bum par cha gsum gyi rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:17597: dkyil 'khor du rigs lnga bskyed cing /
NK024(ya)001:17602: a mi de wa h+r+aih a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a zhes bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:17603: skabs 'dir zhi rgyas dbang drag gi sbyin sreg bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17604: zhes pa tsam las ma bstan cing /
NK024(ya)001:17606: slob dpon pad+ma'i sku gsum dbye ba las /
NK024(ya)001:17608: 'du shes tsam spangs rang gi ngo bo bstan du med pas /
NK024(ya)001:17609: ye shes rang rig pa tsam ni chos kyi sku'o //
NK024(ya)001:17610: longs sku rdo rje 'dzin pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:17611: lag na pad+mo la sogs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17612: sprul sku ni kha cig la nyan thos dang /
NK024(ya)001:17613: kha cig la dbang po'i gzugs can no //
NK024(ya)001:17615: zhes gsal bar ma bstan cing /
NK024(ya)001:17616: mdo dbang khams lugs su kri ya'i khongs su u
NK024(ya)001:17617: pa bsdus te sgrub mchod dbang bskur sogs mi mdzad
NK024(ya)001:17618: cing / glan ston sogs kyang de ltar bzhed par snang /
NK024(ya)001:17619: 'on kyang zur lugs kyi yig rnying gi rtsa ba
NK024(ya)001:17620: 'di tsam la brten nas rnam snang mngon byang sogs
NK024(ya)001:17621: las btus te bri bar bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:17623: bcu gnyis pa rten 'brel rab gnas bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:17624: zhes gsungs pa rdor dril dang bcas te me tog 'thor zhing ye d+har+m+aa brjod la /
NK024(ya)001:17625: thog mar sngon 'gro'i gtor ma bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:17627: b+hu mi pa ti sa pa ri w+aa ra a k+aa ro lan gsum gyis bsngosa /
NK024(ya)001:17628: me tog sogs kyis mchod la rdor dril 'dzin pas /
NK024(ya)001:17629: lha dang lha min gsang sngags dang //
NK024(ya)001:17630: phyogs bcu kun gyi dri za dang //
NK024(ya)001:17631: gza' dang mi'am ci gang dag /
NK024(ya)001:17632: bgegs kyi tshogs rnams rab tu nyon //
NK024(ya)001:17633: bdag gis de ring khyod mchod kyis //
NK024(ya)001:17634: song zhig bgegs chen 'gro bar gyis //
NK024(ya)001:17635: phyin chad de ltar ma byed cig /
NK024(ya)001:17636: khyod kyi stobs dang rtsal mthong na //
NK024(ya)001:17637: khyod ni bgegs kyang byed par nus //
NK024(ya)001:17638: khyod ni lha yi sprul pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:17639: khyod ni bgegs byed mi nus min //
NK024(ya)001:17640: sngon chad mchod sbyin ma thob pas //
NK024(ya)001:17641: de ring bdag gis mchod byas nas //
NK024(ya)001:17642: khyod kyis kyang ni mchod khyed la //
NK024(ya)001:17643: bgegs kyi dbang po khyod song zhig /
NK024(ya)001:17646: na mahs man+ta badz+ra nam tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha
NK024(ya)001:17647: na s+pho ta ya h+aum ta ka ham zhes mi
NK024(ya)001:17648: g.yo bas bsang / stong pa'i ngang las las rin
NK024(ya)001:17649: po che'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:17650: nang du so so'i rig pas byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17651: g.yo bas bsang / mchod yon / dri chab /
NK024(ya)001:17655: zhal zas la sogs pa mchod rdzas ji snyed yod
NK024(ya)001:17656: pa thams cad dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam
NK024(ya)001:17658: lag gnyis thal mo gyen du bkan la g.yas kyi
NK024(ya)001:17659: mthe bo dang mathe'u chung gis g.yon gyi mthe bong
NK024(ya)001:17660: dang mathe'u chung la 'khrud cing sor mo lhag ma
NK024(ya)001:17661: rnams snyim pa ltar bzed pa mchod yon gyi rgyas
NK024(ya)001:17662: / na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga na sa ma sa ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17663: lag gnyis gshibs te thal mo kha phyir bstan du bkan /
NK024(ya)001:17664: mthe bo gnyis mdzub mo la sbyar ba dri chab kyi rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17665: na ma sa man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam bi shud+d+he gan d+ho da b+h+aa wa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17666: lag pa gnyis gyen bstan mtheb srin rtse sbyar me tog 'dzin tshul gyi rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17667: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ma h+aa meer+t+ya b+h+yud ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17668: rdo rje khu tshur gnyis mthur du spubs tshul bdug spos kyi rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17669: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam d+harma d+h+aa tu a nu ga te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17670: lag gnyis gshibs te gyen bstan gyi mthe bo bkan la gyen du sgreng ba mar me'i rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17671: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK024(ya)001:17672: a ri tsa s+pha ra na a wa b+h+aa sa
NK024(ya)001:17673: ga ga nod t+aa ra b+h+yahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17674: lag gnyis gyen du bkan pa'i mthe bo gnyis so
NK024(ya)001:17675: so'i lag mthil du bzhag pa la mdzub mos so
NK024(ya)001:17676: sor 'khyud pa zhal zas kyi rgyas /
NK024(ya)001:17677: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam tree ya d+hi k+aa n+aam
NK024(ya)001:17678: a ra ra pa ra ra bi la de wa
NK024(ya)001:17680: zhes sngags rgya rnams lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:17681: skyabs sems bdun rnam dag sogs bye brag pa yod
NK024(ya)001:17682: kyang 'dir 'jug pa bde zhing don la mi 'gal
NK024(ya)001:17683: bas / skyabs sems tshad med bzhi sogs spyi ltar la bdun rnam dag ni /
NK024(ya)001:17684: mdun gyi nam mkhar dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo mngon sum lta bur dmigs la /
NK024(ya)001:17685: na mahgu ru b+h+yah na mah man+dala sa pa ri wa ra b+h+yah zhes phyag dang /
NK024(ya)001:17686: gu ru man+dala sa pa ri w+aa ra a r+g+ham sogs kyis mchod cing /
NK024(ya)001:17687: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK024(ya)001:17691: rnam snang mngon byang las kyang rnam snang gtso rkyang du mdzad la /
NK024(ya)001:17692: de yang rgyud sde'i babs kyi sngags rgya shin tu mang ba rnams btang snyoms su bzhag ste /
NK024(ya)001:17693: don mi 'gal tsam bsdu ba la /
NK024(ya)001:17694: rang gi snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor as mtshan
NK024(ya)001:17695: pa de'i sgra chos thams cad gdod nas ma byung
NK024(ya)001:17696: ma skyes pa'i stong par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:17697: stong pa'i ngang las rang sems zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17698: as mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las de'i ngang
NK024(ya)001:17699: nas snying rje'i dbang gi sgyu ma lta bu'i a
NK024(ya)001:17701: don gnyis byas yongs su gyur pa las bdag nyid
NK024(ya)001:17702: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad chen po pad
NK024(ya)001:17703: dkar dang zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs pa thor tshugs
NK024(ya)001:17704: dbu rgyan can / ras dar gyis stod smad g.yogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:17705: sku mdog dkar po zla ba'i dkyil 'khor ltar 'od
NK024(ya)001:17706: zer kun nas 'phro ba phyag gnyis chos 'chad kyis
NK024(ya)001:17707: 'khor lo 'dzin pa mtshan nyid thams cad rdzogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17708: skur gyur / lag gnyis khong stong du sbyar te
NK024(ya)001:17709: mthe bo gnyis phan tshun du phye nas gung mo
NK024(ya)001:17711: rnal 'byor 'dzin pa'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:17712: na mah san+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ma h+aa yo ga yo
NK024(ya)001:17713: gi shwa r+ai khwa na dza ri ke s+w+aa h+aa
NK024(ya)001:17714: / ting nge 'dzin yongs su rdzogs shing brtan par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:17715: rang dam tshig pa'i thugs kar zla ba las gnas pa'i bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:17716: zhes pa'i sngags phreng gis mtshan pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:17717: mdun stod du rang 'dra'i ye shes pa rnam snang
NK024(ya)001:17718: gi thugs kar zla dkyil sngags phreng dang bcas pa'ang
NK024(ya)001:17719: bsam la / mdun gyi lha'i thugs ka nas sngags
NK024(ya)001:17720: phreng rnams tshur byung ste snying khar gsan par bsam
NK024(ya)001:17721: la rlung nang du bsdus te bsams la sngags shub
NK024(ya)001:17722: bsam la / bur bzla / phyir gtor ba'i tshe
NK024(ya)001:17723: sngags phreng rnams phyir song ste mdun gyi lha'i thugs
NK024(ya)001:17724: kar gnas par bsam la srog rtsol bsdam te yid
NK024(ya)001:17725: bzlas bya'o //'di ni bi ma las /
NK024(ya)001:17726: da ni bdun pa u pa'i khrid //
NK024(ya)001:17727: lha dang bdag gnyis dpon g.yog blta //
NK024(ya)001:17728: lus ngag yid gsum phyag rgya sgom //
NK024(ya)001:17730: kun mkhyen klong chen zhabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:17731: spyod pas rang dang lha gnyis mnyam par blta //
NK024(ya)001:17732: rang nyid dam tshig mdun du ye shes lha //
NK024(ya)001:17733: grogs po'i tshul gyis dngos grub len pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:17735: ji ltar bya ba'i tshul rnam snang mngon byang ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:17737: skabs 'dir gsang chu'i dod dang las bum sgrub pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17739: bum pa gzhan nam de nyid du khams gsum rnam
NK024(ya)001:17740: rgyal bskyed bzlas nas bar chad bsrung bar sgom mo
NK024(ya)001:17742: mngon byang gi dkyil chog tu'ang skabs 'dir las bum
NK024(ya)001:17743: sgrub tshul gsungs pa cho ga mi 'dra ba'i khyad
NK024(ya)001:17745: 'jug pa bde ba'i phyir las bum kri ya'i skabs ltar 'dir bsgrub bo //
NK024(ya)001:17747: mngon byang gi dkyil chog tu bgegs bskrad bsrung sogs rgyas par 'byung kyang 'dir bsdus te /
NK024(ya)001:17748: gsum rgyal gyi sngags dang bcas las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:17749: stong pa'i ngang las bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang
NK024(ya)001:17750: mdzad kyi sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK024(ya)001:17751: cho 'phrul las byung ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi
NK024(ya)001:17752: sgo bzhi pa khang brtsegs kyi rnam pa can nub
NK024(ya)001:17753: phyogs kyi sgo rtag tu phye ba /
NK024(ya)001:17754: rtsig pa lnga nang nas rim bzhin dkar ser dmar
NK024(ya)001:17755: ljang sngo ba'i rim pa dang ldan pa'i phyir 'dod
NK024(ya)001:17757: sgo bzhir rta babs rim bzhi glo 'bur du byas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17762: dbus dkar ba la ka ba brgyad du btsugs pa
NK024(ya)001:17763: la thogs phub pa'i ya phubs shin tu mtho ba'i
NK024(ya)001:17764: rtser nor bu'i tog gis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:17765: pha gu dang d+r+wa phyed mda' yab shar bus brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:17766: phyi rol tu mtsho dang rdzing bu pad+ma sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:17767: dang chu bya ljon shing dang rin po che'i phreng
NK024(ya)001:17768: bas bskor zhing rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i ra ba
NK024(ya)001:17769: dang 'od zer gyi phreng bas khor yug tu bskor
NK024(ya)001:17770: pa'i nang gi dbus su pad+ma 'dab bzhi sdong bu
NK024(ya)001:17771: ge sar lha snam dang bcas par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:17772: dbus su bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad sku
NK024(ya)001:17773: mdog dkar po chos 'chad kyi steng na 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:17774: can / shar du mi bskyod pa sngon po g.yas sa gnon dang /
NK024(ya)001:17775: g.yon mnyam gzhag gi steng na rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17776: lhor rin 'byung ser po mchog sbyin dang mnyam gzhag gi steng na rin po che 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17777: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas dmar po mnyam gzhag gi steng na pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17778: byang du don yod grub pa ljang gu g.yas skyabs sbyin dang g.yon rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17779: lnga ka'ang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:17780: kyis brgyan cing rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs
NK024(ya)001:17781: pa'o // phyi rol gyi gra bzhi'i shar lhor sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17782: lho nub tu phreng ba ma ser mo me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17783: nub byang du glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
