NK024(ya)001:17784: byang shar du gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur ba /
NK024(ya)001:17785: de'i phyi rol gyi gra bzhi'i shar lhor bdug spos ma dkar mo bdug spos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17786: lho nub tu me tog ma dmar ser me tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17787: nub byang du mar me ma dmar mo mar me 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17788: byang shar du dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17789: snam bu'i shar du dus ldan ma dkar mo dpal be bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17790: pad+ma can dkar mo 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17791: lhor 'jigs bral ma sngon mo pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17792: 'od ldan ma sngon mo rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17793: nub tu mdangs can ma dmar mo gdugs 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17794: dri med ma dmar mo bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17795: byang du rgyal gdug ma ljang gu dung bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17796: yid bzang ma ljang gu gser nya 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17797: de dag thams cad kyang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17798: phyi rol gyi khor yug la mgon po bdun cu rtsa lnga ni /
NK024(ya)001:17799: shar du lha chen dbang phyug chen po dkar po tri shul 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17800: lhor brgya byin ser po rdo rje gdengs pa /
NK024(ya)001:17801: nub tu tshangs pa ser po rin po che 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17802: byang du khyab 'jug ljang gu 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17803: shar lhor 'dod pa'i dbang phyug dmar mo mda' lnga dang 'od ma'i gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17804: lho nub tu tshogs bdag dkar po dgra s+t+wa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17805: nub byang du b+h+ring gi ri ti dkar po rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17806: byang shar du gzhon nu gdong drug dmar po shak+ti dang mdung thung 'dzin pa ste lha chen brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:17807: shar du mtha' yas dkar po ut+pala 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17808: lhor 'jog po dmar po rin po che 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17809: nub tu stobs rgyu nag po sbrul 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17810: byang du rigs ldan ljang gu rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17811: shar lhor nor rgyas ser po bum pa 'dzin ba
NK024(ya)001:17812: lho nub tu dung skyong ljang gu dung 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:17813: / nub byang du pad+ma dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17814: byang shar du pad+ma chen po dmar po rin po
NK024(ya)001:17815: che dang sbrul zhags 'dzin pa gdengs ka dang sprul
NK024(ya)001:17817: shar du pa wa sangs dkar po me tog ku mu ta dang shing tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17818: lho phur bu mthing kha po ti bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17819: nub tu zla ba dkar po mchog sbyin gyis me tog ku mu ta 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17820: byang du lhag pa ljang gu ut+pala 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17821: shar lhor mig dmar dmar po bum pa dang me sgron 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17822: lho nub tu sgra gcan dud kha stod mi lus
NK024(ya)001:17823: la smad sbrul mjug can pad sdong dang ral gri
NK024(ya)001:17824: 'dzin pa / nub byang du nyi ma dmar ser pad+ma dang dbyug pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17825: byang shar du spen pa dmar nag dbyug to dang dgra s+t+wa 'dzin pa ste gza' brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:17826: shar du brgya byin mig stong pa dkar ser rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17827: shar lhor me lha dmar po bgrang phreng 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17828: lhor gshin rje sngo nag thod dbyug thogs pa /
NK024(ya)001:17829: lho nub tu bden bral smug nag dbyug pa dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17830: nub tu chu lha dkar dmar sbrul zhags bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17831: nub byang du rlung lha ljang gu ba dan 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17832: byang du gnod sbyin ljang ser dbyug to bsnams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17833: byang shar du dbang ldan thal skya rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17834: nub smad du sa'i lha mo gser mdog bum pas snams pa /
NK024(ya)001:17835: shar stod du nyi zla gnyis dmar dkar me tog 'dzin pa ste phyogs skyong bcu /
NK024(ya)001:17836: shar du smin drug dmar po rin po che'i gdu bu 'dzin pa bum pa'i khri la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17837: snar ma dkar po rna cha 'dzin pa khyu mchog gi khri la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17838: mgo ser po gdu bu bsnams pa sha ba'i khri la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17839: lag dmar po lag gdub bsnams pa sbrul gyi khri la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17840: nabs so dkar po gdu bu 'dzin pa pad+ma la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17841: rgyal dkar po rin chen 'dzin pa bum pa'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17842: skag dkar po rin po che'i ga'u 'dzin pa bya rog gi khrir gnas pa ste shar skar bdun /
NK024(ya)001:17843: mchu mthing kha snye ma 'dzin pa ma he'i khri la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17844: bre ljang gu pad+ma bsnams pa rin po che'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17845: dbo ser po mnyam bzhag gi steng na rin po
NK024(ya)001:17846: che'i myu gu 'dzin pa gser gyi khrir gnas pa
NK024(ya)001:17847: / me bzhi ser po pad dkar bsnams pa glang po che'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17848: nag pa ljang gu pad+ma bsnams pa rma bya'i khri gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17849: sa ri dmar po ri rab 'dzin pa spyang mo'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17850: sa ga mthing kha rin po che'i phreng ba bsnams pa rta'i khrir gnas pa ste lho skar bdun /
NK024(ya)001:17851: lha mtshams dmar ser bum pa 'dzin pa khyim bya'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17852: s+n+ron dmar po pad+ma bsnams pa nang tshangs can gyi gdan la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17853: snubs ljang gu dbyug pa 'dzin pa sbal pa'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17854: chu stod dmar po pad dmar 'dzin pa phub kyi khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17855: chu smad dmar skya pad+ma dang bum pa 'dzin pa mi'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17856: gro zhun dmar po pad+ma bum 'dzin kur ma'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17857: byi zhun sngon po pad+ma bum 'dzin sbre mong gi khrir gnas pa ste nub skar bdun /
NK024(ya)001:17858: mon gre dkar ljang ut+pala 'dzin pa glang dkar gyi khri gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17859: mon gru dkar ljang pad+ma 'dzin pa 'bol stan la gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17860: khrums stod ljang gu ral gri 'dzin pa rta'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17861: khrums smad ser po dbyug pa bsnams pa rin po che'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17862: nam gru ljang nag pad+ma 'dzin pa rta'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17863: dbyug gu ljang gu go cha bsnams pa mi'i khrir gnas pa /
NK024(ya)001:17864: bra nye sngo ljang 'khor lo 'dzin pa khri med pa ste byang skar bdun /
NK024(ya)001:17865: gnod sbyin brgyad ni phyogs bzhir gnod sbyin lag na
NK024(ya)001:17866: rdo rje can bzhi sngon po rdo rje 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:17867: / shar du gnod sbyin rdo rje 'chang dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:17868: lhor gnod sbyin ha ri ka sngon po /
NK024(ya)001:17869: nub tu pany+tsi ka dmar po /
NK024(ya)001:17870: byang du narti ka ser po rnams lcags khrab gyon zhing mtshon cha thogs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:17871: shar du yul 'khor srung dkar po pi wang sgreng ba /
NK024(ya)001:17872: lhor 'phags skyes po sngon po ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17873: nub tu spyan mi bzang dmar po sprul zhags 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17874: byang du rnam thos sras ljang ser ne'u le 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:17875: bzhi ka'ang go cha can no //'dir yang lha thems las /
NK024(ya)001:17876: lha brgyad klu brgyad gza' brgyad dang //
NK024(ya)001:17877: phyogs skyong nyi zla phyed bcu gcig /
NK024(ya)001:17878: rgyu skar nyer brgyad gnod sbyin brgyad //
NK024(ya)001:17879: rgyal chen bzhi ste bdun cu lnga //
NK024(ya)001:17881: 'dir rgyud de'i bzhugs tshul gyi ye shes pa dgug bstim sogs mi bya bar /
NK024(ya)001:17882: de ltar rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de'i 'og tu
NK024(ya)001:17883: gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17884: de lta bu'i rang bzhin du gsal bar bsgom zhing
NK024(ya)001:17885: / de la sngags rgyas gnas rnams dang lha rnams
NK024(ya)001:17886: byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshul 'byung kyang ha cang spros
NK024(ya)001:17887: pas dub ste bzhag pas de'i phyir rang bzhin dang
NK024(ya)001:17888: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor tha mi dad du bltas pas
NK024(ya)001:17889: / khyab / de la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17890: rnam snang mngon byang las btus pa 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:17892: bcom ldan 'das byang chub rtogs pa'i dus na rtag tu 'gro ba gsum la khyab par mdzad pas /
NK024(ya)001:17893: sems can gyi skal ba ji lta ba bzhin 'tshams
NK024(ya)001:17894: par snang ba 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das
NK024(ya)001:17895: pa'i rigs sngags dang gsang sngags la sogs pa'i ngo
NK024(ya)001:17896: bo nyid dag gis sems can rnams kyi don mdzad
NK024(ya)001:17898: gang du yang mi bzhud pa la gas na /
NK024(ya)001:17899: 'dir bdag cag rnams kyi rgyud sde las gsungs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:17900: cho ga bzhin du rang bzhin dang gzugs brnyan gyi
NK024(ya)001:17901: dkyil 'khor dbyer med par bskyed lags kyis /
NK024(ya)001:17902: bdag cag rnams kyi bsod nams spel ba'i slad du
NK024(ya)001:17903: sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:17904: du mngon sum ltar bzhugs shing byin gyis brlab tu
NK024(ya)001:17906: rnam snang mngon byang las ye shes pa spyan 'dren mi 'byung yang /
NK024(ya)001:17907: rtsa bar mdo tsam du gsungs pa bzhin spos btul zhing rdor dril dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:17908: ma lus sems can bdud sde dpung bcas dngos rnams
NK024(ya)001:17909: ma lus bcom ldan rnam snang 'khor bcas gshegs su
NK024(ya)001:17910: gsol // zhes spyan drangs te rang bzhin dang gzugs
NK024(ya)001:17911: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dbyer med du gyur par bsam
NK024(ya)001:17912: gsol // mo // mchod pa bzhi'i dang po phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17913: 'gro ba rgyud lnga 'khor ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:17914: sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor gyis gzir 'gro gzigs nas //
NK024(ya)001:17915: thugs rjes sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:17916: thugs rje'i bdag nyid khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:17917: sems can smin cing grol bar mdzad pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:17918: sems can khams na bzhugs shing spyod gyur kyang //
NK024(ya)001:17919: chags pas ma gos pad+ma ltar dag pa //'dod chags dag pa'i bdag nyid khyod la 'dud //
NK024(ya)001:17920: sems can bkren pa chos kyis phongs gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:17921: ma rig thibs po'i nang du song ba rnams //'phags pa'i nor bdun dag gis tshim mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:17922: ye shes sgron me khyod la phyag sems can 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor nub pa la //
NK024(ya)001:17923: thugs rjes thabs dang shes rab grur bzhugs nas //
NK024(ya)001:17924: zhi ba rin chen gling mchog skyel mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:17925: kun gyi ded dpon khyod la kun nas 'dud //
NK024(ya)001:17926: sems can las kyi chu bor gru nub rnams //
NK024(ya)001:17927: dam chos bdud rtsi'i zam pas sgrol mdzad cing //'phags lam yan lag brgyad la sbyor mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:17928: gsung gi mnga' bdag khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:17929: gnyis pa phyi'i mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:17930: rab 'byams zhing rnams mtha' yas par //
NK024(ya)001:17931: bdag pos bzung dang ma bzung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:17932: dri zhim tsan+dana ga bur dang //
NK024(ya)001:17933: me tog dkar po chu gtsang bcas //
NK024(ya)001:17934: legs sbyar bsil zhing gdug sel gyi //
NK024(ya)001:17935: lha rdzas mchod yon dam pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:17936: rang bzhin gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor la //
NK024(ya)001:17937: sngags pas nan tan gyis mchod bya //
NK024(ya)001:17940: de nas thog mtha'i tshigs bcad rkang pa gnyis thog
NK024(ya)001:17941: mthar sbyar zhing so so'i sngags rgya dang bcas pas
NK024(ya)001:17942: / tsan+dana ta kar sri ka dang //
NK024(ya)001:17943: gur gum ga bum dri zhim ldan //
NK024(ya)001:17944: sbrul snying la sogs lhan skyes dang //
NK024(ya)001:17945: sbyar dang yongs gyur dri bzang gis //
NK024(ya)001:17947: n+aa ga ge sar su nan ka /
NK024(ya)001:17948: tsam+pa a shwa ti la ka /
NK024(ya)001:17949: de sogs bkra shis me tog gis //
NK024(ya)001:17950: a ka ru dang sgron shing dang //
NK024(ya)001:17951: ga bur tsan+dana du ru ka /
NK024(ya)001:17952: sa la'i thar chu la sogs spos //
NK024(ya)001:17953: bkra shis 'jig rten rnam grags pas //'bru mar dri zhim las skyes pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:17954: mar me rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK024(ya)001:17955: nyi zla nor bu'i 'od la sogs //
NK024(ya)001:17957: gtsang zhing legs sbyar khan+d+ha'i zas //
NK024(ya)001:17958: shing tog sna tshogs li kha ra //
NK024(ya)001:17959: ma du shi ra bu ram zho //
NK024(ya)001:17960: ro brgya ldan pa'i zas mchog gis //
NK024(ya)001:17961: pi wang gling bu rnga sgra dang //
NK024(ya)001:17962: lha yi rnga chen mur na dza //
NK024(ya)001:17963: rgyud mang gser gyi gling bu'i phreng //
NK024(ya)001:17964: glu gar rtsed 'jo rol mo yis //
NK024(ya)001:17965: zhes rol mo'i sngags rgya rgyud sde gzhan nas 'byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:17967: phyogs su gdugs dang ba dan rnams /
NK024(ya)001:17968: kha dog sna tshogs du ma dang //
NK024(ya)001:17969: rta babs bzang po rnams kyang ni //
NK024(ya)001:17970: dril bu dang bcas rab tu 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:17972: tsh+aa t+r+aa p+aa ta g+han+de pra t+aits+tsha s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17973: zhes pa phyag rgya dang bcas pas dbul /
NK024(ya)001:17974: de nas mchod bum rnams lag tu thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:17975: lha rdzas bum pa brgyad gyur ni //
NK024(ya)001:17976: sman dang rin chen thams cad blug /
NK024(ya)001:17977: spos kyi chus ni rab tu bkang //
NK024(ya)001:17978: ldum bu dag gis kha brgyan te //
NK024(ya)001:17979: de ni 'bras bu kha yang mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:17980: me tog spos la sogs pas brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:17981: mgrin pa ras kyis bcings pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:17983: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam g+ha ta pra t+aits+tsha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:17985: de nas gos zung rnams thogs la //
NK024(ya)001:17986: lha yi gtso bo rnams la ni //
NK024(ya)001:17987: ras ni zung re zung re 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:17988: sems dpa' chen po phal rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:17989: ya re yang ni dbul bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:17990: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam badz+ra wastra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:17992: bzhi pa sgrub pa'i mchod pa gnyis sta gon ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:17993: de nas 'das gtor gsum rgyal gyi sngags kyis bsang /
NK024(ya)001:17995: stong pa'i ngang las las rin po che'i snod du
NK024(ya)001:17996: gtor ma kha dog dri ro nus pa phun sum
NK024(ya)001:17997: tshogs par gyur / +aahh+aum lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:18000: p+au tsa de wi tram mad+g+aa la de wi ash+ta
NK024(ya)001:18001: sa pa ri w+aa ra a k+aa ro btags pa
NK024(ya)001:18003: mdun bskyed la dmigs te lha lnga dang sgeg sogs brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:18004: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad sogs kyi sngags kyang cung zad re bazla'o //
NK024(ya)001:18005: gsum pa bum pa sgrub pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18006: rnam bum gsum rgyal gyi sngags kyis bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:18007: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+aum las rin po che'i bum
NK024(ya)001:18008: pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang
NK024(ya)001:18009: gzhal yas khang du gyur pa'i dbus su pad+ma 'dab
NK024(ya)001:18010: ma bzhi pa'i lte ba dang 'dab bzhir h+aum tram
NK024(ya)001:18011: h+r+aih+aah las / dbus su rnam snang dkar po chos 'chad kyis 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:18012: shar du mi bskyod pa sngon po sa gnon mnyam gzhag rdo rje can /
NK024(ya)001:18013: lhor rin chen 'byung ldan ser po mchog sbyin mnyam gzhag rin chen can /
NK024(ya)001:18014: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas dmar po mnyam gzhag pad+ma can /
NK024(ya)001:18015: byang du don grub ljang gu skyabs sbyin mnyam gzhag rgya gram can /
NK024(ya)001:18016: lnga ka'ang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan
NK024(ya)001:18017: cing zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:18018: dam tshig pa dang rang 'dra'i ye shes kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:18025: zhal zas rnams sngags rgyas dbul /
NK024(ya)001:18027: phyag 'tshal byang chub sems khyod la //
NK024(ya)001:18033: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha
NK024(ya)001:18034: sid+d+hi +aah zhes pa rnams dril nas brgya rtsa bzlas
NK024(ya)001:18035: te / sngar bzhin mchod bstod dang /
NK024(ya)001:18036: mthar dung chos kyi chu phul te zhu ba'i chur blta'o //
NK024(ya)001:18037: skabs 'dir sngar bzhin cha gsum btang la rang nyid 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin bdag 'jug blang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:18038: sbyin sreg bshad kyang phyag len du mi gnang /
NK024(ya)001:18039: slob dpon gyi bya ba rtsa ba'i sa bcad rnams
NK024(ya)001:18040: dkrugs bshad kyi dbang gis sna tshogs su gyur pa
NK024(ya)001:18041: sdebs te bstan pas 'khrugs par mi lta'o //
NK024(ya)001:18042: de nas slob ma rnams 'dus pa la /
NK024(ya)001:18044: bum pa'i chus thams cad khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18046: ji ltar bltams pa sogs brjod cing las bum gyis
NK024(ya)001:18047: khrus dang sngon 'gro gtor ma gtor ba sogs snga
NK024(ya)001:18048: ma ltar la bden brdar gyi tshe /
NK024(ya)001:18049: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18052: rnam par snang mdzad dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:18054: dbang chas rnams sta gon bya /
NK024(ya)001:18055: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu tshar rjes /
NK024(ya)001:18056: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:18057: don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK024(ya)001:18058: par bya'o / de'i phyir du 'dir spyod pa'i rgyud
NK024(ya)001:18059: kyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs la dbang dang gdams pa
NK024(ya)001:18060: blangs te sems can gyi don rgya chen po bgyid
NK024(ya)001:18061: snyam pa byang chub kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed pa
NK024(ya)001:18064: 'dir spyod pa'i rgyud rnam par snang mdzad mngon par
NK024(ya)001:18065: byang chub pa la sogs pa'i rgyud kyi rjes su
NK024(ya)001:18066: 'brangs te u pa ya'i dkyil 'khor du smin byed
NK024(ya)001:18067: kyi dbang bskur bar byed pa la /
NK024(ya)001:18068: dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la 'bring gi tha ma kri ya ni sngon du song /
NK024(ya)001:18069: 'bring gi 'bring u pa ya yin la /
NK024(ya)001:18070: 'bring gi rab yo ga ni slad kyis 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:18071: de yang snga rabs su rgyud sde 'og ma 'di
NK024(ya)001:18072: rnams dar rgyas chung ba'i dbang gis phyag len yang
NK024(ya)001:18073: dag mi dag sna tshogs shig 'dug cing /
NK024(ya)001:18074: khyad par spyod rgyud 'di la las bya rgyud du bsdus te 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:18075: la las yo gar don gyis tshang ba'i dbang du mdzad pa sogs 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:18076: 'dir zur chen thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aaka 'byung dang /
NK024(ya)001:18077: dngos slob bde legs pa la sogs nges par zur du mdzad pa'i phyag rgyun /
NK024(ya)001:18078: 'jam pa'i dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan dang /
NK024(ya)001:18079: rigs sras pan chen sku mched sogs kyis thugs nyams su bstar zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18080: lha thems su khor yug gi lha'i mngon rtogs rnams kyang gsal bar mdzad 'dug pa bzhin /
NK024(ya)001:18081: 'dir yang slob dpon gyis bgyi bar 'os pa'i sgrub
NK024(ya)001:18082: mchod skabs rgyud sde'i dgongs don ltar lhag chad med
NK024(ya)001:18084: 'on kyang spyod rgyud kyi gzhung dang mi 'dra bar
NK024(ya)001:18085: phyag len 'ga' zhig bla med ltar bgyis pa ni
NK024(ya)001:18087: de yang theg pa gong ma 'og mar bkral du mi rung zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18088: 'og ma gong mar bkral ba ni ches khyad par 'phags te /
NK024(ya)001:18089: sngags kyis btab pa'i sa bon ni //
NK024(ya)001:18090: nyi ma gcig la lo tog smin //
NK024(ya)001:18091: zhes gsungs pas kyang shes par nus shing /
NK024(ya)001:18092: slob dpon klu sgrub kyis shes rab snying po sngags su bkral te /
NK024(ya)001:18093: yum chen mo la phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis bskor ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK024(ya)001:18094: bya rgyud kyi bcu gcig zhal dpal mo lugs klu
NK024(ya)001:18095: sgrub kyis bla med du bkral ba lta bu yin
NK024(ya)001:18096: / spyod rgyud rang rkang la sgrub mchod kyi tshe yang /
NK024(ya)001:18097: kun mkhyen klong chen zhabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:18098: spyod pas rang dang lha gnyis mnyam par blta //
NK024(ya)001:18099: rang nyid dam tshig mdun du ye shes lha //
NK024(ya)001:18100: grogs po'i tshul gyis dngos grub len pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:18102: da lam 'dir sgrub mchod grub nas dbang bskur bar
NK024(ya)001:18103: byed pa la sta gon dang dngos gzhi gnyis las
NK024(ya)001:18106: khyor chu blud de dam la bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:18107: so shing dor la dngos grub brtag /
NK024(ya)001:18109: ku sha byin la rmi lam brtag /
NK024(ya)001:18110: ces pa tsam las ma gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:18111: de yang phyag len gtsang mar byed na /
NK024(ya)001:18112: lha sta gon tshar ma thag slob ma rnams sta gon bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18113: gdod dkyil 'khor bris te sgrub mchod byas /
NK024(ya)001:18114: slad kyis dbang bskur ba rigs par snang zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18116: 'on kyang 'dir cho ga zor yang ba'i khyad dang /
NK024(ya)001:18117: dbang dngos gzhi nyung zad las med pa sogs dngos
NK024(ya)001:18118: ste sprel na skyon med cing rigs par mthong zhing
NK024(ya)001:18119: / gsar ma'i phyag len zhib pa rnams su yang
NK024(ya)001:18120: dngos ste sbrel ba'i srol 'dug par brten sbrel te
NK024(ya)001:18121: / bya ba la / thog mar rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:18122: bcu pa bla ma la phyag btsal man+dala phul te /
NK024(ya)001:18124: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi
NK024(ya)001:18125: dad pa'i zhabs drung du sta gon gyi chos rnams
NK024(ya)001:18126: zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul zhing gsol ba gdab
NK024(ya)001:18129: bla ma slob dpon dgongs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18130: bdag ming 'di zhes bya ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:18131: bla ma dam par gsol 'debs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:18132: bdag gi bla ma mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18133: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab //
NK024(ya)001:18134: spro ba bskyed pa ni gzhan las blangs te gsan pas khyab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:18136: khyod ni tshul chen snod yin gyis //
NK024(ya)001:18137: bu tshur theg pa chen po yi //
NK024(ya)001:18138: gsang sngags spyod tshul cho ga ni //
NK024(ya)001:18139: khyod la yang dag bstan par bya //
NK024(ya)001:18140: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gang 'das dang //
NK024(ya)001:18141: de bzhin gshegs dag ma byon dang //
NK024(ya)001:18142: da ltar byung ba'i mgon po rnams //'gro la phan phyir bzhugs pa dag /
NK024(ya)001:18143: de dag kun gyi gsang sngags kyi //
NK024(ya)001:18144: cho ga mchog bzang 'di mkhyen nas //
NK024(ya)001:18145: dpa' bo byang chub shing drung du //
NK024(ya)001:18146: thams cad mkhyen pa mnyam med brnyes //
NK024(ya)001:18147: gsang sngags sbyor ba mnyam med de //
NK024(ya)001:18148: sh+aakya seng ge skyob pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:18149: bdud sde shin tu mi bzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:18150: dpung chen dag kyang de yis bcom //
NK024(ya)001:18151: de bas kun mkhyen thob bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:18152: bu yi blo gros 'di gyis shig /
NK024(ya)001:18154: de nas dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:18155: gzhan yang sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams mngon sum du nam mkha' gang bar dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:18157: bdun rnam dag gi slad du 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:18158: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK024(ya)001:18159: sogs spyi ltar lan gsum bya /
NK024(ya)001:18161: de nas skyabs 'gro sems bskyed gong bzhin phog la
NK024(ya)001:18162: +aah h+aum zhes rdo rje dri chu dang bcas pas
NK024(ya)001:18163: gnas gsum du reg cing bsrung ba bya /
NK024(ya)001:18164: zhes gsungs pa'i don khyed rang rnams tha mal pa'i
NK024(ya)001:18165: lus spangs nas rdo rje sems dpa'i skur gyur pa'i
NK024(ya)001:18166: gnas gsum du dri chu'i thig les yas nas mar
NK024(ya)001:18167: reg pas 'khor lo pad+ma rdo rje gsum gyi gdan
NK024(ya)001:18168: dang / mas nas yar reg pas 'bru gsum gyis mtshan pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:18170: h+aum +aah zhes yas mas su reg cing /
NK024(ya)001:18171: slar yang rdo rje gnas gsum du gtugs pas brtan cing bsrung bar byas pa yin no //
NK024(ya)001:18175: zhes dri bzang gi chu blud pas sdig pa dag par mos so //
NK024(ya)001:18176: dam la bzhag pa ni dngos gzhir 'thad /
NK024(ya)001:18177: so shing dor ba ni u du wa ra dang /
NK024(ya)001:18178: a shwa tha la sogs pa'i shing bzang po sor
NK024(ya)001:18179: brgyad pa me tog gis brgyan cing dris bkus pa
NK024(ya)001:18180: / na mahs man+ta badz+ra nam tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na s+pho ta ya h+aum ta ka ham /
NK024(ya)001:18181: zhes mi g.yo ba'i sngags kyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:18182: sngags des slob ma la byin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18183: ba byung gis byugs pa'i dri'i dkyil 'khor zlum po
NK024(ya)001:18184: byas pa'i steng du ltos med du dor bas so
NK024(ya)001:18185: shing gi mgo shar du bltas na sgrub pa mchog
NK024(ya)001:18186: dang rgyas pa / lhor bltas na mngon spyod /
NK024(ya)001:18187: nub tu bltas na mchog myur ba dang dbang /
NK024(ya)001:18188: byang du bltas na zhi ba /
NK024(ya)001:18189: byang shar du bltas na zhi rgyas gnyis /
NK024(ya)001:18191: lho nub tu bskrad pa dang bsnyems pa /
NK024(ya)001:18192: nub byang du gnod sbyin mo'i dngos grub /
NK024(ya)001:18193: rtse mo bar snang la bltas na nam mkhar 'gro ba /
NK024(ya)001:18195: mthur du bltas na sa 'og gi dngos grub 'grub
NK024(ya)001:18196: bo //'di ni spyod rgyud rang lugs las bshad do
NK024(ya)001:18197: // de nas bu mos bkas pa'i srad bu dmar
NK024(ya)001:18198: po'am skud pa gzhan dang ku shas kyang rung ste
NK024(ya)001:18199: // / mdud pa gsum bor la gong bzhin mi g.yo ba'i sngags brgya rtsa'am /
NK024(ya)001:18200: ma grub na mdud pa re la lan re basngagasa
NK024(ya)001:18201: te slob ma'i dpung pa g.yon par bcings te bsrung
NK024(ya)001:18202: ngo // de nas d+hi has byin gyis brlabs pa'i ku sha che chung gnyis gtad de /
NK024(ya)001:18203: brtul zhugs bzang po khyed rnams kyis //
NK024(ya)001:18204: nang par thams cad nga la bzlos //
NK024(ya)001:18207: bcu gsum pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18208: 'dir skabs su bab pas sbyor te /
NK024(ya)001:18211: 'khor ba sdug bsngal gtam gyis 'jigs pa bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:18212: mya ngan 'das pa'i gtam gyis brod pa bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:18213: dal 'byor phun sum tshogs pa'i lus 'di la //
NK024(ya)001:18214: nyon mongs dbang gis rkyen gyis chud mi gsan //
NK024(ya)001:18215: zhes pas rang yang de'i don dran pas dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK024(ya)001:18216: slob ma'i rgyud la'ang de'i don bskyed par bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18219: dang po byang chub tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18220: bar du dge ba bya ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:18221: mthar dge ba byang chub tu bsngo dgos par bshad do //
NK024(ya)001:18224: mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:18225: dal 'byor rnyed dka' chud zos su mi gtong bar
NK024(ya)001:18226: bya ba thog mtha' bar dge bya tshul sogs ci
NK024(ya)001:18227: rigs par spros la gdams so //
NK024(ya)001:18228: des slob ma sta gon song /
NK024(ya)001:18229: gnyis pa dngos gzhi'i don du bla ma dang dkyil
NK024(ya)001:18230: 'khor gyi gtso bo tha mi dad pa la dngos
NK024(ya)001:18231: gzhi'i dbang rnams zhu ba'i don du man+dala phul /
NK024(ya)001:18232: dngos sta sbrel na gsol gdab mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:18233: ma sbrel na gsol btab dang skyabs sems rgyun bshags gong ltar byas la /
NK024(ya)001:18236: 'dir bu ci la dga' sogs 'og nas zhes 'byung bas /
NK024(ya)001:18237: de nas bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri /
NK024(ya)001:18238: skal bzang bdag bde chen la dga' zhes bya /
NK024(ya)001:18240: bu tshur shog cig theg chen po //
NK024(ya)001:18241: bla med spyod pa'i chu dbang sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:18242: zhes rdo rjes drangs la gral du bzhag go //
NK024(ya)001:18245: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:18246: ma grol ba rnams dgrol bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:18247: dbugs ma byung rnams dbyugs dbyung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:18248: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:18249: bla ma la zhus khyod spro 'am //
NK024(ya)001:18253: de nas yan lag brgyad pa dbul /
NK024(ya)001:18255: rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:18257: skyabs sems dang bdun rnam dag gong du song bas yan lag brgyad pa'ang des khyab /
NK024(ya)001:18258: rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzung ba ni kri ya'i dbang gi dus ltar /
NK024(ya)001:18259: bla med dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK024(ya)001:18260: bdag ni rtag tu skyabs su mchi //
NK024(ya)001:18262: byang chub sems mchog bsgrub par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:18263: zhes pa'i bar lan gsum gyis sdom pa bzung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:18265: de nas dbang kho na ma gtogs gzhan ma bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:18266: gong du dam la bzhag ces pa'i tshig ris la
NK024(ya)001:18267: brten nas dam la bzhag pa'i dod rdo rje spyi
NK024(ya)001:18268: bor bzhag ste / badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18270: slob ma rnams lag gnyis thal mo khong stong du
NK024(ya)001:18271: sbyar la mthe bo gnyis bsgrengs te dam tshig la
NK024(ya)001:18272: gnas pa'i phyag rgya'i bar du me tog gi phreng
NK024(ya)001:18275: a sa me tri sa me sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:18277: me tog dor ba'i slad du rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:18278: thugs rje chen po mnga' ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:18279: mgon po rnams kyi thugs kyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:18280: rnam pa sprul nas chos rnams kyi //
NK024(ya)001:18281: mtshan nyid 'di dag rtogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:18282: ces brjod cing gtso bo la dmigs te me tog dor du gzhug go //
NK024(ya)001:18283: slar yang slob dpon gyi me tog slob ma'i spyi bor bzhag cing rnam snang gi sngags brjod do //
NK024(ya)001:18284: skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor bstan pa ni gtso bo lha lnga dang /
NK024(ya)001:18286: bkra shis kyi lha mo brgyad de nang na gnas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18287: khor yug gi 'jig rten pa sogs brten pa lha dang /
NK024(ya)001:18288: rten gzhal yas khang gi mtshan nyid dang bcas mngon
NK024(ya)001:18289: sum du mthong ba'i 'du shes bskyed du 'jug go
NK024(ya)001:18291: de nas bum pa dang rigs lnga sku thogs te dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:18292: zhes 'byung bas rnam rgyal bum pa dang rigs lnga tsaklisa dbang bskur zhing 'di skad do //
NK024(ya)001:18295: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK024(ya)001:18296: mchog sbyin mnyam gzhag phyag rgya dang //
NK024(ya)001:18297: skyabs kyi phyag rgya rnam pa lnga //
NK024(ya)001:18298: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:18299: spros med spros bral chos kyis dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:18300: bum pa zlum po chos kyi gter //
NK024(ya)001:18301: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //'gro ba'i nad sel bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:18303: don dam bden pa'i chos nyid las //
NK024(ya)001:18304: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK024(ya)001:18305: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa //
NK024(ya)001:18306: u pa ya yi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:18308: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi dkon mchog rin po che rnam pa gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:18309: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la u pa ya'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:18310: bskur bas rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang
NK024(ya)001:18311: thob pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:18315: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18319: rgyas pa la spro na kri ya'i nyer drug kyang bskur bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18322: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus /
NK024(ya)001:18323: dpal phyag na rdo rje la rin po che sna
NK024(ya)001:18324: lnga'i ri rab kyis dbang bskur bas zhes sogs nas
NK024(ya)001:18325: shing gi lha mos kan+da k+aa ri phul ba'i bar
NK024(ya)001:18326: gyi rdzas dbang nyer drug po kri ya ltar bskur
NK024(ya)001:18327: ro // bsdu na gong du song bas 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:18328: de rjes slob dpon gyis slob ma rnams la 'di skad ces gdams so //
NK024(ya)001:18329: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyis //
NK024(ya)001:18330: dam pa'i chos dang byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:18331: srog gi phyir yang da phyin chad //
NK024(ya)001:18332: yongs su btang bar mi bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18333: khyod kyi ser sna dang ni gang //
NK024(ya)001:18334: sems can gnod par mi bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18335: dam tshig 'di dag sangs rgyas kyi //
NK024(ya)001:18336: brtul zhugs bzang po khyod la bshad //
NK024(ya)001:18337: ji ltar rang gi srog bsrung ba //
NK024(ya)001:18338: de ltar khyod kyis 'di dag bsrungs //
NK024(ya)001:18340: de ltar dbang grub nas lam 'khyer bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18341: theg pa lha snying bslab bya sogs spyi dang /
NK024(ya)001:18342: nang gses su du mar yod pa las /
NK024(ya)001:18348: dbang sems dpa' bzhi lam 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:18349: lta ba yo ga dang mthun no //
NK024(ya)001:18350: dam tshig rje 'bangs kyi tshul te /
NK024(ya)001:18353: snang ba rigs bzhi dpon g.yog tshul //
NK024(ya)001:18356: ting nge 'dzin ni sems rang rig rang gsal du
NK024(ya)001:18357: bsgom pa'o //'bras bu rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang thob
NK024(ya)001:18358: ste / rnal 'byor ting 'dzin rab ldan pas //
NK024(ya)001:18359: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK024(ya)001:18360: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:18370: lte bar tram ser po bsgoms pas ming bzhi'i phung
NK024(ya)001:18371: po sbyangs nas rdo rje bzhi mngon du 'gyur ba'o
NK024(ya)001:18372: //'gag drug ni / gnas me ri 'bar ba /
NK024(ya)001:18379: de dag gi don ni theg pa lam 'khyer gyi
NK024(ya)001:18380: sa bcad drug po 'dir mdo tsam las ma gsungs
NK024(ya)001:18381: pas gzhan dang sbyar te bshad na /
NK024(ya)001:18382: dang po 'jug sgo khrus dang gtsang spra /
NK024(ya)001:18383: gnyis pa lta ba yo ga dang mthun zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18384: spyod pa ni bya rgyud bzhin yin la /
NK024(ya)001:18385: gsum pa bsrung bya'i tshul khrims kyang bya rgyud dang mthun /
NK024(ya)001:18386: bzhi pa ting 'dzin bdag dang lha gnyis mnyam par lta ba /
NK024(ya)001:18387: bdag dam tshig dang lha ye shes sems dpa' mdun
NK024(ya)001:18388: du dmigs te grogs po'i tshul gyis dngos grub len
NK024(ya)001:18389: pa dang / lnga pa spyod pa ni bza' ba
NK024(ya)001:18390: zas dang bgo ba gos sogs kyi bya ba drug
NK024(ya)001:18392: drug pa 'bras bu ni rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang
NK024(ya)001:18393: skye ba drug gis 'grub bo //'gag drug ni gong
NK024(ya)001:18394: ltar ro // lha lam 'khyer rnam snang gtso 'khor stong ngo //
NK024(ya)001:18395: bsdu na rigs lngar 'du ba ltar dang /
NK024(ya)001:18396: dbang yang de bzhin lam du 'khyer zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18399: zhes sogs dkyil chog nas 'byung ba ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:18400: gtso bor khrid rim gdams ngag lam 'khyer ni /
NK024(ya)001:18401: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' bdag gi de kho na nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:18402: lha ye shes sems dpa' lha'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK024(ya)001:18403: de gnyis kyi dpral bar dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:18406: lte bar tram ser po bzhi sa bon sngags kyi
NK024(ya)001:18407: tshul du bsgoms pas sngags kyi de kho na nyid
NK024(ya)001:18408: dang / des ming bzhi'i phung po sbyangs te rdo
NK024(ya)001:18409: rje bzhi mngon du 'gyur ba ni chos kyi de
NK024(ya)001:18411: gdams ngag nyams su blang ba'i sgom khrid do //
NK024(ya)001:18412: de ltar u pa ya spyod pa'i rgyud kyi dkyil
NK024(ya)001:18413: 'khor du smin grol legs par thob pa'i dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:18414: dang sdom pa'i tshogs bsrung snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos
NK024(ya)001:18417: bran du khas blangs gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:18418: de'i dge ba bsngo ba sogs snga ma ltar la /
NK024(ya)001:18422: sangs rgyas gtso la yon tan mchog mnga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:18423: che dgus mchod cing smon lam sprin tshogs 'du //
NK024(ya)001:18424: go 'phang mchog brnyes bde ba'i char 'bebs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:18425: sangs rgyas bden pas deng 'dir bde legs sgo //
NK024(ya)001:18426: skyob pa'i chos la legs pa'i mchog mnga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:18427: shin tu phan phyir bde dang brtser ldan zhing //'khor ba rtag bde myang 'das thob pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:18428: dam chos bden pas deng 'dir dge 'dun che la mthu rtsal rmad mnga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:18429: bslab gzhi legs bcas brtson pa'i rnal 'byor can //
NK024(ya)001:18430: bdag gzhan don chen bsgrub pa'i lam zhugs pa //
NK024(ya)001:18431: dge 'dun bden pas deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:18432: ces brjod la slob ma dagye'o //
NK024(ya)001:18434: de nas dkyil 'khor mchod gshegs zhes 'byung bas dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa rnams kha gsos zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18435: sta gon gyi skabs ltar mchod pa bzhis mchod cing /
NK024(ya)001:18436: bstod pa yang mchod pa dang por yod pas zur du mi dgos /
NK024(ya)001:18437: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab cing /
NK024(ya)001:18438: dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i lha tsaka rnams la /
NK024(ya)001:18439: bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:18440: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK024(ya)001:18441: ji srid mchod pa bdag bgyid na //
NK024(ya)001:18442: de srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18443: su pra tish+tha badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:18445: rang bzhin dang gzugs brnyan dbyer med pa'i dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18446: bum nang gi ye shes pa rnams chos sku'i ngang du gshegs /
NK024(ya)001:18447: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bsdus te thig shul dbyi /
NK024(ya)001:18449: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18450: zhes gsungs pa ltar bsngo smon gdab /
NK024(ya)001:18451: gong ltar bkra shis brjod cing me tog gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:18452: nub mo'i tshogs bskang rnams kyang snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:18454: spyod rgyud gser ri'i phreng ba mdzes pa'i khongs //
NK024(ya)001:18455: legs bshad rol mtshor 'khyil ba'i zegs ma kun //
NK024(ya)001:18456: blo gros bum par yongs bsdus man ngag gis //
NK024(ya)001:18457: rab brgyan don gnyer gdul bya'i mgron du sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:18458: u pa ya yi theg pa'i rin chen khams //
NK024(ya)001:18459: rnam snang mngon byang cho ga'i sreg byed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:18460: ma sbyangs de srid don byar mi nus pas //
NK024(ya)001:18461: legs bshad dpyad pa gsum gyis dag par byas //
NK024(ya)001:18462: de phyir phyogs 'dir rab dgyes dpyod ldan rnams //
NK024(ya)001:18463: zol zog bcos mas gdul bya mi 'brid par //
NK024(ya)001:18464: dngos bstan lam bzang rin chen them skas la //
NK024(ya)001:18465: bla med nor bu'i rgyan ldan 'di zung zhig /
NK024(ya)001:18466: ces pa yang bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o////yo
NK024(ya)001:18467: ga'i theg pa'am rnal 'byor rgyud rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK024(ya)001:18468: dkyil 'khor chen po'i cho ga ston par byed pa
NK024(ya)001:18471: dkyil 'khor bsham khungs mchod pa bsham //
NK024(ya)001:18472: rab gnas chog gzhung cha gsum dang //
NK024(ya)001:18473: dpang skong khrus bya sdom rten khri //
NK024(ya)001:18475: mchod bstod bdag 'jug chos bshad dang //
NK024(ya)001:18477: rdzas dbang lha dang lam 'khyer bzhi //
NK024(ya)001:18478: theg pa lha snying bslab bya dang //
NK024(ya)001:18479: theg sgo lta khrims ting spyod 'bras //'gag gnas ston 'khor theg phyir dgos //
NK024(ya)001:18480: gdams ngag ngang sgom bkra shis bsngo //
NK024(ya)001:18481: zhes sa bcad nyer bdun nang gses dang bcas bstan pa las /
NK024(ya)001:18486: ri rab kyi steng na rdo rje rtse gcig rtse
NK024(ya)001:18487: gsum rtse lnga'i brag ri la bya spyod rnal 'byor
NK024(ya)001:18488: gsum / ma h+aa yo ga gzhal yas khang zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor man chad la /
NK024(ya)001:18489: u nu yo ga ye shes kyi me dpung dang lung gi zhi khro mar bcad /
NK024(ya)001:18490: a ti yo ga dbu'i gtsug sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:18491: steng gi rgyal mtshan rtse gcig tu 'dus pa la
NK024(ya)001:18493: gnyis pa lam du dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18495: rta babs them skas bzhi pa yan chad la dbu sems dang /
NK024(ya)001:18496: bya spyod rnal 'byor te spyod pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:18497: de ni ma h+aa yo ga gtsor byas pa'i lugs so //
NK024(ya)001:18498: a nu gtsor byed na dbu sems gcig tu dril nas ma h+aa brgyad pa la'o //
NK024(ya)001:18499: a ti gtsor byed na bya spyod gcig tu dril nas a nu brgyad pa la'o //
NK024(ya)001:18501: gsum pa ji ltar bri ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:18503: sa chog sngar byas pa'i shul yin na ma byas kyang rung la /
NK024(ya)001:18506: gong du sa chog rgyas par grub pas bya mi dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:18508: de'i dbus su ling tshe dagu'am 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad glo 'bur gru chad sgo nyis rim bya /
NK024(ya)001:18509: sgo rkyang byed na lha snam bya /
NK024(ya)001:18518: lha lta gon ni med du mi rung bas /
NK024(ya)001:18519: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu bdun par sta gon zhes gsungs pa ltar 'og tu 'chad /
NK024(ya)001:18522: khungs ni de nyid 'dus pa las so //
NK024(ya)001:18523: zhes gsungs pa yo ga de nyid 'dus pa las bshad /
NK024(ya)001:18524: lha sta gon bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:18525: gang du dkyil 'khor bya ba'i gzhir dri bzang gi chus byugs te /
NK024(ya)001:18526: lha sta gon gyi lha gnas mi 'chol bar bya ba'i phyir las thig 'deb pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18527: 'dir zur lugs dang khams lugs gnyis ka mthun par /
NK024(ya)001:18528: gzhal yas khang sgo sbrag gam sgo rkyang lha snam
NK024(ya)001:18529: can bya bar gsungs pa gzhal yas khang phyi mar
NK024(ya)001:18530: byang sems bcu drug ma gtogs med pas gzhal yas
NK024(ya)001:18531: khang nyis rim la dgos pa cher mi 'dug kyang
NK024(ya)001:18532: / bla ma snga ma rnams phyag bzhes su nyis
NK024(ya)001:18533: rim kho na mdzad pas nyis rim du bya ba
NK024(ya)001:18534: / la / thig btab pa'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:18535: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po klong chen rab 'byams
NK024(ya)001:18536: kyis gsang 'grel mun sel du gsungs pa'i thig nyid
NK024(ya)001:18537: skabs su babs par snang bas de'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:18538: thog mar rgyud thig ltar cha chen bcu drug btab pa de la man ngag gis phye ste /
NK024(ya)001:18539: cha chen bcu drug nang ma gsum //
NK024(ya)001:18540: phyed du bgos te drug tu bya //
NK024(ya)001:18541: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK024(ya)001:18542: gnyis pa cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:18543: gsum pa bzhi pa mi gdab bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:18544: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK024(ya)001:18545: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK024(ya)001:18546: de ni nang gi sgo yin no //
NK024(ya)001:18547: cha chen bzhi pa phyi yi khyams //
NK024(ya)001:18548: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK024(ya)001:18549: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma dgab //
NK024(ya)001:18550: bdun pa cha bzhir bgo bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:18551: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK024(ya)001:18552: ces gsungs pa'i phyir de nyid lag len du bstar
NK024(ya)001:18553: ba'i tshe cha chen bcu drug gi nang ma gsum
NK024(ya)001:18554: po tal mar mi gtong bar zur thig gi steng
NK024(ya)001:18555: nas mnan te btab la rtsig mun ka ba ka
NK024(ya)001:18556: rgyan gyi thig rnams nang ma'i rta babs 'don khyad
NK024(ya)001:18557: kyi nang rtsig par reg cing phyi cha chen bzhi
NK024(ya)001:18558: pa'i phyed du sleb par btab la /
NK024(ya)001:18559: de la rta bab bzhir bcad do //
NK024(ya)001:18560: gzhal yas khang phyi ma'i cha chen lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18561: drug pa phyed gdab phyi ma bgo ba sogs kyang zur thig gi steng du mnan te btab /
NK024(ya)001:18562: rtsig mun ka ba ka rgyan rnams nang rtsig par
NK024(ya)001:18563: zug dgos phyir cha chen lnga pa'i nang du mnan
NK024(ya)001:18564: cing / phyi ma rta babs pad+ma chos 'khor gdugs
NK024(ya)001:18565: tog sogs 'don pa'i khyad kyis phyir sleb pa'i tal
NK024(ya)001:18566: cing / mar btab bo // de ltar las thig
NK024(ya)001:18567: btab zin pa'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du rdo
NK024(ya)001:18568: rje'i gdung bzhis bcad pa'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir 'khor
NK024(ya)001:18569: lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i rnam pa bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18570: de nas lha gnas rnams su dri'i thig le dang /
NK024(ya)001:18571: de'i kar tshom bu re bkod pa ni 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:18572: lnga po'i lte ba dang rtsibs rdo rje'i gdung gi
NK024(ya)001:18573: zur bzhi dkyil 'khor nang ma'i gru chad la phyi
NK024(ya)001:18574: nang du tshom bu gnyis re /
NK024(ya)001:18575: sgo nang ma bzhir re re /
NK024(ya)001:18576: de'i phyir khyams kyi lha snam la phyogs bzhir tshom
NK024(ya)001:18577: bu bzhi re bkod pa'i mthar mtshams 'dzin nas bzung
NK024(ya)001:18580: sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod gor mchod du bshams /
NK024(ya)001:18582: rang nyid stan la 'khod de thog mar mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18584: zhes rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi phyag rgya ni rdo
NK024(ya)001:18585: rje'i thal mo las mthe bong gnyis brkyang la mdzub
NK024(ya)001:18586: mo gnyis mche ba ltar byas te bgegs bsal /
NK024(ya)001:18587: badz+ra dz+wa la a na la ha na da ha
NK024(ya)001:18588: pa tsa ma th+aa b+ha ny+dza ra na h+aum phata
NK024(ya)001:18589: / zhes rdo rje me'i phyag rgya ste sor mo
NK024(ya)001:18590: rnams nang du bsnol ba gyen du bstan pa 'bar
NK024(ya)001:18591: ba ltar byas te gzi byin bskyed /
NK024(ya)001:18592: stong pa'i ngang las las byung ba'i rin po che
NK024(ya)001:18593: las grub pa'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba rnams
NK024(ya)001:18594: kyi nang du zhu ba las byung ba'i lha rdzas
NK024(ya)001:18601: gzhan yang rol mo dang 'phan gdugs la sogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:18602: mchod rdzas bsam gyis mi khyab pa dwangs shing thogs
NK024(ya)001:18603: pa med pa nam mkha'i khams thams cad gang bar
NK024(ya)001:18604: gyur / badz+ra ar+g+ham +aahh+aum zhes sogs so so'i sngags rgyar bcas pas byin gyis brlabs pa'i mthar /
NK024(ya)001:18605: dril bu rgyun chags su dkrol la /
NK024(ya)001:18606: d+harma ra ni ta sogs brjod do //
NK024(ya)001:18607: de nas spyi ltar skyabs 'gro sems bskyed byas te /
NK024(ya)001:18609: de nas rang stong pa nyid kyi lkog mar h+r+aihls
NK024(ya)001:18610: pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad par lce la h+aum las rdo
NK024(ya)001:18611: rje rtse gcig par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:18612: badz+ra dzi hwa zhes pas lce byin gyis brlabs /
NK024(ya)001:18613: lag pa gnyis su a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du h+aum las rdo rje /
NK024(ya)001:18614: sor mo rnams kyang rdo rje rtse gcig par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:18615: zhes pa stong pa nyid la lkog ma dang lce
NK024(ya)001:18616: lag sogs mi 'byung bas stong pa'i ngang las lhar
NK024(ya)001:18617: ldang tshul zur tsam bstan zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18618: spyir phyogs 'dir dang por mkhas grub rnams kyis 'chad nyan sogs rgya cher mdzad mod kyang /
NK024(ya)001:18619: phyis rgyun ma chad tsam las dar so med pa'i
NK024(ya)001:18620: dbang gis rtogs dpyod nyung zhing khyad par yo ga'i
NK024(ya)001:18621: skabs 'dir chog khrigs kyang thog mar dkyil 'khor gyi
NK024(ya)001:18622: lha tshogs bskyed / de nas lce lag byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:18623: de nas bgegs bskrad bsang gtor bya ba /
NK024(ya)001:18625: de nas dkyil 'khor spyan 'dren mchod bstod sogs chog
NK024(ya)001:18626: khrigs shin tu 'khrug cing go dka' ba 'dug par
NK024(ya)001:18627: / rnal 'byor rgyud gzhan nas kha 'geng ba ma
NK024(ya)001:18628: gtogs cho ga mi tshang bas 'dir dag par bya
NK024(ya)001:18629: / ba la / thog mar lce lag byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:18630: stong pa'i ngang las skad cig gis rdo rje sems
NK024(ya)001:18631: dpar gsal ba'i lkog mar h+r+aihls pad+ma dmar po 'dab
NK024(ya)001:18632: ma brgyad pa'i steng du h+aum las rdo rje dkar
NK024(ya)001:18633: po rtse gcig pa nyal stabs su gnas par gyur
NK024(ya)001:18635: lag pa gnyis kyi mthil du a a las zla
NK024(ya)001:18636: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum h+aum las rdo
NK024(ya)001:18637: rje rtse lnga pa re re /
NK024(ya)001:18638: de zhu ba lag pa la thim pas lag pa gnyis rdo rje'i rang bzhin dang /
NK024(ya)001:18639: sor mo rnams rdo rje rtse gcig par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:18642: e ma sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK024(ya)001:18643: thugs rje can gyi thabs chen gyis //
NK024(ya)001:18644: zhi yang sems can 'dul don du //
NK024(ya)001:18645: dri ma med pa'i khro bor gyur //
NK024(ya)001:18647: tshig de skad brjod pa'i rkyen gyis rang nyid khro
NK024(ya)001:18648: bo me ltar 'bar ba sku mdog sngon po zhal
NK024(ya)001:18649: gcig phyag gnyis pa g.yas rdo rje gsor ba'i tshul
NK024(ya)001:18650: dang / g.yon khu tshur gyis dril bu bsnyems pa'i tshul gyis 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:18651: cung zad khro bo sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:18654: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK024(ya)001:18655: dpa' bo'i stangs stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:18656: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gis //
NK024(ya)001:18657: bgegs dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:18658: zhes bskrad cing mtshams bcad de steng 'og phyogs mtshams
NK024(ya)001:18659: thams cad rdo rje'i gur dang sa gzhir bsam mo
NK024(ya)001:18660: // zhes 'byung ba gsar rnying bka' gter mtha' dag
NK024(ya)001:18661: las khro bo spyan 'dren sogs 'byung bas de'i phyir
NK024(ya)001:18663: rang me ltar 'bar ba'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas khro bo'i tshogs spyan drangs par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:18666: ye shes bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:18667: ma rig 'dod pa'i mun khams thams cad bsreg /
NK024(ya)001:18668: zhe sdang gshin rje'i 'jigs pa thams cad 'joms //
NK024(ya)001:18669: dpa' bo chen po dpa' mtshan stag lpags can //
NK024(ya)001:18670: log 'dren srin po'i mtha' gnon dgra 'dul ba //
NK024(ya)001:18671: rig pa'i rgyal po khro bo bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:18672: log 'dren 'dul ba'i slad du spyan 'dren na //'gro ba'i don du mchod kyis gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18673: badz+ra kro d+ha r+aa dza sa pa ri wa ra e h+ye his spyan drangs /
NK024(ya)001:18674: pad+ma ka ma la ya s+t+wam gyi gdan dbul /
NK024(ya)001:18684: chos nyid stong pa gnyis med ngang nyid las //'jig rten spyod pa'i tshul yang mi spong zhing //
NK024(ya)001:18685: thabs la mkhas pas 'jigs byed skur ston pa //
NK024(ya)001:18686: khro chen 'bar ba'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18687: ye shes zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK024(ya)001:18688: sku yi cha lugs za byed rngam stabs can //
NK024(ya)001:18689: gsung gi nga ro 'brug stong ldir ba'i sgra //
NK024(ya)001:18690: ma lus dbang du sdud la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18691: lhag pa'i ye shes rol pa ston mdzad cing //
NK024(ya)001:18692: sdigs pa'i mtshon cha sna tshogs phyag na bsnam //
NK024(ya)001:18693: nyon mongs dug chen rtsad nas 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:18694: sbrul gdug rgyan gyi brgyan la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18695: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK024(ya)001:18696: dpa' bo'i stangs stabs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK024(ya)001:18697: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gis //
NK024(ya)001:18698: bgegs dpung bsreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18699: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar gzi brjid 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:18700: glog stong 'gyu 'dra'i khro gnyer mche ba gtsigs //
NK024(ya)001:18701: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug sgra stong bzhin sgrog /
NK024(ya)001:18702: khro rgyal bgegs tshogs 'dul la phyag 'tshal bstod //'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrog cing //
NK024(ya)001:18703: bgegs rnams ma lus 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:18704: dngos grub ma lus stsol ba'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:18705: bgegs kyi dgra la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18707: dkyil 'khor chen po'i sa gzhi la gnas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:18708: lha la sogs pa'i bgegs tshogs kun nyon cig /
NK024(ya)001:18709: nga ni gnas 'dir dkyil 'khor chen po 'bri //
NK024(ya)001:18710: khyed rnams 'di nas gzhan du 'gro bar gyis //
NK024(ya)001:18711: gal te nga yi tshig las 'da' byed na //
NK024(ya)001:18712: ye shes spyan gyi rdo rje 'bar ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:18713: mgo bo tshal pa brgyar ni 'gas 'gyur zhing //
NK024(ya)001:18714: bgegs rnams brlag par 'gyur ba gdon mi za //
NK024(ya)001:18715: zhes pas bgegs la bka' bsgo /
NK024(ya)001:18718: rdo rje h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya phyogs bcur ston zhing /
NK024(ya)001:18719: sum+b+ha'i sngags brjod pas steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad
NK024(ya)001:18720: rdo rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla
NK024(ya)001:18721: bre de las ye shes kyi me lce rnam par
NK024(ya)001:18722: 'phro ba'i srung 'khor du gyur par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:18723: rnal 'byor rgyud las skabs 'dir sngags rgya rnam grangs
NK024(ya)001:18724: mang bar bshad kyang 'di tsam gyi 'thus par sems
NK024(ya)001:18728: mdun gyi nam mkhar bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings
NK024(ya)001:18729: kyi dkyil 'khor la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK024(ya)001:18730: dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba badz+ra sa m+aa dzah na
NK024(ya)001:18731: ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka
NK024(ya)001:18732: tsit+ta pra na me na badz+ra b+han+d+ha nam ka ro
NK024(ya)001:18735: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:18740: las kyi rigs su chung pa thams cad dang /
NK024(ya)001:18744: rig sngags kyi lha thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:18745: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba phyogs bcu'i rig sngags
NK024(ya)001:18746: kyi lha thams cad kyi spyan sngar sdig pa so
NK024(ya)001:18747: sor bshags so // phyogs bcu na 'das pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18751: 'phags pa nyan thos yang dag par song ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:18752: yang dag par zhugs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:18753: sems can thams cad kyi bsod nams kyi tshogs la rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:18754: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgya bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi
NK024(ya)001:18755: 'khor lo bskor bar mi mdzad pa rnams la 'khor
NK024(ya)001:18756: lo bskor bar bya ba'i phyir bskul bar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18757: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das mya ngan las
NK024(ya)001:18758: 'da' bar bzhed pa de dag mya ngan las mi
NK024(ya)001:18760: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la bdag
NK024(ya)001:18761: nyid kyi lus 'bul gyi dus thams cad du so
NK024(ya)001:18763: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa'i mgon po khyed
NK024(ya)001:18764: rnams kyis dam tshig chen po'i dngos grub stsal du
NK024(ya)001:18765: gsol / bdag gi dge ba'i las rnams 'di dag
NK024(ya)001:18766: gis //'jig rten 'dir ni myur du sangs rgyas nas
NK024(ya)001:18767: //'gro la phan phyir chos rnams ston bgyid cing //
NK024(ya)001:18768: sems can ma lus sdug bsngal gzir las sgrol bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:18769: ces pas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags /
NK024(ya)001:18770: de nas de dag mi dmigs pa'i ngang la bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:18771: de nas dang po bdag bskyed ni /
NK024(ya)001:18772: khams lugs su rtsa lha thams cad bskyed tshul gsungs kyang /
NK024(ya)001:18773: 'dir 'jug pa bde zhing don la mi 'gal ba'i phyir dang /
NK024(ya)001:18774: zur lugs su cho ga ma tshang ba rnams gzhan phan ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:18776: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+h+aah sarba d+h+aar+m+aahswa b+ha wa shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:18778: de'i ngang las pam las pad+ma dang a las zla
NK024(ya)001:18779: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum las rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:18780: dkar po rtse lnga pa h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK024(ya)001:18781: de las 'od zer 'phro 'dus gcig tu gyur pa
NK024(ya)001:18782: las rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dkar
NK024(ya)001:18783: po rab tu dgyes pa'i spyan gdangs pa /
NK024(ya)001:18785: rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:18786: phyag g.yas pa rdo rje rtse lnga pa thugs kar gtod de 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:18787: g.yon pa dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK024(ya)001:18788: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs par bsam ste /
NK024(ya)001:18789: phyag 'tshal ba'i thal mo dpral bar bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:18790: b+h+ri ta b+h+ri ta sarba +aa wa ra na ni h+aum phata kyis sku dang /
NK024(ya)001:18791: thal mo snyim par sbyar ba mgrin par bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:18792: tra na tra na sarba +aa wa ra n+aa ni h+aum phata kyis gsung dang /
NK024(ya)001:18793: rdo rje thal mo las gung mo gnyis dang mtha' bzhi sbyar te brkyang ba'am /
NK024(ya)001:18794: bla ma phyi ma rnams rdo rje bsdams pa las gung mo dang mtha' bzhi sbyar bar bzhed /
NK024(ya)001:18795: phyag rgya de snying gar bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:18796: ts+tshin+da sarba +aa wa ra n+aa ni h+aum phata kyis thugs byin gyis brlab bo //
NK024(ya)001:18797: de nas rdo rje bsdams pa las gung mo rdo rje 'dra bar gshibs /
NK024(ya)001:18798: mthe bong dang mthe chung gnyis brkyang ba phyag na rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:18801: mdzub mo dang srin lag pad+ma 'dra bar byas pa sbyong rgyal gyi phyag rgya dpral bar bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:18804: mdzub mo dang srin lag rin po che 'dra bar
NK024(ya)001:18805: byas pa dbang bskur ba'i phyag rgya rna ba g.yas
NK024(ya)001:18808: mthe bong dang mathe'u chung so sor mnyam la lhag
NK024(ya)001:18809: ma thams cad brkyang ba sdig pa bsreg pa'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:18811: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih de nyid g.yon du bsgyur
NK024(ya)001:18812: ba las thams cad pa'i phyag rgya rna ltag g.yon
NK024(ya)001:18813: du bzhag la / karma a b+hi shi ny+tsa +aah
NK024(ya)001:18814: zhes brjod cing gnas de rnams su mi bskyod pa
NK024(ya)001:18815: du bzhag la / / rnam par snang mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:18818: don yod grub pa rnams bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:18819: de nas bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:18820: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i smin mtshams nas 'od
NK024(ya)001:18821: zer 'phros pas sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:18822: thams cad zhi bar bsam la rdor dbyings rtsa ba'i
NK024(ya)001:18823: snying po / bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:18826: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah zhes sogs ci mang bzlas mthar /
NK024(ya)001:18827: yig brgya tshar gsum brjod cing /
NK024(ya)001:18828: bdag bskyed la yid mchod bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:18829: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha p+au tsa
NK024(ya)001:18830: me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma
NK024(ya)001:18831: ye h+aum / de bzhin du push+pe nas /
NK024(ya)001:18833: kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i gsung ltar /
NK024(ya)001:18834: rang bzhin chos sku dag pa'i klong //
NK024(ya)001:18835: sna tshogs thabs mkhas thugs rje yis //
NK024(ya)001:18836: rigs lnga ye shes lnga ston pa //
NK024(ya)001:18837: lha yi lha la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK024(ya)001:18838: ces bstod pa ni bdag bskyed kyi bya ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:18840: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor badz+ra yak+shasa bsang /
NK024(ya)001:18842: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung /
NK024(ya)001:18846: sum las ri rab kyi steng du b+h+rum las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:18847: snod kyi ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:18848: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las /
NK024(ya)001:18849: lha'i gzhal yas khang rin po che sna tshogs las
NK024(ya)001:18850: grub pa nyis rim gru bzhi sgo bzhi rta babs
NK024(ya)001:18851: dang bcas pa'i dbus dang phyogs bzhi'i ling tshe la
NK024(ya)001:18852: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re re'i dbus su seng
NK024(ya)001:18853: ge'i khri / shar du glang po che'i khri /
NK024(ya)001:18856: byang du shang shang gi khri rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:18857: gzhan yang lha gnas so sor rang rang gi gdan dang bcas par gyur /
NK024(ya)001:18858: dbus su bud+d+h+aa bee ro tsa na las rnam par snang mdzad /
NK024(ya)001:18859: de'i phyogs bzhir badz+ra s+t+wa badz+ri h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18861: d+harma badz+ra h+r+aih karma badz+ra a zhes 'khor sems ma bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:18862: shar gyi rtsibs dbus su badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yahh+aum las mi bskyod pa /
NK024(ya)001:18863: rtsibs bzhir badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18864: badz+ra r+aa dza dzah badz+ra r+aa ga hoh badz+ra s+aa d+hu du /
NK024(ya)001:18865: shar gyi sems dpa' bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:18867: rat+na sam+b+ha wa tram las rin 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:18873: nub rtsibs kyi dbus su pad+ma a mi de wa hrihls snang ba mtha' yas /
NK024(ya)001:18874: rtsibs bzhir badz+ra d+har+m+aa h+r+aih badz+ra tik+sh+na d+h+r+ai /
NK024(ya)001:18877: nub kyi sems dpa' bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:18878: byang rtsibs kyi dbus su karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a las don grub /
NK024(ya)001:18883: byang gi sems dpa' bzhi dang /
NK024(ya)001:18884: gru chad bzhi'i phyi nang la badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18886: badz+ra g+ai t+ai h+r+aih badz+ra n+air+t+ya a /
NK024(ya)001:18889: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih badz+ra gan+d+he a rnams las sgeg sogs brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:18890: sgo bzhir badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18892: badz+ra +aa be sha a las sgo ma bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:18893: snam bu la gnas pa'i byang sems rnams la rtsa rig bzla bar zur lugs su bshad pas /
NK024(ya)001:18894: durga brjod pas byang sems bcu drug tu gsal bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:18895: rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:18896: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah spos dang bcas te rdor dril 'dzin pas /
NK024(ya)001:18898: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:18899: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha /
NK024(ya)001:18900: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:18901: bcom ldan 'khor bcas 'dir ni gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18902: dzahh+aum bam hoh b+ha ga wan /
NK024(ya)001:18903: e h+ye hi ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:18904: bcom ldan 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:18905: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK024(ya)001:18906: bdag gi mchod yod bzhes nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:18907: byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18908: ga ga na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18910: ji ltar bltams pa tsam gyi ni //
NK024(ya)001:18913: pra wa ra sat+ka ra pra t+aits+tsha hoh bdag dang 'gro la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:18914: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul mthu yis ni //
NK024(ya)001:18915: ji srid mchod pa bdag bgyid na //
NK024(ya)001:18916: de srid bcom ldan bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:18923: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK024(ya)001:18924: pra na me na badz+ra b+han+d+ha n+aam ka ro mi
NK024(ya)001:18925: / sgo bzhi'i phyag rgya rim bzhin bcas la /
NK024(ya)001:18926: badz+ra am gu sha dzah zhes mdun bskyed dang nye bar dgug /
NK024(ya)001:18928: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la gzhug /
NK024(ya)001:18929: badz+ra s+pho ta bam gyis mi 'bral bar bcings /
NK024(ya)001:18930: badz+ra a be sha ya as dbyer med du gyur par bsam mo //
NK024(ya)001:18932: byin gyis brlab pa gong du song /
NK024(ya)001:18933: 'bul ba ni spos dang mar me spar la thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:18936: lha sogs bdag gir ma byas pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:18937: me tog chu skyes thang skyes rnams //
NK024(ya)001:18938: thub pa'i dbang phyug rnams la 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:18939: sarba ta th+aa ga ta push+pe p+au tsa me g+ha
NK024(ya)001:18940: sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum
NK024(ya)001:18941: / gnas mchog 'adi'am gzhan gang dag spos kyi shing bzang po //
NK024(ya)001:18942: lha dang mi yi spos chog rnams //
NK024(ya)001:18943: thub pa'i dbang phyug sarba d+h+au pe p+au tsa gnas mchog 'adi'am rin chen sgron sogs nyi zla'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:18944: phyogs dus kun tu rab spros te //
NK024(ya)001:18945: thub pa'i dbang phyug sarba +aa lo ke gnas mchog gur gum la sogs dri yi chab //
NK024(ya)001:18947: thub pa'i sarba gan+d+he gnas mchog zhal zas ro mchog brgya ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:18948: thams cad sbyar ba'i bshos 'di dag /
NK024(ya)001:18949: thub pa'i sarba nee wi d+ya gnas mchog dri med yid du 'ong ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:18950: sil snyan dam pa 'di dag ni //
NK024(ya)001:18951: thub pa'i sarba shap+da rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:18952: gzhan yang rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun dang /
NK024(ya)001:18955: dngos gzhi'i dus rgyas par spro la /
NK024(ya)001:18957: las rin chen bdun sprul te /
NK024(ya)001:18958: sarba bid p+au ra p+au ra su ra su ra
NK024(ya)001:18959: a brta ya a brta ya hoh so so'i phyag
NK024(ya)001:18961: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsakra rat+na pu dzi te h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18962: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma ni rat+na sarba ta
NK024(ya)001:18963: th+aa ga ta wa rti sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK024(ya)001:18964: ma h+aa ta sarba ta th+aa ga ta hasti sarba
NK024(ya)001:18965: ta th+aa ga ta tu ram ga a shwa sarba
NK024(ya)001:18966: ta th+aa ga ta khad+ga 'dod yon lnga ni /
NK024(ya)001:18967: sarba ta th+aa ga ta r+au pa k+aa ma gu na pu dzi te h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:18968: sarba ta th+aa ga ta shap+da sarba ta th+aa ga
NK024(ya)001:18969: ta gan+d+he sarba ta th+aa ga ta r+aa sa sarba
NK024(ya)001:18970: ta th+aa ga ta spar+she zhes mchod /
NK024(ya)001:18974: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:18976: phyag 'tshal don yod grub pa la'o //
NK024(ya)001:18979: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:18980: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:18981: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:18982: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la //
NK024(ya)001:18983: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa //
NK024(ya)001:18984: me long ye shes bdud 'dul chen po'i phyag 'tshal mi bskyod rdo rje la //
NK024(ya)001:18985: rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK024(ya)001:18986: mnyam nyid mchog sbyin phyag 'tshal rdo rje rin chen la //'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK024(ya)001:18987: kun rtog ting 'dzin phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la //
NK024(ya)001:18988: don yod rdo rje bskyod pa'i rlung //
NK024(ya)001:18989: bya grub skyabs sbyin phyag 'tshal don yod grub pa la //
NK024(ya)001:18990: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:18991: zhing rdul kun gyi grangs snyed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:18992: lus btud pa yis rnam kun tu //
NK024(ya)001:18993: mchog tu dad pas bstod par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:18997: las rin po che'i snod du zhu ba las byung
NK024(ya)001:18998: ba'i gtor ma kha dog dri ro nus pa phun
NK024(ya)001:18999: sum tshogs pa'i bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur
NK024(ya)001:19000: / +aahh+aum lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs la /
NK024(ya)001:19001: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra a k+aa ro btags pa lan gsum gyas dbul /
NK024(ya)001:19002: sta gon la gnas par gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19003: rdo rje dril bu dang spos 'dzin pas bus mo btsugs la /
NK024(ya)001:19004: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:19005: rig sngags rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:19006: bdag ni brtse bar gyur nas su //
NK024(ya)001:19007: slob ma rnams la brtse ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:19008: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:19010: bcom ldan bdag ni gus pa lags //
NK024(ya)001:19011: de bas gnang ba mdzad pa'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:19012: sangs rgyas 'jig rten mgon brtse dang //
NK024(ya)001:19013: byang chub sems dpa' dgra bcom dang //
NK024(ya)001:19014: gsang sngags lha gzhan gang lags dang //'jig rten skyong ba'i lha rnams dang //
NK024(ya)001:19015: gang yang 'byung po mthu chen dang //
NK024(ya)001:19016: gang yang lha yi spyan mnga' ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:19017: sems can bstan la dga' ba rnams //
NK024(ya)001:19018: bdag la dgongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19019: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:19020: sang ni dkyil 'khor bzang po'i ming //
NK024(ya)001:19021: rdo rje'i dbyings chen ci nus kyis //
NK024(ya)001:19022: cho ga bzhin du bris lags na //
NK024(ya)001:19023: bdag dang slob mar bcas rnams la //
NK024(ya)001:19024: thugs ni brtse bar dgongs nas su //
NK024(ya)001:19025: tshogs pa thams cad dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:19026: byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19028: khyed kyis sems can don kun sogs nas /
NK024(ya)001:19029: slar yang 'byon par mdzad du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19030: badz+ra sat+wa h+aum lan gsum gyis thal mo spyi bor bkod de /
NK024(ya)001:19031: badz+ra muhzhesa se gol gtogs nas lha rnams sang 'byon
NK024(ya)001:19032: par zhal gyis bzhes te gshegs par bsam la nam
NK024(ya)001:19034: de nas tshom bu dang mchod gtor rnams bsdu zhing bsngo smon dang shis brjod bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:19036: de nas dkyil 'khor bri ba'i gong du thig tshon
NK024(ya)001:19037: byin rlabs spro na rnal 'byor rgyud lugs su bya
NK024(ya)001:19038: dgos kyang cho ga mi 'dra ba'i khyad par mang
NK024(ya)001:19039: zhing ha cang spros pas dub par snang bas /
NK024(ya)001:19040: thog mar sgo 'byed kyi dbang gi skabs su byin
NK024(ya)001:19041: gyis brlabs pa'i las thig dang tshon gyis bris pas
NK024(ya)001:19042: khyab / ji ltar bri ba ni dbus dang phyogs
NK024(ya)001:19043: bzhi'i 'khor lo rnams ser po'am yang na phyogs mdog
NK024(ya)001:19044: rdo rje'i gdung mthing kha la rdo rje ser po
NK024(ya)001:19045: khyab / / dbus ma'i re mig sngon po /
NK024(ya)001:19046: gzhan re mig sogs nang gi khyams shar dkar /
NK024(ya)001:19050: rtsig pa nang nas rim pa bzhin du ser sngo dmar ljang dkar ba /
NK024(ya)001:19054: pu shu'am shar bu dkar po sogs gzhal yas khang gnyis ka la 'dra /
NK024(ya)001:19055: gzhal yas khang phyi nang gi bar gyi khyams kyang phyogs mdog go //
NK024(ya)001:19056: rta babs nang ma la glang rgyab chos 'khor sogs med cing /
NK024(ya)001:19057: phyi ma la glang rgyab mig gsum dang pad+ma chos
NK024(ya)001:19058: 'khor gdugs tog dbus rwa sogs spyi dang 'dra zhing
NK024(ya)001:19059: / rta babs kyi mdog mas rim bzhin ser ljang sngo dmar ro //
NK024(ya)001:19060: phyi pad rdor me ri gsum spyi ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:19061: de ltar dkyil 'khor bris zin nas rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa mchod pa bsham pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19063: mchod pa bum pa gtor ma cha gsum la sogs pa gong bzhin du bsham /
NK024(ya)001:19065: bum pa ni gsar ma'i yo ga'i skabs rnam rgyal bum pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:19067: mchod pa'i bum pa sogs mang du bshad kyang /
NK024(ya)001:19068: 'di la rnam bum dang las bum gnyis kyis 'thus
NK024(ya)001:19069: pas rnam bum dang dbang bum gcig tu bsdus pas
NK024(ya)001:19072: bum pa bsham zhes pa tsam las sgrub tshul ma gsungs shing /
NK024(ya)001:19077: byang gi bum pas dbang bskur tshul bskur tshig dang
NK024(ya)001:19078: bcas gsungs pas bum pa lnga byed pa yo ga
NK024(ya)001:19080: dkyil 'khor dbus su bum pa mgul chings ser po
NK024(ya)001:19081: 'khor lo'i mtshan ma can rnam snang gi tsakli dang
NK024(ya)001:19082: bcas pa / shar du bum pa mgul chings dkar
NK024(ya)001:19083: po rdo rje'i mtshan ma can dang mi bskyod pa'i
NK024(ya)001:19084: bcas pa / tsakli can / lhor bum pa mgul
NK024(ya)001:19085: chings sngon po rin po che'i mtshan ma dang rin
NK024(ya)001:19087: nub tu bum pa mgul chings dmar po pad+ma'i mtshan ma dang snang ba mtha' yas kyi tsakli can /
NK024(ya)001:19088: byang du bum pa mgul chings ljang gu rgya gram gyi mtshan ma dang don grub kyi tsakli can /
NK024(ya)001:19089: thams cad kyang nang sum gnyis dri bzang gi chu
NK024(ya)001:19090: bum rdzas nyer lnga dang ldan pa kha rgyan dung
NK024(ya)001:19091: chos gzungs rdor dang bcas pa bsham /
NK024(ya)001:19092: slob dpon gyi mdun du las bum dar sngon gyis
NK024(ya)001:19093: dkris shing bcud ldan kha rgyan dang mche ba'i mtshan
NK024(ya)001:19095: mchod bum ma byung yang 'thus la /
NK024(ya)001:19097: brgyad dam bcu drug 'bru sman dri chab kyis bkang
NK024(ya)001:19098: ba kha rgyan dang bcas pas dkyil 'khor gyi mtha'
NK024(ya)001:19099: bskor zhing / bum pa ma 'byor na ting la
NK024(ya)001:19100: sogs pas mchod bum gyi dod bya bar bshad do
NK024(ya)001:19101: bskor zhing / // dkyil 'khor gyi mthar mtshams 'dzin dang chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod bzang ba /
NK024(ya)001:19102: 'das gtor dkar zlum 'dab bzhi can dang /
NK024(ya)001:19103: sngon 'gro'i gtor ma gnyis kyang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:19104: cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor ma bsdus na mchod pa kha gsos shing gtor ma yang bsham /
NK024(ya)001:19105: bsdus tshar na dkyil 'khor 'di ga'i nye logs su cha gsum gyi gtor ma bsham /
NK024(ya)001:19106: gzhan yang lha dbang dang rdzas dbang gi chas rnams kyang 'byor shoms su bsham mo //
NK024(ya)001:19107: rtsa ba gsum gyi gtor ma gzhan rnams kyang kha gaso'o //
NK024(ya)001:19108: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bzhi pa rab gnas ni /
NK024(ya)001:19110: rab gnas rgyas bsdus gang mos bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:19112: rdor dril dang bcas pas rten 'brel snying po brjod
NK024(ya)001:19113: cing me tog gtor zhing sgo 'byed skabs ltar dmigs
NK024(ya)001:19114: pa bya'o // rtsa ba'i sa bcad lnga pa chog gzhung ni /
NK024(ya)001:19116: chog gzhung 'og nas 'byung ba ltar byas la /
NK024(ya)001:19118: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi bla dpe'i mchan
NK024(ya)001:19119: bur chog gzhung gzhan phan snying po ltar bya gsungs
NK024(ya)001:19120: pa / 'dir gzhan phan mtha' yas nas med du
NK024(ya)001:19121: mi rung ba rnams blangs te bri bar bya ba
NK024(ya)001:19124: zhes lag gnyis thal sbyar bsnol ba'i gung mdzub kyi
NK024(ya)001:19125: bar du me tog bzung ba 'thor zhing dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:19126: khang par zhugs te stan la 'dug go //
NK024(ya)001:19128: bgegs gtor btang la sum+b+ha nis bgegs bskrad do //
NK024(ya)001:19129: zhes 'byung bas sngon 'gro gtor ma dang po chab kyis bran te /
NK024(ya)001:19130: so so'i sngags rgya dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:19132: badz+ra dz+wa la a na la ha na da ha pa tsa ma tha b+hany+dza ra na h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:19133: las rin po che'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang du bdud rtsi'i tshogs kyis gang bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:19134: a k+aa ro lan gsum gyi byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:19135: ta ki h+aum dzah zhes bgegs rnams bkug la lag
NK024(ya)001:19136: g.yon khu tshur gyis mthe bo sgreng zhing g.yas pas
NK024(ya)001:19137: mchog sbyin bskor ba'i mthar se gol gtog cing /
NK024(ya)001:19138: gung ka re gung ka re s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19139: pi tsi pi tsi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19141: sarba big+h+n+aa na grah+ne dam ar+g+ham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19144: sarba big+h+n+aana na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo sogs
NK024(ya)001:19145: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags btags pa lan gsum gyis
NK024(ya)001:19147: zhes bskrad la sum+b+ha sogs kyi sngags dang /
NK024(ya)001:19148: yungs thun gyis brab cing mtshams bcad do //
NK024(ya)001:19149: de nas mchod pa byin brlab sta gon gyi skabs ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:19151: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed byas la zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:19152: de nas tshad med bzhi bsgom /
NK024(ya)001:19154: skyabs sems tshad med bzhi sogs kyang snga ma ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:19155: de nas sta gon ltar lce lag byin brlab khro
NK024(ya)001:19156: bo spyan 'dren dang bgegs bskrad cing bsrung ba tshogs
NK024(ya)001:19157: bsag / bdag bskyed sogs sta gon gyi skabs ltar bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:19159: rigs lnga'i bum par mtshams kyi mchod lha sgo ma dang /
NK024(ya)001:19160: phyogs kyi sems ma rnams rigs bzhi so sor bsdus
NK024(ya)001:19161: te bskyed pa dang bsgrubs na legs par snang zhing
NK024(ya)001:19162: / rtsa lha rnams mi chad cing dbang bum dang
NK024(ya)001:19163: rnam bum gnyis thun mong du 'gyur bas legs par
NK024(ya)001:19164: / snang ngo // bum pa lnga dang las bum bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:19165: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK024(ya)001:19166: lnga'i steng du b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i bum pa
NK024(ya)001:19167: lnga yangs shing rgya che ba lha'i gos kyi mgul
NK024(ya)001:19168: chings dang dpag bsam shing gi kha brgyan pa /
NK024(ya)001:19169: nang chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis gang ba'i dbus
NK024(ya)001:19170: su gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang bcas
NK024(ya)001:19171: pa lngar gyur / dbus kyi bum nang gi gzhal
NK024(ya)001:19172: yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i dbus seng ge'i khrir
NK024(ya)001:19173: bud+d+h+aa bee ro tsa na las rnam snang ser po
NK024(ya)001:19174: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:19175: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du badz+ra sa t+wa badz+ri h+aum las spyan ma dkar mo rdo rje can /
NK024(ya)001:19176: lhor rat+na badz+ri t+r+aam las m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo rin chen can /
NK024(ya)001:19177: nub tu pad+ma badz+ri h+r+aihls gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma can /
NK024(ya)001:19178: byang du karma badz+ri a las sgrol ma ljang gu rgya gram can no //
NK024(ya)001:19179: shar gyi bum nang gi gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:19180: rtsibs bzhi'i dbus glang po che'i khrir badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yahh+aum
NK024(ya)001:19181: las mi bskyod pa dkar po sa gnon gyi phyag
NK024(ya)001:19182: rgya can / rtsibs bzhi'i shar du badz+ra sat+wa h+aum
NK024(ya)001:19183: las rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po rdo rje can
NK024(ya)001:19184: rgya can / / lhor badz+ra r+aa dza dzahls rdo rje rgyal po ser po lcags kyu can /
NK024(ya)001:19185: nub tu badz+ra r+aa ga hohls rdo rje chags pa dmar po mda' gzhu can /
NK024(ya)001:19186: byang du badz+ra s+aa d+hu du las rdo rje legs pa ljang gu se gol can /
NK024(ya)001:19187: rtsibs kyi phyi'i mu khyud la badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum las sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19188: badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum las bdug spos ma dkar mo spos khang 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19189: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' byams pa /
NK024(ya)001:19192: mya ngan dang mun pa thams cad nges par 'joms
NK024(ya)001:19193: pa bzhi dkar po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin
NK024(ya)001:19194: pa / badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahls rdo rje lcags kyu ma dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:19195: lho'i bum nang gi gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs
NK024(ya)001:19196: bzhi'i dbus rta'i khrir rat+na sam+b+ha wa t+r+aam las rin
NK024(ya)001:19197: 'byung sngon po mchog sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:19198: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du badz+ra rat+na t+r+aam las rdo rje rin chen sngon po rin chen can /
NK024(ya)001:19199: lhor badz+ra te dz+aar+ya las rdo rje gzi brjid dmar po nyi ma can /
NK024(ya)001:19200: nub tu badz+ra ke tu b+h+ri las rdo rje rgyal mtshan sngon po rgyal mtshan can /
NK024(ya)001:19201: byang du badz+ra ha sa ha las rdo rje bzhad pa dkar po so phreng can /
NK024(ya)001:19202: mu khyud la badz+ra m+aa le tram las phreng ba ma ser mo phreng ba can /
NK024(ya)001:19203: badz+ra push+pe tram las me tog ma ser mo me tog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19204: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' spos kyi glang po /
NK024(ya)001:19207: ye shes tog bzhi ser po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19208: badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum las rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:19209: nub kyi bum nang gi gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:19210: rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su rma bya'i khrir pad+ma de wa
NK024(ya)001:19211: h+r+aihls snang mtha' dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag
NK024(ya)001:19212: rgya can / rtsibs bzhi'i shar du badz+ra d+har+m+aa h+r+aihls rdo rje chos dmar po pad+ma can /
NK024(ya)001:19213: lhor badz+ra tik+sh+na d+h+ai las rdo rje rnon po sngon po ral gri can /
NK024(ya)001:19214: nub tu badz+ra he tu krum las rdo rje rgyu ser po 'khor lo can /
NK024(ya)001:19215: byang du badz+ra b+h+aa sha b+h+aa las rdo rje smra ba dmar po ljags 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19216: mu khyud la badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aihls glu ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19217: badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih las mar me ma dmar mo mar me 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19218: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' 'od dpag med /
NK024(ya)001:19221: d+r+wa ba can gyi 'od bzhi dmar po rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19222: badz+ra s+pho ta bam las rdo rje lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa rnams so //
NK024(ya)001:19223: byang gi bum nang gi gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:19224: rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su shang shang gi khrir karma a
NK024(ya)001:19225: mo g+ha sid+d+hi a las don grub ljang gu skyabs
NK024(ya)001:19227: rtsibs bzhi'i shar du badz+ra karma kam las rdo rje las ljang gu rgya gram can /
NK024(ya)001:19228: lhor badz+ra rak+sha ham las rdo rje bsrung ba ser po go khrab 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19229: nub tu badz+ra yak+sha h+aum las rdo rje gnod sbyin sngon po mche ba can /
NK024(ya)001:19230: byang du badz+ra san+d+hi bam las rdo rje khu tshur ser po khu tshur can /
NK024(ya)001:19231: mu khyud la badz+ra nir+t+ya a las gar ma ljang gu gar byed pa /
NK024(ya)001:19232: badz+ra gan+d+he a las dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19233: gzhan yang byang chub sems dpa' rdo rje snying po /
NK024(ya)001:19236: kun tu bzang po rnams ljang gu rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19237: badz+ra +aa be sha +aahls dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19238: thams cad kyang dar dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19239: las kyi bum par pad zla'i steng du b+h+r+aum las
NK024(ya)001:19240: rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs
NK024(ya)001:19241: su rdzogs pa'i nang chu dang bcud sna tshogs kyis
NK024(ya)001:19242: gang ba'i steng du pad zla'i gdan la h+aum las
NK024(ya)001:19243: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin sngon po mche ba
NK024(ya)001:19244: 'dzin pa khro tshul dar dang rin po ches brgyan
NK024(ya)001:19245: pa'o // badz+ra sa m+aa dzahzhesa rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bca' ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:19246: ma lus sems can sogs spyan 'dren nas /
NK024(ya)001:19247: badz+ra +aa be shas dbyer med du gyur pa'i bar lha sta gon bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:19248: b+h+ri ta sogs gnas gsum byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:19250: zhes rigs lnga dbang bskur ba'i sngags rgya rnams bdag bskyed bzhin bya dgos te /
NK024(ya)001:19251: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK024(ya)001:19252: phyi'i lugs su rigs lngas dbang bskur /
NK024(ya)001:19253: nang gi bzhin sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs /
NK024(ya)001:19255: mchod bstod kyang lha sta gon bzhin la /
NK024(ya)001:19257: 'jigs pa'i h+aum sgra nges sgrogs shing //
NK024(ya)001:19258: zhes sh+lo ka gcig gis bstod /
NK024(ya)001:19259: gzungs thag blangs te bzlas pa bya ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:19260: rang gi snying ga nas sngags phreng gzugs thag la
NK024(ya)001:19261: brten te song bas lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul
NK024(ya)001:19262: te ba spu'i bu ga nas bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun
NK024(ya)001:19263: byung bas bum pa gang bar bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:19264: zur lugs su rtsa rig bzla bar gsungs pa lha
