NK024(ya)001:19265: mi'i theg pa'i skabs kyi lam 'khyer du yang 'byung
NK024(ya)001:19267: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga ti pa
NK024(ya)001:19268: ri sho d+ha na r+aa dza ya ta th+aa ga
NK024(ya)001:19269: ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:19271: sho d+ha ne sho d+ha ne sarba p+aa pam bi
NK024(ya)001:19272: sho d+ha ne shud+d+he bi shud+d+he sarba karma a ba
NK024(ya)001:19273: ra na bi shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19274: zhes pa spyir brgya rtsa dang /
NK024(ya)001:19275: bye brag tu dbus kyi bum par dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:19280: pad+ma badz+ra h+r+aih karma badz+ra a rnams bdun nam gsum bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:19281: shar gyi bum par dmigs la /
NK024(ya)001:19285: badz+ra r+aa dza dzah badz+ra r+aa ga hoh badz+ra s+aa d+hu du /
NK024(ya)001:19289: badz+ra gu sha dzahrnamasa bdun nam gsum bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:19300: badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum rnams bdun nam gsum bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:19301: nub kyi bum par dmigs la /
NK024(ya)001:19302: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih brgya rtsa bzlas /
NK024(ya)001:19303: badz+ra d+har+m+aa h+r+aih badz+ra tik+sh+na d+h+ai /
NK024(ya)001:19306: badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aih sems dpa' bzhir rtsa rig /
NK024(ya)001:19307: badz+ra s+pho ta bam rnams bdun nam gsum bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:19308: byang gi bum par dmigs te /
NK024(ya)001:19309: karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a /
NK024(ya)001:19318: badz+ra +aa be sha a rnams bdun nam gsum brlabs so //
NK024(ya)001:19322: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19323: zhes nyer gcig bzlas mthar gong bzhin mchod bstod byas la ye shes pa gshegs /
NK024(ya)001:19324: dung chos kyi chu blug pas dam tshig pa bum
NK024(ya)001:19325: chur gyur par bsam ste yig brgya brjod pas brtan
NK024(ya)001:19326: par bsam mo // gsum pa mdun bskyed bsgrub cing mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19328: de nas bum pa'i chus phyogs kun tu gtor zhing /
NK024(ya)001:19330: tsan+dana chu la bden pa brdar ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:19331: phyogs bcur gtor bas yongs su dag gyur te //
NK024(ya)001:19332: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:19333: dri med yon tan dag dang ldan gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19334: sarba bi sho d+ha ni h+aum h+r+aihtha /
NK024(ya)001:19336: las bum gyi chus phyogs bcur gtor ro //
NK024(ya)001:19338: zhes rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi phyag rgyas bgegs bsal /
NK024(ya)001:19339: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:19340: zhes pas bdag dang snang ba thams cad stong par gyur par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:19341: stong pa'i ngang las yam las rlung /
NK024(ya)001:19345: sum las ri rab kyi steng du b+h+r+aum las 'od 'phros /
NK024(ya)001:19346: snod kyi ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK024(ya)001:19347: tshur 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rin po che
NK024(ya)001:19348: sna tshogs las grub pa'i lha'i gzhal yas khang pa
NK024(ya)001:19349: nyis rim gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:19350: rtsig pa lnga nang nas rim pa bzhin du ser
NK024(ya)001:19351: sngo dmar ljang dkar ba'i steng rin po che'i pha
NK024(ya)001:19352: gus bskor ba la steng nas d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:19353: ba phyed pa 'phyang zhing mda' yab dang pu shus
NK024(ya)001:19355: sgo bzhi'i steng gi thad sor ka ba bzhi bzhis bteg pa'i rta babs bang rim bzhi pa /
NK024(ya)001:19356: gzhal yas khang nang ma'i dbus ka ba brgyad kyis
NK024(ya)001:19357: bteg pa'i rdo rje'i gdung bzhis mig mang ris su
NK024(ya)001:19358: byas pas mdzes par phub pa dbus dang /
NK024(ya)001:19359: phyi'i rta babs bzhi'i steng du bum pa bre chos
NK024(ya)001:19360: kyi 'khor lo gdugs tog dang bcas pas mdzes par
NK024(ya)001:19361: byas pa / nang gi khyams dbus sngo /
NK024(ya)001:19365: byang ljang ba'i re mig gi phyogs bzhi dbus dang
NK024(ya)001:19366: lngar 'khor lo phyogs mdog can rtsibs bzhi pa re
NK024(ya)001:19367: re'i dbus su seng ge'i khri /
NK024(ya)001:19368: shar du glang po che'i khri /
NK024(ya)001:19371: byang du shang shang gi khri /
NK024(ya)001:19372: lha gnas rnams su pad+ma dang zla ba'i gdan re rer gyur /
NK024(ya)001:19373: dbus kyi gdan gyi steng du bud+d+h+aa bee ro tsa
NK024(ya)001:19374: na las dbus su rnam snang ser po kun tu
NK024(ya)001:19375: zhal byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can /
NK024(ya)001:19376: zhabs rdo rje'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK024(ya)001:19377: de'i shar gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs la badz+ra sat+wa badz+ri
NK024(ya)001:19378: h+aum las sems ma rdo rje ma'i ngo bo rdo
NK024(ya)001:19379: rje rtse lnga pa dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:19380: lhor rat+na badz+ri t+r+aam las rin chen rdo rje ma'i
NK024(ya)001:19381: ngo bo yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK024(ya)001:19382: / nub tu pad+ma badz+ri h+r+aihls rdo rje chos ma'i
NK024(ya)001:19383: ngo bo pad dkar 'dab ma bcu drug pa 'dab
NK024(ya)001:19384: brgyad mthur du bstan cing 'dab brgyad steng du 'dzum
NK024(ya)001:19385: pa'i nang dang po'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa chud
NK024(ya)001:19386: / pa / byang du karma badz+ri a las rdo
NK024(ya)001:19387: rje las ma'i ngo bo sna tshogs rdo rje rwa
NK024(ya)001:19389: re mig shar gyi rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su glang po
NK024(ya)001:19390: che'i khrir badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yahh+aum las mi bskyod pa dkar
NK024(ya)001:19391: po sa gnon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:19392: de'i shar rtsibs la badz+ra sa t+wa h+aum las rdo
NK024(ya)001:19393: rje sems dpa' dkar po rdo rje dang dril bu
NK024(ya)001:19394: 'dzin pa / lhor badz+ra r+aa dza dzahls rdo rje rgyal po ser po lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19395: nub tu badz+ra r+aa ga hohls rdo rje chags pa dmar po mda' gzhu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19396: byang du badz+ra s+aa d+hu du las rdo rje legs pa ljang gu se gol ster ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:19397: re mig lho'i rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su rta'i khrir rat+na
NK024(ya)001:19398: sam+b+ha wa t+r+aam las rin chen 'byung ldan sngon po
NK024(ya)001:19399: g.yas mchog sbyin dang g.yon mnyam gzhag can /
NK024(ya)001:19400: de'i shar rtsibs la badz+ra rat+na t+r+aam las rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:19401: rin chen sngon po g.yas rin po che dpral bar
NK024(ya)001:19402: 'jog cing g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK024(ya)001:19403: lhor badz+ra te dz+aar+ya las rdo rje gzi brjid dmar po nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19404: nub tu badz+ra ke tu b+h+ri las rdo rje rgyal mtshan sngon po rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19405: byang du badz+ra ha sa ha las rdo rje bzhad pa dkar po so'i phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19406: re mig nub kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su
NK024(ya)001:19407: rma bya'i khrir pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aihls snang
NK024(ya)001:19408: ba mtha' yas dmar po ting nge 'dzin gyi phyag
NK024(ya)001:19409: rgya can / shar rtsibs la badz+ra d+har+m+aa h+r+aihls rdo
NK024(ya)001:19410: rje chos dmar po g.yon pad+ma dang g.yas pas de'i
NK024(ya)001:19411: rgya can / kha 'khyer ba / lhor badz+ra tik+sh+na
NK024(ya)001:19412: d+h+r+ai las rdo rje rnon po sngon po g.yas ral
NK024(ya)001:19413: gri dang g.yon po ti 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19414: nub tu badz+ra he tu krum las rdo rje rgyu
NK024(ya)001:19415: ser po g.yas ba'i gung mo la 'khor lo rtsibs
NK024(ya)001:19417: byang du badz+ra b+h+aa sha b+h+aa las rdo rje smra ba dmar po ljags 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19418: re mig byang gi rtsibs bzhi'i dbus su shang shang
NK024(ya)001:19419: gi khrir karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi a las don
NK024(ya)001:19420: grub ljang gu g.yas skyabs sbyin dang g.yon mnyam gzhag
NK024(ya)001:19421: rgya gram can / shar rtsibs la badz+ra karma kam
NK024(ya)001:19422: las rdo rje las ljang gu g.yas sna tshogs rdo
NK024(ya)001:19423: rje dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19424: lhor badz+ra rak+sha ham las rdo rje bsrung ba ser po go cha 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19425: nub tu badz+ra yak+sha h+aum las rdo rje gnod sbyin
NK024(ya)001:19426: sngon po phyag gnyis kyis g.yas g.yon gyi thad kar
NK024(ya)001:19428: byang du badz+ra sin+d+hi bam las rdo rje khu tshur
NK024(ya)001:19429: ser po rdo rje rtse lnga pa gnyis dam tshig
NK024(ya)001:19431: shar lho'i re mig tu badz+ra sa t+wa badz+ri h+aum
NK024(ya)001:19432: las rdo rje spyan ma dkar mo g.yas rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:19433: / lho nub kyi re mig tu rat+na badz+ri t+r+aam
NK024(ya)001:19434: las m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo g.yas rin po che
NK024(ya)001:19435: / / nub byang gi re mig tu pad+ma badz+r+ai h+r+aihls gos dkar mo dmar mo g.yas pad+ma /
NK024(ya)001:19436: byang shar gyi re mig tu karma badz+ri a las sgrol ma ljang gu g.yas rgya gram /
NK024(ya)001:19437: bzhi ka'ang g.yon gdan la brten cing sems skyil gyis
NK024(ya)001:19438: bzhugs pa sgeg cing chags pa'i nyams can nu 'bur
NK024(ya)001:19440: shar lho'i gru chad kyi nang du badz+ra l+aa s+ya
NK024(ya)001:19441: h+aum las sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:19442: / lho nub kyi gru chad kyi nang du badz+ra
NK024(ya)001:19443: m+aa le tram las phreng ba ma ser mo phreng
NK024(ya)001:19444: / ba 'dzin pa / nub byang gi gru chad
NK024(ya)001:19445: kyi nang du badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aihls glu ma dmar
NK024(ya)001:19447: byang shar gyi gru chad kyi nang du badz+ra n+air+t+ya
NK024(ya)001:19448: a las gar ma ljang gu rdo rje rtse gsum
NK024(ya)001:19450: shar lho'i gru chad kyi phyi rol tu badz+ra d+h+au
NK024(ya)001:19451: pe h+aum las bdug spos ma dkar mo spos khang
NK024(ya)001:19452: 'dzin pa / lho nub kyi gru chad kyi phyir
NK024(ya)001:19453: badz+ra push+pe t+r+aam las me tog ma ser mo me
NK024(ya)001:19454: 'dzin pa / tog 'dzin pa / nub byang gi
NK024(ya)001:19455: gru chad kyi phyir badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aihls mar
NK024(ya)001:19456: me ma dmar mo mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa
NK024(ya)001:19458: gyi gru chad kyi phyir badz+ra gan+d+he a las dri
NK024(ya)001:19459: chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19460: gzhal yas khang nang ma'i shar sgor badz+ra am gu
NK024(ya)001:19461: sha dzah las rdo rje lcags kyu ma dkar mo
NK024(ya)001:19463: lho sgor badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum las rdo rje zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19464: nub sgor badz+ra s+pho ta bam las rdo rje lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:19465: byang sgor badz+ra +aa be sha a las rdo rje dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19466: gzhal yas khang phyi ma'i lha snam la na mo
NK024(ya)001:19467: sogs rtsa ris bcu drug sbrul 'khyil ba lta bu
NK024(ya)001:19469: shar du byang chub sems dpa' byams pa /
NK024(ya)001:19472: mya ngan dang mun pa thams cad nges par 'joms pa bzhi dkar po /
NK024(ya)001:19476: ye shes tog bzhi ser po /
NK024(ya)001:19480: d+r+wa ba can gyi 'od bzhi dmar po /
NK024(ya)001:19481: byang du rdo rje snying po /
NK024(ya)001:19484: kun tu bzang po bzhi ljang gu /
NK024(ya)001:19485: thams cad kyang rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pas sems dpa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19486: gtso 'khor thams cad kyang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan cing /
NK024(ya)001:19487: dar gyi stod g.yogs dang sham thabs can /
NK024(ya)001:19488: gdan la sems dpa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19489: de lta bu'i mngon par rtogs pa'i legs cha 'ga' zhig khams lugs nas kyang btus shing /
NK024(ya)001:19490: gtso bo ni kun tu zhal rigs te /
NK024(ya)001:19492: yo ga'i gtso bo kun tu zhal //
NK024(ya)001:19494: de nas rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:19495: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:19496: spos dang bcas pa'i rdo rje dril bu 'dzin pas /
NK024(ya)001:19497: nyang gter rdor dbyings dkyil chog nas 'byung ba ltar /
NK024(ya)001:19498: ma lus sems can kun gyi mgon gyur cing //
NK024(ya)001:19499: bdud sde dpung bcas mi bzad 'joms mdzad lha //
NK024(ya)001:19500: dngos rnams ma lus ji bzhin mkhyen gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19501: rgyal ba 'khor bcas spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19502: sarba ta th+aa ga ta e h+ya hi b+ha ga
NK024(ya)001:19503: wan ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya ho
NK024(ya)001:19507: ji ltar bde gshegs bltams pa tsam gyis ni //
NK024(ya)001:19508: lha rnams kun gyis sku khrus gsol ba ltar //
NK024(ya)001:19509: dri med lha yi chu gtsang rab sbyar ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:19510: rgyal ba rnams la sku khrus gsol bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:19511: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos kyi sku //
NK024(ya)001:19512: mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba longs spyod sku //
NK024(ya)001:19513: stong gsum dbang sgyur thugs rje sprul pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19514: sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan sangs rgyas la //
NK024(ya)001:19515: nyon mongs dri ma yongs kyis mi mnga' yang //'gro ba las kyi sgrib pa sbyangs slad du //
NK024(ya)001:19516: sku gsung thugs la khrus chab 'di gsol bas //
NK024(ya)001:19517: mi gtsang dri ma'i tshogs rnams dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19518: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pra b+ha wa sat+ka ra
NK024(ya)001:19519: pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha
NK024(ya)001:19520: ra na sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19521: de bzhin gshegs dang de yi sras rnams la /
NK024(ya)001:19522: rin chen bum pa mang po spos kyi chus //
NK024(ya)001:19523: yid 'ong legs par bkang ba glu dang ni //
NK024(ya)001:19524: rol mor bcas pa du mas sku khrus gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19525: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19526: de dag sku la mtshungs pa med pa'i gos //
NK024(ya)001:19527: gtsang la dri rab bgos pas sku phyis pas //'gro kun bag chags dri ma kun dag nas //
NK024(ya)001:19528: rnam dag ye shes rgyal ba'i sku thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:19529: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih a k+aa ya bi sho d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19530: de nas gos zung thogs la /
NK024(ya)001:19531: srab 'jam yang ba lha yi gos //
NK024(ya)001:19532: mi bskyod rdo rje'i sku brnyes la //
NK024(ya)001:19533: mi phyed dad pas bdag 'bul na //
NK024(ya)001:19534: bdag kyang rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:19535: sna tshogs dbang po'i gzhu ltar rab bkra zhing //
NK024(ya)001:19536: gang la reg na bde ba'i rgyur gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:19537: gos bzang rin chen bdag blo sbyang phyir 'bul //
NK024(ya)001:19538: bzod pa dam pa'i gos kyis brgyan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19543: mya ngan mi 'da' thugs rje chen po'i ngang //
NK024(ya)001:19544: nyon mongs mi spong rkyen gyis gos pa med //
NK024(ya)001:19545: ma chags dag la gtsang zhing mdzes pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:19546: pad+ma'i gdan la brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19547: pad+ma ka ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:19548: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus 'khor bcas ni //'gyur med chos kyi dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK024(ya)001:19549: gnyis med dam tshig don la thugs dgongs la //
NK024(ya)001:19550: dgyes pa'i tshul gyis brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19551: pad+ma ka ma la ye s+t+wam /
NK024(ya)001:19552: bdag dang 'gro ba rnams la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:19553: nyid kyi rdzu 'phrul chen po'i mthu yis ni //
NK024(ya)001:19554: bla med mchod sprin ji srid bdag bgyid na //
NK024(ya)001:19555: de srid bcom ldan 'khor bcas bzhugs su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19556: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa ma ya +aa be sha ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK024(ya)001:19557: bcom ldan 'dir ni byon pa legs //
NK024(ya)001:19558: bdag cag bsod nams skal bar ldan //
NK024(ya)001:19559: thugs rje chen pos brtser dgongs te //
NK024(ya)001:19560: mchod pa dam pa bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19561: sarba ta th+aa ga ta na mah sa man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam /
NK024(ya)001:19562: ga ga na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19567: zhes mchod nas rdo rje thal mo dpral bar sbyar la /
NK024(ya)001:19568: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK024(ya)001:19569: pra na me na badz+ra ban+d+ha n+aam ka ro mi
NK024(ya)001:19570: / zhes phyag byas par mos te /
NK024(ya)001:19571: sgo ba bzhi'i phyag rgya rim par bca' ba dang bstun /
NK024(ya)001:19572: badz+ra am gu sha dzahs nam mkha'i lha mdun bskyed dang nye bar dgug /
NK024(ya)001:19573: badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum gis gzhug /
NK024(ya)001:19574: badz+ra s+pho ta bam gyis phan tshun mi 'bral bar bcings /
NK024(ya)001:19575: badz+ra +aa be sha yas lha rnams dbyer med du
NK024(ya)001:19576: dbang du byas par bsam pa ste ye shes pa
NK024(ya)001:19578: mdun bskyed kyi lha rnams la b+h+ri ta sogs rigs
NK024(ya)001:19579: gsum gyi sngags rgyas lan gsum byin gyis brlab pa
NK024(ya)001:19580: dang / bud+d+ha sogs dbang bskur ba rnams gong bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:19581: skabs 'dir gsar ma'i yo ga ltar na phyag rgya
NK024(ya)001:19582: bzhis rgyas gdab pa dang las la sbyar ba'i phrin
NK024(ya)001:19583: bcol mdzad cing / des mtshungs nyang gter rdor dbyings su /
NK024(ya)001:19584: bar 'dir sems can thams cad skye med ngang du rgyas gdab phrin las bcol /
NK024(ya)001:19585: rang don du byed na lha so so'i snying po dang sku mdog phyag mtshan gsal gdab /
NK024(ya)001:19586: ces 'byung bas gsar rnying bka' gter thams cad dgongs
NK024(ya)001:19587: pa gcig par snang bas rgyas gdab phrin bcol ris
NK024(ya)001:19588: par snang yang / bka' ma mdo dbang gi skabs 'dir rgyas gdab dmigs bsal ma byung zhing /
NK024(ya)001:19589: cho ga zor yang ba dang chad pa'i skyon med par rtogs te ma bris so //
NK024(ya)001:19591: nyang gter bde gshegs 'dus pa'i rdor dbyings rigs brgya'i
NK024(ya)001:19592: lag len chog sgrigs rin po che'i sgron me dang
NK024(ya)001:19593: / de'i gsal byed byang pa rig 'dzin phrin las
NK024(ya)001:19594: rnam rgyal gyis mdzad pa'i rdor dbyings dam pa rigs
NK024(ya)001:19595: brgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rin po che'i phreng
NK024(ya)001:19596: ba gzhan phan rnam par rol pa'i rgyan las byung
NK024(ya)001:19597: ba ltar brjod na legs par mthong bas /
NK024(ya)001:19598: de'i tshul ni slar yang mdun bskyed kyi mchod pa rnams gsar du spro ba'am /
NK024(ya)001:19599: kha gsos shing sngar ltar byin gyis brlabs te /
NK024(ya)001:19600: thog mar nyer spyod 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:19601: tshigs bcad la thal mo sbyor zhing sngags la gar
NK024(ya)001:19602: skor sngon du 'gro bas so so'i las rgya'i mthar
NK024(ya)001:19603: se gol gtog pa dang bcas te 'di ltar /
NK024(ya)001:19605: yan lag brgyad ldan dri ma med pa'i chu //
NK024(ya)001:19606: rtsi shing sna tshogs 'o mar rab sbyar te //
NK024(ya)001:19607: rgyal ba'i sku mdun mchod yon 'di phul bas //'gro ba'i nad zhi bkra shis phun tshogs shog /
NK024(ya)001:19608: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza
NK024(ya)001:19609: me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma
NK024(ya)001:19610: ye h+aum / spos dang tsan+dana la sogs dri sbyar ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:19611: las kun tshim byed chu gtsang dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19612: rgyal ba rnams kyi zhal la bsil bar gyur //'gro kun glo bur dri ma dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19613: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pra b+ha wa sat+ka ra
NK024(ya)001:19614: pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza chu dang thang skyes yid las
NK024(ya)001:19615: byung ba yi // byang chub yan lag mdzes pa'i me tog 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19616: bsam gtan rang bzhin rgyal ba'i dbu la 'bul //'gro kun mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19617: bush+pe p+au dza lhan cig skyes dang yongs sbyar las gyur pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19618: dri zhim rab tu tshim ldan bdug spos 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19619: shes rab rang bzhin rgyal ba'i shangs la 'bul //'gro kun tshul khrims rnam par dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19620: d+h+au pe p+au dmar gsal mdangs ldan gtsang zhing mdzes ldan pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19621: me shel gsal byed ye shes sgron me 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19622: smon lam rang bzhin rgyal ba'i spyan la 'bul //'gro
NK024(ya)001:19623: kun sku lngar yongs su dag gyur cig /+aa lo
NK024(ya)001:19624: ke tsan+dana gur gum a kar la sogs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19625: dri zhim rab tu sbyar ba'i byug pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19626: thabs kyi rang bzhin rgyal ba'i sku la 'bul //'gro kun zag med phung po thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19627: gan+d+he kha dog dri dang ro brgya ldan pa'i zas //
NK024(ya)001:19628: longs spyod mchod pa'i sprin du byin brlabs te //
NK024(ya)001:19629: stobs kyi rang bzhin rgyal ba'i zhal la 'bul //'gro kun sred med bu yi mthu thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:19630: nee wi d+ya pi wang gling bu cang te'u kar ko ta //
NK024(ya)001:19631: dril bu cha lang la sogs rol mo'i sgra //
NK024(ya)001:19632: glu gar dbyangs kyi mchod pa ji snyed pa //
NK024(ya)001:19633: tshangs pa'i dbyangs sgra rgyal ba'i snyan la 'bul //'gro kun tshangs pa dbyangs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:19634: sarba ta th+aa ga ta shap+da pra t+aits+tsha p+au dza
NK024(ya)001:19635: me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma
NK024(ya)001:19637: gzhan yang rgyal srid rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK024(ya)001:19639: zhes 'byung ba nyang gter rdo byings dkyil chog rin chen phreng ba las /
NK024(ya)001:19641: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad la //'khor lo rin chen 'di phul bas //
NK024(ya)001:19642: srid pa'i 'khor lo rgyun bcad de //
NK024(ya)001:19643: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:19644: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsakra rat+na pu dzi te +aahh+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19645: bde bar nor bu bkres shing phongs pa rgyun bcad de //'byor pa phun sum tshogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19646: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma ni rat+na bde bar btsun mo shes rab dbyings kyi don rtogs nas //
NK024(ya)001:19647: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:19648: wa ti rat+na bde bar blon po bsam yas bstan pa rab 'dzin cing //
NK024(ya)001:19649: yon tan thams cad ldan par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19650: ma h+aa ta rat+na bde bar glang po bla med theg par rab zhon nas //
NK024(ya)001:19651: thams cad mkhyen grong bgrod par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19652: hasti rat+na bde bar rta mchog srid pa'i gzeb las nges grol te //
NK024(ya)001:19653: rdzu 'phrul shugs thob sangs rgyas shog /
NK024(ya)001:19654: tu rang+ga a shwa rat+na bde bar gshegs pa dmag
NK024(ya)001:19655: dpon rin chen phas kyi rgol ba tshar bcad nas
NK024(ya)001:19656: // bsnyes bral mchog ni thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19657: khad+ga rat+na 'dod yon lngas mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19659: kha dog dbyibs legs yid 'ong rgyan phreng ldan //
NK024(ya)001:19660: phyogs dus kun na gzugs mchog ci mchis pa //
NK024(ya)001:19661: mos blos dkyil 'khor lha la bdag 'bul na //
NK024(ya)001:19662: bzhes shig bla med grub mchog stsal du gsol //
NK024(ya)001:19663: sarba ta th+aa ga ta r+au pa k+aa ma gu na pu dzi te +aahh+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19664: phyogs dus kun na zin dang ma zin pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19665: yon tan tshig brjod sgra snyan yid 'ong ldan //
NK024(ya)001:19666: mos blos bzhes shig shap+da phyogs dus kun na tsan+dana sbrul snying dang //
NK024(ya)001:19667: a gar la sogs dbang po tshim byed dri //
NK024(ya)001:19668: mos blos bzhes shig gan+d+he phyogs dus kun na ro dang bcud ldan pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19669: lus sems brtas byed ro mchog ci mchis pa //
NK024(ya)001:19670: mos blos bzhes shig r+aa sa phyogs dus kun na 'jam mnyen 'khril chags pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:19671: reg bya'i khyad par lus sems bde bskyed rnams //
NK024(ya)001:19672: mos blos bzhes shig spar+she 'di rnams kyi phyag rgya
NK024(ya)001:19673: brir ma lang bas shes na rnal 'byor rgyud lugs
NK024(ya)001:19674: spyi ltar bya'o // mchod phreng 'di rnams kyang rgyas
NK024(ya)001:19675: pa'i yan lag tu 'dug pas nyang gter rdor dbyings
NK024(ya)001:19676: las 'byung ba 'di ltar bkra shis rtags brgyad kyis
NK024(ya)001:19677: spyi ltar bya'o // mchod pa ni / h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19678: rin chen gser gdugs bkra shis rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:19679: bde gshegs dbu la mtshan dang dpe byad shar //
NK024(ya)001:19680: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul lags na //'gro kun mgo la gdugs kyi bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:19681: rin chen rgyal mtshan bkra shis bde gshegs sku la
NK024(ya)001:19682: mtshan bla med dkon mchog 'gro kun bdud las rgyal
NK024(ya)001:19683: ba'i bkra rin chen gser nya bkra bde gshegs spyan
NK024(ya)001:19684: la bla med 'gro kun spyan lnga ldan pa'i rin
NK024(ya)001:19685: chen dung dkar bde gshegs gsung la bla med 'gro
NK024(ya)001:19686: kun chos sgra gsung gi rin chen bum pa bde
NK024(ya)001:19687: gshegs mgur la bla med 'gro kun 'chi med tshe
NK024(ya)001:19688: yi rin chen pad+ma bde gshegs ljags la bla med
NK024(ya)001:19689: 'gro kun yon tan kun ldan rin chen dpal be'u
NK024(ya)001:19690: bde gshegs thugs la bla med 'gro kun mi 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:19692: rin chen 'khor lo bkra shis rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:19693: bde gshegs zhabs la mtshan dang dpe byad shar //
NK024(ya)001:19694: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul lags na //'gro
NK024(ya)001:19695: kun 'khor ba rgyun gcod bkra shis shog /'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:19696: rdzas brgyad kyis mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19697: 'jig rten 'adi'am stong gsum gzhan dag na //
NK024(ya)001:19698: ma rmos lo tog 'bras gro nas dang khre //'bru sna ji snyed yod pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19699: bla med dkon mchog gsum la 'bul lags na //'gro
NK024(ya)001:19700: kun bkres pa'i sdug bsngal sel bar shog /'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:19701: 'di 'am rgya mtsho chu bo chu gling 'bab chu
NK024(ya)001:19702: dang // chu sna ji snyed yod pa'i bla med
NK024(ya)001:19703: 'gro kun skoms pa'i sdug bsngal sel bar shog /'jig
NK024(ya)001:19704: rten ga bur gur gum gi wang dz+aa ti dang
NK024(ya)001:19705: dang // // sman sna ji snyed yod pa'i bla
NK024(ya)001:19706: med 'gro kun nad kyi sdug bsngal sel bar shog
NK024(ya)001:19707: /'jig rten tsan+dana a gar gu gul gla rtsi dang
NK024(ya)001:19708: dang // // // dri sna ji snyed bla med
NK024(ya)001:19709: 'gro kun nyon mongs nad rnams zhi bar shog /'jig
NK024(ya)001:19710: rten gser dang zangs lcags g.yu dang gzi mchong dang
NK024(ya)001:19711: dang // // // // rin chen rnam pa ji snyed yod pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19712: bla med 'gro kun rin chen rgyan dang ldan par
NK024(ya)001:19713: shog /'jig rten ka ra bu ram sbrang rtsi khan+ta
NK024(ya)001:19714: dang // bcu dang ro ldan ji snyed yod pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19715: bla med 'gro kun bdud rtsi'i bcud kyis tshim gyur
NK024(ya)001:19716: shog /'jig rten 'o ma mar dang zho dang khrum
NK024(ya)001:19717: dang thud // snying po ji snyed yod pa'i mchod pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:19718: bla med 'gro kun bcud len lus la rgyas par
NK024(ya)001:19719: shog /'jig rten bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bshos
NK024(ya)001:19720: dang skyems / kha mngar skyur rtsub zas mchog ji snyed kun //
NK024(ya)001:19721: bla med 'gro kun lus ngag yid gsum tshim gyur shog /
NK024(ya)001:19722: de nas rgyan gyis mchod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:19724: rin chen rgyan mchog dkyil 'khor 'phags pa'i mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:19725: bla bre kha dog dbyibs legs mkha' ltar mnyam //
NK024(ya)001:19726: dar gyi lda ldi shes rab rlung gis bskyod //
NK024(ya)001:19727: sna tshogs mdzes pa'i rgyan gyis skar ltar klubs //
NK024(ya)001:19728: yon chab dam pa gtsang zhing me re bstim //
NK024(ya)001:19729: zhugs tog dam pa gza' skar bkram pa bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:19730: bdug spos sprin gtibs snang gsal nyi zla 'dra //
NK024(ya)001:19731: dri mchog yid 'ong zhal zas ro mchog ldan //
NK024(ya)001:19732: rol mo'i sgra sgrog 'brug stong ldir ba bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:19733: thugs rje brtse ldan khyed la 'bul bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:19734: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhing khams thams cad du //
NK024(ya)001:19735: yid du 'ong ba'i mchod sprin bsngo ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:19736: rol mo sil snyan 'phan gdugs bla bre dang //
NK024(ya)001:19737: rgyal mtshan lhab lhub me tog phreng bdug spos //
NK024(ya)001:19738: mchod sprin sna tshogs phyogs bcur rab 'bul bas //
NK024(ya)001:19739: sangs rgyas rnams kyi zhing khams rab 'byams su //
NK024(ya)001:19740: bla med mchod sprin 'byung zhing yon tan rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:19741: bde gshegs zhabs la spyi bos gtugs gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19742: dam chos kun dang mchod rten sku gdug la //
NK024(ya)001:19743: yid 'ong mchod sprin sna tshogs 'byung ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:19744: rin chen me tog mdzes pa'i char rgyun rnams //
NK024(ya)001:19745: dus rnams rtag tu rgya chen 'bebs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:19746: hoh mgon po bdag gi bsod nams kyis stobs dang /
NK024(ya)001:19747: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi mthu dang /
NK024(ya)001:19748: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i byin rlabs dang /
NK024(ya)001:19749: gsang sngags rig sngags gzungs sngags snying po phyag rgya la sogs pa'i mthu dang /
NK024(ya)001:19750: bdag gi bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i stobs kyis
NK024(ya)001:19751: bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhing khams dang
NK024(ya)001:19753: kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin rgya che ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:19754: phun sum tshogs pa mnga' thang chen po dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:19755: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK024(ya)001:19756: na mo b+ha ga wa te badz+ra sa ra pra ma rda na ye /
NK024(ya)001:19757: ta th+aa ga ta ya ar+ha te samyak+sam bud+d+ha ya /
NK024(ya)001:19762: ma h+aa bo d+hi tsat+ta badz+ra /
NK024(ya)001:19764: u pa sam kra ma na badz+ra le s+w+aa h+aa /
NK024(ya)001:19766: zur lugs kyi lha thems dang khams lugs kyi sgrub
NK024(ya)001:19767: mchod skabs kyi bstod pa lha dbang gi bskur tshig
NK024(ya)001:19768: sogs 'dra min sna tshogs las dpyad pa ni 'di
NK024(ya)001:19769: ltar / rdo rje dril bu 'dzin cing bstod dbyangs dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:19771: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:19772: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19773: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:19774: phyag 'tshal rnam par snang mdzad la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19775: me long ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK024(ya)001:19776: sems ma rdo rje'i phyag rgya ste //
NK024(ya)001:19777: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa //
NK024(ya)001:19778: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:19779: mnyam nyid ye shes rin chen sems ma'i rin chen ser po zur brgyad pa //
NK024(ya)001:19780: bstod cing gus pas kun rtog ye shes chos kyi sems ma'i pad dkar 'dab ma bcu drug pa //
NK024(ya)001:19781: bstod cing bya grub ye shes las kyi sems ma'i rdo rje rgya gram ljang gu la //
NK024(ya)001:19782: bstod cing gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:19783: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa //
NK024(ya)001:19784: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19785: bdud 'dul chen po'i phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:19786: phyag 'tshal rdo rje mi bskyod la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19787: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK024(ya)001:19788: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19789: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang //
NK024(ya)001:19790: phyag 'tshal phyag na rdo rje la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19791: rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19792: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:19793: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19795: rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK024(ya)001:19796: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:19797: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK024(ya)001:19798: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gzhu rdo rje legs pa sems dpa'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19799: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //
NK024(ya)001:19800: rab dgyes rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19801: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dgyes rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK024(ya)001:19802: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19803: rdo rje ma chog sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:19805: rdo rje rin chen rdo rje'i don //
NK024(ya)001:19806: rdo rje nam mkha'i nor bu che //
NK024(ya)001:19807: nam mkha'i snying po rdo rje phyug /
NK024(ya)001:19808: phyag 'tshal rdo rje snying khyod la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19809: rdo rje gzi brjid cher 'bar ba //
NK024(ya)001:19810: rdo rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:19811: rdo rje 'od zer gzi brjid che //
NK024(ya)001:19812: phyag 'tshal rdo rje 'od rdo rje sems can don rab gsal //
NK024(ya)001:19813: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rab dga' byed //
NK024(ya)001:19814: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK024(ya)001:19815: phyag 'tshal rdo rje dpal rdo rje bzhad mo bzhad pa che //
NK024(ya)001:19816: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK024(ya)001:19817: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje ston //
NK024(ya)001:19818: phyag 'tshal rdo rje bzhad 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK024(ya)001:19819: kun rtog ye shes rdo rje'i gsung //
NK024(ya)001:19820: rdo rje ting 'dzin phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:19821: phyag 'tshal snang ba mtha' yas la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19822: rdo rje chos rab de nyid don //
NK024(ya)001:19823: rdo rje pad+ma rab dga' byed //'jig rten dbang phyug rab mdzes can //
NK024(ya)001:19824: phyag 'tshal rdo rje can rdo rje rnon po theg pa che //
NK024(ya)001:19825: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //'jam dpal rdo rje rab tu dga'//
NK024(ya)001:19826: phyag 'tshal rdo rje blo rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK024(ya)001:19827: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK024(ya)001:19828: rab bskor rdo rje las byung ba //
NK024(ya)001:19830: rdo rje gsung ba rang rig mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19831: rdo rje zlos pa rab grub sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:19832: mi gsung rdo rje mchog grub smra //
NK024(ya)001:19833: phyag 'tshal rdo rje gsung khyod la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19834: phrag dog rdo rje bskyod mdzad rlung //
NK024(ya)001:19835: nan tan ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK024(ya)001:19836: rdo rje skyabs sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:19837: phyag 'tshal rdo rje don grub la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19838: rdo rje las rab rdo rje'i bka'//
NK024(ya)001:19839: las kyi rdo rje kun rab 'phro //
NK024(ya)001:19840: rdo rje nges pa rgya che ba //
NK024(ya)001:19841: phyag 'tshal rdo rje kun khyod la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19842: rdo rje bsrung ba brtan pa che //
NK024(ya)001:19843: rdo rje go cha sra ba che //
NK024(ya)001:19844: brtson 'grus rdo rje thub dka' ba //
NK024(ya)001:19846: rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK024(ya)001:19847: rdo rje mche ba gtsigs pa che //
NK024(ya)001:19848: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi zad pa //
NK024(ya)001:19849: phyag 'tshal rdo rje drag po la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19850: rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu 'dud //
NK024(ya)001:19851: rdo rje bcings pa rab grol byed //
NK024(ya)001:19852: rdo rje khu tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19853: phyag 'tshal rdo rje khu tshur la'o //
NK024(ya)001:19854: grwa yi phyogs ni kun tu yang //
NK024(ya)001:19855: rigs kyi yum bzhi'i skur bstan pa //
NK024(ya)001:19856: lha mo spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK024(ya)001:19857: dkar mo sgrol ma khyod phyag 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:19858: shar lho'i lha mo l+aa s+ya ma //
NK024(ya)001:19860: phyag gnyis khu tshur me long bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19861: de la bstod de phyag kyang 'tshal //
NK024(ya)001:19862: lho nub lha mo m+aa le ma //
NK024(ya)001:19864: phyag gnyis rin chen phreng ba bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19865: de la bstod cing phyag nub byang lha mo g+ai ti ma //
NK024(ya)001:19866: sku mdog dmar la 'od phyag gnyis pi wang rgyud mang bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19867: de la bstod cing byang shar lha mo n+air+t+ya ma //
NK024(ya)001:19868: sku mdog ljang la phyag gnyis phyag rgya gar bsgyur ma //
NK024(ya)001:19869: de la shar lho'i lha mo d+h+au pe ma //
NK024(ya)001:19870: sku mdog dkar la phyag mtshan phyag na spos khang bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19871: de la lho nub lha mo push+pe ma //
NK024(ya)001:19872: sku mdog ser la phyag mtshan phyag na me tog bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19873: de la bstod nub byang lha mo +aa lo ke //
NK024(ya)001:19874: sku mdog dmar la phyag mtshan phyag na mar me bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:19875: de la byang shar lha mo gan+d+he ma //
NK024(ya)001:19876: sku mdog ljang la phyag mtshan phyag na dri chab de la shar phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK024(ya)001:19877: sku mdog dkar la phyag mtshan phyag na lcags kyu de la lho phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK024(ya)001:19878: sku mdog ser la phyag mtshan phyag na zhags pa de la nub phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK024(ya)001:19879: sku mdog dmar la phyag mtshan phyag na lcags sgrog /
NK024(ya)001:19880: de la byang phyogs skyong ba'i sgo ma ni //
NK024(ya)001:19881: sku mdog ljang la phyag mtshan phyag na dril bu de la bskal pa bzang po rgyal sras mchog /
NK024(ya)001:19882: byams pa la sogs bcu drug po //
NK024(ya)001:19883: rab dga' la sogs mnga' mdzad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:19884: byang sems rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:19885: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:19886: zhing rdul kun gyi grangs snyed kyis //
NK024(ya)001:19887: lus btud pa yi rnam kun tu //
NK024(ya)001:19888: mchog tu dad pas bstod par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:19889: de nas 'das gtor chab kyis bran te /
NK024(ya)001:19892: badz+ra dz+wa las gzi byin bskyed /
NK024(ya)001:19893: las rin po che'i snod yangs par bdud rtsi'i tshogs kyis gang bar gyur /
NK024(ya)001:19894: rdo rje bsdams pa 'debs pa'i rgyas a k+aa ro lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlab la /
NK024(ya)001:19895: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa pa ri w+aa ra
NK024(ya)001:19896: a k+aa ro btags pa lan gsum gyis phul zhing
NK024(ya)001:19897: / sngags de nyid kyi mthar mchod sngags btags te nyer spyod kyis mchod /
NK024(ya)001:19899: gsar ma la bdag 'jug grub nas bya ba yin kyang /
NK024(ya)001:19900: zur lugs dang khams lugs gnyis kar snga 'gyur kho
NK024(ya)001:19901: na'i rigs 'gres 'dir mdzad pa 'thad par snang zhing
NK024(ya)001:19902: / ji ltar bya ba'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:19903: yo ga rang lugs ltar gong du bshad pa bzhin badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:19904: zhes rdo rje 'dzin ma'i sngags rgyas mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK024(ya)001:19905: badz+ra d+ha ra zhes pas bdag mi bskyod pa dang tha mi dad par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:19906: de bzhin du rat+na d+ha ras rin 'byung /
NK024(ya)001:19908: bi shwa d+ha ras don grub dang tha mi dad pa'i nga rgyal bzung /
NK024(ya)001:19909: ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya ma ti kra
NK024(ya)001:19910: ma ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya d+ha ra
NK024(ya)001:19912: zhes gtso bo rnam snang dang tha mi dad par bsams la /
NK024(ya)001:19917: ta th+aa ga ta d+ha ra sa ma ya ma ti kra ma ta /
NK024(ya)001:19918: ta th+aa ga ta sa ma ya d+ha ra at+ma ko&a ham /
NK024(ya)001:19919: zhes lan gsum brjod cing nga rgyal bzung /
NK024(ya)001:19920: de nas rang rigs 'dus rdor sems kyi rnam pas
NK024(ya)001:19921: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas thon te rang gnas su
NK024(ya)001:19922: 'dug la / dkyil 'khor brtan byed bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:19924: badz+ra a be sha a'i bar gyi lha sngags rnams brgya rtsa sogs ci 'grub dang /
NK024(ya)001:19925: thun mong du durga ci rigs bzlas so //
NK024(ya)001:19926: cha gsum ni snga ma ltar btang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:19927: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bdun par dpang skong bshad pas
NK024(ya)001:19928: spro na dpang skong phyag brgya pa tshar gcig 'don
NK024(ya)001:19929: / des rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu gsum pa mchod bstod rgyas par grub nas /
NK024(ya)001:19930: bcu bzhi pa bdag 'jug ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:19931: de nas rigs lnga'i sdom pa bzung la rang nyid dkyil 'khor la 'jug ces gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:19932: slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba ltar rang nyid kyis dbang blang ngo //
NK024(ya)001:19933: des slob dpon gyi bya ba grub pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:19934: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu pa rgyan dang /
NK024(ya)001:19935: bcu gcig pa khrir 'dzeg pa ni go sla /
NK024(ya)001:19936: bcu gnyis pa dkyil 'khor sgom pa ni rgyas par grub bo //
NK024(ya)001:19937: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:19939: rdzas dbang gi dbang chas rnams gtso bor gyur pa'i dgos pa kun tshogs bar byas la /
NK024(ya)001:19941: khrus bya slob mas yon phul zhes gsungs pa'i don //
NK024(ya)001:19942: ji ltar bltams pa zhes sogs sngags dang bcas te las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK024(ya)001:19944: bgegs gtor btang la sum+b+hasa bgegs bskrad do //
NK024(ya)001:19945: zhes gsungs pas sngon 'gro gtor ma gnyis pa bshams te chab kyis bran //
NK024(ya)001:19946: dkyil 'khor snga ma rnams bzhin bsang sbyang byin brlab sngags bsngosa bden brdar /
NK024(ya)001:19949: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor lha
NK024(ya)001:19950: tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa
NK024(ya)001:19953: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:19955: man+dala gyi me tog bkye bsdu byas te /
NK024(ya)001:19957: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK024(ya)001:19958: don du khyab bdag rnam snang chen po'i go 'phang
NK024(ya)001:19959: thob par bya / de'i ched du bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:19960: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen por dbang dang
NK024(ya)001:19961: gdams pa tshul bzhin du blangs te sems can gyi
NK024(ya)001:19962: don bgyid snyam pa byang chub kyi mchog tu thugs
NK024(ya)001:19963: bskyed pa gsal btab ste gsan 'tshal /
NK024(ya)001:19964: de la 'dir yo ga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor 'di nyid ji ltar sgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:19965: kun mkhyen klong chen zhabs kyis /
NK024(ya)001:19966: rnal 'byor dngos gzhir gnyis su med pa la //
NK024(ya)001:19967: sbyor rjes lha ni dgug gshegs gnyis su byed //
NK024(ya)001:19968: chu la chu bzhag gnyis med dngos grub len //
NK024(ya)001:19969: zhes gsungs pa ltar bya dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:19970: de yang bdag bskyed rigs 'dus rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK024(ya)001:19971: bum bskyed rigs lnga'i dbang gi bum par rigs dbye ba'i sgrub tshul /
NK024(ya)001:19972: mdun bskyed rtsa lha so bdun byang sems bcu drug
NK024(ya)001:19973: dang bcas pa tshul bzhin sgrub mchod byed pa sogs
NK024(ya)001:19974: rtsa ba mi nyams shing cho ga gzhan gyis gsal
NK024(ya)001:19975: bar byas te legs par grub pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:19976: 'on kyang zur lugs 'dir cho ga rnams rtsa thob tsam dang /
NK024(ya)001:19977: zhal 'phangs sogs shin tu mi bde ba dang /
NK024(ya)001:19978: kah thog lugs su rgyud sde'i dbye tshul cher med par /
NK024(ya)001:19979: sgo 'byed nas a ti'i bar cho ga'i chings gcig
NK024(ya)001:19980: gis bshad pas phyag len bde ba ltar snang yang
NK024(ya)001:19981: / cung zad mi legs par shes te /
NK024(ya)001:19982: 'dir cho ga'i bye brag so sor ma 'dres shing
NK024(ya)001:19983: spyi khyab tu bla med kho nas brgyan te khrigs
NK024(ya)001:19984: su byas pas / dpyad bzod pa'i lugs su bya bgyis pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:19985: slob ma'i bya bar 'jug pa'i chos sogs mi gsal
NK024(ya)001:19986: ba rnams zur lugs su dbang gi sngon 'gro dngos
NK024(ya)001:19988: ces gsungs pas legs cha dang /
NK024(ya)001:19989: med du mi rung ba'i kha 'geng bar 'os pa
NK024(ya)001:19990: rnams nyang gter rdor dbyings dang gzhan phan mtha' yas
NK024(ya)001:19992: gzhan ma'i bsre bslad med par dbang bskur bar bya ba la /
NK024(ya)001:19995: slob mas yon phul zhes dang /
NK024(ya)001:19996: phyag btsal man+dala phul zhes gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:19997: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo rnam snang
NK024(ya)001:19998: chen po tha mi dad pa la yo ga rdo
NK024(ya)001:19999: rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du smin byed kyi dbang
NK024(ya)001:20000: rnams zhu ba'i yon tu man+dala phul /
NK024(ya)001:20001: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu drug pa gsol ba btab pa 'dir blangs te /
NK024(ya)001:20002: snyim pa me tog dang bcas pa thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20004: bcom ldan nam mkha'i sangs rgyas kun //
NK024(ya)001:20005: theg pa chen po'i mthu ldan la //
NK024(ya)001:20006: bdag gis rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20007: rang bzhin ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan lhas //
NK024(ya)001:20008: bdag la dbang mchog deng gsol cig /
NK024(ya)001:20009: sangs rgyas bka' yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK024(ya)001:20010: bdag nyid dad pas 'jug lags na //
NK024(ya)001:20011: dkyil 'khor bcas pa'i lha tshogs kyis //
NK024(ya)001:20012: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20013: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK024(ya)001:20014: bsod nams can du bdag nyid 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20015: sngon las bzang pos 'brel ba lags //
NK024(ya)001:20016: thugs kyi sras su dgongs par mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:20017: ces lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab bo /
NK024(ya)001:20019: ngan song gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyang ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20020: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20021: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20022: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20025: dbang chog rgyal po'i rgyud kyi rjes su 'brangs te phyag len man ngag bzhin bkrol bar /
NK024(ya)001:20026: slob dpon gyis phyag rgya rdo rje bsdams te /
NK024(ya)001:20028: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK024(ya)001:20029: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing
NK024(ya)001:20030: khams mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bden pa
NK024(ya)001:20031: dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK024(ya)001:20032: rigs kyi bu 'di rnams kyi rgyu 'dod chags zhe
NK024(ya)001:20034: rkyen srog gcod ma sbyin len log lta sogs kyi
NK024(ya)001:20035: 'bras bu dmyal ba yi dwags dud 'gror skye ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20036: sdig sgrib bag chags dang bcas pa thams cad phyag
NK024(ya)001:20037: rgya'i 'od zer gyis byang zhing dag par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:20038: / phyag rgya bkrol te sprul cing /
NK024(ya)001:20039: da ha da ha sarba na ra ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20040: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20041: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ga te he dun h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20042: ces brjod cing phyag rgya sprugs pas de'i 'od zer
NK024(ya)001:20043: gyis slob ma'i gnas gsum gyi las sgrib sbyangs bar
NK024(ya)001:20044: bsam mo // sems bskyed gtso bor gyur pa'i rgyun
NK024(ya)001:20045: bshags kyi slad du mdun gyi dkyil 'khor chen po
NK024(ya)001:20046: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor la
NK024(ya)001:20047: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i sprin phung ltar
NK024(ya)001:20048: 'thibs pa'i spyan sngar pha mas thog drangs rigs drug
NK024(ya)001:20049: bar do dang bcas pa'i sems can dang lhan cig
NK024(ya)001:20050: par rgyun bshags bgyid snyam pas 'di'i rjes zlos lan
NK024(ya)001:20051: bsam mo // gsum mdzod / rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:20052: de nas yan lag bdun pa bsdus pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20053: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:20054: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK024(ya)001:20055: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rangs //
NK024(ya)001:20056: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis bzung //
NK024(ya)001:20057: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs mchog la //
NK024(ya)001:20058: byang chub bar du bdag skyabs mchi //
NK024(ya)001:20059: rang gzhan don ni rab sgrub phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20060: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20061: byang chub mchog gi sems ni bskyed bgyis nas //
NK024(ya)001:20062: sems can thams cad bdag gi mgron du gnyer //
NK024(ya)001:20063: byang chub spyod mchog yid 'ong spyad par bgyi //'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas myur thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:20065: de nas nang gi sems bskyed pa ni slob dpon gyis sa ma ya a zhes brjod pas /
NK024(ya)001:20066: khyed rang rnams kyi snying khar kun rdzob byang chub
NK024(ya)001:20067: sems kyi ngo bo zla ba'i dkyi 'khor cha shas
NK024(ya)001:20068: yongs su rdzogs pa nya gang ba'i steng /
NK024(ya)001:20069: don dam byang chub sems kyi ngo bo rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa 'od zer 'phro ba /
NK024(ya)001:20070: de gnyis dbyer med du sems skyed snyam pa'i 'dun pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20071: slob dpon gyis rdo rje snying gar bzhag ste sngags
NK024(ya)001:20072: brjod pas sems bskyed de brtan par byas pa'i mos
NK024(ya)001:20073: pa mdzod / su ra ti sa ma ya s+t+wam hoh sid+d+hi badz+ra ya th+aa su kham /
NK024(ya)001:20074: de nas sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20075: de yang 'dzin rgyu'i dam tshig thams cad rigs lnga spyi dang /
NK024(ya)001:20076: bye brag gnyis su 'dus pa'i dang po ni /
NK024(ya)001:20077: sems can thams cad kyi don du rnam byang bsgrub snyam pa'i smon pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:20078: de'i ched du nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK024(ya)001:20080: sems can don byed rnams sgrub pa 'jug pa'i sems bskyed /
NK024(ya)001:20081: bye brag ni rnam snang gi dam tshig tu dkon mchog gsum 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:20082: mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig tu rdor dril phyag rgya bla ma rnams 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:20083: rin 'byung gi dam tshig tu zang zing mi 'jigs byams chos bzhi sbyin pa /
NK024(ya)001:20084: 'od dpag med kyi dam tshig tu nyan rang bya spyod rnal 'byor gyi rgyud rnams 'dzin pa /
NK024(ya)001:20085: don grub kyi dam tshig tu dam tshig dang sdom
NK024(ya)001:20086: pa de dag nan tan gyis bsrungs pa'i steng du
NK024(ya)001:20087: bla ma dang dkon mchog mchod pa la brtson par
NK024(ya)001:20088: bya dgos pa de rnams legs par bzung snyam pas
NK024(ya)001:20091: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:20092: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:20093: dus 'di nas ni bzung nas su //
NK024(ya)001:20094: ji srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK024(ya)001:20095: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK024(ya)001:20096: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20097: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK024(ya)001:20098: dam pa bdag gis bskyed par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20099: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20100: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20101: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK024(ya)001:20102: bdag gis brtan por bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20103: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK024(ya)001:20104: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK024(ya)001:20105: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor las skyes pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20106: sdom pa deng nas brtan por bzung //
NK024(ya)001:20107: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK024(ya)001:20108: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK024(ya)001:20109: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20110: slob dpon dag kyang bzung ba bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20111: rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK024(ya)001:20112: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK024(ya)001:20113: nyin re bzhin ni lan drug tu //
NK024(ya)001:20114: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:20115: byang chub chen po las byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:20116: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa la //
NK024(ya)001:20117: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK024(ya)001:20118: dam pa'i chos ni bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20119: las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK024(ya)001:20120: sdom pa thams cad ldan par ni //
NK024(ya)001:20121: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20122: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20123: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK024(ya)001:20124: dam pa bdag gis bskyed bgyis nas //
NK024(ya)001:20125: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20126: bdag gis sdom pa ma lus bzung //
NK024(ya)001:20127: ma grol ba ni dgrol bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20128: ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20129: dbugs ma phyin pa dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK024(ya)001:20130: sems can mya ngan 'das la dgod //
NK024(ya)001:20131: ces lan gsum brjod pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20132: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu dgu pa dam tshig dbog pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20133: skabs 'dir gsar ma'i yo gar rigs gsum spyi'i sngags rgya dang /
NK024(ya)001:20134: rdo rje khu tshur gyi sngags rgyas byin rlabs 'byung yang dmigs bsal ma bshad phyin ma dgos shing /
NK024(ya)001:20135: dam tshig pa bskyed pa 'thad pas /
NK024(ya)001:20137: dam tshig pa bskyed la zhes 'byung bas /
NK024(ya)001:20138: de'i tshul ni slob dpon gyis badz+ra a d+hi tish+tha dz+ny+aa na sa ma ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20139: zhes brjod pas khyed rang rnams rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK024(ya)001:20140: gzugs su gyur pa'i mos pas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK024(ya)001:20143: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bco lnga pa chos bshad pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20144: 'dir mdzad pa gsan pas khyab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:20146: 'jig rten du ni kun mkhyen dag /
NK024(ya)001:20147: u dum+wa ra'i me tog bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:20148: brgya lam la ni res 'ga' zhig /'byung 'gyur yang ni mi 'byung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:20149: gsang sngags spyod pa'i tshul 'byung ba //
NK024(ya)001:20150: de bas kyang ni dkon pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:20151: gang gi sems can mnyam med don //
NK024(ya)001:20152: bla med byed par nus pa yin //
NK024(ya)001:20153: bskal pa bye ba du ma ru //
NK024(ya)001:20154: sngon chad sdig pa byas pa gang //
NK024(ya)001:20156: de dag zad par 'gyur yin na //
NK024(ya)001:20157: grags pa mtha' yas sngags spyod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20158: tshul la gnas na smon ci dgos //
NK024(ya)001:20159: skyob pa'i gsang sngags bzlas na ni //
NK024(ya)001:20161: gang gi spyod pa mchog 'di la //
NK024(ya)001:20162: blo gros shin tu mi g.yo na //
NK024(ya)001:20163: sdug bsngal thams cad 'byung ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:20165: bdag nyid chen po khyed rnams kyi //
NK024(ya)001:20166: rnyed pa mnyam med de ring rnyed //
NK024(ya)001:20167: gang phyir rgyal ba sras bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:20168: bdag nyid chen po kun gyi ni //
NK024(ya)001:20169: bstan pa 'di la khyed rnams kun //
NK024(ya)001:20170: yongs su bzung ste skye bzhin pa //
NK024(ya)001:20171: de phyir khyed rnams theg chen du //
NK024(ya)001:20172: sang ni rab tu skye bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20173: theg pa chen po cher 'byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:20174: lam mchog 'di ni dpal dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:20175: khyed rnams der ni dang bas na //
NK024(ya)001:20176: rang byung skal ba chen po pa //'jig rten thams cad mkhyen pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:20177: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid du 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20180: de'i don ni rnam snang mngon byang gi rgyud nas
NK024(ya)001:20181: gsungs pa'i tshigs su bcad pa 'di'i don ci zhe
NK024(ya)001:20182: na / 'jig rten du u dum+wa ra'i me tog
NK024(ya)001:20183: dkon pa bas kyang sangs rgyas 'jig rten du 'byung
NK024(ya)001:20184: na / ba dkon / de bas kyang gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa dkon la /
NK024(ya)001:20185: de yang phan yon chen po dang ldan pas /
NK024(ya)001:20186: bskal pa du mar bsags pa'i sdig pa rnams kyang
NK024(ya)001:20187: dkyil 'khor 'di mthong ba'i mod la 'dag par 'gyur
NK024(ya)001:20188: na / dbang blangs te dam tshig dang sdom pa
NK024(ya)001:20189: la nan tan du byas te lha sgom zhing sngags
NK024(ya)001:20190: bzla ba la brtson par byas na ngan 'gro'i sdug
NK024(ya)001:20191: bsngal skyob par lta ci smos /
NK024(ya)001:20192: de bas na khyed rnams kyis rnyed pa'i mchog rnyed
NK024(ya)001:20193: cing rgyal ba sras bcas kyis yongs su bzung ste
NK024(ya)001:20194: de'i rigs su skye bzhin par gyur la /
NK024(ya)001:20195: theg chen sngags kyi lam 'di la brten nas 'jig
NK024(ya)001:20196: rten na thams cad mkhyen pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa
NK024(ya)001:20197: nyid du 'gyur bar gdon mi za bas don de
NK024(ya)001:20198: la dga' ba khyad par can bsgoms mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20200: de nas me tog phreng ba bzung /
NK024(ya)001:20202: mchan bur me tog gtad mig dar bcings zhes 'byung bas /
NK024(ya)001:20203: a kham w+ai ra h+aum zhes mig dar bcings /
NK024(ya)001:20204: badz+ra m+aa le h+aum zhes me tog gi phreng ba gtad /
NK024(ya)001:20205: de yang a thung ngus nam mkha' 'gengs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:20206: +aahringa pos nam mkha' gang ba'i don yin zhes bla mas gsung ngo //
NK024(ya)001:20207: sngar gyi rdo rje sems dpa' nga rgyal la gnas bzhin pas /
NK024(ya)001:20208: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i phyir me tog gi phreng ba 'dzin bzhin pas /
NK024(ya)001:20209: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bco brgyad pa sgo 'byed pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20211: shar sgo nas lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas tshig 'di dag gi rjes zlos bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20212: rab gnas sgo 'di zhe sdang gis //
NK024(ya)001:20213: thogs med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK024(ya)001:20214: snying rje'i sbyin pa rdo rje'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:20215: thugs rje thabs mkhas sprul pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:20216: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya mchog 'di yis //
NK024(ya)001:20217: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20218: badz+ra kro d+ha ta th+aa ga tod sa ma ye
NK024(ya)001:20219: ta th+aa pra be sh+ai kram s+pha ra na sa
NK024(ya)001:20221: ces rdo rje'i 'gros kyis 'jug pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20222: de bzhin du zhags pa'i phyag rgyas lho sgor 'khod de rjes zlos bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20223: rab gnas sgo 'di nga rgyal gyis //
NK024(ya)001:20224: thogs med dus nas byams pa'i rigs mthun rin chen
NK024(ya)001:20225: thugs rje thabs mkhas zhags pa'i phyag rgya de ring
NK024(ya)001:20226: thar pa'i rat+na kro d+ha zhes rin chen 'gros kyis
NK024(ya)001:20228: de nas lcags sgrog gi phyag rgyas nub sgo nas rjes zlos bya zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20230: thogs med dus nas dga' ba don spyod pad+ma'i thugs
NK024(ya)001:20231: rje lcags sgrog de ring pad+ma zhes pad+ma'i 'gros kyis
NK024(ya)001:20233: de nas dril bu'i phyag rgya byang sgor /
NK024(ya)001:20234: rab gnas sgo 'di phrag dog gis /
NK024(ya)001:20235: thogs med btang snyoms snyan smra las kyi rigs //
NK024(ya)001:20236: thugs rje dril bu'i phyag de ring karma zhes rgya gram 'gros kyis 'jug go //
NK024(ya)001:20237: slar yang shar sgo nas thun mong du 'jug pa'i gsol gdab 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20240: snying po'i pho brang dam pa 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:20241: bla med byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK024(ya)001:20242: dngos grub dam pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20243: bdag nyid dad pas 'jug tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20244: zhes dad pas lan gsum du gsol ba btab bo //
NK024(ya)001:20245: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi sgo phye ste /
NK024(ya)001:20249: byang chub rin chen sems bskyed de /
NK024(ya)001:20250: 'khor ba'i nang nas rab drangs te //
NK024(ya)001:20251: bde gshegs sras su bskyed pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20252: bla med 'bras bu smin bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20253: bdag gis slob ma 'jug par bgyi //
NK024(ya)001:20254: zhes brjod de gnang ba sbyin la /
NK024(ya)001:20256: bla mas slob mar rdo rje gtad la /
NK024(ya)001:20258: sangs rgyas kun gyi ye shes dag /
NK024(ya)001:20259: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:20260: sangs rgyas kun tu rab sgrub phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20261: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis long //
NK024(ya)001:20262: zhes slob ma rdo rje 'dzin du bcug la /
NK024(ya)001:20264: bla ma'i phyag gi rdo rje la bzung ste dkyil 'khor gyi nang du zhugs pas /
NK024(ya)001:20265: dkyil 'khor gyi lha phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20267: de nas bla ma rigs lnga dbyer med la phyag byas te /
NK024(ya)001:20269: phyag 'tshal ba'i mos pas thal mo sbyar te /
NK024(ya)001:20272: bcom ldan snying po'i pho brang 'dir //
NK024(ya)001:20273: rgyal ba rigs lnga 'khor bcas la //
NK024(ya)001:20274: skal ldan rgyal sras dag pa zhog /
NK024(ya)001:20275: rab tu gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK024(ya)001:20277: ye shes pa dbab pa'i don du gsol ba btab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20278: bdag ni dam tshig 'khor lo ste //
NK024(ya)001:20279: rigs lnga'i dam tshig yin pa'i phyir //'khor lo ye shes bla med 'di //
NK024(ya)001:20280: de ring bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20281: zhes lan gsum gyi rjes zlos bya /
NK024(ya)001:20285: nga ni dam tshig 'khor lo ste //
NK024(ya)001:20286: rgyal ba rigs lnga yin par grags //'khor lo ye shes bla med pa //
NK024(ya)001:20287: de ring khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK024(ya)001:20289: rtsa ba'i sa bcad bcu dgu pa ye shes dbab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20291: ye shes dbab ces gsungs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:20293: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams
NK024(ya)001:20294: cad bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs
NK024(ya)001:20295: kyi rnam par sku che ba ri rab kyi zhes
NK024(ya)001:20296: pa tsam las ma gsungs pas /
NK024(ya)001:20297: de'i don gsal bar byas pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20298: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams la gus 'dud byas pa'i rkyen gyis /
NK024(ya)001:20299: lha tshogs rnams kyi sku las rang 'dra'i ye shes pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:20300: gzhan yang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa
NK024(ya)001:20301: thams cad bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi lha
NK024(ya)001:20302: tshogs kyi rnam par sku che ba ri rab tsam
NK024(ya)001:20304: yang chung rdul phran tsam tshad med grangs med par char bzhin du babs te /
NK024(ya)001:20305: khyed rang rnams kyi lus la zhugs pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20306: de lta bu'i ye shes pa rnams snying gar zla
NK024(ya)001:20307: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du h+aum gi rnam par
NK024(ya)001:20309: slob dpon gyis badz+ra pra be sha ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20310: zhes lan mang du brjod cing rdo rje bsdams pa'i
NK024(ya)001:20311: phyag rgya slob ma'i snying gar gtug tshul bya zhing
NK024(ya)001:20312: sgrub grogs kyis rol mo bya /
NK024(ya)001:20313: ye shes pa brtan byed du slob ma rnams kyi spyi bor rdo rje bzhag cing /
NK024(ya)001:20315: a sa me tro sa me ma h+aa sa ma ye h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20317: de nas gong du sbyin pa'i me tog rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyas bzung ste /
NK024(ya)001:20318: dkyil 'khor la me tog dbul ba'i don du dkyil
NK024(ya)001:20319: 'khor gyi lha la bzang ngan med kyang las kyis
NK024(ya)001:20320: 'brel ba'i lha dang mjal bar shog snyam pas 'di'i
NK024(ya)001:20322: sngon gyi tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK024(ya)001:20323: dge ba'i las kyis bsnyen pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:20324: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK024(ya)001:20325: da lta nyid du 'bab par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20326: sangs rgyas dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20327: bdag la thugs brtser dgongs nas ni //'gro la phan phyir brtse chen gyis //
NK024(ya)001:20328: dman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20329: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes pas dkyil 'khor du me tog dor /
NK024(ya)001:20330: me tog gang la phog pa'i lhas khyed rang rnams
NK024(ya)001:20331: kyi spyi bor me tog bzhag ste byin gyis brlabs
NK024(ya)001:20334: pra ti grih+na swa mi mam gyis spyi bor bzhag la gang babs pa'i lhar bsam /
NK024(ya)001:20336: me tog gang la phog pa'i lha de'i skur gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20337: mig dbye'i gsol gdab 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20340: shin tu ma rig rmongs pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:20341: bdag ni ldongs par gyur pas na //
NK024(ya)001:20342: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK024(ya)001:20343: bdag gi mig 'di dbye bar gsol //
NK024(ya)001:20346: bla mas mig thur ram rdo rjes mig dbye zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20349: rdo rje sems dpa' bdag nyid de //
NK024(ya)001:20350: khyod kyi mig ni rab 'bar yin //
NK024(ya)001:20351: thams cad rdo rje 'bar ba'i mig /
NK024(ya)001:20352: phye bas khyod kyis mthong bar 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20353: badz+ra ha se ut+ga ta ya h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20355: dkyil 'khor lta bar bskul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20358: da ni dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK024(ya)001:20359: gsang sngags chen po'i snod du 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20360: rnyed pa mnyam med de ring rnyed //
NK024(ya)001:20361: dam tshig gang yang 'da' ma byed //
NK024(ya)001:20362: bla med byang chub thob par 'gyur //
NK024(ya)001:20364: de yang rten gzhal yas khang nyis rim mtshan nyid
NK024(ya)001:20365: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang du brten pa
NK024(ya)001:20366: lha bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs
NK024(ya)001:20367: mngon sum lta bur bzhugs pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:20368: ling tshe'i dbus su rnam snang la yum bzhi'i ngo bo phyag rgya bzhis bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:20369: phyogs bzhi'i ling tsher rigs bzhi la rang rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi res bskor ba /
NK024(ya)001:20370: ling tshe'i zur bzhir yum bzhi /
NK024(ya)001:20371: glo 'bur gyi gru chad bzhir sgeg sogs brgyad /
NK024(ya)001:20373: phyi nang gi bar gyi khyams la sems dpa' bcu
NK024(ya)001:20374: drug dang bcas dngos su mjal bas 'di rnams mnyes
NK024(ya)001:20375: pa'i thabs la brtson par mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20377: byang chub kyi chu sbyin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20378: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK024(ya)001:20379: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK024(ya)001:20381: bdag nyid sngags sogs de bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:20383: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20385: zhes gsungs ba bkrol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20386: las bum gyi chu sbyin zhing /
NK024(ya)001:20387: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK024(ya)001:20388: dam tshig 'das na sreg par byed //
NK024(ya)001:20389: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK024(ya)001:20391: ci ste dam tshig 'das na ni //
NK024(ya)001:20392: de ma thag tu bkas nas gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:20393: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:20394: bdun brgyud rigs rnams brlag par byed //
NK024(ya)001:20395: de bas rtag tu bu khyod kyis //
NK024(ya)001:20396: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK024(ya)001:20397: sdom pa dang ni bla ma'i bka'//
NK024(ya)001:20398: shin tu mos pas bsrung bar bya //
NK024(ya)001:20399: zhes pas dam tshig bsgrag cing /
NK024(ya)001:20400: de ltar bsrung bya'i dam tshig 'di rnams gsan pas khyab par gda'/
NK024(ya)001:20401: khyod kyis srog chags bsad mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20402: ma byin par yang blang mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20403: rdzun dang 'dod la spyod pa rnams //
NK024(ya)001:20404: dngos grub 'dod pas bya ba min //
NK024(ya)001:20405: chang ni btung bar mi bya zhing //
NK024(ya)001:20406: sha la sogs pa bza' mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20407: sems can gnod pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:20408: nam yang bya ba ma yin no //
NK024(ya)001:20409: dkon mchog gsum ni yongs mi spang //
NK024(ya)001:20410: dus kun tu ni byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:20411: snying po sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK024(ya)001:20412: lha dang bla ma de bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:20413: sdig la sogs pa gang yin dang //
NK024(ya)001:20414: bla ma'i bka' las 'da' mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20415: lha la phul ba'i rnying pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20416: de yi grib ma'ang 'gom mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20417: phyag rgya'i gzugs la de bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:20418: sngags dang lha la smad mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20419: gdon gyi las sogs bya ba min //
NK024(ya)001:20420: mu stegs can la smad mi bya //
NK024(ya)001:20421: mdor na yid gnyis the tshom som nyi mi bya ste /
NK024(ya)001:20422: bdag gi de nyid dang ni sngags sogs de bzhin no //
NK024(ya)001:20423: zhes brjod pas sdom pa sbyin la /
NK024(ya)001:20424: de lta bu'i dam tshig rgyud la gnas par mos te 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20425: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK024(ya)001:20427: de nas dbang dngos gzhi'i don du gsol ba btab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK024(ya)001:20430: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dgongs su gsol /
NK024(ya)001:20431: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du bdag la dbang bskur du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:20434: slob ma dbang stegs kyi khrir 'khor los sgyur ba'i 'dug stangs kyis bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:20435: zhes 'byung bas spro na dbang stegs bris pa'am yang
NK024(ya)001:20436: na pad 'dab kyi steng du dbang khrir bzang po'i
NK024(ya)001:20438: bla mas bzhengs te dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs su 'dud pa dang bcas te /
NK024(ya)001:20440: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mkhyen par gsol ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20441: bdag rdo rje slob dpon ming 'di zhes bgyi ba
NK024(ya)001:20442: thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob par bya ba
NK024(ya)001:20443: dang / sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan ma
NK024(ya)001:20444: lus pa bsgrub cing sems can gyi don yongs su
NK024(ya)001:20446: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis /
NK024(ya)001:20447: bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo thugs rje'i
NK024(ya)001:20448: mnga' bdag rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i che ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20449: yon tan gyi dbang rnams rim pa bzhin du bskur
NK024(ya)001:20450: zhing byin gyis brlab tu gsol /
NK024(ya)001:20453: zur lugs dbang byang gi mchan bur /
NK024(ya)001:20454: dbang gi sngon 'gro dngos gzhi gzhan phan ltar /
NK024(ya)001:20455: dngos gzhi thog mar bum dbang ni /
NK024(ya)001:20456: rin chen mdzes pa'i bum pa 'dis //
NK024(ya)001:20457: zhes sogs kyis dbang bskur lus gang dri ma dag ces gsungs 'dug kyang /
NK024(ya)001:20458: 'di khar bskur tshig yod phyin bum dbang bskur tshig
NK024(ya)001:20459: gzhan nas len mi dgos kyang tshig rkang la chad
NK024(ya)001:20460: lhag 'dug pa gsal ba'i dgongs pa yin par snang
NK024(ya)001:20466: byang gi bum pas rim pa bzhin dbang bskur zhing zhes gsungs bas /
NK024(ya)001:20467: lha bum gtso bo nas rim par blangs te /
NK024(ya)001:20468: de yang mdun gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi thugs
NK024(ya)001:20469: ka nas sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab
NK024(ya)001:20471: bla ma lhan cig par rigs lnga'i rang bzhin can
NK024(ya)001:20472: gyi bum pa'i chus dbang bskur bas sgo gsum gyi
NK024(ya)001:20473: sgrib gnyis bag chags dang bcas pa byang zhing dag
NK024(ya)001:20475: rin chen mdzes pa'i bum pa 'dis //
NK024(ya)001:20476: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi chus //
NK024(ya)001:20477: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK024(ya)001:20478: gti mug sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:20479: bud+d+ha k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK024(ya)001:20482: de bzhin du shar gyi bum pa dpral bar bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:20483: rin chen gnyis med skal ldan zhe sdang h+aum badz+ra k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20485: lho'i bum pa rna ltag g.yas su bzhag la //
NK024(ya)001:20486: rin chen gnyis med skal ldan nga rgyal t+r+aam rat+na k+aa la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa t+r+aam /
NK024(ya)001:20488: nub kyi bum pa ltag par bzhag ste /
NK024(ya)001:20489: rin chen gnyis med skal ldan 'dod chags h+r+aihpad+ma k+aa
NK024(ya)001:20490: la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih blug btung khrus bya'o
NK024(ya)001:20491: // byang gi bum pa rna ltag g.yon du bzhag la /
NK024(ya)001:20492: rin chen gnyis med skal ldan phrag dog +aahkarma k+aa
NK024(ya)001:20493: la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah blug btung khrus bya'o
NK024(ya)001:20496: lha dbang gi sku rnams rim pas thogs te /
NK024(ya)001:20498: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:20499: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje sku //
NK024(ya)001:20500: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK024(ya)001:20501: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20504: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa //
NK024(ya)001:20505: me long ye shes bdud 'dul de yi dbang mchog a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20506: rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK024(ya)001:20507: mnyam nyid mchog sbyin de yi a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20508: 'dod chags rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK024(ya)001:20509: kun rtog ting 'dzin chen po'i de yi a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20510: don yod rdo rje bskyod pa'i rlung //
NK024(ya)001:20511: bya grub skyabs sbyin de yi a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20512: me long ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK024(ya)001:20513: sems ma rdo rje'i phyag rgya ste //
NK024(ya)001:20514: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga can //
NK024(ya)001:20516: mnyam nyid ye shes rin chen sems ma'i rin chen ser po zur brgyad can //
NK024(ya)001:20518: kun rtog chos kyi pad dkar 'dam ma bcu drug can de yi a b+hi h+aum /
NK024(ya)001:20519: bya grub las kyi las kyi sna tshogs rdo rje can //
NK024(ya)001:20521: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK024(ya)001:20522: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa kun //
NK024(ya)001:20523: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang /
NK024(ya)001:20525: rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20526: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK024(ya)001:20527: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20529: rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK024(ya)001:20530: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:20531: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK024(ya)001:20533: rdo rje legs pa sems dpa'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20534: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //
NK024(ya)001:20535: rab dgyes rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20536: de yi a b+hi h+aum rdo rje rin chen rdo rje'i don //
NK024(ya)001:20537: rdo rje nam mkha'i nor bu che //
NK024(ya)001:20538: nam mkha'i snying po rdo rje phyug /
NK024(ya)001:20540: rdo rje gzi brjid cher 'bar ba //
NK024(ya)001:20541: rdo rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i 'od //
NK024(ya)001:20542: rdo rje 'od zer gzi brjid che //
NK024(ya)001:20544: sems can don rab rdo rje dpal //
NK024(ya)001:20545: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rab dga' byed //
NK024(ya)001:20546: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK024(ya)001:20548: rdo rje bzhad pa bzhad pa che //
NK024(ya)001:20549: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK024(ya)001:20550: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje ston /
NK024(ya)001:20552: rdo rje chos rab de nyid ston //
NK024(ya)001:20553: rdo rje pad+ma rab dga' byed //'jig rten dbang rab rdo rje can //
NK024(ya)001:20555: rdo rje rnon po theg pa che //
NK024(ya)001:20556: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //'jam dpal rdo rje rab blo zab //
NK024(ya)001:20558: rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK024(ya)001:20559: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK024(ya)001:20560: rab bskor rdo rje las byung ba //
NK024(ya)001:20562: rdo rje bsrung ba rang rig mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20563: rdo rje zlos pa rab sgrub sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:20564: mi gsung rdo rje mchog grub pa //
NK024(ya)001:20566: rdo rje las rab rdo rje'i dka'//
NK024(ya)001:20567: las kyi rdo rje kun rab sgrol /
NK024(ya)001:20568: rdo rje nges pa rgya che ba /
NK024(ya)001:20570: rdo rje bsrung ba brtan pa che //
NK024(ya)001:20571: rdo rje go cha sra ba che //
NK024(ya)001:20572: brtson 'grus mchog ni thub par dka'//
NK024(ya)001:20574: rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK024(ya)001:20575: rdo rje mche ba 'jigs pa che //
NK024(ya)001:20576: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi bzad pa /
NK024(ya)001:20578: rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab 'dud nyid /
NK024(ya)001:20579: rdo rje 'ching ba rab sgrol byed //
NK024(ya)001:20580: rdo rje khu tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20582: shar phyogs sgo skyong byams pa ma //
NK024(ya)001:20583: sku mdog dkar la 'od zer 'phro //'gugs byed phyag na lcags kyu bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:20585: lho sgo'i sgo skyong snying rje ma //
NK024(ya)001:20586: sku mdog ser mo 'od chings bya phyag na zhags pa bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:20588: nub kyi sgo skyong dga' ba ma //
NK024(ya)001:20589: sku mdog dmar la sdom byed phyag na lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:20591: byang gi sgo skyong btang snyoms ma //
NK024(ya)001:20592: sku mdog ljang la myos byed phyag na dril bu bsnams //
NK024(ya)001:20594: shar gyi lha mo l+aa s+ya ma /
NK024(ya)001:20595: dkar mo sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin //
NK024(ya)001:20596: phyag gnyis khu tshur 'gying ba'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:20598: lho yi lha mo m+aa le ma //
NK024(ya)001:20599: ser mo tshul khrims phyag gnyis me tog phreng ba 'dzin /
NK024(ya)001:20601: nub kyi lha mo g+ai ti ma //
NK024(ya)001:20602: dmar mo bzod pa'i phyag gnyis pi wang bsgyur ba'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:20604: byang gi lha mo n+air+t+ya ma //
NK024(ya)001:20605: ljang gu brtson 'grus phyag gnyis gar stabs bsgyur ba'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:20607: shar lho lha mo d+h+au pe ma //
NK024(ya)001:20608: dkar mo shes rab phyag na spos kyi dud sprin 'phro /
NK024(ya)001:20610: lho nub lha mo push+pe ma /
NK024(ya)001:20611: ser mo bsam gtan phyag na me tog phung po mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:20613: nub byang lha mo +aa lo ke //
NK024(ya)001:20614: dmar mo smon lam phyag na snang ba'i 'od zer 'bar //
NK024(ya)001:20616: byang shar lha mo gan+d+he ma //
NK024(ya)001:20617: ljang gu thabs kyi phyag na dri yi bsil zer dang //
NK024(ya)001:20619: bskal pa bzang po'i rgyal sras mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20620: byams pa la sogs bcu drug po //
NK024(ya)001:20621: rab dga' la sogs mnga' mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:20622: de yi a b+hi zhes pas lha dbang rdzogs par bskur nas /
NK024(ya)001:20623: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyi shu pa rdzas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:20625: rdzas dbang rim pa bzhin thogs nas /
NK024(ya)001:20626: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi rtser khang brtsegs
NK024(ya)001:20627: 'bar ba'i dbus su dpal kun rig rnam par snang
NK024(ya)001:20628: mdzad kyis byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub
NK024(ya)001:20629: pa la phyag rgya chen po lnga'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:20630: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par gyur to
NK024(ya)001:20631: // de bzhin du phyag rgya lnga'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:20632: sku lnga ye shes lnga mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam
NK024(ya)001:20634: byang chub mchog dang sa gnon dang //
NK024(ya)001:20635: mchog sbyin mnyam gzhag skyabs sbyin te //
NK024(ya)001:20636: rgyal ba rigs lnga'i sku yi rgya //
NK024(ya)001:20637: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:20638: rgyal po mchog gi phyag rgya che //
NK024(ya)001:20639: phyag rgya'i dbang mchog mi 'da' ba //
NK024(ya)001:20640: ye shes nga dang rigs lnga'i dbang //
NK024(ya)001:20641: dbang gi bkra shis dang po'o //
NK024(ya)001:20642: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad
NK024(ya)001:20643: kyis 'khor rnams la snying po sngags kyi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:20644: bas rtogs pa'i ye shes phun sum tshogs de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:20645: du sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes kyi byin rlabs
NK024(ya)001:20646: snying po sngags kyi dbang bskur bas rtogs pa'i ye
NK024(ya)001:20647: shes phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang thugs kyi sa bon
NK024(ya)001:20648: yig 'bru mchog / sngags kyi byin rlabs bsam mi khyab //
NK024(ya)001:20649: ye shes thugs kyi sa bon mchog /'bras bu sngags kyi bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:20650: snying po rigs lnga sangs rgyas kun gyi mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20651: gsung mchog sngags kyi phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:20652: byin rlabs chen po bla na med pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:20653: sngags mchog dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20654: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser
NK024(ya)001:20655: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams
NK024(ya)001:20656: la gser gyi thur ma'i dbang bskur bas ma rig
NK024(ya)001:20657: pa'i ling tog byang nas she sa rab kyi mig
NK024(ya)001:20658: gsal de bzhin du gser gyi thur ma'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:20659: bas ma rig pa'i ling tog byang nas shes rab
NK024(ya)001:20660: kyi mig gsal ba'i dbang gser gyi thur ma thogs
NK024(ya)001:20661: nas ni // mig mkhan rgyal pos dbang bskur bzhin //
NK024(ya)001:20662: bu khyod ma rig mi shes pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20663: rab rib rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK024(ya)001:20665: rin chen gser gyi thur ma yis //'bar ba'i ye shes bsal phye nas //
NK024(ya)001:20666: nges par legs pa'i dgongs pa 'grub //
NK024(ya)001:20667: shes rab ye shes spyan ldan pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20668: dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20669: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20670: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la me long
NK024(ya)001:20671: gi dbang bskur bas chos thams cad snang la rang
NK024(ya)001:20672: bzhin med par rtogs de bzhin du me long gi
NK024(ya)001:20673: dbang bskur bas chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel
NK024(ya)001:20674: sgyu ma tsam rtogs pa'i dbang chos sku gzugs brnyan
NK024(ya)001:20675: lta bu ste // rten 'brel mthu las snang ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20676: brjod med rang bzhin dag pa'i don //
NK024(ya)001:20677: chos nyid sgyu mar gsal bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:20678: snang sems dri ma sel ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:20679: mi mngon dbang po gsal ba ltar //
NK024(ya)001:20680: ye shes gsal ba'i me long gi //
NK024(ya)001:20681: dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20682: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20683: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:20684: bzhi'i dbang bskur bas 'gro don thogs pa med par
NK024(ya)001:20685: de bzhin du 'khor lo bzhi'i dbang bskur bas rdzu
NK024(ya)001:20686: 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan zhing khams gsum du
NK024(ya)001:20687: 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i 'og tu gser gyi
NK024(ya)001:20688: 'khor lo dag / brjod pa med pa'i 'bru bkod nas //
NK024(ya)001:20689: gzhan gyi don la phan pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20690: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bskor bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:20691: nyon mongs ma lus gzhom pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20692: legs pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang //'bras bu kun tu 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20693: dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20694: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20695: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la dung gi
NK024(ya)001:20696: dbang bskur bas tshangs pa'i dbyangs sgrog pa'i dbang thob
NK024(ya)001:20697: de bzhin du dung gi dbang bskur bas tshangs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:20698: dbyangs lta bu sgrog pa'i dbang chos dung rgyal bas
NK024(ya)001:20699: bus nas ni //'jig rten sems can skal ldan la
NK024(ya)001:20700: // rnam gsal sdig byang chos thob pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20701: tshangs pa'i sgra skad sgrog par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20702: skyob pa'i mgon po tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK024(ya)001:20703: tshangs pa'i gsung mchog 'gro la sgrog /'jig rten gsum du rgyas pa'i sgra //
NK024(ya)001:20704: dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20705: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad
NK024(ya)001:20706: kyis 'khor rnams la me tog phreng ba'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:20707: bas tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs par gyur to //
NK024(ya)001:20708: de bzhin du me tog phreng ba'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:20709: tshul khrims yongs su rdzogs te ngan song las thar
NK024(ya)001:20710: ba'i dbang sdug cing mdzes pa'i me tog rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:20711: dgos pa'i don rnams myur bar 'byin //
NK024(ya)001:20712: thams cad kun gyi yid du 'ong //'byor pa'i longs
NK024(ya)001:20713: spyod rgyan du shog kha dog dbyibs legs rin chen
NK024(ya)001:20714: me tog 'di // nam mkha' gang zhing sa gzhi khyab byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20715: mchod pa'i sprin gyi phung po char 'bebs pa //
NK024(ya)001:20716: mdzes pa'i dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20717: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi rtser
NK024(ya)001:20718: 'khor rnams la rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas thugs rdo
NK024(ya)001:20719: rje rigs kyi dbang thob par de bzhin du rdo
NK024(ya)001:20720: rje'i dbang bskur bas thugs ye shes rdo rje'i dbang
