NK024(ya)001:20722: sku yi phyag rgyar rtag brtan pa //
NK024(ya)001:20723: ye shes rdo rje lta bu ste //
NK024(ya)001:20724: rdo rje thugs kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK024(ya)001:20725: me long ye shes thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20726: rdo rje'i rigs mchog rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK024(ya)001:20727: dkar la dag pas shar phyogs sangs rgyas zhing //
NK024(ya)001:20728: bde ba chen po kun la khyab pa'i bdag /'di ni dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20729: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20730: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la rin po
NK024(ya)001:20731: che'i dbang bskur bas yon tan rin po che'i mdzod
NK024(ya)001:20732: thob de bzhin du rin po che'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:20733: yon tan rin po che'i dbang sku yi phyag rgyar
NK024(ya)001:20734: 'gro ba kun gyi re ba skong //
NK024(ya)001:20735: yon tan rin chen rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:20736: mnyam nyid ye shes rin chen rigs mchog yon tan
NK024(ya)001:20737: ser la dag pa lho phyogs bde ba chen po
NK024(ya)001:20738: kun la 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o
NK024(ya)001:20739: // a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:20740: 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la pad+ma'i
NK024(ya)001:20741: dbang bskur bas gsung pad+ma rigs kyi dbang thob de
NK024(ya)001:20742: bzhin du pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas 'gro don byed pa
NK024(ya)001:20743: la nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i dbang sku
NK024(ya)001:20744: yi phyag rgya pad+ma dbang gi rang bzhin te //
NK024(ya)001:20745: gsung gi rang bzhin 'byung ba'i mdzod //
NK024(ya)001:20746: kun rtog ye shes pad+ma rigs mchog chos kyi dmar
NK024(ya)001:20747: la dag pa phun tshogs bde ba chen po kun
NK024(ya)001:20748: la 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20749: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20750: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la sna tshogs
NK024(ya)001:20751: rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas phrin las bzhi'i dbang de
NK024(ya)001:20752: bzhin du rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas phrin las
NK024(ya)001:20753: bzhi'i dbang / sku yi phyag rgya las rnams ma lus rdzogs pa'i mchog /
NK024(ya)001:20754: phrin las don yod grub pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:20755: bya grub ye shes bya ba'i rigs mchog las kyi
NK024(ya)001:20756: ljang gu dag pas phun tshogs bde ba chen pos
NK024(ya)001:20757: kun la 'di ni dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig
NK024(ya)001:20758: pa'o // a b+hi gtso bu ma thogs la /
NK024(ya)001:20759: sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das rnam par
NK024(ya)001:20760: snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la bdud rtsi'i bum pas
NK024(ya)001:20761: dbang bskur bas rnam par rtog pa sel de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:20762: du thugs bdud rtsi'i bum pas dbang bskur bas las
NK024(ya)001:20763: dang nyon mongs pa'i nad byang ba'i dbang spros med
NK024(ya)001:20765: bum pa bzang po yum gyi gter //
NK024(ya)001:20766: phan byed sman pa'i mchog yin te //'gro ba'i nad rnams sel bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:20767: bum pa zlum po spros med chos kyi dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:20768: thugs rje chen pos phan mdzad yum gyi tshul //'khor ba gnas skyong dri ma dag mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:20769: sgrib sel dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20770: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20771: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la seng ge'i
NK024(ya)001:20772: dbang bskur bas log phyogs zil gyis gnon par de
NK024(ya)001:20773: bzhin du seng ges dbang bskur bas gsung rab rgya
NK024(ya)001:20774: mtsho'i sgras thams cad zil gyis gnon nas stong spyi
NK024(ya)001:20775: phud kyi sems can thams cad skad cig la sangs
NK024(ya)001:20776: rgya bar byed pa bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang
NK024(ya)001:20777: po'i dbang gzugs bzang sems can kun gyi gtso bo
NK024(ya)001:20778: ste // zil gnon sgra 'byin sder chags skrag par byed //
NK024(ya)001:20779: phyogs mthun kun bskyed seng ge dpa' dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:20780: thams cad zil gnon dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20781: seng ge nga ro sgra chen thogs med pa //'jigs med 'joms pa'i sgra rnams bsgrags nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:20782: bdud dpung ma lus zil gyis gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20783: che mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20784: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20785: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la nyi mas
NK024(ya)001:20786: dbang bskur bas ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20787: dbang de bzhin du nyi mas dbang bskur bas skye
NK024(ya)001:20788: 'gro thams cad kyi rgyud la ye shes 'char ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20789: dbang nyi ma mun sel shes rab sgron //
NK024(ya)001:20790: kun la gsal ba'i rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20791: thams cad kun gyi dpal du shar //
NK024(ya)001:20792: ma rig gsal ba'i sgron mer shog /
NK024(ya)001:20793: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcur khyab par brdal //
NK024(ya)001:20794: thugs rje mchog gyur sman pa mtha' dag gsal //
NK024(ya)001:20795: rang bzhin 'od gsal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:20796: shes rab dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20797: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20798: rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la zla ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20799: dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba sel ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20800: dbang de bzhin du zla ba'i dbang bskur bas sems
NK024(ya)001:20801: can gyi nyon mongs pa'i gdung ba thams cad sel
NK024(ya)001:20802: ba'i dbang thams cad kun gsal chu shel lta bu
NK024(ya)001:20803: ste / dgos pa'i don 'byin dkar la dag pa'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:20804: tshad med thabs mchog zla ba rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20805: ma rig mun sel ye shes sgron mer shog /
NK024(ya)001:20806: dkar la dag pa'i zla ba dri ma med //
NK024(ya)001:20807: thabs kyi mtshan nyid skyon gyis ma gos te //
NK024(ya)001:20808: yongs su dag pas mun pa sel ba'i sman //
NK024(ya)001:20809: thabs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bco lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20810: a b+hi sngon gyi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po tshul ji lta bu dang ldan zhe na /
NK024(ya)001:20811: rgyal po rgyal rigs spyi bo nas dbang bskur ba gso sbyong gi nyi mar khrus byas te /
NK024(ya)001:20812: pho brang gi steng 'khor gyi dbus na gnas pa'i
NK024(ya)001:20813: tshe shar phyogs kyi nam mkha' la 'khor lo rtsibs
NK024(ya)001:20814: stong yod pa'i lte ba mu khyud gser las grub
NK024(ya)001:20815: pa / bzo bos ma byas par rang byung ba rgyal po'i lag pa g.yas su babs so //
NK024(ya)001:20816: de'i tshe rgyal pos bsams pa /
NK024(ya)001:20817: rtags 'di dang sbyar na bdag ni 'khor los sgyur
NK024(ya)001:20818: ba'i rgyal po yin nges so snyam nas 'khor lo
NK024(ya)001:20819: bskor zhing nam mkha' la 'gro zhing dpung gi tshogs
NK024(ya)001:20821: gling bzhi'i rgyal po thams cad kyis mdun bsu zhing gnas pa'i tshe /
NK024(ya)001:20822: thams cad dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam la 'god
NK024(ya)001:20823: pa'i dbang dang ldan de bzhin du 'khor lo rin
NK024(ya)001:20824: po che'i dbang bskur bas 'jig rten gyi 'gro ba
NK024(ya)001:20825: ma lus pa smin grol lam la 'god pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:20826: dus gsum rgyal bas bskor ba'i 'khor lo 'di //
NK024(ya)001:20827: mi khom rgyun gcod rgyu dang 'bras bu ston //'khor lo sgyur ba'i dbang phyug rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20828: bla ma 'khor lo dam pa bskor gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:20829: stong nyid ye shes gsal ba'i 'khor lo la //
NK024(ya)001:20830: chos nyid dbyings las phrin las cir yang ston //
NK024(ya)001:20831: sems can kha lo gyen du sgyur mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:20832: chos 'khor dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20833: a b+hi 'khor los sgyur ba'i glang po ni kha
NK024(ya)001:20834: dog dkar po yan lag bdun dang ldan pa lha
NK024(ya)001:20835: ma yin dang g.yul 'gyed par g.yul las rgyal ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20836: mthu dang ldan pa'i dbang bskur bas rgol ba thams
NK024(ya)001:20837: cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang theg pa'i don dam
NK024(ya)001:20839: yan lag bdun mdzes ku mu ta yi mdog /
NK024(ya)001:20840: gdul dka' stobs chen glang po rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20841: khyu mchog rlabs chen stobs lnga rdzogs par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20842: stobs mchog pha rol gnon pa'i mthu mnga' ba //
NK024(ya)001:20843: gdug pa'i stobs ldan gzhan gyis mi rdzi ba //
NK024(ya)001:20844: pha rol rdzu 'phrul mthu stobs gnon mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20845: mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20846: a b+hi 'khor los sgyur ba'i rta mchog rin chen ni /
NK024(ya)001:20847: sngon po rngog ma dmar po gling bzhi yu tsam
NK024(ya)001:20848: gyis bskor nas rdzu 'phrul dang ldan zhing shes bya
NK024(ya)001:20849: la thogs pa med pa'i dbang 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:20851: brtson 'grus myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul shugs kyis 'gro //
NK024(ya)001:20852: cang shes sprin gyi shugs 'chang rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20853: mi gnas ye shes yid bzhin spyod par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20854: rdzu 'phrul thogs med kun tu myur ba'i shugs //
NK024(ya)001:20855: kun tu bgrod pa'i don la myur ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:20856: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs kun tu ston mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20857: thogs med dbang gi bkra shis bco brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20858: a b+hi 'khor los sgyur ba'i nor bu rin po
NK024(ya)001:20859: che bee d+aur+ya'i rang bzhin zur brgyad pa mun pa
NK024(ya)001:20862: dpag tshad du 'od kyis khyab pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:20863: nyon mongs pa'i mun pa bsal te lhag mthong gi
NK024(ya)001:20864: ye shes rtogs pa'i dbang dkon mchog gsum gyi yon
NK024(ya)001:20865: tan rin po che //'khor ba'i mun sel bde ba'i
NK024(ya)001:20866: snying po 'byung // dgos pa mchod sbyin nor bdun phun sum tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:20867: yid bzhin nor bu rin chen spyod par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20868: dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i nor bu rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20869: thams cad kun gyi yid dang mthun pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:20870: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:20871: yid bzhin dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20872: a b+hi blon po rin po che ni mkhas pa
NK024(ya)001:20873: gsal ba yid gzhungs pa dpag tshad tshun chad kyi
NK024(ya)001:20874: gter mthong ba rgyal po'i dgos pa bsgrub pa /
NK024(ya)001:20875: thams cad sgrub pa de'i dbang bskur bas lha'i mig
NK024(ya)001:20876: rnam par dag pa thob cing 'phags pa'i nor bdun
NK024(ya)001:20877: dang ldan pa'i gang la ci dgos dpag bsam shing
NK024(ya)001:20878: lta bu //'gro la snying po tshogs gnyis rdzogs par
NK024(ya)001:20879: smon // dbang phyug blon po'i nor bu rin po
NK024(ya)001:20880: che //'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal thabs thob par shog
NK024(ya)001:20881: smon // / mdzangs pa'i 'phrul 'byin blon po rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20882: legs nyes kun phyed gcod pa'i don la mkhas //'gal ba cham 'bebs mdzangs pa'i 'phrul bag can //
NK024(ya)001:20883: blon po dbang gi bkra shis nyi shu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20884: a b+hi btsun mo rin po che ni rgyal rigs
NK024(ya)001:20885: su skye ba gzugs mdzes pa lta na sdug pa
NK024(ya)001:20887: ba spu'i khung nas tsan+dana gyi dri 'byung ba lus la reg pa tsam gyis bde ba /
NK024(ya)001:20888: de'i dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin zhi ba'i chos
NK024(ya)001:20889: la dbang 'byor te 'jig rten las 'das pa'i spyod
NK024(ya)001:20890: yul yongs su dag pa'i pha rol phyin bcu sems
NK024(ya)001:20892: shes rab gzung 'dzin btsun mo rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20893: bsdu ba rnam bzhi tshad med bzhi po yis //
NK024(ya)001:20894: tshe dang longs spyod dbang rnams sbyor par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20895: shes rab dbyings las grub pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:20896: dgos pa'i don 'grub btsun mo ste //
NK024(ya)001:20897: smon lam mthu stobs 'brel ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:20898: dbang gi bkra shis nyer gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20899: a b+hi dmag dpon rin po che ni mkhas pa
NK024(ya)001:20900: dpa' ba pha rol gyis dpung 'joms pa'i dgra 'thab
NK024(ya)001:20901: kyi sbyor ba la mkhas pa /
NK024(ya)001:20902: pha rol 'joms pa'i dbang bskur bas 'jig tshogs kyi lta ba'i ri bo nyi shu 'joms pa'o /
NK024(ya)001:20903: phan pa'i go bgos gnod pa'i dpung 'joms shing //'jigs pa'i skyabs byed 'gro la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK024(ya)001:20904: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i dmag dpon 'di //
NK024(ya)001:20905: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul dpung gis bsrung bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:20906: drag shul dregs pas pha rol 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:20907: nyon mongs mi shes g.yul ngo sel byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:20908: rnam par rtog pa'i tshogs kyis mi tshugs pa'i //'dul thabs dbang gi bkra shis nyer gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20909: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20910: rnam par snang mdzad kyi 'khor rnams la ye shes
NK024(ya)001:20911: kyi ral gri'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs ba'i d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:20912: ba gcod pa'i dbang dam pa thob de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:20913: ral gri'i dbang bskur bas sdug bsngal 'khrul ba'i d+r+wa
NK024(ya)001:20914: ba gcod pa'i dbang sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba kun bcad
NK024(ya)001:20915: de // mi shes d+r+wa ba gcod tshul du //
NK024(ya)001:20916: rnon pos bag chags gcod pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:20917: thams cad kun las rgyal bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:20918: sgrib gnyis d+r+wa ba rtol byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:20919: ye shes rno ba thogs pa med //
NK024(ya)001:20920: mi shes bag chags gcod byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20921: dbang gi bkra shis nyer gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20922: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20923: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la mda' gzhu'i
NK024(ya)001:20924: dbang bskur bas thabs shes 'brel ba'i dbang de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:20925: du mda' gzhu'i dbang bskur bas thabs shes zung 'jug
NK024(ya)001:20926: rnam thar rgya mtsho'i dbang rgol ba'i tshogs 'joms myur
NK024(ya)001:20928: thabs kyis 'dul la nyes pas ma gos te //
NK024(ya)001:20929: dngos po kun 'joms pha rol 'bigs byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:20930: thabs kyis 'dul ba'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20931: thabs shes dbyer med rang bzhin ro gcig pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20932: thugs rje myur mgyogs thabs tshogs 'gro la 'byung //
NK024(ya)001:20933: yang rab rtsal mchog blo gros rnam par gnon //
NK024(ya)001:20934: thabs shes dbang gi bkra shis nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20935: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20936: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la gnam ral
NK024(ya)001:20937: gri dbang bskur bas bar chad kyi bdud bcom de
NK024(ya)001:20938: bzhin du gnam ral gyi dbang bskur bas bdud dpung
NK024(ya)001:20939: mtha' dag 'joms pa'i dbang thob par stobs ldan dbang
NK024(ya)001:20940: phyug mthu stobs che ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:20941: bdud dpung phas kyi bdo ba kun btul nas //
NK024(ya)001:20942: che btsan drag po kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:20943: thams cad mthu stobs dag gi dbang byed shog /
NK024(ya)001:20944: rin chen rgyan mdzes gnam ral rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20945: log pa'i phyogs kun tshar gcod zil gyis gnon //
NK024(ya)001:20946: thabs la mkhas pa'i sde dpung chen po ste //
NK024(ya)001:20947: rgyal thabs dbang gi bkra shis nyer lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20948: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20949: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la shan nye
NK024(ya)001:20950: ba'i rin po che'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i sgrib
NK024(ya)001:20951: ba gcod pa'i dbang de bzhin du nye ba'i rin
NK024(ya)001:20952: po che'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i sgrib pa gcod
NK024(ya)001:20953: pa'i dbang nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa
NK024(ya)001:20954: dang // dngos po mtshan ma ma lus gzhom pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:20955: mi shes rnam par rtog pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:20956: gdugs pa 'joms pa'i dbang rnams thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20957: rin chen mdzes pa'i shan mchog rin po che //
NK024(ya)001:20958: rnam gcod rnam pas pha rol nyes pa gcod //
NK024(ya)001:20959: ye shes rno mchog kun gyi yid du 'ong //
NK024(ya)001:20960: nyes gcod dbang gi bkra shis nyer drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20961: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20962: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la zhwa nye
NK024(ya)001:20963: ba'i rin po che'i dbang bskur bas bgegs dang log
NK024(ya)001:20964: 'dren med pa'i tshe dbang de bzhin du zhwa nye
NK024(ya)001:20965: ba'i rin po che'i dbang bskur bas bgegs dang bar
NK024(ya)001:20966: chad gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa'i dbang tsha grang
NK024(ya)001:20968: gdung ba bsil ba'i nyer mkho ste //'bras bu thar
NK024(ya)001:20969: pa thob bya'i phyir //'jigs pa bzhi yi skyabs su
NK024(ya)001:20970: shog / rin chen rgyan mchog dbu zhwa rin po
NK024(ya)001:20971: che //'jigs pa bzhi skyob log pa'i skyon la grol
NK024(ya)001:20972: shog / // mi 'gyur g.yung drung tshe yi dbang thob pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:20973: g.yung drung dbang gi bkra shis nyer bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20974: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20975: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la tshangs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:20976: khab skud kyi dbang bskur bas legs pa'i yon tan
NK024(ya)001:20977: 'grub pa'i de bzhin du nye ba'i rin po che
NK024(ya)001:20978: khab skud kyi dbang bskur bas legs pa'i yon tan
NK024(ya)001:20979: mtha' dag rub pa'i dbang tshangs pa'i khab skud nye
NK024(ya)001:20981: legs pa'i yon tan tshang bar rdzogs pa'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:20982: nyes pa kun grol legs pa'i rang bzhin can //
NK024(ya)001:20983: phun sum tshogs pa'i dpal gyis 'byor par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20984: tshangs pa'i khab skud legs pa'i dgos pa grub //
NK024(ya)001:20985: gang la yid dang 'tshams pa drub byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:20986: don gyis thugs rje chen pos mtshams sbyor ba'i //'tshem skud dbang gi bkra shis nyer brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20987: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:20988: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la na bza'
NK024(ya)001:20989: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas grang ba'i sdug bsngal
NK024(ya)001:20990: bas skyob pa'i de bzhin du gos rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:20991: dbang bskur bas 'di phyir grang ba'i nyon mongs pa
NK024(ya)001:20992: zhi ba'i dbang nyes pa kun skyob na bza' rin
NK024(ya)001:20993: po che // bde ba yid bzhin zad pa med pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:20994: yon tan tshang ba'i na bza' dam pa 'di //'di dang pha rol gnyis su gyon par shog /
NK024(ya)001:20995: rin chen na bza' ji ltar lta na sdug /
NK024(ya)001:20996: che chung 'tshams la dro la dbyibs legs mdzes //
NK024(ya)001:20997: yon tan bla med 'phags pa'i sku dang mtshungs //
NK024(ya)001:20998: chos rtags dbang gi bkra shis nyer dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:20999: a b+hi sngon ri rib kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:21000: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la phyags nye
NK024(ya)001:21001: ba'i rin po che'i dbang bskur ba'i thugs rjes 'gro
NK024(ya)001:21002: ba'i phyags pa'i dbang de bzhin du phyags nye ba'i
NK024(ya)001:21003: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas thugs rjes 'gro la
NK024(ya)001:21004: phyags pa'i dbang rin chen phyags kyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21005: // kun la snyoms pa'i thugs rje yis //
NK024(ya)001:21006: sems can don la thogs med de //'gro ba 'dren pa'i dpal du shog /
NK024(ya)001:21007: rin chen mdzes pa'i phyags mchog dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21008: gar yang thogs med phyogs bcur bgrod nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:21009: don rnams ma lus rdzogs par byed pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21010: yongs grub dbang gi bkra shis sum cu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21011: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:21012: rnam par snang mdzad kyis krish+na s+aa ra'i lpags pa
NK024(ya)001:21013: rin po che'i dbang bskur bas snying rjes sems can
NK024(ya)001:21014: 'dren pa'i dbang de bzhin du lpags pa rin po
NK024(ya)001:21015: che'i dbang bskur bas thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don rgya
NK024(ya)001:21016: chen po grub pa'i dbang krish+na s+aa ra'i pags pa
NK024(ya)001:21017: mchog tu shis // sems can kun la snyoms pa'i snying rje can //
NK024(ya)001:21018: yon tan mtha' dag tshang ba'i byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:21019: snying rje'i 'gro don dgongs pa 'grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21020: snying rje tshad med sems can kun la dgongs //
NK024(ya)001:21021: nyam thag 'phongs pa mgon med rnams kyi skyabs //
NK024(ya)001:21022: sems can 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa'i //'gro don dbang gi bkra shis so gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21023: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis yungs kar bgegs
NK024(ya)001:21024: kyi gnyen por sbyin pa de bzhin du dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21025: bas bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cus mi tshugs shing
NK024(ya)001:21026: mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa'i yungs kar rdo rje'i
NK024(ya)001:21028: rtog bral mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje yi //
NK024(ya)001:21029: rtog pa'i bgegs rnams rab tu 'joms mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:21030: phyogs dus kun tu bgegs rnams zhi bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:21031: yungs kar rdo rjes bgegs tshogs 'joms //
NK024(ya)001:21032: bdud dpung 'dul byed thugs rje can //
NK024(ya)001:21033: dgra bgegs kun las rab rgyal ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:21034: dbang gi bkra shis so gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21035: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang
NK024(ya)001:21036: skyong gis zho phul bas gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21037: rdzas su byin gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du ting
NK024(ya)001:21038: nge 'dzin gyi gzi brjid dang ldan pa'i dbang ba
NK024(ya)001:21039: zho kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:21040: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs te //
NK024(ya)001:21041: yon tan kun gyi snying po gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21042: bkra shis des ni snying po thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21043: zho ni bcud ldan bkra shis rdzas kyi mchog /'dod pa'i don 'byung 'dod 'jo ba las byung //
NK024(ya)001:21044: nyon mongs 'phongs pa ngoms shing tshim byed pa //
NK024(ya)001:21045: bcud ldan dbang gi bkra shis so gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21046: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bra ze ko
NK024(ya)001:21047: da lis r+ts+wa durba phul bas rgyu chung ngu las
NK024(ya)001:21048: 'bras bu mang po 'byung ba'i byin gyis brlabs pa
NK024(ya)001:21049: bzhin du dge ba chung du las bsod nams phun
NK024(ya)001:21050: sum tshogs pa'i durbasa tshe ni 'phel bar byed pa
NK024(ya)001:21051: ste // rdo rje sems dpa' tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK024(ya)001:21052: skye shi gnyis kyi sdug bsngal rgyun chad de //'chi ba med pa tshe yi rig 'dzin shog /
NK024(ya)001:21053: durba r+ts+wa mchog bsod nams mang po 'phel //
NK024(ya)001:21054: bkra shis mdog legs 'bras bu yang dag rgyas //
NK024(ya)001:21055: yid la gang bsam 'phral du 'grub byed pa'i //'dod 'byung dbang gi bkra shis so bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21056: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mos
NK024(ya)001:21057: li khri phul bas dbang gi rang bzhin du byin
NK024(ya)001:21058: gyis brlabs pa de bzhin du thugs rje chen pos
NK024(ya)001:21059: sems can la rjes su 'dzin pa'i dbang li khri
NK024(ya)001:21060: dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin la //
NK024(ya)001:21061: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21062: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa //
NK024(ya)001:21063: rgyal ba'i bstan pa rab tu rgyas gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:21064: kha dog dmar po nub phyogs pad+ma'i rigs //
NK024(ya)001:21065: chags pa gnyis ldan bdag gzhan don gnyis 'grub //
NK024(ya)001:21066: gsung gi bdag nyid don ston bkra shis rdzas //
NK024(ya)001:21067: sku tshe dbang gi bkra shis so lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21068: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das kyi kun gzhi'i rnam
NK024(ya)001:21069: shes lan gsum gyi bar du gnas gyur pa me
NK024(ya)001:21070: long lta bu'i ye shes brnyes nas mngon par rdzogs
NK024(ya)001:21071: par sangs rgyas pa bzhin du me long gi dbang
NK024(ya)001:21072: bskur bas / bag la nyal gyi dri ma phra
NK024(ya)001:21073: mo yang rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK024(ya)001:21074: bcom nas mngon par rdzogs par 'tshang rgya ba'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:21075: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK024(ya)001:21076: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du bdag gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:21077: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21078: bkra shis des ni sgrib pa dag gyur cig /
NK024(ya)001:21079: me long gdong bstan bzhin gyi dri ma sel //
NK024(ya)001:21080: de bzhin nyon mongs shes bya'i sgrib pa dag /
NK024(ya)001:21081: gsal la rang bzhin med pa'i chos nyid la //
NK024(ya)001:21082: gsal ba'i dbang gi bkra shis so drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21083: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la brgya byin gyis
NK024(ya)001:21084: dung g.yas 'khyil phul bas gsung dbyangs drug cus chos
NK024(ya)001:21085: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba bzhin du tshangs pa'i sgra
NK024(ya)001:21086: skad phun sum tshogs pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK024(ya)001:21087: ba'i dbang dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21088: tshul // yon tan rgya mtsho'i bdag nyid mchog gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:21089: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21090: bkra shis de ni tshig la dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:21091: chos sgra chen po phyogs bcur grags pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:21092: rgyal ba'i gsung mchog dung gi 'bras bu ste //
NK024(ya)001:21093: ma lus 'gro ba kun gyi rgyud grol ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:21094: gsung mchog dbang gi bkra shis so bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21095: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la glang po che
NK024(ya)001:21096: sa skyong gis gi wang phul bas bdud bzhi las
NK024(ya)001:21097: grol bar byin gyis brlabs pa bzhin du nyon mongs
NK024(ya)001:21098: pa'i nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi las thar pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:21099: gi wang dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman /
NK024(ya)001:21100: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur nas //
NK024(ya)001:21101: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21102: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal zhi bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:21103: yon tan phun tshogs bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi sel //
NK024(ya)001:21104: sman mchog skye 'gro ma lus kun gyi gsos //
NK024(ya)001:21105: byin gyis brlabs pa bkra shis tshe yi rgyu //
NK024(ya)001:21106: nad med dbang gi bkra shis so brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21107: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la shing gi lha
NK024(ya)001:21108: mo 'od 'chang mas bilba'i 'bras bu phul bas 'bras
NK024(ya)001:21109: bu'i chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:21110: sku dang ye shes stobs dang mi 'jigs pa sogs
NK024(ya)001:21111: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang
NK024(ya)001:21112: bilba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //'jig rten
NK024(ya)001:21114: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur ba yi //
NK024(ya)001:21115: bkra shis des ni 'jig rten 'grub par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21116: yal ga lo 'dab me tog g.yu lor 'khyil //'bras
NK024(ya)001:21117: bu yid 'ong 'byor ba'i longs spyod ldan //'dod rgu
NK024(ya)001:21118: kun dang mthun par spyod pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21119: phun tshogs dbang gi bkra shis so dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21120: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la byang chub kyi shing drung du bdud kyis rgol ba'i dus su //
NK024(ya)001:21121: thugs dpal gyi be'ura bkra shis pa de bzhin du
NK024(ya)001:21122: thugs la dpal 'bar zhing bkra shis pa'i dbang dpa'
NK024(ya)001:21123: be'u thugs kyi bkra shis te //'dren pa rnams kyi
NK024(ya)001:21124: thugs lags pas // bla med thar lam drang ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:21125: thugs la dpa' be'u'i bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:21126: gzhan gyi mi thub che ba'i rtags dang ldan //
NK024(ya)001:21127: bdo ba'i phyogs rnams kun la khyad par 'phags //
NK024(ya)001:21128: thugs ka nyid la mngon par gsal bar ston //
NK024(ya)001:21129: dpa' be'u dbang gi bkra shis bzhi bcu pa'o /
NK024(ya)001:21130: a b+hi sdon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgol
NK024(ya)001:21131: ba'i dus su phyag zhabs 'khor lor bkra shis pa
NK024(ya)001:21132: de bzhin du 'khor lo'i dbang skur bas phyag zhabs
NK024(ya)001:21133: 'khor los mtshan pa'o 'khor lo'i bkra shis phyag zhabs
NK024(ya)001:21134: mthil // skyob ba'i sangs rgyas 'dren pa'i lha //
NK024(ya)001:21135: nyon mongs sems can dman pa'i gsos //
NK024(ya)001:21136: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i gzhan gyis bdo ba'i phyag zhabs
NK024(ya)001:21137: mthil la 'khor lo dbang gi bkra shis zhe gcig
NK024(ya)001:21138: pa'o // a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud
NK024(ya)001:21139: kyis rgol ba'i tshe ljags pad+mara bkra shis pa de
NK024(ya)001:21140: bzhin du pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas ljags pad+mas mtshan pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21141: dbang gsung mchog pad+ma chos kyis rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:21142: nyon mongs ma gos pad+ma'i thugs //
NK024(ya)001:21143: thams cad sgrol ba'i gsung lags te //
NK024(ya)001:21144: ljags mchog pad+ma'i gzhan gyis bdo ba'i ljags kyi mchog la pad+ma dbang gi bkra shis zhe gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21145: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgol
NK024(ya)001:21146: ba'i dus su sku rgyal mtshan du bkra shis pa
NK024(ya)001:21147: de bzhin du rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas sku
NK024(ya)001:21148: rgyal mtshan gyis mtshan pa'i mi nub rgyal mtshan brtan
NK024(ya)001:21149: pa'i sku // thams cad bdud kyi sde btul nas //
NK024(ya)001:21150: dpung 'joms sangs rgyas sku bstod do //
NK024(ya)001:21151: sku mchog sangs rgyas gzhan gyis bdo ba'i sku yi
NK024(ya)001:21152: mchog la rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis zhe gsum
NK024(ya)001:21153: pa'o // a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud
NK024(ya)001:21154: kyis rgol ba'i dus su mgul bum par bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:21155: pa de bzhin du bum pas dbang bskur bas mgul
NK024(ya)001:21156: bum pas mtshan pa'i bkra shis bum pa dam pa
NK024(ya)001:21157: pa'o // 'di // bcom ldan 'das kyi mgul lags te //
NK024(ya)001:21158: mgul mchog bkra shis 'di byin pas //
NK024(ya)001:21159: bum pa'i bkra shis thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21160: gzhan gyis bdo ba'i mgul gyi mchog la bum pa dbang gi bkra shis zhe bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21161: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgol
NK024(ya)001:21162: ba'i dus dbu la gdugs su bkra shis pa de
NK024(ya)001:21163: bzhin du gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas dbu gdugs kyi
NK024(ya)001:21164: mtshan pa'i dbang gdugs kyis tsha ba'i sdug bsngal kun
NK024(ya)001:21165: bsal te // nyon mongs ma lus kun las rgyal ba dang //
NK024(ya)001:21166: che ba'i yon tan ma lus rgyas pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:21167: log pa'i phyogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21168: gzhan gyis bdo ba'i dbu sku'i mchog la gdugs mchog dbang gi bkra shis zhe lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21169: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgol
NK024(ya)001:21170: ba'i dus su tshems dung gis bkra shis pa de
NK024(ya)001:21171: bzhin du dung gi dbang bskur bas tshems dung gis
NK024(ya)001:21172: mtshan ba'i dbang snyan pa'i sgra rnams phyogs bcur sgrog
NK024(ya)001:21173: pa dang // mu stegs log pa'i phyogs rnams skrag byed cing //
NK024(ya)001:21174: sems can kun gyi shes pa grol ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:21175: gsung mchog dung gi rgyal po'i bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:21176: gzhan gyis bdo ba'i gsung gi mchog la dung dkar dbang gi bkra shis zhe drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21177: a b+hi sngon bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyis rgol
NK024(ya)001:21178: ba'i dus su nywa bzhi nyar bkra shis pa de
NK024(ya)001:21179: bzhin du nya'i dbang bskur bas spyan dang nywa bzhir
NK024(ya)001:21180: nyas mtshan pa'i dbang phyag zhabs nywa shar byin brlabs
NK024(ya)001:21181: te //'jam mnyen yid 'ong kun gyi dpal //
NK024(ya)001:21182: nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:21183: nya ltar nywa bzhi'i gzhan gyis bdo ba'i nywa sha
NK024(ya)001:21184: bzhi las nywa bzhi dbang gi bkra shis zhe bdun
NK024(ya)001:21185: pa'o // a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser bcom
NK024(ya)001:21186: ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la
NK024(ya)001:21187: sna tshogs rdo rje'i dbang bskur bas phrin las bzhi
NK024(ya)001:21189: de bzhin du rgya gram gyi dbang bskur bas rig
NK024(ya)001:21190: sngags 'chang rnams kyis bsrung zhing phrin las bzhi thogs
NK024(ya)001:21191: pa med par grub pa'i dbang dogs dang som nyi
NK024(ya)001:21192: med pa la // gtsug tu rgya gram dbang bskur bas //
NK024(ya)001:21193: rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis kyang //
NK024(ya)001:21194: bsrung zhing rtag tu skyob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21195: phrin las thogs pa med pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21196: bya ba ye shes nan tan la //
NK024(ya)001:21197: dgos pa'i don rnams kun grub pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21198: dbang gi bkra shis zhe brgyad pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21199: a b+hi sngon zhes pa nas 'khor rnams bar 'di man 'gre /
NK024(ya)001:21200: la cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas rdul gyi bag
NK024(ya)001:21201: chags dang bral bar de bzhin du cod pan gyi
NK024(ya)001:21202: dbang bskur bas sbyor ba khams gsum na gnas kyang
NK024(ya)001:21203: sdug bsngal gyi bag chags dang bral ba'i dbang bkra
NK024(ya)001:21204: shis rtags ldan dar gyi cod pan 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21205: dbang gi rang bzhin dmar po 'bar ba ste //
NK024(ya)001:21206: dbang bskur spyi bor btags pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK024(ya)001:21207: dbang gi bkra shis dam pa thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21208: chos nyid dar dang 'dra ba mtshungs pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21209: don dam nyid du rtogs pa mngon byung ba //'di nyid legs pa'i don nyid mngon ston pa //
NK024(ya)001:21210: cod pan dbang gi bkra shis zhe dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21211: a b+hi sngon la mchod pa rnam lnga'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21212: bas rdo rje rgyal thebs kyi dbang thob de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:21213: du mchod rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas rdo rje rgyal
NK024(ya)001:21214: thebs las mtha' dag byed pa'i dbang thabs chen stobs
NK024(ya)001:21216: dmigs pa lnga dang ting 'dzin cha dbye ste //
NK024(ya)001:21217: rkyen dang 'tshams pa'i mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21218: thams cad phul bas stobs mchog bkra shis shog /
NK024(ya)001:21219: dri chab dri bsang me tog mdzes par bkram //
NK024(ya)001:21220: bdug spos yid tshim arga bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK024(ya)001:21221: lha bshos bro ldan 'od gsal mar me ste //
NK024(ya)001:21222: mchod rdzas dbang gi bkra shis lnga bcu pa'o /
NK024(ya)001:21223: a b+hi sngon la nyan pa'i dbang bskur bas gsang
NK024(ya)001:21224: sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang thob de
NK024(ya)001:21225: bzhin du ka pa li'i dbang bskur bas sngags rgyud
NK024(ya)001:21226: mtha' dag nyan pa'i dbang gdung ba sems bskyed dad
NK024(ya)001:21228: brtson 'grus shugs kyis thams cad thob pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:21229: dad pa'i shugs kyis kun tu nyan pa dang //
NK024(ya)001:21230: shes rab stobs kyis thams cad shes par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21231: shes rab rgya che nyan pa'i phyogs med byed //
NK024(ya)001:21232: bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' bzhin rjes su slob //
NK024(ya)001:21233: sems dang chos nyid gnyis su med pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21234: nyan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis nga gcig pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21235: a b+hi sngon la phyags shing gi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21236: theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i de bzhin du phyags
NK024(ya)001:21237: shing gi dbang bskur bas theg pa mtha' dag 'chad
NK024(ya)001:21238: pa'i dbang rin chen phyags shing 'khor ba'i kha lo
NK024(ya)001:21239: 'dren //'gro ba ma lus thar lam gnas su bskyel
NK024(ya)001:21240: / skyes mchog dug gsum sman pa'i rgyal po ste //
NK024(ya)001:21241: ma rig rmongs pa'i 'gro ba 'dren par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21242: gti mug rmongs pa'i shes pa bkrol nas kyang //
NK024(ya)001:21243: ma rig log par rtog pa grol mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:21244: thugs rje che bas shes pa rgyud 'grol ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:21245: chos 'chad dbang gi bkra shis nga gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21246: a b+hi sngon la glegs bam gyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21247: chos kyi sgo mo thams cad la mkhas pa'i de
NK024(ya)001:21248: bzhin du glegs bam gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi
NK024(ya)001:21249: sgo thams cad la mkhas pa'i dbang gsung rab glegs
NK024(ya)001:21250: bam chos kyi gzugs brnyan te //
NK024(ya)001:21251: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus bskyed mdzad pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21252: thams cad kun gyi dbang po sgrol ba'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:21253: chos rnams thams cad 'chad pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:21254: gsung rab chos 'chad gzhung mchog glegs bam ste //
NK024(ya)001:21255: chos nyid sgra sgrog yi ge phreng ba bskor //
NK024(ya)001:21256: blo la rab 'bring ji ltar 'tshams par ston //
NK024(ya)001:21257: glegs bam dbang gi bkra shis nga gsum pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21258: a b+hi sngon la rdo rje dril bu'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21259: bas ye shes lnga thob nas 'gro ba'i don byed
NK024(ya)001:21260: de bzhin du rdo rje dril bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21261: ye shes lnga rtogs nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21262: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med chos kyi sku //'du
NK024(ya)001:21263: 'bral med pa chos kyi dbang mchog ste //'bras bu
NK024(ya)001:21264: stobs ldan phyag rgya chen po nyid //
NK024(ya)001:21265: rdo rje dril bu 'chang ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:21266: rig pa ye shes rdo rje rtse lnga pa //
NK024(ya)001:21267: ye shes lnga yi rtags kyi ngo bo nyid //
NK024(ya)001:21268: g.yon pa'i dril bus gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrog /
NK024(ya)001:21269: thabs shes dbang gi bkra shis nga bzhi pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21270: a b+hi sngon ri rib kyi rtser bcom ldan 'das
NK024(ya)001:21271: rnam par snang mdzad kyis 'khor rnams la dbu rgyan
NK024(ya)001:21272: gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal srid chen po
NK024(ya)001:21273: la mnga' brnyes pa'i de bzhin du rin po che'i
NK024(ya)001:21274: dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal srid
NK024(ya)001:21275: 'dzin pa'i mya ngan 'das pa thugs rje'i dpal //
NK024(ya)001:21276: rin chen dbu rgyan chos kyi rgyal //
NK024(ya)001:21277: dbang dang byin rlabs sbyin pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:21278: chos kyi rgyal srid byed par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21279: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa'i dbu rgyan can //
NK024(ya)001:21280: legs par kun skyob chos kyi rgyal srid mthu //
NK024(ya)001:21281: phyag rgya rigs lnga mthu dang ldan byed pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21282: dbu rgyan dbang gi bkra shis nga lnga pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21283: a b+hi sngon la rin po che'i dpung rgyan gyi
NK024(ya)001:21284: dbang bskur bas mi 'jigs pa bzhi la mnga' brnyes
NK024(ya)001:21285: de bzhin du dpung rgyan gyi dbang bskur bas mi
NK024(ya)001:21286: 'jigs pa bzhi'i mi 'jigs phas kyi rgol ba thul
NK024(ya)001:21287: ba dang // mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog bkra shis thub pa yi //
NK024(ya)001:21288: mnga' mdzes phung po'i rtags kyi dam pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:21289: rgyan mchog dam pa ston pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK024(ya)001:21290: rin chen dpung rgyan sh+aa ri ra yi rgyan //
NK024(ya)001:21291: chos nyid don rtogs mthun par bstan pa'i phyir //
NK024(ya)001:21292: dgongs pa ting 'dzin legs par dbang bskur bas //
NK024(ya)001:21293: dpung rgyan dbang gi bkra shis nga drug pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21294: a b+hi sngon la do shal phreng ba'i dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21295: bas che ba'i yon tan rgyas shing mnga' brnyes de
NK024(ya)001:21296: bzhin du do shal gyi dbang bskur bas che ba'i
NK024(ya)001:21297: yon tan rgyas pa'i dbang rin chen phreng bas 'gro
NK024(ya)001:21299: phreng ba do shal 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK024(ya)001:21300: sku yi rgyan mchog yon tan sku la brgyan //
NK024(ya)001:21301: phreng thag bzang pos phrin las rgyun mi chad //
NK024(ya)001:21302: rtag tu yon tan zla ltar 'phel bar shog /
NK024(ya)001:21303: rin chen dbang po rgyas pa'i yon tan mchog /
NK024(ya)001:21304: sku tshe zhing khams mdzad pa bsam mi khyab //'gro ba'i dbul sel bde legs kun 'byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:21305: phreng ba dbang gi bkra shis nga bdun pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21306: a b+hi sngon la phyag gdub kyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21307: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i dbang thob de bzhin
NK024(ya)001:21308: du gdu bu'i dbang bskur bas tshul khrims rnam par
NK024(ya)001:21309: dag pa'i dbang sil snyan mdzes pa'i rgyan legs te
NK024(ya)001:21310: // yid du 'ong ba'i phyag gdub 'di //'bras bu
NK024(ya)001:21311: thob pa'i dbang mchog ste //'gro ba'i yid du 'ong
NK024(ya)001:21312: // bar shog / rin chen phyag gdub dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21313: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyis //
NK024(ya)001:21314: nges legs yon tan kun 'byung ba'i //
NK024(ya)001:21315: dbang gi bkra shis nga brgyad pa'o /
NK024(ya)001:21316: a b+hi sngon la zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21317: stobs bcu'i de bzhin du zhabs gdub kyi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21318: bas stobs bcu la mnga' brnyes pa'i dbang rgyan gyi
NK024(ya)001:21320: rdo rje zhabs kyi chas rab 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21321: khyod kyi zhabs la dbang bskur bas //'gro ba'i don la chags par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21322: rin chen zhabs gdub dam pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21323: legs par mdzes pa'i yon tan gyi //
NK024(ya)001:21324: nges par mdzad pa'i yon tan grub //
NK024(ya)001:21325: dbang gi bkra shis nga dgu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21326: a b+hi sngon la dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur bas
NK024(ya)001:21327: 'khor 'das kyi chos la dbang de dang rjes su
NK024(ya)001:21328: mthun par dar dpyangs kyi dbang bskur bas 'khor 'das
NK024(ya)001:21329: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i dbang dar dpyangs gyen
NK024(ya)001:21331: chos kyi sku dang gnyis su med //'phred dang mthur du 'phyang ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:21332: longs sprul sku gnyis thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21333: dmar po g.yas 'phur chos nyid mngon du rtogs //
NK024(ya)001:21334: sngon po 'phred 'phur phrin las rnam bzhi mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:21335: mthing kha dmar ljang klu gdug zil gnon pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21336: dar dpyangs dbang gi bkra shis drug cu pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21337: a b+hi sngon la rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur
NK024(ya)001:21338: bas rigs nges pa'i rdzas su gyur te rdo rje
NK024(ya)001:21339: 'chang gi gral thob de bzhin du rdo rje'i mig
NK024(ya)001:21340: gi dbang bskur bas nges pa'i sras kyi dbang rdo
NK024(ya)001:21341: rje ming mchog dam pa'i dpe las gras //
NK024(ya)001:21342: thugs las gsung du byung nas btags pa 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21343: dag cing tshul bzhin yid la bskur ba yis //
NK024(ya)001:21344: thams cad ston pa'i ming mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21345: ston pa'i thugs rjes nges pa'i ming btags pa //
NK024(ya)001:21346: thugs kyi ngang nas nges pa'i sras su mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:21347: rdo rje 'chang gi dbang thob mtshan gyi dbang //
NK024(ya)001:21348: mtshan mchog dbang gi bkra shis re gcig pa'o /
NK024(ya)001:21349: a b+hi sngon ri rab kyi rtser rigs bzhi'i sangs
NK024(ya)001:21350: rgyas kyis byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub
NK024(ya)001:21351: pa la mngon shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba dang 'bras
NK024(ya)001:21352: bu ri rab kyi rtser rin po che'i khang par
NK024(ya)001:21353: rnam par snang mdzad rdo rje dbyings su mngon par
NK024(ya)001:21354: byang chub pa lngas dbang bskur bas 'bras bu ri
NK024(ya)001:21355: rab kyi rtser mngon par byang chub par gyur cig
NK024(ya)001:21356: / mngon shes lnga ldan 'bras bu sa bcu 'das //
NK024(ya)001:21357: yi ge 'khor lo rdzogs pa che la gnas //'bras bu dam pa mngon par sangs rgyas te //
NK024(ya)001:21358: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK024(ya)001:21359: dbang mchog thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yis //
NK024(ya)001:21360: chos rnams thams cad ma lus thob pa ste //
NK024(ya)001:21361: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang mchog yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21362: phyi yi dbang gi bkra shis re gnyis pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21371: zhes yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa gnyis po rdzogs par bskur ro //
NK024(ya)001:21372: de nas bum pa'i dbang yang bskur 'thung khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:21373: zhes gsungs pas slar yang rten byed du bum dbang bskur zhing chu 'thung khrus bya'o //
NK024(ya)001:21374: des dbang dngos gzhi'i rim pa rnams legs par grub pa yin /
NK024(ya)001:21375: de nas rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer gnyis pa lam
NK024(ya)001:21376: 'khyer bzhi nang gses dang bcas pa'i dang po rtsa
NK024(ya)001:21377: ba'i sa bcad nyer gsum pa theg pa lam 'khyer
NK024(ya)001:21378: la 'jug sgo sogs drug yod pa 'og tu 'chad
NK024(ya)001:21381: bzhi pa dbang lam 'khyer rnams ni rtsa bar /
NK024(ya)001:21383: lha rigs lngas gtso byas rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs /
NK024(ya)001:21384: snying po bud+d+ha bee ro tsa na /
NK024(ya)001:21387: pad+ma a mi de wa h+r+aih karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi +aah zhes pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21388: dbang yo ga drug cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK024(ya)001:21389: zhes gsungs pa'i don lha lam 'khyer du bcom ldan
NK024(ya)001:21390: 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po sgrub
NK024(ya)001:21391: cing mchod pa ni lha lam 'khyer gyi gtso bo
NK024(ya)001:21392: dang / rgyun par rigs lnga bsgom pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21393: snying po 'di rnams dang 'khor gyi sngags rnams dang /
NK024(ya)001:21395: dbang ni bshad ma thag pa ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:21396: theg pa lam 'khyer nang gses dang bcas pa rnams ni /
NK024(ya)001:21398: theg pa yo ga'i theg pa'o //'jug sgo ting nge 'dzin gtso che ste /
NK024(ya)001:21400: mtshan med chos nyid gnyis so //
NK024(ya)001:21401: de'ang rdo rje rtse mo las //
NK024(ya)001:21402: dka' thub smyung gnas 'dir mi dgos //
NK024(ya)001:21403: khrus dang gtsang sbra 'dir mi dgos //
NK024(ya)001:21404: sangs rgyas thams cad sems dpa' che //
NK024(ya)001:21407: lta ba don dam pa'i bden pa mtshan nyid med
NK024(ya)001:21408: pa'i spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba rtogs pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21411: rigs lnga gsal ba grogs po'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:21412: dam pa rnam snang chen por rtogs //
NK024(ya)001:21414: bsrung ba'i dam tshig ni rab byung gi bslab pa gsum ldan du bsrung /
NK024(ya)001:21415: khyim pas rigs lnga'i dam tshig bsrung ste /
NK024(ya)001:21417: gal te rab tu byung ba na //
NK024(ya)001:21418: sdom pa gsum la gnas par bya //
NK024(ya)001:21419: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK024(ya)001:21421: khyim pa'i tshul du bya ba ni //
NK024(ya)001:21422: rigs lnga rgyal po rtag tu bsrung //
NK024(ya)001:21427: dam tshig pa ye shes sems dpa' grogs po'i tshul du dmigs nas mngon byang lnga sgom mo //
NK024(ya)001:21434: lha'i ting 'dzin dang ma bral bas phrin las bzhi'i
NK024(ya)001:21435: sgo nas rang gzhan gyi don gtso bor byed pa
NK024(ya)001:21437: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK024(ya)001:21438: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK024(ya)001:21439: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK024(ya)001:21440: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa mchog /
NK024(ya)001:21442: gsang rdzas kyang skabs su spyod de /
NK024(ya)001:21444: mgo bo thod pa'i dum bu dag /
NK024(ya)001:21445: ma mo rten pa'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:21446: bum pa khrag gis bka' ba yang //
NK024(ya)001:21447: dkyil 'khor gra bzhir bzhag par bya //
NK024(ya)001:21449: don dam pa'i ye shes rtogs pa'i chos sku //
NK024(ya)001:21451: de las shar ba sprul sku'o //
NK024(ya)001:21453: rigs lngar shar ba grogs po'i tshul //
NK024(ya)001:21454: dam pa rnam snang chen por rtogs //
NK024(ya)001:21455: yan lag dgu ldan stug po bkod //
NK024(ya)001:21457: gnas lha bya skad snyan ljon shing gi tshal rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du'o //
NK024(ya)001:21458: ston pa ni slob dpon chen po ku ma ti'o
NK024(ya)001:21459: //'khor slob ma ni rdo rje khyung grags rtsal la
NK024(ya)001:21460: sogs pa'o // dbang gi yo ga'i dbang drug cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK024(ya)001:21461: rgyu mtshan ni bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku che ba'i yon tan brjod pa'o //
NK024(ya)001:21462: dgos pa ni dbang de thob pas bkra shis shing rgyud la yon tan skye ba'o //
NK024(ya)001:21463: de nas dbang de mi nyams shing brtan pa'i phyir gdams ngag gsal gdab pa ni /
NK024(ya)001:21464: rang gi snying gi dkyil 'khor du dwangs ma chen
NK024(ya)001:21465: po lnga gnas pa ni rang bzhin gyi rigs lnga
NK024(ya)001:21466: dang ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gdod ma nas gnas
NK024(ya)001:21467: pa'o // de yang spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam zhig bsam /
NK024(ya)001:21469: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor nas thigs pa shar //
NK024(ya)001:21470: zhes pa thig le dkar po de yas mar babs
NK024(ya)001:21471: pas snying gi dkyil du dwangs ma rigs lngar gnas
NK024(ya)001:21472: pa la gnyis med du 'dres par bsam /
NK024(ya)001:21473: de don dam pa mtshan nyid med pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK024(ya)001:21474: rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar snang ba ni kun rdzob ye shes kyi snang ba /
NK024(ya)001:21475: de'i rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i ngang las blo
NK024(ya)001:21476: ma bcos par gnas pa dbyings chos nyid yin no
NK024(ya)001:21477: // zhes gsungs pa'i theg pa'i 'jug sgo mtshan bcas dang mtshan med kyi chos nyid gnyis dang /
NK024(ya)001:21478: rdo rje rtse mo'i don bzhin khrus dang gtsang sbra
NK024(ya)001:21479: dka' thub smyung gnas sogs la ma ltos par spyad
NK024(ya)001:21480: / lta ba mtshan nyid med pa'i spros pa'i mtha' brgyad dang bral ba /
NK024(ya)001:21481: tshul khrims ni rab byung gi bslab pa gsum dang /
NK024(ya)001:21482: khyim pas rigs lnga'i dam tshig bsrung /
NK024(ya)001:21483: sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni mngon byang lnga'i tshul gyis so //
NK024(ya)001:21484: spyod pa ni lha'i ting 'dzin gyi ngang nas phrin
NK024(ya)001:21485: las rnam bzhi'i sgo nas rang gzhan gyi don sgrub
NK024(ya)001:21486: pa'o //'bras bu don dam rtogs pa'i chos sku'i gdangs
NK024(ya)001:21488: longs sku las sprul sku rnams thob bo //
NK024(ya)001:21489: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer lnga pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi 'khrid tshul ni /
NK024(ya)001:21490: rang gi snying gi dkyil du dwangs ma kha dog
NK024(ya)001:21491: lnga ldan ni rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor
NK024(ya)001:21492: gdod ma nas gnas pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:21493: rang gi spyi bor thig le dkar po ril ma tsam zhig kyang gsal btab /
NK024(ya)001:21495: nam mkha'i dkyil nas thig pa shar //
NK024(ya)001:21496: zhes pa'i don spyi bo'i thig le dkar po de
NK024(ya)001:21497: yas nas mar babs pas snying gi dkyil du dwangs
NK024(ya)001:21498: ma rigs lngas gnas ba dang gnyis med du 'dres
NK024(ya)001:21499: par bsam la / don dam mtshan nyid med pa'i ngang la ci nus su mnyam par bzhag /
NK024(ya)001:21500: rjes thob ni rigs lnga rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar
NK024(ya)001:21501: snang ba ni kun rdzob ye shes kyi snang ba
NK024(ya)001:21502: de'i rang bzhin gnyis med kyi ngang la shes pa
NK024(ya)001:21503: ma bcos par bzhag pa dbyings kyi chos nyid yin
NK024(ya)001:21504: pas de ltar lam du 'khyer ro //
NK024(ya)001:21505: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer bzhi pa 'gag drug ni gzhung ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:21506: de dag gi rim pas yo ga rnal 'byor rgyud
NK024(ya)001:21507: kyi smin grol gyi lam rnams legs par grub pa'i
NK024(ya)001:21508: dam tshig khas blangs kyi don du 'di'i rjes zlos
NK024(ya)001:21509: mdzod / dam tshig bsdus te khang blang ba /
NK024(ya)001:21512: de'i dge ba bsngo ba sogs snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:21513: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer drug pa bkra shis ni /
NK024(ya)001:21515: me tog bkram la rol mo dang bcas pas /
NK024(ya)001:21516: rnam par snang mdzad ye shes dam pa mtsho chen ldan //
NK024(ya)001:21517: zla ba nya 'dra'i sku mnga' srid pa mtha' phyin pa //
NK024(ya)001:21518: dgongs pa mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis gang yin pa //
NK024(ya)001:21519: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:21520: mi 'khrugs rgyal po srid dang gti mug rnam sbyong ba //
NK024(ya)001:21521: dge ba mnyam med sems can don rdzogs rab ldan pa //
NK024(ya)001:21522: mgon po yon tan mtha' dag rdzogs pa'i bkra shis
NK024(ya)001:21523: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan rnams kyis brgyan byas
NK024(ya)001:21524: shing // yang dag 'byor ba'i sbyin pa sbyin mdzad mi bslu ba //
NK024(ya)001:21525: rin chen 'byung ldan zhes bya'i bkra shis bsam gtan dang ni ting 'dzin pha rol phyin gnas shing //
NK024(ya)001:21526: ye shes pad+ma'i steng bzhugs dpag med tshe ldan pa'o
NK024(ya)001:21527: //'od dpag med pa'i byin rlabs bkra shis sems can
NK024(ya)001:21528: don phyir las la thugs ni sbyor mdzad pa'i //'gro
NK024(ya)001:21529: ba thams cad 'ching bas bcings las sgrol mdzad pa
NK024(ya)001:21530: // thugs mchog don yod grub pa'i bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK024(ya)001:21531: ces brjod la me tog gtor /
NK024(ya)001:21533: de nas dkyil 'khor la mchod bstod dngos grub blangs /
NK024(ya)001:21537: zhes gsungs pa'i bla ma la yon dbul ba ni gtang rag man+dala gyis 'thus /
NK024(ya)001:21539: dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa rnams gsar du bsham pa'am zhal gsos te sngar bzhin bsang sbyang /
NK024(ya)001:21540: byin gyis brlabs te 'bul ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:21541: lha sta gon gyi skabs ltar gnas mchog 'di 'am gzhan dag tu //
NK024(ya)001:21542: lha sogs bdag gir ma byas pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21543: zhes sogs rol mo'i bar du phul la /
NK024(ya)001:21544: bstod pa yang sta gon ltar /
NK024(ya)001:21545: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK024(ya)001:21547: bstod par 'os pa thams cad la //
NK024(ya)001:21550: bcom ldan 'das bdag dang sems can thams cad kyi sgrib gnyis byang zhing tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:21551: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ma lus pa stsal du gsol /
NK024(ya)001:21552: zhes 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba btab /
NK024(ya)001:21554: gzhan yang sngags gzhung spyi ltar bcad lhug gi sgo nas nyes byas bshags te bzod par gsol /
NK024(ya)001:21555: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la dmigs te //
NK024(ya)001:21556: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK024(ya)001:21559: lan gsum gyi thal mo spyi bor bkod /
NK024(ya)001:21560: badz+ra mumh zhes se gol lag gnyis phyir bsnol du gtog pas /
NK024(ya)001:21561: rdul tshon dang bum nang gi ye shes pa rnams gshegs /
NK024(ya)001:21562: dam tshig pa bdag la bsdu /
NK024(ya)001:21563: rdo rje'i rtses dbang ldan gyi me ri nas dbus
NK024(ya)001:21564: kyi bar drud cing bsdus te thig shul kyang dabyi'o
NK024(ya)001:21565: // bdag bskyed rdor sems kyang dar cig mi dmigs par bsam la /
NK024(ya)001:21566: slar yang gzhan don du sgyu ma lta bu'i lha skur langs te /
NK024(ya)001:21572: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah
NK024(ya)001:21573: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa
NK024(ya)001:21575: de bzhin du w+aa ka badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa tsit+ta badz+ra sogs /
NK024(ya)001:21576: rigs lnga dang sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK024(ya)001:21581: zhes las kyi sems dpa' bzhis bsrung ngo //'di rnams nyang gter rdor dbyings kyi dgongs pa ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:21582: rtsa ba'i sa bcad nyer bdun pa bsngo ba ni /
NK024(ya)001:21584: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo bar bya'o /
NK024(ya)001:21585: zhes gsungs pas bsngo smon gyi rim pa dang /
NK024(ya)001:21587: nub mo zhi khro'i phrin gzhung tshogs bskang rnams kyang snga ma ltar ro //
NK024(ya)001:21589: rnal 'byor yo ga'i chu klung mtha' yas pa //
NK024(ya)001:21590: rdo rje dbyings kyi rgya mtshor rab 'dren pa'i //
NK024(ya)001:21591: legs bshad rin chen 'byung ba'i chu gter 'di //
NK024(ya)001:21592: rnam dpyod ma dros klung gi dpal las thon //'khor lo'i mgon po yongs 'dzin klu dbang tshogs //
NK024(ya)001:21593: bsten phyir gzhung lugs rgya mtsho mang mthong bas //
NK024(ya)001:21594: thar 'dod las stegs gru gzings 'di sbyar ba //
NK024(ya)001:21595: don mthun blo gsal tshogs kyis bzung bya'i gnas //
NK024(ya)001:21596: snga 'gyur bla med rgya mtsho'i klong chen por //
NK024(ya)001:21597: bya spyod rnal 'byor chu klung ro gcig tu //
NK024(ya)001:21598: gyur slad rnyog ma'i dri mar gyur pa kun //
NK024(ya)001:21599: rang gzhung ke ta ka yis dwangs par byas //
NK024(ya)001:21600: yo ga'i sgrub dkyil sa bon ches phra yang //
NK024(ya)001:21601: gsar rnyi nga bka' gter drod gsher gyis smin pas //
NK024(ya)001:21602: rig 'dzin yongs 'du'i ljon pa rgya che ba //
NK024(ya)001:21603: phan bde'i lo 'bras bzhad pa'i dga' ston ster //
NK024(ya)001:21604: rang gzhung yo ga'i shing rta bzang po la //
NK024(ya)001:21605: nyang gter 'khor lo'i 'phrul sbyar gzhan phan blos //
NK024(ya)001:21606: mtha' yas rin chen du ma'i legs bshad kyis //
NK024(ya)001:21607: rab brgyan rnam mkhyen bgrod pa'i ngal 'tsho'i stegs //'di lta'i ring srol dri med ma bzung bar //
NK024(ya)001:21608: blos byas rang bzo'i 'khyog lam ngal bsten yang //
NK024(ya)001:21609: gol sa'i g.yang la rang gzhan kun lhung bas //
NK024(ya)001:21610: dri med rgyud sde'i lam bzang 'di bsten cig /
NK024(ya)001:21611: ces bya ba ni bar skabs kyi tshigs su bcad pa'o //
